NK022(za)001:0: 'dus pa chen po mdo'i sgrub khrigs bzhin dbang byang
NK022(za)001:1: lag len mkhas pa glan bsod nams mgon gyis mdzad
NK022(za)001:3: gsang ba'i bdag po phyag na rdo rje la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK022(za)001:4: 'dus pa chen po mdo'i dkyil 'khor gyi dbang gi las khrigs la don gsum ste /
NK022(za)001:5: phun sum tshogs pa lnga'am drug gis bsgrub pa'i gzhi bzungs ba dang /
NK022(za)001:6: bsnyen bsgrub bzhi'i las kyi gzhung bsrangs ba dang /
NK022(za)001:7: rjes la don brgyad kyis mjug bsdu ba'o //
NK022(za)001:15: de la dang po ston pa ni /
NK022(za)001:19: slob dpon mtshan nyid brtag pa ni /
NK022(za)001:20: ye shes snying po khyod nyon cig /
NK022(za)001:21: ces pa la sogs pa dang /
NK022(za)001:22: yang rnam par snang mdzad thig le dbang gi tan tra las /
NK022(za)001:23: de dang mtshungs par ldan pa dang //
NK022(za)001:24: brtan zhing dus la blo gros ldan //
NK022(za)001:25: ces pa la sogs pa gsungs pa dang /
NK022(za)001:27: ston pa mdzod ldan chu bo rdzogs //
NK022(za)001:28: gnyer ldan rgyud dang las la mkhas //
NK022(za)001:29: man ngag drod tshad brgyad 'chang ba //
NK022(za)001:30: zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs so //
NK022(za)001:32: slob dpon nyid dang dgongs pa khyad par med pa'o //
NK022(za)001:35: gzhung kun nas bshad pa'i las bzhi po gang du dgos pa'i skabs kyi mtshan nyid dang ldan pa'o //
NK022(za)001:36: gnas phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK022(za)001:39: sde dpung chen pos mi tshugs shing //
NK022(za)001:40: sa dang bar snang shis pa dang //
NK022(za)001:41: lo rgyus rnam gnyis ldan pa dang //
NK022(za)001:42: yid 'ong sa btsal rgyas par bya //
NK022(za)001:45: zur brgyad la sogs rtse mngas dang //
NK022(za)001:46: zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs pas /
NK022(za)001:48: gnas kyi gzhi brtag pa dang /
NK022(za)001:49: mtshams kyi dgra brtag pa dang /
NK022(za)001:50: gnas kyi ri'am phyogs brtag pa'o //
NK022(za)001:51: de yang gtsug lag gi lha bzhi yod cing /
NK022(za)001:52: lha chos mi chos kyi bkra shis pa'i gnas btsal la /
NK022(za)001:53: ngan pa dor la bzang po blang ste /
NK022(za)001:54: de yang khyad par du gang zag khyad par can
NK022(za)001:55: gyi zhabs kyis bcag pa byin che ba'i gnas dang
NK022(za)001:56: / grub pa thob pa bkra shis pa'i gnas dang /
NK022(za)001:58: yid dang 'thad cing rnal 'byor pa gtso 'khor dang
NK022(za)001:59: bcas pa nyams dga' ba'i gnas su sgrub pa po
NK022(za)001:60: rnams 'dus la / der khang pa sum rim du byas te /
NK022(za)001:61: de nyid du steng brgyan dang /
NK022(za)001:63: gzhan yang mchod pa'i sprin sna tshogs kyis bstibs par bya'o //
NK022(za)001:65: 'khor khang phyi nang bar ldan pa //
NK022(za)001:66: rin chen byug pas bsrung ba dang //
NK022(za)001:67: rin chen spras pas gzhal yas khang //
NK022(za)001:71: ston pa mchod brtson rtogs pa gsal //
NK022(za)001:72: ces pa la sogs gsungs pas /
NK022(za)001:73: skyon drug spang shing yon tan drug dang ldan pa'i 'khor karma las mkhan /
NK022(za)001:75: las kyi khrigs la mkhas pa dang /
NK022(za)001:80: rdul phyag skyes bu la sogs pa'o //
NK022(za)001:82: bsgrub dang sgom la dga' ba dang zhes so //
NK022(za)001:83: yo byad phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK022(za)001:84: yo byad gda' ba kun bsdus nas zhes pa /
NK022(za)001:85: bkod pa sku'i rten tsa ka li phyi nang gi dang /
NK022(za)001:86: lugs sku dang thod pa la sogs pa'o //
NK022(za)001:87: bris pa gsung gi rten yi ge dang /
NK022(za)001:88: thugs kyi rten phyag mtshan rdo rje 'khor lo la sogs pa'o //
NK022(za)001:95: de dag ni bsgrub pa rdzas kyi yo byad do //
NK022(za)001:96: 'tsho ba zas kyi yo byad sha mar la sogs
NK022(za)001:97: pa kun zhag grangs kyi ldab thang du bsham pa
NK022(za)001:98: dang / mnyes pa lha'i yo byad ni /
NK022(za)001:100: thun mong gi lnga la sogs pa'o //
NK022(za)001:101: rkyen bzlog dgos pa'i yo byad ni /
NK022(za)001:102: dgra rkyen bzlog pa'i go mtshon dang //
NK022(za)001:103: bgegs bzlog pa'i phur bu dang //
NK022(za)001:106: nad bzlog pa'i sman pa sman dang bcas pa'o //
NK022(za)001:107: de rnams la'ang tha mal gyi rnam par skad cig kyang mi lta bar /
NK022(za)001:108: dngos grub chen po'i yo byad du lta'o //
NK022(za)001:110: gos brgyan bza' btung gsang ba dang //
NK022(za)001:111: sgrub pa'i yo byad lnga rnams dang //
NK022(za)001:112: dkyil 'khor yo byad mchod pa'i rdzas //
NK022(za)001:113: zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs so //
NK022(za)001:114: lnga pa dus phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK022(za)001:115: bsgrub pa gzung ba'i dus dang /
NK022(za)001:117: smin par thob pa dbang du bsgrub pa'i dus so //
NK022(za)001:119: gong ma rnams 'dzom pa'i dus te /
NK022(za)001:122: tshes grangs yar gyi brgyad la rtsam zhes pa'i don no //
NK022(za)001:123: gnyis pa ni bsnyen pa rdzogs nas /
NK022(za)001:124: lhag pa'i sems bskyed pa'i dus su /
NK022(za)001:127: dang po sems bskyed 'jug dus su //
NK022(za)001:128: rdzas kyi dbang bcu rdzogs par sbyin ces so //
NK022(za)001:130: zhag ni sum cu phrag drug gam zhes pa lags pa'o //
NK022(za)001:134: gnyis pa bsnyen bsgrub bzhis gzhung bsrang ba ni /
NK022(za)001:136: bsnyen pa dang ni nye bsnyen po //
NK022(za)001:137: bsgrub pa dang ni bsgrub chen po //
NK022(za)001:139: bsgrub pa'i shoms 'bras bu dang 'brel pa ni bsnyen pa ste /
NK022(za)001:140: dbang thob pa non pa'i rdo rje slob dpon la /
NK022(za)001:141: rang nyid dbang gang zhu ba'i zhu ba phul la /
NK022(za)001:143: slob dpon gyis bsnyen pa byas nas sta gon yan chad bsnyen pa /
NK022(za)001:144: zhag du byed pa'i phyed nye bsnyen /
NK022(za)001:145: zhag du byed pa'i nub tha ma ma rtogs kha pa'i dbang kadu tshogs bzhi tshogs sam /
NK022(za)001:146: drug tshogs su byed pa bsgrub pa /
NK022(za)001:147: nub tha ma la rtags dang mtshan ma bzang po
NK022(za)001:148: byung nas dngos grub len kha ma bsgrub pa chen
NK022(za)001:149: po'o // de ltar don bzhi las /
NK022(za)001:150: bsnyen pa ni gnas mtshan nyid dang ldan par sngon 'gro'i chos rnams rdzogs par byas la /
NK022(za)001:151: lta ba dbyings ye shes dbyer med rtogs pa'i ngang las /
NK022(za)001:152: sgom pa don dang yi ge'i rjes su 'jug pa /
NK022(za)001:153: de la rim cig char gnyis las /
NK022(za)001:154: dbang po rab 'bring tha ma gsum gyis 'jug cing bgrod de /
NK022(za)001:155: don du na yi dam lha la brtan pa ma thob kyi bar du bsnyen pa bskyal lo //
NK022(za)001:156: de ni smin par slob pa'i dbang du'o //
NK022(za)001:157: mos slob ltar du gnyis las /
NK022(za)001:158: sngon du bya ba'i bsnyen pa dang /
NK022(za)001:159: dkyil 'khor gyi las kyi rim pa'o //
NK022(za)001:161: slob dpon rgyal po dbang gi chu bo rdzogs shing /
NK022(za)001:163: bka' dang rgyu 'bras kyi chos la ma rmongs par mkhyen pa'i bla ma la zhu phul la /
NK022(za)001:164: de bar du bla mas bum pa bcas te /
NK022(za)001:168: rang gang mos kyi lha la grangs kyi bsnyen pa ci rigs par bskyal lo //
NK022(za)001:169: de bar du slob bus mdzad byang bzhin du gang
NK022(za)001:170: dgos pa'i yo byad rnams zhal nas byung ba bzhin
NK022(za)001:171: bsag go // gnyis pa las kyi rim pa la gnyis te /
NK022(za)001:172: bsnyen bsgrub kyi skabs su dkyil 'khor gyi bya ba'i rim pa dang /
NK022(za)001:173: bsgrub pa chen po'i skabs su dngos grub thob nas dbang gi las rim mo //
NK022(za)001:176: sa gzhi bsnyam dang tshang thig dang //
NK022(za)001:177: tshon dang bri ba'i rnam pa dang //
NK022(za)001:178: rab gnas sbyin sreg 'jug pa dang //
NK022(za)001:179: yon tan rnam bcu rgyas bshad bya //
NK022(za)001:180: zhes bsnyen bsgrub kyi skabs su gsungs pa dang /
NK022(za)001:182: dang po sa gzhi yongs su bzung //
NK022(za)001:183: gnyis pa sta gon la gnas te //
NK022(za)001:184: nub gsum pa la 'jug par bya //
NK022(za)001:187: gzhi dang rang mtshan slang dbang dang //
NK022(za)001:188: sbyang sbyin srung dang bzung ba ni //
NK022(za)001:189: dang po'i nying lag nyid du bshad //
NK022(za)001:190: ces pa la sogs pa mang zhig gsungs kyang /
NK022(za)001:192: zhag bcu gcig gi dbang du /
NK022(za)001:193: nub dang po'i cho ga ni /
NK022(za)001:195: spyi dbang chen po'i dbang bskur ba'i //
NK022(za)001:196: dang po phun sum tshogs ldan nas //
NK022(za)001:197: tshad phyin rab 'byams slob dpon gyis //
NK022(za)001:198: snod dang ldan pa'i 'khor bsdus nas //
NK022(za)001:199: gzhung dang mthun pa'i gnas dag tu //
NK022(za)001:200: sa chog sogs byas gnas la ldan //
NK022(za)001:201: dgos pa tshang ba'i yo byad rdzogs //
NK022(za)001:203: thog ma ba'i cho ga la don brgyad kyis ston pa ni /
NK022(za)001:204: dang po gzhi brtag pa ni don bzhis bstan te /
NK022(za)001:205: dang po nam mkha' brtag pa ni /
NK022(za)001:206: man ngag rdo rje las rim las /
NK022(za)001:207: zur brgyad la sogs rtse mngas dang //
NK022(za)001:209: gnyis pa gnas kyi ri brtag pa ni /
NK022(za)001:210: brums chags shing lhun stug pa /
NK022(za)001:211: ri'i dbyibs rin po che brtsegs pa ltar 'dug pa'o /
NK022(za)001:218: mtshams kyi dgra bzhi la sogs med pa ni sa gzhi brtag pa zhes bya'o //
NK022(za)001:219: gnyis pa sa rang gi mtshan nyid brtag pa ni /
NK022(za)001:223: thang kar sog le lta bu dang /
NK022(za)001:226: bkra shis rtsa dang me tog shing //
NK022(za)001:227: zhes pa la sogs pa bzang po'i mtshan nyid dang ldan pa der sgrub po rnams 'dus la /
NK022(za)001:228: las tshogs dge ba'i dpung bskyed pa la kun gyis 'bad do //
NK022(za)001:229: gsum pa sa bslang ba ni /
NK022(za)001:230: mngon pa mi la bslang ba dang /
NK022(za)001:231: mi mngon ces pa mi ma yin pa la bslang ba'o //
NK022(za)001:234: blon po lta bu gang yang rung ba pa'i bdag
NK022(za)001:235: po gang yin pa la rin bcal la sa rgyas
NK022(za)001:236: gdab bo // gnyis pa la bde bar gshegs pa la bslang ba dang /
NK022(za)001:237: sa yi lha mo la bslang ba'o //
NK022(za)001:239: gnas der man+dala khru gang ba zhig byas la /
NK022(za)001:241: tsan+dana gyi chus chag chag btab ste /
NK022(za)001:242: de'i steng du mchod pa lnga dang /
NK022(za)001:244: gser skyems la sogs pa bshams la /
NK022(za)001:245: sngags mkhan nyid chas gos dkar po dang ldan par stan bde ba la 'dug ste /
NK022(za)001:246: rnam par mi rtog pa'i ngang las big nan ta kri'i sngags brjod cing /
NK022(za)001:247: rang khro bo bdud rtsi 'khyil par bskyed la mchod pa lnga spyi dang mthun par brlab /
NK022(za)001:248: gtor ma bdud rtsi thal sbyor gyis ye shes kyi bdud rtsir brlab /
NK022(za)001:249: gser skyems brtag pa rnam gsum gyis brlabs la /
NK022(za)001:250: zhi ba thung lugs su 'dzab yan chad bya /
NK022(za)001:251: de nas sa gzhi ye nas sangs rgyas spyan gyi rang bzhin yin pa de la /
NK022(za)001:252: rnal 'byor rang nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin gyis kyang de bzhin du bsgom ste /
NK022(za)001:253: ngag tu pad+ma sur+ya man+dala zhes brjod pas sa nyid gser gyi sa gzhir bsam pa ni /
NK022(za)001:255: gnyis pa sa'i lha mo la bslang ba ni /
NK022(za)001:256: de'i steng du lam ser po las /
NK022(za)001:258: sa'i lha mo sangs rgyas spyan sku mdog ser mo /
NK022(za)001:260: phag gi khri la bzhugs pa /
NK022(za)001:261: g.yas pa sa gnon gyi phyag rgya la /
NK022(za)001:262: g.yon pa rat+na'i bum pa bsnams pa /
NK022(za)001:263: 'ja' tshon sna lnga'i 'od dang ldan par bsgoms la /
NK022(za)001:264: rnam snang gis dbu rgyan cing sku gsung thugs su byin gyis brlabs te /
NK022(za)001:265: sa man dzas snyan gsan phab la /
NK022(za)001:266: sa yi lha mo spyan drangs te rdo rje dril bu thogs la /
NK022(za)001:267: don dam gser gyi sa la mnga' mdzad pa //
NK022(za)001:274: lha mo bzhi bsnol gyis mchod /
NK022(za)001:275: de nas 'dod pa'i don du slar gsol te /
NK022(za)001:276: skyob pa sangs rgyas zhes pa'i tshig brjod la /
NK022(za)001:277: lag pa g.yas pa tri shul la'i phyag rgya bcas la sa la gtug cing /
NK022(za)001:278: a hi b+ha ba ye swa h+aa zhes brjod pas /
NK022(za)001:279: sa yi lha mo nyid dpang po'i tshul du sku
NK022(za)001:280: lte ba yan chad 'thon nas bzhugs par bsam mo
NK022(za)001:281: // de nas mgron spyan drangs pa ni /
NK022(za)001:283: 'dzam gling spyir gnas mthu chen dbang bsgyur ma //
NK022(za)001:284: zhes pa la sogs pa dang /
NK022(za)001:285: bsgrub pa gang byed kyi yul phyogs na yod pa'i bdud dang /
NK022(za)001:287: sa bdag la sogs pa spyan drang pa /
NK022(za)001:288: yul rigs 'di'i sa la mnga' mdzad pa /
NK022(za)001:289: zhes pa la sogs pa brjod pas mdun du byon par bsam la /
NK022(za)001:290: a rga gtor ma la bran te /
NK022(za)001:291: h'u rgyas par bshams pa'i mchod sbyin gtor ma 'di /
NK022(za)001:293: dam rdzas bdud rtsi'i mchod pa bzhes su gsol //
NK022(za)001:294: zhes brjod la gtor ma dang /
NK022(za)001:295: dkar gsum mngar gsum rang gi sngags dang /
NK022(za)001:296: 'od zer rnam rgyal gyi sngags dang phyag rgyas byin la gang bcol nyan par bsam /
NK022(za)001:297: de nas phrin las bcol ba ni /
NK022(za)001:298: ri rab chen po'i gling bzhi 'bar /
NK022(za)001:300: de nas sa yi bdag po de rnams rang rang gi gnas su bskyod pa'i phyir /
NK022(za)001:302: h'u lcags ri gser ri dngul gyi ri //
NK022(za)001:303: zhes pa la sogs pa'i tshig brjod pa /
NK022(za)001:304: nam mkha' mdzod kyi sngags dang phyag rgyas dbul /
NK022(za)001:305: de nas gser skyems lhag ma phyogs kun tu gtor zhing /
NK022(za)001:306: yul gyi gdon bgegs la gnod pa ma byed cig ces bka' basgo'o //
NK022(za)001:307: de nas gtor ma'i smon lam gdab ste /
NK022(za)001:308: na mo dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK022(za)001:309: zhes pa la sogs pa brjod la /
NK022(za)001:310: sa bdag kun mnyes nas gzhan du gshegs par bsam /
NK022(za)001:311: de nas sa yi lha mo dge ba'i dpang por bzhag pa la gzhol ba ni /
NK022(za)001:312: sngon 'das pa'i dus su sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das zhes pa la sogs nas /
NK022(za)001:313: a ho zhes pa'i bar du brjod la /
NK022(za)001:314: mdzub mo gnyis smin mtshams su snol te /
NK022(za)001:315: b+he a kra ma ya zhes pa'i sngags brjod pas lha mo nam mkha' la brteg nas /
NK022(za)001:316: dpang po la bzhugs su gsol bar bsgom mo //
NK022(za)001:317: de nas badz+ra sa ma ya h+aum dza /
NK022(za)001:318: zhes brjod nas dpang po'i lha rnams spyan drang /
NK022(za)001:319: h'u bzhes dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyi byin bsdus nas bdag la thim pas /
NK022(za)001:320: bdag gi lus 'od du gyur pa las /
NK022(za)001:321: h'u badz+ra d+h+rika zhes brjod pas /
NK022(za)001:322: rang nyid zhe sda nga rdo rje sku mdog mthing nag g.yas pa rdo rje /
NK022(za)001:323: g.yon pa sdigs mdzub gdengs pa /
NK022(za)001:325: sdang mig bgegs la lta ba /
NK022(za)001:326: thugs kha dang zhabs mthil gnyis la gom pa'i stabs
NK022(za)001:327: bgrod pas rdo rje rgya gram 'bar bar bsams la
NK022(za)001:328: / rdo rje gsor zhing mi 'gro ba'i bgegs rnams la song zhig par bka' bsgo ba ni /
NK022(za)001:329: dkon mchog gsum gyi bka' bden pa dang /
NK022(za)001:330: zhes pa la sogs pa dang /
NK022(za)001:331: sum b+ha ni'i sngags bzlas shing /
NK022(za)001:332: nyungs dkar gtor bas 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad khro bo'i sprul pas gang nas /
NK022(za)001:336: spyan la ye shes kyi me byung bas /
NK022(za)001:337: me'i gur du gyur par bsgom /
NK022(za)001:338: de nas rang gi gnas su brjid kyis 'dug la
NK022(za)001:339: thal mo sbyar ba lha mo'i mdun du brtugs la
NK022(za)001:340: / ji ltar che mchog rdo rje yi //
NK022(za)001:341: zhes pa la sogs pa dang /
NK022(za)001:342: rat+na pa sham si ti ku ru'i sngags lan gsum brjod cing /
NK022(za)001:343: phyag rgya sa la lan gsum bsnun pas /
NK022(za)001:344: sa yi lha mo 'dzum pa'i mdangs dang bcas nas sa gzhi la thim pas /
NK022(za)001:345: sa gzhi ye shes lnga'i ngo bo rin po che sna tshogs pa'i ngo bor gyur par bsam /
NK022(za)001:346: de yan chad ni sa bslangs pa'i cho ga'o //
NK022(za)001:347: sa dbang du bya ba ni /
NK022(za)001:348: zangs sam shing dmar po la phur pa rtse mo zla gam pa zhig byas la /
NK022(za)001:349: bdag gi thugs kha'i h'u las pad+ma ki la ya'i sngags brjod pas /
NK022(za)001:350: khro bo stod zhal gcig phyag bzhi pa /
NK022(za)001:351: smad phur pa zla gam du 'dug pa sku mdog dmar po /
NK022(za)001:352: g.yas g.yon dang po pad+ma dang zhags pa /
NK022(za)001:353: tha ma gnyis phur pa 'dril ba zhig byung nas /
NK022(za)001:355: sku gsung thugs su byin gyis brlabs te /
NK022(za)001:356: pad+ma dbang gi khro mchog chags pa'i sku //
NK022(za)001:358: pad+ma ki la ya'i sngags brjod de /
NK022(za)001:359: phur pa dkyil 'khor dbus su btab pas /
NK022(za)001:360: de las 'od zer dmar po 'phros pas /
NK022(za)001:362: sa gzhi bdag gi dbang du 'dus par bsam mo //
NK022(za)001:363: sa sbyang ba la bzhi ste /
NK022(za)001:364: las dang bya bas sbyang ba dang /
NK022(za)001:366: sngags dang phyag rgyas sbyang ba dang /
NK022(za)001:368: dang po ni sa bdag lto 'phye'i dus tshod ma nor bar byas la /
NK022(za)001:369: khru gru bzhi pa brkos la brtag ste /
NK022(za)001:372: dang po ni sa ngan pa sa'i ro la sogs pa byung na spang la /
NK022(za)001:373: bzang po snum zhing kha dog rin po cher gsal
NK022(za)001:374: ba sa'i rtsigs ma med cing thog ma bas lhag
NK022(za)001:376: sa sas brtag pa ste lhag na bzang bar blang bya'o //
NK022(za)001:377: sa chu yis brtag pa ni /
NK022(za)001:378: sa brkos pa'i nang du chu blug ste /
NK022(za)001:379: las mkhan nyid yi ge brgya pa bgrang zhing /
NK022(za)001:380: phar la gom pa lnga bcu phyin /
NK022(za)001:381: tshur la lnga bcu yongs la /
NK022(za)001:382: chu bri tshabs che zhing skams na ngan pas /
NK022(za)001:383: gzhan du 'apho'am zhi ba'i sbyin sreg gis sbyang bar bya'o //
NK022(za)001:384: bri tshabs chung mtshan nyid bzang na /
NK022(za)001:385: lnga tshar nyi shu rtsa lnga'i rdzas bsogs te rdza so btang ba gcig gi nang du blugs la /
NK022(za)001:386: sa brkos pa de'i nang du bcug ste /
NK022(za)001:387: de rjes a las zla ba'i dkyil 'khor de'i steng du tra las rin po che'i mchod sdong la /
NK022(za)001:388: rang ji ltar 'dod pa'i dgos 'dod 'byung bar bsam ste /
NK022(za)001:389: g.yam pas kha bcad la 'this par brdigs la bzhag go //
NK022(za)001:390: de nas las mkhan rnams dkyil 'khor gcig tu bzhugs te /
NK022(za)001:391: dkyil 'khor gyi tshad rgyas 'bring bsdus pa la sogs mang du smos kyang /
NK022(za)001:392: rgya rab tshad 'dom gang la dpangs khru gang bar brtsig go //
NK022(za)001:393: de la 'og ma yengs brtag pa ni /
NK022(za)001:395: 'bru lnga spos lnga rin chen lnga //
NK022(za)001:396: snying po lnga dang sman lnga dang //
NK022(za)001:397: bdud rtsi lnga ni rab bsnyams la //
NK022(za)001:398: zhes sa sum cu po de cha bsnyams la /
NK022(za)001:399: ba yi rnam lnga sbyar ba'i mde gus mnyam zhing /
NK022(za)001:400: 'thug srab glang ko tsam du byugs te /
NK022(za)001:401: me long gi ngos ltar ter teng bar byas la bzhag pa ni las dang bya bas sbyang ba'o //
NK022(za)001:403: sa'i mtshan nyid bzang ngan ji ltar 'dug kyang /
NK022(za)001:404: rdo rje slob dpon gyiis me lha spyan drangs pa yan chad byas la /
NK022(za)001:405: las mkhan gyis zhi ba'i sbyin sreg skabs 'dir rgyas par gtang ngo //
NK022(za)001:406: sngags dang phyag rgyas sbyang ba ni /
NK022(za)001:407: bdag nyid khro bor gsal ba'i g.yas kyi sor mo lnga la nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor re bsam /
NK022(za)001:408: de'i steng du h'u re bsams te /
NK022(za)001:409: de 'phros 'dus pa las rdo rje rtse lnga par gyur par bsam ste /
NK022(za)001:410: badz+ra kro ta'i sngags lan gsum brjod cing pho brang ngam sa la lan gsum brdabs pas /
NK022(za)001:411: rdo rje dang yi ge'i 'od kyis sa'i nyes skyon
NK022(za)001:412: thams cad dag nas sa gzhi ye shes rang snang
NK022(za)001:413: du bsam pa ni sngags dang phyag rgyas sbyangs ba'o
NK022(za)001:414: // ting nge 'dzin gyis sbyang ba la gnyis las /
NK022(za)001:415: mtshan med kyis sbyang ba ni /
NK022(za)001:416: ma h+aa shu dz+nya ta'i sngags brjod pas /
NK022(za)001:417: chos thams cad sems nyid du rnam par dag pas
NK022(za)001:418: sa dang sar 'dzin pa thams cad chos nyid don
NK022(za)001:419: dam skye ba med pa stong pa nyid du sbyang
NK022(za)001:420: ngo // mtshan bcas kyis sbyang ba ni /
NK022(za)001:421: skad cig ma las rang gi rig pa h'u cig tu gyur par bsam /
NK022(za)001:423: e ya ba su la ra zhes 'phros 'dus pa las 'byung ba dbang chen gyi dkyil 'khor bskyed /
NK022(za)001:424: b+h+ru gyi 'phro 'du las b+h+ru bi sha'i sngags kyis
NK022(za)001:425: 'dus pa chen po'i dkyil 'khor gdan dang bcas par
NK022(za)001:426: sems pa ni mtshan bcas lha'i ting nge 'dzin sa
NK022(za)001:427: dang sar 'dzin gyis rtog pa thams cad kun rdzob
NK022(za)001:429: de yan chad ni sa sbyang ba'i cho ga'o //
NK022(za)001:430: yan lag dang rtsa ba gnyis ka'i dkyil 'khor gyi cho ga'o //
NK022(za)001:431: drug pa sa byin gyis brlab pa dang /
NK022(za)001:433: 'og tu dkyil 'khor sta gon la gnas pa'i skabs su bya'o //
NK022(za)001:434: brgyad pa sa gzhi bzung ba ni /
NK022(za)001:435: de'i nub mo sgrub pa po rnams 'dus la cho
NK022(za)001:436: ga zab mo dbang gi sngon du 'gro ba'i las
NK022(za)001:437: la 'bad do // de yang cha rkyen bsdu zhing
NK022(za)001:438: slob ma rnams nang du 'dus la gleng gzhi bshad
NK022(za)001:439: la 'bad do // / gags brgyad bshad la thugs dam bskang //
NK022(za)001:442: don bzhi po 'di dag lag len khrigs su sbyar na /
NK022(za)001:443: thog ma cha rkyen bsdu ba ni /
NK022(za)001:444: mchod pa'i cha rkyen phyi nang gsang ba'i rdzas khyad par can dang /
NK022(za)001:449: thugs rje'i rgyun thag phur bu dang /
NK022(za)001:452: rgyal mtshan dang do shal rdzas rnams bsdus te gcad /
NK022(za)001:454: de rnams gzhung las ji ltar byung ba bzhin bsham /
NK022(za)001:455: dbang gi rdzas ni bum pa lnga dang /
NK022(za)001:457: phyi nang gsang ba'i rdzas khyad par can rnams 'tshogs par bsogs la /
NK022(za)001:458: thugs dam bskang ba'i cho ga bya ste /
NK022(za)001:459: phyi 'jig rten pa 'khor dang bcas pa'i thugs dam bskang ba ni /
NK022(za)001:460: dar phyar rol mo'i sgra sbyar la //
NK022(za)001:461: byin gyis brlabs la gser skyems rgyas par btang /
NK022(za)001:462: khyad par du gnas so gzhi bdag la gser skyems dang gtor ma byin la gnas so zhu /
NK022(za)001:463: gtsang rigs kyi mgon po bdun cu rtsa gnyis la cha gsum btang la thugs dam bskang /
NK022(za)001:465: gzhan yang 'jig rten gyi lha 'dre thams cad la phud gtor byin la /
NK022(za)001:466: bsgrub pa chen po 'di dbu bzung nas mjug ma
NK022(za)001:467: thon gyi bar la bar chod kyi sbyor ba zhi
NK022(za)001:469: khyad par du mgon po dang /
NK022(za)001:470: lha mo la sdongs grogs gyis shig par bka' bsko /
NK022(za)001:471: dkon mchog gsum la gsol ba drag tu gdab /
NK022(za)001:472: de nas nang gi thugs dam bskang ba ni /
NK022(za)001:473: cha gsum gyi dri chab khyer la tshogs las bya /
NK022(za)001:474: mchod pa mdos kyi dkyil 'khor bzhengs la /
NK022(za)001:475: phyi cha mthun sprul pa'i ma mo gzhung bzhin mchod la bar chod srungs shig par thugs dam bskul /
NK022(za)001:476: nang ting nge 'dzin gyis bskyed pa'i ma mo yig
NK022(za)001:477: 'bru'i sgo nas ting nge 'dzin gyis dkyil 'khor bskyed
NK022(za)001:478: la / ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor spyan drang /
NK022(za)001:479: bstims la mchod bstod 'dod pa'i don la gsol ba btab /
NK022(za)001:480: gsang ba thig le'i ma mo gsang ba tsan d+ha li'i man ngag rtsa rlung bcu bdun /
NK022(za)001:481: rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i ma mo mkha' klong gnyis med du la zla /
NK022(za)001:482: srungs ma thugs dam can la phud gtor byin la bar chod srungs shiig par bka' bsgo /
NK022(za)001:483: phur pa drug skor gyis dam sri'i mgo brdung /
NK022(za)001:486: ma 'dres pa bsre ba cho ga na ji ltar yod pa bzhin rgyas par bya /
NK022(za)001:487: 'dres pa dang zab cing rgya che ba'i chos bshad de /
NK022(za)001:488: de yang 'o skol 'khor ba khrag gi rgya mtsho lta bu'i nang na /
NK022(za)001:489: sdug bsngal gyi rba klong dpag tu med pa la longs spyod cing /
NK022(za)001:490: 'phags pa'i zhal nyi zer tsam yang ma mthong /
NK022(za)001:491: 'dod yon la mngon par chags pa ni lan tsha'i chu dang 'dra /
NK022(za)001:492: ci byas sdug bsngal la spyod pa ni rgya mtsho'i gzan dang 'dra /
NK022(za)001:493: zhen bya ma yin pa la mngon par zhen pa ni gshang pa'i srin bu dang 'dra /
NK022(za)001:494: de ltar 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal gyi rang bzhin lags pas /
NK022(za)001:495: 'khor ba las thar bar byed pa shin tu gal che lags so //
NK022(za)001:496: 'khor ba las thar bar byed pa la yang dag
NK022(za)001:497: par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyis chos kyi sgo mo
NK022(za)001:498: dpag tu med pa cig gsungs /
NK022(za)001:499: de la bla ma chos dang ldan pa'i skyes bu
NK022(za)001:500: dam pa rnams kyis ston chos grangs dang grangs kyis
NK022(za)001:501: gsungs kyang / smin par byed pa dbang gi lam
NK022(za)001:502: dang grol bar byed pa bskyed rdzogs kyi lam gnyis
NK022(za)001:504: de las 'dir smin par byed pa dbang gi lam yin te /
NK022(za)001:506: dper na bu tsha med pa'i khyims //
NK022(za)001:507: shi ba tsam gyis stongs par 'gyur //
NK022(za)001:508: de bzhin dbang dang bral na yang //
NK022(za)001:510: ces pas dper na bu tsha med pa'i khyim de
NK022(za)001:511: shi ba tsam gyis rabs chad nas stongs pa ltar
NK022(za)001:512: / skyes bu ji ltar yon tan che yang dbang
NK022(za)001:513: dang dam tshig dang bral na 'bras bu rgyun chad
NK022(za)001:515: des na zab mo dbang gis rgyud smin par bya ba gal che'o //
NK022(za)001:516: de yang dal ba dang 'byor pa 'gro ba mi yi lus ni thob /
NK022(za)001:517: 'dzam bu'i gling las yag sar ni skyes /
NK022(za)001:519: dbang po la ni lhag chad med /
NK022(za)001:520: dam pa'i chos dang phrad nas dbang rin po che
NK022(za)001:521: 'di lta bu la longs spyad du yod pa ni
NK022(za)001:522: rang gi pho sgo mo sgo'am mkhar che'am rkyen dbang
NK022(za)001:523: las grub pa ma yin te /
NK022(za)001:524: bla ma dkon mchog gi sku drin dang rang gi
NK022(za)001:525: bsod nams dpag tu med pa'i mthu las grub pa
NK022(za)001:526: yin pas dga' ba dang spro ba sang gyis /
NK022(za)001:527: thugs la gzengs stod par yang ba gyis shig /
NK022(za)001:528: mos pa dang gus pa'i dpung rkyen nges shes kyi rgyal mtshan gzugs 'tshal lo //
NK022(za)001:529: de yang dbang zab mo 'di yang 'brel pa bzhi dang ldan 'tshal ba lags te /
NK022(za)001:533: phyag bzhes byin brlabs dang 'brel te mkhas grub gong ma rnams kyis las grags pa rnams /
NK022(za)001:534: gleng gzhi zhes su rnam par bshad /
NK022(za)001:536: de la rgyud rgyal grags pa'i gleng gzhi ni /
NK022(za)001:537: ston pa 'das nas lo nyer brgyad lon pa'i dus su /
NK022(za)001:538: rgyal po dza'i khang thog tu po ti dang glegs bam gyi char babs pa'i lo rgyus /
NK022(za)001:539: gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa ji ltar byung ba'i
NK022(za)001:540: tshul gdul bya la grags lugs kyi gleng gzhi bshad
NK022(za)001:541: pas / skal ldan rjes 'jug gi tshogs rnams yid
NK022(za)001:542: ches te dkyil 'khor chen po 'di'i don ji ltar
NK022(za)001:544: gdams ngag phyag bzhes dang 'brel te /
NK022(za)001:545: mkhas pa gong ma rnams kyis mdzad pa'i las tho khyad par can kun dang 'brel pa'o //
NK022(za)001:546: phyag bzhes byin brlabs dang 'brel te /
NK022(za)001:547: grub thob kyi bka' brgyud rin po che gangs kyi
NK022(za)001:548: thigs pa lta bu gcig nas gcig tu brgyud de
NK022(za)001:549: zang za ra tshags su byon nas /
NK022(za)001:550: dpal kun tu bzang po nas da ltar gyi bla
NK022(za)001:551: ma yan chad la gang zag tha mal gyi lhad
NK022(za)001:552: med de / grub thob byin brlabs kyi brgyud pa ma chad pa yin no //
NK022(za)001:553: de lta bu'i dbang rin po che 'di /
NK022(za)001:554: yul phun sum tshogs pa lnga dang ldan par 'tshal te /
NK022(za)001:555: de yang gnas phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK022(za)001:556: tshogs khang ye shes kyi gzhal yas khang /
NK022(za)001:557: thar pa chen po'i grong mchog dge legs kyi stan
NK022(za)001:558: kham chen po dngos grub 'byung ba'i gnas chen po
NK022(za)001:559: lags pas / tha mal gyi kham pa legs pa dang nyes pa dang /
NK022(za)001:561: mi dga' ba'i rnam par mi lta bar ye shes chen po'i pho brang du longs spyod cig /
NK022(za)001:562: ston pa phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK022(za)001:563: dbang bskur ba'i bla ma rdo rje 'dzin chen po ste /
NK022(za)001:566: slob dpon mtshan nyid brtag pa ni //
NK022(za)001:567: ye shes snying po khyod nyon cig /
NK022(za)001:568: brtan zhing dul la g.yo sgyu med //
NK022(za)001:569: gsang sngags brgyud kyi sbyor shes pas //
NK022(za)001:570: dkyil 'khor bri ba'i las la mkhas //
NK022(za)001:571: de nyid bcu ni yongs shes shing //
NK022(za)001:572: sems can rnams la mi 'jigs sbyin //
NK022(za)001:573: theg pa che la brtag dga' ba //
NK022(za)001:574: de ni slob dpon yin par gsungs shig ces pa dang /
NK022(za)001:575: yang thig le dbang gi tan tra las /
NK022(za)001:576: de'ang mtshungs par ldan pa dang //
NK022(za)001:577: brtan zhing dul la blo gros ldan //
NK022(za)001:578: bzod ldan drang zhing g.yo sgyu med //
NK022(za)001:579: ces pa nas gsung gi bar dang /
NK022(za)001:581: ston pa mchod rtson ces pa'i tshig gsungs pas //
NK022(za)001:582: mtshan nyid de dag dang ldan pas ni dbang gi slob dpon bya bar gsung gis /
NK022(za)001:583: su tho thod kyis bya bar ma gsungs so //
NK022(za)001:584: de lta bas nas dbang gi slob dpon ni /
NK022(za)001:585: sangs rgyas thams cad 'dus pa'i ngo bo lags pas tha mal gyi spyod pa legs nyes dang /
NK022(za)001:586: thugs la 'dogs mi 'dogs su 'dzin pa skad cig
NK022(za)001:587: kyang mi sems par bla ma la sangs rgyas su
NK022(za)001:588: lta'o // 'khor phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK022(za)001:589: slob ma mtshan nyid dang ldan pa zhig dgos te /
NK022(za)001:591: bsgom dang bsgrub la dga' ba dang //
NK022(za)001:592: rtag tu bla ma la gus shing //
NK022(za)001:593: dus su bla ma mchod byed pa //
NK022(za)001:594: yon tan dang ldan slob ma yin //
NK022(za)001:597: thos bsam bsgom la rab sbyangs pa'i //
NK022(za)001:600: shes rab kyi ni blo phye nas //
NK022(za)001:601: nges par brtags pa'i sa gzhi la //
NK022(za)001:602: blo la nges pa'i lung 'di bstan //
NK022(za)001:603: zhes gsungs pas slob ma yang mtshan nyid de dag dang ldan dgos te /
NK022(za)001:604: su tho thod gang rung rung gi spyod yul ni ma yin no //
NK022(za)001:605: de lta bas na 'dir 'tshogs pa rnams mched rdo
NK022(za)001:606: rje spun bya ba lags pas 'di nas rdo rje
NK022(za)001:607: 'chang gi gral du ma sleb bar du /
NK022(za)001:608: dam tshig lu gu brgyud du sbrel te gcig gi
NK022(za)001:609: grogs gcig gis byas nas sangs rgyas kyi sa la
NK022(za)001:611: de la mthun mi mthun dang /
NK022(za)001:614: de la sogs pa'i rnam par mi lta bar thams
NK022(za)001:615: cad lha dang lha mo'i rnam par gyis la longs
NK022(za)001:616: spyod cig / yo byad phun sum tshogs pa'ang /
NK022(za)001:618: yo byad dka' ba kun bsdus nas //
NK022(za)001:619: khyad par mchod dang ldan pa yis //
NK022(za)001:620: dngos grub bsgrub pa'i rdzas su bzhag /
NK022(za)001:623: bcos bu'i ras ni zhes pa dang //
NK022(za)001:625: gnas dang longs spyod ci bde dang zhes gsungs pas /
NK022(za)001:630: dkyil 'khor dbang gi yo byad do //
NK022(za)001:631: de la dgra'i rkyen bzlog pa'i go mtshon dang /
NK022(za)001:632: bgegs kyi rkyen bzlog pa'i gu gul dang /
NK022(za)001:636: nad rkyen bzlog pa'i sman dang sman par bcas pa /
NK022(za)001:637: gtsang cha dang spra bar bcas pa spyad yig la sogs pa'o //
NK022(za)001:642: mchod pa rten gyi yo byad kyang /
NK022(za)001:645: lugs sku la sogs pa ste /
NK022(za)001:647: mig gi rten yang mngon par bkram //
NK022(za)001:649: 'tsho ba zas kyi yo byad kyang /
NK022(za)001:658: rdo rje kun tu rgyu dang /
NK022(za)001:659: rdo rje ka ta ri la sogs pa pu tsa 'os pa rnams so //
NK022(za)001:662: bde ba chen po'i tshogs su bshad //
NK022(za)001:664: khu byug rol pa'i rgyud phyi ma las /
NK022(za)001:665: kun tu rgyu dang gal phyis dang //
NK022(za)001:666: zla rgyas zla phrom lnga gsum rdzas //
NK022(za)001:667: bsgrub pa tshogs kyi rdzas su bzhag /
NK022(za)001:670: bum pa lnga la sogs pa phyi nang gi rdzas rnams so //
NK022(za)001:671: de ltar yo byad phun sum tshogs pa de dag kyang /
NK022(za)001:672: bde ba chen po'i yo byad ma /
NK022(za)001:673: longs spyod ye shes chen po'i ngo bo'o //
NK022(za)001:674: dngos grub chen po'i rdzas kho na lags pas /
NK022(za)001:681: de la sogs pa skad cig kyang mi skye mi
NK022(za)001:682: lta bar dngos grub chen po'i rol par spyod cig
NK022(za)001:683: / dus phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK022(za)001:692: skar ma bzang po la 'jug ste /
NK022(za)001:694: tshes grangs yar gyi brgyad la brtsam //
NK022(za)001:695: shin tu skar ma rgyal rnams la //
NK022(za)001:696: byang chub spyod pa che spyod bya //
NK022(za)001:697: snga dro'i dus su dkyil 'khor bri //
NK022(za)001:699: de ltar phun sum tshogs pa lnga dang ldan nas /
NK022(za)001:700: dbang gi gleng gzhi bshad par bya ste /
NK022(za)001:701: rnam par snang mdzad thig le dbang gi tan tra las byung ba'i rim pa /
NK022(za)001:702: 'dod pa khams kyi gnas rigs 'di na slob dpon dung gi phreng ba can zhes bya ba /
NK022(za)001:703: gos su dung gi phreng ba gon pa rdzu 'phrul dang ldan pa zhig la /
NK022(za)001:704: slob ma rgyal bu phru gu zhig yod de /
NK022(za)001:705: rgyal bu de la bram ze des bslab sbyang la sogs pa mang po bslabs nas /
NK022(za)001:706: rig pa'i gnas lnga la mkhas par gyur pa dang /
NK022(za)001:707: rgyal bus bsam pa da ni nga yang shes pa mang por gyur te /
NK022(za)001:708: bdag gi gong du bram ze 'di las ma rtogs pa gzhan su yang ma shor te /
NK022(za)001:709: 'di gong du mi gtang ngo snyam nas /
NK022(za)001:710: bram ze la rgun chang blud de rgyal ba dang /
NK022(za)001:711: lce ni lcags kyus drangs te bcad /
NK022(za)001:712: lus la rus sbal gyi khrag gis byugs /
NK022(za)001:713: bud med mang po mnan zhing brtul /
NK022(za)001:714: bsgyid pa ni mnan zhing bcad nas bzhag pas /
NK022(za)001:715: bram ze re zhig nas sad pa dang /
NK022(za)001:716: drung na su 'dug 'bod par 'dod pas ni lce bcad nas smra ma shes te /
NK022(za)001:717: lta bar bsam pas ni mig kyang med /
NK022(za)001:718: langs nas 'gro bar bsams pas ni sgyid pa bcad nas 'gro ma nus /
NK022(za)001:719: bud med mang po mnan shing brtul bas dran pa nyams /
NK022(za)001:720: lus la khrags gis byugs pas chu bur gyi nad dang rkong pas gang bar gyur to //
NK022(za)001:721: de nas bram zes bsam pa 'di ltar sdug bsngal la nyon mongs shing nyams thag pa 'di /
NK022(za)001:722: tshe rabs sngon gyi rnam par smin pa zhig yin nam /
NK022(za)001:723: 'on te gong du shor gyis dgos pa'i phrag dog cig yin bsnyam du bsams shing brtags pa dang /
NK022(za)001:724: rgyal bu phru gus gong du shor gyis dogs pa'i phrag dog yin par rig nas /
NK022(za)001:726: rgyal bu phru gu khyod ngas de tsam du blo sbyong ni byas /
NK022(za)001:727: bshes gnyen ni mthar phyin nas /
NK022(za)001:728: nga la 'di lta bu'i barngana byed pa /
NK022(za)001:729: khyod kyang skye ba gcig gis tshe thung la /
NK022(za)001:730: nga yi lus la ru sbal gyi khrag gis skus pas /
NK022(za)001:731: khyod kyi lus la mdze dang /
NK022(za)001:738: nad rnam pa drug gis thebs pa dang /
NK022(za)001:739: nga yi lus la bud med kyis brtul bas /
NK022(za)001:740: khyod kyi lus la sha za mo stong gi tshang bca' ba dang /
NK022(za)001:741: nga yi mig brtsegs pas khyod kyang long ba dang /
NK022(za)001:742: nga'i lce bcad pas khyod kyang smra ba lkugs pa dang /
NK022(za)001:743: nga'i sgyid pa bcad pas khyod kyang zha zhing 'gro mi shes par gyur cig /
NK022(za)001:744: de nas tshe 'phos nas kyang ngan song gsum rim par brgyud de /
NK022(za)001:745: dmyal ba'i sar skyes nas tshe rabs grangs med pa'i
NK022(za)001:746: bar du 'phags pa'i 'bras bu mi thob cing byang
NK022(za)001:747: chub kyi myu gu sngo skams su gyur cig /
NK022(za)001:748: de skad ces dmod bor ba dang /
NK022(za)001:749: de nas rgyal bu phru gu de dus myur du tshe 'phos nas /
NK022(za)001:750: rang gi nyes byas kyi rnam smin dang /
NK022(za)001:751: bram ze'i dmod mo 'dom pa de'i dbang gis sems
NK022(za)001:752: can gyi nang nas lus hrul po gcer bu can
NK022(za)001:754: lus la nad rnam pa drug gis thebs nas mi bde /
NK022(za)001:755: sha za mo stong gi tshang bcas /
NK022(za)001:758: rkang pa zha ba la sogs pa sdug bsngal bar gyur skad /
NK022(za)001:759: de nas tshe 'phos nas kyang dmyal khams bcu drug
NK022(za)001:760: gi kha brgyud nas bskal pa grangs med par bsgrangs
NK022(za)001:761: kyi bar du yang 'phags pa'i zhal mthong bar ma
NK022(za)001:762: gyur cig / byang chub kyi myu gu sngo skams su gyur pa la thug pa dang /
NK022(za)001:763: bcom ldan 'das nyid kyi thugs kha nas dpal phyag na rdo rje phyung nas /
NK022(za)001:764: mdun drang po na bka' nod pa las /
NK022(za)001:765: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
NK022(za)001:766: lag na rdo rje khyod song la 'dod khams 'di
NK022(za)001:767: na sems can lus hrul po gcer bu can zhes
NK022(za)001:768: bya ba / tshe snga ma la slob dpon bram
NK022(za)001:769: ze zhig la rngan sna tshogs pa byas pa'i rnam
NK022(za)001:771: bram ze'i dmod pa 'dom pa'i dbang gis /
NK022(za)001:772: da lta yang byang chub kyi myu gu sngo skams la thug /
NK022(za)001:773: lus kyi rgyud ni nyon mongs shing sdug bsngal bar gyur te /
NK022(za)001:774: de nas tshe 'phos nas kyang dmyal khams kyi kha brgyud de /
NK022(za)001:775: las kyi rnam par smin pa gzhan gyis dmyal bar ltung ba ni /
NK022(za)001:776: rnam par smin pa bri nas mtho ris su 'gro srid kyis /
NK022(za)001:777: 'di ni slob dpon la rngan byas pas nam yang thar pa'i gnas med pas /
NK022(za)001:778: lag na rdo rje khyod song la cho ga zab
NK022(za)001:779: mo'i byin brlabs mchog gi dbang dam pa 'di rnams
NK022(za)001:780: bskur la mtho ris kyi gnas su skye bar gyis
NK022(za)001:781: shig / ces bka' stsal pa dang lag na rdo rje yid rangs te /
NK022(za)001:782: bcom ldan 'das la slar gsol ba /
NK022(za)001:783: bcom ldan 'das dbang thams cad kyi rang bzhin bshad du gsol /
NK022(za)001:785: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa //
NK022(za)001:786: rgyal rigs btsun par skyes pa'i tshe //
NK022(za)001:787: rgyal srid 'bangs kyi phul ba ni //
NK022(za)001:788: tshig btsun yul la dbang bsgyur ba'i //
NK022(za)001:789: sa bdag rgyal por gnas pa bzhin //
NK022(za)001:790: bcom ldan byang chub spyod pa'i tshe //
NK022(za)001:791: lha dang lha min 'khor bcas la //
NK022(za)001:792: dbang bskur rdzas kyis mnga' gsol bas //
NK022(za)001:793: de nas byang chub mngon sangs rgyas //
NK022(za)001:794: phyag rgya gsang ba'i gnas srungs te //
NK022(za)001:795: bdud rtsi bum pas sdig rnams bkrus //
NK022(za)001:796: phreng ba cod pan tshul khrims dang //
NK022(za)001:797: rnam lnga'i thur mas bag chags bsal //
NK022(za)001:798: me long 'khor lo dung rgya gram //
NK022(za)001:799: sna bdun 'khor los stegs btsugs te //
NK022(za)001:800: ral gri shes rab mda' gzhu dang //
NK022(za)001:801: seng ge nyi zla lta bu dang //
NK022(za)001:802: 'bras bu bkra shis rdzas brgyad sbyin //
NK022(za)001:803: bden pa'i bka' brjod bden bdar dang //
NK022(za)001:804: ting 'dzin tshangs pa'i glu dbyangs dang //
NK022(za)001:805: rten 'brel rdzas rnams bshams nas ni //
NK022(za)001:806: dbang mchog dpe ni dbang bskur ro //
NK022(za)001:808: de nas phyag na rdo rjes rdo rje lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par bzhugs nas /
NK022(za)001:809: de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyi sku dang gsung dang
NK022(za)001:810: thugs rdo rje rnam par dag pa'i phyag rgya bcings
NK022(za)001:811: te / sems can lus hrul po gcer bu can gyi gnas lngar bkod nas srung bas /
NK022(za)001:812: sha za mo stong gi gnas kyang byer ro //
NK022(za)001:813: de nas 'du 'bral med pa gsang ba'i dbang gis /
NK022(za)001:814: byang chub kyi myu gu sngo skams su gyur la thug pa sos nas /
NK022(za)001:815: de bzhin gshegs pa'i snying po can du byin gyis brlabs so //
NK022(za)001:816: de nas dam ldan par gyur to //
NK022(za)001:817: cod pan gyis dbang bskur bas khams gsum na gnas
NK022(za)001:818: pa'i bsam sbyor ngan pa'i bag chags dang bral bar
NK022(za)001:819: gyur to // de nas dam pa rnams kyi thugs
NK022(za)001:820: rje'i byin rlabs kyis bdud rtsi'i bum pas dbang bskur
NK022(za)001:821: gyur to // bas / lus mi bde ba rnams bkrus nas dag par gyur to //
NK022(za)001:822: me tog phreng bas dbang bskur bas tshul khrims kyi phreng ba zhig ral yongs su rdzogs nas /
NK022(za)001:823: ngan song las bzlog pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur to //
NK022(za)001:824: cod pan gyis dbang bskur bas khams gsum na gnas
NK022(za)001:825: pa'i bsam sbyor ngan pa'i bag chags dang bral bar
NK022(za)001:826: gyur to // de nas gser gyi thur mas dbang
NK022(za)001:827: bskur bas ma rig pa'i ling thog thibs pa byang
NK022(za)001:829: me long gis chos thams cad gzugs brnyan nam rten 'brel sgyu ma lta bur mthong ngo //
NK022(za)001:830: gser gyi 'khor los rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa dang ldan nas /
NK022(za)001:831: khams gsum thams cad du 'gro nus par gyur to //
NK022(za)001:832: dung gis tshangs pa'i sgra skad phun sum tshogs pa dang ldan par gyur to //
NK022(za)001:833: rgya gram gyis phyogs bcu nas sngags 'chang rnams kyis rtag tu bsrung bar gyur to //
NK022(za)001:834: de nas rat+na sna bdun mkha' las rgyud mar byung ste /
NK022(za)001:841: glang po rnams kyis dbang bskur bas phyir mi ldog
NK022(za)001:842: pa'i 'khor lo bsgyur ba'i rgyal po sprin dpung zhes
NK022(za)001:844: de la ye shes kyi ral gri dang /
NK022(za)001:845: thabs shes rab zung du 'brel ba'i mda' gzhu dang /
NK022(za)001:846: brjid pa'i seng+ge myur ba'i gzugs can rnams kyis dbang bskur bas skad cig la sangs rgyas te /
NK022(za)001:847: bcom ldan 'das kun tu bzang po zhes bya bar gyur to //
NK022(za)001:848: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis legs so zhes bya bas bstod nas /
NK022(za)001:849: nyi ma dang zla ba phyag tu phul ma thag tu /
NK022(za)001:850: nyi mas skye 'gro ma lus pa'i sems can gyi
NK022(za)001:851: rgyud la ye shes kyi 'od zer chen po dus
NK022(za)001:852: mtha' med par shar bas gro zhing 'jam par gyur
NK022(za)001:853: to // zla bas ni stong gsum gyi mun pa
NK022(za)001:854: thams cad dus gcig tu bsal nas du sa dang
NK022(za)001:855: snang ba thams cad du bsil zhing snang bar gyur
NK022(za)001:856: to // to // de nas thams cad mkhyen pa'i
NK022(za)001:857: ye shes kyi go 'phang chen po rdzogs par gyur
NK022(za)001:858: to // to // te / thams cad nas thams
NK022(za)001:859: cad du bkris nas grub pa'i rdzas su gsungs pa
NK022(za)001:860: to // to // te / dang / 'dod pa khams kyi lha dang 'og min gyi lha dang /
NK022(za)001:863: gang zag dad pa gsal zhing rig pa'i glang po dang /
NK022(za)001:864: mkhyen pa'i dpal la sogs te sbyin pa'i gnas su bskyed pa'i phyir /
NK022(za)001:865: bkra shis kyi mnga' gsol nas /
NK022(za)001:866: gzhan la phan pa'i don du tshigs su bcad de bstod pa /
NK022(za)001:867: de bzhin gshegs pa dges pa dges pa che //
NK022(za)001:868: rdo rje bdag ni brtan du ma btang zhig /
NK022(za)001:869: nyungs dkar dngos grub rdzas kyis bgegs kyi sbyor ba rnams 'jig cing /
NK022(za)001:870: zho'i rnam par rgyal byed ting 'dzin bcud kyis 'tsho ba dang /
NK022(za)001:871: dur bas dge ba'i rtsa ba dpag med tshogs ldan zhing /
NK022(za)001:872: li khris lha mo mang po dbang du bsdus pa phyed par shog /
NK022(za)001:873: me long gis ni chos kun gzugs brnyan lta bur rtogs pa dang /
NK022(za)001:874: dung gis 'jig rten gsum du chos kyi grags pa thob gyur nas /
NK022(za)001:875: g+hi ha gis ni dug gsum zhi byed chos srog mang po 'tsho ba dang /
NK022(za)001:876: bil bas mtshungs med bla med byang chub snying po thob par shog /
NK022(za)001:877: zhes brjod nas bkra shis rdzas brgyad kyi mnga' gsol nas /
NK022(za)001:878: so so'i yon tan ji ltar gsungs pa bzhin bkra shis par gyur bgyi bar gda' /
NK022(za)001:879: de lta bas na gzhan gyi sdig pa mtshams med pa lnga dang /
NK022(za)001:881: log pa brgyad la sogs pa rnams 'dag cing 'joms par 'gyur ba ni lta smos kyang ci dgos /
NK022(za)001:882: bla ma la brnyas pa byas pa'i rnam smin kyang /
NK022(za)001:883: dbang bskur ba'i phrin las khyad par can gyis 'dag
NK022(za)001:884: par 'gyur ba ni khyad par rmad du byung ba'i
NK022(za)001:885: phrin las te / bde ba chen po la dgongs la thugs bde bar nos shig /
NK022(za)001:886: de dag ni dbang gi gleng gzhi bshad pa'o //
NK022(za)001:887: da ni 'di na mar dbang mi 'chags pa'i gags brgyad bshad par bya ste /
NK022(za)001:889: dper na chu rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag cing dngas pa la /
NK022(za)001:890: glo bur gyi rnyog mas brnyog nas mi gsal ba'am /
NK022(za)001:891: 'byung chen ltos kyi nam mkha' rang bzhin gyis rnam
NK022(za)001:892: par dag pa la glo bur gyi sprin dang khu
NK022(za)001:893: barlangasa kyis bsgribs nas mi gsal ba bzhin /
NK022(za)001:894: chos nyid rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag cing gsal ba la /
NK022(za)001:895: glo bur gyi rnam par rtog pa'am /
NK022(za)001:896: bag chags sprin lta bur byung nas sgribs pa ni /
NK022(za)001:898: sangs rgyas kun gyi dngos grub dang //
NK022(za)001:899: byin brlabs dbang mchog 'byung ba ni //
NK022(za)001:900: dper na rgya mtsho dngas pa la //
NK022(za)001:901: nyi zla'i gzugs brnyan 'byung ba yang //
NK022(za)001:902: rnyog ma chu'i gags gyur bzhin //
NK022(za)001:903: byin rlabs dbang mchog 'byung ba'i gags /
NK022(za)001:904: rnam pa brgyad du 'byung bar bshad //
NK022(za)001:907: sngon 'byung ston pa slob dpon la //
NK022(za)001:908: bka' bcag brnyas pa byed pa ni //
NK022(za)001:909: dbang dang dngos grub dam pa'i gags //
NK022(za)001:911: bla ma ni sangs rgyas thams cad 'dus pa'i sku /
NK022(za)001:912: dngos grub 'byung ba'i rtsa ba lags pas bka' bcag dang brnyas pa spang bar bya'o //
NK022(za)001:913: bla med rdo rje 'gro ba'i spun //
NK022(za)001:914: 'khu ldog gdungs pa'i sems med na //
NK022(za)001:915: dbang dang dngos grub gags gnyis pa //
NK022(za)001:916: zhes mched la brtse ba dang gdung ba'i sems cher bya'o //
NK022(za)001:917: byang chub lam la 'du med cing //
NK022(za)001:918: thar pa 'dren pa'i lha spong pa //
NK022(za)001:919: dngos grub 'byung ba gags gsum pa //
NK022(za)001:920: zhes pas don dam byang chub sems dang /
NK022(za)001:921: kun rdzob byang chub sems ma spong zhig /
NK022(za)001:922: de'i rtags yi dam gyi lha dang nam du yang 'bral bar ma byed cig /
NK022(za)001:923: snying rje'i yul gyur sems can la //
NK022(za)001:924: thag pa gcod pa gags bzhi pa //
NK022(za)001:925: zhes pas khams gsum gyi sems can thams cad la snying rje'i thag pa ma gcad cig /
NK022(za)001:926: gsang sngags gsang ba'i lta spyod rnams //
NK022(za)001:927: yengs la byin pa lnga pa'i gags //
NK022(za)001:928: zhes pas snod kyis ma smin pa dang /
NK022(za)001:929: zab pas ma smin pa dang /
NK022(za)001:930: chos kyis ma smin pa la sogs pa snod du
NK022(za)001:931: mi rung ba'i gang zag rnams la gsang sngags zab
NK022(za)001:933: thar lam ston pa 'dud med cing //
NK022(za)001:934: ser snas bcings pa drug pa'i gags //
NK022(za)001:935: zhes pas dbang bskur ba'i bla ma la mos gus med cing /
NK022(za)001:936: dbang 'chags pa'i rten yon dbul ba la ser sna ma byed cig /
NK022(za)001:937: gzu lums dbang med las la spyod //
NK022(za)001:938: dngos grub 'byung ba'i gags bdun pa //
NK022(za)001:939: zhes pa bla ma'i bka' ma thob cing dbang ma
NK022(za)001:940: bskur bar gsang sngags zab mo'i don la gzu lums
NK022(za)001:941: dang ras chod ma byed cig /
NK022(za)001:942: 'dod pa kheng grags lta bur byed cing /
NK022(za)001:943: gsang ba'i dam tshig spong ba ni /
NK022(za)001:944: 'di ni brgyad pa'i gags su bstan //
NK022(za)001:945: ces pas 'dod pa dang kheng grags lhur ma len par /
NK022(za)001:946: gsang sngags kyi dam tshig rin po che gser dang 'dra ba 'di ma spong cig /
NK022(za)001:947: nyams pa 'di dag sus spong ba //
NK022(za)001:948: dngos grub dbang gi snod du bshad //
NK022(za)001:949: 'di ltar khyod kyi rab bstan na //
NK022(za)001:950: bu khyed nang par 'dri byed pa //
NK022(za)001:951: dkyil 'khor drung du legs par nyon //
NK022(za)001:953: gags brgyad gsal bar byed pa'i pra khrid /
NK022(za)001:954: snyan rgyud yi ge med pa'i gdams pa /
NK022(za)001:958: // // de ltar dbang gi gleng gzhi tshar nas /
NK022(za)001:959: skyabs 'gro sems bskyed rdo rje rgyal thebs kyis sna drangs la /
NK022(za)001:961: phrin las kyi zhal bskos byas la /
NK022(za)001:962: zhi khro dang ma mo gzhung bsrang /
NK022(za)001:963: gzhan yang sngags pa rnams kyis bsgrub pa bka' brgyad char gyi phrin las lcogs tshad bya'o //
NK022(za)001:966: lhag ma la sogs pa spyi dang mthun par bya /
NK022(za)001:967: yo byad ma tshogs pa kun de'i nyin mo len du bzhug go //
NK022(za)001:968: de rnams ni sngon 'gro gnad kyi yig chung zhes bya'o //
NK022(za)001:972: // // bla ma dam pa rnams la na mo /
NK022(za)001:973: da ni dbang gi dngos gzhi'i cho ga bshad par bya ste /
NK022(za)001:974: de la mdo yongs rdzogs dang /
NK022(za)001:976: dang po la yan lag gi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK022(za)001:977: rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor gnyis su ngos bzung ste /
NK022(za)001:978: de yang dbang gi chu bo bzhi las /
NK022(za)001:979: yo ga la sogs theg drug la //
NK022(za)001:980: phyi dbang brgyud kyi chu bos bya //
NK022(za)001:982: thog mar yan lag gi dkyil 'khor bstan pa ni /
NK022(za)001:983: lha ma'i dkyil 'khor gyi cho ga dang /
NK022(za)001:988: yo ga'i dkyil 'khor gyi cho ga'o //
NK022(za)001:989: de la snga dro dang po /
NK022(za)001:991: phyi dbang gi lugs su 'bum lnga gdon cing sbyin pa dgye /
NK022(za)001:992: srog dang rgya blu lam 'phrang bsal /
NK022(za)001:993: tsh+wa tsh+wa chu gtor la sogs pa'i //
NK022(za)001:994: chos spyod skyabs 'gro sems bskyed sogs //
NK022(za)001:995: dge tshogs dpung bskyed bsngo ba bya //
NK022(za)001:996: zhes gsungs pas gang bya ba dang gang byed pa'i
NK022(za)001:997: las thams cad kyi sngon du 'gro ba ni dge
NK022(za)001:998: ba yin te / dge spyod kyi brtul zhugs la
NK022(za)001:999: gnas pa'i rnal 'byor pa ji ltar bsam pa bzhin
NK022(za)001:1000: 'grub cing 'bras bu yang mthar phyin par 'gyur ro
NK022(za)001:1001: ba yin te / // de cis mngon na sngon
NK022(za)001:1002: gyi rgyal ba rnams kyis rab tu basngagasa pa'i phyir
NK022(za)001:1003: ba yin te / // / theg pa chen po'i
NK022(za)001:1004: dge ba'i bshes gnyen gyi gsung las gsal bar byed
NK022(za)001:1005: ba yin te / // / pa'i phyir ro // gzhan yang /
NK022(za)001:1006: tshogs bsags pa las bde ba 'byung //
NK022(za)001:1007: zhes pa las gang dang gang gi sngon du dge
NK022(za)001:1008: tshogs dpung bskyed pa ni gdams pa'i gnad yin no
NK022(za)001:1012: chu gtor gtang ba la sogs pa dge ba'i dpung bskyed la /
NK022(za)001:1014: sngon 'gro la nan chags cher byas pas /
NK022(za)001:1015: bar chad 'byung mi srid yin gsung gin gada'o //
NK022(za)001:1017: de ltar gong du sa'i cho ga dang /
NK022(za)001:1018: sngon du 'gro ba'i las rnams tshar nas /
NK022(za)001:1019: nub gnyis pa la lha mi nyan rang gsum gcig tu dril la bskur te /
NK022(za)001:1020: dgong mo las mkhan gyis dkyil 'khor chag chag btab la /
NK022(za)001:1022: lho nub tu lha mi'i dkyil 'khor gling bzhi gling phran dang bcas pa /
NK022(za)001:1023: gling bzhi phyogs mtshon mu khyud lcags khar bri /
NK022(za)001:1024: dbus kyi lte ba la rnam snang pad+ma bzhi la rgyal po chen po bzhis bskor ba bkod /
NK022(za)001:1026: gling bzhi gling phran bcu gnyis dgod gsung ngo //
NK022(za)001:1028: dkyil 'khor gyi zur bcu gcig tu nyan thos kyi
NK022(za)001:1029: dkyil 'khor dbus ser po la pad+ma rim pa gsum
NK022(za)001:1032: bcu drug mdzes mtshon du bri /
NK022(za)001:1033: dkyil 'khor gyi zur gcig tu rang rgyal gyi dkyil
NK022(za)001:1034: 'khor dbus dmar po la nang du pad+ma 'dab ma
NK022(za)001:1035: bzhi / phyi rim du brgyad bcu gnyis bri'o //
NK022(za)001:1036: de nas dkyil 'khor bri ba zin pa dang /
NK022(za)001:1037: las mkhan gyis phyi mtshams bcad /
NK022(za)001:1038: sa'i rjes la rol mo'i sgra sbyar te /
NK022(za)001:1039: lha mi nyan rang rim pas sngon la bum pa bkod te /
NK022(za)001:1040: lha ma'i bum pa chas su bcug la rnam snang bskyed la dgod /
NK022(za)001:1041: dbang rdzas ka med rnams go rim du dgod /
NK022(za)001:1042: mched lcam rnams rang gi lo grangs dang mnyam pa'i
NK022(za)001:1043: tsha tsha kar zhal nas phyung la dkyil 'khor la
NK022(za)001:1044: dgod / rten 'brel snying pos rab gnas bya'o //
NK022(za)001:1045: de nas nyan thos kyi dkyil 'khor la lte ba
NK022(za)001:1046: la bum pa bden pa bzhir byin gyis brlabs la
NK022(za)001:1047: bkod / pad+ma 'dab ma bcu drug la mchog bcu drug gi tsa ka li bkod /
NK022(za)001:1048: sku'i rten sh+aaka thub bris sku'am lugs sku bkram /
NK022(za)001:1049: gsung gi rten glegs bam bzhugs /
NK022(za)001:1050: thugs kyi rten rdo rje dril bu bkod /
NK022(za)001:1051: de nas rang rgyal gyi dkyil 'khor gyi lte ba
NK022(za)001:1052: la bum pa chas su bcug la sh+aaka thub rdzogs
NK022(za)001:1054: pad+ma 'dab ma bcu gnyis la rang sangs rgyas bcu gnyis kyi tsa ka li bkod /
NK022(za)001:1056: dkyil 'khor gyi rgyan thams cad bkram zhing bstar bar bya'o //
NK022(za)001:1057: de nas kun gral la 'dug la /
NK022(za)001:1058: slob dpon gyis skyabs 'gro sems bskyed kyi chos bshad /
NK022(za)001:1059: e ma sangs rgyas kyis mtshams bcad /
NK022(za)001:1061: theg pa'i lam khyer la lha mi'i theg pa /
NK022(za)001:1062: lha lam khyer rnam par snang mdzad mi 'khrugs pa /
NK022(za)001:1063: snying po lam khyer la na mo b+ha ga wa te dang kam ka ni /
NK022(za)001:1065: rdzogs pa chen po'i gzhung phrin /
NK022(za)001:1067: gnas rten dang sman lha'am cha gsum chog phrin /
NK022(za)001:1069: mtshan mo mdo mchod las mkhan gyis gzhung bsrang /
NK022(za)001:1071: kun gyis langs la bskor ba bya zhing skyabs 'gro dang sems bskyed la 'bad do //
NK022(za)001:1072: de nas bsnyen pa bskyal lo //
NK022(za)001:1073: nyan thos la dkyil 'khor bri ba la sogs gong du song nas /
NK022(za)001:1075: theg pa las nyan thos kyi theg pa /
NK022(za)001:1076: de la lta sgom spyod 'bras bzhi sbyar te /
NK022(za)001:1077: gzung 'dzin don dam du 'dod pa lta ba /
NK022(za)001:1078: de'i ngang la gnas pa sgom pa /
NK022(za)001:1079: de dang tshul mthun par spyod pa spyod pa /
NK022(za)001:1080: dgra bcom pa thob par 'dod pa 'bras bu'o //
NK022(za)001:1081: lha lam khyer ni sh+aaka thub /
NK022(za)001:1082: snying po lam khyer ni mu ni bzlas pa /
NK022(za)001:1083: rang rgyal la yang dkyil 'khor bri ba la sogs gong du bstan nas /
NK022(za)001:1084: theg pa la rang sangs rgyas /
NK022(za)001:1086: theg pa lam khyer la chos kyi bdag la phyogs gcig rang bzhin med par rtogs par lta ba /
NK022(za)001:1087: sgyu ma'i ye shes rten 'brel bcu gnyis kyi don sgom pa ni sgom pa /
NK022(za)001:1088: rdzu 'phrul gyi sgo nas gzhan don shas 'ga' tsam spyod pa ni spyod pa /
NK022(za)001:1089: yid bzhin bde ba mchog gi sa thob pa ni 'bras bu'o //
NK022(za)001:1090: chos kyi bdag la phyogs gcig rang bzhin med par rtogs pas nyan thos las 'phags so //
NK022(za)001:1091: lha lam khyer la sh+aaka thub /
NK022(za)001:1092: snying po lam khyer las rten 'brel snying po /
NK022(za)001:1093: dbang lam khyer las rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba bcu gnyis kyis dbang bskur /
NK022(za)001:1094: de ltar bsnyen pa rnams rdzogs nas /
NK022(za)001:1095: lto zos la mched lcam rnams phyir phyung la khrus bya /
NK022(za)001:1096: slob bus nang du dbang khri rtsig /
NK022(za)001:1097: mched lcam rnams 'ong dus su lha'i nga rgyal gyis bgegs bskrad /
NK022(za)001:1098: kun gral la 'dug la rol mo'i sgra sbyar /
NK022(za)001:1099: lha tshogs rim par spyan drangs la /
NK022(za)001:1100: slob bus mdo mchod rnam lnga gyer zhing dbul /
NK022(za)001:1101: sdom rten ci rigs par bla ma la dbul /
NK022(za)001:1102: bla ma sh+aakya thub par bsgoms la dbang gos dang ldan zhing stegs la 'dzegs la /
NK022(za)001:1103: gsol ba btab par bya ste 'di skad du /
NK022(za)001:1104: kun mkhyen ye shes phung po can //
NK022(za)001:1105: srid pa'i 'khor lo rnam sbyong ba'i //
NK022(za)001:1106: de ring bshad pa'i rin chen mchog /
NK022(za)001:1107: gtso bos bdag la sku drin skyobs //
NK022(za)001:1109: dus khrims sogs bsnyen gnas kyi sdom pa 'bog /
NK022(za)001:1110: rtsa ba bzhi'i sdom pa 'bog ste /
NK022(za)001:1111: slob dpon sh+aaka thub du bsgoms la /
NK022(za)001:1112: btsun pa dgongs su gsol lo //
NK022(za)001:1113: zhes pa la sogs pa las byang ltar du bya /
NK022(za)001:1114: dge bcu dang sdig bcu'i spang blang bshad /
NK022(za)001:1115: lci ba bzhi dang log pa brgyad la sogs pa rgyas bsdus ci rigs su bshad de /
NK022(za)001:1117: theg pa dang po bcu drug mgon //
NK022(za)001:1118: zhes gsungs pa mi chos bcu drug la gzhi blangs /
NK022(za)001:1119: chos dge ba bcu spyad pa'i phan yon gyi lung dkras sdang ltar du drang /
NK022(za)001:1120: de nas rdo rje rgyal po nyid sh+aakya thub pa'i nga rgyal du zhugs la /
NK022(za)001:1121: snang srid kyi bcud thams cad bdag gi spyi bor thim pa las /
NK022(za)001:1122: spyi bo nas rin po che sna tshogs pa 'phros nas dgos 'dod yongs su skongs par bsams la /
NK022(za)001:1123: las mkhan gyis bum pa gdan drangs la dbang bskur /
NK022(za)001:1124: de nas tsa ka li ka kha'i dbang bskur /
NK022(za)001:1125: de bzhin du slob bu la yang bskur ro //
NK022(za)001:1126: de yang gags drug bshad na /
NK022(za)001:1127: gong du bshad pa'i gnas ni chu bo na ra dza ra'i 'gram du'o //
NK022(za)001:1128: gang gis bshad pa'i bstan pa ni sh+aakya thub pa chen po'o //
NK022(za)001:1129: gang la bshad pa'i 'khor ni byang chub sems dpa' don grub /
NK022(za)001:1130: gang bshad pa'i theg pa ni lha mi'i theg pa ste /
NK022(za)001:1132: rgyu mtshan nyid kyi theg pa'i dbang gi sngon du 'gro ba'i phyir ro //
NK022(za)001:1133: dgos pa ni 'jig rten pa'i bya ba las 'phags pa'i dgos pa yod skad /
NK022(za)001:1135: gang gis gang la ci phyir gang dgos pa //
NK022(za)001:1136: 'di ni lha mi'i theg pa'i gags nas drug yin //
NK022(za)001:1139: dge bcu dag la gtsor byed pas //
NK022(za)001:1141: zhes pas dbang mi zad pa'am 'phel bar byed pa'i
NK022(za)001:1142: rtags su rang gi spyi bor zla ba nya gang
NK022(za)001:1143: pa zhig bsgom / de'i steng du sh+aakya thub pa
NK022(za)001:1144: 'du 'bral med par bya ba dang spyod pa ci
NK022(za)001:1145: pa zhig bsgom / byed kyang / spyi bos sh+aakya thub pas bka' bsgo nas byed pas /
NK022(za)001:1146: sh+aakya thub pa'i gsung la 'da' ba ni mi dge ba'i sems med pa'o //
NK022(za)001:1147: de ni ye shes kyi ngang sgom chung ngun gyi thad kar gzigs shig /
NK022(za)001:1148: 'di ni dbang don chen po dkras sdang las /
NK022(za)001:1149: lha mi'i theg pa'i skabs so //
NK022(za)001:1150: 'di ni 'khrul snang rtsad gcod nam mkha' dang mnyam pa'i rgyud las gsungs so //
NK022(za)001:1151: 'di dag re re la zhag re byed na /
NK022(za)001:1152: khrus bya ba nas sdom pa len pa la sogs pa sngon la byed de pra khrid ltar ro //
NK022(za)001:1153: de nas bka' drin gsol ba dang /
NK022(za)001:1154: yon dbul ba la sogs dus gcig la bya /
NK022(za)001:1155: lha mi'i dkyil 'khor gyi cho ga'o //
NK022(za)001:1156: de nas nyan thos kyi dbang bskur te /
NK022(za)001:1157: slob bu khrus bya ba nas rnam lnga dbul ba dang /
NK022(za)001:1158: mdo mchod bya ba la sogs pa gong gis 'dres /
NK022(za)001:1159: de nas rgyu bdag nyid dkyil 'khor du zhugs la
NK022(za)001:1160: sh+aakya thub pa la bden pa bzhi'i dbang zhus la
NK022(za)001:1161: / de nyid sh+aaka thub tu bsgom ste spyi bor
NK022(za)001:1162: rin po che 'od sna tshogs 'phro ba zhig bsgom
NK022(za)001:1163: / / de nas bus gsol ba btab pa gong bzhin du bya'o //
NK022(za)001:1164: de nas rab tu byung ba zhu ste /
NK022(za)001:1165: mkhan po la rab tu byung bar zhu ba bya /
NK022(za)001:1167: ston pa bcom ldan 'das sh+aakya thub pa bya ba
NK022(za)001:1168: la sogs pa las byang nas byung ba ltar bya
NK022(za)001:1169: / mkhan pos bar chad gsum dris la gtsug phud breg /
NK022(za)001:1170: skyabs su gsol ba dang sems bskyed sngon du song bas /
NK022(za)001:1171: mkhan po dgongs su gsol zhes pa la sogs pa dge sbyong gi sdom pa 'bog /
NK022(za)001:1173: dang po bla gos dang chos gos byin gyis brlabs la sbyin /
NK022(za)001:1174: ngo tsha dang khrel yod kyis dbang bskur ro //
NK022(za)001:1177: chu tshags byin gyis brlabs la sbyin la mkho ba'i yo byad du dbang bskur ba /
NK022(za)001:1178: de nas slob dpon gyis dbang rdzas bum pa blangs
NK022(za)001:1179: la bden pa bzhi dang mchog bcu drug gi dbang
NK022(za)001:1180: bskur / lam khyer gsum po bshad la sgom du bzhug /
NK022(za)001:1181: de nas dbang mi nyams par bya ba'i phyir 'debs chung zhig bya na /
NK022(za)001:1182: rang gi dpral bar rus pa'i thig le nyungs dkar tsam zhig bsgom /
NK022(za)001:1183: de la shes pa gtad pas thig le de je
NK022(za)001:1184: che je che la snang srid thams cad keng rus
NK022(za)001:1186: de yang yul rang brgyud pa la brten na chags
NK022(za)001:1187: sdang rmongs gsum skye ste nyon mongs pa 'khor ba'i
NK022(za)001:1188: rgyu yin / des 'bras bu sdug bsngal gyi bden pa myong ba yin te /
NK022(za)001:1189: de'i gnyen por rus pa'i 'khor lo yul mi sdug pa bsgoms pas /
NK022(za)001:1190: nyon mongs pa chags sdang mi skye /
NK022(za)001:1191: kun 'byung gi nyon mongs pa rtsad bcad nas /
NK022(za)001:1192: 'bras bu sdug bsngal las rang bzhin gyis 'gog pa de ka lam gyi bden pa yin gsung /
NK022(za)001:1193: theg pa lam khyer gyi dbang du byas na /
NK022(za)001:1194: nyan thos gzung 'dzin don dam du 'dod pa lta ba la sogs pa gong gi 'agre'o //
NK022(za)001:1195: bsgom chen gyi 'dug tshul ni mi blo 'pham po sdug gtam gtong ba lta bu'o //
NK022(za)001:1196: mi dge bcu dgra dang tsher ma bzhin du bltas nas spong /
NK022(za)001:1197: dge bcu sman dang phan pa'i zas ltar bsten nas len /
NK022(za)001:1198: de yang nyan thos la 'du shes bcu ste /
NK022(za)001:1199: srog gcod pa la btsan dug lta bu'i 'du shes dang /
NK022(za)001:1200: nyon mongs pa la dug sbrul lta bu'i 'du shes dang /
NK022(za)001:1201: kha zas la mtha' 'khob kyi rgan rgon lta bu'i 'du shes dang /
NK022(za)001:1202: gos la rma dkris lta bu'i 'du shes dang /
NK022(za)001:1203: rnyed pa dang bkur sti la rgya dang snyi lta bu'i 'du shes dang /
NK022(za)001:1204: bla ma dang dkon mchog la nor bu rin po che lta bu'i 'du shes dang /
NK022(za)001:1205: chos la lam lta bu'i 'du shes dang /
NK022(za)001:1206: sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa la gser lta bu'i 'du shes dang /
NK022(za)001:1207: tshul khrims la rgyan lta bu'i 'du shes dang /
NK022(za)001:1208: chos nyid mngon du gyur pa la mun khung du
NK022(za)001:1209: sgron me bteg pa lta bu'i 'du shes dang bcu'o
NK022(za)001:1210: // de dag ni dbang rdo rje zam pa las kyang bshad do //
NK022(za)001:1211: nyan thos kyi gags drug ni /
NK022(za)001:1212: gnas wa ra na se'i bsil khang du /
NK022(za)001:1213: ston pa sh+aakya thub pa chen pos /
NK022(za)001:1214: 'khor mchog chen po brgyad la sogs pa la /
NK022(za)001:1215: bden pa bzhi yis dbang bskur nas /
NK022(za)001:1216: 'bras bu dgra bcom pa thob ste /
NK022(za)001:1217: dgos pa mu stegs rtag chad rang rgyud du 'dod pa las grol ba'i dgos pa yod /
NK022(za)001:1219: gang gis gang la gang du gang bstan pa /
NK022(za)001:1220: ci'i phyir dang dgos par bcas pa ste /
NK022(za)001:1221: 'di ni nyan thos theg pa'i gags drug yin //
NK022(za)001:1224: de nas rang rgyal gyis dbang bskur te /
NK022(za)001:1226: sdom rten phul la rang sangs rgyas kyi sdom pa 'bog /
NK022(za)001:1227: de nas dbang lam khyer bum dbang dang rten cing 'brel pa bcu gnyis kyi dbang bskur /
NK022(za)001:1229: theg pa las rang sangs rgyas /
NK022(za)001:1230: de la lta sgom spyod 'bras bzhi gong du smos pa bzhin 'dir bshad /
NK022(za)001:1231: nyan thos las khyad par 'phags pa'ang 'adre'o //
NK022(za)001:1232: de nas yang dbang 'chad par byed pa'am gnas pa'i rten du 'debs chung zhig bya na /
NK022(za)001:1233: rang gi spyi bor thig le dmar po sran ma tsam zhig sgom /
NK022(za)001:1234: de las mtho bar thig le dkar po sran ma tsam zhig bsgom /
NK022(za)001:1235: de nas thig le dmar po de la shes pa
NK022(za)001:1236: gtad pas je che je che la snang srid thams
NK022(za)001:1237: cad dmar lam song bar bsam /
NK022(za)001:1238: dmar po de chags pa'i rang bzhin lugs 'byung 'khor ba'i chos yin gsung /
NK022(za)001:1239: yang thig le dkar po de la sems gtad pas
NK022(za)001:1240: je che je che la snang srid thams cad dkar
NK022(za)001:1242: dkar po de lugs min mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos yin gsung /
NK022(za)001:1243: dkar dmar gnyis po 'dres nas spyi bo na mar babs /
NK022(za)001:1244: snying gi dkyil du thim pas /
NK022(za)001:1245: rang gi sems dang dbyer med du 'dres pas 'khor
NK022(za)001:1246: ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa thams cad mnyam
NK022(za)001:1247: pa nyid du blo kyur la bzhag gsung /
NK022(za)001:1248: lha rje sh+aaka mgon ni de tsam gcig tu la zhag gsum bsgom skad /
NK022(za)001:1250: gnas ri bo bya rkang can /
NK022(za)001:1251: dbang rten cing 'brel par byung ba lugs 'byung dang /
NK022(za)001:1252: lugs bzlog 'khor ba dang 'das pa dbyer med du rtogs pa'i dgos pa yod /
NK022(za)001:1253: de min kun nyan thos dang 'dra /
NK022(za)001:1254: lam khyer ngang bsgom chen po'i thad kar lta'o //
NK022(za)001:1255: de dag ni rang sangs rgyas kyi theg pa'o //
NK022(za)001:1256: de nas dkyil du bum chus sku khrus gsol /
NK022(za)001:1258: dam pa tog dkar gyis bkra shis gsol /
NK022(za)001:1259: lha mi nyan rang rnams kyi cho ga /
NK022(za)001:1260: tho yig pra khrid rnams dang mi 'gal bar bsdebs pa /
NK022(za)001:1264: // // bla ma dam pa rnams la na mo /
NK022(za)001:1265: nub gsum pa byang chub sems dpa'i theg pa'i dbang la /
NK022(za)001:1266: phyi dro dkyil 'khor chag chag gdab la pad+ma brgyad ldan nam nyi shu tham pa zhal dbye /
NK022(za)001:1268: nang du rol mo'i sgra sbyar la /
NK022(za)001:1269: dbus kyi lte ba la bum pa thub pa chen po dang /
NK022(za)001:1270: yum chen mo shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin mar bskyed la dgod /
NK022(za)001:1271: dbus kyi lte ba la thub pa chen po dgod /
NK022(za)001:1272: pad+ma 'dab ma bzhi'i shar du yum chen mo /
NK022(za)001:1276: gru chad la lha mi dgod /
NK022(za)001:1277: lha rnams kyi phyogs bzhi mtshams bzhi shar stod nub smad du byang chub sems dpa' bcu bkod do //
NK022(za)001:1278: 'di dag gi sngags tsa ka na yod /
NK022(za)001:1279: mdzad pa rdu'i dbang rdzas dkyil 'khor gyi mtha' mar bkod /
NK022(za)001:1281: sku gsung thugs kyi rten bkram /
NK022(za)001:1287: dge ba la rjes su yi rang ba dang /
NK022(za)001:1288: mya ngan las mi 'da' bar gsol ba btab pa dang /
NK022(za)001:1289: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor bar bskul ba dang /
NK022(za)001:1290: mjug dge ba'i rtsa bar bsngo ba la sogs pa byas la /
NK022(za)001:1291: mched rnams la rdo rje slob dpon gyis sems bskyed kyi sdom pa 'bog /
NK022(za)001:1292: de nas mtshan mo bsnyen pa bskyal te /
NK022(za)001:1293: lam khyer bzhi la theg pa'i lam khyer byang chub sems dpa' /
NK022(za)001:1294: lha yum chen mo la sras phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas kyis bskor ba'am /
NK022(za)001:1295: tsa ka li'i lha bco lnga /
NK022(za)001:1297: g+ha te dbang mdzad pa nyi shu'i dbang /
NK022(za)001:1298: gdam ngag ni bu gcig pa la ma brtse ba lta bu /
NK022(za)001:1299: byams pa dang snying rje bsgom pa'i sgo nas sems can thams cad la khyab par bsgom /
NK022(za)001:1300: lta ba ni bdag med kyi don rtog /
NK022(za)001:1301: sgom pa ni rnam par mi rtogs pa bsgom /
NK022(za)001:1302: spyod pa pha rol tu phyin pa drug ldan gyi bsgrub pa nyams su blang /
NK022(za)001:1303: 'bras bu bcu gcig kun tu 'od thob /
NK022(za)001:1304: sgom chen gyi 'dug tshugs ni yul dpon yul tshis byed pa lta bu /
NK022(za)001:1305: don spyi don la dmigs pa kho na'o //
NK022(za)001:1306: de la ye shes kyi ngang bsgom gyi dbang du byas na /
NK022(za)001:1307: de yang bden pa gnyis kyi don bsgom pa ste /
NK022(za)001:1308: de nas kun rdzob kyi dbang du byas na dbang
NK022(za)001:1309: rdzas lag tu gtad nas ting nge 'dzin dang cho
NK022(za)001:1311: skur byed bcas pa ye shes chen po'i mdzad pa nyi shu'i dbang de rang yin pas /
NK022(za)001:1312: don dam par na snying gi dkyil du thig le lcog sgong tsam zhig sgom /
NK022(za)001:1313: 'od kyi rnam pa kha dog gang du yang ma nges pa zhig bsgom /
NK022(za)001:1314: de yang thig le stong pa skye ba med //
NK022(za)001:1316: thig le de brtags pas kha dog gi rnam pa ma 'gags par cir yang snang ba /
NK022(za)001:1317: kha dog rnams la brtags pas phyogs gcig pa gang du yang ma grub bo //
NK022(za)001:1318: de bzhin du kun rdzob tu dbang rdzas dang dbang
NK022(za)001:1319: bskur ba la sogs cir yang ma 'gags par shar
NK022(za)001:1320: yang / don dam par na gang du yang ma
NK022(za)001:1321: dmigs par chos nyid spros pa thams cad dang bral
NK022(za)001:1322: zhing ci'i ngo bor yang ma grub par gnas pa
NK022(za)001:1323: yang / yin no // de ltar spros pa thams
NK022(za)001:1324: cad dang bral ba'i ngang la ma bcos par gnas
NK022(za)001:1325: pa med pa'i tshul gyis gnas par bya'o //
NK022(za)001:1328: kun rdzob ma 'gags pa'i snang ba /
NK022(za)001:1329: rang nyid yum chen mo shes rab kyi pha rol
NK022(za)001:1330: tu phyin mar bsgoms la spyod pa rnam bzhi lha
NK022(za)001:1331: dang mi 'bral bar bya ba ni /
NK022(za)001:1332: bden pa gnyis zung du 'jug pa'i lam pa zhes bya ste /
NK022(za)001:1333: ye shes kyi ngang sgom chen po'i thad kar gzigs /
NK022(za)001:1334: da ni byang chub sems dpa'i gags drug bshad na /
NK022(za)001:1335: gong du bskur ba'i gnas ni bya rgod phung po'i ri'am /
NK022(za)001:1337: gang gis bskur ba'i ston pa ni phyogs bcu'i de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyis bskur /
NK022(za)001:1338: gang la bskur ba'i 'khor ni byang chub sems dpa' rgyal bu don grub la sogs pa la bskur /
NK022(za)001:1339: gang bskur ba'i dbang ni ye shes mdzad pa nyi shu'i dbang bskur /
NK022(za)001:1340: ci'i phyir dbang bskur na mdzad pa nyi shu yongs su rdzogs pa'am /
NK022(za)001:1341: mi lus lha ru bsgrub par bya ba'i phyir bskur ro //
NK022(za)001:1342: dgos pa ni bdud kyi dpung bcom nas chos kyi rgyal srid chen po 'dzugs pa'i dgos pa yod /
NK022(za)001:1344: gang gis gang la gang du ji lta bar //
NK022(za)001:1345: tshul dang dgos par bcas pa rnam drug gis //
NK022(za)001:1346: 'di ni byang chub sems dpa'i gags drug yin //
NK022(za)001:1351: 'di dag ni pha rol tu phyin pa'i dbang gi gdams pa ste /
NK022(za)001:1352: phal la ma mchis thugs kyi dkyil du phyung /
NK022(za)001:1355: nor bu byi dor byas na dgos pa 'byung //
NK022(za)001:1356: rtsags cha gnam du phyar na sgal can 'phags //
NK022(za)001:1357: drang po'i thig gdab sgur po ras su 'gro //
NK022(za)001:1358: sbal bu pad+ma'i drung na 'dam la spyod //
NK022(za)001:1363: // // bla ma dam pa rnams la na mo /
NK022(za)001:1364: de nas nub bzhi pa gsang sngags bla na med pa'i theg pa la /
NK022(za)001:1365: phyi pa thub pa brgyud kyi theg pa dang /
NK022(za)001:1366: nang pa thabs kyi brgyud kyi theg pa gnyis /
NK022(za)001:1367: dang po la spyir gsum du gsungs kyang /
NK022(za)001:1368: dkyil 'khor kri yog gnyis kyis bri ste /
NK022(za)001:1369: dkyil 'khor la chag chag gdab ste /
NK022(za)001:1370: dkyil 'khor gyi zur gcig tu kri ya'i dkyil 'khor rnam 'joms dang mthun par bzhengs /
NK022(za)001:1371: de nas yo ga'i dkyil 'khor gyi sta gon gyi cho ga byas la thig gdab /
NK022(za)001:1372: steng du dri'i thig le bya /
NK022(za)001:1373: lha grangs dang mnyam pa'i me tog gi tshom bu dgod /
NK022(za)001:1374: rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor bskyed /
NK022(za)001:1377: gsol ba btab pa la sogs pa bya /
NK022(za)001:1379: yo ga'i dkyil 'khor pho brang cha lnga pa bri /
NK022(za)001:1380: de nas rol mo sbyar la /
NK022(za)001:1381: kri ya'i dkyil 'khor la bum pa chas su bcug la rab gnas rnam 'joms ltar bya /
NK022(za)001:1382: pho brang gi dkyil du bkod /
NK022(za)001:1383: dbang rdzas nyi shu rtsa drug gi tsa ka li bkod de /
NK022(za)001:1384: de nas yo ga'i dkyil 'khor la bum pa chas su bcug la dbus su bkod /
NK022(za)001:1385: lha tshogs sum cu rtsa bdun gyi tsa ka li dang /
NK022(za)001:1386: yo ga bkra shis drug cu rtsa bzhi'i tsa ka li bkod /
NK022(za)001:1387: kri yog gnyis kyi dkyil 'khor gyi mtha' mar dam rdzas la sogs pa dang /
NK022(za)001:1390: thugs rje'i gzung thag 'phan la sogs /
NK022(za)001:1392: gzhan yang mchod pa'i sprin gyis stibs par bya'o //
NK022(za)001:1393: de nas kri ya'i mchod pa las mkhan gyis gzhung bsrang la /
NK022(za)001:1394: rdo rje slob dpon gyis lam khyer bzhi ldan du byas te /
NK022(za)001:1395: theg pa lam khyer la gsang sngags kri ya /
NK022(za)001:1396: lha lam khyer la rigs gsum mgon po /
NK022(za)001:1401: dbang lam khyer la kri ya'i dbang mchog nyi shu rtsa drug go //
NK022(za)001:1403: de nas yo ga'i mchod pa'i gzhung ni phyed pa dang bsrang /
NK022(za)001:1405: lha lam khyer lha tshogs sum cu rtsa bdun /
NK022(za)001:1406: snying po lam khyer b+hud+ha b+aee ro tsa na /
NK022(za)001:1410: a mo g+ha si ti a /
NK022(za)001:1412: theg pa lam khyer yo ga'i theg pa /
NK022(za)001:1413: dbang lam khyer yo ga'i dbang mchog drug cu rtsa bzhi'o //
NK022(za)001:1416: nam langs pa dang tshogs la rol la kri yog gi dbang bskur ba'i cho ga bya ste /
NK022(za)001:1417: mched lcam rnams phyir phyung la la la khrus bya /
NK022(za)001:1418: nang du slob bus dbang khri brtsigs /
NK022(za)001:1419: mched lcam rnams nang du 'ong dus su bgegs bskrad /
NK022(za)001:1420: gral la 'dug la rdo rje slob dpon gyis dbang khri'i steng du 'dzegs te /
NK022(za)001:1422: dbang bskur ba'i nus pa dang ldan par bya /
NK022(za)001:1423: de nas sngon la bum pa'i dbang bskur /
NK022(za)001:1424: de nas gsang sngags kri ya'i dbang mchog nyi shu rtsa drug bskur /
NK022(za)001:1425: rdzas dbang spyi bor bzhag la rgyud la bstims /
NK022(za)001:1426: mched rdo rje'i spun rnams lus lha'i 'khyer so /
NK022(za)001:1429: 'khyer so gsum la gnas par bya'o //
NK022(za)001:1430: lta ba ni don dam dag pa'i mtha' bzhi dang bral ba /
NK022(za)001:1431: kun rdzob rigs gsum lha'i dkyil 'khor du 'dod /
NK022(za)001:1433: cho ga yan lag bcu gcig sgom /
NK022(za)001:1434: spyod pa ni khrus dang gtsang sbra la spyod /
NK022(za)001:1435: 'bras bu rigs gsum rdo rje 'dzin pa'i sa thob /
NK022(za)001:1437: rang gi spyi bor thig le dkar dmar mthing gsum brtseg mar bsgom /
NK022(za)001:1438: thig le dkar po la 'od 'phros pas sems can gyi sdig sgrib sbyangs te /
NK022(za)001:1439: de bzhin gshegs pa la phog pas sku mnyes pa'i pu tsa dbul /
NK022(za)001:1440: 'od de tshur 'dus nas spyi bor thim pas /
NK022(za)001:1441: sku'i lha 'jam dpal sku mdog ser po /
NK022(za)001:1442: zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa ral gri dang ud pa la 'dzin pa gcig sgom /
NK022(za)001:1443: de nas thig le dmar po pu mthing kha thugs khar thim pa 'dre /
NK022(za)001:1444: de ltar lus ngag yid gsum de bzhin gshegs pa'i
NK022(za)001:1445: sku gsung thugs kyi ngo bor bsgom nas spyod lam
NK022(za)001:1446: rnam pa bzhi / ka ba rtsis 'da' ba med
NK022(za)001:1447: pa ni spyod pa dbang chags pa'i rten yin no
NK022(za)001:1448: rnam pa bzhi / // kri ya'i gags drug sbyor na /
NK022(za)001:1449: gang du gsungs pa'i gnas ni sngon 'byung wa ra na sir gsungs la /
NK022(za)001:1450: rjes 'jug tu pad+ma me tog 'ja' tshon gyi gling du dbang bskur /
NK022(za)001:1451: gang gis bskur ba'i ston pa ni sngon 'byung bcom ldan 'das kyis bskur la /
NK022(za)001:1452: rjes 'jug tu slob dpon chen po sh+aan tis bskur ro //
NK022(za)001:1453: gang la bskur ba'i yul ni /
NK022(za)001:1454: sngon 'byung du byang chub sems dpa' phyag na rdo rje la bskur /
NK022(za)001:1455: rjes 'jug tu slob dpon zla 'bar rtsal la bskur /
NK022(za)001:1459: dpag bsam gyi shing la sogs pa dbang mchog nyi shu rtsa drug bskur /
NK022(za)001:1460: ci'i phyir na sngon 'byung du phyag na rdo rje
NK022(za)001:1461: la bcom ldan 'das kyi thugs rjes bzung ba dang
NK022(za)001:1462: / rjes 'jug tu snod bcud 'dzom pa'i dus su bstan /
NK022(za)001:1463: zhes gsungs pas bla ma sbyangs pa'i yon tan dang ldan pas /
NK022(za)001:1464: slob bu snod dang ldan zhing las 'phro yod pa /
NK022(za)001:1465: zab mo'i don la mos pa zhum pa med pa'i brtson 'grus kyis gdams pa zhu nus pa /
NK022(za)001:1467: yid ches pa'i dam tshig dang ldan pa ste /
NK022(za)001:1468: de'i rjes su 'jug pa'i phyir dbang bskur ro //
NK022(za)001:1469: dgos pa ni rin po che ri rab kyi dbang
NK022(za)001:1470: bskur bas mthu stobs khyad par can dang ldan pa'i
NK022(za)001:1471: dgos pa yod cing mchod rten gyi dbang bskur bas
NK022(za)001:1472: chos sku thob pa'i dgos pa yod la /
NK022(za)001:1473: dpag bsam gyi shing los dbang bskur bas dgos 'dod
NK022(za)001:1474: yid bzhin du 'grub pa'i dgos pa yod pa la
NK022(za)001:1475: sogs nyi shu rtsa drug po de rang yin no
NK022(za)001:1477: de nas yo ga'i dbang la /
NK022(za)001:1478: slob dpon bdag 'jug byas nas lha la dbang zhu ste /
NK022(za)001:1480: bgegs bskrad la bum pa'i dbang bskur /
NK022(za)001:1481: de nas yo ga'i dbang rtsa ba bcu la yan lag drug cu rtsa bzhir phye la bskur /
NK022(za)001:1482: dbang rdzas mgo la bzhag la rgyud la bstim mo //
NK022(za)001:1483: de la dbang chags pa'i rten du 'debs bya na /
NK022(za)001:1484: rang gi snying gi dkyil na dngas ma chen po lnga gnas pa ni /
NK022(za)001:1485: ring bzhin gyi rigs lnga dang ye shes lnga'i ngo bor gdod ma nas gnas pa yin /
NK022(za)001:1486: de la rang gi spyi bor thig le dkar po ril ma tsam gcig bsam /
NK022(za)001:1487: de gsal ba dang nam mkha'i dkyil nas thig pa shar zhes pas /
NK022(za)001:1488: thig le dkar po de yas mar babs pas /
NK022(za)001:1489: snying gi dkyil du dngas ma lnga rigs lngar gnas pa dang gnyis su med par 'dres par bsam /
NK022(za)001:1490: de ni don dam mtshan ma med pa'i ngo bo nyid do //
NK022(za)001:1491: rigs lngar gnas shing rigs lnga rdo rje dbyings kyi
NK022(za)001:1492: dkyil 'khor gyi lhar snang ba ni kun rdzob ye
NK022(za)001:1494: de dag gnyis su med pa'i ngang las /
NK022(za)001:1495: blo rang bzhin gyis gnas pa ni dbang chags pa'i rten yin gsung ngo //
NK022(za)001:1496: de la yo ga'i gags sbyar na /
NK022(za)001:1497: gang du bskur ba'i gnas ni lha bya skad ljon
NK022(za)001:1498: shing gi tshal rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor du
NK022(za)001:1499: / gang gis bskur ba'i ston pa ni slob dpon chen po ku ma tis bskur /
NK022(za)001:1500: gang la bskur ba'i yul ni rdo rje khyung grags rtsal la sogs pa'o //
NK022(za)001:1501: gang bskur ba'i dbang ni yo ga bkra shis drug cu rtsa bzhi'i dbang bskur te /
NK022(za)001:1503: bcom ldan 'das dpal rnam par snang mdzad kyis che ba'i yon tan smos pa'i phyir ro //
NK022(za)001:1504: gang dgos pa ni gang gis thob pa bkra shis par bya ba'i dgos pa yod /
NK022(za)001:1505: de nas dbang gnas par bya ba'i phyir rten 'brel gyi rab gnas bya /
NK022(za)001:1513: // // bla ma dam pa rnams la na mo /
NK022(za)001:1514: 'dir nub lnga pa nas bcu'i bar du gsang sngags bla na med pa'i theg pa /
NK022(za)001:1515: rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor bstan pa ni don bzhi ste /
NK022(za)001:1521: phyi nang gi bshags pa bya ba dang /
NK022(za)001:1522: dkyil 'khor gyi cho ga gnyis las /
NK022(za)001:1523: dang po ni yan lag gi skabs su rgyas par byas pas chog go //
NK022(za)001:1524: 'dir na rag dong sprugs brgya tshar dang /
NK022(za)001:1525: srid pa'i spyi mdos zur tsam byas kyang mi 'gal lo //
NK022(za)001:1526: gnyis pa sta gon gyi cho ga la don lnga ste /
NK022(za)001:1532: sngon la pho brang byi dor legs par byas la /
NK022(za)001:1534: de nas yan lag rab gnas bya ste /
NK022(za)001:1535: dbus kyi pho brang nas gcal ba'i sa phyogs gang
NK022(za)001:1536: bde bar man+dala pad+ma 'dab brgyad mdzes tshon du bya
NK022(za)001:1537: / mtha' ma rdo rje ra bas bskor ro //
NK022(za)001:1538: de'i steng du rdzas dang mchod pa'i rnam pa bkod pa ni /
NK022(za)001:1539: dbus su rat+na'i bum pa la sogs pa rdo rje rgya gram gyis mtshan pa gcig gi nang du /
NK022(za)001:1541: snying po lnga tshar nyi shu rtsa lnga 'tshogs par blugs la /
NK022(za)001:1543: gzungs thag dang ldan par bya /
NK022(za)001:1544: 'dab ma'i shar du rat+na'i snod du dam tshig gi thig dang /
NK022(za)001:1545: gtor ma lho ru rdo rje dril bu du yod pa nub tu bum rdzas /
NK022(za)001:1546: byang du bdud rtsi ban d+ha gang bzhag /
NK022(za)001:1547: dbus kyi pho brang gi steng du /
NK022(za)001:1550: dam rdzas bdud rtsi rnam gsum bzhag /
NK022(za)001:1551: rdo rje slob dpon gyi mdun du rigs kyi bum
NK022(za)001:1552: pa lnga la so so'i thugs mtshan bris la bzhag
NK022(za)001:1553: / phyi nang gi mchod pa kun tshang bar bsham /
NK022(za)001:1554: de nas slob dpon chas gos dkar por zhugs la phyag thung lugs su btsal /
NK022(za)001:1556: ye nas mnyam nyid kyis bshags /
NK022(za)001:1557: kun tu bzang po bla na med ces pas dam bca' /
NK022(za)001:1558: dus gsum sangs rgyas kyis byin dbab /
NK022(za)001:1559: pu tsa rnams rim pas byin gyis brlabs /
NK022(za)001:1560: zhi ba thung lugs su bstod pa yan chad bya'o //
NK022(za)001:1561: khro bo yang thung ngur gzhung bsrang /
NK022(za)001:1563: gu gul dang dri zhim pos bdugs te /
NK022(za)001:1564: las thams cad pa'i bum pa ra ya kha gsum gyis sbyangs la /
NK022(za)001:1565: shu dz+nya tas stong pa nyid kyi ye shes su bsam /
NK022(za)001:1566: bum pa'i phyir dur khrod du 'bar ba la nang rat+na'i gzhal yas khang du bsgom /
NK022(za)001:1567: de'i nang du ma sur+ya man+dala zhes nyi ma'i gdan bsam /
NK022(za)001:1568: de'i steng du h'u ljang gu'i 'phro 'du las /
NK022(za)001:1569: big nan ta krid a mri ta kun d+ha li ha na ha na h'u phata /
