NK022(za)001:1570: ces brjod la bdud rtsi 'khyil pa ljang khu g.yas rdo rje rgya gram /
NK022(za)001:1571: g.yon dril bu thogs pa gcig bsgom /
NK022(za)001:1572: de la ye shes lngas dbang bskur /
NK022(za)001:1573: karma he ru kas dbu brgyan /
NK022(za)001:1574: ye shes sems dpa' spyan drangs bstim /
NK022(za)001:1576: kun tu bzang po nas lha mo bzhi snol gyis mchod /
NK022(za)001:1577: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha hi zhes sman dbul /
NK022(za)001:1579: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin bsdus pas dbul /
NK022(za)001:1581: phyogs bcu dus bzhis bstod la /
NK022(za)001:1582: rgya mtsho lnga'i smon lam gdab /
NK022(za)001:1583: de nas mdzub mo gnyis sbyar nas bum pa la gtugs la /
NK022(za)001:1584: +aahmh'u s+w+aa h+aa zhes brgya rtsa brgyad bzlas pas ting
NK022(za)001:1585: nge 'dzin gyis bdud rtsi 'khyil pa 'od du zhu
NK022(za)001:1586: nas bdud rtsi'i rgya mtshor mer gyis gyur par bsam
NK022(za)001:1587: / sarba b+hi shud+d+he d+harma th+aa badz+ra si ti h'u /
NK022(za)001:1588: zhes bum pa'i chus kun la gtor bas nyes skyon
NK022(za)001:1589: thams cad dag nas chos nyid stong pa nyid kyi
NK022(za)001:1591: de nas dam rdzas bdud rtsi gsum gyi chag chag gdab ste /
NK022(za)001:1592: bdud rtsi dri chen zhes pa dang /
NK022(za)001:1593: ma h+aa ba su tas dri chen gyi chag chag gdab /
NK022(za)001:1594: dam rdzas dag pa'i zhes pa dang ma h+aa ku kus dri chu /
NK022(za)001:1595: bka' gsang rmad du byung ba dang ma h+aa rak+tasa rak+ta'i chag chag gdab bo //
NK022(za)001:1596: de nas thig le rab gnas la /
NK022(za)001:1597: ye shes dang dam tshig go //
NK022(za)001:1599: stong pa nyid kyi ngang las /
NK022(za)001:1604: e man+dala zhes gdan lnga bsam /
NK022(za)001:1605: de dag gi thugs kha nas h'u swa a ha zhes yig 'bru dgod /
NK022(za)001:1606: yang dam tshig gi thig la sur+ya /
NK022(za)001:1611: de nas yang rang gi thugs kha'i 'od zer phyogs kun tu 'phros nas /
NK022(za)001:1612: badz+ra sa ma ya h'u dza zhes pa dang /
NK022(za)001:1613: e ha hi lan gsum brjod nas phyogs bcu dus
NK022(za)001:1614: gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa rnams mdun gyi nam
NK022(za)001:1615: mkha' la spyan drangs te brten par bzhugs su gsol
NK022(za)001:1616: la / phyag nas phyogs bcu dus bzhi yan chad kyis bstod cing /
NK022(za)001:1618: ho dgongs su gsol lo mi gnas pa'i ye shes chen po'i bdag nyid /
NK022(za)001:1619: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad bdag la dgongs su gsol lo //
NK022(za)001:1620: bdag rdo rje slob dpon gyis slob ma 'di rnams
NK022(za)001:1621: kyi don du 'dus pa chen po'i dkyil 'khor sku
NK022(za)001:1622: gsung thugs yon tan phrin las mi zad pa brgyan
NK022(za)001:1623: gyi 'khor lo gsang ba bas kyang yang gsang thugs
NK022(za)001:1624: kyi dkyil 'khor / lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor du thig 'debs pas /
NK022(za)001:1625: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis bdag la mthu bstan du gsol /
NK022(za)001:1626: byin gyis brlab tu gsol lo //
NK022(za)001:1628: rdo rje ye shes kyi thig stsal du gsol /
NK022(za)001:1629: badz+ra tik+na tish+tha g+hu he sa ma ya dz+nya na
NK022(za)001:1630: a g+hu sha dza dza zhes lan gsum brjod do
NK022(za)001:1631: // mdun gyi de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyi sbyor ba byang chub kyi sems kyi chu rgyun yang /
NK022(za)001:1632: ye shes lnga'i chu rgyun du kha dog lngar gsal bar bsam nas /
NK022(za)001:1633: thig le lnga po la thim par bsam /
NK022(za)001:1634: sku gsung thugs kyi gnas gsum nas 'od zer dkar
NK022(za)001:1635: dmar mthing gsum 'phros nas dam tshig gi thig la
NK022(za)001:1636: thim pas / thig gi dngos po nyid sku gsung thugs su gyur par bsam /
NK022(za)001:1637: de nas slob dpon shar du bltas /
NK022(za)001:1639: thig sna yum la gtad la dbyangs dang bcas pas /
NK022(za)001:1640: yi ge h'u zhes bya ba ni //
NK022(za)001:1641: rdo rje rigs kyi rang bzhin te //
NK022(za)001:1642: zhe sdang dngos po sbyang bya'i phyir //
NK022(za)001:1643: byin brlabs dam pa mdzad du gsol //
NK022(za)001:1644: ma h+aa shu nya ta'i sngags brjod pas /
NK022(za)001:1645: thig stong pa nyid kyi ye shes su gyur par bsam /
NK022(za)001:1646: de nas yi ge zhes pa dang /
NK022(za)001:1647: sngags a ta ri sha brjod pas /
NK022(za)001:1648: me long lta bu'i ye shes kyi ngo bo thig dkar brengs kyis gyur par bsgom /
NK022(za)001:1650: sa man ta'i sngags kyis mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes kyi ngo bo thig ser po /
NK022(za)001:1652: pra ta b+he sha'i sngags kyis so sor rtogs pa'i ye shes kyi ngo bo thig dmar po /
NK022(za)001:1654: tri ta a nu'i sngags kyis bya ba grub pa'i
NK022(za)001:1655: ye shes kyi ngo bo thig ljang khur gyur par
NK022(za)001:1656: bsgom mo // de nas thig skud rnams gcig tu bsgom la /
NK022(za)001:1657: yang dag bsgrub pa'i las byang las byung ba bzhin du /
NK022(za)001:1658: dur khrod gsang ba mchog gi dkyil 'khor du zhes pa nyid bsgyur te /
NK022(za)001:1660: gsang sngags sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK022(za)001:1661: gnyis med byang chub sems kyi 'phro 'du las //
NK022(za)001:1662: rdo rje ye shes thig chen 'di btab pas //
NK022(za)001:1663: pho brang dkyil 'khor yid bzhin lhun gyis grub //
NK022(za)001:1665: zhes bzlas kyis thig skud sgril nas ye shes lnga'am
NK022(za)001:1666: sku gsung thugs yon tan las nyi shu rtsa lnga'i
NK022(za)001:1668: de nas dam tshig gi thig lag tu thogs la /
NK022(za)001:1669: a h'u zhes sku gsung thugs su byin phab ste /
NK022(za)001:1670: thig skud la thim pa dang /
NK022(za)001:1672: bde gshegs sku'i rang bzhin te /
NK022(za)001:1673: lus kyi dngos po sbyang bya'i phyir /
NK022(za)001:1674: byin brlabs dam pa mdzad du gsol /
NK022(za)001:1676: yi ge am gsung gi ngag gi dngos po waka
NK022(za)001:1677: badz+ra yi ge h'u thugs kyi yid kyi dngos po
NK022(za)001:1678: byin rlabs tsit+ta badz+ra de nas thig rnams gcig tu
NK022(za)001:1679: sdom la / mu mtha' g.yo 'gul med pa'i /
NK022(za)001:1680: rnal 'byor mnyam nyid thod rgal du /
NK022(za)001:1681: khro gtum rngam pa'i las mdzad pa'i /
NK022(za)001:1682: gnas mdzad gzhal yas bri bar bya'o //
NK022(za)001:1683: ahmh'u badz+ra dz+nya na ma ti kra ma h'u /
NK022(za)001:1684: zhes brjod te thig re re'ang gsum gsum dgu phrugs dang ldan par bsam la /
NK022(za)001:1685: kun bzang nas glu ye shes yan chad kyi thung lugs su lcogs na bya'o /
NK022(za)001:1686: de nas rdo rje dril bu'i rab gnas ni /
NK022(za)001:1687: rdo rje dril bu khro zhal can la sogs pa du yod dang /
NK022(za)001:1688: dril bu tshangs pa'i gsung zhal dang ldan pa mdun du bzhag la /
NK022(za)001:1689: bsang sbyang stong pa nyid kyi ngang las /
NK022(za)001:1690: rdo rje'i lte ba la che mchog rdzogs tshul du bskyed /
NK022(za)001:1691: yar gyi ra lnga la rigs lnga zhi khro gnyis gang rung bar dpa' bo 'bru lnga'i sngags sam /
NK022(za)001:1694: mu la ma pya ta lnga 'am lngar yum bskyed /
NK022(za)001:1695: rtse dgu yin na mtshams kyi rwa bzhi la lung gi he ru ka bzhi bskyed /
NK022(za)001:1696: yar gyi pad+ma 'dab ma brgyad la sems dpa' brgyad /
NK022(za)001:1697: mar gyi la yum bskyed do //
NK022(za)001:1698: khro zhal bzhi la sgo ma bzhi dang /
NK022(za)001:1700: rim pa la dbang gang byed pa'i lha rnams rdzogs par bskyed /
NK022(za)001:1701: de nas dril bu'i lte ba la khro bo gnam zhal ma /
NK022(za)001:1702: zhal la yum chen mo shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin ma /
NK022(za)001:1703: ra lnga la rigs lnga gang rung /
NK022(za)001:1704: mar gyi pad+ma'i phyogs bzhi dbus dang lngar yum lnga /
NK022(za)001:1706: gong ras brgyad la khro mo brgyad /
NK022(za)001:1707: mtha' ma'i rdo rje ra ba la khro bo khro mo nyi shu bskyed /
NK022(za)001:1708: dril bu'i lce la khro mo gar bsgyur ma bskyed /
NK022(za)001:1709: rtse dgu yin na mtshams kyi rwa bzhi la las bzhi'i snying po bskyed do //
NK022(za)001:1710: de dag sngags sam ting nge 'dzin gyis gsal bar bskyed la /
NK022(za)001:1712: sku gsung thugs su byin gyis brlabs /
NK022(za)001:1713: dbab drang bstim brtan kun bzang nas bstod pa yan chad kyis mchod de /
NK022(za)001:1714: h'u zhes brjod pas lha rnams rang rang gi gnas
NK022(za)001:1715: nas 'od du zhu nas rdo rje dril bu la
NK022(za)001:1716: thim pas / rdo rje dril bu nyid ye shes
NK022(za)001:1717: kyi rdo rje dril bur gyur pa las sngags badz+ra
NK022(za)001:1718: d+ha ka dz+wa la ha na badz+ra pa tsa dz+nya
NK022(za)001:1719: thim pas / na badz+ra h'u / g+han d+ha pa sha d+harma d+har tu h'u /
NK022(za)001:1720: zhes brjod pas rdo rje la 'bras bu'i chos thams cad rdzogs nas 'gro don mdzad par bsam /
NK022(za)001:1721: dril bu'i sgra stong pa nyid kyi ngang chos sgra sgrogs par bsam la /
NK022(za)001:1722: rdo rje dril bu lag tu bzung nas 'gro ba'i don la bskul te /
NK022(za)001:1723: h'u rdo rje dril bu rig pa 'dzin //
NK022(za)001:1724: thabs dang shes rab gnyis med pa'i //
NK022(za)001:1726: chos la de bzhin dbang bsgyur shog /
NK022(za)001:1727: ces brjod nas rdo rje gsor bas khams gsum zil gyis mnan /
NK022(za)001:1728: dril bu bsil bas khams gsum dbang du bsdus par bsgom /
NK022(za)001:1729: de nas ban d+ha'i rab gnas ni /
NK022(za)001:1731: stong pa nyid kyi ngang nas b+h+ru las 'dus pa
NK022(za)001:1732: chen po'i rtsa ba'i gzhal yas khang gdan dang bcas
NK022(za)001:1733: pa bskyed / de la dbang bskur /
NK022(za)001:1734: brlab dbab drang bstim brtan kun bzang nas gtum chen gyis bstod la /
NK022(za)001:1736: ru lu cung zad zhig bzlas pas lha rnams 'od
NK022(za)001:1737: du zhu nas ye shes kyi chu rgyun du mer
NK022(za)001:1739: de nas tshon byin gyis brlabs pa ni /
NK022(za)001:1740: tshon gzhan rnams rigs dang mthun par bkod la /
NK022(za)001:1741: rtsa ba'i tshon lnga po la h'u sgril ma bkod /
NK022(za)001:1742: zer yang dpa' bo 'bru lnga bkod /
NK022(za)001:1743: 'di rnams dbus kyi pho brang gi steng du dam
NK022(za)001:1744: rdzas bdud rtsi rnam pa gsum dgod pa'i skabs su
NK022(za)001:1745: dgod do // de la rab gnas bya ba ni //
NK022(za)001:1746: sarba b+hi sho d+ha dang ra ya kha gyis sbyangs la /
NK022(za)001:1747: tshon gyi dngos po stong par sgom /
NK022(za)001:1753: e man+dala zhes gdan lnga bsam /
NK022(za)001:1754: cho ga gsum gyis lhar bskyed /
NK022(za)001:1756: brlab dbab drang bstim brtan kun bzang nas bstod pa'i bar byas la /
NK022(za)001:1758: h'u kun mkhyen ye shes dag pa la //
NK022(za)001:1759: dug lngas bsgrib pas ma mthong bas //
NK022(za)001:1760: mtshon cing dag par byas pa'i phyir //
NK022(za)001:1761: byin brlabs dam pa mdzad du gsol //
NK022(za)001:1763: zhes sor mo lngas bsnun zhing spungs la gong gi rigs lnga 'od du zhu ba las /
NK022(za)001:1764: ye shes re re'ang lnga lnga dang ldan par bsam mo //
NK022(za)001:1765: de ltar yan lag rab gnas zin pa dang /
NK022(za)001:1766: rdo rje slob dpon chas gos rnam pa lngas brgyan
NK022(za)001:1767: h'u zhes rdo rje 'gros kyis dkyil 'khor bskor la
NK022(za)001:1768: / dkyil 'khor gyi dbus su phyin la /
NK022(za)001:1769: zhal shar du bltas la rnam par rgyal ba'i nga rgyal dang /
NK022(za)001:1770: h'u gi bstang bstabs kyis bzhugs te 'dug pa la /
NK022(za)001:1771: 'dus pa chen po'i lha tshogs rnams mdun gyi nam mkha' la spyan drangs te /
NK022(za)001:1772: phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod pa'am /
NK022(za)001:1773: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi mchod pa phul la /
NK022(za)001:1774: yum bzhi po rigs bzhir byin gyis brlab /
NK022(za)001:1775: bskur dbab drang bstim brtan la gsang yum bzhis phyogs nas gsol ba gdab ste /
NK022(za)001:1776: dril bu'i sgra dang bcas par /
NK022(za)001:1778: sangs rgyas kun dang grong khyer nyid //
NK022(za)001:1779: de ring shis par mdzad du gsol //
NK022(za)001:1780: thams cad bdag nyid dgongs su gsol //
NK022(za)001:1784: zhi ba'i ye shes rang snang ba'i //
NK022(za)001:1785: brgyan rnams kun gyis rab mdzes pa //
NK022(za)001:1786: sangs rgyas kun gyi sku'i mchog /
NK022(za)001:1787: dkyil 'khor chen po srung du gsol //
NK022(za)001:1789: yon tan rin chen rgyas pa'i gtso //
NK022(za)001:1790: ma lus kun gyis re ba bskong //
NK022(za)001:1791: sangs rgyas kun gyi yon tan mchog /
NK022(za)001:1792: dkyil 'khor chen po srung du gsol //
NK022(za)001:1794: rang bzhin dag pa gos pa med //
NK022(za)001:1795: sangs rgyas kun gyi gsung gi mchog /
NK022(za)001:1796: 'dod chags pha rol phyin pas mnyes //
NK022(za)001:1797: dkyil 'khor chen po srung du gsol //
NK022(za)001:1799: bsam pa thams cad yongs rdzogs pas //
NK022(za)001:1800: thams cad sgrol ba'i ded dpon mchog /
NK022(za)001:1801: sangs rgyas kun gyi phrin las mchog /
NK022(za)001:1802: dkyil 'khor chen po srung du gsol //
NK022(za)001:1804: bsod nams ye shes tshogs rdzogs pa'i //
NK022(za)001:1805: rang gi mtha' dbus med pa'i dkyil //
NK022(za)001:1807: dkyil 'khor snying po bshad du gsol //
NK022(za)001:1808: ces brjod la lung gis bskul lo //
NK022(za)001:1809: rdo rje rgyal pos lan du /
NK022(za)001:1810: phyogs bcu ma lus thams cad kyi //
NK022(za)001:1811: rgyal ba sras bcas dgongs su gsol //
NK022(za)001:1812: bdag cag rdo rje rgyal po yis //
NK022(za)001:1813: slob bu rnams kyi don phyir du //
NK022(za)001:1814: dkyil 'khor chen po bdag bgyid pas //
NK022(za)001:1815: bdag cag rjes su bsrung ba'i phyir //
NK022(za)001:1816: sa 'di shis par byin brlabs par //
NK022(za)001:1817: bde bar gshegs pas mdzad du gsol //
NK022(za)001:1819: de nas slob dpon gyi thugs kha'i 'od zer gyis
NK022(za)001:1820: nam mkha' la bzhugs pa'i lha tshogs rnams h'u bzhis
NK022(za)001:1821: byin bsdus nas thugs khar thim par bsam /
NK022(za)001:1822: slob bu rnams rang yi dam gang byed kyi khro bor bsam la /
NK022(za)001:1823: dbang po sgo lnga nas 'od zer sna tshogs 'phro bar bsam zhing /
NK022(za)001:1824: byang shar mtshams nas rdo rje 'gros kyis /
NK022(za)001:1825: dkyil 'khor gyi mtha' ma bskor la /
NK022(za)001:1827: khro bcu'i sngags kyis bgegs rnams gzir cing bskrad /
NK022(za)001:1828: gral la 'khod la lus ngag yid gsum sku gsung
NK022(za)001:1829: thugs su byin gyis brlab cing go bgo lus srungs
NK022(za)001:1830: bya'o // de nas theg chen bzhi bcu par phye ma gdab /
NK022(za)001:1831: lnga pa yan chad kyi cha la dbus kyi lte ba la chag gang gis mtho bar byas la /
NK022(za)001:1832: rdo rje dbyings kyi thig rdzogs par gdab /
NK022(za)001:1833: mtha'i cha thig chen la thig chung spyi dang mthun par gdab bo //
NK022(za)001:1834: de ltar thig thebs pa dang /
NK022(za)001:1835: 'khar phor gyi nang du phud la a mri ta dang /
NK022(za)001:1843: bsnyug ma'i mgo srin bal lam /
NK022(za)001:1844: dar dkar gyi ye'u byas la /
NK022(za)001:1845: dri'i nang du bcug bzhin thig le lha gnas su bya /
NK022(za)001:1850: h'u h'u h'u badz+ra tsit+ta h'u /
NK022(za)001:1851: a a a badz+ra b+ha tra sa man ta a /
NK022(za)001:1852: a kra ma h+aa kro ta sh+ri he ru ka h'u /
NK022(za)001:1853: ka ta ma h+aa kro ti sh+aa ri h'u /
NK022(za)001:1854: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK022(za)001:1855: zhes brjod la me tog gi phung po byas la /
NK022(za)001:1861: mu d+ha du shwa ri zhes mi bskyod yab yum bkod /
NK022(za)001:1862: de nas rang rang gi gnas su sangs rgyas bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis po bkod do //
NK022(za)001:1863: de nas cha chen drug pa'i 'khor lo'i brtsibs dgu ru bsam la /
NK022(za)001:1864: byang shar du badz+ra he ru ka zer yang dbus su dgod /
NK022(za)001:1865: shar du b+hud+d+ha he ru ka /
NK022(za)001:1867: nub tu pad+ma he ru ka /
NK022(za)001:1868: byang du karma he ru ka /
NK022(za)001:1872: byang shar yak+sha he ru kar bskyed /
NK022(za)001:1873: de nas gru chad glo 'bur bzhis sa brgyad du /
NK022(za)001:1874: sur+ya zhes pa dri'i thig le brgyad bya /
NK022(za)001:1875: ko'u ri brgyad kyi sngags brjod la me tog gi phung po brgyad bya /
NK022(za)001:1876: de nas khyams dang po'i sgo dang bcas pa la
NK022(za)001:1877: phyogs bzhi mtshams bzhi ru sur+ya ces dri'i thig le
NK022(za)001:1878: brgyad bya / sing ha ma brgyad kyi sngags brjod la me tog gi phung po brgyad bya /
NK022(za)001:1879: sgo bzhi ru sur+ya zhes dri'i thig le bya /
NK022(za)001:1880: badz+ra a g+hu sha dza zhes pa la sogs pa
NK022(za)001:1881: bzhi'i sngags brjod la me tog gi phung po bya'o
NK022(za)001:1882: // de nas bar khyams gnyis pa'i phyogs mtshams bzhi ru sur+ya zhes dri'i thig le brgyad bya /
NK022(za)001:1883: a rak+mo h'u zhes me tog gi phung po brgyad bya /
NK022(za)001:1884: sgo bzhir dri'i thig le bzhi bya /
NK022(za)001:1885: sh+ri badz+ra mud ka ra sha ra ya ya na ma /
NK022(za)001:1886: sh+ri badz+ra g+han d+ha pra tsa la na ma /
NK022(za)001:1887: sh+ri badz+ra ra ga sha ra ya ya na ma /
NK022(za)001:1888: sh+ri badz+ra kha tong ka pra dza la ya ya na ma /
NK022(za)001:1889: zhes me tog gi phung po bzhi bya'o //
NK022(za)001:1890: de'i phyi rim du bar khyams gsum pa'i phyogs bzhir thig le drug drug nyi shu rtsa bzhi bya /
NK022(za)001:1891: sgo bzhir thig le bzhi bya /
NK022(za)001:1892: dbang phyug ma nyi shu rtsa brgyad kyi sngags brjod
NK022(za)001:1893: la me tog gi phung po nyi shu rtsa brgyad
NK022(za)001:1894: bya'o // de'i phyi rim du bar 'khyams bzhi pa
NK022(za)001:1895: la sur+ya zhes dri'i thig le phyogs bzhir brgyad brgyad
NK022(za)001:1897: e a ra li h'u zhes me tog gi phung po sum cu rtsa gnyis bya'o //
NK022(za)001:1898: de'i phyi rim du bar khyams lnga pa la ma
NK022(za)001:1899: bdun sring bzhi'i khyams te shar lho nub gsum du
NK022(za)001:1900: dri'i theg le gnyis gnyis bya /
NK022(za)001:1902: sgo bzhir re re bcu gcig bya /
NK022(za)001:1903: ma ma da du h'u zhes me tog gi tshom bu bcu gcig bya'o //
NK022(za)001:1904: de'i phyi rim du bar khyams drug pa la sur+ya
NK022(za)001:1905: zhes dri'i thig le shar nub tu bzhi bzhi bya
NK022(za)001:1908: ging ka ra ha ha ru lu b+h+yo zhes me tog gi tshom bu bco brgyad bya'o //
NK022(za)001:1909: de'i phyi rim du bar khyams bdun pa la shar nub tu bcu gnyis bcu gnyis /
NK022(za)001:1911: shar sgo nub sgo ru drug drug /
NK022(za)001:1912: lho sgo byang sgor bzhi bzhi'o //
NK022(za)001:1913: kro ta kro ti h'u zhes me tog gi phung po drug cu tham pa bya'o //
NK022(za)001:1914: de'i phyi rim du khyams brgyad pa'i shar phyogs su sur+ya zhes dri'i thig le drug cu bya /
NK022(za)001:1915: rba na rba na a g+hu sha dza dza zhes me tog gi phung po drug cu bya'o //
NK022(za)001:1916: de bzhin du lho phyogs su ha la ha la pa sha h'u zhes pa drug cu /
NK022(za)001:1917: nub byang su gardza gardza spo ta ba zhes pa drug cu /
NK022(za)001:1918: byang phyogs su pa tsa pa tsa g+han d+ha ho
NK022(za)001:1919: zhes pas dri'i thig le bya zhing me tog gi
NK022(za)001:1920: tshom bu bya'o // de nas khyams dgu pa la
NK022(za)001:1921: yang dri'i thig le shar nub tu bcu gsum bcu
NK022(za)001:1922: tshom bu bya'o // gsum / lho byang du bcu gnyis bcu gnyis drug cu bya /
NK022(za)001:1923: ma ma sha ra h'u zhes me tog gi phung po drug cu tham pa bya'o //
NK022(za)001:1924: de nas khyams bcu pa la sur+ya tsan+t+ra pad+ma man+dala zhes dri'i thig le bya /
NK022(za)001:1925: ma h+aa gu ru sha ri ra zhes me tog gi phung po ci rigs su bya'o //
NK022(za)001:1926: de yan chad dkyil 'khor sta gon la gnas pa'o //
NK022(za)001:1927: de nas don gnyis pa lha sta gon la gnas pa ni /
NK022(za)001:1929: nang du rtsa ba dang yan lag gi mchod pa bsham /
NK022(za)001:1932: ye nas mnyam nyid kyis bshags pa bya /
NK022(za)001:1935: mchod pa rnams byin gyis brlabs /
NK022(za)001:1936: de nas rang nyid kun bzang du gsal ba'i thugs
NK022(za)001:1937: kha nas h'u gnas pa la dkyil 'khor gyi 'og
NK022(za)001:1938: na yar la 'byung ba ri brtseg dang /
NK022(za)001:1939: zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor gdan dang bcas pa dbus kyi pho brang zlum po la bskyed /
NK022(za)001:1940: de'i nang du zhi ba'i lha rnams sngags kyis tshang bar bskyed /
NK022(za)001:1941: gsang bdag he ru kar gnas pa'i thugs kha nas /
NK022(za)001:1942: dkyil 'khor gyi 'og na yar dbang chen khro bo'i dkyil 'khor gdan dang bcas pa bskyed /
NK022(za)001:1943: de'i nang du khrag 'thung yab yum bcu /
NK022(za)001:1954: steng phyogs khro bo khro mo drug cu /
NK022(za)001:1955: shar du dung gi pho nya drug cu /
NK022(za)001:1956: lhor gser gyi pho nya drug cu /
NK022(za)001:1957: nub tu bse'i pho nya drug cu /
NK022(za)001:1958: byang du g.yu'i pho nya drug cu /
NK022(za)001:1959: 'og tu ma mo las byed drug cu /
NK022(za)001:1960: rig 'dzin la sogs pa thams cad sngags kyis rdzogs tshul du bskyed /
NK022(za)001:1961: zhi khro gnyis ka la dus gcig tu ye shes lngas dbang bskur /
NK022(za)001:1962: sku gsung thugs su byin gyis brlabs /
NK022(za)001:1963: sa man dzas snyan gsan dbab /
NK022(za)001:1964: e ha hi dang ru lus spyan drang /
NK022(za)001:1965: dza h'u ba hos gnyis su med par bstim /
NK022(za)001:1968: lha mo bzhi snol gyi mchod pa dbul /
NK022(za)001:1969: bdud rtsi'i zhi ba'i lha rnams la tshogs las ltar /
NK022(za)001:1971: khro bo la rtsa sngags kyis dbul /
NK022(za)001:1973: zhi ba'i lha rnams la su ra tos gtor ma dbul /
NK022(za)001:1974: khro bo la dza h'u ba hos dbul /
NK022(za)001:1975: zhi ba la gsang gnan gyis mchod /
NK022(za)001:1976: khro bo rak+ta tshar gsum dbul /
NK022(za)001:1978: gtum chen gyis bstod la dril bu bsil zhing dbyangs dang bcas pas /
NK022(za)001:1979: mgon po thugs rje che ldan pa //
NK022(za)001:1980: thams cad kun nas dgongs su gsol //
NK022(za)001:1981: deng gi gnas mchog dam pa 'dir //
NK022(za)001:1982: slob ma rnams kyi don phyir du //
NK022(za)001:1983: sang gi nang par gdugs bdal nas //
NK022(za)001:1984: dkyil 'khor chen po bzhengs gsol bas //
NK022(za)001:1985: sta gon la ni bzhugs nas kyang //
NK022(za)001:1986: byin rlabs dam pa mdzad du gsol //
NK022(za)001:1987: zhes brjod la dril bu bsil /
NK022(za)001:1988: de ni lha sta gon la gnas pa'o //
NK022(za)001:1989: de nas gsum pa bum pa sta gon la gnas
NK022(za)001:1990: pa dang yo byad sta gon la gnas pa bya
NK022(za)001:1991: ste / gang du yan lag rab gnas kyi skabs
NK022(za)001:1992: su bum pa lnga dkar zhal nas phyung ba rigs
NK022(za)001:1993: lnga'i phyag mtshan lngas mtshan pa de /
NK022(za)001:1994: rdo rje slob dpon gyi mdun du snam bu gtsang ma'i khar bzhag la /
NK022(za)001:1996: na mo phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs
NK022(za)001:1997: pa thams cad kyi sku dang gsung dang thugs dang
NK022(za)001:1998: yon tan dang phrin las dang bkod pa mi zad
NK022(za)001:1999: pa brgyan gyi 'khor lo'i bka' bden pa dang /
NK022(za)001:2000: bden pa yang dag pa dang /
NK022(za)001:2001: bden pa chen po'i byin gyis brlabs dang /
NK022(za)001:2002: bcom ldan 'das zhi khro gsang ba mchog gi dkyil 'khor bka' bden pa dang /
NK022(za)001:2003: bden pa chen po'i byin gyis brlabs kyis /
NK022(za)001:2004: rnal 'byor pa bdag cag gi slob ma 'di rnams
NK022(za)001:2005: kyi don du bum pa lha'i dkyil 'khor du bzhengs
NK022(za)001:2006: par 'tshal bas / bar du gcod pa'i bgegs dang
NK022(za)001:2007: 'byung po thams cad 'dir ma gnas par gzhan du
NK022(za)001:2008: par 'tshal bas / deng shig / h'u h'u h'u
NK022(za)001:2009: bi shwa badz+ra kro ta dz+wa la man+dala phata phata
NK022(za)001:2010: phata ha la ha la h'u phata /
NK022(za)001:2011: ces brjod nas rdo rje thogs te /
NK022(za)001:2012: nyungs dkar gtor bas bgegs thams cad bskrad par bsam /
NK022(za)001:2013: de'i rjes su bgegs kyis mi tshugs par bya ba'i phyir gu gul gyis bdug /
NK022(za)001:2014: de nas bkra shis par bya ba'i phyir spos kyis bdug /
NK022(za)001:2015: ra ya kha zhes bum pa'i dngos po dang mtshan ma'i skyon sbyangs la /
NK022(za)001:2016: swa b+ha ba shud+d+ho'i sngags kyis stong par bsam /
NK022(za)001:2017: de nas dbus kyi bum pa rdo rjes mtshan pa la b+h+ru gyi 'phro 'du las /
NK022(za)001:2018: b+h+ru bi sha bi shud+d+he'i sngags brjod pas zhi ba'i
NK022(za)001:2019: gzhal yas khang gdan dang bcas pa bskyed la bum
NK022(za)001:2020: pa'i nang du / nas sam nyungs dkar blug cing kun bzang yab yum gyis gtso byas nas /
NK022(za)001:2021: mdun du mi bskyod pa yab yum bskyed la lha
NK022(za)001:2022: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis rtsa sngags kyis rdzogs tshul du
NK022(za)001:2023: bskyed / de nas shar du rnam snang gis gtso byas pa'i lha bzhi bcu bskyed /
NK022(za)001:2026: byang du don grub kyis gtso byas pa bum lung
NK022(za)001:2027: bzhin lnga tshar nyi shu rtsa lnga'i rdzas la sogs
NK022(za)001:2028: pa so so rang rang gi bum pa la blug
NK022(za)001:2031: gzungs thag la sogs pa rigs dang mthun par bya'o //
NK022(za)001:2032: de nas khro bo gsang ba'i bum pa ni /
NK022(za)001:2033: ban d+ha dkar po la lcang lo can gnyis dar mthing dmar gyi khud du bzhag la /
NK022(za)001:2034: de'i nang du rdo rje rdzas slob dpon gyi gtso
NK022(za)001:2035: byas pa'i mched rdo rje'i spun du yod kyi grangs
NK022(za)001:2036: sman bzang po'i ri lu byas la bzhugs /
NK022(za)001:2037: de nas bum pa bsangs sbyangs /
NK022(za)001:2039: b+h+ru las 'dus pa chen po'i gzhal yas khang gdan dang bcas par bskyed la /
NK022(za)001:2040: gtso bo nas ma bdun sring bzhi yan chad bum pa'i nang gi nyungs dkar blug cing /
NK022(za)001:2042: lnga tshar nyi shu rtsa lnga'i rdzas 'bru bcud kyi phud tshang bar blug /
NK022(za)001:2043: de'i khar rdo rje bzhag la gzungs thag btags la /
NK022(za)001:2044: thod pa gcig gis kha bcad /
NK022(za)001:2045: kha dog lnga'i dar gyis kha bkab la bzhag /
NK022(za)001:2046: yang gcig tu 'di ltar bya ste /
NK022(za)001:2047: zhi ba'i bum pa lnga po rigs lnga rang rang du rdzogs par byin gyis brlabs nas /
NK022(za)001:2048: de nas khro bo'i bum pa la snod ban d+ha mtshan nyid dang ldan pa lnga /
NK022(za)001:2049: rigs lnga so so'i thugs mtshan bris la bsang /
NK022(za)001:2051: de nas dbus kyi bum pa la che mchog yab
NK022(za)001:2052: yum gyis gtso byas pa'i lha lnga brgya brgyad cu
NK022(za)001:2053: rtsa gsum dang / rig 'dzin rtsal 'chang thams cad tshang bar bkod /
NK022(za)001:2054: rigs pa bzhi'i bum pa la /
NK022(za)001:2055: rigs rang rang gis gtso byas pa'i lha lnga bcu
NK022(za)001:2056: rtsa brgyad po bkod la rdzas thams cad tshang bar
NK022(za)001:2057: blug ste / kha brgyan mgul chings /
NK022(za)001:2058: gzungs thag la sogs pa kun dang ldan par byas nas /
NK022(za)001:2059: zhi khro gnyis kyi bum pa rnams phyogs bzhi dbus dang lngar bzhag /
NK022(za)001:2060: man 'dzi'i steng du ka pa la lngar bdud rtsi blug /
NK022(za)001:2062: khar rdo rje gzungs thag btags nas /
NK022(za)001:2063: de nas zhi khro gnyis ka'i bum pa'i lha la dmigs la ye shes lngas dbang bskur /
NK022(za)001:2064: sku gsung thugs su byin gyis brlabs /
NK022(za)001:2065: rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor la sa man dzas snyan gsan dbab /
NK022(za)001:2067: dza h'u ba hos gnyis su med par bstim /
NK022(za)001:2068: ka ya wak+ka tsit+tasa brtan par bzhugs su gsol /
NK022(za)001:2069: kun bzang na mar mchod pa rnam lnga dbul /
NK022(za)001:2070: sman mchod la ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha hi zhes pas dbul /
NK022(za)001:2071: ma h+aa b+ha ling+ta kha hi zhes gtor ma dbul /
NK022(za)001:2073: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin ni rgyas par dbul /
NK022(za)001:2076: gtum chen gyis bstod la khro bo gsang ba'i bum pa'i gzungs thag nas lag pa g.yon gyis bzung /
NK022(za)001:2077: g.yas kyis phreng ba bsgrangs la /
NK022(za)001:2078: g+hu ya dz+nya na 'am ru lu cung zhig bzlas
NK022(za)001:2079: pas ting nge 'dzin ni bdag gi thugs kha nas
NK022(za)001:2080: 'od zer 'phros pas rdo rje la phog /
NK022(za)001:2081: rdo rje la 'od 'phros pas bum pa'i nang gi lha la thim /
NK022(za)001:2083: klad pa dung khang du song /
NK022(za)001:2085: rdo rje nas yum gyi mkhar babs /
NK022(za)001:2087: slar yum gyi zhal na mar byung /
NK022(za)001:2088: yang yab kyi zhal du thim /
NK022(za)001:2089: srog dag pa'i lam nas byung /
NK022(za)001:2091: yum gyi mkhar babs sbyor ba byas pa'i sbyor mtshams nas chu rgyun babs pas /
NK022(za)001:2094: ma h+aa te pa sa ta h'u /
NK022(za)001:2095: zhes brjod pas lha 'khor dang bcas pa bdud rtsi'i rgya mtshor mer gyis byung ste /
NK022(za)001:2096: bum pa gang bas dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs
NK022(za)001:2097: pa thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin
NK022(za)001:2098: las lnga dang / rigs lnga ye shes lnga'i yon tan yongs su rdzogs par bsam la /
NK022(za)001:2100: gsal ldan ma 'am byin brlabs las //
NK022(za)001:2102: dbyings nas dkyil 'khor spyan drangs mchod //
NK022(za)001:2103: mnyes nas grub pa'i dam tshig mchog /
NK022(za)001:2104: bdag nyid chen po mchod pa yis //
NK022(za)001:2105: sangs rgyas dkyil 'khor ma lus mnyes //
NK022(za)001:2106: srid gsum 'gro ba thams cad la //
NK022(za)001:2107: dga' ba chen pos khyab par gyur //
NK022(za)001:2108: sgyu 'phrul dra ba brtan pa yis //
NK022(za)001:2109: phyogs bcu dus bzhir gshegs pa yi //
NK022(za)001:2110: sangs rgyas dkyil 'khor ma lus dang //
NK022(za)001:2113: de nas zhi ba'i bum pa lnga po la /
NK022(za)001:2114: bum pa lnga po phyogs bzhi dbus dang lngar bzhag /
NK022(za)001:2115: dbus kyi bum pa'i mdun du thod pa dum bu gcig pa'i nang du 'bru bcud kyi phud blugs /
NK022(za)001:2116: de la a mri ta btab /
NK022(za)001:2117: khar rdo rje bzhag la bdud rtsi lngar byin gyis brlab /
NK022(za)001:2120: yang thugs kha nas 'od zer 'phros rdo rje la phog /
NK022(za)001:2121: de nas mar la babs pas bum pa'i lha la phog /
NK022(za)001:2123: glad pa dung khang du song /
NK022(za)001:2125: srog dag pa'i lam nas phyung /
NK022(za)001:2126: rdo rje nas yum gyi mkha' babs /
NK022(za)001:2128: yang yum gyi zhal nas yang byung /
NK022(za)001:2130: gong bzhin sbyor ba byas pas sbyor mtshams nas chu rgyun byung nas ka p+aa la gang /
NK022(za)001:2131: de la gong gi sngags brjod nas ban d+ha nas bdud rtsi thigs pa gsum blugs pas /
NK022(za)001:2132: lha gtso 'khor dang bcas pa bdud rtsir gyur te /
NK022(za)001:2133: bum pa gang bas dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs
NK022(za)001:2134: pa thams cad kyi rdo rje rigs kyi yon tan
NK022(za)001:2135: rdzogs par bsam / de nas shar lho nub byang
NK022(za)001:2136: du ban d+ha rdo rje dang bcas pa bzhag la
NK022(za)001:2137: rdzogs par bsam / / bsang sbyang gong bzhin bya /
NK022(za)001:2138: rang rang gi gnas dang phyogs su rigs bzhi 'khor bcas bskyed /
NK022(za)001:2139: rigs bzhi rang rang du rdzogs par byin gyis brlab pa gang bzhin bya /
NK022(za)001:2140: de rnams zin pa dang rol mos sna drangs la /
NK022(za)001:2141: rdo rje slob dpon gyis khro bo gsang ba'i bum pa bzung /
NK022(za)001:2142: zhi ba'i bum pa kun rgyal thebs la sogs pa kun la gtad la /
NK022(za)001:2143: dkyil 'khor gyi mtha' ma bskor zhing dbyangs dang bcas pas /
NK022(za)001:2144: h'u bum pa ma lags rgyal po lags //
NK022(za)001:2145: rgyal po'i sngags kyis btab nas kyang //
NK022(za)001:2146: rgyal po chen por mnga' gsol gyis //
NK022(za)001:2147: rgyal po'i tshul du bzhugs su gsol //
NK022(za)001:2148: zhes brjod la khro bo'i bum pa rang gi mdun du dgod /
NK022(za)001:2149: bum pa lnga po phyogs bzhi dbus dang lngar dgod pa'am /
NK022(za)001:2150: yang na rdo rje rgyal po'i mdun du gral rims su dgod /
NK022(za)001:2151: las thams cad pa'i bum pa khro bo bdud rtsi
NK022(za)001:2152: 'khyil par byin gyis rlabs la las mkhan gyi mdun
NK022(za)001:2153: du dgod do // de dag ni bum pa'i sta gon zhes bya'o //
NK022(za)001:2154: de nas yo byad byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK022(za)001:2155: der bsags pa'i yo byad la 'dus pa'i phud bsogs la /
NK022(za)001:2156: spyir byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK022(za)001:2157: ra ya kha gis rdzas kyi dngos po dang mtshan ma sbyangs la /
NK022(za)001:2159: sa ha ra na h'u zhes 'phros 'dus pas /
NK022(za)001:2160: tra rat+na tree lo kya man+dala h'u /
NK022(za)001:2161: zhes brjod pas yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin po che mi zad pa'i gter dang ldan pa /
NK022(za)001:2162: rin po che'i rtse mo la +aahmh'u gsum gyi 'od 'phros pas /
NK022(za)001:2163: phyi nang gsang ba'i longs spyod bsam gyis mi khyab pa 'byung bar bsam mo //
NK022(za)001:2164: bye brag tu brlab pa ni /
NK022(za)001:2165: yo byad de rnams tsho gsum du bcad la /
NK022(za)001:2166: tsho gcig bam ser po'i 'phro 'du las dpa' bo 'bru lngar bskyed la tshogs dang mchod pa bya /
NK022(za)001:2167: tsho gcig a dang ma'i 'phro 'du las /
NK022(za)001:2168: gtor ma byin gyis rlabs pa bzhin du 'dod yon du brlabs la sgrub pa po rnams rol /
NK022(za)001:2169: tsho gcig nam mkha' mdzod kyi sngags kyis mang zhing rgya che bar byin gyis brlabs la /
NK022(za)001:2171: lcogs na rtags pa drug gis byin gyis brlabs /
NK022(za)001:2172: de'i rjes su mched rdo rje'i spun rnams lha dang lha mo'i rang bzhin du byin gyis brlabs te /
NK022(za)001:2173: de dag ni yo byad kyi sta gon zhes bya'o //
NK022(za)001:2174: don lnga pa slob ma sta gon la gnas pa ni /
NK022(za)001:2175: nyi shu rtsa gnyis kyis ston te /
NK022(za)001:2176: rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi lhor man+dala bya ste /
NK022(za)001:2177: de la chag chag gdab cing pad+ma 'dab brgyad mdzes mtshon du byas la /
NK022(za)001:2178: so shing la sogs pa'i rdzas bsham /
NK022(za)001:2179: las mkhan gyis thun mong dang khyad par gyi mchod pa bshams la phrin las thugs lugs su /
NK022(za)001:2180: mtshams nas 'dzab dang bstod pa yan chad bya /
NK022(za)001:2181: de'i bar la slob bu rnams kyis khrus bya /
NK022(za)001:2183: bla ma'i g.yas phyogs su gral rim du 'dug la /
NK022(za)001:2184: bla ma la zhu ba ni /
NK022(za)001:2185: slob bu rnams kyis thal mo sbyar la bzod par gsol ba ni /
NK022(za)001:2186: ho mi gnas pa'i ye shes chen po'i bdag nyid /
NK022(za)001:2187: 'dus pa chen po'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs 'khor
NK022(za)001:2188: rgyal ba rgya mtsho zhing gi rdul snyed dang bcas
NK022(za)001:2189: pa rnams gsan cing dgongs su gsol lo //
NK022(za)001:2190: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi ba rnams 'khor ba las
NK022(za)001:2191: nges par phyung nas 'gro ba sems can rnams kyi
NK022(za)001:2193: byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed nas bslab pa mthar phyin par 'tshal bas /
NK022(za)001:2194: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi zhal bstan cing
NK022(za)001:2195: byin gyis brlabs pa dang dbang bskur du gsol lo
NK022(za)001:2197: smon 'jug gnyis kyi sgo nas e ma ngo mtshar lngas sems bskyed la gnang ba sbyin pa ni /
NK022(za)001:2198: rdo rje slob dpon badz+ra he ru kar bsgom la /
NK022(za)001:2199: e ma bde gshegs snying po las /
NK022(za)001:2201: ye nas lhun rdzogs sangs rgyas chos //
NK022(za)001:2202: khyed la rab tu bstan par bya //
NK022(za)001:2203: zhes brjod la slob bu rnams kyis phyag 'tshal lo //
NK022(za)001:2204: de nas spro ba bskyed pa'i phyir dkyil 'khor gyi don bshad de /
NK022(za)001:2206: gzugs brnyan lhag pa'i gzugs brnyan dang //
NK022(za)001:2208: byang chub sems dang tshogs mchog bstan //
NK022(za)001:2209: ces pa la sogs pa'i don bshad la /
NK022(za)001:2210: slob bu rnams kyis gsol ba gdab pa ni /
NK022(za)001:2211: bcom ldan che mchog he ru ka /
NK022(za)001:2213: thar lam chen po bdag 'dod de //
NK022(za)001:2214: de'i dbang dang dam tshig dang //
NK022(za)001:2215: mgon po dpa' bo skyabs song zhing //
NK022(za)001:2216: theg chen khang par bzhugs pa dang //
NK022(za)001:2217: mkhyen rabs ye shes bdag la stsol //
NK022(za)001:2219: de nas slob dpon gyis lan gnang bar sbyin pa ni /
NK022(za)001:2220: bu 'dir shog cig ci bde ba'i //
NK022(za)001:2221: las spyod rim par 'gro ba dang //
NK022(za)001:2222: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje zung //
NK022(za)001:2223: 'dus pa chen po'i dbang rdzogs sbyin //
NK022(za)001:2225: de nas bu rnams kyi glad pa'i dung khang du
NK022(za)001:2226: ma las nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor gyi 'phro 'du las
NK022(za)001:2228: a yu h'u dza zhes brjod pas tshe'i rang bzhin
NK022(za)001:2229: mi tig dkar po dri ma med par gyur par
NK022(za)001:2230: bsam / de nas yang glad pa'i dung khang du b+h+ru zhes pa'i 'phro 'du las /
NK022(za)001:2231: zla kha dmar po sgo gcig pa gcig bsam /
NK022(za)001:2232: de'i nang du badz+ra kro ta h'u ka ra h'u zhes pas h'u ka ra bskyed /
NK022(za)001:2233: badz+ra kro ta ar+ya a tsa la h'u zhes pas mi g.yo mgon pos sgo srung bar bsam /
NK022(za)001:2234: de nas sgrib pa bral ba ni /
NK022(za)001:2235: bdag nyid dpal du gsal ba'i sor mo bcu las
NK022(za)001:2236: nyi zla'i gdan gyi steng du yig 'bru bcu bkod
NK022(za)001:2237: la / rigs lnga yab yum gyi 'phro 'du byas nas /
NK022(za)001:2239: na mo phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs
NK022(za)001:2240: pa thams cad kyi bden pa chen po'i byin gyis
NK022(za)001:2241: brlabs kyis / gang zag 'di rnams kyi rgyud la
NK022(za)001:2242: gnas pa'i las dang nyon mongs pa'i sgrib pa dang
NK022(za)001:2243: brlabs kyis / / lta ba dman zhing shes rab zhan pa'i sgrib pa dang /
NK022(za)001:2244: khyad par du gsang sngags kyi dkyil 'khor chen po'i
NK022(za)001:2245: sgor zhugs nas gsang ba zab mo'i dbang nod pa
NK022(za)001:2246: la sgrib pa gangs kyi rim pa bzhin du gnas
NK022(za)001:2247: pa thams cad skad cig tsam la byang zhing dag
NK022(za)001:2248: par gyur cig / badz+ra b+han d+ha pra th+aa zhes
NK022(za)001:2249: brjod pas sgrib pa ma lus pa sregs sbyangs nas
NK022(za)001:2250: par gyur cig / / sems nyid shel sgong lta bur gyur par bsam /
NK022(za)001:2251: de ka la badz+ra a be sha ya a a /
NK022(za)001:2252: zhes brjod pas gong gi khro bo 'od du zhu nas las bkrag dang ldan par bsam la /
NK022(za)001:2254: sngar bskyed pa'i lhar bskyed la /
NK022(za)001:2255: go bgo lus srungs byas la bzhag /
NK022(za)001:2256: de nas slob bus phyag byas la /
NK022(za)001:2258: dpa' bo rdo rje 'dzin pa khyed //
NK022(za)001:2260: sdug bsngal chu bo rgyun bzlog pa //
NK022(za)001:2261: don gnyis bdag gis mngon bya'i phyir //
NK022(za)001:2262: thabs kyi las mtha' gang lags pa //
NK022(za)001:2263: rim pa yang dag bstan bya'i phyir //
NK022(za)001:2264: thugs rje nye bar spyod mdzad de //
NK022(za)001:2265: di ring gnas par mdzad du gsol //
NK022(za)001:2267: slob bu rnams kyi lus ngag yid gsum sku gsung thugs su byin gyis ba rlabs la /
NK022(za)001:2268: dpal ldan rdo rje sku gsung thugs 'chang ba //
NK022(za)001:2269: rdo rje mi phyed sku gsung thugs dang ldan //
NK022(za)001:2270: ding nas bdag la byin gyis brlabs nas su //
NK022(za)001:2271: rdo rje sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub sbyin //
NK022(za)001:2272: +aahmh'u zhes bdud rtsi lce thog tu bzhag la /
NK022(za)001:2274: wa ka sid+d+hi +aah tsit+ta sid+hi h'u /
NK022(za)001:2275: sarba ta tha ga ta ka ya waka tsit+ta badz+ra swa b+ha ba ad ma ko&a ham /
NK022(za)001:2276: zhes brjod la gnas gsum du rdo rjes gtug go //
NK022(za)001:2277: de nas slob bu rnams las mkhan gyis man+dala gyi rtsar drangs la /
NK022(za)001:2278: rdo rje slob dpon gyis rdo rje'i phyed lag tu gtad la /
NK022(za)001:2279: bdag ni las mchog skal bar ldan //
NK022(za)001:2280: ding nas theg pa chen po la //
NK022(za)001:2281: brtan par bya phyir bdag la ni //
NK022(za)001:2282: ye shes srung ba mdzad du gsol //
NK022(za)001:2284: big nan ta krid a mri ta kun d+ha li h'u phata /
NK022(za)001:2288: de nas badz+ra dz+hi ha sa b+ha ra pra ti ni h'u phata /
NK022(za)001:2290: so shing byin la sbom pos lce bzhar /
NK022(za)001:2292: de nas man+dala gyi steng du bud thabs su mkha' dbyings kyi phyag rgya bcas pa'i bar nas bskur /
NK022(za)001:2294: byang shar du 'gyel na bskyar ro //
NK022(za)001:2295: de nas badz+ra rak+sha rak+sha h'u phata /
NK022(za)001:2296: ces srung skud byas la pho'i dpung pa g.yas /
NK022(za)001:2297: mo'i dpung pa g.yon la bcings /
NK022(za)001:2302: badz+ra ki li ki la yas phur pa sras mchog tu byin gyis brlabs la sbyin /
NK022(za)001:2303: mched lcam gyis phyag byas la sems rtse gcig tu 'dug go //
NK022(za)001:2304: de nas sa tshon rnam pa lngas byang shar gyi
NK022(za)001:2305: mtshams nas re ga mdzub gang ba zhig drangs la
NK022(za)001:2306: / zangs gzhong gis kha bkab la rdo rjes mnan la bzhag go //
NK022(za)001:2307: de nas dbang gi gleng gzhi bshad de /
NK022(za)001:2308: de yang rgyal ba sku gsum po rim par brgyud pa'i mthar ni /
NK022(za)001:2309: dbang gi chu bo chen po bzhi zhes grags pa las /
NK022(za)001:2310: theg pa'i rim pa'i chu bo chen po bzhi ni /
NK022(za)001:2311: yo ga la sogs theg drug las //
NK022(za)001:2312: phyi dbang brgyud kyi chu bo bya //
NK022(za)001:2313: bskyed pa ma h+aa yo ga la //
NK022(za)001:2314: nang dbang 'byung ba'i chu bo bya //
NK022(za)001:2315: rdzogs pa a nu yo ga la //
NK022(za)001:2316: bsgrub dbang grags pa'i chu bo bya //
NK022(za)001:2317: rdzogs chen a ti yo ga la //
NK022(za)001:2318: gsang ba man ngag gi chu bo bya /
NK022(za)001:2319: zhes pa rnams ni theg pa'i rim pa'i chu bo zhes bya ba yin /
NK022(za)001:2321: phyi nang gi chos thams cad rgya gar chos kyi rgyal po las byung ste /
NK022(za)001:2322: de yang dbang gi chu bo chen po lnga zhes bya bar grags te /
NK022(za)001:2323: de la rgya gar gyi slob dpon chen po pad+ma sa b+ha bas /
NK022(za)001:2325: des gshen che mchog shes rab la dbang bskur /
NK022(za)001:2326: des dar rje dpal gyi grags pa la bskur /
NK022(za)001:2327: des ye shes blo gros la dbang bskur /
NK022(za)001:2328: des mnyos nyi ma rgyal po la dbang bskur te /
NK022(za)001:2329: de dag ni lung gi spyi sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba dang /
NK022(za)001:2330: gzhung don thabs kyi zhags pa'i dbang gi lugs te /
NK022(za)001:2331: chu bo chen po gcig ces bya'o //
NK022(za)001:2332: yang rgya gar gyi slob dpon chen po rdo rje bzhad pas rdo rje grags pa la dbang bskur /
NK022(za)001:2333: des kyang mnyos nyi ma rgyal po la dbang bskur te /
NK022(za)001:2334: de dag ni sku gsung thugs gsang ba sde gsum gyi dbang yin te /
NK022(za)001:2335: dbang gi chu bo chen po gnyis /
NK022(za)001:2336: rnam gcig tu yang rgya gar gyi slob dpon h'u ka ras /
NK022(za)001:2337: nam mkha'i snying po la dbang bskur /
NK022(za)001:2338: des mkhar chen dpal gyi grags pa la /
NK022(za)001:2339: des skyo stag gi rdo rje la /
NK022(za)001:2340: des la byid ye shes rtsegs pa la /
NK022(za)001:2341: des lo dpal gyi blo gros la /
NK022(za)001:2342: des dpal gyi grags pa la /
NK022(za)001:2343: des kyang mnyos nyi ma rgyal po la dbang bskur te /
NK022(za)001:2344: de dag ni dpal yang dag gi lugs te dbang gi chu bo gsum /
NK022(za)001:2345: yang rgya gar gyi slob dpon bye ma la mu tras /
NK022(za)001:2346: gnyags dz+nya na ku ma ra la dbang bskur /
NK022(za)001:2347: des 'o bran dpal gyi gzhon nu la /
NK022(za)001:2348: des dar rje dpal gyi grags pa la /
NK022(za)001:2349: des ye shes blo gros la /
NK022(za)001:2350: des kyang mnyos nyi ma'i rgyal po la dbang bskur te /
NK022(za)001:2351: de dag ni lung dang man ngag gi dbang bskur te /
NK022(za)001:2352: dbang gi chu bo chen po bzhi zhes bya /
NK022(za)001:2353: yang rnam gcig tu rgya gar gyi slob dpon chen po sangs rgyas gsang bas /
NK022(za)001:2354: a tsa ra man dzu sh+ri la dbang bskur /
NK022(za)001:2355: des lang gsum rgyal ba'i byang chub la /
NK022(za)001:2356: des lang gsum g.yu skra la /
NK022(za)001:2357: des ru ye shes blo gros la /
NK022(za)001:2358: des kyang mnyos nyi ma'i rgyal po la dbang bskur te /
NK022(za)001:2359: de dag ni yo ga phyi'i dbang bskur te dbang gi chu bo chen po lnga zhes bya'o //
NK022(za)001:2360: de dag ni so so rang rang nas brgyud pa'i
NK022(za)001:2361: khungs kyi dbang gi chu bo chen po zhes bya'o
NK022(za)001:2362: // de dag las rgya gar gyi dbang gi chu bor grags lugs bzhi dang /
NK022(za)001:2363: bod du dbang gi chu bor grags lugs bzhi las /
NK022(za)001:2365: yi dam gyi lhas dbang bskur nas thob pa dang /
NK022(za)001:2366: bka' brgyud brtags kyi dbang bskur nas thob pa dang /
NK022(za)001:2367: rigs pa rtsal gyi dbang bskur nas thob pa dang /
NK022(za)001:2368: dge ba'i bshes gnyen mkhas btsun gyis dbang bskur nas thob pa dang bzhi'o //
NK022(za)001:2369: de la yi dam lhas dbang bskur nas thob pa ni /
NK022(za)001:2370: slob dpon chen po dga' rab rdo rje ste /
NK022(za)001:2371: dpal rdo rje sems dpa' dngos su byon nas dbang bskur te /
NK022(za)001:2372: byang chub kyi sems ye nas ma bcos pa /
NK022(za)001:2373: ye nas lhun gyis grub par gnas par bshad pa de yin no //
NK022(za)001:2374: de ni zab mo dbang gi brgyud pa ste dbang bskur ba'i skabs su shes par byos shig /
NK022(za)001:2375: bka' brgyud kyi dbang bskur nas thob pa ni /
NK022(za)001:2376: rgyal po dza zhes pa de nyid yin te /
NK022(za)001:2377: de yang rgyal ba dgongs pas brgyud /
NK022(za)001:2379: gang zag rna bas nas rna bar brgyud de /
NK022(za)001:2380: rgyal ba kun tu bzang pos 'khor rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas la bshad /
NK022(za)001:2381: des rigs gsum mgon po la bshad /
NK022(za)001:2382: de la rig pa 'dzin pa mi ma yin pa la brgyud pa dang /
NK022(za)001:2383: mi dang mi ma yin pa gnyis ka la brgyud pa rnam pa gnyis las /
NK022(za)001:2384: dang po ni rigs gsum gyis lha klu gnod sbyin
NK022(za)001:2385: gsum gyi gnas gsum du rang rang dang mthun par
NK022(za)001:2386: chos bstan to // don gnyis pa rig pa 'dzin
NK022(za)001:2387: pa mi dang mi ma yin pa gnyis ka la
NK022(za)001:2388: chos bstan to // brgyud pa ni / rigs gsum gyi nang nas drag shul can gyi mchog /
NK022(za)001:2389: gsang ba'i bdag po phyag na rdo rje de sangs
NK022(za)001:2390: rgyas thub pa mya ngan las 'das nas lo nyi
NK022(za)001:2391: shu rtsa brgyad lon pa'i dus su /
NK022(za)001:2392: ma la ya'i rtser dam pa'i rigs can lnga la chos kyi 'khor lo bskor te /
NK022(za)001:2393: de yang ji ltar zhe na /
NK022(za)001:2394: za hor gyi rgyal khams zhes bya ba'i nye 'khor na /
NK022(za)001:2395: ston pas zhabs kyis bcags pa'i sa phyag na rdo rje'i pho brang /
NK022(za)001:2396: byang phyogs lcang lo can gyi gnas /
NK022(za)001:2397: ri ma la ya na gnam lcags thog yod pa'i rtse mo zhes bya ba cig yod do //
NK022(za)001:2398: ri de yang rtse mo ri dwags kyi rgyal po seng ge'i 'khra sar gyur pa /
NK022(za)001:2399: 'dab shod ni gcan zan gyi rgyal po stag gi 'khra sar gyur pa /
NK022(za)001:2405: 'bras bu'i sman sna tshogs kyi shing skyes pa /
NK022(za)001:2406: ngos la brag dkar po seng ge khyi tshugs su
NK022(za)001:2407: bsdad pa 'dra ba grangs dang grangs kyis yod pa
NK022(za)001:2408: / de'i shar ngos na tri shang a su ra
NK022(za)001:2409: ba zhes bya ba gnod sbyin gyi phug yod de
NK022(za)001:2410: / / de yang sgo zla kham la ngo mtshar gyi ri mo rang byung ba /
NK022(za)001:2411: phugs rin po che zur brgyad la nyi zla'i ri mo rang snang ba /
NK022(za)001:2412: ri de'i spyi bo na bya ka lan ta ka zhes bya ba /
NK022(za)001:2413: don gnyis par mi sgrogs te gcig tu sgrogs par byed pa'i tshang bcas pa /
NK022(za)001:2414: dper na gnas der gang zag las dang skal bar ldan pa rnams kyis bgrod cing phyin pa las /
NK022(za)001:2415: las dang skal ba med pa rnams kyis bgrod cing phyin par mi nus pa'o //
NK022(za)001:2416: de lta bu'i gnas khyad par can der gsang ba'i
NK022(za)001:2417: bdag pos dam pa'i rigs can lnga la chos kyi
NK022(za)001:2418: 'khor lo bskor ba'i byin brlabs kyis /
NK022(za)001:2419: shar phyogs za hor gyi yul /
NK022(za)001:2420: a pa tra mu dz+nya na zhes pa na /
NK022(za)001:2421: rgyal po'i rigs can gsang sngags go ba'i skal ba dang ldan pa /
NK022(za)001:2422: 'gugs pa'i sgra dza zhes bya ba'i mig can de la /
NK022(za)001:2423: gsang sngags mi yul du 'byung ba'i ltas bdun shar te /
NK022(za)001:2424: dang po ni ri de'i rtse mor dpal phyag na rdo rje'i pho brang byon nas /
NK022(za)001:2425: sku'i khru bdun las 'od sngon po 'phros pas 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad sregs /
NK022(za)001:2426: gsung gi sgra 'brug stong lta bur ldir /
NK022(za)001:2427: thugs kyi dkyil 'khor nas rdo rje 'od 'bar ba
NK022(za)001:2428: cig shar bas rgyal po nyid kyi thugs khar thim
NK022(za)001:2429: / nyi ma 'od 'bar ba zhig shar bas spyi bor thim /
NK022(za)001:2430: zla ba 'od 'bar ba cig shar bas /
NK022(za)001:2431: rgyal po'i rkang mthil du thim nas snang srid kyi
NK022(za)001:2432: ltos thams cad rgyal po'i lto ba na 'phyo ba
NK022(za)001:2433: gcig rmis so // gnyis pa ni sangs rgyas thams
NK022(za)001:2434: cad dang chos kyi sgrog gleng mdzad cing nyi zla
NK022(za)001:2435: la zhon te gser gyi 'khor lo bskor nas srid
NK022(za)001:2436: pa gsum la dbang bsgyur ba zhig rmis so //
NK022(za)001:2437: gsum pa ni nam mkha' la sprin gser gyi kha dog can 'khrigs /
NK022(za)001:2438: cho 'phrul gyi 'brug sgra snyan par tshim pa ni grag /
NK022(za)001:2439: rin po che sna tshogs kyi smug pa ni 'thibs //
NK022(za)001:2440: rin po che bee d+aur+ya'i 'od ni byung /
NK022(za)001:2441: snang srid gsal ba'i glog ni 'gyus nas /
NK022(za)001:2442: rin chen sna tshogs kyi char mngon par bab pa zhig rmis /
NK022(za)001:2443: bzhi pa ni 'jig rten gyi gtos po kun ni bsgyur /
NK022(za)001:2444: rin po che sgron me 'bar ba shar bas snang srid kyi mun pa thams cad ni sangs /
NK022(za)001:2445: bdud rtsi dang sman gyi chu rgyun byung bas 'gro ba thams cad kyi gcong rnying ni sbyangs /
NK022(za)001:2446: 'gro ba thams cad rdo rje rnal 'byor zhes pa'i sgra ti ri ri sgrogs pa zhig rmis so //
NK022(za)001:2447: lnga pa ni sprin gyi nang nas nyi ma'i dkyil
NK022(za)001:2448: 'khor la rin po che sna tshogs kyi 'od zer
NK022(za)001:2449: can gcig shar ba'ii dkyil na /
NK022(za)001:2450: rin po che smug po dpal be'u'i sgro 'dos bcas pa phyi nang med par gsal ba'i nang nas /
NK022(za)001:2451: gser gyi glegs bam la bee d+aur+ya zhun mas rang
NK022(za)001:2452: gnad du bris pa'i glegs bam mang po zhig gis
NK022(za)001:2453: gtams pa skar mda' ltung ba bzhin du babs pa
NK022(za)001:2454: zhig rmis so // drug pa ni yang glegs bam dang po ti de rnams la /
NK022(za)001:2455: byang chub sems dpa' dang rig 'dzin dang lha dang
NK022(za)001:2456: lha mo tshad med pa rnams yon tan gyi sgra
NK022(za)001:2458: gar gyi ling long dang rol mo'i cha byad mang po 'don bskor ba zhig rmis so //
NK022(za)001:2459: bdun pa ni nam mkha'i sprin gseb nas lung bstan pa'i sgra byung ste /
NK022(za)001:2460: las dang skal bar rab ldan zhing //
NK022(za)001:2461: rgyal bas 'byung bar lung bstan pa'i //
NK022(za)001:2462: bsod nams chen po'i dra ma khyod //
NK022(za)001:2463: sprul pas ji ltar lung bstan bzhin //
NK022(za)001:2464: da lta dus 'dir mngon shar gyis //
NK022(za)001:2465: 'khor ba'i snying po sbyang ba'i phyir //
NK022(za)001:2466: nga yi cho 'phrul byin rlabs kyis //
NK022(za)001:2467: bstan pa'i snying po dam pa zhig /
NK022(za)001:2468: skal ldan khyod la bstan par bya //
NK022(za)001:2469: ma la ya zhes bya ba'i ri //
NK022(za)001:2470: dgon pa chen po'i gnas zhig na //
NK022(za)001:2471: ye shes snying po can rnams kyi //
NK022(za)001:2472: gsang bar bya ba dam pa zhig /
NK022(za)001:2473: yod kyis gsang bar nan tan gyis //
NK022(za)001:2474: de la sems kyi me long gyis //
NK022(za)001:2475: mngon du gsal bar rtog ma thag /
NK022(za)001:2476: sangs rgyas pa la bskal ba mnyam //
NK022(za)001:2477: bde ba can zhes bya ba'i ri //
NK022(za)001:2478: 'od kyi rgyal po zhes bya ba'i //
NK022(za)001:2479: kun rigs bde ba chen por 'gyur //
NK022(za)001:2480: rdo rje gsang chen gsang ba yi //
NK022(za)001:2481: dam pa'i mdzod gsum rabs ga cig ni //
NK022(za)001:2483: rim par brgyud de grags par 'gyur //
NK022(za)001:2484: zhes lung bstan pa rmis so //
NK022(za)001:2485: de nas rgyal po gnyid sad nas rab tu dga' ste 'khor mang du bsdus nas /
NK022(za)001:2486: rmi lam du ji ltar byung ba'i tshul rnams bzlas nas /
NK022(za)001:2487: rmi lam 'di dag dang sbyar na bdag las dang skal bar ldan par nges so //
NK022(za)001:2488: zhes gsungs nas pho brang gi yang thog tu phyin pas /
NK022(za)001:2489: rmi lam du ji ltar byung ba dang mthun par /
NK022(za)001:2490: dpal phyag na rdo rje'i sku gzugs rin po che las grub pa zhig mthong nas /
NK022(za)001:2491: rgyal po dga' ste bskor ba dang mchod pa byas nas /
NK022(za)001:2493: sngon tshe gong nas bsnyen pa yi //
NK022(za)001:2494: las kyis mjal ba'i lha mchog 'di //
NK022(za)001:2495: bskal ba brgyar yang mi gtong /
NK022(za)001:2496: e ma ho ngo mtshar rmad kyi sku //
NK022(za)001:2497: 'dren pa'i mchog gi dpal lags gang //
NK022(za)001:2498: mos pas gzungs kyi lha mchog 'dzin //
NK022(za)001:2499: zhes gsol nas yi dam du bcas so //
NK022(za)001:2500: de nas yang rgyal po'i thugs dgongs la brtags 'di dang ldan pa dang /
NK022(za)001:2501: ri bo 'di yang dpal phyag na rdo rje'i rang bzhin du 'dug pa dang /
NK022(za)001:2502: rig 'dzin mang po grub pa thob pa'i gnas yin pa gtam snying du thos pa dang /
NK022(za)001:2503: rmi lam dang mthun pa'i ltas rnams kyang nam mkha' la mngon du snang ba dang /
NK022(za)001:2504: gcan gzan gdug pa can rnams kyang dge ba can
NK022(za)001:2505: la dad pa'i tshul 'di dag dang ldan pas nges
NK022(za)001:2507: gzugs brnyan de la brten nas zla ba bdun du bsgrubs pas /
NK022(za)001:2508: rmi lam du ji ltar byung ba dang tshul mthun par /
NK022(za)001:2509: glegs bam dang po ti mang po'i char mngon sum du babs nas /
NK022(za)001:2510: yang phyag na rdo rje'i sku gzugs de nyid kyi mdun du rang byung du byon nas /
NK022(za)001:2511: der po ti rnams la rgyal po rab tu dga' ba'i tshul gyis bltas pas /
NK022(za)001:2512: tshig 'bru gcig gi yang bda' ma 'byed nas the tshom du gyur te /
NK022(za)001:2513: e ma ho sngags kyi tshul rtags 'di dang ldan
NK022(za)001:2514: na glegs bam 'di rnams la zab mo gsang ba'i
NK022(za)001:2515: don zhig yin par nges na /
NK022(za)001:2516: bdag gis ma rtogs pa 'di cis nyes bsnyams nas bshums so //
NK022(za)001:2517: de nas yang cung zad cig nas the tshom gyi nyon mongs pa zhi ste /
NK022(za)001:2518: da yang 'jig rten gyi khams na 'di dag bda' 'byed pa su zhig yod ces bsgrags pas /
NK022(za)001:2519: za hor gyi rgyal po u ra tsa zhes bya ba'i bshes gnyen can yod pas /
NK022(za)001:2520: des shes par rigs so thos nas pho nya bardzangasa te /
NK022(za)001:2521: lo rgyus zhib tu gsol nas spyan drangs pas /
NK022(za)001:2522: slob dpon gyi zhal nas gal te bdag gis ma
NK022(za)001:2523: shes na der phyin pa tshul ma yin par 'gyur
NK022(za)001:2524: gyi / de dag glang po che la bkal la 'dir skyol cig ces gsung nas /
NK022(za)001:2525: po ti de dag glang po che la bkal te bskyal bas /
NK022(za)001:2526: btags pas tshig 'bru gcig kyang ma shes nas /
NK022(za)001:2527: 'di dag bdag gi spyod yul du ma gyur kyis /
NK022(za)001:2528: rgyal po nyid kyi dgongs pa'i rtsal gyis dpag 'tshal lo //
NK022(za)001:2529: zhes slar bardzangasa pas rgyal po'i thugs dgongs la /
NK022(za)001:2530: 'di dag la kun gyi thun mong ma yin pa
NK022(za)001:2531: ngo mtshar rmad du byung ba'i don zhig yod par
NK022(za)001:2532: nges pas / sangs rgyas kyi chos thos pa'i gzhung las byung ba bzhin du /
NK022(za)001:2535: mchod pa rgya chen po byas nas brtags pas /
NK022(za)001:2536: rdo rje sems dpa' bsgrub pa'i le'u bda' 'byed par gyur to //
NK022(za)001:2537: de nas le'u de'i gzhung bzhin du bsgrub pas /
NK022(za)001:2538: rdo rje sems dpa'i zhal bstan nas /
NK022(za)001:2539: rigs kyi bu dngos grub ci 'dod gsungs pas /
NK022(za)001:2540: bdag ni po ti dang glegs bam 'di rnams kyi don rtogs par 'tshal lo zhes zhus pas /
NK022(za)001:2541: lan du rigs kyi bu rang gi rgyud sbyongs dang /
NK022(za)001:2542: khyod kyi ston pa ni gsang ba'i bdag pos don ma lus pa bston par 'gyur ro //
NK022(za)001:2543: zhes gsung nas mi snang bar gyur to //
NK022(za)001:2544: de nas yang rang gi rgyud sbyangs pas dpal phyag na rdo rje mngon sum du byon nas /
NK022(za)001:2545: de'i tshe nyid kyis rdo rje nam mkha' la yar nas brdal zhugs mdzad de /
NK022(za)001:2546: h'u h'u h'u rdo rje 'du bar 'dus pa rnams //
NK022(za)001:2547: rigs ma yin pa rigs min 'gyur //
NK022(za)001:2548: skal ldan can gyi rigs su 'gyur //
NK022(za)001:2549: thams cad rdo rje gsang ba por //
NK022(za)001:2550: rak+sha kro ta tsit+ta dz+wa la ra /
NK022(za)001:2551: zhes brjod pas 'jig rten gyi dregs pa can thams
NK022(za)001:2552: cad rdo khab len la lcags 'du ba'i tshul du
NK022(za)001:2554: de dag la rdo rje gsang ba'i ming so sor
NK022(za)001:2555: btags nas grub pa lung gi gsang sgo phye ste
NK022(za)001:2557: tan tra sde bco brgyad la sogs pa rgyal po
NK022(za)001:2558: dza dang dam pa'i rigs can lnga la bshad de
NK022(za)001:2559: / de rnams ni rig 'dzin rig pa'i brgyud pa zhes bya'o //
NK022(za)001:2560: gang zag snyan khung brgyud pa ni /
NK022(za)001:2561: de dag gi nang nas rgyal po dza dang /
NK022(za)001:2562: mi las dge ba snyen chen po li tsa byi dri ma med par grags pas /
NK022(za)001:2563: rgyal po u pa ra tsa la bshad /
NK022(za)001:2564: des sh+aakya su tri la bshad /
NK022(za)001:2565: des sras mo go ma de byi la bshad /
NK022(za)001:2566: des gsang 'dzin ka ma la shi la la bshad /
NK022(za)001:2567: des a tsa ra dz+ai na mi tra la bshad /
NK022(za)001:2568: des rdo rje bzhad pa la bshad /
NK022(za)001:2570: des sti ra ma ti la bshad /
NK022(za)001:2572: des bde ba gsal mdzad la bshad /
NK022(za)001:2573: des sh+aakya de ba la bshad /
NK022(za)001:2574: des blo gros de ba la bshad /
NK022(za)001:2575: des rdo rje sgyegs pa la bshad /
NK022(za)001:2576: des chos blon de ba la bshad /
NK022(za)001:2577: des mkhan po chos rgyal skyong la bshad /
NK022(za)001:2578: des d+harma b+ho de la bshad /
NK022(za)001:2579: de dag ni rgya gar gyi brgyud pa yin no //
NK022(za)001:2580: de nas bod kyi yul du brgyud lugs ni /
NK022(za)001:2581: dus der slob dpon chen po gnubs sangs rgyas ye
NK022(za)001:2582: shes rin po che zhes bya ba lo lnga bcu
NK022(za)001:2583: rtsa bzhi lon pa zhig gis bal yul du phyin
NK022(za)001:2584: nas bal po ba su d+ha ra la /
NK022(za)001:2585: yon phul mnyes par byas sgra skad slabs chos zhus pas gnang nas /
NK022(za)001:2586: slob dpon gyi gsung nas rgya gar gyi yul na /
NK022(za)001:2587: nga'i slob dpon chen po gsal ba'i brgyan zhes bya ba /
NK022(za)001:2588: lo stong drug brgya lon pa gcig bzhugs kyis /
NK022(za)001:2589: khyod de'i spyan sngar song zhig gsung nas gnubs sangs rgyas kyis rgya gar yul du phyin pas /
NK022(za)001:2590: a tsar+ya gsal ba'i brgyan mthong nas /
NK022(za)001:2591: gsang sngags kyi rgyud sde mang po zhus pas gnang /
NK022(za)001:2592: 'dus pa chen po mdo'i theg pa rim dgu'i dbang yang bskur skad do //
NK022(za)001:2593: de nas sangs rgyas ye shes kyis /
NK022(za)001:2594: ru chos rgyal skyong zhes bya ba dpal dgongs pa
NK022(za)001:2595: 'dus pa phul du gyur pa de bru zha'i yul
NK022(za)001:2596: du bzhud nas / yang phyin pas /
NK022(za)001:2597: slob dpon d+harma ra tsa dang /
NK022(za)001:2599: d+ha na raka shi ta dang /
NK022(za)001:2600: lo ts+aa ba che btsan skyes dang /
NK022(za)001:2601: thams cad tshogs pa'i zhal mthong nas chos zhus pa gnang ste /
NK022(za)001:2602: sangs rgyas ye shes rin po che la bshad /
NK022(za)001:2603: des pa kor blon chen 'phags pa dang /
NK022(za)001:2605: so ye shes dbang phyug dang /
NK022(za)001:2607: de rnams la tsan dan gyi sdong po lta bur gnang ste /
NK022(za)001:2608: de la pa kor gyis rtsa ba khyer /
NK022(za)001:2612: gnubs kyis rangs sa khyer te /
NK022(za)001:2615: 'bras bu ma lus par khyer ba ni yon tan rgya mtsho yin no //
NK022(za)001:2616: gdams ngag gi dbang du byas na /
NK022(za)001:2618: gnubs sangs rgyas ye shes la da mnyam bzhag gi dbang man ngag cig zhu 'tshal byas pas /
NK022(za)001:2619: bsam gtan mig gi sgron ma gnang ngo //
NK022(za)001:2620: de ltar thugs kyi sras bzhi la sogs pas /
NK022(za)001:2621: zhu bsod nams sh+aakya la bshad /
NK022(za)001:2622: des bde gshegs zur po che la /
NK022(za)001:2624: des glan nya tshal ba sh+aakya byang chub la /
NK022(za)001:2626: yang zur po ches zur chung la /
NK022(za)001:2627: des chu dbar gyi glan sh+aakya bzang po la /
NK022(za)001:2630: des lha rje chen po glan rdo rje 'od la /
NK022(za)001:2631: des bla chen bsod rgyal la /
NK022(za)001:2632: des dpal ldan chos kyi seng ge la /
NK022(za)001:2633: des bla ma se cig mo ba la /
NK022(za)001:2634: khong gnyis la glan pan bsod nams mgon po bdag
NK022(za)001:2635: gis gtad rgya dang bcas nas zhus pa lags so
NK022(za)001:2636: // des dpal ldan bla ma dam pa bsam grub rdo rje la gnang /
NK022(za)001:2637: des rin po che zur ha sh+aakya 'byung gnas la /
NK022(za)001:2638: de nyid kyi drung nas bdag bo d+hi rat+na ma
NK022(za)001:2639: ti gnyis la gtad rgya dang bcas pa gnang ngo
NK022(za)001:2640: // de dag bka' brgyud kyi dbang bskur nas thob pa zhes pa'am /
NK022(za)001:2641: dge ba'i bshes gnyen gyis dbang bskur thob pa zhes bya /
NK022(za)001:2642: khyad par du rgyal po chen po dza nyid ni
NK022(za)001:2643: bka' brgyud kyi dbang bskur nas thob pa zhes bya'o
NK022(za)001:2644: // rang rig pa rtsal gyi dbang bskur nas thob pa ni /
NK022(za)001:2646: phyi nang gi chos thams cad rang gi rig pa
NK022(za)001:2647: byang chub kyi sems nyid rdo rje sems dpa'i ngo
NK022(za)001:2648: bo yin par rig pa la rang shar te /
NK022(za)001:2651: dug gsum rtsad nas bcad nas /
NK022(za)001:2652: rang gis rtogs nas dbang thob pa ste /
NK022(za)001:2653: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las su rang bzhin gyis lhun gyis grub pa'o //
NK022(za)001:2654: dge ba'i bshes gnyen gyis dbang bskur nas thob pa ni /
NK022(za)001:2655: slob dpon chen po bi ma la mi tra ste /
NK022(za)001:2656: rgya gar gyi rgyal po la bod kyi rgyal pos gser bskur nas /
NK022(za)001:2657: bdag la chos thams cad kyi de kho na nyid
NK022(za)001:2658: kyi don la mkhas pa'i pan+ti ta gcig gtang 'tshal
NK022(za)001:2659: ces bang chen pa zhig bardzangasa pas /
NK022(za)001:2660: rgya gar gyi rgyal pos mchod gnas pan+ti ta lnga brgya rtsa gcig bzhugs pa la bka' stsal pas /
NK022(za)001:2661: pan+ti ta lnga brgya rtsa gcig yod pa'i dkyil na
NK022(za)001:2662: slob dpon b+hi ma la bzhugs pa la kun gyis
NK022(za)001:2663: gzigs nas / brda' yis bskul bas /
NK022(za)001:2664: b+hi ma las rig nas bod du byon te /
NK022(za)001:2665: de ni dge ba'i bshes gnyen pan+ti ta lnga brgyas dbang bskur nas mdzad pa'o //
NK022(za)001:2666: de dag ni rgya gar gyi chu bo chen po bzhi zhes bya'o //
NK022(za)001:2667: rgya gar nas bod du byon pa'i pan+ti ta bzhi ni /
NK022(za)001:2669: b+hi ma la mi tra dang /
NK022(za)001:2671: sangs rgyas gsang ba dang bzhi byon pa las /
NK022(za)001:2672: b+hu d+ha kug ta ni gangs ti se nas slar
NK022(za)001:2673: log nas rgya gar du gshegs te bod kyi lha
NK022(za)001:2674: sras khri srong lde'u btsun gyis dbu mdzad pa la
NK022(za)001:2675: gdams ngag rnams dris nas phar gshegs so //
NK022(za)001:2676: shan ting garba ni dgongs pa la gshegs nas bod la ma phan skad /
NK022(za)001:2680: de la rgya gar gyi pad+ma sa b+ha ba dang /
NK022(za)001:2681: b+hi ma la mi tra gnyis /
NK022(za)001:2682: bod kyi gnubs nam mkha'i snying po dang /
NK022(za)001:2683: rgyal po g.yu sgra snying po dang gnyis te bzhi'o //
NK022(za)001:2684: de ltar bzhi pos gnyags dz+nya ku ma ra la dbang bskur nas /
NK022(za)001:2685: da ltar gyi bla ma yar khams su brgyud pa
NK022(za)001:2686: ni smin shing yid ches pa lo rgyus kyi dbang
NK022(za)001:2687: du bshad pa zhes bya ba lags pas /
NK022(za)001:2688: kun gyis thugs la bde bar nos shig /
NK022(za)001:2689: snyad khung brgyud pa'i gdams pa /
NK022(za)001:2691: de nas gags brgyad bshad la /
NK022(za)001:2692: nyon mongs 'di dag su spong ba //
NK022(za)001:2693: dngos grub dbang gi snod du gyur //
NK022(za)001:2694: dri ma med pa'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK022(za)001:2695: legs par nyon la gnyid log cig /
NK022(za)001:2697: 'di nas de'i nub mo las mkhan gyis zhi khro gzhung bsrang /
NK022(za)001:2699: srid pa'i spyi mdos byas la /
NK022(za)001:2701: ku sha sran dang sngas kyi mtshams su bcug la /
NK022(za)001:2702: rnal 'byor pho gzhogs g.yas 'og tu bcug mo rnams
NK022(za)001:2703: gzhogs g.yon 'og tu bcug la rmi lam thun gsum
NK022(za)001:2704: du bcad la / tho rangs ye shes lha'i rmi lam la brtags la ngan na /
NK022(za)001:2705: slob bu rnams bdud rtsi 'khyil par bskyed la /
NK022(za)001:2706: big nan ta kri'i sngags kyis srungs la bzhag go //
NK022(za)001:2707: de dag zhag lnga pa'i cho ga'i las kyi khrigs su shes par bya'o //
NK022(za)001:2708: de nas rdo rje slob dpon gyis gtso byas la /
NK022(za)001:2709: nyi ma shar ba dang drag po'i sbyin bsreg bya /
NK022(za)001:2710: zangs gzhong kha sbub pa slang la /
NK022(za)001:2711: re ga 'dres nas 'dug na nyams pa yod pa yin pas ngos bzung la phyir phyung la gtang /
NK022(za)001:2712: dog gis khyer na bshags pa bya /
NK022(za)001:2713: ma 'dres par gsal bar gyur pa la 'dus pa chen po'i dkyil 'khor bri ste /
NK022(za)001:2714: de yang slob dpon chas gos ser po byas la mdzub mo gnyis po smin mtshams su bsnol la /
NK022(za)001:2717: zhes brjod nas tshom bu'i lha tshogs dang thig nam mkha' la brteg la bzhag la /
NK022(za)001:2718: sa tshon stegs khar bzhag ste /
NK022(za)001:2719: dbus nas rdo rje slob dpon gyis bag tsam bri /
NK022(za)001:2720: de nas zhal dbang thob par byas la bri'o //
NK022(za)001:2721: bri thabs shog chung dag tu lta'o //
NK022(za)001:2722: de nas bri ba zin pa dang /
NK022(za)001:2723: yar nam mkha' la bteg pa'i lha rnams dkyil 'khor la bstim mo //
NK022(za)001:2724: de yan chad ni nyin mo'i las so //
NK022(za)001:2725: de nas dgongs mo phyir cha gsum btang nas /
NK022(za)001:2726: gtor ma dang po mi gtang bar bzhag la phyogs bzhir tho bzhi brtsigs te /
NK022(za)001:2727: las mkhan gyis tho chog rgyas par bya'o //
NK022(za)001:2728: de nas kun nang du 'dus la /
NK022(za)001:2729: rdzas cha kun rdo rje rgyal po'i mdun du tshang bar bsogs la /
NK022(za)001:2730: gral phyag tshul phyag rgyas par bya /
NK022(za)001:2731: thun mong srung ba'i 'khor los mtshams rgyas par bcad /
NK022(za)001:2732: de nas them pa'i phyir rol du dam sri rgyas par las mkhan gyis phur pa bzhi mnan la /
NK022(za)001:2736: dang po ni dam sri'i 'gugs 'dren byas la dam sri bcug pa'i cho ga bya ste /
NK022(za)001:2737: h'u rang bzhin dag pa'i ngo bo la //
NK022(za)001:2738: sangs rgyas sems can gnyis med de //
NK022(za)001:2739: ma rtogs pa dang log par rtogs //
NK022(za)001:2740: phyogs rtogs yang dag nyid ma rtogs //
NK022(za)001:2741: sgrib pas sems dpang dma' ba dang //
NK022(za)001:2742: sems kyi rtogs pas bcings pa yi //
NK022(za)001:2743: gzhi stong ci la'ang bar chad byed //
NK022(za)001:2744: rang gi dam tshig rang ma 'da' //
NK022(za)001:2745: 'dzam bu gling gi lho phyogs na //
NK022(za)001:2746: 'di nas dpag tshad brgyad khri na //
NK022(za)001:2747: gshin rje'i rgyal po chos ston gyis //
NK022(za)001:2748: khyod kyi chos skal de ru nyon //
NK022(za)001:2749: ma 'da' rang rang gnas su dengs //
NK022(za)001:2750: sa ma ya ka pany+tsa rak+sha rak+sha h'u phata /
NK022(za)001:2751: ces brjod la tshig nas ji ltar brjod pa bzhin du bsams la /
NK022(za)001:2753: ling ga la thag pa nag po'i ske la btags la sgo'i phyogs su /
NK022(za)001:2754: khro bo'i zhabs 'og tu yong sar byas nas /
NK022(za)001:2755: mgo mthur la bstan te snying khar seng phur dar gyi cod pan can btags la /
NK022(za)001:2756: sgo'i mdun bsham du btags so //
NK022(za)001:2757: gnyis pa ni lugs rkyang gi sog pa g.yon pa la /
NK022(za)001:2758: khro bo gshin rje gshed po'i gzugs bri /
NK022(za)001:2760: sh+ri ya man+ta ka h'u zhes sku bskyed /
NK022(za)001:2761: sa man dzas snyan gsan dbab /
NK022(za)001:2762: h'u khro bo'i rgyal po gshin rje gshed //
NK022(za)001:2763: ding gi gnas mchog dam pa 'dir //
NK022(za)001:2764: thugs rje'i dbang gis gshegs su gsol //
NK022(za)001:2767: dza h'u ba hos spyan drang /
NK022(za)001:2769: bde bar gshegs so nas lha mo bzhi bsnol yan chad kyis mchod la /
NK022(za)001:2770: h'u sum cu rtsa gsum lha'i mdun sa nas //
NK022(za)001:2771: bcom ldan chos rje 'od kyis bka' stsal pa //
NK022(za)001:2772: lha srin sde brgyad 'byung po'i dpon rnams kun //
NK022(za)001:2773: bsgrub pa mchog la ding 'dir bdag 'jug gis //
NK022(za)001:2774: bla med byang chub 'bras bu ma thob par //
NK022(za)001:2775: sgo 'di yan chad su yang 'da' bar ma byed cig /
NK022(za)001:2777: khro bo'i rgyal po gshin rje gshed po la phrin las su bcol ba ni /
NK022(za)001:2778: bdag cag la dngos grub kyi sdong grogs dang /
NK022(za)001:2779: phyi mtshams srung zhing nang mtshams bskyang ba dang /
NK022(za)001:2780: khyad par du yang bsgrub pa 'di dbu btsugs nas phyi'i dgra bgegs nang du mi btang zhing /
NK022(za)001:2781: nang gi dngos grub phyir mi gtang ba dang /
NK022(za)001:2782: rdo rje ya ma dam sri la sogs pa'i bar chad thams cad srung du gsol /
NK022(za)001:2783: ces brjod la sgo'i gong du btags te /
NK022(za)001:2784: de ni ye shes lha'i sgo byang ngo //
NK022(za)001:2785: de nas gsang mtshams bcad de /
NK022(za)001:2786: kun kyis langs la rdo rje thugs khar bzung nas /
NK022(za)001:2787: mi rtog pa'i ngang las thugs khar h'u bsams te /
NK022(za)001:2788: 'phros 'dus pa las rdo rje rtse lnga pa cig tu gyur /
NK022(za)001:2790: badz+ra kro ta a mri ta kun d+ha li h'u phata /
NK022(za)001:2791: ces brjod pas bdag nyid bdud rtsi 'khyil pa sku
NK022(za)001:2792: mdog ljang khu rdo rje rtse gsum pa thogs pa
NK022(za)001:2795: rnam 'joms kyi yang snying yan chad brjod pas /
NK022(za)001:2796: rang dang 'dra ba'i sprul pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa 'phros nas /
NK022(za)001:2797: bgegs thams cad bskrad h'u zhes pas brjod pas khro bo'i gur du gyur /
NK022(za)001:2798: ra zhes brjod pas de las me 'bar nas me'i
NK022(za)001:2799: gur du gyur nas bskal pa'i rlung gis kyang mi
NK022(za)001:2801: de nas gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor la rdzas dgod pa ni /
NK022(za)001:2802: zhi ba'i gzhal yas khang bskyed la /
NK022(za)001:2803: bdag nyid kun bzang yab yum du bskyed /
NK022(za)001:2804: mkha' gsang byin gyis brlabs nas sbyor ba'i bda' bskul /
NK022(za)001:2805: byang chub sems kyi 'od zer las kun bzang yab yum bton nas tsa ka li la bstim zhing /
NK022(za)001:2806: dkyil 'khor gyi dbus su sngags brjod la bkod /
NK022(za)001:2807: mi bskyod pa yab yum mkha' gsang nas bton la /
NK022(za)001:2808: h'u badz+ra d+h+ri ka gis kun bzang gi mdun du dgod /
NK022(za)001:2809: de bzhin du thub pa yan chad so so rang
NK022(za)001:2810: rang gi gnas su so so rang rang gi sngags
NK022(za)001:2811: brjod la rim pa ma nor bar dgod do //
NK022(za)001:2812: de nas yang dbang chen khro bo'i dkyil 'khor bskyed la /
NK022(za)001:2813: mkha' gsang byin gyis brlabs pa'i dgongs pa gong bzhin byas la /
NK022(za)001:2814: a kra ma h+aa'i sngags kyis kun bzang gi mdun du dgod /
NK022(za)001:2815: de nas 'khor lo rtsibs dgu pa'i byang shar du /
NK022(za)001:2816: rigs kyi gtso bo badz+ra he ru ka'i rtsa sngags kyis dgod /
NK022(za)001:2817: phyogs kyi rtsibs bzhi la rigs bzhi'i he ru ka sngags kyis dgod /
NK022(za)001:2818: mtshams kyi bzhi la lung gi he ru ka bzhi'i rtsa sngags kyis dgod /
NK022(za)001:2819: gru chad glo 'bur la ko'u ri brgyad kyi rtsa sngags brjod la dgod /
NK022(za)001:2820: de nas bar 'khyams dang po mdog ser po la
NK022(za)001:2821: he brgyad la sing ha brgyad kyi rtsa sngags kyis
NK022(za)001:2822: bskor la / sgo bzhir phata bzhi la sgo ma bzhi dgod /
NK022(za)001:2823: bar 'khyams mdog dkar po gnyis pa la a brgyad las /
NK022(za)001:2824: spor ma brgyad la a rak+mo ha zhes pas dgod /
NK022(za)001:2825: sgo bzhir dza h'u ba ho bzhi las /
NK022(za)001:2826: gsang yum bzhi sh+ri badz+ra ka ra mud kha ka ra ya ya na ma /
NK022(za)001:2827: sh+ri badz+ra g+han d+ha pra dza la na ma /
NK022(za)001:2828: sh+ri badz+ra ra ka sa ma ya ya na ma /
NK022(za)001:2829: sh+ri badz+ra kha tong kha pra dza la ya ya na ma /
NK022(za)001:2831: de nas khyams gsum pa mdog dmar po la b+h+yo
NK022(za)001:2832: nyi shu rtsa brgyad las dbang phyug ma nyi shu
NK022(za)001:2833: rtsa brgyad kyi sngags kyis dgod /
NK022(za)001:2834: de yan chad ni khrag 'thung rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor zhes bya /
NK022(za)001:2835: bar khyams bzhi pa ni phrin las myur mgyogs kyi dkyil 'khor mdog ser po /
NK022(za)001:2836: e sum cu so gnyis las mkha' 'gro sum cu so gnyis /
NK022(za)001:2837: e a ra li h'u zhes pa'i sngags kyis dgod /
NK022(za)001:2838: de nas bar khyams lnga pa mdog dmar po la /
NK022(za)001:2839: h'u bdun la ma mo bdun /
NK022(za)001:2840: tim bzhi las sgo ma bzhi /
NK022(za)001:2841: ma ma da du h'u zhes pa bdun /
NK022(za)001:2842: dza dun ting b+h+yo zhes pa bzhis dgod de /
NK022(za)001:2843: 'di yang dam tshig rgyal po'i dkyil 'khor /
NK022(za)001:2844: bar khyams drug pa ni sgrol ba'i ging gi dkyil 'khor zhes bya ste /
NK022(za)001:2845: mdog dkar po h'u bco brgyad las ging chen bco brgyad /
NK022(za)001:2846: ging ka ra ha ha ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK022(za)001:2848: de nas bar khyams bdun pa khro bo rol pa'i dkyil 'khor nag po la /
NK022(za)001:2849: h'u drug cu las khro bo drug cu kro ta kro ti h'u zhes pa'i sngags kyis dgod /
NK022(za)001:2850: bar khyams brgyad pa ni mgyogs 'gro yid kyi dkyil 'khor zhes bya ste /
NK022(za)001:2851: mdog phyogs mtshon la shar du dza drug cu las
NK022(za)001:2852: rba na rba na a g+hu sha dza zhes dung
NK022(za)001:2853: gi pho nya drug cu dgod /
NK022(za)001:2854: de bzhin du lho phyogs su ha la ha la pa sha h'u zhes /
NK022(za)001:2855: nub phyogs su gardza gardza spo ta ba zhes /
NK022(za)001:2856: byang phyogs su pa tsa pa tsa g+han+d+ha ho zhes pas dgod /
NK022(za)001:2857: de nas khyams dgu pa ni dam tshig rgya mtsho'i
NK022(za)001:2858: dkyiil 'khor mdog ljang gu ma ma drug cu las
NK022(za)001:2859: / 'og phyogs kyi ma mo drug cu ma ma sha ra h'u zhes pa'i sngags kyis dgod /
NK022(za)001:2860: des nas bar khyams bcu pa mdog mdzes mtshon ni tha ma rdo rje ra ba la /
NK022(za)001:2861: ma h+aa g+hu ru sha ri ra zhes rig 'dzin
NK022(za)001:2862: rtsal 'chang rnams shar stod nas gral rims su dgod
NK022(za)001:2863: par bya'o // de nas khro bo gsang ba'i bum pa rdo rje slob dpon gyi mdun du dgod /
NK022(za)001:2864: zhi ba'i bum pa lnga po tshig dang sngags kyis
NK022(za)001:2865: phyogs bzhi dbus dang lngar dgod pa'am dkyil 'khor gyi
NK022(za)001:2866: mtha' mar gral rims su dgod /
NK022(za)001:2867: las thams cad pa'i bum pa dang rtsa ba dang
NK022(za)001:2868: yan lag gi mchod pa las mkhan gyi mdun du
NK022(za)001:2869: dgod / rtag pa gsum rdo rje slob dpon gyi mdun du dgod /
NK022(za)001:2870: gzhan yang 'dab brgyad dar sna dang bcas pa dang /
NK022(za)001:2871: gri brgyad me long dang bcas pa /
NK022(za)001:2872: phur bu brub khung dang bcas pa /
NK022(za)001:2873: 'phan dang bla re la sogs brgyan dang mchod par 'os pa'i rgyan kun gyis brgyan par bya'o //
NK022(za)001:2874: de nas dkyil 'khor lha tshogs de rnams la byin dbab ste /
NK022(za)001:2875: spos dkar gyi dud pa btang nas /
NK022(za)001:2876: rol mo'i sgra sbyar la pho rnams la ha sta /
NK022(za)001:2877: mo rnams kyis phreng ba g.yab cing /
NK022(za)001:2879: h'u nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam pa'i 'jig rten nas /
NK022(za)001:2880: rnal 'byor dbang phyug rigs kyi yum dang bcas //
NK022(za)001:2881: rgyal ba'i srungs mar gyur pa'i dam tshig can //
NK022(za)001:2882: mchod do bla ma rnams la skyabs su mchi //
NK022(za)001:2883: h'u mi gnas ye shes thugs kyi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK022(za)001:2884: bcom ldan che mchog khro rgyal 'khor dang bcas //
NK022(za)001:2885: sngags tshig bshugs pa'i bda' yis spyan 'dren gyis //
NK022(za)001:2886: phyag rgya gar gyi mchod pas g.yab 'dor na //
NK022(za)001:2887: dpal chen yab yum thugs dam rjes dgongs la //
NK022(za)001:2888: thugs dam bda' la dgongs te gshegs su gsol //
NK022(za)001:2889: h'u chos nyid bde ba chen po'i skur byung ba //
NK022(za)001:2890: bcom ldan che mchog yab yum gshegs su gsol //
NK022(za)001:2891: dur khrod dregs pa'i tshogs rnams 'joms mdzad pa //
NK022(za)001:2892: rgyud lung khro rgyal yab yum gshegs su gsol //
NK022(za)001:2893: ye shes 'bar ba brgyad kyi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK022(za)001:2894: ko'u ri khro mo brgyad po gshegs su gsol //
NK022(za)001:2895: chos nyid mkha' ltar dag pa'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK022(za)001:2896: seng ha phra men brgyad po gshegs su gsol //
NK022(za)001:2897: 'bar ba'i bar khyams dur khrod nang shed du //
NK022(za)001:2898: spor ma gsang yum tshogs rnams gshegs su gsol //
NK022(za)001:2899: tshad med bzhi rdzogs gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK022(za)001:2900: rta gdong sgo ma 'khor bcas gshegs su gsol //
NK022(za)001:2901: dam tshig lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK022(za)001:2902: dbang phyug ma sring 'khor bcas gshegs su gsol //
NK022(za)001:2903: zhe sdang 'bar ba thugs kyi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK022(za)001:2904: khro rgyal srin po 'khor bcas gshegs su gsol //
NK022(za)001:2905: dur khrod 'bar ba chen po'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK022(za)001:2906: mkha' 'gro sum cu rtsa gnyis gshegs su gsol //
NK022(za)001:2907: sgrol byed 'bar ba las kyi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK022(za)001:2908: rdo rje ging chen 'khor bcas gshegs su gsol //
NK022(za)001:2909: ci bgyi bka' nyan las kyi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK022(za)001:2910: pho nya sder mo 'khor bcas gshegs su gsol //
NK022(za)001:2911: las rnams yongs su grub pa'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK022(za)001:2912: ye shes ma mo'i tshogs rnams gshegs su gsol //
NK022(za)001:2913: sdom pa sa la gnas pa'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK022(za)001:2914: rig 'dzin rtsal 'chang 'khor bcas gshegs su gsol //
NK022(za)001:2915: ding gi gnas mchog dur khrod tshogs re 'dra //
NK022(za)001:2916: ban d+ha gsar rnying tshogs ni rdza ltar lhags //
NK022(za)001:2917: keng rus gsar snying tshogs ni ri ltar spungs //
NK022(za)001:2918: rak+ta gsar rnying tshogs ni mtsho ltar 'khyil //
NK022(za)001:2919: mang sa gsar rnying tshogs ni thang ltar brdal //
NK022(za)001:2920: zhing chen gsar rnying tshogs ni bye ltar bkram //
NK022(za)001:2921: tsit+ta gsar rnying tshogs ni rlung ltar spungs //
NK022(za)001:2922: byang chub sems kyi tshogs ni gangs ltar chags //
NK022(za)001:2923: rgyan cha gsar rnying tshogs ni sprin ltar gtibs //
NK022(za)001:2924: sta na 'ga' na'i tshogs ni dbyings na rol //
NK022(za)001:2925: rdo rje mched lcam lha dang lha mor rol //
NK022(za)001:2926: ma mo mkha' 'gro'i tshogs ni mkha' ltar 'thibs //
NK022(za)001:2927: rnal 'byor longs spyod che la spyan 'dren na //
NK022(za)001:2928: thugs dam bdag la dgongs te gshegs nas kyang //
NK022(za)001:2929: dkyil 'khor chen po 'di la byin phob la //
NK022(za)001:2930: bsgrub pa'i rtags dang mtshan ma bstan nas kyang //
NK022(za)001:2931: bla med sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub stsol //
NK022(za)001:2932: badz+ra sa ma ya sid+d+hi phem phem /
NK022(za)001:2933: badz+ra yo gi ni sa ma ya dza /
NK022(za)001:2934: badz+ra a be sha ya a a /
NK022(za)001:2935: zhes brjod pas lha tshogs de rnams dkyil 'khor dang
NK022(za)001:2936: tsa ka li'i thog tu byon te pra be shas
NK022(za)001:2937: sgo phye / a be shas gnyis su med par
NK022(za)001:2938: thim pas lha rnams gzi byin dang ldan par bsam
NK022(za)001:2939: sgo phye / mo // de nas bar mtshams bcad pa ni /
NK022(za)001:2940: mi rtog pa'i ngang las bsam /
NK022(za)001:2941: de la bee ro tsa na zhes brjod pas bdag
NK022(za)001:2942: nyid rnam par snang mdzad dkar po zhal gsum phyag
NK022(za)001:2943: drug pa / zhal dbus dkar ba g.yas sngo ba /
NK022(za)001:2945: g.yas g.yon dang po gnyis 'khor lo pad+ma /
NK022(za)001:2949: tha ma ral gri bsnams pa /
NK022(za)001:2950: nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan la bzhugs par bsam /
NK022(za)001:2951: de'i thugs kha nas bton la /
NK022(za)001:2952: ma sur+ya man+dala zhes nyi dkyil bsam /
NK022(za)001:2953: yang thugs kha nas h'u ljang khu cig byung la /
NK022(za)001:2954: badz+ra kro ta ar+ya a tsa la badz+ra ma h+aa kro ta h'u phata /
NK022(za)001:2955: ces brjod pas mi g.yo mgon po mdog sngo skya /
NK022(za)001:2958: phyag g.yas na rdo rje ral gri dang mda' /
NK022(za)001:2959: g.yon na dgra sta zhags pa gzhu bsnams pa zhig mdun du bka' nod du bsam la /
NK022(za)001:2960: me'i dkyil 'khor dang phata na ma sa man ta'i
NK022(za)001:2961: sngags brjod nas ral dri'i phyag rgyas g.yas nas glad
NK022(za)001:2962: la bskor bas bgegs thams cad bskrad /
NK022(za)001:2963: g.yon nas bskor bas ral gri'i gur du gyur par bsgom /
NK022(za)001:2964: bsnyen par gnang ba'i dbang bzhi skabs 'dir bskur ro //
NK022(za)001:2965: de nas ye nas mnyam nyid la sogs pa brjod nas thal mo 'byed pa ltar byas la /
NK022(za)001:2966: ting nge 'dzin gyis gzhal yas khang gi sgo shags kyis phye nas /
NK022(za)001:2967: lha rnams kyi zhal mngon sum du mthong bar bsam /
NK022(za)001:2969: shar lho nub byang la sogs pa brjod la yan
NK022(za)001:2970: lag rnam pa lnga la sogs pa btsugs nas phyag
NK022(za)001:2971: 'tshal bas lha dang gnyis su med par bsam mo
NK022(za)001:2972: // de yan chad ni bsnyen bsgrub bzhi las bsnyen pa'i cho gar shes par bya'o //
NK022(za)001:2973: spyi don gnyis la nye ba'i bsnyen pa ni /
NK022(za)001:2974: lha dang mkhon lcugs sbyang ba'i phyir bshags pa bya /
NK022(za)001:2975: 'gro don mthar phyin par bya ba'i phyir dam bca' /
NK022(za)001:2976: las byas don yod par bya ba'i phyir ram dam
NK022(za)001:2977: can dbang du 'du ba'i phyir byin dbab par bya'o
NK022(za)001:2978: // de nas ma tra mnan pa ni bdag nyid byang shar du phyin la /
NK022(za)001:2979: badz+ra sh+ri he ru ka h'u zhes brjod pas /
NK022(za)001:2980: skad cig gis he ru kar bskyed la lcags kyu'i phyag rgya bcas nas /
NK022(za)001:2981: ma tra kha r+au tra a g+hu sha dza dza h'u zhes lan gsum brjod pas /
NK022(za)001:2982: skad cig gis mdun du 'ongs par bsam la /
NK022(za)001:2983: badz+ra g+hu he tri sha sa ma ya s+t+wa /
NK022(za)001:2984: zhes lan gsum du thod pa'i phyag rgya bstan nas /
NK022(za)001:2985: ma tra bya ba'i zhes pa nas /
NK022(za)001:2986: sdong grogs mdzod cig ces pa dang /
NK022(za)001:2987: badz+ra sh+ri he ru ka'i sngags brjod nas /
