NK022(za)001:2988: kha tra kha'i phyag rgya bcas nas brgyab pas /
NK022(za)001:2989: sdong gog 'gyel ba bzhin 'go bo lho nub /
NK022(za)001:2990: rkang pa byang shar du bstan nas g.yon gyis g.yas mnan nas 'gyel bar bsams la /
NK022(za)001:2991: bdag gi zhabs g.yas pa'i mthe bong dza'i 'phro 'dus lcags kyur bsams nas /
NK022(za)001:2992: rkang pa g.yas teg ge byas la gnas kyi sgo zhes pa nas /
NK022(za)001:2993: phye zhig ces pa yan chad brjod /
NK022(za)001:2994: h'u h'u phata phata ma tra ka r+au tra h'u phata /
NK022(za)001:2997: zhes pas rkang pa phral bar bsam /
NK022(za)001:2998: de nas ral gri'i phyag rgya bcas la /
NK022(za)001:2999: ka tar kha pra be sha phata /
NK022(za)001:3000: ces brjod pas khog pa dral bar bsam /
NK022(za)001:3001: de nas pri h'u zhes brjod pas kho'i shes pa h'u dkar po gcig tu gyur nas /
NK022(za)001:3002: de bdag gi thugs khar thim pas thugs ye shes dbyer med par bsam /
NK022(za)001:3003: de ka la b+h+ru bi sha bi shud+d+he b+han d+ha dz+nya na ra zhes brjod pas /
NK022(za)001:3004: khog pa nyid zla ga smug nag tu gyur pa las /
NK022(za)001:3005: b+h+ru kha pra be sha phata ces pas sgo phyes bar bsams nas /
NK022(za)001:3006: nang du h'u h'u h'u zhes brjod nas phyin par bsam /
NK022(za)001:3007: ha ha h'u h'u s+pha ra na phata /
NK022(za)001:3008: sa ha ra na h'u zhes brjod pas gzhal yas khang gi sgo bcad par bsam /
NK022(za)001:3009: de ka'i rjes la steng yang rdo rje'i tshig dbyangs dang bcas pa brjod nas /
NK022(za)001:3010: badz+ra yak+sha kro ta h'u phata /
NK022(za)001:3011: badz+ra badz+ra ra ya kha zhes phyag rgyas bskor bas /
NK022(za)001:3012: steng 'og rdo rje'i gur du gyur nas bskal pa'i rlung gis kyang mi thar bar bsam la /
NK022(za)001:3014: dam sri phur pa bzhin du las mkhan gyis mnan /
NK022(za)001:3016: zhag gi zo ris skra mtshams su gdab /
NK022(za)001:3017: thal chen gyi tshom bu dpral ba'i dbyings su tri shul rtse gsum gyi dbyibs su gdab /
NK022(za)001:3018: rak+ta'i thig le ban d+ha zlum po'i dbyibs su smin mtshams su gdab /
NK022(za)001:3019: rtsa ba dang yan lag gi mchod pa byin gyis brlabs /
NK022(za)001:3020: zhi khro gnyis sgyu 'phrul ltar gzhungs bsrang /
NK022(za)001:3021: kun bzang he ru kas gtso byas la /
NK022(za)001:3024: de dag ni zhag drug pa'i nub mo'i phrin las su shes par bya'o //
NK022(za)001:3025: de nas nam langs pa dang /
NK022(za)001:3026: rab tu gnas par bya ba la don brgyad de /
NK022(za)001:3027: sngon du bya ba'i cho ga dang /
NK022(za)001:3028: ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor bskyed pa dang /
NK022(za)001:3029: rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor spyan drangs la bstim pa dang /
NK022(za)001:3030: dbang po skyon gsal gyis chos bdun bya ba dang /
NK022(za)001:3031: me long phul la chu bdun gyi sku khrus gsol zhing sku phyi ba dang /
NK022(za)001:3032: che ba'i yon tan dang brgyan cha rnams kyis dbang bskur zhing mnga' gsol bar bya ba dang /
NK022(za)001:3033: phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod pa rdzogs par dbul ba dang /
NK022(za)001:3034: bden pa'i byin rlabs dmigs shing brtan par bzhugs su gsol te /
NK022(za)001:3035: de la yon bdag la sogs pas bskor ba bya
NK022(za)001:3036: zhing phyag btsal nas mi 'bral zhing mngon du gyur
NK022(za)001:3037: cig par smon lam gdab pa'o //
NK022(za)001:3038: de la dang po mngon du bya ba ni /
NK022(za)001:3039: dkyil 'khor gyi shar du man+dala pad+ma 'dab brgyad mdzes tshon du bya /
NK022(za)001:3040: grub na rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor du bri /
NK022(za)001:3041: de'i dbus su man 'dzi'i khar rat+na'i snod du /
NK022(za)001:3042: snam bu'am ras gtsang ma ltab tshigs legs par byas la bzhag /
NK022(za)001:3043: de'i khar bze zhal gyi nang du me log bzhag /
NK022(za)001:3044: rtsa ba dang yan lag gi mchod pa bsham /
NK022(za)001:3045: shar du dbang po skyon gsal ba'i thur ma la sogs pa'i rdzas bsham /
NK022(za)001:3046: lhor rgyas pa'i sbyin sreg gi thab bca' /
NK022(za)001:3048: byang du tshogs las bya ba'am /
NK022(za)001:3050: 'khar ba la sogs pa'i snod du ba'i rnam lnga sbyar ba la sogs sbyar ba'i chus /
NK022(za)001:3051: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ka ya bi shwa d+ha
NK022(za)001:3052: na h'u zhes brjod cing me long gi ngos la
NK022(za)001:3054: dri nga ba dang dngos po'i mtshan ma thams cad
NK022(za)001:3055: bsal nas nyon mongs pa'i sgrib pa dag par bsam
NK022(za)001:3057: +aahmh'u h+r+ai th+aa zhes brjod cing byugs pas thugs rje byang chub kyi gzungs dang ldan par bsam /
NK022(za)001:3058: de nas shing shun lnga'i phye ma dang ba yu lnga'i chu sbyar la /
NK022(za)001:3059: gong gi sngags bzlas shing blugs pas /
NK022(za)001:3060: khams lnga'i rtog pa dag nas che ba'i yon tan phun sum tshogs par bsam /
NK022(za)001:3061: de nas kha tshar ma nyams pas /
NK022(za)001:3062: rat+na pra pan tsa ra ha s+w+aa h+aa /
NK022(za)001:3063: zhes brjod cing phyis pas gzung 'dzin gyi lta ngan sel cing shes bya'i sgrib pa dag par bsam /
NK022(za)001:3064: de nas spos dkar la sogs pa dri bzang po
NK022(za)001:3065: phul bas sangs rgyas kyi mdzad pa'i phrin las yongs
NK022(za)001:3067: de ltar zin pa dang rtsa ba las kyi cho ga lung gi zhi khro'i rang gzhung bsrang ste /
NK022(za)001:3073: mchod pa kun byin gyis brlabs /
NK022(za)001:3074: de nas bum pa byin brlabs bya ste nub phyogs su dgod /
NK022(za)001:3075: de nas chu bdun tshan gnyis brtag pa gsum dang
NK022(za)001:3076: ldan par byin gyis brlabs la byang phyogs su dgod
NK022(za)001:3078: rgyal theb kyis rtsa ba las kyi dkyil 'khor zhi khro gzhungs bsrang /
NK022(za)001:3079: las mkhan cha gcig gis lung gi zhi khro gzhung bsrang /
NK022(za)001:3080: rgyud ltar zhi khro gnyis kyi dkyil 'khor bskyed /
NK022(za)001:3082: sku gsung thugs su byin gyis brlabs /
NK022(za)001:3083: rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor spyan drangs /
NK022(za)001:3084: 'dod pa'i don du gsol ba btab pa yan chad bya /
NK022(za)001:3085: rdo rje rgyal pos rgyas pa'i sbyin sreg bya /
NK022(za)001:3088: de dag ni sngon 'gro'i cho ga'o //
NK022(za)001:3089: gnyis pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor bskyed pa /
NK022(za)001:3090: dbang chen po'i dkyil 'khor gyi cho ga la 'jug pa ni /
NK022(za)001:3091: dang po mtshams bcad pa ni skad cig gis rdo rje gzhon nur bskyed la /
NK022(za)001:3092: ma sur+ya man+dala zhes phyogs mtshams su myad /
NK022(za)001:3093: steng 'og gnyis su nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor bcu bsam /
NK022(za)001:3094: sum b+ha ni lan bcus phyogs bcu'i gdan bting la /
NK022(za)001:3095: de'i steng du khro bo bcu bskyed la bskul ba ni /
NK022(za)001:3096: h'u dbang mchog sgrub pa po'i dkyil 'khor du /
NK022(za)001:3097: nga ni dkyil 'khor 'khor lo'i las byed kyis //
NK022(za)001:3098: phyogs skyong bcu po mnan pa dang //
NK022(za)001:3099: 'khor gyi gdon tshogs ma lus kun //
NK022(za)001:3100: dus gsum sangs rgyas bka' byung gis //
NK022(za)001:3102: badz+ra kro ta sh+ri he ru ka h'u zhes pa nas /
NK022(za)001:3103: spo ta ya spo ta ya h'u phata /
NK022(za)001:3104: ces pa yan chad brjod la phur pa bcu phyogs bcur gdab /
NK022(za)001:3106: de nas gsang ba'i dri chab kyis kun sbyangs la /
NK022(za)001:3107: bdag nyid kun bzang yab yum gyi sbyor ba'i mkha' nas /
NK022(za)001:3108: rdo rje sems dpa' mdun gyi nam mkha' la bton /
NK022(za)001:3109: rdo rje sems dpa'i thugs kha'i h'u las /
NK022(za)001:3110: ra ya kha gis dkyil 'khor gyi dngos po dang mtshan ma sbyangs la smon lam gdab ste /
NK022(za)001:3111: na mo mi gnas pa'i ye shes chen po'i bdag nyid /
NK022(za)001:3112: phyag rgya'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs thams cad bdag la gsan cing dgongs su gsol /
NK022(za)001:3113: da ltar yang bdag cag gi mtha' yas pa'i sems can thams cad 'khor ba las bsgral ba'i phyir /
NK022(za)001:3114: 'dus pa chen po'i lha tshogs rnams la rab tu gnas pa'i phrin las bgyi bar 'tshal bas /
NK022(za)001:3115: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis bdag la mthu bstan du gsol /
NK022(za)001:3118: rab gnas ye shes kyi snang ba thob par mdzad du gsol lo //
NK022(za)001:3119: ces brjod la phreng ba dkyil 'khor gyi dbus su dor /
NK022(za)001:3120: rat+na ma l+ye a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u zhes phreng ba
NK022(za)001:3121: dam tshig gi phyag rgyas blangs la mgo la bcing
NK022(za)001:3122: ngo / de nas phyag rgya thal mo khong stong du sbyar la /
NK022(za)001:3123: ma h+aa shu dz+nya na ta dz+nya na badz+ra d+harma d+har du swa b+ha ba ad ma ko&a ha /
NK022(za)001:3124: zhes lan gsum brjod pas gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor chos nyid rnam par dag pa'i klong /
NK022(za)001:3125: stong pa nyid kyi ye shes su bsgom /
NK022(za)001:3126: yang rdo rje sems dpa'i thugs kha nas khro bo
NK022(za)001:3127: ltar 'byung ba rim rtseg gi dbang chen gyi dkyil
NK022(za)001:3128: 'khor bskyed la / b+h+ru smug nag las 'dus pa
NK022(za)001:3129: chen po'i gzhal yas khang gdan dang bcas pa bskyed
NK022(za)001:3130: 'khor bskyed la / la / bdag kun tu bzang po'i sbyor mtshams nas rdo rje sems dpa' byung /
NK022(za)001:3131: de'i thugs kha nas h'u bco brgyad bton la /
NK022(za)001:3132: brgyud lung gi he ru ka dgu klong bskyed /
NK022(za)001:3133: ha brgyad las koo'u ri brgyad /
NK022(za)001:3134: he brgyad las seng ha brgyad /
NK022(za)001:3135: phata bzhi las sgo ma bzhi /
NK022(za)001:3136: a brgyad las spor ma brgyad /
NK022(za)001:3137: dza h'u ba ho bzhi las gang gsang yum bzhi /
NK022(za)001:3138: b+h+yo nyi shu rtsa brgyad la dbang phyug ma nyi shu rtsa brgyad de /
NK022(za)001:3140: e sum cu rtsa gnyis las phrin las myur mgyogs kyi dkyil 'khor bskyed /
NK022(za)001:3141: h'u drug cu las khro bo rol pa'i dkyil 'khor bskyed /
NK022(za)001:3142: dza h'u ba ho drug cu las mgyogs 'gro yid kyi dkyil 'khor bskyed /
NK022(za)001:3143: ma drug cu las dam tshig rgya mtsho'i dkyil 'khor bskyed /
NK022(za)001:3144: dza bco brgyad las bsgrol ba ging gi dkyil 'khor bskyed /
NK022(za)001:3145: b+h+yo bcu gcig las ma bdun sring bzhi'i dkyil 'khor bskyed /
NK022(za)001:3146: de'ang dam tshig rgya mtsho'i dkyil 'khor ro //
NK022(za)001:3147: de nas de'i steng phyogs su yang bdag kun tu bzang po yab yum gyi sbyor mtshams nas /
NK022(za)001:3148: rdo rje sems dpa' byung de'i thugs kha nas 'byung ba lnga'i yi ge dang /
NK022(za)001:3149: b+hu bton la zhi ba ltar gyi dbang chen gyi
NK022(za)001:3150: dkyil 'khor gzhal yas khang gdan dang bcas pa bskyed
NK022(za)001:3151: la / rang rang gi gnas su sangs rgyas bzhi
NK022(za)001:3152: bcu rtsa gnyis po kun bzang gis gtso byas la
NK022(za)001:3153: la / bskyed / zhi khro gnyis ka la dus gcig tu /
NK022(za)001:3154: ye shes lngas dbang bskur nas /
NK022(za)001:3155: h'u rin chen bum pa dbang bskur bas /
NK022(za)001:3157: shu dz+nya ta la sogs pa brjod /
NK022(za)001:3158: sku gsung thugs su byin gyis brlab /
NK022(za)001:3159: de nas smon lam gdab ste /
NK022(za)001:3160: na mo phyogs bcu'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad
NK022(za)001:3161: kyi sku dang gsung dang thugs dang yon tan dang
NK022(za)001:3162: phrin las dang / zhing khams dag pa zad mi
NK022(za)001:3163: shes pa brgyan gyi 'khor lo'i bka' bden pa dang
NK022(za)001:3164: phrin las dang / / bden pa chen po'i byin gyis brlab kyis /
NK022(za)001:3165: 'dus pa chen po'i lha rnams la ye shes lngas
NK022(za)001:3166: dbang bskur bas rnam par shes pa tshogs brgyad ye
NK022(za)001:3167: shes su lngar lhun gyis grub pa'i don /
NK022(za)001:3168: phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor gyi dbang phyug chen po rnams dang ding gi yon gyi bdag po dang /
NK022(za)001:3169: srid pa gsum gyis bsdus pa'i sems can thams cad kyis thob par gyur cig /
NK022(za)001:3170: sku gsung thugs su byin gyis brlabs pas /
NK022(za)001:3171: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las bkod pa mi
NK022(za)001:3172: zad pa brgyan gyi 'khor lo lhun gyis grub pa'i
NK022(za)001:3174: de yan chad ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor bskyed pa'o //
NK022(za)001:3175: de nas gsum pa ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor spyan drangs pa ni /
NK022(za)001:3176: spos chen gyi dud pa btang /
NK022(za)001:3178: chos sku rig pa rang snang ba'i //
NK022(za)001:3179: rdo rje dbyings kyi lha tshogs dang //
NK022(za)001:3180: khams gsum ma lus bdal ba'i phyir //
NK022(za)001:3182: rdo rje 'chang gral rims bsnyeg pa'i //
NK022(za)001:3184: smon lam dam tshig lung bzhin du //
NK022(za)001:3185: gnas 'dir ma lus gshegs su gsol //
NK022(za)001:3187: sprin dpung bzhin du gshegs su gsol //
NK022(za)001:3188: chos kyi dbyangs kyi pho brang nas //
NK022(za)001:3189: gzhal yas chen po'i gnas mchog nas //
NK022(za)001:3190: rgyal ba 'khor bcas ma lus kun //
NK022(za)001:3191: thugs rje'i dbang gis gshegs su gsol //
NK022(za)001:3192: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten thams cad nas //
NK022(za)001:3193: rgyal ba gar bzhugs 'khor bcas dang //
NK022(za)001:3194: rdo rje dam can ji snyed pa //
NK022(za)001:3195: thams cad kun nas dgongs su gsol //
NK022(za)001:3196: rgyal ba'i thugs dam bskang ba dang //
NK022(za)001:3197: 'khor ba yongs su sbyang ba'i phyir //
NK022(za)001:3199: thugs dam dbang gis gshegs su gsol //
NK022(za)001:3200: badz+ra sa ma ya h'u dza zhes snyan gsan dbab /
NK022(za)001:3201: thugs rje lcags kyu dang e ha his spyan drang /
NK022(za)001:3203: sems can don phyir brjod la /
NK022(za)001:3204: ka ya wak+ka tsit+tasa brtan par bzhugs su gsol lo //
NK022(za)001:3206: de nas bzhi pa dbang po skyon bsal gyi chos bdun la /
NK022(za)001:3212: so mngas gser gyi chan pa dang bdun gyis dbang
NK022(za)001:3213: po rnams kyi skyon bsal ba rab gnas bzhin bya
NK022(za)001:3214: / don lnga pa dngos po skyon sbyang gi chos dgu la /
NK022(za)001:3215: dang po me long dbul ba ni /
NK022(za)001:3216: me long dag la gzugs brnyan snang ba ltar //
NK022(za)001:3218: nang du rten rnams gsal gyis phab pas snang la rang bzhin med par gyur nas /
NK022(za)001:3219: sems can thams cad kyi rgyud la bag chags g.ya'
NK022(za)001:3220: dang 'dra ba dag nas chos sku dri ma med
NK022(za)001:3222: de nas chu bdun tshan gnyis la /
NK022(za)001:3228: rin po che chab dang bdun bdun gyis zhi ba'i lha la khrus chab gsol /
NK022(za)001:3235: dri chu dang bdun gyis khro bo'i lha la khrus gsol /
NK022(za)001:3236: de nas ras kyis sku phyis te /
NK022(za)001:3237: de dag ni dngos po skyon sbyang gi chos dgu zhes bya'o //
NK022(za)001:3238: don drug pa che ba'i yon tan dang /
NK022(za)001:3239: rgyan cha'i sgo nas mnga' gsol zhing bskur ba dang /
NK022(za)001:3240: bdun pa phyi nang gsang gsum gyi mchod pa rdzogs par dbul ba ni don bzhi ste /
NK022(za)001:3241: gzugs bye brag tu mnga' gsol ba dang /
NK022(za)001:3242: mdzes pa brgyan du mnga' gsol ba dang /
NK022(za)001:3243: che ba'i longs spyod phun sum tshogs pa'i mnga' gsol ba dang /
NK022(za)001:3244: mchod pas mnyes pa yongs su bzung bar mnga' gsol ba dang bzhi'o //
NK022(za)001:3255: phyag mtshan la sogs pa gzugs bye brag tu mnga' gsol ba'o //
NK022(za)001:3256: de ka'i rjes su khro bo la /
NK022(za)001:3276: dur khrod kyi chas la sogs pa dbul /
NK022(za)001:3286: na bza' la sogs bcu gcig gis mdzes pa rgyan du mnga' gsol /
NK022(za)001:3296: chung ma la sogs pa longs spyod phun sum tshogs par mnga' gsol /
NK022(za)001:3303: bdag med phyogs bral gyi nang gi phyag 'tshal /
NK022(za)001:3304: chos sku mu mtha' rab gnas ltar 'tshal /
NK022(za)001:3305: dngos la don bcu bzhi ste /
NK022(za)001:3306: phyag rgya bzhi la sngags kyis dbul /
NK022(za)001:3307: khro bo gnas yul sgo ma nyi shus dbul /
NK022(za)001:3310: rnam lnga la sogs rnams spyir dbul /
NK022(za)001:3311: bdud rtsi dang gtor ma so sor dbul te /
NK022(za)001:3312: de dag la las gzhung dang /
NK022(za)001:3313: rab tu gnas pa'i tshig dang /
NK022(za)001:3314: bsgrags pa la sogs pa bstun la bya'o //
NK022(za)001:3315: bstod pa ni don rtags gang rung gis bstod /
NK022(za)001:3316: de rnams ni mchod pas mnyes par yongs su bzung ba'i mnga' gsol zhes bya'o //
NK022(za)001:3317: de nas brgyad pa bkra shis bya /
NK022(za)001:3318: spyi btsan du brtan par bzhugs su gsol /
NK022(za)001:3319: sgo btsan du yon bdag dang /
NK022(za)001:3320: mched lcam rnams kyis bskor ba bya /
NK022(za)001:3322: de dag ni rab tu gnas pa dkyil 'khor zhal gyi cho ga /
NK022(za)001:3323: bsnyen bsgrub bzhi las nye bsnyen /
NK022(za)001:3324: zhag drug pa yan chad kyi khrigs su shes par bya ste /
NK022(za)001:3325: nyin mo'i las su rab gnas de ltar du bya'o //
NK022(za)001:3326: spyi don gsum pa bsgrub pa dkyil 'khor zhag gi cho ga bya ba'i man ngag ni /
NK022(za)001:3327: 'dir zhag bcu gcig gi dbang du /
NK022(za)001:3330: dgu pa'i khrigs su bstan te /
NK022(za)001:3334: rtsa ba dang yan lag gi mchod pa gsar ba bsham /
NK022(za)001:3336: de nas gdod nas ma skyes dang /
NK022(za)001:3337: srid pa phyi nang snod bcud ces pa la sogs pas phrin las kyis dbu drangs la /
NK022(za)001:3339: steng 'og phyogs mtshams dngos po cir snang yang dad ces pas gsal bdab /
NK022(za)001:3341: sgrib pa rnam gnyis dngos po cir snang yang /
NK022(za)001:3346: mthu dang bral ba'i rdzu 'phrul cir snang yang /
NK022(za)001:3348: ma tra mnan zhing gsang mtshams bcad la /
NK022(za)001:3349: khro bo bcu'i stang stabs bya /
NK022(za)001:3351: rtags gdab nas mchod pa byin gyis brlabs la /
NK022(za)001:3352: thun mong rdzas kyi dngos po cir snang yang /
NK022(za)001:3354: de nas las mkhan gyis zhi khro gnyis brgyud ltar
NK022(za)001:3355: du bskyed cing gzhung bsrang la lung gis gsal gdab
NK022(za)001:3356: / gzhung gi skabs su lha kun bzang yab yum
NK022(za)001:3357: gyis gtso byas la 'dod pa'i don la gsol ba
NK022(za)001:3360: lha'i gtso bo kun bzang gis gtso byas te /
NK022(za)001:3361: rig pa gsung gi byin brlabs kyis /
NK022(za)001:3362: zhes pa la sogs pa'i tshig gis rigs lnga'i 'dzab bya /
NK022(za)001:3363: chos sku nam mkha'i bstod pa btang /
NK022(za)001:3366: thub pa yan chad la rgyas par dbul /
NK022(za)001:3368: de nas khro bo la 'dzab khang dbye /
NK022(za)001:3369: sngon la che mchog zhal byang byas la 'gu ya dz+nya na bzlas /
NK022(za)001:3370: de nas rdo rje sems dpa' gnas 'gyur ba //
NK022(za)001:3371: zhes pa la sogs pa'i tshig gis rigs lnga'i 'dzab bya /
NK022(za)001:3372: de nas dbang mchog gi bya /
NK022(za)001:3373: de nas lung gi he ru ka bzhi'i bya /
NK022(za)001:3378: phyogs bcu dus bzhi dang gtum chen gyis bstod /
NK022(za)001:3379: tshogs kyi mchod pa phul la tshogs kyi 'khor lo bskor /
NK022(za)001:3381: de dag ni nub mo'i las so //
NK022(za)001:3382: de nas nam langs pa dang las mkhan gyis lung gi lhag ma btang la /
NK022(za)001:3383: gtor ma ke tshang du bsag go //
NK022(za)001:3384: de nas snga dro cho ga 'bring po la /
NK022(za)001:3394: las mkhan gyis zhi khro gnyis rgyud ltar bskyed la lung gis gsal gdab /
NK022(za)001:3395: 'dzab rigs lnga yan chad rdzogs par bya /
NK022(za)001:3396: de nas bo d+hi tsit+ta bsgrang /
NK022(za)001:3398: khro bo la ru lu 'bru brgyad kyi 'dzab bya /
NK022(za)001:3399: yang na lha ci gsal du khams gsum thams cad brlabs la /
NK022(za)001:3400: gsang ba thugs kyi snying po thon tshad bzlas /
NK022(za)001:3401: rdo rje slob dpon gyis bum pa'i gzungs thag nas bzung la /
NK022(za)001:3404: rdo rje rgyal theb kyis 'dzab sna drangs la 'dzab ci rigs su bzlas /
NK022(za)001:3408: gung dang dgongs kyi bsnyen lugs la /
NK022(za)001:3410: ye nas mnyam nyid kyis bshags /
NK022(za)001:3412: byin dbab mchod pa byin gyis brlabs /
NK022(za)001:3413: lung gi gsal gdab mi dgos /
NK022(za)001:3414: zhi khro gnyis kyi gzhal yas khang dang /
NK022(za)001:3416: kun bzang na mar mchod pa rnam lnga dbul /
NK022(za)001:3417: sngags sam mtshan bsdus la zhi khro gnyis ka la bdud rtsi dbul /
NK022(za)001:3418: gtor ma sngags kyis so sor dbul /
NK022(za)001:3419: stan 'gan sngags dang ting nge 'dzin gyis dbul /
NK022(za)001:3420: zhi khro sngags kyis khrag dbul /
NK022(za)001:3421: badz+ra e pa h'u la sogs pa brjod la rgya mtsho lnga'i smon lam gdab /
NK022(za)001:3422: 'dod pa'i don du gsol ba btab la /
NK022(za)001:3426: de dag ni dkyil 'khor zhag gi cho ga bya ba'i man ngag ste /
NK022(za)001:3427: bsgrub pa zhag grangs du byed pa de ltar du bya'o //
NK022(za)001:3428: spyi don bzhi pa bsgrub pa chen po ni /
NK022(za)001:3429: 'dir zhag bcu gcig gi dbang du byas na /
NK022(za)001:3430: bcur 'gro ba'i dgongs mo phrin las thung ba dang sbrel la dbang gi sbyin sreg bya /
NK022(za)001:3432: dkyil 'khor gyi mtha' mar rdo rje rgya gram phye yis bri /
NK022(za)001:3433: dngos grub kyi zhal zas dang /
NK022(za)001:3436: mchur ba la sogs pa mched lcam du yod kyi grangs pas lnga'am gsum gyis lhag par byas la /
NK022(za)001:3439: nub tu dbang bshos dang rdo rje tshe /
NK022(za)001:3440: rdo rje slob dpon gyi phyogs su gsal shing 'dzugs
NK022(za)001:3441: pa'i zla kham dang bkra shis kyi bya kha sprod
NK022(za)001:3442: dgod / gsol byang bdud rtsi barlona sbyor la 'dza'
NK022(za)001:3443: gad kyis bkang ba khur bas kha bcad pa dpral
NK022(za)001:3444: ba rang la bstan pa dgod /
NK022(za)001:3445: de'i nub mo'i phrin las la sngon 'gro bsgrub pa'i dus kyis phrin las rgyas pa ltar bya /
NK022(za)001:3446: mchod pa byin gyis brlabs pa'i dus dpal bshos la
NK022(za)001:3447: bdag gi thugs kha nas h'u dkar po 'phros 'dus
NK022(za)001:3449: dpal bshos byang chub kyi sems dkar dmar gnyis kyi
NK022(za)001:3450: ngo bo las longs spyod sna tshogs pa 'byung bar
NK022(za)001:3451: bsam / dbang bshos la thugs kha h+ai tra 'phro 'du las /
NK022(za)001:3455: zhes brjod pas rin po che'i mchod sdong las /
NK022(za)001:3456: phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod pa mang po 'byung bar brlab //
NK022(za)001:3457: 'brang rgyas dang tshe lcam lugs ltar byin gyis brlab /
NK022(za)001:3458: gsol byang la thugs kha nas b+h+ru 'phros 'dus pas gsol byang la thim pas /
NK022(za)001:3459: b+h+ru bi sha b+hi shud+d+he badz+ra dz+nya na tsakra sur+ya tsan+t+ra rat+na pad+ma man+dala zhes brjod pas /
NK022(za)001:3460: 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi mu khyud dang bcas pa gsal bar bskyed la /
NK022(za)001:3461: der dpal chen po la koo ri brgyad kyi bskor bar bskyed la /
NK022(za)001:3462: +aahmh'u gsum gyi sngags bzlas dkyil 'khor gyi lha'i 'od
NK022(za)001:3463: zer gsol byang la 'phros nas thim pas sku gsung
NK022(za)001:3464: thugs kyi dngos grub kyi ngo bo yi ge 'bru
NK022(za)001:3466: de ni che mchog glang po'i dkyil 'khor zhes bya'o //
NK022(za)001:3472: de nas de dag tshar ba dang /
NK022(za)001:3473: slob bu rnams phyir phyung la khrus bya /
NK022(za)001:3474: rdo rje rgyal theb kyis nang du dbang gi khri rtsig /
NK022(za)001:3475: de'i bar rdo rje slob dpon gyis rang nyid dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa'i cho ga bya ste /
NK022(za)001:3476: khrus byas la gos gsar pa gyon nas dkyil 'khor
NK022(za)001:3477: gyi shar phyogs su phyin nas stan bde ba la
NK022(za)001:3478: 'dug ste / lag tu me tog thogs la thal mo sbyar te /
NK022(za)001:3479: ye shes rgyal pos gsol ba btab la /
NK022(za)001:3480: dkyil 'khor gyi lha la me tog gtor cing /
NK022(za)001:3481: badz+ra kro ta sa ma ya /
NK022(za)001:3482: zhes pa'i sngags tshan lngas pi ti bskul /
NK022(za)001:3483: de nas bdag gi lus ngag yid gsum las /
NK022(za)001:3484: 'od dkar dmar mthing gsum 'phros nas dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams kyi sku gsung thugs la phog pas /
NK022(za)001:3485: lha thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs mchod pa chen pos mnyes par byas /
NK022(za)001:3486: khyad par du'ang dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo'i steng na
NK022(za)001:3487: rang gang mos pa'i bla ma de bzhugs pa de
NK022(za)001:3488: yang mchod pas mnyes par bya'o //
NK022(za)001:3489: de nas thal mo sbyar la ngag tu /
NK022(za)001:3490: bla ma rdo rje 'dzin pa chen po dang /
NK022(za)001:3491: rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs rnams dang /
NK022(za)001:3492: lha dang mkha' 'gro rig pa 'dzin pa thams cad bdag la dgongs su gsol lo //
NK022(za)001:3493: bdag rdo rje slob dpon gyis sems can thams cad kyi don bya ba dang /
NK022(za)001:3494: slob ma 'di rnams 'khor ba las yongs su bsgral ba'i slad du /
NK022(za)001:3495: 'dus pa chen po'i dbang bskur bar 'tshal gyis /
NK022(za)001:3496: bdag gi ngag nus pa dang ldan par byin gyis brlab tu gsol /
NK022(za)001:3498: bla ma dang dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo'i sku gsung
NK022(za)001:3499: thugs la 'od zer dkar dmar mthing gsum byung nas
NK022(za)001:3500: / bdag gi lus ngag yid gsum la thim pas /
NK022(za)001:3501: lus ngag yid gsum gyi rtogs pa rang rgyud pa dag nas /
NK022(za)001:3502: lha'i sku gsung thugs dang gnyis su med pa'i rang bzhin du bsam /
NK022(za)001:3503: des mtshon nas lha thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs la 'od byung nas /
NK022(za)001:3504: bdag la thim pas bdag dang lha tha dad med par bsam /
NK022(za)001:3505: de nas lha thams cad zhal 'dzum pa dang bcas nas /
NK022(za)001:3506: rigs kyi bu phrin las ci dga' bar spyod cig ces gnang ba thob par bsam /
NK022(za)001:3507: de nas slob bu dbang bskur ba'i dbang rnams bdag nyid kyang lha la zhu /
NK022(za)001:3508: bdag sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las kyi gzi
NK022(za)001:3509: brjid dang ldan par bsam la dbang khri'i steng 'dzeg
NK022(za)001:3510: go // 'di dag ni slob dpon bdag 'jug gi pra khrid ces bya'o //
NK022(za)001:3512: rdo rje rgyal theb kyis nang nas gu gul gyi dud pa thogs la /
NK022(za)001:3513: bdud rtsi 'khyil pa'i sngags rings kyis bgegs bskrad /
NK022(za)001:3514: de nas phyi nas las mkhan gyis sna drangs la ru lu gar gyi dbyangs brjod cing /
NK022(za)001:3516: rdo rje slob dpon la skor ba lan gsum byas la gral rim du bzhugs so //
NK022(za)001:3517: de nas slob ma dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa'i cho ga bya ste /
NK022(za)001:3519: de nas slob ma bzhugs par bya /
NK022(za)001:3523: r+au tra dkyil 'khor du bzhugs pa'i cho ga don sum cus ston pa ste /
NK022(za)001:3524: bag tsam lag tu blang mi bde gsung nas /
NK022(za)001:3525: rdo rje las kyi rim pa ltar don bco brgyad dam /
NK022(za)001:3526: bcu bdun pos 'di ltar mdzad de //
NK022(za)001:3527: thog mar dbang phyug 'jug pa sogs nas //
NK022(za)001:3528: gnyis pa bzod par gsol ba ni /
NK022(za)001:3529: rdo rje slob dpon gyis thal mo sbyar la //
NK022(za)001:3530: rdo rje ye shes thob byed pa'i //
NK022(za)001:3531: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi //
NK022(za)001:3533: bdag gi slob ma bzhug par bgyi //
NK022(za)001:3534: bzod par mdzad de dgongs su gsol //
NK022(za)001:3536: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad zhal 'dzum pa dang
NK022(za)001:3537: bcas nas dkyil 'khor du chug cig par gnang ba
NK022(za)001:3538: thob par bsams / de nas lnga pa dri ba ni /
NK022(za)001:3539: bu khyod dga' ba ci la dga' //
NK022(za)001:3540: bu khyod dad pa ci la dad //
NK022(za)001:3541: khyod kyi dgos pa ji lta bu //
NK022(za)001:3542: da lta nyid du 'dir smros shig /
NK022(za)001:3544: slob bu rnams kyis bdag ni skal ldan bden chen te //
NK022(za)001:3546: byang chub sems la bdag dad do //
NK022(za)001:3547: theg chen chos la bdag mos so //
NK022(za)001:3549: yang slob bu rnams kyis gsol ba btab pa ni /
NK022(za)001:3550: e ma bde gshegs snying po nas //
NK022(za)001:3551: ye nas lhun rdzogs sangs rgyas chos //
NK022(za)001:3552: khyed kyis rang la bstan du gsol //
NK022(za)001:3553: ye shes rdo rje'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK022(za)001:3554: rdo rje lam nas drangs nas kyang //
NK022(za)001:3556: byin rlabs dbang mchog blang bar bagyi'o //
NK022(za)001:3558: de nas drug pa lus dbul ba ni /
NK022(za)001:3559: h'u rang lus gdos pas bcings pa'i phung po 'di //
NK022(za)001:3560: bdag med rgyal ba'i zhing du sbyar ba'i phyir //
NK022(za)001:3561: lus srog rdzas kyi mchod pa dam pa 'di //
NK022(za)001:3562: bla med dman pa'i mchod par 'bul lags na //
NK022(za)001:3563: gnyis su med pa'i tshul gyis dgongs nas su //
NK022(za)001:3564: blang dor med pa'i tshul gyis bzhes su gsol //
NK022(za)001:3566: bdun pa b+he na badz+rasa bgegs bskrad /
NK022(za)001:3567: de nas slob bu rnams kyi klad pa dung khang du /
NK022(za)001:3568: ma las nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor gyi 'phro 'du las 'od 'phros pas /
NK022(za)001:3569: 'od kyis lus 'go mjug khyab par bsam /
NK022(za)001:3570: a yu h'u dza ces brjod pas /
NK022(za)001:3571: tshe'i rang bzhin mu tig dkar po dri ma med par ltar gyur par bsams /
NK022(za)001:3572: de nas yang klad pa dung khang du b+h+ru ces pa'i 'phro 'du las /
NK022(za)001:3573: zla kham dmar po sga zhes pa zhig bsam /
NK022(za)001:3574: de'i nang badz+ra kro ta h'u zhes h'u ka ra bskyed /
NK022(za)001:3575: badz+ra kro ta ar+ya a tsa la h'u zhes mi g.yo mgon pos sgo srungs par bsams /
NK022(za)001:3576: de nas sgrib pa bral ba ni /
NK022(za)001:3577: bdag gi dpal du gsal ba'i sor mo bcu la nyi zla'i gdan gyi steng du /
NK022(za)001:3579: rigs lnga yab yum gyi 'phro 'du byas nas bden pa brjod pa ni /
NK022(za)001:3580: na mo phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs
NK022(za)001:3581: pa thams cad kyi bden pa'i byin gyi rlabs kyis
NK022(za)001:3582: / gang zag 'di rnams kyi rgyud la gnas pa'i las dang nyon mongs pa'i sgrib pa dang /
NK022(za)001:3583: lta ba dman zhing shes rab zhan pa'i sgrib pa dang /
NK022(za)001:3584: khyad par du gsang sngags chen po'i dkyil 'khor gyi
NK022(za)001:3585: sgor zhugs gsang ba zab mo'i dbang nod pa la
NK022(za)001:3586: / sgrib pa grangs kyi rim pa bzhin du gnas
NK022(za)001:3587: pa thams cad skad cig tsam la byang zhing dag
NK022(za)001:3588: / par gyur cig / badz+ra b+han+d+ha tra th+aa /
NK022(za)001:3590: sgrib pa ma lus pas sregs sbyangs nas sems nyid shel sgong lta bur gyur par bsam /
NK022(za)001:3591: de ka la badz+ra a be sha ya a a zhes brjod pas /
NK022(za)001:3592: gong gi khro bo de 'od du zhu nas lus bkrag dang ldan par bsams la /
NK022(za)001:3593: rang gang mos pa'i lha'i sngags phog pa'i lhar bskyed pa go bgos lus srungs byas la bdag go //
NK022(za)001:3594: de nas yang slob bu rnams kyis thal mo sbyar la ngag tu /
NK022(za)001:3595: rdo rje rnal 'byor mchog gi lha //
NK022(za)001:3597: rdo rje can la phyag 'tshal te //
NK022(za)001:3598: byams mgon khyed la skyabs su mchi //
NK022(za)001:3601: sangs rgyas dag ni thams cad kyi //
NK022(za)001:3602: gsang ba rdo rje gsum las byung //
NK022(za)001:3603: khams gsum kun gyis phyag byas pas //
NK022(za)001:3604: dbang bskur gnang ba chen po sbyin //
NK022(za)001:3606: de nas dam tshig gi sdom pa blang zhing rdo rje slob dpon bskul ba ni /
NK022(za)001:3607: a a la la te zhes pa'i tshig bzhi dang /
NK022(za)001:3608: byang chub rdo rje'i tshig bzhi slob bus brjod la /
NK022(za)001:3609: slob dpon gyis badz+ra a mri ta +aahmh'u h+r+ai th+aa zhes brjod nas /
NK022(za)001:3610: rdo rjes bdud rtsi lce thog tu bzhag pas dam tshig gi snod dang ldan par bsam /
NK022(za)001:3611: de nas dam tshig de nyid tshig gi sgo nas 'bog ste /
NK022(za)001:3612: dpal ldan rdo rje sku gsung thugs 'chang ba /
NK022(za)001:3614: dam tshig sdom pa chen po 'di //
NK022(za)001:3615: sngar gyi rgyal ba rnams kyi thugs //
NK022(za)001:3616: da lta nga'i snying la gnas //
NK022(za)001:3617: de nas mched lcam kun gyi srog /
NK022(za)001:3618: ces brjod la +aahmh'u gsum gyis sbyin /
NK022(za)001:3619: de nas dam tshig de nyid srungs cig par bka' nan bya ba ni /
NK022(za)001:3620: bu'i snying khar rdo rje bzhag la /
NK022(za)001:3621: sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang ba 'di //
NK022(za)001:3622: dam nyams ma 'dres gang la ni //
NK022(za)001:3623: nam yang smra bar ma byed cig /
NK022(za)001:3624: theg pa chen po ston byed pa //
NK022(za)001:3625: nga la brnyas dang smad mi rung //
NK022(za)001:3626: sku gsung thugs la rtag gnas te //
NK022(za)001:3627: ma lus sems can don gyis shig /
NK022(za)001:3629: bcu gcig pa chu nan bya ba ni /
NK022(za)001:3630: de nas tsan+dana dkar dmar sbyar ba'i chu rdo rje gnod sbyin du bskyed la /
NK022(za)001:3631: sngar gyi dam tshig de dag ma srungs na skyon yod par dam bsgrags pa ni /
NK022(za)001:3632: 'di ni khyod kyi dmyal ba'i chu //
NK022(za)001:3633: dam tshig 'das na sreg par byed //
NK022(za)001:3634: rdo rje khro bo chen po 'gyur //
NK022(za)001:3635: rdo rje chu 'di btung bar gyis //
NK022(za)001:3638: srungs na yon tan yod do bar bsgrags pa ni /
NK022(za)001:3639: de lta bas na bu khyod kyi /
NK022(za)001:3640: dam tshig 'di dag bsrung bar gyis //
NK022(za)001:3641: dam tshig srungs na dngos grub 'byung //
NK022(za)001:3642: rdo rje bdud rtsi'i chu 'thung shig /
NK022(za)001:3643: badz+ra ud ka tra h'u th+aa zhes sbyin /
NK022(za)001:3645: rgyal bas gsungs pa'i ye shes gang //
NK022(za)001:3646: de ring dngos grub mchog tu gsungs //
NK022(za)001:3647: dam tshig che ba'i chen po mchog /
NK022(za)001:3648: bye brag med par khyed kyis spyod //
NK022(za)001:3649: dge dang mi dge'i chos rnams la //
NK022(za)001:3650: lhag par brten par mi bya ste //
NK022(za)001:3651: mnyam nyid rin chen klong zhugs nas //
NK022(za)001:3652: ci la yang thogs pa med par spyod /
NK022(za)001:3653: kye ma rgyal ba'i rigs su gyur pa'i bu khyod rnams /
NK022(za)001:3654: rdo rje slob dpon snying ltar khur //
NK022(za)001:3655: rdo rje mched la mig bzhin gyis //
NK022(za)001:3656: yi dam lha ni dpon ltar khur //
NK022(za)001:3657: gsang ba'i dam tshig rang mtshan ltar //
NK022(za)001:3658: nam yang de bzhin sems par gyis //
NK022(za)001:3659: sems can thams cad bu ltar zung //
NK022(za)001:3660: rgyal ba'i bka' las ma 'da' shig /
NK022(za)001:3663: sangs rgyas kun dang mnyam sbyor ba'i //
NK022(za)001:3664: dam tshig sdom pa chen po ni //
NK022(za)001:3665: lha rnams dang ni mi rnams dang //
NK022(za)001:3666: bsgrub pa po dang rnal 'byor pa //
NK022(za)001:3667: de dag nyams na khrag chen po //
NK022(za)001:3668: nyams pa'i snying nas drangs te 'thung //
NK022(za)001:3669: i dan te na ra kan zhes bsgrag go //
NK022(za)001:3670: de nas bcu gsum pa rin po che'i me tog dor te /
NK022(za)001:3671: me tog la sogs rin chen phreng //
NK022(za)001:3672: sngon tshe ye shes bsnyen pa'i lha //
NK022(za)001:3673: thugs rjes bzung bar dgongs nas kyang //
NK022(za)001:3674: gang yin de la 'bab gyur cig /
NK022(za)001:3675: pra ti dza badz+ra ho zhes brjod la rigs gang la phog pa brtag go //
NK022(za)001:3676: de nas bcu bzhi pa lha dbab ste /
NK022(za)001:3677: sngar rigs gang la phog pa ste /
NK022(za)001:3678: dam tshig gi phyag rgyas rang rang gi snying gi dkyil du bstim mo //
NK022(za)001:3679: de nas bco lnga pa lha mi spang bar bya ba'i phyir nan tan bya ba ni /
NK022(za)001:3680: lha ma bsgom pa'i skyon dang /
NK022(za)001:3681: bsgom pa'i yon tan bshad de /
NK022(za)001:3683: dad med nyams na phung bar 'gyur ces pa dang /
NK022(za)001:3684: lha spangs dge spyad don med 'gyur //
NK022(za)001:3686: gang zhig phyag rgya 'di spangs na //
NK022(za)001:3687: zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs so //
NK022(za)001:3689: bdag nyid lha dang mnyam sbyar na //
NK022(za)001:3691: lha'i sku nyid gsal sgoms na //
NK022(za)001:3693: de nyid chu zla'i tshul shes na //
NK022(za)001:3694: ye shes tshogs chen rdzogs par 'gyur //
NK022(za)001:3696: de nas bcu drug pa mig dbye ste /
NK022(za)001:3697: rus lag tu rdo rje thogs la /
NK022(za)001:3698: de ring dad pa'i shugs kyis ni //
NK022(za)001:3700: sangs rgyas gdung gi rigs su 'khrungs //
NK022(za)001:3701: sangs rgyas dngos grub thams cad ni //
NK022(za)001:3702: brten nas thob par gyur pa yin //
NK022(za)001:3703: badz+ra tsak+shu pra be sha ya phata /
NK022(za)001:3705: ma rig pa'i mun pa bsal nas rang la ye
NK022(za)001:3706: nas gnas pa'i dkyil 'khor don mthong bar bsam mo
NK022(za)001:3707: // de nas bcu bdun pa dkyil 'khor dang lha'i don rtags bshad pa ni /
NK022(za)001:3708: chos kyi dbyings spros pa thams cad dang bral ba'i rtags su lte ba zlum po'o //
NK022(za)001:3709: ye shes lnga dang ldan pa'i rtags su 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi lte ba dang lngar byung /
NK022(za)001:3710: ye nas rgyu 'bras gnyis su med pa'i phyir rdo rje'i ra ba /
NK022(za)001:3711: tshad med pa bzhi dang ldan pa'i phyir gru chad bzhi byung /
NK022(za)001:3712: lhag pa'i ye shes phrin las bzhi dang ldan pa'i phyir glo 'bur bzhi /
NK022(za)001:3713: che ba'i yon tan phyogs med nas rgyas pa'i rtags su gru bzhi lham par byung ba /
NK022(za)001:3714: ting nge 'dzin bzhi'i rtags su sgo bzhi /
NK022(za)001:3715: dur khrod kyi thod pa skam rlon la gnam lcags kyi gzer gyis gtams pa ni /
NK022(za)001:3716: sku lnga lhun gyis grub pa'i rtags /
NK022(za)001:3717: zhing lpags kha sbyar gyi sgo la skar ma'i gzer gyis gtams nas /
NK022(za)001:3718: rus sbal gyi ma them la chu srin gyi ya them zhing skam po'i sgo skyes /
NK022(za)001:3720: gza' chen po brgyad kyi gdung /
NK022(za)001:3721: rgyu skar nyi shu rtsa brgyad kyi phyam gyis gtams nas /
NK022(za)001:3722: sbrul nag 'bar bas gral ma byas pa ni 'khor ba ma spangs dor ba med pa'i rtags /
NK022(za)001:3723: de dag ni nang dur khrod 'bar ba'i rtags yin /
NK022(za)001:3724: rang bzhin gyis sku lnga lhun gyis grub pa'i phyir rtsig pa lnga sbrag tu byung ba dang /
NK022(za)001:3725: rin chen 'bar ba'i ka ba la /
NK022(za)001:3726: rin po che'i gdung brgyad 'go bsnol ba /
NK022(za)001:3727: rin po che gzhan rnam pa mang po'i gral phyam
NK022(za)001:3728: gyis gtams pa ni ma rig pa'i mun pa sel
NK022(za)001:3729: ba'i rtags / zla phyed rdo rje'i rdung mgo dang /
NK022(za)001:3730: bcu gcig rdo rjes gtams pa ni pha rol gyi rgol ba gzhan gyis mi shigs pa'i rtags /
NK022(za)001:3731: dra ba dra phyed mu tig gi phreng ba can
NK022(za)001:3732: gyi gseb nas gzugs la sogs pa'i lha mo mang
NK022(za)001:3734: pha gu rin chen seng mgo can du byung ba dang /
NK022(za)001:3735: mda' yab dkar po pu shu'i tshul du byung bas
NK022(za)001:3736: yongs su bskor ba ni che ba'i yon tan ma
NK022(za)001:3737: 'gags cing / chos rnams lhun gyis grub pa mtshon pa'i rtags /
NK022(za)001:3738: theg pa brgyad nas bgrod cing 'bras bu thob pa'i rtags su rta babs brgyad byung /
NK022(za)001:3743: chu srin gyi skye nas dar chen gyi mtsho dang /
NK022(za)001:3744: dpag bsam gyi ljon shing gis yongs su bskor ba
NK022(za)001:3745: ni 'khor 'das gnyis su med cing rtog pa dang
NK022(za)001:3747: rdo rje ra bas yongs su bskor ba ni ji
NK022(za)001:3748: ltar snang yang don gnyis med las ma 'das pa'i
NK022(za)001:3749: rtags / bskal ba'i me ris yongs su bskor ba ni thams cad la dbang bsgyur ba'i rtags /
NK022(za)001:3750: de dag ni dkyil 'khor gyi don rtags bshad pa'o //
NK022(za)001:3751: lha'i don rtags bshad pa ni /
NK022(za)001:3752: me tog phog pa'i lha'i snying po /
NK022(za)001:3757: de rnams bshad la lha ngo shes su bzhug go //
NK022(za)001:3758: 'dir bco lnga pa ma sgom na skyon yod pas sgoms shig pa'i nan tan mdzad do //
NK022(za)001:3759: bco brgyad pa yon dbul ba ni /
NK022(za)001:3760: dbang bskur ba'i ting la dbul ba phyag bzhes yin no //
NK022(za)001:3761: de ltar dkyil 'khor gyi don rtags dang /
NK022(za)001:3763: de dag gi khungs smos pa'am yid ches par bya ba'i phyir brgyud pa khungs kyi gtad rgya'am /
NK022(za)001:3764: zab mo dbang gi gleng gzhi gdams pa dang bcas pa bshad pa ni las 'di ru gzigs shig /
NK022(za)001:3765: de nas brgyud pa'i khungs ngo shes nas grub pa'i 'bras bu thob pa'i phyir /
NK022(za)001:3766: dngos grub blang ba'i rim pa ni /
NK022(za)001:3767: thog mar 'byung po lta nyan tshar bcad pa'i phyir khro bo bcu'i mtshams drag tu bcad /
NK022(za)001:3768: lha dang mkhon lcugs sbyang ba'i phyir bshags pa rgyas bsdus gang rung bya /
NK022(za)001:3769: 'gro don mthar phyin par bya ba'i phyir dam bca' /
NK022(za)001:3770: rang nyid gzi byin dang ldan par bya ba'i phyir byin dbab /
NK022(za)001:3771: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga'i dngos grub nye rtogs su ster ba'i phyir /
NK022(za)001:3772: nga ni dpal ldan rdo rje /
NK022(za)001:3776: rgya gram 'chang la sogs pas lha dbab /
NK022(za)001:3777: dngos grub kyi snod du rung bar bya ba'i phyir /
NK022(za)001:3778: nam mkha'i mtha' klas chos kyi dbyings la sogs pas po ti bskul /
NK022(za)001:3779: de'i rjes su rig 'dzin dngos grub las 'di ltar bskul /
NK022(za)001:3780: ye shes lha'i dngos grub dus nye bar thob par
NK022(za)001:3781: bya ba'i phyir gsal shing gi cho ga yang las
NK022(za)001:3783: de dag legs par tshar ba dang /
NK022(za)001:3784: dkyil 'khor lha'i dbang bskur bar bya ste /
NK022(za)001:3785: de yang dbang don bsdus pa'i rgyud las /
NK022(za)001:3786: yo ga la sogs theg drug la //
NK022(za)001:3787: phyi dbang brgyud kyi chu bso bya //
NK022(za)001:3788: bskyed pa ma ha yo ga ni //
NK022(za)001:3789: nang dbang 'byung ba'i chu bso bya //
NK022(za)001:3790: rdzogs pa a nu yo ga la //
NK022(za)001:3791: sgrub dbang grags pa'i chu bso bya //
NK022(za)001:3792: rdzogs chen a ti yo ga ni //
NK022(za)001:3793: gsang dbang rdzogs pa'i chu bso bya //
NK022(za)001:3795: yang dbang don rgyas pa las /
NK022(za)001:3796: sa bcu'i byang chub rigs can 'gyur //
NK022(za)001:3797: bcu gcig gsang sngags nang pa ste //
NK022(za)001:3798: bcu gsum bla ma chen po grags //
NK022(za)001:3800: yo ga la sogs pa sngon du 'gro ba'i dbang rdzogs nas /
NK022(za)001:3801: da gsang sngags nang gi dbang bskur ba la /
NK022(za)001:3802: dbang mchog sum cu so drug tu grags te /
NK022(za)001:3804: phyi dang nang dang gsang ba yi //
NK022(za)001:3805: bcu dang bcu gcig bcu gsum dang //
NK022(za)001:3806: rnam pa gnyis kyi khyad par gyis //
NK022(za)001:3807: dbang mchog sum cu so drug rdzogs //
NK022(za)001:3812: zab mo'i dbang gnyis su bstan pa las /
NK022(za)001:3814: ma h+aa dang a nu gnyis thun mong du bstan pa las /
NK022(za)001:3815: ngos bzung nas ngo sprad pa med /
NK022(za)001:3816: lam khyer gyi dbang du byas na /
NK022(za)001:3817: theg pa ma h+aa ngos bzung /
NK022(za)001:3818: dbang la phyi dbang dang nang dbang ma h+aa ltar ngos bzung /
NK022(za)001:3819: bsgrub dbang gsang dbang gnyis a nu ltar ngos bzung /
NK022(za)001:3820: de la 'dir gang yang rung bar phyir dbang bskur ba'i dbang du byas na /
NK022(za)001:3821: slob dpon chen po chas gos dang ldan par byas stan brjid bag dang ldan pa la /
NK022(za)001:3822: slob ma la sogs pa kun yang chas gos dang ldan par byas /
NK022(za)001:3825: thor tshugs la sogs mdzes par byas /
NK022(za)001:3826: man+dala mdzes par byas pa'i steng du tshom bu bkod /
NK022(za)001:3827: 'khor lo'i gdan phul nas 'khor lo'i gdan la bzhugs /
NK022(za)001:3828: lag tu kha gser kha g.yu la sogs thogs la brjid dang ldan par dbang bskur ba ni /
NK022(za)001:3829: rgyal po ltar bskur ba yin gsungs /
NK022(za)001:3830: yang slob dpon gyis kyang 'chag che chung la sogs legs par byas /
NK022(za)001:3833: dri bzang pos legs par byugs /
NK022(za)001:3834: gtsang ma'i gos gyon dpral ba /
NK022(za)001:3836: snying kha la sogs par dri bzang po'i thig le byas nas /
NK022(za)001:3837: gtsang sar bzhugs pa la slob ma la sogs pa rnams kyang /
NK022(za)001:3841: gtsang ba'i zas zos nas skyon gyis ma gos pa rnam par dag pa la dbang bskur ba ni /
NK022(za)001:3842: bram ze ltar dbang bskur ba bya ba yin gsung /
NK022(za)001:3843: yang slob dpon kyang ye shes lha'i ngang la gtsang sme'i rtog pa thams cad dang bral nas /
NK022(za)001:3844: brtul zhugs chen po'i ngar dang ldan par gnas pa la /
NK022(za)001:3845: slob ma rnams kyang ya nga ba dang bag tsha ba med par /
NK022(za)001:3846: mos pa dang gus pa'i brtul zhugs dang ldan par gnas pa la dbang bskur ba ni /
NK022(za)001:3847: brdal pa ltar dbang bskur ba yin gsung /
NK022(za)001:3848: de ltar de dag ni bzlog pa tha dad par
NK022(za)001:3849: snang yang dbang bskur ba'i dus su gsum ka 'grub
NK022(za)001:3850: ste gcig tu 'byung ba yin gsung /
NK022(za)001:3851: de lta bas na dbang stegs bzang po'i steng du
NK022(za)001:3852: 'dug ste yi dam gang yin kyang che mchog chen
NK022(za)001:3853: po'i nga rgyal du zhugs la /
NK022(za)001:3854: spyi bo nas rta'i 'dur glu phyogs bcu ru 'tsher
NK022(za)001:3855: zhing bsgrags pas sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa'
NK022(za)001:3856: thams cad mdun gyi nam mkha' la byon nas /
NK022(za)001:3857: bdag nyid kyi lus ngag yid gsum la thal /
NK022(za)001:3858: dbang bskur ba'i nus pa dang ldan par byas /
NK022(za)001:3859: yang brgyud pa'i bla ma rnams kyang byon /
NK022(za)001:3860: rta'i rna ba gnyis phum phum gyi gseb tu brgyud pa'i ngo bo bla ma yin pas /
NK022(za)001:3861: bla ma rin po che'i phung po'am 'od kyi phung
NK022(za)001:3862: po 'od zer dang bcas pa gcig tu bsgoms nas
NK022(za)001:3863: / slob ma rnams kyi bag chags dang snod ngan pa'i dri ma dag par bsams te /
NK022(za)001:3864: de dag ni phrin las kyi srog shing yin zhes gsung ngo //
NK022(za)001:3865: snying rje byang chub kyi sems dang ldan pas sems kyi dpa' bskyed /
NK022(za)001:3866: sems can 'di dag 'khor ba las bsgral nas thar
NK022(za)001:3867: pa'i lam la dgod du yod pa 'di dga' bsnyan
NK022(za)001:3869: rnal 'byor rang 'dod skad cig tsam yang med par
NK022(za)001:3870: thag bcad pa ni phrin las kyi gzhung shing yin
NK022(za)001:3871: gsung / de nas slob ma rnams la dper na
NK022(za)001:3872: yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin po che dbang gi
NK022(za)001:3873: rgyal po de dgos don thams cad kyi 'byung gnas
NK022(za)001:3874: gsung / yin pas / rang gis ji ltar gsol ba btab pa bzhin 'byung ba ltar du /
NK022(za)001:3875: bla ma yang dgos 'dod thams cad kyi 'byung gnas /
NK022(za)001:3876: nor bu rin po che lta bu lags pas /
NK022(za)001:3877: ji ltar gsol ba btab pa ltar 'byung bas gsol ba thob cig par bskul la /
NK022(za)001:3878: slob bus gsol ba btab pa ni /
NK022(za)001:3879: sangs rgyas rdo rje 'dzin pa la //
NK022(za)001:3880: sa mtha'i sems dpa' chen po yis //
NK022(za)001:3881: ji ltar mchod cing zhus pa ltar /
NK022(za)001:3882: de bzhin skal ldan bdag cag la //
NK022(za)001:3883: rnal 'byor dbang phyug chen po yis //
NK022(za)001:3884: dbang rnams rim par stsal du gsol //
NK022(za)001:3887: sangs rgyas dag ni thams cad kyi //
NK022(za)001:3888: gsang ba rdo rje gsum las byung //
NK022(za)001:3889: khams gsum kun gyis phyag bgyis pas //
NK022(za)001:3890: dbang bskur gnang ba chen po sbyin //
NK022(za)001:3892: de nas dbyangs dang bcas pas /
NK022(za)001:3894: slob bu rnams la dbang bskur bas //
NK022(za)001:3895: sems can don du bdag brtson na //
NK022(za)001:3896: bzod pa mdzod de dgongs su gsol //
NK022(za)001:3897: badz+ra sa ma ya h'u dza /
NK022(za)001:3899: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa thams
NK022(za)001:3900: cad mdun gyi nam mkha' la sprin dpung bzhin du
NK022(za)001:3901: byon nas / dbang bskur cig par bka' stsal bar bsam /
NK022(za)001:3902: de nas shu dz+nya ta la sogs pa'i sngags brjod la /
NK022(za)001:3904: ka ya wak+ka tsit+ta'i sngags brjod nas /
NK022(za)001:3905: bdag nyid sku gsung thugs kyi gzi byin dang ldan par bsams la /
NK022(za)001:3907: rgyal ba sangs rgyas thams cad kun //
NK022(za)001:3909: dang ba'i yid kyis zhugs nas kyang //
NK022(za)001:3910: byin brlabs dbang mchog nod par mdzod //
NK022(za)001:3912: dbang bzhi yongs su rdzogs par bskur te /
NK022(za)001:3913: thog mar phyi phan pa'i dbang bcu la /
NK022(za)001:3914: dang po zhi ba lha'i phyag rgya'i dbang /
NK022(za)001:3918: lnga la bkra shis rdzas brgyad kyi dbang /
NK022(za)001:3919: drug pa rin chen sna bdun dbang /
NK022(za)001:3921: brgyad pa brgyan cha rtags kyi dbang /
NK022(za)001:3925: dang po gsang ba nyan pa'i dbang /
NK022(za)001:3928: bzhi pa rdo rje rgyal po'i dbang /
NK022(za)001:3930: drug pa thun mong ma yin pa rin chen sna bdun gyi dbang /
NK022(za)001:3931: bdun pa zhi khro phyag rgya chen po'i dbang /
NK022(za)001:3932: brgyad pa sku gsung thugs kyi dbang /
NK022(za)001:3934: bcu pa bkra shis rtags kyi dbang /
NK022(za)001:3935: bcu gcig pa thig le ming gi dbang ngo //
NK022(za)001:3936: bsgrub pa'i dbang bcu gsum la /
NK022(za)001:3937: dang po shes rig pa'i dbang /
NK022(za)001:3938: gnyis pa khams gsum byang chub sems kyi dbang /
NK022(za)001:3939: gsum pa yi ge 'khor lo'i dbang /
NK022(za)001:3940: bzhi pa 'gro don rdzogs byed thong gshol gyi dbang /
NK022(za)001:3941: lnga pa dug gsum brtan sprugs thod pa tshar gsum gyi dbang /
NK022(za)001:3942: drug pa nyon mongs gcod pa mtshon cha'i dbang /
NK022(za)001:3943: bdun pa spyod bzhin ma chags pad+ma'i dbang /
NK022(za)001:3944: brgyad pa rnam bzhi las rdzogs sti ra dbyug pa'i dbang /
NK022(za)001:3945: dgu pa don dam dbyer med sbrul nag chun po'i dbang /
NK022(za)001:3946: bcu pa gnyis med sbyor rtags lha mo yum gyi dbang /
NK022(za)001:3947: bcu gcig pa bdag nyin chen po longs spyod sna tshogs kyi dbang /
NK022(za)001:3948: bcu gnyis pa mnga' bdag chen po bsgrub rdzas kyi dbang /
NK022(za)001:3949: bcu gsum pa grags pa rdo rje ming gi dbang /
NK022(za)001:3950: de dag ni tsa ka li na ji ltar yod pa bzhin du bskur la mgrin dbang du bya /
NK022(za)001:3951: gsang dbang ni skabs 'dir mi bskur bar las 'di'i man ngag gis /
NK022(za)001:3952: dbang steng gi skabs su phal gyi spyod pa ma
NK022(za)001:3953: yin par slob bu snod dang ldan pa la bla
NK022(za)001:3954: ma'i man ngag gis shes par byos shig /
NK022(za)001:3955: de nas rjes su thod sku bkod nas yod na yang dag bzhin bskur ro //
NK022(za)001:3957: lha dbang de dag 'chags par byed pa'i rten du /
NK022(za)001:3959: man ngag sgom pa gnyis las /
NK022(za)001:3961: sngar me tog phog pa'i lha gang yin pa de 'di ltar yin gyi ngo sprad /
NK022(za)001:3962: de'i rjes su snying po'i rjes gnang byin pas gsung ngo sprad /
NK022(za)001:3963: dbang rdzas mgo thog tu bzhag nas dbang bskur bas phrin las ngo sprad /
NK022(za)001:3964: de yang thog ma nas yin pa la yin pa ltar ngo sprad /
NK022(za)001:3965: shes pa ni gser sbram ngo shes pa lta bu ste de ni lha ngo sprad pa'o //
NK022(za)001:3966: des nye bar mtshon nas snang grags thams cad lha
NK022(za)001:3967: dang gzhal yas khang gi dkyil 'khor du longs spyod
NK022(za)001:3968: pa ni lha lam khyer du khyer ba'o //
NK022(za)001:3969: lhar snang ba thams cad sems nyid du thag chod pa ni lha la lhar rol pa'o //
NK022(za)001:3970: thams cad lha'i rang bzhin du lta ba ni lta ba'o //
NK022(za)001:3971: de'i ngang la gnas pa sgom pa /
NK022(za)001:3972: spyod lam rnam bzhi lha dang mi 'bral ba ni spyod pa /
NK022(za)001:3973: de las mi 'da' ba dam tshig /
NK022(za)001:3975: rnal 'byor gyi 'dug tshul ni glang po che rgun chang gis myos pa lta bu'o //
NK022(za)001:3976: thad ka ni ngang bsgom chung ngun gyi thad kar sleb ste /
NK022(za)001:3977: de yang bdag lhar gsal ba'i spyi bor thig le dmar po sran ma tsam zhig bsgom /
NK022(za)001:3978: de bas khru gang gis mtho bar thig le dkar po sran ma tsam zhig bsgom /
NK022(za)001:3979: de nas sna bug g.yon nas 'od dmar po sran ma tsam zhig byung nas /
NK022(za)001:3980: spyi bo'i thig le dmar po la phog pas /
NK022(za)001:3981: des bdag rkyen byas nas thig le dmar po la 'od 'phros pas /
NK022(za)001:3982: sems can la phog pas sems can gyi don byas
NK022(za)001:3983: de bzhin gshegs pa la phog pas thugs mnyes pa'i
NK022(za)001:3984: mchod pa phul / 'od tshur 'dus thig le dmar
NK022(za)001:3985: po la thim pas thig le dmar po 'od du
NK022(za)001:3986: mchod pa phul / zhu bar bsam / yang sna
NK022(za)001:3987: bug g.yas nas 'od dkar po byung nas gang gi
NK022(za)001:3988: thig le dkar po la phog pas /
NK022(za)001:3990: de bzhin gshegs pa thugs mnyes /
NK022(za)001:3991: tshur 'dus thig le dkar po la thim /
NK022(za)001:3992: de babs nas dmar po la thim pas /
NK022(za)001:3993: gnyis ka snying gi dkyil du thim pas dkar dmar
NK022(za)001:3994: 'dres nas rang gi spyi bo tshangs pa'i bu ga
NK022(za)001:3995: nas mar thim / de nyid snying gi dkyil du dkar dmar 'dres pa'i ngo bo /
NK022(za)001:3996: bde stong gnyis med kyi ngang la blo bskur la bzhag /
NK022(za)001:3997: de ni lha bsgom pa'i man ngag ces bya'o //
NK022(za)001:3998: da man ngag bsgom pa steng sgo dang 'og sgo gnyis las /
NK022(za)001:4000: ngang bsgom 'bring po'i thad kar sleb ste /
NK022(za)001:4001: rang gi lus rkyal stong lta bu stong sang nge ba'i nang na /
NK022(za)001:4002: rtsa a ba d+hu ti sbom phra mda' snyug tsam /
NK022(za)001:4003: phyi dmar la nang dkar ba /
NK022(za)001:4004: yar sna rtse'u chung la thugs pa mar sna gnyen
NK022(za)001:4005: po che la thug pa de ni srog shing yin
NK022(za)001:4007: 'og sgo rlung gi 'khor lo gnyis 'khri 'phang yin no //
NK022(za)001:4009: snying chos kyi 'khor lo bum pa /
NK022(za)001:4012: lus mchod rten chen po gcig du bsgom /
NK022(za)001:4013: de'i spyi bor srog mi shigs pa'i thig le /
NK022(za)001:4014: yi ge ham gi nang bzhin sran ma tsam zhig gnas pa la 'od phyogs bcur 'phros pas /
NK022(za)001:4015: 'phags pa mchod sems can gyi don byas /
NK022(za)001:4016: 'od tshur 'dus gong gi yi ge ham gi thig
NK022(za)001:4017: le la phog pas de 'od du zhu nas rang
NK022(za)001:4018: gi rtsa ba'i bla ma ni mchod rten gyi tog
NK022(za)001:4019: gi tshul du bzhugs par bsgom /
NK022(za)001:4020: de la shes pa bcug pas bla ma'ang 'od du zhu nas /
NK022(za)001:4021: spyi bo tshangs pa'i bu ga nas rang gi snying gi dkyil du /
NK022(za)001:4022: rang gi shes pa dang 'dres pa la blo bskyur la bzhag go //
NK022(za)001:4023: da 'og sgo bde ba bsgom pa ni /
NK022(za)001:4024: yang rang gi spyi bor thig le dmar po sran ma tsam zhig bsgom /
NK022(za)001:4025: de las mda' gang gis mtho bar thig le dkar po sran ma tsam zhig bsgom /
NK022(za)001:4026: dmar po de shes rab kyi cha yin la dkar po thabs kyi cha yin /
NK022(za)001:4027: de nas thig le dmar po de la shes pa
NK022(za)001:4028: bcug pas de chags pa'i rang bzhin yin pas 'dar
NK022(za)001:4029: ba bsgom / de 'dar bas bdag rkyen byas pas thig le dkar po'ang 'dar te /
NK022(za)001:4030: mar la babs nas dmar po la thim pas dkar dmar dbyer med du 'dres nas /
NK022(za)001:4031: spyi gtsug na mar thim pas snying gi dkyil du
NK022(za)001:4032: bde stong dbyer med du blos bskyur la bzhag go
NK022(za)001:4033: // de dag ma h+aa'i man ngag gi bsgom 'debs yin no //
NK022(za)001:4034: lung a nu yo ga'i dbang du bshad na /
NK022(za)001:4035: theg pa ni a nu yo ga'i theg pa /
NK022(za)001:4036: lta ba dbyings ye shes dbyer med /
NK022(za)001:4037: de'i ngang la gnas pa ni sgom pa /
NK022(za)001:4038: spyod lam rnam bzhi dbyings dang ye shes kyi ngang la spyod pa ni spyod pa /
NK022(za)001:4039: de las mi 'da' bar dam tshig /
NK022(za)001:4041: skabs kyi sgom chen gyi 'dug tshul ni chu bo chen po'i gzhung bzhin 'phel 'grib med pa'o //
NK022(za)001:4042: bsgom pa'i thabs ni ngang bsgom chen po'i thad kar sleb ste /
NK022(za)001:4043: de yang snying gi dkyil du thig le dkar po phug ron gyi sgo nga tsam zhig bsgom /
NK022(za)001:4045: 'od de spyi gtsug tshangs pa'i bu ga na yar skar mda' 'thon pa'i tshul du 'thon nas /
NK022(za)001:4046: de nyid thig le gcig la thig phran bsam gyis mi khyab pa 'phros nas /
NK022(za)001:4048: stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams khengs par bsam /
NK022(za)001:4049: thig phran thams cad tshur 'dus nas thig le spyi
NK022(za)001:4050: bo la thim pas thig phran rnams dang spyi bo
NK022(za)001:4051: gnyis su med pa'i dbyings ye shes dbyer med par
NK022(za)001:4052: sras bde ba chen po'i ngang la gnas par bya'o
NK022(za)001:4053: // zhes pa ni kun la med pa'i gdam ngag go //
NK022(za)001:4054: da ni gags drug po sbyar na /
NK022(za)001:4056: gang gis gang la gang bstan pa //
NK022(za)001:4057: ci'i phyir dang dgos pa ye gnas pa //
NK022(za)001:4058: 'di ni nang gi gags drug bstan pa yin //
NK022(za)001:4060: gang du gsungs pa'i gnas ni pad+ma me tog 'ja' tshon gyi tshal du'o //
NK022(za)001:4061: gang gis bskur ba'i slob dpon ni /
NK022(za)001:4062: slob dpon chen po ro langs bde ba'i dngos grub ces bya ba des so //
NK022(za)001:4063: gang la bskur na slob dpon chen po h'u mdzad
NK022(za)001:4064: rdo rje dang 'jam dpal bshes gnyen la sogs pa
NK022(za)001:4065: mngon par shes pa lnga dang ldan pa rnams la
NK022(za)001:4066: bskur / gang bskur ba'i dbang ni dbang mchog sum cu rtsa drug /
NK022(za)001:4071: gsang ba zab mo'i dbang gnyis bskur /
NK022(za)001:4072: rgyu mtshan ni mi lus lha ru bsgrub pa'i phyir dbang bskur /
NK022(za)001:4073: dgos pa'i 'bras bu ni yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi sa thob pa kho na'o //
NK022(za)001:4074: de dag ni nang gi gags drug ces bya'o //
NK022(za)001:4075: de ltar dbang chags par byed pa'i /
NK022(za)001:4077: man ngag gi 'debs la sogs pa tshar nas /
NK022(za)001:4078: ru lu dang g+hu ya dz+nya na thon tshad cig brjod la /
NK022(za)001:4079: bdag cag rdo rje slob dpon mched dang lcam dral gyi bsnyen pa dang /
NK022(za)001:4082: bsgrub pa chen po'i sgo nas /
NK022(za)001:4083: bzlas brjod kyi bsnyen pa bargya'am stong la sogs pa 'bul zhing mchis na /
NK022(za)001:4084: thugs rje chen pos dgongs shing bzhes nas bdag cag la /
NK022(za)001:4085: sku gsung thugs kyi po ti dus da lta nyid du thob par stsal du gsol lo //
NK022(za)001:4087: de nas mar me blangs la 'dus pa chen po'i lha tshogs rnams kyis /
NK022(za)001:4088: mi gnas pa'i ye shes dang /
NK022(za)001:4089: stong pa nyid kyi ye shes dang /
NK022(za)001:4090: me long lta bu'i ye shes dang /
NK022(za)001:4091: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes dang /
NK022(za)001:4092: so sor rtog pa'i ye shes dang /
NK022(za)001:4093: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes dang /
NK022(za)001:4094: klong du gyur pa'i ye shes dang /
NK022(za)001:4095: dbyings su bsgrol ba'i ye shes dang /
NK022(za)001:4096: mda' dka' thugs kyi ye shes dang /
NK022(za)001:4097: thugs ye shes dgu'i nang nas 'char ba'i pi ti bdag cag rdo rje slob dpon dang /
NK022(za)001:4098: mched dang lcam dral rnams kyis thob po a la la ho zhes kun la 'grim mo //
NK022(za)001:4099: de nas tshe dbang bskur te /
NK022(za)001:4100: a yu dmar po rdo rje dbang gi tshe /
NK022(za)001:4101: zhes pa dbyangs dang sngags dang smon lam la sogs pa brjod la kun la bskur /
NK022(za)001:4102: de nas gsol byang blangs la /
NK022(za)001:4103: ltar dkar la 'tsher ba la sogs pa dang /
NK022(za)001:4104: ka ya wa ka tsit+ta la sogs pa brjod la sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub blang /
NK022(za)001:4105: mched lcam gzhan rnams la gsol byang gi nang nas ting gis dum zhig bcus la /
NK022(za)001:4106: de nas las mkhan gyis gzhan ma rnams la sbyin no //
NK022(za)001:4107: de nas zhal zas kyi dbang bskur ba ni /
NK022(za)001:4108: las mkhan gyis tshogs mchod zur tsam byas kyang mi 'gal /
NK022(za)001:4109: zla kha zhal gyi dkyil 'khor du //
NK022(za)001:4110: rang gi ye shes mngon snang ba'i //
NK022(za)001:4111: 'dod don gsang ba'i longs spyod brgyan //
NK022(za)001:4112: yongs su rdzogs pa'i dngos grub stsol //
NK022(za)001:4113: bdag cag rdo rje slob dpon mched dang lcam dral rnams kyis rdo rje tshe gsol bas /
NK022(za)001:4114: tshe dbang phun sum tshogs pa'i bskal ba dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK022(za)001:4115: ma h+aa mang sa gsol bas rnal 'byor gyi dbang phyug chen po thob par gyur cig /
NK022(za)001:4116: 'dza' gad dpa' bo gsol bas 'gro ba mang po dbang du 'dus par gyur cig /
NK022(za)001:4117: zla rgyas gsol bas tshogs gnyis rgyun du rdzogs par gyur cig /
NK022(za)001:4118: gal phyis gsol bas bsam pa thams cad lhun gyis grub par gyur cig /
NK022(za)001:4119: zla phrom gsol bas chos nyid zhi ba'i ting nge 'dzin dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK022(za)001:4120: 'jam des gsol bas byang chub kyi sems dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK022(za)001:4121: zhal zas kha ba dang dngar ba dang /
NK022(za)001:4123: ro rnam pa sna tshogs gsol bas zhi khro sprul pa'i tshogs la mnga' brnyes par gyur cig /
NK022(za)001:4124: ces brjod pa pi ti'i zhal zas rnams kun gyis rim par rol lo //
NK022(za)001:4125: de nas dngos grub kyi lhag ma gsum la /
NK022(za)001:4126: yi dam lha'i bskal ba rdo rje slob dpon rol /
NK022(za)001:4127: dkyil 'khor lha'i bskal ba rgyal theb la sbyin /
NK022(za)001:4128: rig 'dzin rtsal 'chang gi bskal ba de na yod pa'i slob bu las can la sbyin no //
NK022(za)001:4129: de nas gzhan rnams ci rigs su rigs pas spyad la sbyin pa ni gal che bar gsungs so //
NK022(za)001:4130: de dag tshar ba dang pi ti brtan pa bya ba'i phyir /
NK022(za)001:4132: ka ya wak+kisa brtan par bzhugs /
NK022(za)001:4133: me tog kun gyis lag tu 'grims /
NK022(za)001:4134: nas la rten 'brel snying pos rab gnas byas la dbang rdzas 'jug pa'i snod du blugs pa'am /
NK022(za)001:4135: rang gi khyim yin na mdzod phugs su dor /
NK022(za)001:4136: de nas mar me'i smon lam gdab pa ni /
NK022(za)001:4137: kun srin lag sbrel rdo rje slob dpon gyi phyag g.yon pas mar me bzung la /
NK022(za)001:4138: dur khrod gsang ba'i tshig dbyangs dang bcas pa dang /
NK022(za)001:4139: tshig lhug pa gnyis kyis mar me'i smon lam gdab /
NK022(za)001:4140: dngos grub kyi drin lan bsab pa'i phyir yon dbul te /
NK022(za)001:4142: rgyal srid dang ni rang gi lus //
NK022(za)001:4143: zhes pa la sogs pa dang /
NK022(za)001:4144: rdo rje theg pa'i gzhung las kyang /
NK022(za)001:4145: che bar rgyal srid yul 'khor zhes pa /
NK022(za)001:4151: yun du dad pa dang dam tshig /
NK022(za)001:4152: zhu khar sris zhu dang gus pa /
NK022(za)001:4153: mchog tu brtse sems dang gdung ba la sogs pa /
NK022(za)001:4154: mnyes pa sna tshogs chu bo gzhung bzhin dbul lo //
NK022(za)001:4155: de nas rus zhabs slob bu'i spyi bor bzhag la /
NK022(za)001:4156: di ring phan chad bu khyod kyis //
NK022(za)001:4157: rdo rje sems dpa' nga yin gyis //
NK022(za)001:4158: nga yis ji ltar bsgo ba bzhin //
NK022(za)001:4159: bu khyod kyis kyang bya dgos so //
NK022(za)001:4161: slob bus bla ma rdo rje rgyal po la //
NK022(za)001:4162: dad mos gus pa'i sems ldan pas //
NK022(za)001:4163: bka' yis ji ltar bsgo ba bzhin //
NK022(za)001:4164: lus ngag yid gsum mnyer gyis blang //
NK022(za)001:4166: las bzhi'i bro byas kyang mi 'gal lo //
NK022(za)001:4170: de dag nyin mo'i las su bya ba'o //
NK022(za)001:4171: de nas zhag bcu gcig tu 'gro ba'i tshe /
NK022(za)001:4172: dkyil 'khor gling bzhi pa zhig mdzad kyin yod de /
NK022(za)001:4173: slob dpon gtso bo'i mdun du shar lho'am gang 'os der /
NK022(za)001:4174: gsang dbang dkyil 'khor pad+ma 'dab bzhi rigs lnga'am /
NK022(za)001:4176: 'dab brgyad rigs brgya sogs gang ltar kyang mtha' sgo khor yug bya'o //
NK022(za)001:4177: yab kyis yum la dbang bskur ba //
NK022(za)001:4178: rdo rje sbas pa sor bzhi dang //
NK022(za)001:4179: 'gren pa'i rdo rje mdzub gang gi tshad bya /
NK022(za)001:4180: yum gyis yab la dbang bskur ba /
NK022(za)001:4182: sras krug skyo kha sor bcu gnyis pa'o //
NK022(za)001:4183: de'ii steng du thod par gsang dbang dam rdzas barlona sbyor dang /
NK022(za)001:4186: 'de gu gang byed pa sngar gyi phabs dang bcas pa'o //
NK022(za)001:4187: byang shar lha mo tsan d+ha li'i sa'am gang 'os der /
NK022(za)001:4188: dbang gsum pa gsang dbang shes rab ye shes kyi dmigs rten du /
NK022(za)001:4190: tshe rdzas dang mchod pa slob bu spyir bsdus pa dang bcas pa'o //
NK022(za)001:4191: lho nub srin po gnas pa'i sa'am gang 'os der /
NK022(za)001:4193: a ti rdzogs pa chen po'i dkyil 'khor pad+ma 'dab
NK022(za)001:4194: ma bcu drug dang nyi gdan dmar ba la a
NK022(za)001:4195: bcu drug / dbus la a kha sbyor dang bco brgyad rtsa ris snying gzugs dang bcas par /
NK022(za)001:4196: rdo rje tsaka bum pa dang bcas pa'o //
NK022(za)001:4197: sa cha gang 'os gcig tu gdan la zhi ba'i
NK022(za)001:4198: dkyil 'khor sngar gyi bsgrub pa dang dgongs pa 'dus
NK022(za)001:4200: dpon slob grangs bsnyen tshang ba bya /
NK022(za)001:4202: lha bla ma dang yi dam gtso bo dang dbyer med /
NK022(za)001:4203: snying pa gsang ba ltar bzlas /
NK022(za)001:4205: bde ba gcig tu chos skyong mgon po lcam dral gyi gtor ma dgod /
NK022(za)001:4206: de nas zhi khro lung gi cho ga gzhung bskangs tshang bar bya /
NK022(za)001:4207: a ti la nyin mo'am nub mo kun bzang don gyi phrin las bya /
NK022(za)001:4212: de dag man ngag tu shes par bya /
NK022(za)001:4213: chos skyong gi gtor dbang bya /
NK022(za)001:4217: de nas nam langs pa dang /
NK022(za)001:4221: las mkhan dang mched lcam gyis phyir brtan ma bskyang /
NK022(za)001:4222: slob dpon dang rgyal theb kyis nang du dug gsum gyi sbyin sreg bya /
NK022(za)001:4224: rgyal theb kyis mtho bsgyel la ya hi gats+tshasa gshegs su gsol /
NK022(za)001:4226: ye shes lha'i sgo byang la sku khrus gsol la tshags bya /
NK022(za)001:4227: bar chad bgegs kyi sgo byang de la mchog phur
NK022(za)001:4228: dar gyi cod pan gcig bdud rtsi 'khyil par bskyed
NK022(za)001:4229: la / sku gsung thugs su byin gyis brlabs la sgo byang de dkyil 'khor gyi 'og tu bzhugs /
NK022(za)001:4230: phur pa de g+ha ta yas dril nas sgo byang la gdab /
NK022(za)001:4231: der bdud rtsi thigs pa gcig blugs nas /
NK022(za)001:4232: ting nge 'dzin nam byang chub kyi sems ma skyes bar du thar pa'i dus med par bsam ste /
NK022(za)001:4233: des ni las rjes bkra shis par 'gyur ba'i dgos pa yod do //
NK022(za)001:4234: de nas dpon slob kun 'dus la bkra shis bya /
NK022(za)001:4238: bdud rtsi gangs dkar zhun gyi zhu //
NK022(za)001:4239: nam mkha'i mthong nas thigs pa shar //
NK022(za)001:4240: phreng ba ut+pala rgyan gyis brgyan //
NK022(za)001:4241: lhun po'i logs la dpal du shar //
NK022(za)001:4242: sil bu mu tig 'bras bu'i zhing //
NK022(za)001:4243: rin chen sa la rtsi ru rdol //
NK022(za)001:4244: rang byung sems nyid chen po de //
NK022(za)001:4245: rnal 'byor rig pa'i khyung phrug rgyas //
NK022(za)001:4246: bka' drin sgo nga'i nang nas rdol //
NK022(za)001:4247: bde ba pad+ma'i nang gi dri //
NK022(za)001:4248: srog tshal bung ba'i mchu yis 'jib //
NK022(za)001:4250: de ltar bla ma chen po gong ma brgyud pa dang bcas kyi gsung dang /
NK022(za)001:4252: kho bos lag len mang du mthong ba dang /
NK022(za)001:4253: bsnyen sgrub bzhi ldan ma'i bsgrub pa'i khrigs la brten nas /
NK022(za)001:4254: 'dus pa chen po'i lag len 'di ni phyi rabs dbang 'di la 'jug pa rnams kyi don du /
NK022(za)001:4255: glan ban bsod nams mgon po bdag gis bkod pa'i dge bas /
NK022(za)001:4256: sems can thams cad yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas myur du thob par gyur cig /
NK022(za)001:4258: 'dus pa chen po mdo'i dbang gi cho ga'i lag len rdzogs so //
NK022(za)001:4261: // // lha mi nyan rang 'jug chog bzhugs /
NK022(za)001:4268: thams cad kyang 'di lta ste 'dul ba'i dbang gis lha dang mi'i theg pa dang /
NK022(za)001:4269: zhes theg pa'i dang po 'di la'ang kun 'du ba dang /
NK022(za)001:4271: dge bcu spyod cing mi dge spong byed pa //
NK022(za)001:4272: 'dod khams lha dang mi ru skye ba'i rgyu //
NK022(za)001:4273: tshad med bzhi spyod mi g.yo sgom byed pa //
NK022(za)001:4274: tshangs gnas la sogs rim par skye ba'i rgyu //
NK022(za)001:4276: gal te bsdom pa yi tshul khrims ma blangs pa dang /
NK022(za)001:4277: dge ba'i chos bsdus pa'i tshul khrims bslab pa la mi slob par tshul khrims 'chal ba bkag ste /
NK022(za)001:4279: tshul khrims 'chal ba ngan 'gro der 'gro ste //
NK022(za)001:4280: de la thos pa mang pos bskyab mi nus //
NK022(za)001:4282: slob dpon pad+mas lam rim las /
NK022(za)001:4283: sdom pa kun la yod med kyi //
NK022(za)001:4284: skyabs su ma song pa la med //
NK022(za)001:4287: da ltar thub pa'i bstan pa dkon mchog gsum yod pas /
NK022(za)001:4289: sh+aakya'i rgyal por dbang bskur ba dang /
NK022(za)001:4290: rgyal por snang ba de la skyabs shing /
NK022(za)001:4293: khyims pa dang rab tu byung ba gang yang rung ba la brten cing skyabs zhu bar bya'o //
NK022(za)001:4294: de yang bod kyi bka' bcad ltar du lha mi yis 'dul ba la the bas /
NK022(za)001:4295: thams cad mkhyen pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK022(za)001:4296: lha mi'i theg pa'i sgor 'jug cing sdom pa 'bog pa ni /
NK022(za)001:4297: sku gsung thugs kyi rten dgram /
NK022(za)001:4301: tsog pur 'dug la ngan song gi sdug bsngal las
NK022(za)001:4302: thar nas lha mi'i go 'phangs khyad par can thob
NK022(za)001:4303: par bya / de'i phyir ji srid 'tsho'i bar du
NK022(za)001:4304: lha mi'i theg pa la 'jug snyam du bsam du
NK022(za)001:4305: par bya / bcug la / rjes bzlos mdzod ces dang /
NK022(za)001:4306: sngar chos 'brel med na ston pa'am /
NK022(za)001:4307: yod na slob dpon dgongs su gsol /
NK022(za)001:4308: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi ba dus 'di nas bzung ste /
NK022(za)001:4311: sangs rgyas la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK022(za)001:4312: 'dod chags dang bral ba rnams kyi mchog /
NK022(za)001:4317: lha mi'i theg pa la gnas par slob dpon gyis bzung du gsol lo //
NK022(za)001:4319: yang na lan gnyis ston pa /
NK022(za)001:4320: tha ma slob dpon gyis bzung du gsol ces /
NK022(za)001:4321: lan gcig tha ma'i tshe bslab sdom thob pas slob dpon zhes gor bzhug /
NK022(za)001:4322: slob dpon gyis thabs yin no //
NK022(za)001:4323: slob mas legs so zhes brjod do //
NK022(za)001:4324: de nas bslab pa brjod pa ni /
NK022(za)001:4325: 'dod khams mtho ris su skye ba la mi dge spangs /
NK022(za)001:4326: dge ba spyad pas mtho ris thob cing /
NK022(za)001:4327: khams gong ma gzugs khams dang srid rtser skye ba la tshad med pa bzhi dang /
NK022(za)001:4328: mi g.yo ba'i bsam gtan gyi bslab pa dgos par bshad pas gang mos dang /
NK022(za)001:4329: ci nus de brjod pas bslab pa khas len pa lan gcig brjod de /
NK022(za)001:4330: bla mas slob ma la ngan song gsum gyi sdug bsngal las thar nas /
NK022(za)001:4331: lha mi'i go 'phang khyad par can tshe rabs kun tu thob par bya /
NK022(za)001:4332: de'i ched du mi dge ba ci nus kyis spangs /
NK022(za)001:4333: dge ba ci nus kyis bsgrub snyam du bsams la /
NK022(za)001:4336: ji ltar drang srong chen po'am /
NK022(za)001:4337: 'phags pa dgra bcom pa chen po rnams kyis /
NK022(za)001:4338: sngon lha mi'i theg pa la zhugs te ji srid 'tsho'i bar du /
NK022(za)001:4341: 'dod pas log par g.yem pa dang /
NK022(za)001:4347: gnod sems dang log par lta ba la sogs pa mi dge ba spangs te /
NK022(za)001:4348: mi dge ba las slar log pa de bzhin du /
NK022(za)001:4349: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi bas kyang dus 'di nas bzung ste /
NK022(za)001:4351: srog gcod pa dang ma byin par len pa dang 'dod pas log par g.yem pa dang /
NK022(za)001:4357: log par lta ba la sogs pa mi dge ba spong ste /
NK022(za)001:4358: mi dge ba las slar log par bagyi'o //
NK022(za)001:4359: ji ltar drang srong chen po'am 'phags pa dgra bcom pa chen po rnams kyi rjes su slob bo //
NK022(za)001:4363: ji ltar drang srong chen po'am /
NK022(za)001:4364: 'phags pa dgra bcom pa chen po rnams kyis /
NK022(za)001:4368: btang snyoms te tshad med pa dang /
NK022(za)001:4369: bsam gtan gyi sems bsgrubs te gnas pa ltar du /
NK022(za)001:4370: bdag kyang rjes su slob bo //
NK022(za)001:4371: rjes su bsgrub bo rjes su bgyid do //
NK022(za)001:4373: slob dpon gyis thabs yin no //
NK022(za)001:4375: log lta la sogs zhes pa /
NK022(za)001:4378: dngos gazhi'am srung 'dod na mi dge bcu chang dang bcu gcig bsdom pa'o //
NK022(za)001:4380: tshangs gcod la sdig pa rang bzhin dang /
NK022(za)001:4381: rang bzhin gyi steng du bcas pa'i skyon spong ba'i khyad yod pas /
NK022(za)001:4382: de'i sdom pa lha mi la bsnyen gnas 'bog pa ni /
NK022(za)001:4383: sngar chos 'brel med na btsun pa'am ston pa /
NK022(za)001:4384: sngar chos 'brel yod na slob dpon dgongs su gsol /
NK022(za)001:4385: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi ba dus 'di nas bzung ste /
NK022(za)001:4388: sangs rgyas la skyabs su mchi /
NK022(za)001:4389: 'dod chags dang bral ba rnams kyi mchog /
NK022(za)001:4393: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi ba dus 'di nas bzung ste /
NK022(za)001:4394: ji srid 'tsho'i bar du bsnyen gnas yan lag brgyad pa'am /
NK022(za)001:4395: srog gcod lta bu'am gang 'os par /
NK022(za)001:4398: slob dpon gyis bzung du gsol /
NK022(za)001:4399: zhes lan gsum gyi tha ma la cis kyang slob dpon zhes dang /
NK022(za)001:4400: slob dpon gyis thabs yin no //
NK022(za)001:4401: slob mas legs so zhes brjod pa mthun yang /
NK022(za)001:4402: dus bzang bsnyen gnas ltar du zla ba byung ngo cog gi nya dang /
NK022(za)001:4404: tshes brgyad la bsnyen gnas yan lag brgyad par slob dpon zhes bya'o //
NK022(za)001:4405: sdom la gnas pa'i btsun pa dang /
NK022(za)001:4406: sdom de bston par nus pa'i ston pa dang /
NK022(za)001:4407: sdom de bdag rgyud la byin skyes nas thob pas slob dpon du shes dgos pa'o //
NK022(za)001:4408: rgyal po lta bu ni bsnyen gnas mdzad kyang khri stan che mtho dang /
NK022(za)001:4409: rin po che'i rgyan phreng dang /
NK022(za)001:4410: gser dngul len dgos pas yan lag brgyad do //
NK022(za)001:4411: btsun mo lta bu ni rin po che len pas
NK022(za)001:4412: yan lag dgu'i bslab pa brjod pa lan gcig rjes
NK022(za)001:4413: bzlos mdzod / bsnyen gnas yan lag rtsa ba dang rtsa ba'i yan lag tu len pa dang /
NK022(za)001:4414: zhag nyi ma grangs gang len kha bsgyur shes par bya'o //
NK022(za)001:4416: ji ltar sngon gyi 'phags pa dgra bcom pa de dag gis srog gcod pa spangs te /
NK022(za)001:4417: srog gcod pa las slar bzlog pa de bzhin du /
NK022(za)001:4418: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi bas kyang dus 'di nas bzung ste /
NK022(za)001:4419: zla ba byung cog gi nya dang /
NK022(za)001:4421: tshes brgyad la srog gcod pa spangs te /
NK022(za)001:4422: srog gcod pa las slar bzlog par bagyi'o //
NK022(za)001:4423: yan lag dang po 'dis bdag 'phags pa dgra bcom
NK022(za)001:4424: pa de dag gis slab pa la rjes su slob
NK022(za)001:4427: gzhan yang 'phags pa dgra bcom pa de dag gis /
NK022(za)001:4428: ma byin par len pa dang /
NK022(za)001:4429: mi tshangs bar spyod pa dang /
NK022(za)001:4433: myos par 'gyur ba bag med pa'i gnas dang /
NK022(za)001:4438: rgyan dang kha dog 'chang ba dang /
NK022(za)001:4440: dus ma yin pa'i kha zas spangs te /
NK022(za)001:4441: dus ma yin pa'i kha zas las slar log pa
NK022(za)001:4442: de bzhin du bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi bas kyang
NK022(za)001:4445: zla ba byung ngo cog gi nya dang /
NK022(za)001:4446: gnam stong dang tshes brgyad la ma byin par len pa dang /
NK022(za)001:4447: mi tshangs bar spyod pa dang /
NK022(za)001:4457: rgyan dang kha dog 'chang ba dang /
NK022(za)001:4459: dus ma yin pa'i kha zas spangs te /
NK022(za)001:4460: dus ma yin pa'i kha zas las slar log par bagyi'o //
NK022(za)001:4461: yan lag brgyad pa 'dis bdag 'phags pa dgra bcom
NK022(za)001:4462: pa de dag gi bslab pa la rjes su slob
NK022(za)001:4465: slob dpon gyis thabs yin no //
NK022(za)001:4467: ces glu gar rtsed rol spos rgyan bsdom nas /
NK022(za)001:4468: srog rkun 'khrigs rdzun te rtsa bzhi /
NK022(za)001:4469: chang dri phreng brgyan khri chen dus min zas dang brgyad yin /
NK022(za)001:4470: yan lag dgu'i steng nas brgyad pa ltar /
NK022(za)001:4471: rtsa ba bu gar bzhugs pa'i phyogs ma the zhes
NK022(za)001:4472: pa khri stan rkang mtho sa khru gang lhag tu
NK022(za)001:4473: ma the ba'o // mtho ba yan lag bcu pa ltar khri gdan mthon po dang /
NK022(za)001:4475: dus ma yin pa'i kha zas dang /
NK022(za)001:4476: gser dngul len pa spangs te /
NK022(za)001:4477: gser dngul len pa las slar log pa de bzhin du zhes dang /
NK022(za)001:4478: sha mar la dus ma yin pa'i kha zas dang gser dngul len pa spangs te /
NK022(za)001:4479: gser dngul len pa las slar log par bagyi'o //
NK022(za)001:4480: yan lag bcu pa 'dis bdag 'phags pa dgra bcom pa zhes pa'o //
NK022(za)001:4481: yang zhag dang dus bzang la de'i tshes gnam stong la ngo bo dang /
NK022(za)001:4482: nya bsu stong skyol ces tshes bcu dang tshes gcig dang bcu bzhi gnyis kyang zhar la 'byung ba'o //
NK022(za)001:4483: yang bslab pa brjod pa la 'di skad du /
NK022(za)001:4484: gzhan yang 'phags pa dgra bcom pa de dag gi
NK022(za)001:4485: slab pa la rjes su slob ces pa la 'du
NK022(za)001:4486: bar mdzad pa'o // 'on kyang yid kyi dam bca' dang /
NK022(za)001:4487: slob dpon gyis bka' gnang ba dang khas len pa'i tshig la don nges par bkrol bar bya'o //
NK022(za)001:4488: za gcig par byed na'ang dus ma yin pa'i kha zas spong pa la 'du ba'o //
NK022(za)001:4489: sgos su bslab pa brjod pa la /
NK022(za)001:4490: za gcig pa la gnas nas /
NK022(za)001:4491: yang nas yang du za ba spangs te /
NK022(za)001:4492: yang nas yang du za ba las slar log par bagyi'o //
NK022(za)001:4493: bdag 'phags pa zhes pa sogs mthun /
NK022(za)001:4494: dus gsum lnga gang srung ba 'di'i skabs sbyar te /
NK022(za)001:4495: gnam stong gi lha bcom ldan 'das rgyal ba sh+aakya thub pa'o //
NK022(za)001:4496: gnam stong srungs bas bskal ba stong gi bar du mu ge'i bskal pa las thar ro //
NK022(za)001:4497: nya'i lha sangs rgyas snang ba mtha' yas yin no //
NK022(za)001:4498: nya srungs bas bskal ba khri'i bar du nad kyi bskal ba las thar ro //
NK022(za)001:4499: tshes brgyad kyi lha ni sangs rgyas sman gyi lha bee d+aur+ya 'od kyi rgyal po yin no //
NK022(za)001:4500: tshes brgyad srungs pas bskal ba nyi khri'i bar du
NK022(za)001:4501: mtshon gyi bskal ba las thar nas 'phrul dag'i gnas
NK022(za)001:4502: su skye'o // gnam stong gi nyu le ma lha tshangs pa yin no //
NK022(za)001:4505: mu ne mu ne ma h+aa mu ne ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK022(za)001:4506: nya'i nyu le ma tshangs pa kun grol yin no //
NK022(za)001:4509: tshes brgyad kyi nyu le ma rgyal bu the'u tshe yin no //
NK022(za)001:4511: bi shad tshe bi shad tshe /
NK022(za)001:4512: ma h+aa bi shad tshe sa mud ga te s+w+aa h+aa /
NK022(za)001:4514: tshes gcig sangs rgyas rgyal ba ting nge 'dzin gyi rgyal po ni /
NK022(za)001:4515: ngan song sbyong ba'i rgyal po dang /
NK022(za)001:4516: steng gi phyogs nas dgra bcom pa yang dag par
NK022(za)001:4517: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas ngan song thams cad rnam par
NK022(za)001:4518: sbyong ba gzi brjid kyi rgyal po dang /
NK022(za)001:4519: sangs rgyas rnam par snang mdzad dang gsum gcig par cing /
NK022(za)001:4521: na mo b+ha ga ba te /
NK022(za)001:4522: sarba durga te pa ri sho d+ha ya /
NK022(za)001:4523: ra tsa y+aa ta th+aa ga t+aa ya /
NK022(za)001:4524: ar ha te samyaka sa b+hud+ha y+aa /
NK022(za)001:4526: sho d+ha ni bi sho d+ha ni /
NK022(za)001:4527: bi shwo d+ha ni bi shwo d+ha ni /
NK022(za)001:4530: sarba karma a ba ra na bi shwo d+ha na ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK022(za)001:4531: zhes ngan song sbyong brgyud rtag pa las bshad pa'o //
NK022(za)001:4532: 'on kyang snying po mu ne la bsdud /
NK022(za)001:4533: gcig dang brgyad dang bcu dang bco lnga dang nyer gnyis dang gnam stong ste dus drug go //
NK022(za)001:4534: tshes bcu la sangs rgyas mi 'khrugs pa'i snying po /
NK022(za)001:4535: na mo rad na tra ya ya /
NK022(za)001:4536: ka ka ni ka ka ni /
NK022(za)001:4537: ro tsa ni ro tsa ni /
NK022(za)001:4538: troo ta ni troo ta ni /
NK022(za)001:4539: tra sa ni tra sa ni /
NK022(za)001:4542: sarba karma pa ra pa ram ni me ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK022(za)001:4544: 'khor sangs rgyas stong yang snying po mu ne la bsdud /
NK022(za)001:4545: byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po sa'i snying pos bcom ldan 'das la zhus pa'i mdo las /
NK022(za)001:4546: sems can skye bo rnams kyis dus drug dang /
NK022(za)001:4547: dus gsum la sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi mtshan nas brjod cing /
NK022(za)001:4548: phyag 'tshal nas za gcig pa thub na /
NK022(za)001:4549: ji tsam byang ba dang ngan song gang las thar ba'i yon tan ni /
NK022(za)001:4550: zla ba 'khor gcig gi tshes gcig la lha'i bu gzhon nu nyid nyul du 'ong ste /
NK022(za)001:4551: 'jig rten mi rnams dge sdig ci byed pa nyul lo //
NK022(za)001:4552: de'i nyi ma la rgyal ba'i ting nge 'dzin gyi
NK022(za)001:4553: rgyal po la mtshan nas brjod cing za gcig pa
NK022(za)001:4554: thub na / bskal pa bzhi bcu'i sdig pa byang zhing /
NK022(za)001:4555: mtshon ral gri dang mdung thung gi bskal pa nas thar bar 'gyur ro //
NK022(za)001:4556: tshes brgyad la rgyal bu the'u nyid nyul du mchis te /
NK022(za)001:4558: sangs rgyas sman gyi lha bee d+aur+ya 'od kyi rgyal
NK022(za)001:4559: po'i mtshan nas brjod cing phyag 'tshal te za gcig
NK022(za)001:4560: pa thub na / bskal pa sum cu'i sdig pa las thar cing /
NK022(za)001:4561: gsod cing brdung ba'i du khahls thar bar 'gyur ro //
NK022(za)001:4562: tshes bcu la gshin rje'i 'khor na gnas pa'i tshe /
NK022(za)001:4563: rtog pa'i dbang po tshad med ces bya ba nyul du mchis te /
NK022(za)001:4564: de'i nyi ma la bskal pa bzang po'i sangs rgyas
NK022(za)001:4565: stong la mtshan nas brjod cing phyag 'tshal nas za
NK022(za)001:4567: bskal pa stong gi sdig pa byang zhing /
NK022(za)001:4568: chu tshan khol ma'i ngan song las thar bar 'gyur ro //
NK022(za)001:4569: tshes bco lnga pa gshin rje'i 'khor na lam brgyud lnga la dbang byed pa'i ded dpon /
NK022(za)001:4570: tshangs pa kun grol nyul du mchis te /
NK022(za)001:4571: de'i nyi ma la sangs rgyas snang ba mtha' yas
NK022(za)001:4572: kyi mtshan nas brjod cing phyag 'tshal nas za ga
NK022(za)001:4574: bskal pa nyis brgya'i sdig pa byang zhing shin tu grang ba'i dmyal ba las thar bar 'gyur ro //
NK022(za)001:4575: gnam stong la lha'i dbang po tshangs pa nyul mchis te /
NK022(za)001:4576: de'i nyi ma la sangs rgyas sh+aakya thub pa'i mtshan nas brjod cing za gcig pa thub na /
NK022(za)001:4577: bskal pa brgya stong gi sdig pa byang zhing /
NK022(za)001:4578: me ma mur gyi ngan song las thar bar 'gyur ro //
NK022(za)001:4579: skya rengs shar nas phyed kyi bar /
NK022(za)001:4580: de'i bar du zos pa dag /
NK022(za)001:4581: bskal pa'i dus su zos pa yin /
NK022(za)001:4582: gdugs tshod bza' ba'i dus bstan pa'o //
NK022(za)001:4584: lha mi'i theg pa'i lam 'degs pa'o //
NK022(za)001:4585: gang la yid kyis phyag byas pa //
NK022(za)001:4586: de ni phyag byas dang po yin //
NK022(za)001:4587: zhes mtshan dran pas mos pa'o //
NK022(za)001:4588: mtshan barjo da ngag gi phyag 'tshal bas phyag tu bshad pa /
NK022(za)001:4591: zhes brjod na de dag thams cad rim gyi sdug bsngal las thar bar 'gyur ro //
NK022(za)001:4593: lus ngag yid gsum gus pas phyag legs par 'tshal ba'i phan yon lung las /
