NK022(za)001:4594: de'i lus kyis ji tsam non pa'i sa de'i rdul
NK022(za)001:4595: dbang chen gser gyi sa gzhi la thug pa'i bar
NK022(za)001:4596: gyi rdul phran gyi grangs dang mnyam pa'i steng 'khor
NK022(za)001:4597: lo bsgyur ba thob cing mthar byang chub thob par
NK022(za)001:4598: lung bstan / sangs rgyas kyi dbu skra dang /
NK022(za)001:4599: sen mo bzhugs pa'i mchod rten la dge tshul gyis phyag 'tshal bas /
NK022(za)001:4600: kun dga' bo la bka' stsal pa'o //
NK022(za)001:4601: lha'i bu gzhon nu ni gshin rje gdong drug pa'o //
NK022(za)001:4602: sangs rgyas kyi dus mchod chen po bzhi /
NK022(za)001:4603: pan chen sh+aakya sh+ris gsungs pa'ang de la tshang ste /
NK022(za)001:4604: rta zla dang po'i tshes gcig nas /
NK022(za)001:4605: bco lnga cho 'phrul chen po bstan //
NK022(za)001:4606: mdo sde 'dzangs blun gnyan yod dar //
NK022(za)001:4607: de nas dgu bcu sa ga'i nya //
NK022(za)001:4609: mngon par sangs rgyas zhag gcig nas //
NK022(za)001:4611: zla grangs bzhi dang drug pa'i stod //
NK022(za)001:4612: rgya che rol pa'i dus mchod ni //
NK022(za)001:4613: ba ra na ser tshes bzhi dar //
NK022(za)001:4614: tshes lnga nas bzung slar zhag brgya //
NK022(za)001:4615: sangs rgyas lha yul dbyar gnas grol //
NK022(za)001:4616: zla dgu'i nya la mu stegs kyi //
NK022(za)001:4617: ston pa drug btul sangs rgyas kyi //
NK022(za)001:4618: cho 'phrul chung ba yangs pa che //
NK022(za)001:4619: gzhan yang sangs rgyas zla bcu gnyis //
NK022(za)001:4620: rgyal nya 'khrungs shing chos la gshegs //
NK022(za)001:4621: rgyal por dbang bskur dus bzang mdzad //
NK022(za)001:4622: nyer gnyis yum chen lha yul gshegs //
NK022(za)001:4623: tshes brgyad rgyal bas myang 'das gsungs //
NK022(za)001:4624: zla gsum nag nya dbang sbyin mdzad //
NK022(za)001:4625: dus mchod dam bcas sdig dag tshul //
NK022(za)001:4626: bla ma'i dam tshig nyams pa dang //
NK022(za)001:4627: byang chub sems la ngan sems bskyed //
NK022(za)001:4628: rnyed phyir chos 'dra ston pa dang //
NK022(za)001:4629: sdig la sbyor dang dge 'dun gyi //
NK022(za)001:4630: yo byad rkus dang rtsa ltung byung //
NK022(za)001:4631: dkon mchog spong dang mtshams med byas //
NK022(za)001:4632: stan la zhugs nas rtsod pa byed //
NK022(za)001:4633: mdza' bshes bcugs dang bcu po ni //
NK022(za)001:4634: dmyal bar skye bar gsungs pa las //
NK022(za)001:4635: myur du zad nas kun mkhyen thob //
NK022(za)001:4637: mi mthun bsdum dang mchod rten bzhengs //
NK022(za)001:4638: rnying pa gso dang yid rang pas //
NK022(za)001:4639: bsod nams dpag med thob par 'gyur //
NK022(za)001:4641: dus chen bzhi dang tha mal ba'i //
NK022(za)001:4642: khyad par sil bu myang 'das las //
NK022(za)001:4643: sa ya phrag brgya'i 'gyur du gsungs //
NK022(za)001:4645: zas skom rin chen sman sogs kyis //
NK022(za)001:4646: mchod na skye ba thams cad du //
NK022(za)001:4647: gnas dang longs spyod grogs la sogs //
NK022(za)001:4648: de dag mchog tu gyur pa thob //
NK022(za)001:4649: lha yis srungs dang bar chad med //
NK022(za)001:4650: sbyin pa gtong zhing tshul khrims ldan //
NK022(za)001:4651: snying rjes gzhan gyi dbugs 'byin cing //
NK022(za)001:4652: nad med 'dod pa chung ba dang //
NK022(za)001:4654: 'tsho ba rnam par dag pa dang //
NK022(za)001:4655: dam tshig nyams pa 'byang bar byed //
NK022(za)001:4656: dge 'dun byang chub sems dpa' dang //
NK022(za)001:4657: gshin rje rnams kyi brgyan du 'gyur //
NK022(za)001:4658: gnod gcod sdug bsngal mi 'byung zhing //
NK022(za)001:4660: tshe rabs kun tu dpal 'byor lus //
NK022(za)001:4661: thob nas rab tu 'byung ba dang //
NK022(za)001:4662: dge ba'i bshes gnyen brten byed cing //
NK022(za)001:4665: dus bzangs gzhan yang bstan pa ni //
NK022(za)001:4666: bla ma dang ni mdza' bshes dang //
NK022(za)001:4667: byang chub sems dpa' 'grongs pa'i dus //
NK022(za)001:4668: nyi zla sgra gcan gdon gyis zin //
NK022(za)001:4669: mu ge sde rtsod nad yams 'byung //
NK022(za)001:4670: dus chen bzhi dang bcu gnyis la //
NK022(za)001:4672: lha mi'i dge ba stobs can la sogs /
NK022(za)001:4673: yan lag dang po 'dis bdag 'phags pa dgra bcom
NK022(za)001:4674: pa zhes srog sdom la'ang sdom pa kun tshang pas
NK022(za)001:4677: bslab pa rin po che 'di sangs rgyas bzhugs dus ni'ang /
NK022(za)001:4678: khyim bdag mgon med zas sbyin gyi drung du len pa mang zhing /
NK022(za)001:4679: khyim bdag des kyang de'i nyin gyi 'tsho ba byin skad /
NK022(za)001:4680: sha ri'i bu sogs dgra bcom dang /
NK022(za)001:4681: dge slong phal pa la'ang mos phyogs kyis len pa dang /
NK022(za)001:4683: klu'i rgyal pos bsnyen gnas kyi dpe la brten nas blangs pas lha'i rgyal po thob pa dang /
NK022(za)001:4684: rten dkon mchog drung du blangs nas srungs pas phan bde thob pa dang /
NK022(za)001:4685: rten med kyang dkon mchog drung du mos gus byas nas blangs cing srungs pas thob ste /
NK022(za)001:4686: de nyid kyi dge rtsa cher 'phel nas sangs rgyas thob par gsungs te /
NK022(za)001:4687: gang byed kyang dkon mchog la dad pa gal che ba dang /
NK022(za)001:4688: ngan song las thar ba'i nges 'byung ni /
NK022(za)001:4689: dud 'gro gnas dang kha 'thor ltar dud 'gro yi
NK022(za)001:4690: dwags dmyal ba las thar ba de 'dod pa gal
NK022(za)001:4691: che bas de yod pa'i phan yon lung las /
NK022(za)001:4692: gcig dang brgyad dang bco lnga la //
NK022(za)001:4693: bsnyen gnas yan lag brgyad srungs na //
NK022(za)001:4696: nga ni sangs rgyas sh+aakya thub pa nyid ni mthar thug yin la /
NK022(za)001:4697: de ma thob bar du'ang dus bzangs la /
NK022(za)001:4698: dmyal bar skyes pas kyang lhas mchod pa dang lha'i bde ba tshe rabs du mar thob par gsungs /
NK022(za)001:4699: gzhan yang sbyor ba zhes srog gcod pa la gnod sems lta bu dang /
NK022(za)001:4700: dngos gzhi zhes mi gsad par bsams pa de mtshon dug ngan sngags lta bus gsad pa dang /
NK022(za)001:4701: rjes zhes gsod par bsams pa de rkyen des shi ba lta bu dang /
NK022(za)001:4702: gsum tshang ba'i srog gcod dang /
NK022(za)001:4703: dngos gzhi mi bsad par bsams kyang /
NK022(za)001:4704: phyugs shi ba lta bu srog gcod rtsa ba yi
NK022(za)001:4705: ltung ba na smad cing yan lag tu rtogs te
NK022(za)001:4706: / mi la brten pa sogs srog gcod kyi cha la rtogs pa dang /
NK022(za)001:4707: srog tsam la snying brtse bas srog mi gcod pa ni /
NK022(za)001:4708: srog chags mtha' yas las srog sdom yang mtha' yas pa dang /
NK022(za)001:4709: srog byin gyi dge ba tshad med pa dang /
NK022(za)001:4710: spyir srog mi gcod kyang sgos dgra la snying na ba ni /
NK022(za)001:4711: dung srin can ltar srog sdom skyon can dang /
NK022(za)001:4712: rtsa ba'i skyon byung na bsnyen gnas kyi sdom pa bskyar te blang /
NK022(za)001:4713: skyon gyi nyes pa bshags cing dge sangs rgyas su sngo ba dang /
NK022(za)001:4714: yan lag nyes pa ni rang gis bshags nas dag pas bskyar len mi dgos pas /
NK022(za)001:4715: 'di yod smra ba'i sde pa ltar bod du /
NK022(za)001:4716: srog rkun rdzun 'khrig rtsa ba'i yan lag mchog mgo lta bur bshad pa dang /
NK022(za)001:4717: gzhan yan lag rkang lag lta bu chad kyang mi 'chi ba ltar du bshad /
NK022(za)001:4718: sde pa gzhan chang rtsa ba dang 'khrig yan lag tu byed pa ltar de'i skabs shes par bya'o //
NK022(za)001:4723: da ni nyan thos ba slab sdom len dgos tshe //
NK022(za)001:4724: sangs rgyas ma byon chos dang nyan thos med //
NK022(za)001:4725: rang rgyal lha mi'i theg pas bde 'gro yod //
NK022(za)001:4726: de phyir drang srong rjes 'brang bslab sdom ni //
NK022(za)001:4727: lha mi'i theg par bshad kyang khams gsum 'khor //
NK022(za)001:4728: sangs rgyas byon nas chos bstan nyan thos kyi //
NK022(za)001:4729: bslab sdom ma thob rang rgyal 'phags pa med //
NK022(za)001:4730: lha mi'i bde 'gro thob kyang 'khor bar 'khyams //
NK022(za)001:4731: dge ba zag bcas nyon mongs las skyon gyis //
NK022(za)001:4732: bsam gtan tshad med skyon 'dres thob spyad kyang //
NK022(za)001:4734: brgya byin mchod 'os nyid du gyur nas kyang //
NK022(za)001:4735: sa steng dag tu yang bran nyid du 'gyur //
NK022(za)001:4736: 'khor lo bsgyur ba nyid du gyur na yang //
NK022(za)001:4737: sa steng dag tu yang bran nyid du 'gyur //
NK022(za)001:4740: lha mi'i theg pas ngan 'gro las thar kyang //
NK022(za)001:4741: brtan pa ma thob dbang med slar ngan 'gro //
NK022(za)001:4742: mngon shes rdzu 'phrul thob kyang nyams na skyor //
NK022(za)001:4743: nyan thos bslab sdom bde 'gro ngan 'gro gnyis //
NK022(za)001:4744: re mos 'khor ba'i mtha' las nges 'byung blos //
NK022(za)001:4745: 'khor ba'i 'dam las so sor thar pa ni //
NK022(za)001:4746: rigs bdun dge slong pha ma dge slong ma //
NK022(za)001:4747: dge tshul pha ma dge bsnyen pha ma'o //
NK022(za)001:4748: dge slong ma'ang pha ltar 'jug pa dang //
NK022(za)001:4749: dge slong ma yis 'jug pa rgya che'o //
NK022(za)001:4750: lha mis dkon mchog gral du ma sleb kyang //
NK022(za)001:4751: nyan thos dge bsnyen dkon mchog gral du sleb //
NK022(za)001:4752: sangs rgyas zhabs 'bring 'khor bzhi dge slong dang //
NK022(za)001:4753: dge bsnyen pha ma'o dge tshul dge slong ma //
NK022(za)001:4754: dge bsnyen la bsdom gnam sbyar ma gsungs skad //
NK022(za)001:4755: dkon mchog gsum sgra mi grag gyur srid na'ang //
NK022(za)001:4756: de dag sangs rgyas nyid kyis dus bab mkhyen brtses mdzad //
NK022(za)001:4757: sangs rgyas mya ngan mi 'da' chos mi nub //
NK022(za)001:4758: rgyal dang rgyal sras tshul gyis kun rtag skyong //
NK022(za)001:4759: dge bsnyen dang po skyabs 'gro'i nyan thos ni //
NK022(za)001:4760: 'phags pa rgyun zhugs khyim pa du ma'ang bshad //
NK022(za)001:4762: sangs rgyas chos dang dge 'dun skyabs song ste //
NK022(za)001:4763: sangs rgyas 'grub bya bsnyam du kun mkhyen yid byed na //
NK022(za)001:4764: mkhas pas tshul khrims pha rol phyin gnas rig par bya //
NK022(za)001:4766: nyan thos 'phags la smon pa'i dge 'dun bshad //
NK022(za)001:4768: dgra bcom thob na nyes rtsa bzhi choms bshad //
NK022(za)001:4769: gang du skyes kyang ji srid 'tsho bar du //
NK022(za)001:4770: rgyal dang rgyal chos dge 'dun skyabs gsol bas //
NK022(za)001:4771: skyabs des kun tu bskyobs shing srung ba yis //
NK022(za)001:4772: srog gcod rkun rdzun 'dod log mi tshangs pa'i //
NK022(za)001:4773: spyod pa lus kyi byed pa mi rdzogs te //
NK022(za)001:4774: so thar rigs bdun sbyor byed bsam pa ni //
NK022(za)001:4775: nyon mongs chags sdang rmongs gsum dgra bcom pas //
NK022(za)001:4776: khrims kun nyes byed na smad sems dul bas //
NK022(za)001:4777: 'phags phyir nyan thos 'khor ba'i bran las thar //
NK022(za)001:4778: nyan thos thob kyang 'phags gnas ma thob na //
NK022(za)001:4779: rang rgyal thob 'phags bse ru ne tsos thar //
NK022(za)001:4781: nga'i nyan thos tshul khrims zhig gyur kyang //
NK022(za)001:4782: skye bo phal pa rnams kyi do ma yin //
NK022(za)001:4783: me tog tsam pa ka ni rnying gyur kyang //
NK022(za)001:4784: me tog phal pa rnams kyi do ma yin //
NK022(za)001:4785: zhes pa mdo mngas dkon mchog thos grol bshad /
NK022(za)001:4786: mdo sde drin lan bsab pa'i le'u las //
NK022(za)001:4787: bslab pa ji srid 'tsho bar bslab bshad pa //
NK022(za)001:4788: lha mi'i bsnyen gnas zhag dus las lhag par //
NK022(za)001:4789: nyan thos gtsor bstan 'chi khar chos ldan pa //
NK022(za)001:4790: nyes bshags sdom bzung smon lam dbang thob pas //
NK022(za)001:4791: tshe 'adi'am bar do phyi ma la //
NK022(za)001:4792: lha mis mtho ris thob ltar nyan thos 'phags thob bshad //
NK022(za)001:4793: lha mi sangs rgyas tshab kyi mkhan po la //
NK022(za)001:4794: ma brten na'ang rang gi 'bras bu thob byed cing //
NK022(za)001:4795: nyan thos sangs rgyas tshab kyi mkhan po dang //
NK022(za)001:4796: gnas kyi bla ma slob dpon rgan brten bshad //
NK022(za)001:4797: de phyir nyan thos dge bsnyen bslab sdom la //
NK022(za)001:4798: mkhan por gsol 'debs byed lugs mi byed lugs //
NK022(za)001:4799: 'jigs skyobs legs smon mkhan gsol mi dgos kyang //
NK022(za)001:4800: 'khor ba las thar nges 'byung mkhan gsol dgos //
NK022(za)001:4801: ngan 'gro'i 'jigs skyob mtho ris legs thob smon //
NK022(za)001:4802: slob dpon khyim pas dge bsnyen dbog thob kyang //
NK022(za)001:4803: nges 'byung dge tshul dge slong thob byed la //
NK022(za)001:4804: btsun pa mkhan po bsnyen rdzogs nges par dgos //
NK022(za)001:4809: bdag 'phags pa go 'phang la dgod pa'i mkhan po 'os pa la zhu ba'i 'dun pas /
NK022(za)001:4810: nyan thos kyi dge bsnyen dang dge tshul dge slong du bya ba ni /
NK022(za)001:4811: sngar chos 'brel med na btsun pa /
NK022(za)001:4812: yod na slob dpon zhes brjod /
NK022(za)001:4813: slob dpon dgongs su gsol bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi ba /
NK022(za)001:4814: slob dpon la mkhan por gsol gyis /
NK022(za)001:4815: slob dpon bdag gi mkhan po mdzad du gsol /
NK022(za)001:4816: slob dpon mkhan pos bdag rab tu dbyung du gsol /
NK022(za)001:4817: ces lan gnyis kyi tha ma /
NK022(za)001:4818: gsum pa'i gsham du mkhan po mkhan pos bdag rab tu dbyung du gsol /
NK022(za)001:4819: ces pa'i tha ma la mkhan por shes dgos pa'o //
NK022(za)001:4821: thams cad mkhyen pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK022(za)001:4822: nyan thos kyi sgor 'jug pa la /
NK022(za)001:4823: thog mar dge bsnyen gyi sdom pa dbog ste /
NK022(za)001:4828: slob dpon gyis mchod pa phul gdams ngag bshad pa /
NK022(za)001:4830: mya ngan las 'das pa'i bsam pa khyad par can brtan po bskyed cing /
NK022(za)001:4833: 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal mtha' dag las grol nas /
NK022(za)001:4834: zhi ba mya ngan las 'das pa'am /
NK022(za)001:4835: sangs rgyas kyi go 'phang thob par bya /
NK022(za)001:4836: de'i ched du bdag gis yongs rdzogs sam /
NK022(za)001:4837: tshangs pa mtshungs par spyod pa'am /
NK022(za)001:4841: skyabs 'gro'i bslab pa gang len pa de'i nges pa bzung ste /
NK022(za)001:4843: chung ngu'i ched du che mi gtang //
NK022(za)001:4844: gong nas gang du khyad zhugs spyad //
NK022(za)001:4846: nyan thos skabs yin kyang sangs rgyas thob 'dod dang /
NK022(za)001:4847: sems can kun la phan ched du dang /
NK022(za)001:4848: lcogs na zab rgyas slab gsung /
NK022(za)001:4849: gzhan yang lha yis dkon mchog sgra sgrogs te /
NK022(za)001:4850: nyan thos ston pa sangs rgyas dkon mchog ni /
NK022(za)001:4851: dang po byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed nas /
NK022(za)001:4852: bskal pa grangs med gsum du tshogs bsags te //
NK022(za)001:4853: byang chub 'di brnyes che la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK022(za)001:4855: sangs rgyas dang nyi ma'i 'od zer dag gis pad mo'i tshal 'byed ltar /
NK022(za)001:4856: gsung gi 'od zer dag gis 'jig rten sad par mdzad /
NK022(za)001:4857: ston pa sh+aakya thub pa sgrol ma thugs rje can /
NK022(za)001:4858: mya ngan 'das ston gang yin la phyag 'tshal //
NK022(za)001:4860: sangs rgyas kyi chos dang chos kyis sdug bsngal thams
NK022(za)001:4861: cad rab tu zhi ba'i de kho na nyid ni
NK022(za)001:4863: ston pa bstan pa bslab don gyis //
NK022(za)001:4864: skyabs gsum rnam par bzhag pa yin //
NK022(za)001:4866: gang len pa'i dge bsnyen gyi bslab pa'am /
NK022(za)001:4867: sdom pa blangs ming gang 'os btags la /
NK022(za)001:4868: ji srid 'tsho'i bar du thang lhod med par /
NK022(za)001:4875: dus 'di nas bzung nas ji srid 'tsho'i bar du /
NK022(za)001:4876: rkang gnyis rnams kyi mchog sangs rgyas la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK022(za)001:4877: 'dod chags dang bral ba rnams kyi mchog chos la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK022(za)001:4878: tshogs rnams kyi mchog dge 'dun la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK022(za)001:4882: slob dpon gyis bzung du gsol /
NK022(za)001:4883: zhes lan gsum gyi tha ma la btsun pa mi zer mkhan po'am slob dpon zer /
NK022(za)001:4884: slob dpon gyis thabs yin no //
NK022(za)001:4886: bslab pa brjod pa'i rjes bzlos khas len lha mi dang spyir 'dra ba las /
NK022(za)001:4887: drang srong chen po mi gsung bar 'phags pa dgra bcom pa gsung /
NK022(za)001:4888: 'on kyang sngon gyi yi ge las /
NK022(za)001:4889: tshangs par spyod pa dge bsnyen gyi bslab pa brjod pa ni /
NK022(za)001:4891: ji ltar 'phags pa dgra bcom pa rnams kyis /
NK022(za)001:4892: ji srid 'tsho'i bar du srog gcod pa spangs te /
NK022(za)001:4893: srog gcod pa las slar bzlog pa de bzhin du /
NK022(za)001:4895: dus 'di nas bzung ste ji srid 'tsho'i bar du srog gcod pa spangs te /
NK022(za)001:4896: srog gcod pa las slar bzlog par bagyi'o //
NK022(za)001:4897: yan lag dang po 'dis bdag 'phags pa dgra bcom
NK022(za)001:4898: pa de dag gi bslab pa la rjes su slob
NK022(za)001:4901: gzhan yang 'phags pa dgra bcom pa de dag gis ji srid 'tsho'i bar du /
NK022(za)001:4902: ma byin par len pa dang /
NK022(za)001:4903: mi tshangs par spyod pa dang /
NK022(za)001:4906: bcos pa'i chang myos par 'gyur ba /
NK022(za)001:4907: bag med pa'i gnas spangs te /
NK022(za)001:4908: bag med pa'i gnas las slar bzlog pa de bzhin du /
NK022(za)001:4909: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi bas dus 'di nas bzung nas /
NK022(za)001:4911: ma byin par len pa dang /
NK022(za)001:4912: mi tshangs par spyod pa dang /
NK022(za)001:4916: myos par 'gyur ba bag med pa'i gnas pa spangs te /
NK022(za)001:4917: bag med pa'i gnas las slar bzlog par bgyid do //
NK022(za)001:4918: yan lag lnga po 'dis ji ltar 'phags pa dgra
NK022(za)001:4919: bcom pa de dag gi bslab pa la rjes su
NK022(za)001:4920: slob bo // rjes su bsgrub bo /
NK022(za)001:4923: slob dpon gyis thabs yin no //
NK022(za)001:4924: slob mas legs so zhes brjod par bya'o //
NK022(za)001:4928: rdzun du smra ba spangs te /
NK022(za)001:4929: rdzun du smra ba las slar bzlog pa de bzhin
NK022(za)001:4930: du ces tshangs spyod kyi rtsa ba bzhi gong bzhin
NK022(za)001:4931: no // 'dod log spong na yang mi tshangs par spyod pa dang zhes pa bzhag la /
NK022(za)001:4932: 'dod pa la log par g.yem pa dang /
NK022(za)001:4936: bcu pa la go mi'i dge bsnyen gsung /
NK022(za)001:4937: gang slob de rnams kyi bsrung bya'i dmigs bshad dang /
NK022(za)001:4938: kye lha mi'i dge bsnyen bsam yas kyang /
NK022(za)001:4939: dkon mchog zhabs 'bring shin tu dkon //
NK022(za)001:4940: nyan thos dge bsnyen nyung na yang //
NK022(za)001:4941: dkon mchog zhabs thog don du 'khod //
NK022(za)001:4942: dge bsnyen gyi cho ga rdzogs so //
NK022(za)001:4946: nyan thos dge tshul bya ba ni //
NK022(za)001:4947: dang por rnam dbye khyad zur tsam //
NK022(za)001:4948: dkyil 'khor grub dus yig brgya bdun //
NK022(za)001:4949: bzlos tshe dngos yid rol mchod skor //
NK022(za)001:4950: lhag chad dag bshad shes mos byas //
NK022(za)001:4951: rten 'brel me tog dor rab gnas //
NK022(za)001:4952: snyan tshar nye snyen rten 'brel mchod //
NK022(za)001:4953: bsgrub pa rdor sems dkyil 'khor sprul //
NK022(za)001:4954: gang byed gzhung la cha gsum rgyan //
NK022(za)001:4955: bsgrub chen rang gzhung bskyed bzlas tshar //
NK022(za)001:4956: khrus bya sha chang sgog tsong spang //
NK022(za)001:4957: dkar mngar dge 'dun spyod rung brten //
NK022(za)001:4958: dpon slob kun kyang gso sbyong bya //
NK022(za)001:4959: sangs rgyas chos dang dge 'dun la //
NK022(za)001:4960: phyag mchod bshags phul bka' gnang bsam //
NK022(za)001:4961: rang gi bslab sdom dran sngo bya //
NK022(za)001:4962: dge bsnyen bar chad ma dris cing //
NK022(za)001:4963: khrus rtags btsun chags med pa dang //
NK022(za)001:4964: chos gos tshal pa byin la'ang skye //
NK022(za)001:4965: thos shes nges shes med pa'i bu //
NK022(za)001:4966: khong pa gnas la bar sdom skye //
NK022(za)001:4967: ma yis 'dun pa rjes bzlos byed //
NK022(za)001:4968: dus lon nges shes bslab skye'ang yod //
NK022(za)001:4969: mtshan gyur dge slong ma de'ang //
NK022(za)001:4970: dge slong phar 'gyur sngar srid bshad //
NK022(za)001:4971: dge tshul thob shes nges shes ldan //
NK022(za)001:4972: rtags ldan bar cha da med la skye //
NK022(za)001:4973: ming ni bsgyur dang ma bsgyur gnyis //
NK022(za)001:4974: dge slong bsnyen rdzogs 'phags skye tshul //
NK022(za)001:4975: dang po zer bzlos zhor ded la //
NK022(za)001:4976: mi spro log bsam de nas ni //
NK022(za)001:4978: 'phags pa rim skyes cung dga' bshad //
NK022(za)001:4979: rang rgyal 'bum las lhag pa yi //
NK022(za)001:4980: rgyal bas tshur shog bsnyen rdzogs kyang //
NK022(za)001:4981: de ni dge 'dun spyod yul min //
NK022(za)001:4982: dge 'dun kyis ni bsnyen rdzogs la //
NK022(za)001:4984: de yi grangs kyi kha bkang la //
NK022(za)001:4986: 'dren par bkag ste mi mnyam phyir //
NK022(za)001:4987: 'phags gcig dge slong bcu mnyam yang //
NK022(za)001:4989: 'phags dang skye bo mnyam slob phyir //
NK022(za)001:4990: gzhan yang dge slong mkhan po dang //
NK022(za)001:4991: las kyi slob dpon gsang ston gyi //
NK022(za)001:4992: slob dpon dus go'i gral gnas dang //
NK022(za)001:4993: grogs ldan dang bcas lngar nges pa'ang //
NK022(za)001:4994: dge 'dun grangs tshang mtshan nyid tshang //
NK022(za)001:4995: brda' sbyor tshul ldan shes dad brtan //
NK022(za)001:4996: bslab sdom med la'ang skyes bshad pa //
NK022(za)001:4997: pha bsad mi skyo'ang pha bsad pa'i //
NK022(za)001:4998: dge slong lha chen mkhan po yi //
NK022(za)001:4999: slob ma dgra bcom dge slong ni //
NK022(za)001:5000: dge 'dun gnas brtan mdzad par bshad //
NK022(za)001:5001: mtha' 'khob chos dar bsod nams thob //
NK022(za)001:5002: skabs 'dir klu grub tsan ti'i slob //
NK022(za)001:5003: mkhan bu rgya gar dbu rgyan gyi //
NK022(za)001:5004: slob dpon dga' rab yod smra'i lugs //
NK022(za)001:5005: nges shes rnyed pas tsa ka li'i //
NK022(za)001:5006: sangs rgyas chos gzungs mchog dge 'dun //
NK022(za)001:5007: kun shes ko 'u di nya dang //
NK022(za)001:5008: rta thul ming chen sha ri'i bu //
NK022(za)001:5009: sgra gcan sras dang gcung dga' sogs //
NK022(za)001:5010: dkon mchog dngos de'ang bla ma yis //
NK022(za)001:5011: brda' sbyor de yis bar sdom dang //
NK022(za)001:5012: bag chags zhogs pas chos sgo phyed //
NK022(za)001:5013: 'dul ba'i nyan bshad chas ldan rung //
NK022(za)001:5014: lha chen bar sdom tshul khrims kyis //
NK022(za)001:5015: dge slong gnas nas phyung na'ang //
NK022(za)001:5016: dge slong chas bskung dkon mchog la //
NK022(za)001:5017: dad pas ngan song grol bsang gsungs //
NK022(za)001:5020: slob mas lha phyag gsum byas la /
NK022(za)001:5021: bdag rab tu byung du gsol zhu /
NK022(za)001:5023: skyabs 'gro skyabs brjod yan chad mthun na'ang /
NK022(za)001:5024: blo gros thabs mkhas kyi skabs las /
NK022(za)001:5025: 'dul ba'i las kyi chog khrigs rnams yig byang la sgrags par ltar du /
NK022(za)001:5026: brkyang ste bkod pa 'di skad du /
NK022(za)001:5028: snga ma de ma byas par phyi ma mi bya zhes gsung na'ang /
NK022(za)001:5029: snga ma dge bsnyen gyi bya ba grub pa yin /
NK022(za)001:5030: mkhan por gsol ba snga ma byas na 'dir bya ste /
NK022(za)001:5031: bdag rab tu dbyung du gsol ces dge tshul gyi mkhan po zhu'o //
NK022(za)001:5032: de nas bdag 'dzin spang ba'i ched du don bshad pa ni /
NK022(za)001:5033: ming sngar ma btags na btags /
NK022(za)001:5034: 'khor ba las thar bar nges 'byung gi bsam pas
NK022(za)001:5035: zhu ba'i tshig bla ma'i rjes su brjod pa ni
NK022(za)001:5036: / mkhan por gsol ba ma btab na slob dpon /
NK022(za)001:5037: btab na mkhan po dgongs su gsol /
NK022(za)001:5041: rkang gnyis rnams kyi mchog sangs rgyas la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK022(za)001:5042: 'dod chags dang bral ba rnams kyi mchog chos la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK022(za)001:5043: tshogs rnams kyi mchog dge 'dun la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK022(za)001:5044: rgyal ba sangs rgyas sh+aakya thub pa /
NK022(za)001:5046: sh+aakya'i rgyal po gtso bo de rab tu byung ba'i rjes su bdag rab tu 'byung bar 'tshal te /
NK022(za)001:5047: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi ba khyim pa'i rtags spong ngo //
NK022(za)001:5048: rab tu byung ba'i rtags nges par yang dag par len te /
NK022(za)001:5049: slob dpon mkhan pos bdag rab tu byung du gsol /
NK022(za)001:5050: ces gnyis dang gsum gyi tha mar mkhan po mkhan pos bdag rab tu dbyung du gsol /
NK022(za)001:5052: kun gyi tha mar slob dpon gyis thabs yin no //
NK022(za)001:5053: slob bus legs so zhes brjod pa mthun no //
NK022(za)001:5054: de nas dge tshul gyi bar chad dri ba ni /
NK022(za)001:5055: sangs rgyas kyi rten la sangs rgyas dngos dang /
NK022(za)001:5056: chos dang dge 'dun la gus phyag gsum dang /
NK022(za)001:5057: mkhan po la phyag gsum phul /
NK022(za)001:5059: ston pa sangs rgyas sh+aakya thub pa ni /
NK022(za)001:5060: skye 'gro mi'i rigs las rab tu byung ste /
NK022(za)001:5061: khrims kyi dngos gzhi dag par srungs ba la brten nas sangs rgyas so //
NK022(za)001:5062: de'i rjes su rab tu byung ba yang /
NK022(za)001:5063: kun la bskal ba med pas /
NK022(za)001:5064: dge tshul gyi bar chad dri ba ni /
NK022(za)001:5065: rab tu byung ba la bar chad med dgos pa yin /
NK022(za)001:5066: de la sdom pa gnas pa'i bar chad bcu /
NK022(za)001:5067: sdom pa skye ba'i bar chad bcu bzhi /
NK022(za)001:5068: 'jig rten gyi kha na ma tho ba'i bar chad nyi shu yod pa yin /
NK022(za)001:5069: de la sdom pa skye ba'i bar chad dang /
NK022(za)001:5070: yon tan gyi bar chad dang /
NK022(za)001:5071: mdzes pa'i bar chad dang gsum med pa rab tu byung ba yang khrims ma nyams par srungs na /
NK022(za)001:5073: lha mi'i go 'phang je mtho thob //
NK022(za)001:5074: de la brten nas nges par legs pa zhi ba
NK022(za)001:5075: mya ngan las 'das pa'i go 'phangs thob par 'gyur
NK022(za)001:5077: nad pa'i sman rkus cing snod kyi rdza chag pa
NK022(za)001:5078: ltar du byang chub kyi lam chad nas 'khor ba
NK022(za)001:5079: ngan song du skye bar 'gyur ro //
NK022(za)001:5080: de yang bar chad 'di rnams skye ba sngon gyi yod kyang /
NK022(za)001:5081: skye ba 'di nas rgyun chad pa dang /
NK022(za)001:5082: tshe rabs kun tu bar chad med par nges par byed pa yin pas /
NK022(za)001:5083: rab tu byung bar 'dod pa khyed rnams ngas dri yis /
NK022(za)001:5084: khyed kyis ma 'dzem par yin pa la yin dang /
NK022(za)001:5085: ma yin pa la ma yin par lan thob cig /
NK022(za)001:5086: mu stegs can ma yin nam /
NK022(za)001:5088: lo bco lnga ma lon pa ma yin nam /
NK022(za)001:5089: lo bco lnga lon pa bya rog bskrod mi nus pa ma yin nam /
NK022(za)001:5090: bya rog nus pa lo bdun ma lon pa ma yin nam /
NK022(za)001:5091: lo bdun lon pa bya rog bskrod mi nus pa ma yin nam /
NK022(za)001:5092: bran la sogs pa ma yin nam /
NK022(za)001:5093: bu lon chags pa ma yin nam /
NK022(za)001:5094: yin zer na khyod kyis bu lon mang yang rung /
NK022(za)001:5095: nyung yang rung cung zad kyang ma lus par 'jal nus sam /
NK022(za)001:5098: mas ma gnang ba ma yin nam /
NK022(za)001:5099: pha mas ma gnang ba yul thag mi ring ba ma yin nam /
NK022(za)001:5101: nad pa yin na de gos par mi nus pa ma yin nam /
NK022(za)001:5104: dge slong ma sun phyung ba ma yin nam /
NK022(za)001:5105: rku thabs su gnas pa ma yin nam /
NK022(za)001:5106: tha dad du gnas pa ma yin nam /
NK022(za)001:5107: gnas par mi bya ba gnas ma yin nam /
NK022(za)001:5108: za ma dang ma ning dang ma ning du rtogs
NK022(za)001:5109: pa'i 'dod chags zhe sdang la sogs lhag par che
NK022(za)001:5110: ba'am chung ba ma yin nam /
NK022(za)001:5113: mu stegs can zhugs pa ma yin nam /
NK022(za)001:5114: pha bsad pa ma yin nam /
NK022(za)001:5115: ma bsad pa ma yin nam /
NK022(za)001:5116: dgra bcom pa bsad pa ma yin nam /
NK022(za)001:5117: dge 'dun gyi dbyen byas pa ma yin nam /
NK022(za)001:5118: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku la ngan sems kyi khrag phyung ba ma yin nam /
NK022(za)001:5119: de ltar mtshams med pa lnga'i las byas sam byed du bcug pa ma yin nam /
NK022(za)001:5120: des sdom pa skye ba'i bar chad bcu bzhi'o //
NK022(za)001:5121: pham par gyur pa'i ltung ba bzhi las gang yang rung ba byung ba ma yin nam /
NK022(za)001:5122: byung na khyed 'babs pa na bslab pa legs par phul lam /
NK022(za)001:5123: gal te ma phul na gsar du 'chags pa'i gegs
NK022(za)001:5124: byed pas bslab pa skyon can rnams phul nas dag
NK022(za)001:5125: pa zung zhig / de'i don go bas nges so //
NK022(za)001:5126: rgyu las log pa'i chad pa khas mi len pa gnas nas phyung ba ma yin nam /
NK022(za)001:5127: lag rdul la sogs pa ma yin nam /
NK022(za)001:5128: skra ser la sogs pa ma yin nam /
NK022(za)001:5129: sen mo gcig pa la sogs pa ma yin nam /
NK022(za)001:5130: rgyal pos bkrabs pa la sogs pa ma yin nam /
NK022(za)001:5131: rgyal pos ma gnang ba ma yin nam /
NK022(za)001:5132: rgyal pos ma gnang ba yul thag mi ring ba ma yin nam /
NK022(za)001:5133: chom rkun par grags pa ma yin nam /
NK022(za)001:5134: phung bkrol ba ma yin nam /
NK022(za)001:5138: mi ma yin pa'i 'gro ba pa ma yin nam /
NK022(za)001:5139: byang gi sgra mi snyan pa ma yin nam /
NK022(za)001:5140: mtshan lan gsum du gyur pa ma yin nam /
NK022(za)001:5141: skyes pa 'dra ba'i bud med ma yin nam /
NK022(za)001:5142: bud med 'dra ba'i skyes pa ma yin nam /
NK022(za)001:5143: sdig sdig lta bu'i mtshan nyid can ma yin nam /
NK022(za)001:5144: gling gzhan nas skyes pa'i tshul byad mi 'dra ba ma yin nam /
NK022(za)001:5145: de ltar 'jig rten gyi kha na ma tho ba skye ba'i bar chad nyi shu'o //
NK022(za)001:5146: de rnams sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa la bcug na
NK022(za)001:5147: mu stegs la sogs pas 'phya zhing smod pa spang
NK022(za)001:5148: pa yin no // ma lags zer na lan du /
NK022(za)001:5149: khyed rnams bar chad dang mi ldan pas na sangs
NK022(za)001:5150: rgyas bstan pa'ii snod du rung bar 'dug pas bdag
NK022(za)001:5151: gis khyod rab tu dbyung bar bagyi'o //
NK022(za)001:5153: de nas btsun chas rnams dkon mchog gi drung du dgongs su gsol nas /
NK022(za)001:5154: gtad pa'i phyir rigs kyi bu de lag pa deng byed du bzhugs shing /
NK022(za)001:5155: 'tsho ba'i yo byad ces bya ba ji srid ma
NK022(za)001:5156: shi ba'i bar 'tsho ba'i bar du 'chang dgos pa'o
NK022(za)001:5157: // gos smad kyi mtha' nas gtad la /
NK022(za)001:5158: slob ma'i lag pa brkyang ba'i khar bzhag cing /
NK022(za)001:5159: 'di ni smad du bgo ba'i mtha' gos zhes bya ba /
NK022(za)001:5160: smad gcer ba dang smad ngo tsha ba'i gnas las
NK022(za)001:5161: skyob par dkon mchog gis bka' gnang ba yin no
NK022(za)001:5162: // stod kyi bla gos gtad la 'di ni stod bla gos zhes bya ba /
NK022(za)001:5164: stod tshad pa'i gnas las skyob /
NK022(za)001:5165: sbrang bu dang lhags pa srung ba la bka' gnang ba yin no //
NK022(za)001:5166: gzhan yang dbyar gos ras chen char cha sogs kyang gtad /
NK022(za)001:5167: ske rags sogs mkho ba'i yo byad kyang gtad /
NK022(za)001:5168: 'di ni lhung bzed bya ba zas lhung sa 'dis
NK022(za)001:5169: zed par byed pa 'di zas kyis 'gengs pa bzhin
NK022(za)001:5170: du rgyud yon tan gyis 'gengs pa yin no //
NK022(za)001:5171: 'di chu tshags zhes bya ba sems can la 'tshe
NK022(za)001:5172: ba spong zhing sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa 'di snying
NK022(za)001:5173: brtse bas khyad par du byas pa yin pas /
NK022(za)001:5174: chu srog chags can la 'dis btsags pa'i chu la longs spyod pa yin no //
NK022(za)001:5175: 'di gding ba zhes bya ba rang gi gos rnams ni sa la reg pa'i skyon yong pa dang /
NK022(za)001:5176: dge 'dun spyi dang gang zag dang khyim pa'i gdan
NK022(za)001:5177: gyi steng du 'di bting nas longs spyod yin no
NK022(za)001:5178: // zhes pa la sogs pa kun gtad tshar ba dang /
NK022(za)001:5179: chas rnams g.yas nas chos skor du mkhan pos bskon cing /
NK022(za)001:5180: kun gyi smon lam bya ste /
NK022(za)001:5181: tshe dang ldan pa che ge mo /
NK022(za)001:5186: rnam par grol ba'i ye shes gzigs pa'i phung po
NK022(za)001:5187: yongs su rdzogs thar pa'i rgyal mtshan brtan par gyur
NK022(za)001:5188: cig / tshangs par spyod pa tshe'i mthar phyin pa dang /
NK022(za)001:5189: tshangs par spyad pa'i 'bras bu bla na med pa'ii sangs rgyas thob par gyur cig /
NK022(za)001:5191: dge tshul de snam sbyar yod pa 'chang du rung yang sbyin par bka' ma gnang bas /
NK022(za)001:5193: khyim pa'i khrod du bgo bar mi bya'o //
NK022(za)001:5194: de nas lus tshang byed du bcug la /
NK022(za)001:5196: skra breg mkhan gyis gtsug phud breg pa spro ba dris la spro na gtsug phud breg /
NK022(za)001:5197: las byed pa'i dge slong ngam dkyil 'khor gyi rten
NK022(za)001:5198: dkon mchog gsum gyi gtso bo thub pa dang snying
NK022(za)001:5199: po chos dang dge 'dun mchog gnas brtan dang /
NK022(za)001:5200: dge slong gang 'dzom la zhu ste dge tshul de ni /
NK022(za)001:5201: dge slong mkhan po gcig nyid kyis byed pa'ang rung skad pa ltar du /
NK022(za)001:5203: zhu ba'i tshig 'di sngar dge slong byed ma myong
NK022(za)001:5204: pa rnams la rku thabs kyi nyes pa srung ba'i
NK022(za)001:5205: phyir rna ba khebs byas la /
NK022(za)001:5206: 'os pa gcig gis dge 'dun la zhu ba byed pa la mos pa bya'o //
NK022(za)001:5207: 'di skad du dge 'dun btsun pa rnams dgongs su gsol lo //
NK022(za)001:5208: ming 'di zhes bgyi ba 'di mkhan po ming 'di
NK022(za)001:5209: zhes bgyi ba las rab tu 'byung bar 'tshal lo
NK022(za)001:5210: // khyim pa gos dkar po can /
NK022(za)001:5211: skra dang kha spu'am skra dang sen mo zhes dge tshul ma la'o //
NK022(za)001:5212: ma breg pa la legs par gsungs pa'i chos 'dul ba la rab tu 'byung bar 'tshal te /
NK022(za)001:5213: ming 'di zhes bgyi ba 'di rab tu 'byung 'tshal bas /
NK022(za)001:5214: skra dang kha spu bregs gos ngur smrig bgos te
NK022(za)001:5215: yang dag pa kho nar dad pas khyim nas khyim
NK022(za)001:5216: med par / mkhan po ming 'di zhes bya ba las rab tu 'byung ste /
NK022(za)001:5217: de yang bar chod kyi chos rnams dag go zhes
NK022(za)001:5218: kho na nyid mchi na ci rab tu dbyung ngam
NK022(za)001:5219: zhes lan gcig brjod cing gcig la kho na /
NK022(za)001:5221: gsum khong rnams zhes te tsa ka dang gral na dge slong kun mthun par mos bya /
NK022(za)001:5222: kun gyis gal te yongs su dag na'o zhes brjod /
NK022(za)001:5223: sngar ma bregs na gtsug phud 'dir breg cing ma
NK022(za)001:5224: brjod na nang par bar chad ma dris pa dang
NK022(za)001:5225: / dris kyang skyon yod na mkhan pos dus dran du /
NK022(za)001:5226: dkon mchog brtse ba can gyis bka' gnang bar ma
NK022(za)001:5227: dran pa la 'gal tshabs can du lung las bshad
NK022(za)001:5228: / de nas slob dpon 'os pa la che ges
NK022(za)001:5229: 'di la dge tshul gyi bslab sdom gnang bar zhu
NK022(za)001:5230: zhes mkhan pos bskul ba'i lan du /
NK022(za)001:5231: 'di yi bar chad kyi chos dag gam zhes dris la /
NK022(za)001:5232: dge tshul gyi bslab sdom don du /
NK022(za)001:5233: slob dpon nam mkhan po rang la phyag gsum byas la /
NK022(za)001:5234: tsog pur 'dug pa la 'di skad brjod de /
NK022(za)001:5235: khyed dge tshul nyid du bsgrub pa la rtags dang cha lugs bsgyur ba dang /
NK022(za)001:5237: don bsgyur ba dang gsum sngar bstan tshar /
NK022(za)001:5238: da de'i bslab sdom thob pa'i don du rjes bzlos mdzod cig /
NK022(za)001:5239: btsun pa'am slob dpon nam mkhan po dgongs su gsol /
NK022(za)001:5240: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi ba dus 'di nas bzung ste /
NK022(za)001:5242: rkang gnyis rnams kyi mchog sangs rgyas la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK022(za)001:5243: 'dod chags dang bral ba rnams kyi mchog chos la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK022(za)001:5244: tshogs rnams kyi mchog dge 'dun la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK022(za)001:5245: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi ba dge tshul du btsun pas zhes pa'am /
NK022(za)001:5249: slob dpon gyis bzung du gsol ces bya ste /
NK022(za)001:5250: de'i tshe bdag la dge tshul gyi bslab pa rgyud
NK022(za)001:5251: la skyes snyam pa'i thob shes 'tshal ba lags so
NK022(za)001:5252: // zhes shes par byas la thabs legs brjod /
NK022(za)001:5253: da ni bslab pa brjod pa'i rjes bzlos lan gcig gis khyab ste /
NK022(za)001:5255: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi ba dus 'di nas bzung ste /
NK022(za)001:5258: ma byin par len pa dang /
NK022(za)001:5259: mi tshangs par spyod pa dang /
NK022(za)001:5262: bcos pa'i chang myos par 'gyur ba bag med pa'i gnas dang /
NK022(za)001:5263: glu gar dang rol mo'i sgra dang /
NK022(za)001:5265: rgyan dang kha dog 'chang ba dang /
NK022(za)001:5268: dus ma yin pa'i kha zas dang /
NK022(za)001:5269: gser dngul len pa spangs te /
NK022(za)001:5270: gser dngul len pa las slar bzlog par bagyi'o //
NK022(za)001:5271: ji ltar 'phags pa dgra bcom pa de dag gis /
NK022(za)001:5273: ma byin par len pa dang /
NK022(za)001:5274: mi tshangs par spyod pa dang /
NK022(za)001:5276: 'bras bu'i chang dang bcos pa'i chang myos par 'gyur ba /
NK022(za)001:5277: bag med pa'i gnas dang glu gar dang rol mo'i sgra dang /
NK022(za)001:5279: rgyan dang kha dog 'chang ba dang /
NK022(za)001:5280: khri gdan mthon po dang khri gdan chen po dang /
NK022(za)001:5281: dus ma yin pa'i kha zas dang /
NK022(za)001:5282: gser dngul len pa spangs te /
NK022(za)001:5283: gser dngul len pa las slar log pa de bzhin du /
NK022(za)001:5284: bdag 'phags pa dgra bcom pa de dag gi bslab pa la rjes su slob bo //
NK022(za)001:5287: zhes lan gcig dang thabs yin no legs so bya /
NK022(za)001:5288: yang bslab pa brjod pa'i skabs su /
NK022(za)001:5290: gang zhig srog gcod gzhan gyi nor 'phrog dang //
NK022(za)001:5291: mi tshangs spyod rdzun bcos pa'i chang la sogs //
NK022(za)001:5292: gar sogs phreng sogs mal chen mtho ba dang //
NK022(za)001:5293: phyi dro'i kha zas dngul nyid spong ba de //
NK022(za)001:5294: nyon mongs dgra g.yul rgyal byed tshul khrims te /
NK022(za)001:5296: 'chi ba'i mche ba 'byin par byed pa'i thabs //
NK022(za)001:5297: rdzogs pa'i byang chub dpal nod dbang bskur yin /
NK022(za)001:5299: dge tshul brtul zhugs chu lon brtsigs pa 'dra /
NK022(za)001:5301: zhes dge tshul gyi bslab pa bcur bzhed pa'o //
NK022(za)001:5302: yang gnang ba bcu gsum ni /
NK022(za)001:5303: 'phang pa dang ni bral ba dang //
NK022(za)001:5304: de bzhin sa ni rko ba dang //
NK022(za)001:5305: rin chen reg dang me la reg /
NK022(za)001:5306: ljon shing 'dzeg dang shing gcod dang //
NK022(za)001:5307: byin len ma byas za ba dang //
NK022(za)001:5308: rtsa sngon mi gtsang 'dor ba dang //
NK022(za)001:5309: de bzhin bsog 'jog za ba dang //
NK022(za)001:5310: sa bon 'joms dang bslab pa'i gzhi //
NK022(za)001:5311: bcu po rnams ni ma rtogs pa //
NK022(za)001:5312: so sor thar pa bstan pa dag /
NK022(za)001:5313: blang ba'i phyogs mthun shes par bya //
NK022(za)001:5314: zhes so thar nyis brgya lnga bcu rtsa gsum du'o //
NK022(za)001:5315: dge tshul gso sbyong ni byams pa lung bstan las /
NK022(za)001:5316: bcu bzhi dang ni bco lnga dang //
NK022(za)001:5317: de bzhin zla phyed tshes brgyad dang //
NK022(za)001:5319: gso sbyong yan lag brgyad srungs na //
NK022(za)001:5320: nga yi bstan la lhags par 'gyur //
NK022(za)001:5323: ding nas srog gcod mi bya zhing //
NK022(za)001:5324: gzhan gyi nor yang blang mi bya //
NK022(za)001:5325: 'khrig pa'i chos kyang mi spyad cing //
NK022(za)001:5326: rdzun gyi tshig kyang mi smra'o //
NK022(za)001:5327: skyon ni mang po nyan bsten pas //
NK022(za)001:5328: chang ni yongs su spang bar bya //
NK022(za)001:5329: de bzhin dus ma yin pa'i zas //
NK022(za)001:5330: dri dang phreng ba dang ni rgyan //
NK022(za)001:5331: gar dang glu sogs spang bar bya //
NK022(za)001:5332: ji ltar dgra bcom rtag tu ni //
NK022(za)001:5333: srog gcod la sogs ma byed pa //
NK022(za)001:5334: de ltar srog gcod la sogs spangs //
NK022(za)001:5335: dge ba gso zhing sdig pa sbyong ba'i phyir //
NK022(za)001:5336: de bzhin gshegs pa'i gso sbyong rgyal bas gsungs //
NK022(za)001:5338: rtsa ba'i srog ni mi rang bzhin gyi char rtogs srog chags tsam dang /
NK022(za)001:5339: rtsa ba'i gzhan nor rgyal po'i tshad kyi bzhi cha rku 'phrog de'i char rtogs che phra du ma'o //
NK022(za)001:5340: rtsa ba'i 'khrig pa gnas dang gnas ma yin la myong ba rgyal bas ma gnang ba ste /
NK022(za)001:5341: char rtogs gnas reg pa dang /
NK022(za)001:5342: rtsa ba'i rdzun mi chos bla ma ste char rtogs shes bzhin gyi don med kyi rdzun no //
NK022(za)001:5343: chang la sogs pa'ang nad dang 'dul ba'i don dang /
NK022(za)001:5344: rgyal ba'i bka' thob pa la bag yod kyis spyod pa la ma rtogs kyi sgeg rgyag ched do //
NK022(za)001:5345: gso ba zhes dge ba ni spang bya dang blang
NK022(za)001:5346: bya ma nor bar mkhyen pa rgyal ba'i bka' drin
NK022(za)001:5347: pa'i dge ba'o // bslab pa bskyar te len pa mi chags bshad /
NK022(za)001:5348: skabs der dge tshul gyi bslab sdom thob pa'i dus go bar brjod nas /
NK022(za)001:5349: bsnyen bskur gyi gnas dang gral shes pa la /
NK022(za)001:5350: de rnams mkhan po'i bka' drin yin pas /
NK022(za)001:5354: stod kyi gos phrag pa dbyung ba dang /
NK022(za)001:5355: rgyan phreng bzhag pa rnams mtha' 'khob dang skabs kyi gnang ba dran pas bago'o //
NK022(za)001:5356: dge tshul nyid du bya ba rdzogs so //
NK022(za)001:5360: dge slong du bya ba ni /
NK022(za)001:5362: khyod kyi mkhan po la ston pa'i 'du shes bskyed par bya /
NK022(za)001:5364: ser mo tsam zhig gyon pa la //
NK022(za)001:5365: ston pa'i 'du shes bskyed par bya //
NK022(za)001:5367: mkhan po'am slob dpon dang las gral du gnas pa rnams la /
NK022(za)001:5368: ston pa sangs rgyas dang ston pa sangs rgyas kyi
NK022(za)001:5369: nyan thos sha ri'i bu la sogs pa mchog rnams
NK022(za)001:5370: ltar du mos pa byas la dge slong gi mkhan
NK022(za)001:5371: por gsol ba gdab pa dang /
NK022(za)001:5372: dge slong du rab tu byung bar gsol ba gdab par bya'o //
NK022(za)001:5373: bdag gi mkhan po mdzad du gsol ces dang /
NK022(za)001:5374: bdag rab tu dbyung du gsol ces pa dang /
NK022(za)001:5375: thabs legs sngar lta mthun pa'o //
NK022(za)001:5376: de nas rab tu byung ba'i chas rnams sngar du bsags pa rnam pa nges par bkod cing /
NK022(za)001:5378: dad pa'i dge 'dun 'khod pa rnams re re'i mdun du bstan la /
NK022(za)001:5382: lhung bzed bzang ngam zhes zhu /
NK022(za)001:5383: len du lhung bzed bzang zhes bkra shis pa'i tshig dang me tog re blug /
NK022(za)001:5384: chas gzhan rnams la yang thams cad kyis spro bar bya'o //
NK022(za)001:5386: mkhan po dang dge 'dun la phyag grub pa dang /
NK022(za)001:5388: dge 'dun gyi las la mi dbang ba'i nyan rna bkag cing /
NK022(za)001:5389: dbang ba'i mdun sa blangs te /
NK022(za)001:5391: dge slong nyid du bsgrub pa la bar chad kyi chos rnams spang ba'i phyir /
NK022(za)001:5392: tshig snga ma nyid ma byas par phyi ma rnams mi bya zhes gsungs pa las /
NK022(za)001:5393: dge bsnyen dang dge tshul du grub cing bar chad
NK022(za)001:5394: dag pas 'dir dkyil 'khor gtso bo sangs rgyas dang
NK022(za)001:5395: chos sgo sde snod kun gyi snying po yi ge'i
NK022(za)001:5397: gnas brtan gzhung bzhin rten la spyan drangs mchod pa grub gnang ba zhus shing /
NK022(za)001:5398: mkhan slob dge 'dun mkhas shing phan thogs kyi yan
NK022(za)001:5399: lag lnga phrugs gang rung dang ldan pa'i mkhan po
NK022(za)001:5400: de nyid btsun pa brtan pas yid ches pa'i yan
NK022(za)001:5401: lag bsnyen pa rdzogs nas bar ma chad lo bcu
NK022(za)001:5402: lon pas / dge slong bcu dang mnyam pa'i dgra bcom ltar mos 'dun skyer rung ba dang /
NK022(za)001:5403: las kyi bya ba la mkhas pa'i kha skong bar
NK022(za)001:5404: 'os pa'i slob dpon rnam pa gnyis dad pa'i dge
NK022(za)001:5405: 'dun dang bcas pa la mos gus mdzod la /
NK022(za)001:5406: skabs 'dir bar chad dri ba lung bstan pa ltar
NK022(za)001:5407: cung zad cig dri ba la gus pas khyed ma
NK022(za)001:5408: 'dzem par byos la yin pa la yin zhes dang
NK022(za)001:5409: / ma yin pa la ma yin zhes brjod cig /
NK022(za)001:5411: skyes pa'i mtshan dang ldan nam /
NK022(za)001:5412: khyed kyi pha ma gson nam /
NK022(za)001:5413: gson zer na khyed kyi pha mas gnang ngam /
NK022(za)001:5417: rtsod pa can ma yin nam /
NK022(za)001:5418: yang dge slong ma la bud med yin nam /
NK022(za)001:5419: bud med kyi mtshan dang ldan nam /
NK022(za)001:5421: yin lags ldan lags gsal bar brjod cing mtshan rtogs par bya /
NK022(za)001:5422: khyed kyis mngal dang shol du bcas pa'i lo nyi shu lon nam /
NK022(za)001:5423: khyed kyi chos gos gsum dang lhung bzed tshang ngam /
NK022(za)001:5425: rgyal pos bkrabs pa ma yin nam /
NK022(za)001:5426: rgyal po la sdigs pa ma yin nam /
NK022(za)001:5427: rgyal po la gnod pa'i las byed pa'am gnod pa'i
NK022(za)001:5428: las byas sam byed du bcug pa ma yin nam
NK022(za)001:5429: / chom rkun par grags pa ma yin nam /
NK022(za)001:5432: dge slong ma sun phyung ba ma yin nam /
NK022(za)001:5433: rku thabs su gnas pa ma yin nam /
NK022(za)001:5434: tha dad du gnas pa ma yin nam /
NK022(za)001:5435: gnas par mi bya ba gnas pa ma yin nam /
NK022(za)001:5436: mu stegs can ma yin nam /
NK022(za)001:5437: mu stegs can zhugs pa ma yin nam /
NK022(za)001:5438: pha bsad pa ma yin nam /
NK022(za)001:5439: ma bsad pa ma yin nam /
NK022(za)001:5440: dgra bcom pa bsad pa ma yin nam /
NK022(za)001:5441: dge 'dun gyi dbyen byas pa ma yin nam /
NK022(za)001:5442: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku la ngan sems kyi khrag phyung ba ma yin nam /
NK022(za)001:5445: khyod la la la'i bu lon mang yang rung nyung yang rung cung zad chags pa med dam /
NK022(za)001:5446: chags zer na khyed bsnyen pa rdzogs nas 'jal nus sam /
NK022(za)001:5447: khyed nad pa ma yin nam /
NK022(za)001:5448: khyed kyi lus la nad kyi rnam pa gang yang rung ba dag med dam /
NK022(za)001:5449: khyod sngon dge slong du rab tu byung ba ma yin nam /
NK022(za)001:5450: yin zer na dge tshul dus ltar bshags pa dang 'bul chog bya /
NK022(za)001:5452: da ltar khyod rab tu byung ba yin nam zhes dri'o //
NK022(za)001:5453: de ltar bar chad med par nges pa'am /
NK022(za)001:5455: dgos skyon dang bral bar nges pa'am /
NK022(za)001:5456: dkon mchog brtse ba can gyis gnang ba'i dus dran bzung la /
NK022(za)001:5457: mkhan pos me tog phyag tu bzhes la /
NK022(za)001:5458: mkhan po rang gis ma lcogs na mkhan po dang 'os pa gzhan dang /
NK022(za)001:5459: slob dpon las cho ga mdzad pa'i slob dpon dang /
NK022(za)001:5460: gsang ste ston pa'i slob dpon dang /
NK022(za)001:5461: dus bgo ba'i las gral ba dang /
NK022(za)001:5462: bsgrub bya'i grogs ldan 'os pa la zhu zhing gsol ba btab pa bya ba gal che zhing /
NK022(za)001:5463: de lta bu gral na med na yid kyis 'os pa gzhan dam bca' bzung la /
NK022(za)001:5465: bsgrub byas gsol ba btab pa'i mkhan pos bzhengs la /
NK022(za)001:5467: snam sbyar mtha' gos bla gos gding ba chu tshags
NK022(za)001:5468: lhung bzed la sogs pa rim pas phyag tu bzhes
NK022(za)001:5470: bsgrub byas phyag byas langs pa'i lag pa dang mkhan
NK022(za)001:5471: po'i phyag steng 'og tu byas reg pa la rjes
NK022(za)001:5472: bzlos byed pas / btsun chas byin brlab byas te /
NK022(za)001:5474: ming 'di zhes bya ba'i chos gos bgyis lags pa
NK022(za)001:5475: rung ba spyad par 'os pa 'di chos gos bla
NK022(za)001:5476: gos su byin gyis brlabs so zhes ltar /
NK022(za)001:5477: mthong gos dang snam sbyar dang gding bar byin gyis brlabs so zhes dang /
NK022(za)001:5478: lhung bzed la blang ba'i snod du byin gyis brlabs so zhes brjod /
NK022(za)001:5479: re zhig g.yar ba la'ang rung /
NK022(za)001:5480: de la sngar byin brlabs gzhan gyis byas na /
NK022(za)001:5481: byin gyis brlabs pa las dngos po 'di slar dbyung bar bagyi'o //
NK022(za)001:5482: zhes byin brlabs dbyung ba la byin brlabs bya /
NK022(za)001:5484: mkhan pos g.yog cing dkyil 'khor dang dge 'dun gyis
NK022(za)001:5485: mthun gyur gyi sgra grag pa la mos 'dun bya
NK022(za)001:5486: / dkon mchog gi mthus de kho na bzhin du
NK022(za)001:5487: gyur cig ces sogs skabs dang mkhyen brtse thabs mkhas
NK022(za)001:5488: / sbyar ba bya'o // snam sbyar bskon dus /
NK022(za)001:5489: 'di mu stegs kyi rtags dang dge tshul gyi chas
NK022(za)001:5490: las khyad par du byed pa dge slong gi chas
NK022(za)001:5492: dge 'dun la bka' gnang ba yin zhes dang /
NK022(za)001:5493: bla gos sogs dge tshul ltar bya /
NK022(za)001:5494: dge slong gi 'tsho ba'i yo byad phrugs bcu gsum ni /
NK022(za)001:5499: mtha' gos kyi gzan rnams nyin gyi chas dang /
NK022(za)001:5500: rngul gzan la ska rags dang /
NK022(za)001:5501: rngul gzan gyi gzan la ska rags dang /
NK022(za)001:5503: sham thabs kyi gzan rnams mtshan gyi chas dang /
NK022(za)001:5504: gdong phyis rnag gzan g.yan pa bkab pa dbyar gyi gos ras chen rnams skabs kyi chas dang /
NK022(za)001:5507: stod la skyes pa'i 'dod chags reg pa srung ba dang /
NK022(za)001:5508: mkho ba'i yo byad tur bu gdan gding ba chu tshags zha khab skud la sogs du ma'o //
NK022(za)001:5509: thams cad kyang 'dus byas mi rtag pa dang /
NK022(za)001:5510: zag bcas sdug bsngal ba dang /
NK022(za)001:5511: mya ngan las 'das pa'i zhi ba'am stong pa nyid dam chos kyi sku dang /
NK022(za)001:5512: chos thams cad bdag med par thams cad shes par bya ba ni /
NK022(za)001:5513: kun gyi byin brlabs des chog pa yin gsung /
NK022(za)001:5514: de ltar shes pa la byang chub yan lag rnams
NK022(za)001:5515: kyi dran pa gso bas mkhar sil kyang gtad nas
NK022(za)001:5516: / 'di ni so so'i skye bo rnams mkhar ba yang yin /
NK022(za)001:5517: bsil byed kyang yin pas mkhar sil du grags na'ang /
NK022(za)001:5518: mchod rten ye shes las grub pa'i kun gsal chos sku steng ma dang /
NK022(za)001:5519: 'og ma bsod nams las grub pa'i snying po gzugs sku /
NK022(za)001:5520: yang na steng gzugs sku sangs rgyas longs spyod rdzogs sku /
NK022(za)001:5521: 'og gzugs sku sangs rgyas sprul sku de gnyis kyi
NK022(za)001:5522: bar stong pa nyid chos kyi sku'i sangs rgyas dang
NK022(za)001:5523: / rwa bzhi sdug bsngal kun 'byung 'gog lam gyi bden bzhi'am /
NK022(za)001:5524: rwa gnyis don dam kun rdzob gnyis /
NK022(za)001:5525: yang mig phyi nang gi rten 'brel bcu gnyis /
NK022(za)001:5526: yar rtse dang mar rtse byang chub kyi yan lag bdun dang 'phags pa'i lam yan lag brgyad /
NK022(za)001:5528: 'khor ba'i rgya mdud la chos kyi 'khor lo /
NK022(za)001:5529: chu shing ltar snying po med na'ang thar ba'i lam dang /
NK022(za)001:5530: gnod pa bskrod cing dge ba la bskul ba'i mkhar ba sil snyan gyi sgra skad /
NK022(za)001:5531: dran pa bzhi dang rdzu 'phrul rkang bzhis yang dag spong ba bzhi dang /
NK022(za)001:5532: dbang po lnga stobs lnga ste dge ba'i phar phyin dran pa gso ba 'di ltar yin zhes sbyin /
NK022(za)001:5533: gal te mkhar ba gzhan 'chang na /
NK022(za)001:5534: dge 'dun gyi gnang ba'am skabs gzhan nad pa la
NK022(za)001:5535: sogs pa 'khar ba'i gnang ba dgos pa yin gsung
NK022(za)001:5536: pa thos / de nas de'i grogs ldan pa la gtad la /
NK022(za)001:5537: btsun chas dge slong gi chas bskon /
NK022(za)001:5538: pha gu dang rtsa dang gding ba la bzhag pa
NK022(za)001:5539: la mkhan pos 'di skad ces dkyil 'khor la ltas
NK022(za)001:5540: shing dge 'dun rnams nges pas 'di skad zhu'o //
NK022(za)001:5541: na mo dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs dang chos smra
NK022(za)001:5542: ba'i dge 'dun chos ldan 'dus pa rnams dgongs su
NK022(za)001:5543: gsol / tshe dang ldan pa mi 'di zhes bya
NK022(za)001:5544: ba 'di nyid dge slong gi dge 'dun du bzung
NK022(za)001:5545: du gsol zhes gsol ba gdab pas /
NK022(za)001:5546: dkyil 'khor lha dang phyogs bcu'i dge 'dun gyi bka' gnang bar mos 'dun byas la /
NK022(za)001:5547: slob dpon rnam gnyis dang dge slong bslab sdom thob
NK022(za)001:5548: pa'i dus bgo ba'i las kyi cho ga shes pa'i
NK022(za)001:5549: kha skong 'os pa yod na de la gtad /
NK022(za)001:5550: dge slong gi bslab sdom thob par nges par slob pa gal che'o //
NK022(za)001:5551: gal te kha skong 'os pa med na de tsam la dge slong du mos 'dun byas nas /
NK022(za)001:5552: slob dpon gyi bya ba gzhan du mkhan pos gsol
NK022(za)001:5553: ba btab pa la brten par dam bcas la slob
NK022(za)001:5554: dpon gyi bya ba'i gdams ngag bsdus nas mkhan pos
NK022(za)001:5556: dge slong gi khrims nyis brgya lnga bcu yod kyang /
NK022(za)001:5557: rtsa ba'i pham pa bzhi la mi spyod dam zhes brjod pa'i lan du mi spyod lags zhes zhu /
NK022(za)001:5558: dge slong gi chos bzhi ste /
NK022(za)001:5559: brdeg pa la slar mi brdeg pa dang /
NK022(za)001:5560: gshe ba la slar mi gshe ba dang /
NK022(za)001:5561: khro ba la slar mi khro ba dang /
NK022(za)001:5562: 'tshang 'bru ba la slar mi 'bru bar spyod dam zhes dris pa'i lan du spyod lags zhu /
NK022(za)001:5563: gnas mal shing drung pa dang /
NK022(za)001:5564: gos phyag dar khrod pa dang /
NK022(za)001:5566: sman rkus te bor ba ni rung ba rnyed kyang sla ba ste /
NK022(za)001:5567: lhag par rnyed pa na khang pa rtsegs pa lnga brgya pa dang /
NK022(za)001:5568: gos tshon sna rgyab pa dang /
NK022(za)001:5569: kha zas ro brgya pa dang /
NK022(za)001:5570: sman rtsa ba la yal 'dab 'bras bu bcas pa yang 'os pa ste /
NK022(za)001:5571: ji ltar bslab pa thob nas dgra bcom pa thob
NK022(za)001:5572: nas lo brgya lon pa des bslab pa de dang
NK022(za)001:5573: khyed kyi bslab pa yang mtshungs pas tshangs pa mtshungs
NK022(za)001:5574: par spyod pa zhes bya ste /
NK022(za)001:5575: de lta bu la khyod slob bam zhes brjod lan slob lags zhu /
NK022(za)001:5576: de nas phyag phul nas bka' drin che'o zhes mkhan po la zhu ba ni /
NK022(za)001:5577: dge bsnyen dge tshul dge slong gang byed kyang /
NK022(za)001:5578: slob dpon des dkon mchog gi gral du khyed tshud pa la dga' ba dang /
NK022(za)001:5579: de mkhan po pa'i bka' drin yin pa la der shes pa'i dge bskul bya'o //
NK022(za)001:5580: grogs kyis kyang de ltar bya'o //
NK022(za)001:5581: ming bla ma slob dpon zer yang rang gis mkhan por bzung /
NK022(za)001:5582: mkhan po yod na gnas kyi bla ma gzhan btsal mi dgos /
NK022(za)001:5583: gzhan du lo lnga dge slong ma brten gyi bar du gnas kyi bla ma dang mi 'bral cing /
NK022(za)001:5584: dge tshul dge bsnyen dang zhag gnyis nyal kyang gsum du sbrel nas lhan du mi nyal /
NK022(za)001:5585: rgan pa la bya ba zhu zhing sangs rgyas dang mkhan po la ming 'bod mi bya /
NK022(za)001:5586: mkhan slob la pha ma dang /
NK022(za)001:5587: rang la bu'i 'du shes bya bar bshad /
NK022(za)001:5588: dge bsnyen gyi skabs ltar skyabs 'gro'i bslab pa bzung ba ni /
NK022(za)001:5592: tshul khrims rjes dran du bzung ba'o //
NK022(za)001:5593: de ltar sdom pa thob pa la rim par tsa
NK022(za)001:5594: ka'i dbang bskur zhing lam khyer ngang bsgom la sogs
NK022(za)001:5595: brjod nas bslab sdom rjes bskyang bar bya'o //
NK022(za)001:5597: mkhan po lung dang man ngag bcas //
NK022(za)001:5598: lhan cig byed pa'i rkyen du 'dod //
NK022(za)001:5600: dge slong gi cho ga slob dpon gyi bya ba kha 'phangs dang bcas pa rdzogs so //
NK022(za)001:5604: da ni rang rgyal bslab sdom tshul //
NK022(za)001:5605: de yang ston pa sangs rgyas gcig /
NK022(za)001:5606: lha mi dang ni nyan thos dang //
NK022(za)001:5607: rang rgyal dang ni byang sems dang //
NK022(za)001:5608: bla na med pa'i theg pa snang //
NK022(za)001:5609: snang yang sangs rgyas thugs mkhyen brtse'i //
NK022(za)001:5610: de bzhin nyid g.yo 'gyur med kyang //
NK022(za)001:5611: gdul bya'i las dang thugs rje 'brel //
NK022(za)001:5613: sems gcig dngas dag kun snang dpe //
NK022(za)001:5614: 'theb tshigs tsam gyi mi gcig gis //
NK022(za)001:5615: lung pa mthong dang me long ni //
NK022(za)001:5616: lag mthil nang du lus rgyan gsal //
NK022(za)001:5617: zla gcig chu mang mthong 'dres ltar //
NK022(za)001:5618: lung spyi rtsa rgyud gsang snying las //
NK022(za)001:5619: de bzhin nyid las ma g.yos kyang //
NK022(za)001:5620: las 'phro'i dbang gis so sor snang //
NK022(za)001:5621: dper na me long chu zla bzhin //
NK022(za)001:5622: de tshe 'gro drug thams cad la //
NK022(za)001:5623: sdig spong gzugs su rnam par bstan //
NK022(za)001:5624: dge tshul rnams la dgra bcom gzugs //
NK022(za)001:5625: rang rgyal rnams la bse ru'i tshul //
NK022(za)001:5626: gzhan yang theg mchog rim pa bzhin //
NK022(za)001:5627: zhes pas lha mi'i theg thub drug /
NK022(za)001:5628: thub re'ang rdul snyed gang 'tshams khyab //
NK022(za)001:5629: kun kyang sdig pa spong gzugs snang //
NK022(za)001:5630: de phyir go mtshon me chu'ang //
NK022(za)001:5631: sdig pa mi dge spong gzugs yin //
NK022(za)001:5632: nyan thos dge ba'i tshul khrims 'dzin //
NK022(za)001:5633: dge bsnyen dge tshul dge slong gis //
NK022(za)001:5634: chos bsdud nyon mongs dgra bcom pa'i //
NK022(za)001:5635: ston pa mkhan slob grogs bcas gzugs //
NK022(za)001:5636: mdo sder ma 'ongs tha ma'i dus //
NK022(za)001:5637: nga nyid mkhan po slob dpon gyi //
NK022(za)001:5639: rang rgyal lus kyi rdzu 'phrul gyis //
NK022(za)001:5640: sems can don byed skye bo yis //
NK022(za)001:5642: ston pa rang rgyal 'bum pas lhag /
NK022(za)001:5643: de la mjal mnyes byed shog smon //
NK022(za)001:5644: ne tso khyu lding bse ru ltar //
NK022(za)001:5645: gcig pa chas tshul ngan bsnyams pas //
NK022(za)001:5647: bse ru ne tso gnyis ka yang //
NK022(za)001:5648: nyan thos sangs rgyas chos dge 'dun //
NK022(za)001:5649: skyabs gsol tshogs lam che 'bring chung //
NK022(za)001:5650: lus tshor sems chos dran nyer bzhag /
NK022(za)001:5652: rkang pa de bzhin sdig spong bshags //
NK022(za)001:5653: dge bskyed dge ba sangs rgyas bsngo //
NK022(za)001:5654: sangs rgyas ma thob bar du ni //
NK022(za)001:5655: rang rgyal thob smon sbyor lam du //
NK022(za)001:5656: drod dang rtse mo bzod pa dang //
NK022(za)001:5657: chos mchog chung 'bring che gsum ste //
NK022(za)001:5658: bcu gnyis tshogs ltar sbyor lam la //
NK022(za)001:5659: dad brtson dran ting shes rab kyi //
NK022(za)001:5660: dbang po lnga dang stobs lnga pos //
NK022(za)001:5661: ma dad le lo brjed ngas dang //
NK022(za)001:5662: rnam g.yeng gti mug bcom pa yi //
NK022(za)001:5663: dge ba'i drod gsum rtags rtse gsum //
NK022(za)001:5664: thob nas stod smad nyon mongs bzod //
NK022(za)001:5666: grogs la skyo bas smon lam du //
NK022(za)001:5668: sangs rgyas rnams kyang mi 'byung zhing //
NK022(za)001:5669: nyan thos rnams kyang med pa na //
NK022(za)001:5670: rang sangs rgyas kyi ye shes ni //
NK022(za)001:5671: rten pa med par rab tu skye //
NK022(za)001:5672: zhes smon de grub rigs mtho ba //
NK022(za)001:5673: rgyal dang bram ze'i rgyud skyes nas //
NK022(za)001:5674: bslab sdom drang srong drung du blangs //
NK022(za)001:5676: bkra shis smon grub spyod lam bslabs //
NK022(za)001:5677: dpag bsam shing drung dben pa skyes //
NK022(za)001:5678: 'bras bu nas bzung rtsa ba'i tshul //
NK022(za)001:5679: bden med bdag med rten 'brel tsam //
NK022(za)001:5680: rtogs grol phyi yi gzugs zhen spangs //
NK022(za)001:5681: dur khrod keng rus mthong ba yis //
NK022(za)001:5682: rga shi nas bzung skye srid mthar //
NK022(za)001:5683: ma rig 'gags snyan rig la ni //
NK022(za)001:5684: skad cig 'gyu mthong de bden zhen //
NK022(za)001:5685: rig pa rkyang 'dod nyams len la //
NK022(za)001:5686: smra bcad 'tsho rkyen bsod snyoms byas //
NK022(za)001:5687: nyan thos gang zag bdag med chos //
NK022(za)001:5688: skad cig sems mthong sangs rgyas kyi //
NK022(za)001:5689: chos sku mthong bas sangs rgyas kyi //
NK022(za)001:5690: gzugs sku lta zhes lung bshad ltar //
NK022(za)001:5691: rang sangs rgyas shis de bde'i rgyus //
NK022(za)001:5693: bde ba mchog de'i sa thob tshe //
NK022(za)001:5694: rang nyid byang chub 'bras bu thob //
NK022(za)001:5695: gzhan dag sdig bzlog rdzu 'phrul ston //
NK022(za)001:5697: gzung don rtog pa spong phyir dang //
NK022(za)001:5698: 'dzin pa mi spong phyir dang ni //
NK022(za)001:5699: rten gyi bse ru lta bu'i lam //
NK022(za)001:5700: zab pa nyid du mngon par brjod //
NK022(za)001:5701: ces gsungs lung las rang rgyal ni //
NK022(za)001:5702: snying rje can 'byung lung bstan ltar //
NK022(za)001:5703: ston pa'i sprul pa de mthong nas //
NK022(za)001:5704: rang rgyal mos 'dun thob mang gyur //
NK022(za)001:5705: de phyir rang rgyal bslab sdom la //
NK022(za)001:5706: rgyu dus nyan thos bslab sdom blang //
NK022(za)001:5707: de thob lha mi'i bslab sdom la //
NK022(za)001:5708: bkra shis smon lam 'gro phan gces //
NK022(za)001:5709: rgyu 'bras gnyis ka'ang tshogs lam gyi //
NK022(za)001:5710: thos bsam lta dus shes dgos bshad //
NK022(za)001:5712: ded dpon rin chen ji bzhin du //
NK022(za)001:5713: gdod mtha'i bye brag 'dir shes dgos //
NK022(za)001:5715: nyan thos bslab len bcas pa'i khrims //
NK022(za)001:5716: shes nas nyams len gnang bkag rgyu'o //
NK022(za)001:5717: lha mi'i bslab len rang bzhin gyi //
NK022(za)001:5718: dge dang mi dge'ang rkyen phan gnod //
NK022(za)001:5719: blang dor shes len 'bras bu'i dape'ang //
NK022(za)001:5720: bsod snyoms mi sbyin sdig pog tshe //
NK022(za)001:5721: dge la khod nges rtsal 'byongs pas //
NK022(za)001:5722: sdig lta gnod sems byed mthong ba'i //
NK022(za)001:5723: mngon shes ltas tshor bsod snyoms byas //
NK022(za)001:5724: mgo bcag ngan sbas kyis bcoms kyang //
NK022(za)001:5725: sdig can de la mi khro bar //
NK022(za)001:5726: snying brtses rdzu 'phrul bstan byas nas //
NK022(za)001:5727: sdig 'gyod sdig grol de mkhyen pas //
NK022(za)001:5728: thugs nas me byung myang 'das kyi //
NK022(za)001:5729: ring bsrel bzhag la mchod smon grub //
NK022(za)001:5730: rang rgyal bsad pa'i sdig can des //
NK022(za)001:5731: rang rgyal rang las lhag pa yi //
NK022(za)001:5732: sangs rgyas bskal mthar mnyes byas nas //
NK022(za)001:5733: dgra bcom longs 'ongs thob ces bshad //
NK022(za)001:5734: de phyir 'bras bu rang byang chub //
NK022(za)001:5735: de yang rang rgyal bslab sdom ni //
NK022(za)001:5736: gnang bkag blang dor shes pa yis //
NK022(za)001:5737: 'gro phan don gnyer rgyu yi dus //
NK022(za)001:5738: rang gzhan phan grub 'bras bu'i dus //
NK022(za)001:5739: thams cad mkhyen pa phyag 'tshal lo //
NK022(za)001:5740: rang rgyal gyi bslab sdom len par 'dod pas /
NK022(za)001:5741: khrus phyag rten mchod bgegs gtor byas nas //
NK022(za)001:5742: bkra shis kyi rdzas 'dzom pa dang /
NK022(za)001:5743: bslab sdom gyi tshig nyan thos kyi dang lha mi'i mgor kha bsgyur shes par bya ste /
NK022(za)001:5745: theg chen ltar du rang gzhan thams cad sangs rgyas byang chub kyi ched du'am /
NK022(za)001:5746: rang gzhung ltar du dmigs gtad kyi rang dang gzhan la phan bde'i don grub pa'i ched du /
NK022(za)001:5747: rang sangs rgyas dang rang byang chub la bslab par mos pa rjes bzlos mdzod cig /
NK022(za)001:5752: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi ba dus 'di nas bzung ste /
NK022(za)001:5754: rkang gnyis rnams kyi mchog ces pa nas nyan thos
NK022(za)001:5755: dge bsnyen dge tshul dge slong gang rung dang gang
NK022(za)001:5756: mos thob nas / lha mi'i sdom bzung dge tshad med bsam brtan bya ste /
NK022(za)001:5758: ston dang bse ru byang chub bar //
NK022(za)001:5759: bsam gtan mtha' rten gcig la kun //
NK022(za)001:5761: bsam gtan bzhi'i ting nge 'dzin la /
NK022(za)001:5765: gcig tu mtshungs par sbyar ro //
NK022(za)001:5766: rjes la bkra shis kyi rdzas dge 'dun gyis spyad par rung ba la rol ba'am /
NK022(za)001:5767: sngon du bkra shis kyi rdzas gang yang rung ba byin gyis brlabs pa la rol nas /
NK022(za)001:5768: rjes bskyang zhing bslab pa thob pa'i dge ba bsngo'o //
NK022(za)001:5769: rang sangs rgyas kyi bslab pa'i cho ga gtan tshigs dang bcas pa /
NK022(za)001:5770: lha mi nyan thos las kha bkang ba'i tshul du cung zad brjod pa'i phyag len rdzogs so //
NK022(za)001:5771: tshul khrims kyi phung po yongs su rdzogs par gyur cig /
NK022(za)001:5776: da ni byang sems theg chen dbang rig gtad //
NK022(za)001:5777: mdo chen lha yi gtso bo 'dam kha gnyis //
NK022(za)001:5778: thub pas gtso mdzad mdo sde spyod dbu ma //
NK022(za)001:5779: thub chen lha las babs pa'i mdzad pa yis //
NK022(za)001:5780: yum lha'i sum cu rtsa gsum skyes don mdzad //
NK022(za)001:5781: yum chen gtso mdzad rnal 'byor spyod dbu ma //
NK022(za)001:5782: thub yum bu mo ri dwags ma der skyes //
NK022(za)001:5783: lus kyi bu gcig sangs rgyas smon grub gsung //
NK022(za)001:5784: sangs rgyas stong rtsa'i yum mchog phar phyin ma //
NK022(za)001:5785: thub chen dka' thub byang chub bar skyabs shing //
NK022(za)001:5786: thub slob rnams kyang srid pa ji srid skyong //
NK022(za)001:5787: des na 'jug sgo lugs gnyis khyad mdzad nas //
NK022(za)001:5788: dbu ma lugs dang sems tsam lugs grags na'ang //
NK022(za)001:5789: mdo dbang lugs la gnyis ka dbu mar mdzad //
NK022(za)001:5790: klu grub g.yu thang kras dgu las kyang bshad //
NK022(za)001:5791: rnal 'byor spyod dbu rnal 'byor spyod khyad bshad //
NK022(za)001:5792: thub pas gtso mdzad dbu ma sems bskyed ltar //
NK022(za)001:5793: bdag bas gzhan gces dmyal gnas skyes la'ang shar //
NK022(za)001:5794: sangs rgyas smon mthong thos dran 'gro drug thub //
NK022(za)001:5795: de phyir sems bskyed nyan thos lha mi'i theg /
NK022(za)001:5796: bslab sdom sngar ma thob la'ang skye zhes gsung //
NK022(za)001:5798: tha dad mi byed smon thob rjes skyong ba //
NK022(za)001:5799: bslab grangs yan lag blo stobs sbyar nas slob //
NK022(za)001:5800: yun chen gtso mdzad smon 'jug gnyis byed ltar //
NK022(za)001:5801: nyan thos lha mi'i sdom ldan rten du byed //
NK022(za)001:5802: de la sems tsam lugs grags mdo dbang ltar //
NK022(za)001:5803: rnal 'byor spyod pa'i dbu ma phyi mo pa'o //
NK022(za)001:5804: lha mis bcas pa'i kha na ma tho dang //
NK022(za)001:5805: rang bzhin kha na ma tho'i dge sdig khyad //
NK022(za)001:5806: ma shes na yang khrims bzang bzung sems dul //
NK022(za)001:5807: tshad med 'tshe gnod phrag dog chags sdang spangs //
NK022(za)001:5808: yid pham sems ngal bso ba'i bsam gtan gyis //
NK022(za)001:5809: dmyal thar lhar skyes dran pa nyer bzhag bshad //
NK022(za)001:5810: nyan thos lha byin rgyal po 'dod dregs shing //
NK022(za)001:5811: thub la dad med brtsod la'ang sdom skyes bshad //
NK022(za)001:5812: rang rgyal slab ni rten 'brel mi shes dang //
NK022(za)001:5813: skyo dad phan sems med la mi skye ba //
NK022(za)001:5814: rten cing 'brel 'byung zab mo'i chos shes shing //
NK022(za)001:5815: rang rgyal gzhan slun 'khrul 'khor la skyo bas //
NK022(za)001:5816: gcig pu byang chub thar pa la dad cing //
NK022(za)001:5817: ltog lta'i sdig lta bsal phyir rdzu 'phrul bsgrub //
NK022(za)001:5818: tshad med byams brtse dga' dang btang snyoms kyi //
NK022(za)001:5819: bsam gtan snyoms 'jug skye sngon sgoms smon grub //
NK022(za)001:5820: da ni byang sems lta ba la //
NK022(za)001:5821: phyi nang phyi pa sems tsam la //
NK022(za)001:5822: dkar dmar rnam bcas rnam bden dang //
NK022(za)001:5823: dkar dmar rnam med rnam rdzun pas //
NK022(za)001:5824: kun rdzob mdo sde sa bcu las //
NK022(za)001:5825: kye kye rgyal ba'i sras dag la //
NK022(za)001:5826: khams gsum po ni sems tsam dang //
NK022(za)001:5827: sems ni stong pa tsam zhes te //
NK022(za)001:5828: don dam rnam shes rang stong la //
NK022(za)001:5829: don dam nang pa'i rnal 'byor spyod //
NK022(za)001:5831: rnam par shes pa don dam 'dod //
NK022(za)001:5832: de yang mkhas rnams mi 'dod de //
NK022(za)001:5833: zhes pas rnam shes ye shes 'byed //
NK022(za)001:5834: gnyis pa gnyis ni dbu ye shes //
NK022(za)001:5835: mdo sde spyod dbu rnal 'byor spyod //
NK022(za)001:5836: dbu ma'i gzhung chen phyi mo pa'o //
NK022(za)001:5837: dang po mdo sde'i dbu don dam //
NK022(za)001:5838: rnam shes mi rtog ye shes ston //
NK022(za)001:5840: rnam par shes pa'i chos nyid 'das //
NK022(za)001:5841: ye shes gnyis med tshul 'chang ba //
NK022(za)001:5843: dbu mar sems bskyed klu sgrub lugs //
NK022(za)001:5844: thub nas 'jam dpal la rgyud gsung //
NK022(za)001:5845: sdom pa nyi shu pa ltar slob //
NK022(za)001:5846: sems bskyed kun rdzob don dam gnyis //
NK022(za)001:5847: don dam blo rab byang chub sems //
NK022(za)001:5849: kun rdzob sgyu ma'i dpe rtogs nas //
NK022(za)001:5850: byang chub ched phyir gang yang spyad //
NK022(za)001:5852: gnyis pa sems tsam lugs grags pa'i //
NK022(za)001:5853: rnal 'byor spyod pa'i dbu sems bskyed //
NK022(za)001:5854: sangs rgyas byams mgon sangs rgyas gsang //
NK022(za)001:5855: zhi ba lha dang jo bo rje //
NK022(za)001:5856: nam mkha' snying po'i mdo sde dang //
NK022(za)001:5857: bslab pa kun las bsdus sogs lugs //
NK022(za)001:5858: de yang yum chen 'bum nyi khri //
NK022(za)001:5859: yum gyi don dam sems skyed smon //
NK022(za)001:5860: 'jug pa phar phyin drug gam bcus //
NK022(za)001:5861: drin lan bsam pas smon 'jug gnyis //
NK022(za)001:5862: yab sras 'jal nas mu stegs kyis //
NK022(za)001:5863: sgrogs tshe kun dga' bos zhus len //
NK022(za)001:5864: kun rdzob sems skyed 'jug pa ni //
NK022(za)001:5865: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas skyabs gsol sbran //
NK022(za)001:5866: nyin mtshan dus gsum mchod bshags bsngo //
NK022(za)001:5867: ltung ba'i lhag ma dpe zhi bya //
NK022(za)001:5870: dngos gzhi dbu ma gso sbyong brgyad //
NK022(za)001:5871: gang nus slob bcug smon 'jug gnyis //
NK022(za)001:5872: sems tsam rnal 'byor spyod dbu ma'o //
NK022(za)001:5873: mdo dbang skabs 'dir mdor bsdus las //
NK022(za)001:5874: rgyas par zhus zhes bka' gnang ltar //
NK022(za)001:5875: dbu ma sems bskyed pa lugs ltar //
NK022(za)001:5876: sangs rgyas thub pa chen po dang //
NK022(za)001:5878: rdo rje brtan pa che ba dang //
NK022(za)001:5879: rdo rje brtan pa chung ba dang //
NK022(za)001:5880: khams pa ba ri lo ts+tsha dang //
NK022(za)001:5881: sa chen kun dga' snying po dang //
NK022(za)001:5882: rje btsun grags pa rgyal mtshan dang //
NK022(za)001:5883: sa skya pan+di ta kun dga' //
NK022(za)001:5884: bla ma 'phags pa blo gros dang //
NK022(za)001:5885: khro phu lo ts+tsha byams pa'i dpal //
NK022(za)001:5886: mkhan chen ka bzhi grags gzhon nu //
NK022(za)001:5887: mkhan chen bsod nams grags chen gyis //
NK022(za)001:5888: bla ma bsam grub rdo rje dang //
NK022(za)001:5890: sangs rgyas don yod grub pa dang //
NK022(za)001:5891: mkhan chen bsod nams byon grags skyobs //
NK022(za)001:5892: da ni sems tsan smon 'jug gnyis //
NK022(za)001:5893: bka' gdams lugs grags mchims la brgyud //
NK022(za)001:5894: sangs rgyas byams pa thogs med dbyig gnyen dang //
NK022(za)001:5895: blo brtan dang ni 'phags pa grol sde dang //
NK022(za)001:5896: btsun pa grol sde mchog sde dul ba'i sde //
NK022(za)001:5897: seng bzang ku su lu gnyis gser gling pa //
NK022(za)001:5898: a ti sha dang 'brom ston spyan mnga' ba //
NK022(za)001:5899: gzhon nu 'od dang char chen dpal ldan gro //
NK022(za)001:5900: sgom seng mchims dang bsod nams ye shes dang //
NK022(za)001:5901: mkhan chen bsod nams grags kyis sh+aakya 'byung ////
NK022(za)001:5904: 'dir slob dpon klu grub kyi bka' srol /
NK022(za)001:5905: theg pa chen po dbu ma'i lugs kyi cho ga bya na /
NK022(za)001:5907: ma blangs pa'i nyes dmigs dang /
NK022(za)001:5909: dang po ni sems bskyed ma thob cing /
NK022(za)001:5910: sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa la ma zhugs na 'khor bar 'khyam /
NK022(za)001:5911: gal te zhugs kyang mya ngan las 'das pa tsam las sangs rgyas mi srid do //
NK022(za)001:5912: gnyis pa ni gnas skabs kyi phan yon /
NK022(za)001:5913: mthong ba'i chos la ming don 'pho zhing byang sems su 'gyur /
NK022(za)001:5915: ngan song 'gogs cing bde 'gro'i mchog thob /
NK022(za)001:5916: mthar thug tu sa pa'i yon tan rnams rims kyis
NK022(za)001:5917: bskyed nas sangs rgyas pa na gzugs kyi sku'i nye
NK022(za)001:5918: len byed pa'o // gang zag bdag dang mtha' yas pa'i sems can thams cad kyis len par bsam /
NK022(za)001:5919: sbyor dngos rjes gsum ka len par sgom pas sems
NK022(za)001:5920: can mtha' yas shing mi zad pa bzhin du bsod
NK022(za)001:5921: nams kyang mtha' yas shing mi zad pa yin no
NK022(za)001:5922: // de ltar shes par byas la /
NK022(za)001:5930: yan lag bdun pa bya ba'o //
NK022(za)001:5931: dang po gnas bzang por dkon mchog gi rten dang mchod pa bsham /
NK022(za)001:5932: gnyis pa dge ba'i bshes gnyen la zhe thag pa nas ston pa sangs rgyas kyi 'du shes bskyed /
NK022(za)001:5934: gus pas phyag byas la man+dala dbul /
NK022(za)001:5935: thal mo sbyar nas 'di skad du /
NK022(za)001:5936: rigs kyi bu bdag la dus gsum gyi de bzhin
NK022(za)001:5937: gshegs pa thams cad kyi bgrod pa gcig pa'i lam
NK022(za)001:5938: / skyabs gsum sngon du 'gro ba can gyi byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed pa bstsal du gsol /
NK022(za)001:5939: zhes lan gsum du gsol ba btab bo //
NK022(za)001:5940: slob dpon gyis nus pa ji ltar bzhin du sbyin zhes khas blang ngo //
NK022(za)001:5941: bzang spyod la sogs pa'i rjes su 'gro bar yan lag bdun pa rgyas par dbul /
NK022(za)001:5942: skyabs 'gro theg chen gyi snying po byang chub la mchis kyi bar du skyabs 'gro rgyas par bya'o //
NK022(za)001:5943: gnyis pa dngos gzhi la gnyis te /
NK022(za)001:5944: thog mar bsam pa sbyang ba dang /
NK022(za)001:5945: bsam pa nges nas dam bca' tshig tu brjod pa'o //
NK022(za)001:5947: lus dang de bzhin longs spyod dang //
NK022(za)001:5948: dus gsum dge ba thams cad kyang //
NK022(za)001:5949: sems can kun gyi don sgrub phyir //
NK022(za)001:5950: phangs pa med par btang bar bya //
NK022(za)001:5951: thams cad btang bas mya ngan 'das //
NK022(za)001:5952: bdag blo mya ngan 'das pa bsgrub //
NK022(za)001:5953: thams cad btang bar chabs gcig la //
NK022(za)001:5954: sems can rnams la btang ba mchog /
NK022(za)001:5956: bdag gi lus longs spyod dge ba'i dngos po dus
NK022(za)001:5957: gsum du bsdus pa nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam pa'i
NK022(za)001:5958: sems can thams cad la thun mong du ltos pa
NK022(za)001:5959: med par sbyin / rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas thob par
NK022(za)001:5960: bya'o bar smon pa rkang gi khong rus pa'i gting
NK022(za)001:5961: med par sbyin / nas sgoms la / de ltar bsam pa nges nas /
NK022(za)001:5962: dam bca' tshig tu brjod pa ni /
NK022(za)001:5963: phyogs bcu na bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad bdag la dgongs su gsol /
NK022(za)001:5964: slob dpon bdag la dgongs su gsol /
NK022(za)001:5965: ji ltar sngon gyi de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bco
NK022(za)001:5966: pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas bcom ldan
NK022(za)001:5967: 'das rnams dang / byang chub sems dpa' chen po de rnams kyis /
NK022(za)001:5968: ji ltar byang chub chen por thugs bskyed pa de bzhin du /
NK022(za)001:5969: bdag gis kyang sems can ma bsgral ba rnams bsgral bar bya ba dang /
NK022(za)001:5970: ma grol ba rnams grol bar bya ba dang /
NK022(za)001:5971: dbugs ma dbyung ba rnams dbugs dbyung ba dang /
NK022(za)001:5972: yongs su mya ngan las ma 'das pa rnams yongs su mya ngan las bzla ba'i phyir /
NK022(za)001:5973: dus 'di nas bzung ste byang chub snying po la mchis kyi bar du /
NK022(za)001:5974: byang chub chen por sems bskyed par bagyi'o //
NK022(za)001:5976: dpon slob gnyis ka'i sems ma yengs par rtse gcig tu bya'o //
NK022(za)001:5977: mjug gi cho ga la gsum ste /
NK022(za)001:5982: deng dus bdag tshe 'bras bu yod //
NK022(za)001:5983: mi yi srid pa legs par thob //
NK022(za)001:5984: de ring sangs rgyas rigs su skyes //
NK022(za)001:5985: sangs rgyas sras su da gyur to //
NK022(za)001:5986: zhes pa brjod du bcug la /
NK022(za)001:5987: byang chub sems dpa' 'am sems mar gyur nas dga' ba sgom /
NK022(za)001:5988: gnyis pa rgyu la gus pa /
NK022(za)001:5989: nag po'i chos bzhi spang ba dang /
NK022(za)001:5990: sems can blos mi spang ba gsum dang /
NK022(za)001:5991: smon pa'i bslab bya bsdus pa /
NK022(za)001:5992: sems can thams cad kyi don du sangs rgyas thob par bya snyam pa'i bsam pa dang /
NK022(za)001:5993: 'jug pa'i bslab bya bsdus pa don med pa'i sdig pa mi byed pa dang /
NK022(za)001:5994: ci nus kyi dge ba bsgrub pa zhes brjod /
NK022(za)001:5995: gsum pa ni don chen po 'grub pa yin pas /
NK022(za)001:5996: lo gdan g.yul ngo legs pa tsam la lha mchod pa yod na /
NK022(za)001:5997: 'dir 'khor ba'i g.yul ngo bzlog rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas
NK022(za)001:5998: kyi rgyal tshab thob pa yin pas gtang rag ci
NK022(za)001:5999: mi bya ste / dkon mchog la mchod pa /
NK022(za)001:6003: 'khor gsum yongs su dag pa'i bsngo bas rgyas gdab /
NK022(za)001:6004: +thii zur gyi chos rje byams pa seng ges /
NK022(za)001:6005: mdo dbang cha lag tu sems bskyed bsdus pa bris pas phan thogs par shog ///
NK022(za)001:6006: byang sems kyi gso sbyong ni /
NK022(za)001:6007: bla ma dang sangs rgyas dang chos dang dge 'dun la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK022(za)001:6009: ji ltar gyi de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas /
NK022(za)001:6011: glang po chen po bya ba shes shing byed pa byas pa /
NK022(za)001:6013: bdag gi don rjes su thob pa /
NK022(za)001:6014: srid pa kun tu sbyor ba /
NK022(za)001:6017: legs par rnam par grol ba'i thugs /
NK022(za)001:6018: legs par rnam par grol ba'i shes rab can de dag gis /
NK022(za)001:6019: sems can thams cad kyi don gyi phyir dang /
NK022(za)001:6020: phan par bya ba'i phyir dang /
NK022(za)001:6021: grol bar bya ba'i phyir dang /
NK022(za)001:6022: nad med par bya ba'i phyir dang /
NK022(za)001:6023: mu ge med par bya ba'i phyir dang /
NK022(za)001:6024: byang chub kyi phyogs kyi chos rnams yongs su rdzogs par bya ba'i phyir dang /
NK022(za)001:6025: bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub rtogs pa bya ba'i phyir dang /
NK022(za)001:6026: gso sbyong nges par mdzad pa de bzhin du /
NK022(za)001:6027: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi bas kyang /
NK022(za)001:6030: nyi ma ma shar gyi bar du /
NK022(za)001:6031: theg pa chen po gso sbyong gi sdom pa nges par yang dag par blang bar bagyi'o //
NK022(za)001:6032: deng nas srog gcod mi bya zhing //
NK022(za)001:6033: gzhan gyi nor yang blang mi bya //
NK022(za)001:6034: 'khrig pa'i chos kyang mi spyad cing //
NK022(za)001:6035: rdzun gyi tshig kyang mi smra'o //
NK022(za)001:6036: skyon ni mang po nyer bsten pas //
NK022(za)001:6037: chang ni yongs su spang bar bya //
NK022(za)001:6038: khrii stan che mtho mi bya zhing //
NK022(za)001:6039: de bzhin dus ma yin pa'i zas //
NK022(za)001:6040: dri dang phreng ba dang ni rgyan //
NK022(za)001:6041: gar dang glu sogs spang bar bya //
NK022(za)001:6042: ji ltar dgra bcom rtag tu ni //
NK022(za)001:6043: srog gcod la sogs mi byed pa //
NK022(za)001:6044: de ltar srog gcod la sogs spang //
NK022(za)001:6045: bla med byang chub myur thob shog /
NK022(za)001:6047: srid pa'i mtsho las 'gro ba sgrol bar shog /
NK022(za)001:6048: byang chub sems dpa'i gso sbyong rang gis blang ba'i cho ga /
NK022(za)001:6049: mdo las byung ba rdzogs so //
NK022(za)001:6050: tshul khrims rnam par dag par brtan pa'i sngags ni /
NK022(za)001:6051: a mo g+ha shi la sa b+ha ra sa b+ha ra /
NK022(za)001:6052: b+ha ra b+ha ra ma h+aa shu d+ha swa h+aa /
NK022(za)001:6053: pad+ma b+hi bu shud+ha b+hu tsa /
NK022(za)001:6054: d+ha ra d+ha ra sa man+ta a ba lo ki te h'u phata s+w+aa h+aa /
NK022(za)001:6055: zhes dang lha snyen bzlas so ////
NK022(za)001:6056: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK022(za)001:6057: sems tsam rnal 'byor spyod pa'i dbu ma la /
NK022(za)001:6058: mdo dbang lugs kyi smon pa dang 'jug pa byang
NK022(za)001:6059: chub tu sems bskyed par bya ba'i cho ga chen
NK022(za)001:6060: po ni / sngon du so sor thar pa'ii sdom pa la gnas pa des /
NK022(za)001:6062: sems can thams cad la byams pa dang snying rje byang chub kyi sems sgom ste /
NK022(za)001:6063: rgyu mtshan gyi sgo nas zhib tu phye la /
NK022(za)001:6064: thabs sna tshogs kyis sems can la snying rje ci skye bya /
NK022(za)001:6065: skyes pa dang sems skyed dngos gzhi la /
NK022(za)001:6066: sngon du sku gsung thugs kyi rten bkram /
NK022(za)001:6068: mchod pa ci rigs par dbul /
NK022(za)001:6069: de nas sems khyad par can skye bar byed pa la gags sgrib pa yin te /
NK022(za)001:6070: tshe rabs thog ma med pa nas las kyi sgrib pa thams cad dang /
NK022(za)001:6071: tshe 'dir yang sdig pa ci bgyis pa thams cad dang /
NK022(za)001:6072: snying rje med cing theg pa chen po la mi mos pa'i sems bskyed pa'i gags dang /
NK022(za)001:6073: sgrib pa thams cad stobs bzhi'i sgo nas bshags te /
NK022(za)001:6075: nyes pa las slar bzlog pa'i stobs dang /
NK022(za)001:6079: sngar gyi sgrib pa thams cad blos blangs nas 'gyod pa dang bcas nas bshags so //
NK022(za)001:6080: nyes pa las slar bzlog pa ni /
NK022(za)001:6081: da phyin chad srog la bab kyang mi byed par khas len cing sdom pa'o //
NK022(za)001:6083: sku gsung thugs kyi rten bzhugs pa rnams dang /
NK022(za)001:6084: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' mkhyen pa'i ye
NK022(za)001:6085: shes brtse ba'i thugs rje dang ldan pa thams cad
NK022(za)001:6086: dang / chos skyong ba'i srungs ma ye shes kyi spyan dang ldan pa thams cad dang /
NK022(za)001:6087: bka' brgyud kyi bla ma rig pa 'dzin pa thams cad dang /
NK022(za)001:6088: rang gi bla ma bzhugs pa'i spyan sngar bshags pa byed pa'o //
NK022(za)001:6089: kye sangs rgyas drung du dpang po gsol bas 'dod don smin che 'phel che'o //
NK022(za)001:6090: chos smra chos ldan chos rten drung na chos bsrung yod pas dpang gsol gnyan /
NK022(za)001:6091: snyigs dus dge 'dun lnga'am bcu drug 'phags 'dra dpang gsol pham lhag dag /
NK022(za)001:6092: spang ltung rdzas spang dgos na'ang zhen bral dge slong cig drung bshags sdig dag /
NK022(za)001:6093: bslab bya nyes sdig rang sems dpang btsugs phyis sdom sngar 'gyod skyon shes dag /
NK022(za)001:6094: sems bskyed spyi ched dor ba'i rang 'dod sems bskyed bskyar blang nyams bshags dag /
NK022(za)001:6095: dpang por dkon mchog rgyal dang rgyal sras bla ma dam pa dgos sngags 'dra'o //
NK022(za)001:6096: rang sems bla ma dkon mchog shes smin ngo 'phrod rang dpangs klong grol brkyang /
NK022(za)001:6097: gnyen po'i stobs ni cho ga gzhung ltar byed pa yin te /
NK022(za)001:6098: gong gi rten gyi stobs kyi sangs rgyas la sogs
NK022(za)001:6099: pa de dag dpang po'i tshul du bzhugs par bsams
NK022(za)001:6100: la / tshe thog ma med pa nas las kyi
