NK022(za)001:6101: sgrib pa byang chub tu sems bskyed pa'i gags dang
NK022(za)001:6102: sgrib pa thams cad blos ril gyis blangs la bshags
NK022(za)001:6103: la / pa bya ste / phyogs bcu dang dus
NK022(za)001:6104: gsum na bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems
NK022(za)001:6105: dpa' thams cad bdag la dgongs su gsol lo //
NK022(za)001:6106: bka' rgyud kyi bla ma yang dag pa'i dge ba'i bshes gnyen thams cad bdag la dgongs su gsol /
NK022(za)001:6108: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi ba tshe rabs thog ma
NK022(za)001:6109: med pa'i dus nas da ltar skye ba 'di la
NK022(za)001:6111: lus ngag yid gsum gyi sgo nas mi dge ba bcu dang /
NK022(za)001:6116: kha na ma tho ba la sogs pa sdig pa
NK022(za)001:6117: mi dge ba'i phyogs nag po'i las ci bgyis pa
NK022(za)001:6118: dang / gzhan bgyid du bcug pa dang /
NK022(za)001:6119: bgyid pa la legs par brjod pa la sogs pa nag po'i las bsags /
NK022(za)001:6120: 'khor ba ngan song gi rgyur gyur pa dang /
NK022(za)001:6121: thams cad mkhyen pa'i gags su gyur pa thams cad /
NK022(za)001:6122: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad dang /
NK022(za)001:6123: yid dam gyi lha tshogs dang /
NK022(za)001:6124: mkha' 'gro chos skyong ba ye shes kyi spyan dang ldan pa thams cad dang /
NK022(za)001:6125: bka' brgyud kyi bla ma yang dag pa'i dge ba'i bshes gnyen pa thams cad dang /
NK022(za)001:6126: slob dpon gyi spyan sngar mthol lo bshags so //
NK022(za)001:6129: phyin chad kyang sdom par bgyid do //
NK022(za)001:6130: sdig sgrib thams cad byang zhing dag par gyur cig /
NK022(za)001:6132: des tshe thog ma med pa nas las kyi sdig
NK022(za)001:6133: sgrib thams cad sangs te 'dag la dag par yang
NK022(za)001:6134: bsam mo // de nas sems skye ba la tshogs rdzogs dgos pa yin te /
NK022(za)001:6135: dag pa gsum dang ldan pas tshogs rdzogs shing bsod nams bsag dgos /
NK022(za)001:6136: de'ang dag pa gsum ni las rnam par dag pa dang /
NK022(za)001:6137: smon lam rnam par dag pa dang /
NK022(za)001:6138: bsam pa rnam par dag pa'o //
NK022(za)001:6139: dang po las rnam par ma dag pa ni /
NK022(za)001:6140: mi lus gtsang ma mi thob /
NK022(za)001:6141: thob kyang dbang po sgo lnga mi tshang /
NK022(za)001:6142: tshang yang dam pa'i chos yod par mi skye /
NK022(za)001:6143: skyes kyang chos bya ba'i bsam pa mi skye ba yin pa la /
NK022(za)001:6144: las rnam par dag pas mi lus gtsang ma ni thob /
NK022(za)001:6146: dam pa'i chos yod par skyes nas da lta chos la 'jug pa yin la /
NK022(za)001:6147: gnyis pa smon lam ma dag na /
NK022(za)001:6148: theg pa chen po'i chos ston pa'i dge ba'i bshes gnyen bla ma dang mi 'phrad /
NK022(za)001:6150: mos kyang chos la mi tshud cing mi 'dzom pa la /
NK022(za)001:6151: smon lam rnam par dag pas bla ma dang mjal /
NK022(za)001:6152: mos shing dad nas da lta bar gang gis kyang ma chod par chos la 'jug /
NK022(za)001:6153: theg pa chen por sems bskyed cing dbang la 'jug pa ni smon lam rnam par dag pa'o //
NK022(za)001:6154: gsum pa bsam pa rnam par ma dag pa ni /
NK022(za)001:6157: grogs kyi zla la legs dang /
NK022(za)001:6158: skabs kyi 'jug kyang bla ma la sogs log lta skye ba yin la /
NK022(za)001:6159: da lta bsam pa rnam par dag pas /
NK022(za)001:6161: grogs kyi zla legs ma yin te /
NK022(za)001:6162: dad pa brten pos byang chub kho na don du gnyer zhing the tshom yid gnyis med pas /
NK022(za)001:6163: dam pa'i chos la thag chod pas log lta med par bla ma dang /
NK022(za)001:6164: theg pa chen po'i chos la dga' zhing mos pas
NK022(za)001:6165: 'jug pa ni bsam pa rnam par dag cing bsod
NK022(za)001:6166: nams bsags pa'o // de ltar dag pa gsum dang ldan pas /
NK022(za)001:6167: tshe thog ma med pa nas da lta yan chod dkar po dge ba'i phyogs bgyis pa dang /
NK022(za)001:6169: gzhan bgyid pa la rjes su yi rang ba la sogs pa'i dge ba thams cad dang /
NK022(za)001:6170: de ring dkon mchog la mchod pa 'bul ba dang /
NK022(za)001:6171: slob dpon mnyes par byas pa dang /
NK022(za)001:6172: dag pa gsum gyi sgo nas sems bskyed pa la
NK022(za)001:6173: sogs pa'i dge ba thams cad blos ril blangs nas
NK022(za)001:6174: / sems can thams cad kyi don du rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas thob par bsngo ste /
NK022(za)001:6175: phyogs bcu dang dus gsum na bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas
NK022(za)001:6176: dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad bdag la dgongs
NK022(za)001:6177: su gsol / bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi bas tshe thog ma med pa'i dus nas /
NK022(za)001:6178: da lta skye ba 'di la thug pa yan chod du /
NK022(za)001:6179: lus ngag yid gsum gyi sgo nas dge ba bcu dang /
NK022(za)001:6180: pha rol du phyin pa drug dang /
NK022(za)001:6182: bsdu ba'i dngos po bzhi la sogs pa /
NK022(za)001:6183: byang chub kyi phyogs dang mthun pa'i dge ba'i rtsa ba bgyis pa dang /
NK022(za)001:6185: gzhan bgyid pa la rjes su yi rang ba la
NK022(za)001:6186: sogs pa'i 'dus byas dang 'dus ma byas kyi dge
NK022(za)001:6187: ba'i rtsa ba thams cad dang /
NK022(za)001:6188: de ring dkon mchog la mchod pa phul ba dang /
NK022(za)001:6189: da lta dag pa gsum gyi sgo nas byang chub
NK022(za)001:6190: tu sems bskyed pa la sogs pa'i dge ba'i rtsa
NK022(za)001:6191: ba 'di dag thams cad gcig tu bsdus shing bsdom
NK022(za)001:6192: ste / sems can thams cad kyi don du bdag
NK022(za)001:6193: bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang
NK022(za)001:6194: chub tu mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas par gyur
NK022(za)001:6195: ste / cig / ces lan gsum du bya'o //
NK022(za)001:6196: de nas sems bskyed pa la /
NK022(za)001:6197: sngon du rgyu gsum 'dzom dgos pa yin te /
NK022(za)001:6199: snying rje byang chub kyi sems dang ldan pa dang /
NK022(za)001:6200: theg pa chen po'i chos bdag med gnyis la sogs mos pa'o //
NK022(za)001:6201: dang po ni dag pa gsum gyi sgo nas bsod nams bsags shing /
NK022(za)001:6204: sngon du byams pa dang snying rje sgom zhing 'gro ba'i don du dmigs pa'o //
NK022(za)001:6205: gsum pa ni theg pa chen po'i chos stong zhing bdag med pa dang /
NK022(za)001:6206: 'gro ba'i don gyi phyir thams cad mkhyen pa'i sangs rgyas thob par 'dod pa'o //
NK022(za)001:6207: de dang ldan pas sems bskyed pa ni /
NK022(za)001:6208: dang po la dkon mchog gsum dang /
NK022(za)001:6209: slob dpon la phyag 'tshal du bcug la /
NK022(za)001:6210: bsam pa ni ji ltar mngon du gshegs shing bzhugs
NK022(za)001:6211: pa'i sangs rgyas byang chub sems dpa' thams cad kyis
NK022(za)001:6212: / snying rje chen pos sems can gyi don du byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed de /
NK022(za)001:6213: bla na med pa'i byang chub thob pa bzhin du /
NK022(za)001:6214: bdag kyang sems bskyed par bya'o snyam du bsams la /
NK022(za)001:6215: phyogs bcu dang dus gsum na bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas
NK022(za)001:6216: dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad bdag la dgongs
NK022(za)001:6217: su gsol / bka' brgyud kyi bla ma yang dag
NK022(za)001:6218: pa'i dge ba'i bshes gnyen thams cad bdag la dgongs
NK022(za)001:6219: su gsol / su gsol / slob dpon bdag la dgongs su gsol //
NK022(za)001:6220: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi ba dus 'di nas bzung ste /
NK022(za)001:6221: ji srid snying po byang chub la mchis kyi bar du /
NK022(za)001:6223: phyogs bcu na bzhugs pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa dgra
NK022(za)001:6224: bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rnams
NK022(za)001:6226: zhi ba 'dod chags dang bral ba rnams kyi mchog /
NK022(za)001:6227: phyogs bcu na bzhugs pa'i dam pa'i chos theg pa
NK022(za)001:6228: chen po bsam gyis mi khyab pa rnams la skyabs
NK022(za)001:6229: su mchi'o // tshogs bsags pa rnams kyi mchog /
NK022(za)001:6230: phyogs bcu na bzhugs pa'i 'phags pa'i dge 'dun phyir
NK022(za)001:6231: mi ldog pa'i byang chub sems dpa' rnams la skyabs
NK022(za)001:6232: su mchi'o // ji ltar sngon du gshegs shing bzhugs
NK022(za)001:6233: pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag
NK022(za)001:6234: par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams dang
NK022(za)001:6235: su mchi'o // / sa chen po la gnas pa'i
NK022(za)001:6236: byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' cha na po rnams
NK022(za)001:6237: kyis dang po byang chub kyi mchog tu sems bskyed
NK022(za)001:6238: su mchi'o // / de / sems can thams cad
NK022(za)001:6239: kyi don du bla na med pa yang dag par
NK022(za)001:6240: rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu sangs rgyas pa de bzhin
NK022(za)001:6241: su mchi'o // / de / du / bdag kyang sems bskyed do //
NK022(za)001:6242: ji srid snying po byang chub la mchis kyi bar du /
NK022(za)001:6243: nag po mi dge ba'i chos thams cad spangs nas /
NK022(za)001:6244: bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang
NK022(za)001:6245: chub tu sangs rgyas par bya snyam du bsam la
NK022(za)001:6247: ji ltar mngon du gshegs shing bzhugs pa'i de bzhin
NK022(za)001:6248: gshegs pa'i dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i
NK022(za)001:6249: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams dang /
NK022(za)001:6250: sa chen po la gnas pa'i byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyis /
NK022(za)001:6251: thugs dang po byang chub kyi mchog tu sems bskyed de /
NK022(za)001:6254: de dang nye ba lnga dang /
NK022(za)001:6257: kha na ma tho ba gsum la sogs pa nag po mi dge ba'i phyogs rnams spangs te /
NK022(za)001:6258: sems can thams cad kyi don du /
NK022(za)001:6259: bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang
NK022(za)001:6260: chub tu mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas pa de
NK022(za)001:6261: bzhin du / bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi ba yang dus 'di nas bzung nas /
NK022(za)001:6262: ji srid snying po byang chub la mchis kyi bar du /
NK022(za)001:6263: sems can thams cad kyi don du sems bskyed de /
NK022(za)001:6266: de dang nye ba lnga dang /
NK022(za)001:6269: kha na ma tho ba la sogs pa sdig pa mi dge ba'i phyogs rnams spangs te /
NK022(za)001:6270: sems can thams cad kyi don du bla na med
NK022(za)001:6271: pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub mngon par
NK022(za)001:6272: rdzogs par sangs rgyas pa bgyid do //
NK022(za)001:6273: ji ltar sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad kyi bslab pa la rjes su slob bo //
NK022(za)001:6276: gnyis pa dge ba chos bsdud kyi tshul khrims ni /
NK022(za)001:6277: ji ltar mngon du gshegs pa'i sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyis /
NK022(za)001:6278: sems can gyi don du byang chub du sems bskyed
NK022(za)001:6279: de dkar po dge ba'i phyogs rnams yongs su rdzogs
NK022(za)001:6280: par byas nas / bla na med pa yang dag
NK022(za)001:6281: par rdzogs pa'i byang chub thob pa bzhin du bdag
NK022(za)001:6283: snying po byang chub la mchis kyi bar du dkar
NK022(za)001:6284: po dge ba'i phyogs rnams yongs su rdzogs par byas
NK022(za)001:6285: te / bla na med pa'i byang chub thob par bya snyam du bsams la /
NK022(za)001:6287: ji ltar mngon du gshegs shing bzhugs pa'i de bzhin
NK022(za)001:6288: gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i
NK022(za)001:6289: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams dang /
NK022(za)001:6290: sa chen po la rab tu gnas pa'i byang chub
NK022(za)001:6291: sems dpa' chen po rnams kyis sems can thams cad
NK022(za)001:6292: kyi don du / dang po byang chub mchog tu thugs bskyed de /
NK022(za)001:6294: pha rol du phyin pa drug la sogs pa byang
NK022(za)001:6295: chub kyi phyogs dang mthun pa'i dkar po'i chos rnams
NK022(za)001:6296: yongs su rdzogs par byas te /
NK022(za)001:6297: sems can thams cad kyi don du bla na med
NK022(za)001:6298: pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu mngon
NK022(za)001:6299: par rdzogs par sangs rgyas pa de bzhin du /
NK022(za)001:6300: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi bas kyang /
NK022(za)001:6301: dus 'di nas bzung nas ji srid snying po byang chub la mchis kyi bar du /
NK022(za)001:6302: sems can thams cad kyi don du sems bskyed de /
NK022(za)001:6303: dge ba bcu dang pha rol du phyin pa drug la sogs pa /
NK022(za)001:6304: byang chub kyi phyogs dang mthun pa'i dge ba'i phyogs rnams yongs su rdzogs par byas te /
NK022(za)001:6305: sems can thams cad kyi don du bla na med
NK022(za)001:6306: pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu mngon
NK022(za)001:6307: par rdzogs par sangs rgyas pa bgyid do //
NK022(za)001:6308: ji ltar sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad kyi bslab pa la rjes su slob bo //
NK022(za)001:6312: gsum pa sems can don byed ni /
NK022(za)001:6314: smon pa ni gzhan don dngos su sgrub par mi nus pa rnams la /
NK022(za)001:6315: smon pas 'jug cing sems bskyed pa'o //
NK022(za)001:6316: 'jug pa ni gzhan don bsgrub par nus tshad /
NK022(za)001:6317: bdag bas gzhan gces par 'dzin pa la sogs dngos su 'jug cing sems bskyed pa'o //
NK022(za)001:6318: de la 'dir sems kyi don bsgrub par nus tshad la dngos su 'jug cing /
NK022(za)001:6319: mi nus pa mgo dang rkang lag gtong ba la sogs pa la smon pas 'jug pa'o //
NK022(za)001:6320: de la smon 'jug gnyis kyi cho ga bsam pas phye la dus gcig tu bya ste /
NK022(za)001:6321: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad kyis dang po byang chub mchog tu thugs bskyed de /
NK022(za)001:6322: snying rje chen pos sems can gyi don du bsdu ba'i dngos po bzhi dang /
NK022(za)001:6323: lus longs spyod la sogs pa btang ste bla na med pa'i sangs rgyas thob pa bzhin du /
NK022(za)001:6324: bdag gis kyang sems bskyed do snyam du bsam la /
NK022(za)001:6326: ji ltar mngon du gshegs shing bzhugs pa'i de bzhin
NK022(za)001:6327: gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i
NK022(za)001:6328: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams dang /
NK022(za)001:6329: sa chen po la gnas pa'i byang chub sems dpa'
NK022(za)001:6330: chen po rnams kyis sems can thams cad kyi don
NK022(za)001:6331: du / dang po byang chub mchog tu thugs bskyed nas /
NK022(za)001:6333: bsdu ba'i dngos po bzhi la sogs pa lus dang
NK022(za)001:6334: ngag dang yid dang longs spyod thams cad btang ste
NK022(za)001:6335: / sems can thams cad kyi don yongs su rdzogs par byas nas /
NK022(za)001:6336: bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang
NK022(za)001:6337: chub tu mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas pa de
NK022(za)001:6338: bzhin du / bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi bas kyang dus 'di nas bzung ste /
NK022(za)001:6339: ji srid snying po byang chub la mchis kyi bar
NK022(za)001:6340: du sems can thams cad kyi don du sems bskyed
NK022(za)001:6341: de / tshad med pa bzhi dang /
NK022(za)001:6342: bsdu ba'i dngos po bzhi la sogs pa lus dang
NK022(za)001:6343: ngag dang yid dang longs spyod thams cad gtong ste
NK022(za)001:6344: / sems can thams cad kyi don yongs su rdzogs par byas nas /
NK022(za)001:6345: bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang
NK022(za)001:6346: chub tu mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas pa bgyid
NK022(za)001:6347: do // ji ltar sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems
NK022(za)001:6348: dpa' thams cad kyi bslab pa la rjes su slob
NK022(za)001:6349: do // bo // rjes su bsgrub bo //
NK022(za)001:6351: sems can ma grol ba thams cad bdag gis grol bar bagyi'o //
NK022(za)001:6352: ma bsgral ba rnams bdag gis bsgral bar bya'o //
NK022(za)001:6353: dbugs ma dbyung ba rnams bdag gis dbugs dbyung bar bya'o //
NK022(za)001:6354: sems can mya ngan las ma 'das pa thams cad bdag gis mya ngan las 'das par bagyi'o //
NK022(za)001:6356: de nas phyag byas la bka' drin che'o zha sa bya'o //
NK022(za)001:6357: de rnams kyi don bshad la ma nyams par bsrung ngo //
NK022(za)001:6358: byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed pa'i cho ga rdzogs so //
NK022(za)001:6362: da ni 'bras bu gsang sngags phyi nang gnyis //
NK022(za)001:6363: phyi la bya rgyud spyod rgyud rnal 'byor rgyud //
NK022(za)001:6364: mtshan nyid rgyu'i theg pas bden pa gnyis //
NK022(za)001:6365: skyed rims rdzogs rims gnyis su smin cing grol //
NK022(za)001:6366: sangs rgyas gsung gcig nyid du gsungs na yang //
NK022(za)001:6367: rang re'i skad dang theg pa rang sar thos //
NK022(za)001:6368: gang de mthar phyin gcig des grol ba dang //
NK022(za)001:6369: kun la rims dang cig char slabs grol ba'o //
NK022(za)001:6370: rgyus grol 'bras bus sangs rgyas sku gsung thugs //
NK022(za)001:6371: de mthus skye 'gro kun gyi lus ngag yid //
NK022(za)001:6372: dag pa'i 'khor rnams rigs kyis bdag dang mjal //
NK022(za)001:6373: mkhyen brtse thabs mkhas mthur ldan chos 'khor skor //
NK022(za)001:6374: rigs kyi gtsor smin 'jam dpal thugs rje che //
NK022(za)001:6375: phyag na rdo rjes bka' rnams bsdus pa'i mthus //
NK022(za)001:6376: thub byon nyan thos shes rab rdzu 'phrul dang //
NK022(za)001:6377: rgyal ba'i rim 'gro thos pa 'dzin pa'i mchog /
NK022(za)001:6378: nyan rang du mas phyogs gcig mtshon mthus snang //
NK022(za)001:6379: sha ri mo'u 'gal bu dang kun dga' snang //
NK022(za)001:6380: rgyal tshab 'od srung nye ba 'khor kun dgas //
NK022(za)001:6381: mngon pa 'dul ba mdo sde'i bka' bsdus snang //
NK022(za)001:6382: de tshe rgyal ba sras 'khor kun dbyer med //
NK022(za)001:6383: khams gsum mgon po rig gsum tri ya na //
NK022(za)001:6384: sku'ang sku gsung thugs phyir gsung dang thugs //
NK022(za)001:6385: gcig kyang mkhyen brtse mthu 'phrul sku gsung thugs //
NK022(za)001:6386: mtshan dang dpe byad tshangs dbyangs ye shes rnams //
NK022(za)001:6387: skye 'gros thob grol phyir du lus ngag yid //
NK022(za)001:6388: zhen bral mtshon phyir grangs gsum rigs gsum la //
NK022(za)001:6389: mos blos lha sku yig gsung thugs mtshan snang //
NK022(za)001:6390: rigs gsum gcig kyang gsum ste dkyil 'khor dgu //
NK022(za)001:6391: 'jam dpal sku dang thugs rje'i gsung dang gsang bdag thugs //
NK022(za)001:6392: 'jam sku gsang bdag gsung sku thugs rje'i thugs //
NK022(za)001:6393: de bzhin thugs rje'i sku dang gsang bdag sku'o //
NK022(za)001:6394: dam ldan bdag nyid dam tshig sems dpa' las //
NK022(za)001:6395: don dam sems nyid ka nas dag pa'i dngos //
NK022(za)001:6396: ye shes lha yi ngo bor ye nas bzhugs //
NK022(za)001:6397: lha mchog ye shes sems dpa' mthun mtho bar //
NK022(za)001:6398: kun rdzob rje dang 'bangs kyi tshul mos dran //
NK022(za)001:6399: de lta'i blos bskyed ye shes gshegs dam bsdud //
NK022(za)001:6400: ka dag chos dbyings rdzogs rims klong du grol //
NK022(za)001:6401: mchod na bsod nams smad na sdig phyir bshags //
NK022(za)001:6402: da ni u pa ya ste lung thob byed //
NK022(za)001:6403: khrus zas byed gtsang bya ba'i rgyud sde las //
NK022(za)001:6404: mi 'gal na'ang gtsang sbra bral spyod brgyud //
NK022(za)001:6405: kun rdzob 'gal 'dra'ang don mthun lung bzhin spyod //
NK022(za)001:6406: tri ya rigs gsum mgon las u pa ya //
NK022(za)001:6407: rigs bzhis khyad mdzad bya spyod gnyis ka brgyud //
NK022(za)001:6408: rigs gsum bum chu bdud rtsir zhu ba na //
NK022(za)001:6409: lha'am yig 'abru'am thugs mtshan gang yin kyang //
NK022(za)001:6410: bar chad gnod pa srid phyir de srung pa //
NK022(za)001:6411: rigs kyi khro bo las byed srungs mar bsgo //
NK022(za)001:6412: lha yig thugs mtshan de la bar chod med //
NK022(za)001:6413: zhu nas bsrung ba'ang khams gsum rnam par rgyal //
NK022(za)001:6414: las bum chu yis gsang sbyang ma byas nas //
NK022(za)001:6415: mchod rdzas brlabs kyang log 'dren gyis rme nyams //
NK022(za)001:6416: phur bus btab kyang log 'dren kyis 'byin pas //
NK022(za)001:6417: bgegs bskrad lha bskyed gces mdzad lha de yang /
NK022(za)001:6418: badz+ra kro ta tree lo kya bi dza ya h'u phata /
NK022(za)001:6419: pad zlar mthing nas phyag gnyis phur pa 'dril //
NK022(za)001:6420: las bum dkyil 'khor bum gdan phur bu'ang 'god /
NK022(za)001:6421: kri u sbrel la gnyis ka rgyud ltar du //
NK022(za)001:6422: sku gsung thugs lha las kyi lha dang bzhi'o //
NK022(za)001:6423: u pa yo ga sbrel bas gnyis rgyud ltar //
NK022(za)001:6424: bdag lus dam tshig sems gsal de yi thugs //
NK022(za)001:6425: ye shes sems gsal mdun nam snying dkyil du //
NK022(za)001:6426: bar ni 'phro 'dus ting 'dzin sems dpa' gsal //
NK022(za)001:6427: kun 'dus rdo rje sems dpa' srid gsum gcig /
NK022(za)001:6428: sems dpa' 'ang mo bzhi zhes u par mdzad //
NK022(za)001:6429: de rnams mthar phyin zhi rgyas dbang drag bzhi'i //
NK022(za)001:6430: phrin las 'grub phyir dpral mgrin snying khar ni //
NK022(za)001:6431: sku gsung thugs ni byin rlabs cho 'phrul dang //
NK022(za)001:6432: ye shes cho 'phrul thugs nang ye shes lha //
NK022(za)001:6433: sku 'am yi ge'am mtshan ma'i gzugs bkod pas //
NK022(za)001:6434: rdo rje bzhi na lha gcig la 'ang bkod //
NK022(za)001:6435: ye shes las ni spyi bor dbang bskur rtags //
NK022(za)001:6436: gtsug brgyan dbang bskur mdzad thob cho 'phrul dang //
NK022(za)001:6437: thugs las mchod byung mchod pa'i cho 'phrul te //
NK022(za)001:6438: ting 'dzin cho 'phrul bzhi yang gnyis ka rgyud //
NK022(za)001:6440: mi g.yo sems dpa' mngon sum du //
NK022(za)001:6441: rigs bzhi rdo rje 'chang gnas pa'o //
NK022(za)001:6442: zhes la rigs lnga'i snang mdzad ni //
NK022(za)001:6443: mi 'bral spyi khyab bzhi zhes gsung //
NK022(za)001:6445: rnam snang mdzad kyi ye shes ni //
NK022(za)001:6446: sangs rgyas kun gyi thugs la gsal //
NK022(za)001:6447: sangs rgyas kun gyi ye shes ni //
NK022(za)001:6448: rnam snang mdzad kyi thugs la gsal //
NK022(za)001:6450: phyag na rdo rje ri rab rtse mo'i rgyud //
NK022(za)001:6451: 'di la sha khrag tsog sgog skya //
NK022(za)001:6452: chang sogs ma bkag byang chub thob spyod brgyud //
NK022(za)001:6453: rnam par snang mdzad mngon par byang chub brgyud //
NK022(za)001:6454: rnam snang thig le dbang yang spyod rgyud gsung //
NK022(za)001:6455: sku gsung thugs dang ldan pa dang //
NK022(za)001:6457: dbu rgyan rigs lnga dkyil 'khor le tshe dgu //
NK022(za)001:6458: rnam snang la sogs rigs lnga 'khor bcas bkod //
NK022(za)001:6459: mkhas grub bi ma u pa'i khrid byang las //
NK022(za)001:6460: lha dang bdag nyid dpon g.yog ltar //
NK022(za)001:6461: lus ngag yid gsum phyag rgya sgom //
NK022(za)001:6463: gu ru pad+mas sku gsum dbye ba las //
NK022(za)001:6464: rig pa snang mdzad chos sku'o mi bskyod pa //
NK022(za)001:6465: snying po byang chub ngang na bzhugs pa'i sku'o //
NK022(za)001:6466: rin 'byung yon tan snang mtha' longs spyod sku //
NK022(za)001:6467: don grub sprul sku'o sku bzhi rigs lnga bkod //
NK022(za)001:6468: chab gtor sman la phye khrog bya ba ltar //
NK022(za)001:6469: gtsang sbra mdzad cing sman sdus bum snod dril //
NK022(za)001:6470: spyod pa'i rgyud ltar byin rlabs sha chang gnang //
NK022(za)001:6471: rnal 'byor yo ga ting 'dzin rtsal 'byor pas //
NK022(za)001:6472: stug po bkod par bdag sems dkyil 'khor shar //
NK022(za)001:6473: mdo dbang lugs la brten bsham mchod nyan thos //
NK022(za)001:6474: rten la spyan drangs mchod pa theg pa che //
NK022(za)001:6475: bdag bskyed mdun skyed mchod pa'i bya ba dang //
NK022(za)001:6476: mdun skyed rgyas pa bdag bskyed dbang bdag 'jug /
NK022(za)001:6477: sku yi phyag rgya chen bskyed gsung yig 'bru //
NK022(za)001:6478: chos kyi phyag rgya'o thugs mtshan phyag rgya bca' //
NK022(za)001:6479: dam tshig phyag rgya'o 'phro dus las kyi rgyas //
NK022(za)001:6480: 'phags mchod 'gro don 'grub byed phyag rgya bzhi'o //
NK022(za)001:6481: bram ze gtsang ltar phyi mchod rnam bdun dang //
NK022(za)001:6482: rgyal po ltar du rgyal srid 'byor rgyas mchod //
NK022(za)001:6483: theg pa'i gong 'og khyad par che bshad kyang //
NK022(za)001:6484: gcig la kun tshang zin so yod shes bya //
NK022(za)001:6485: gsang sngags lha yi thugs dang mdzod spu dang //
NK022(za)001:6486: mchon rten bre gdong gnas nas 'od 'gyed pa'ang //
NK022(za)001:6487: nyan thos thub pa'i sku'i 'od zer ni //
NK022(za)001:6488: mi rtog ngang las mju mdzad kun khyab 'od //
NK022(za)001:6489: slar log gnas thim rgyal bas lung ston tshe //
NK022(za)001:6490: 'das pa lung ston gnam logs 'phongs rgyab logs //
NK022(za)001:6491: ma 'ongs gsang mdun du 'o dmyal zhabs 'thil //
NK022(za)001:6492: dud 'gro zhabs kyi rting pa'o yi dwags la //
NK022(za)001:6493: zhabs kyi mthe bong du 'o mi zhabs sus //
NK022(za)001:6494: stobs kyi 'khor lo bsgyur ba phyag g.yon du'o //
NK022(za)001:6495: stong khams 'khor lo bsgyur ba phyag g.yas pa //
NK022(za)001:6496: nyan thos zhal du'o rang rgyal mdzod spu 'o //
NK022(za)001:6497: sangs rgyas lung ston gtsug tu 'od thim zhes //
NK022(za)001:6498: 'dul ba lung du bshad pa'i sangs rgyas dang //
NK022(za)001:6499: theg chen mdor bshad sangs rgyas stong gsum ni //
NK022(za)001:6500: gang ga'i klung gi bye snyed 'dul sangs rgyas //
NK022(za)001:6501: sngags kyi yi dam sangs rgyas sngags chos dang //
NK022(za)001:6502: rig 'dzin dge 'dun skyabs kyi khyad par mdzad //
NK022(za)001:6503: sngags ni lam myur 'bras bu thob nye 'dod //
NK022(za)001:6504: dus tshod gza' skar tshes 'bum bye 'gyur khyad //
NK022(za)001:6505: bya bas lta ba spyod pas rgod dges 'dzum //
NK022(za)001:6506: rnal 'byor lag 'khyud sngags lha yum bcas bskyed //
NK022(za)001:6508: pad+ma'i steng du rgyal byang sems //
NK022(za)001:6509: lha 'god rgyu mtshan gang yin gsung //
NK022(za)001:6511: skye 'gro las kyi pad stong du //
NK022(za)001:6512: sbal pas rtsed mo bung ba ni //
NK022(za)001:6513: me tog 'jib pa mtshar chen min //
NK022(za)001:6514: smon lam dge mthus rkang rjes pa //
NK022(za)001:6515: lha klus mchod nas skye re mtshar //
NK022(za)001:6516: khrims ldan gtso la dgung zhag tu //
NK022(za)001:6517: nyal yang rtsa sbubs mi nyams mtshar //
NK022(za)001:6518: phyir mi ldog pa'i 'phags par bshad //
NK022(za)001:6519: sangs rgyas thub pa'i rdzu 'phrul gyis //
NK022(za)001:6522: dug can zas kyang dug med mdzad //
NK022(za)001:6523: byang sems 'od zer chen po'i dbang //
NK022(za)001:6525: de bzhin gshegs pa snying po'i mdor //
NK022(za)001:6527: rang bzhugs du ma nam mkha' gang //
NK022(za)001:6528: ci yi rtags zhus sems can la //
NK022(za)001:6529: sangs rgyas dngos bzhugs rtags zhes gsungs //
NK022(za)001:6530: phyi ni pad shun sgribs na 'ang //
NK022(za)001:6531: nang na sangs rgyas 'bru spun bzhin //
NK022(za)001:6532: 'gro la sangs rgyas bzhugs zhes bshad //
NK022(za)001:6534: 'dam gyi dri ngan skyon med ltar //
NK022(za)001:6535: sngags 'chang dug lnga spyod snang yang //
NK022(za)001:6536: skyon bral yon tan mchog tu 'phags //
NK022(za)001:6537: rdzogs chen sems nyid rang snang la //
NK022(za)001:6538: mi srid nam mkhar pad+mo srid //
NK022(za)001:6539: de la rgyal bzhugs chos thos srid //
NK022(za)001:6540: sngags nang rtsa pad kha bye mchod //
NK022(za)001:6542: mngon byang lnga dang cho 'phrul bzhi //
NK022(za)001:6543: yan lag drug ldan stug po bkod //
NK022(za)001:6544: ces pa rin chen gter gtad bshad //
NK022(za)001:6545: chos nyid stong pa gdan zla ba //
NK022(za)001:6546: yig 'bru gsung thugs phyag mtshan dang //
NK022(za)001:6547: sku ni yongs rdzogs mngon byang chub //
NK022(za)001:6548: las lha de lnga'i steng du ni //
NK022(za)001:6549: spyi bo'i h'u las mchod don bsdu //
NK022(za)001:6550: stong pa'i yan lag zla nyi yi //
NK022(za)001:6551: yan lag gsung yig thugs phyag mtshan //
NK022(za)001:6552: sku ni yongs rdzogs yan lag dang //
NK022(za)001:6553: byin gyis brlabs pa'i yan lag drug /
NK022(za)001:6554: phyi rgyud mtshams sbyor i th+ai //
NK022(za)001:6557: // // bcom ldan 'das rdo rje 'dzin la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK022(za)001:6558: gsang sngags phyi'i sgor 'jug cing dbang bskur ba ni /
NK022(za)001:6561: yo ga las dang po bya spyod gnyis las /
NK022(za)001:6562: dang po kri ya'i sgor 'jug ste /
NK022(za)001:6563: sngon du gnas khang phyag bdar legs par byas la /
NK022(za)001:6564: dkyil 'khor ci rigs su bzhengs la /
NK022(za)001:6565: sku gsung thugs kyi rten tshang ba bkram /
NK022(za)001:6566: gtor ma dkar gsum snum khur la sogs pas brgyan pa bsham /
NK022(za)001:6567: rin po che'i snod du dri bzang po'i chus bkang ba bsham /
NK022(za)001:6568: gzhan yang mchod pa 'byor tshad bshams la /
NK022(za)001:6569: phyi gtor 'byung po thams cad pa dang /
NK022(za)001:6570: nye reg 'thor 'thung kri ya'i lugs phyag 'tshal mchod pa rnams ci rigs su dbul lo //
NK022(za)001:6571: de nas bu sems bskyed cing byang chub sems dpa'i don la gnas pa de la /
NK022(za)001:6572: dang po slob dpon gyis gsang sngags kyi yon tan bshad de /
NK022(za)001:6573: don dbyings la ye shes khyad dang /
NK022(za)001:6574: lam byang chub gzhan nas mi tshol ba dang /
NK022(za)001:6575: don nyid rtogs par byed pa'i thabs khyad par can mang du bshad la /
NK022(za)001:6576: des bu 'og ma la skyo ba skyes shing /
NK022(za)001:6577: gsang sngags la brod pa dang spro ba skyes pa dang /
NK022(za)001:6578: bu gsang sngags kyi snod du rung bar bya ba'i phyir /
NK022(za)001:6579: gang dang sgrib pa thams cad bshags te /
NK022(za)001:6580: tshe thog ma med pa nas bsags pa'i gsang sngags
NK022(za)001:6581: kyi snod du mi rung ba'i gags dang sgrib pa
NK022(za)001:6583: stobs bzhi'i sgo nas bshags pa bya ste /
NK022(za)001:6584: de'ang spyir sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad dang /
NK022(za)001:6586: dkar po chos skyong ba'i srungs ma ye shes kyi
NK022(za)001:6587: spyan dang ldan pa rnams sprin gtibs pa bzhin du
NK022(za)001:6589: khyad par du dkon mchog gsum gyi bdag nyid slob dpon gyi spyan sngar bshags te /
NK022(za)001:6590: phyogs bcu dus gsum na bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad dang /
NK022(za)001:6591: slob dpon bdag la dgongs su gsol //
NK022(za)001:6592: bdag ni tshe rabs thog med nas //
NK022(za)001:6593: da lta'i dus 'di yan chod du //
NK022(za)001:6594: ma rig nyon mongs dbang gis na //
NK022(za)001:6595: mi dge sdig pa'i las byas dang //
NK022(za)001:6596: log lta the tshom phyogs ris kyis //
NK022(za)001:6597: theg mchog gsang ba'i snod mi rung //
NK022(za)001:6598: gags dang sgrib pa ci mchis pa //
NK022(za)001:6599: thams cad ma lus bshags par bgyi //
NK022(za)001:6600: zhes lan gsum gyis sdig sgrib thams cad sangs dag par bsam mo //
NK022(za)001:6601: de nas gsang sngags kyi dbang don khyad par can rgyud la skye ba la /
NK022(za)001:6602: tshogs rdzogs dgos pa yin te /
NK022(za)001:6603: tshogs bsags pas chos byed cing gsang sngags la 'jug pa yin pa'i rgyu mtshan bshad la /
NK022(za)001:6604: tshe thog ma med pa nas kyi dge ba'i las 'dus byas dang 'dus ma byas kyi dang /
NK022(za)001:6605: bsod nams dang ye shes kyi tshogs bgyis pa dang /
NK022(za)001:6607: gzhan bgyid pa la rjes su yi rangs ba la sogs thams cad blos ril gyis blangs la /
NK022(za)001:6608: sems can thams cad kyi don du rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi don du sngo ste /
NK022(za)001:6610: bdag gis tshe rabs thog med nas //
NK022(za)001:6611: da lta'i dus 'di yan chod du //
NK022(za)001:6612: dkar po dge ba'i bsam pa yis //
NK022(za)001:6613: dge bcu la sogs byang chub phyogs //
NK022(za)001:6614: bgyid dang rjes su yi rangs pa'i //
NK022(za)001:6615: bsod nams dang ni ye shes tshogs //
NK022(za)001:6616: ma lus gcig tu bsdus byas nas //
NK022(za)001:6617: 'gro don byang chub mthar phyin shog /
NK022(za)001:6619: de nas dbang gi dam tshig zhu ste /
NK022(za)001:6622: lus ngag yid gsum dang 'byor pa'i sgo nas slob dpon mnyes par byas la /
NK022(za)001:6623: slob dpon la bdag gsang sngags kyi dbang gi dam
NK022(za)001:6624: tshig zhu bas sbyin du gsol snyam du bsams la
NK022(za)001:6625: / rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas thams cad kyis //
NK022(za)001:6626: sku gsung thugs kyi gsang ba'i bdag /
NK022(za)001:6627: rdo rje 'dzin pa'i ngo bo nyid //
NK022(za)001:6628: mgon po bdag la dgongs su gsol //
NK022(za)001:6629: bdag ni thugs rjes 'brel ba yis //
NK022(za)001:6630: sangs rgyas bstan pa'i rim zhugs te //
NK022(za)001:6631: byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed kyang //
NK022(za)001:6632: theg mchog gsang ba'i don ma rtogs //
NK022(za)001:6633: de ring gsang ba'i theg pa la //
NK022(za)001:6634: dga' ba lhag pa'i bsam pa yis //
NK022(za)001:6636: brtse ba'i thugs rjes dgongs mdzod la //
NK022(za)001:6637: gsang ba'i dam tshig dbang bskur don //
NK022(za)001:6638: mgon pos bdag la sbyin du gsol //
NK022(za)001:6640: slob dpon gyis gnang ba sbyin pa /
NK022(za)001:6641: bu khyod dad gus shes rab dang //
NK022(za)001:6642: dga' ba lhag pa'i bsam pa yis //
NK022(za)001:6643: theg mchog gsang ba 'jug nges na //
NK022(za)001:6644: gsang sngags 'jug sgo dam tshig dbang //
NK022(za)001:6645: ci rigs par ni sbyin par bya //
NK022(za)001:6646: nan tan gyis ni bslang bar gyis //
NK022(za)001:6648: de nas gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa la sems bskyed pa /
NK022(za)001:6649: ji ltar dus gsum du bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas rnams kyis /
NK022(za)001:6650: gsang sngags rdo rje'i theg par sems bskyed do //
NK022(za)001:6651: bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang
NK022(za)001:6652: chub tu mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas pa de
NK022(za)001:6653: bzhin du / bdag gis kyang sems bskyed par bya'o snyam du bsams la /
NK022(za)001:6655: ji ltar dus gsum mgon po rnams //
NK022(za)001:6656: rdo rje theg par sems bskyed de //
NK022(za)001:6657: dbang bskur dam tshig gzhung sgrubs nas //
NK022(za)001:6658: rdzogs pa'i byang chub mchog thob ltar //
NK022(za)001:6659: bdag kyang sems can don slad phyir //
NK022(za)001:6660: rdo rje theg par sems bskyed de //
NK022(za)001:6661: dbang bskur dam tshig gzhung sgrubs nas //
NK022(za)001:6662: rdzogs pa'i byang chub mchog thob bya'o //
NK022(za)001:6664: sems bskyed pa'i ming bshad do //
NK022(za)001:6665: de nas gsang sngags kyi sgor 'jug cing dam tshig dbog ste /
NK022(za)001:6668: sems can thams cad kyi don yongs su rdzogs par bya /
NK022(za)001:6669: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas myur du thob par bya ba'i
NK022(za)001:6670: phyir bdag sngags kyi sgor 'jug cing dam tshig nos
NK022(za)001:6672: bsgrub snyam du bsam la rdzogs pa'i dgongs su gsol ba 'gre /
NK022(za)001:6673: bla na med pa'i mchog gsum la //
NK022(za)001:6674: deng nas bdag ni skyabs su mchi //
NK022(za)001:6675: bdag ni sangs rgyas bstan pa'i gzhung //
NK022(za)001:6676: spyi dang mi 'gal legs gnas te //
NK022(za)001:6677: theg chen gsang sngags bya ba'i gzhung //
NK022(za)001:6678: khyad par dam tshig dbang gis blang //
NK022(za)001:6679: yang dag nyid du bzung bar bgyi //
NK022(za)001:6680: theg chen gsang ba sngags kyi lha //
NK022(za)001:6681: don gcig gnyis med ye shes don //
NK022(za)001:6682: yang dag nyid du bdag gis bzung //
NK022(za)001:6683: sku yi rigs mchog chen po ni //
NK022(za)001:6684: dam tshig sdom pa la gnas te //
NK022(za)001:6685: bsgrub pa dag kyang ci nus brtsam //
NK022(za)001:6686: pad+ma'i rigs mchog dag pa yi //
NK022(za)001:6687: phyi nang gsang ba'i gsung bsgrags te //
NK022(za)001:6688: dam pa'i chos kyang ma lus bzung //
NK022(za)001:6689: rdo rje rigs mchog dam tshig ni //
NK022(za)001:6690: rdo rje dril bu'i phyag rgya yang //
NK022(za)001:6691: bla ma rdo rje rigs rten bya //
NK022(za)001:6692: mtha' yas sems can don phyir du //
NK022(za)001:6693: gsang sngags dam tshig bdag gis blang //
NK022(za)001:6694: yang dag nyid du bzung bar bya //
NK022(za)001:6695: bla med byang chub mchog sgrub bya'o //
NK022(za)001:6697: byang chub sems don dam kun rdzob gnyis la gnas par bya ba dang /
NK022(za)001:6698: rang bzhin dang bcas pa'i kha na ma tho ba las ldog pa ni spyi'i dam tshig tu'o //
NK022(za)001:6699: khyad par du bcu gsum ste /
NK022(za)001:6700: dkon mchog gsum la dad pa dang /
NK022(za)001:6701: yi dam lha la mos pa dang /
NK022(za)001:6702: bla ma la gus pa dang /
NK022(za)001:6704: nang rme dang rdzas rme mi gtsang dang spyod 'chal rme rtsog spang pa dang /
NK022(za)001:6705: ye shes can rje ltar mchod pa dang /
NK022(za)001:6706: sdig pa can gyi gzhung mi ston pa dang /
NK022(za)001:6707: log par lta ba spang ba dang /
NK022(za)001:6708: snying rje'i thag pa mi gcad pa dang /
NK022(za)001:6709: stong pa nyid kyis sbyang ba la sogs pa brtags
NK022(za)001:6710: pa drug gam bya ba drug la gnas pa dang
NK022(za)001:6711: / gtsor sngags la brtson 'grus bya ba dang /
NK022(za)001:6712: dam med rnams spang ba dang /
NK022(za)001:6713: bka'i don rtogs par brtag pa'o //
NK022(za)001:6714: lhag pa'i dam tshig gsum ste /
NK022(za)001:6715: bla ma rdor dril bsten pa thugs kyi rigs /
NK022(za)001:6716: rgyud mdo sgrag pa gsung gi rigs /
NK022(za)001:6717: dkon mchog gsum mchod pa sku'i rigs so //
NK022(za)001:6721: sku gsung thugs su shes pa'o //
NK022(za)001:6722: zhes dri zhim po'i chus khrus bya'o //
NK022(za)001:6723: mdo'i bkra shis nyer drug dang lha dbang bum dbang bskur nas gtor mchod cha tso dang /
NK022(za)001:6725: gdams skyed rims rdzogs rims la dbang bskur ro //
NK022(za)001:6726: de nas dbang bskur ba la gnyis te /
NK022(za)001:6728: chos dbang sems la bskur ba'o //
NK022(za)001:6729: dang po ni slob dpon kun bzang du gsal ba'i gnas gsum du rigs gsum bskyed la /
NK022(za)001:6730: rigs gsum gyi thugs kha nas 'od 'phros pas bu'i
NK022(za)001:6731: lus ngag yid gsum gyi rgyud sbyangs te bu'i sems
NK022(za)001:6732: stong gsal nam mkha' lta bur dag pa stong pa
NK022(za)001:6733: de las cha sa thams cad gdod ma nas dag
NK022(za)001:6735: dri ma med pa'i sgra byung /
NK022(za)001:6736: der sems stong gsal nam mkha' lta bu'i dkyil 'khor du zla ba'i dkyil 'khor bsam /
NK022(za)001:6737: de'i steng du gsum gyi sa bon /
NK022(za)001:6738: h+r+aihmh'u bsam ste yongs su gyur pa las /
NK022(za)001:6739: ral gri pad+ma rdo rje bsam /
NK022(za)001:6744: zhes pas rigs gsum mgon po sku yongs su rdzogs pa /
NK022(za)001:6745: rgyan dang cha lugs dang bcas pa bskyed /
NK022(za)001:6747: bu'i rigs gsum gyi thugs kha nas 'od 'phros pas
NK022(za)001:6748: 'og min gyi rigs gsum gyi thugs dam gyi rgyud
NK022(za)001:6749: bskul / thugs rje dang dam tshig gis byon nas
NK022(za)001:6750: bu'i lus ngag yid gsum byin gyis brlabs pa las
NK022(za)001:6751: bskul / / yid kyis mos pa bya /
NK022(za)001:6753: de nas bu'i lus ngag yid gsum yi dam lha'i sku gsung thugs su ngo sprad la /
NK022(za)001:6754: snying po brgya rtsa la sogs ci rigs par bzlas su gzhug go //
NK022(za)001:6755: bu'i lus ngag yid gsum la sogs pa /
NK022(za)001:6756: yi dam lha'i sku gsung thugs su ngo sprod la /
NK022(za)001:6757: snying po brgya rtsa la sogs pa ci rigs par bzlas su gzhug go //
NK022(za)001:6758: bu'i lus ngag yid gsum la sogs pa rigs gsum sku gsung thugs las mi 'da' bar gdams so //
NK022(za)001:6760: chos dbang sems la bskur ba ni /
NK022(za)001:6762: gnad kyis brdas la 'gro 'phrang bcad pas ngo sprad la dbang bskur ba zhal las shes par bya'o //
NK022(za)001:6763: dbang thob nas gzhung bzhin dam tshig srung zhing nyams su blang bar bya'o //
NK022(za)001:6764: kri ya'i dbang dang dam tshig dbog pa'i cho ga rdzogs so //
NK022(za)001:6766: // phyag 'tshal mchod pa rgyas 'bring gang 'byor dbul /
NK022(za)001:6767: sdig pa bshags pa la sogs pa bzang spyod kyang rung ngo //
NK022(za)001:6768: de nas gnas pa'i don byin brlabs zhu ste phyag byas la /
NK022(za)001:6769: bla ma dkon mchog gsum po dang /
NK022(za)001:6770: bcom ldan rigs bsdus dgongs su gsol /
NK022(za)001:6771: 'gro ba rnams kyi don slad du //
NK022(za)001:6772: bdag la dgongs shing gzigs su gsol //
NK022(za)001:6773: zhes brjod pas bdag gnang ba gong dang mthun /
NK022(za)001:6774: khrus dang gos gtsang ma skon srung skud sogs sta gon tshar ba nas phyag dang man+dala dbul /
NK022(za)001:6775: bla ma la gsol ba gdab ste /
NK022(za)001:6776: snyim par me tog thogs la /
NK022(za)001:6777: bla ma rdo rje 'dzin pa khyed gtso 'khor dang bcas pa dgongs su gsol /
NK022(za)001:6778: mi shes mun pas sgribs pa la //
NK022(za)001:6779: yi dam drag pa rtsal du gsol //
NK022(za)001:6782: yi dam gsang ba bstan par bya //
NK022(za)001:6783: khyod kyis las 'di bsgrub par gyis //
NK022(za)001:6784: nyes pa dag gis ma gos na //
NK022(za)001:6785: 'bras bu dam pa myur bar thob //
NK022(za)001:6786: lam mchog bsgrub par dka' ba ste //
NK022(za)001:6787: dam tshig 'das na dmyal bar ltung //
NK022(za)001:6793: zhes gyis mchod rdzas su brlab /
NK022(za)001:6796: sku gsung thugs gang dang por dmigs pa'i don nges pas ming btags lha ngo bstan te /
NK022(za)001:6797: snying po phyag mtshan rang pa'am /
NK022(za)001:6798: spyir rdo rje dril bu sbyin /
NK022(za)001:6799: sku spyan ras gzigs dang dbu la spyan ras gzigs dkar po dang /
NK022(za)001:6800: gsung mgrin 'jam dpal dmar po dang /
NK022(za)001:6801: thugs khar phyag rdor bkod pa dang /
NK022(za)001:6803: gsung thugs rje dmar sogs skabs sbyar /
NK022(za)001:6806: thugs rdo rje sogs ming btags /
NK022(za)001:6807: spyod pa'i brgyud rdo rje rtse mo rigs bsdus las /
NK022(za)001:6808: lus kyi las ni rnam gsum dang //
NK022(za)001:6809: ngag gi rnam pa bzhi dag dang //
NK022(za)001:6810: yid kyi rnam pa gsum dag dang //
NK022(za)001:6811: ci rigs par ni bsrung bar bya //
NK022(za)001:6812: zhes gsungs pa ni u pa ya'i theg pa'i dam tshig kri ya ba dang mthun pa'o //
NK022(za)001:6813: khyad par ye shes sems dpa' snying nang rigs bdag gtsug rgyan bya'o //
NK022(za)001:6815: kri ya tshangs pa spyi brgyud kyi dam tshig bcu gsum pa 'di yang mdzad /
NK022(za)001:6816: de ring phan chad khyed rnams kyis //
NK022(za)001:6817: sangs rgyas chos dang dge 'dun dang //
NK022(za)001:6818: rigs sngags gzungs sngags tshogs rnams la //
NK022(za)001:6819: dad pa rab tu brtan par bya //
NK022(za)001:6820: rtag par phyag rgya chen po la //
NK022(za)001:6821: khyad par du ni mos par bya //
NK022(za)001:6822: dam tshig can dang mdza' bo bya //
NK022(za)001:6823: bla ma la yang gus par bya //
NK022(za)001:6824: lha rnams kun la sdang mi bya //
NK022(za)001:6825: dus mtshams rtag tu mchod par bya //
NK022(za)001:6826: ston pa gzhan gyi gzhung mi mchod //
NK022(za)001:6827: rtag tu glo bur mchod mgron bya //
NK022(za)001:6828: srog chags rnams la byams pa'i sems //
NK022(za)001:6829: rab tu brtan pas nye bar bzhag /
NK022(za)001:6830: theg pa la ni dga' rnams kyi //
NK022(za)001:6831: bsod nams bsags la nan tan bya //
NK022(za)001:6832: bzlas brjod byed la 'bad par bya //
NK022(za)001:6833: gsang sngags rgyud la brten pa yi //
NK022(za)001:6834: dam tshig rnams kyang bsrung bar bya //
NK022(za)001:6835: dam tshig med pa rnams la ni //
NK022(za)001:6836: sngags dang phyag rgya sbyin mi bya //
NK022(za)001:6837: gsang sngags brgyud ni legs bsrung zhing //
NK022(za)001:6838: de yang bdag gis rtogs par bya //
NK022(za)001:6840: yang dbus pa blo bsal nas /
NK022(za)001:6841: sngags pas ston pa gzhan la phyag mi byed pa de mi thub ste /
NK022(za)001:6843: dbang po rdo rje 'chang la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK022(za)001:6845: gsungs pa ni ston pa sangs rgyas las gzhan du mos pas btsal ba ma yin no //
NK022(za)001:6846: ston pa'i bka' 'khor na gnas pas /
NK022(za)001:6847: phyogs skyong pa la yid rang bas brtsal te /
NK022(za)001:6848: gzhan du mi dge tshar gcod pa na phur pas btab bo //
NK022(za)001:6850: yo ga'i slob ma dkyil 'khor du bzhugs shing dbang bskur bar bya ste /
NK022(za)001:6851: dang por slob ma dkyil 'khor gyi drung du bkug la /
NK022(za)001:6852: bgegs bskrad kyis dri chabs kyis bsang /
NK022(za)001:6853: de nas byang chub kyi sems bskyed pa dang /
NK022(za)001:6854: sdom bzung pa gzhan dang mthun par bya /
NK022(za)001:6855: de nas ngan song gsum gyi sdig pa gzhom pa /
NK022(za)001:6856: da ha da ha sarba na ra ga te he tu h'u phata /
NK022(za)001:6857: pa tsa pa tsa sarba pre ta ga te he tu h'u phata /
NK022(za)001:6858: ma tha ma tha sarba tir ya ga te he tu h'u phata /
NK022(za)001:6859: a pa me tri pa me ma h+aa sa ma ye h'u /
NK022(za)001:6860: zhes pas dam tshig can du byin gyis brlabs /
NK022(za)001:6861: de nas slob dpon gyis sgo dbye ba /
NK022(za)001:6862: gnas rab sgo bzhi zhe sdang dang /
NK022(za)001:6866: sngon med dus nas bcad lags pas //
NK022(za)001:6867: tshad med bsdus brgyad rigs bzhi yis //
NK022(za)001:6868: thugs rje thabs mkhas sprul pa yi //
NK022(za)001:6869: lcags kyu zhags pa lcags sgrog dang //
NK022(za)001:6870: dril bu'i phyag rgya mchog nyid dang //
NK022(za)001:6871: de nyid thar sgo dbye ru gsol //
NK022(za)001:6872: badz+ra rat+na pad+ma karma pra be sha phata /
NK022(za)001:6874: shar phyogs mngon dag'i pho brang du //
NK022(za)001:6875: bcom ldan rdo rje sems la sogs //
NK022(za)001:6876: skal ldan rgyal sras dag pa bzhin //
NK022(za)001:6877: ngag yid dngas bas gus phyag 'tshal //
NK022(za)001:6878: lho phyogs dpal gyi zhing khams 'dir //
NK022(za)001:6879: bcom ldan rin chen 'byung la sogs //
NK022(za)001:6881: nub bde ldan byang rnam dag bcom ldan snying po pho brang 'dir //
NK022(za)001:6882: bcom ldan rnam par snang mdzad la //
NK022(za)001:6883: skal ldan rgyal sras dag pa bzhin //
NK022(za)001:6884: ngag yid dngas bas gus phyag 'tshal //
NK022(za)001:6885: de nas dkyil 'khor du 'jug par gsol ba btab cing lan gsol /
NK022(za)001:6886: shar phyogs mngon dag'i pho brang nas //
NK022(za)001:6887: rdo rje rigs su sems bskyed nas //
NK022(za)001:6888: thugs kyi dngos grub thob bya'i phyir //
NK022(za)001:6889: bdag gis dad pas 'jug par bgyi //
NK022(za)001:6890: sems can rnams kyi don gyi phyir //
NK022(za)001:6891: byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed nas //
NK022(za)001:6893: sems can don la khyod la gnang //
NK022(za)001:6895: bcom ldan snying po'i pho brang du //
NK022(za)001:6897: sku yi pi ti thob bya'i phyir //
NK022(za)001:6899: de nas slob ma'i gdong g.yogs sdig pa gzhom pa dang /
NK022(za)001:6900: dam tshig can du byed pa yang 'dir /
NK022(za)001:6902: badz+ra a ti tish+ta badz+ra sa ma ya stom /
NK022(za)001:6903: zhes pas slob ma rdo rje las su sgom /
NK022(za)001:6904: de nas sku gsung thugs su byin gyis brlabs te /
NK022(za)001:6905: de la skur brlab pa ni /
NK022(za)001:6906: rdo rje sdams pa las gung mo gnyis rdo rje 'dra bar snyam /
NK022(za)001:6907: mthe bong dang mthe chung so sor brkyang la /
NK022(za)001:6909: bri ta n+ri h+aa sarba a pa ra ni ni h'u phata /
NK022(za)001:6911: gong ma de nyid las mthe chung gnyis bzhibs la sbyar /
NK022(za)001:6912: gung mo dang srin lag pad+ma 'dra bar bkug la lkog mar gtad do //
NK022(za)001:6913: tra tha tra tha sarba a pa ra ni h'u phata /
NK022(za)001:6915: rdo rje bcings pa las gung mo bzhibs la /
NK022(za)001:6916: snying khar gtad la de b+hi tra b+hi tra sarba a par na h'u phata /
NK022(za)001:6918: zhes pas rdo rje 'dzin ma'i phyag rgyas bcings te me tog 'dzin du bzhug /
NK022(za)001:6919: de nas slob mas brjod pa /
NK022(za)001:6920: sngon gyi tshe rabs grangs med nas //
NK022(za)001:6921: dge ba'i las kyis bsnyen pa'i lha //
NK022(za)001:6922: lhag pa'i lha ni gang yin pa //
NK022(za)001:6924: sangs rgyas dngos grub thob bya'i phyir //
NK022(za)001:6925: bdag la thugs rjes dgongs nas kyang //
NK022(za)001:6926: 'gro la phan pa'i gtso chen gyis //
NK022(za)001:6927: smon par dgongs nas bzhes su gsol //
NK022(za)001:6928: badz+ra pra ti g+h+ri na h'u /
NK022(za)001:6929: pra ti sa ma ya stom /
NK022(za)001:6931: de nas slob dpon gyis brjod pa /
NK022(za)001:6932: me tog rin chen la sogs pa //
NK022(za)001:6933: gang la bab pa rigs kyi lha //
NK022(za)001:6934: gtso bo rigs kyi bsgrubs nas ni //
NK022(za)001:6935: dngos grub myur du the tshom med //
NK022(za)001:6936: ces brjod nas lcags kyu'i phyag rgyas me tog phreng ba blangs la /
NK022(za)001:6937: slob ma'i spyi bor bzhag la /
NK022(za)001:6938: badz+ra sa ma ya hri da ya me a be sha ya /
NK022(za)001:6940: gang la bab pa'i lha dang mi gnyis par bsam mo //
NK022(za)001:6941: gdong g.yogs bkrol ba dang slob mas brjod pa /
NK022(za)001:6942: shin tu ma rig rmongs pa yis //
NK022(za)001:6943: bdag ni rmongs par gyur pa dang //
NK022(za)001:6944: de bzhin gshegs pa'i thugs rje yis //
NK022(za)001:6945: bdag gi mig 'di dbye ru gsol //
NK022(za)001:6946: rdo rje sems dpa' bdag nyid de //
NK022(za)001:6947: khyod kyi mig ni rab 'bar yin //
NK022(za)001:6948: thams cad rdo rje 'bar ba'i mig /
NK022(za)001:6949: thams cad khyod kyis mthong bar 'gyur //
NK022(za)001:6950: badz+ra ud ga te tha ya h'u /
NK022(za)001:6954: da ni dad pa rab tu bskyed //
NK022(za)001:6955: sangs rgyas rigs kyi gdung du 'khrungs //
NK022(za)001:6956: bsten na dngos grub thams cad ni //
NK022(za)001:6957: khyod la mngon du phyogs 'gyur gyis //
NK022(za)001:6958: si ti phyir ni man tra skyong //
NK022(za)001:6960: zhes brjod cing dkyil 'khor gyi ngo bstan bgyi /
NK022(za)001:6961: gang la bab pa'i don khyad par du bshad /
NK022(za)001:6962: gong du ma bshad na man ngag gi gleng gzhi dang phan yon 'dir bshad /
NK022(za)001:6963: de nas dam tshig dbogs te /
NK022(za)001:6964: ta tha rigs kyi dam tshig ni //
NK022(za)001:6965: gang gi 'dod la snyoms zhugs pas //
NK022(za)001:6966: de la 'dod pa sbyor bar byed //
NK022(za)001:6967: bud d+ha phyag rgya chen po ni //
NK022(za)001:6968: ye shes dam tshig yin par bshad //
NK022(za)001:6969: rdo rje rigs kyi dngos grub ni //
NK022(za)001:6970: sems can don du khro med pas //
NK022(za)001:6971: khro bo chen po rab tu bston //
NK022(za)001:6972: rdo rje rigs mchog chen po yi //
NK022(za)001:6974: pad+ma rigs kyi dam tshig ni //
NK022(za)001:6975: rang bzhin dag par shes nas kyang //
NK022(za)001:6976: de yi dgongs pa de byed do //
NK022(za)001:6977: pad+ma'i rigs ni chen po yi //
NK022(za)001:6979: rin chen rigs kyi dam tshig ni //
NK022(za)001:6980: nyung ngam yang na mang yang rung //
NK022(za)001:6981: ji tsam nus pa nyid du ni //
NK022(za)001:6982: sbyin pas nyi ma ma stongs par //
NK022(za)001:6983: bya min dam tshig 'di yin no //
NK022(za)001:6984: las kyi rigs kyi dam tshig ni //
NK022(za)001:6986: rigs bzhi sems dpa' rnams kyi dam tshig ni //
NK022(za)001:6987: 'dod pa rnams la chags bral min //
NK022(za)001:6988: dam tshig mdzes pa chen po 'di //
NK022(za)001:6989: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs dam pa //
NK022(za)001:6990: rgyal bar rnams kyang 'da' mi mdzad //
NK022(za)001:6993: don du yang bshad cing bgo bar bya'o //
NK022(za)001:6994: 'di ni spyi yi dam tshig yin //
NK022(za)001:6995: dam tshig bsgrags pa yang yin te //
NK022(za)001:6996: 'di ni khyod kyi dmyal ba'i chu //
NK022(za)001:6997: dam tshig 'das na sreg par bye //
NK022(za)001:6998: dam tshig srungs na dngos grub ni //
NK022(za)001:7000: ci ste dam tshig 'das na ni //
NK022(za)001:7001: de ma thag tu bkas nas shog /
NK022(za)001:7002: rdo rje 'dzin rgyal khros nas kyang //
NK022(za)001:7003: bdun brgyud rigs kyang brlag par byed //
NK022(za)001:7004: de bas rtag tu bu khyod kyang //
NK022(za)001:7005: rgyal bas gsungs pa'i dam tshig dang //
NK022(za)001:7006: sdom pa dang ni bla ma'i bka' //
NK022(za)001:7007: shin tu mos pas srung bar bya'o //
NK022(za)001:7008: khyod kyis srog chags bsad mi bya //
NK022(za)001:7009: ma byin par yang mi bya'o //
NK022(za)001:7010: rdzun dang 'dod la spyod pa dang //
NK022(za)001:7011: sems can gnod par byed pa dang //
NK022(za)001:7012: nam yang bya ba ma yin no //
NK022(za)001:7013: dkon mchog gsum yang yong mi spang //
NK022(za)001:7014: dus kun du ni byang chub sems //
NK022(za)001:7015: snying po sngags dang phyag rgya dang //
NK022(za)001:7016: lha dang bla ma mi spang ngo //
NK022(za)001:7017: sdig pa la sogs thams cad dang //
NK022(za)001:7018: bla ma'i bka' las 'da' mi bya //
NK022(za)001:7019: lha la phul ba'i rnying pa dang //
NK022(za)001:7020: de yi grib ma 'gom mi bya //
NK022(za)001:7021: cung zad mtshan mar bcas pa gang //
NK022(za)001:7023: badz+ra sa ma ya h'u phata /
NK022(za)001:7024: ces tsan+dana gyi chu blud do //
NK022(za)001:7025: de nas slob ma dbang bskur ba'i gsol btab pa /
NK022(za)001:7026: nga ni dam tshig rdo rje ste //
NK022(za)001:7027: rdo rje sems dpa' yin pa'i phyir //
NK022(za)001:7028: rdo rje bla na med pa 'di //
NK022(za)001:7029: de ring bdag la dbab du gsol //
NK022(za)001:7030: slob dpon gyis gnang ba sbyin pa //
NK022(za)001:7031: nga ni dam tshig rdo rje ste //
NK022(za)001:7032: rdo rje sems dpa' yin par grags //
NK022(za)001:7033: rdo rje ye shes bla med 'di //
NK022(za)001:7034: de ring khyod la sbyin par bya //
NK022(za)001:7035: rdo rje rigs gtso chen po dang //
NK022(za)001:7036: khams gsum bdag por dbang bskur ro //
NK022(za)001:7037: phyogs gzhan ma dang dbus rigs dang bsdu zhing sbyar ro //
NK022(za)001:7038: rin chen rigs gtso chen po dang //
NK022(za)001:7039: lha min mchod par dbang bskur ro //
NK022(za)001:7040: pad+ma rigs mchog chen po dang //
NK022(za)001:7041: chos kyi rgyal pos dbang bskur ro //
NK022(za)001:7042: las kyi rigs gtso chen po dang //
NK022(za)001:7043: las bzhi spyod par dbang bskur ro //
NK022(za)001:7044: de la de bzhin gshegs gtso dang //
NK022(za)001:7045: chos rnams kun la dbang bskur ro //
NK022(za)001:7046: gong gi rigs dang sdeb bo //
NK022(za)001:7048: sangs rgyas kun gyi ye shes dbang //
NK022(za)001:7049: de ring khyod la bskur bar bya //
NK022(za)001:7050: sangs rgyas kun tu rab bsgrub phyir //
NK022(za)001:7051: rdo rje 'di ni khyod kyis zung //
NK022(za)001:7053: slob ma rdo rje 'dzin du bcug la /
NK022(za)001:7054: dbang bskur ba'i stegs bur drangs la /
NK022(za)001:7055: khri thog tu 'khor lo bsgyur ba'i rgyal po'i 'dug stangs su bzhag la /
NK022(za)001:7056: de nas dbang bskur bar mkhyen par gsol ba ni /
NK022(za)001:7057: bdag slob dpon ming 'di zhes bya bas /
NK022(za)001:7058: slob ma ming 'di zhes bgyi ba /
NK022(za)001:7059: thams cad mkhyen pa'i go 'phang thob par bgyi ba
NK022(za)001:7060: dang sangs rgyas kyi che ba'i yon tan ma lus
NK022(za)001:7061: par bsgrub cing / sems can gyi don yongs su rdzogs par bgyi ba'i slad du /
NK022(za)001:7062: man+dala gyi rgyal po ming 'di zhes bgyi bar dbang bskur bar 'tshal gyis /
NK022(za)001:7063: bcom ldan 'das ye shes kyi gtso bo thugs rje'i
NK022(za)001:7064: mnga' bdag rnams kyis ta th+aa'i che ba'i yon tan
NK022(za)001:7065: gyi dbang rnams rim pa bzhin du bskur zhing byin
NK022(za)001:7068: dkyil 'khor gang byed pa so so'i dbang rnams rdzogs par bskur ro //
NK022(za)001:7070: // de nas sa tra ha las ni /
NK022(za)001:7076: ming gi dbang dang drug 'byung ngo //
NK022(za)001:7077: de la ngan song sbyong ba'i nang nas /
NK022(za)001:7078: dbu brgyan la sogs pa bcu 'byung ngo //
NK022(za)001:7079: mngon par byang chub pa'i tan tra las ni /
NK022(za)001:7080: thur ma la sogs pa drug 'byung ngo //
NK022(za)001:7081: de la dbang bskur ba'i rim pa ni /
NK022(za)001:7083: tan tra las ni bum pa sna la 'byung //
NK022(za)001:7084: ngan song sbyong ba las ni dbu brgyan sna la 'byung //
NK022(za)001:7085: rnam par snang mdzad thig le dbang gi tan tra las ni /
NK022(za)001:7087: de ltar rgyud rnams kyi nang nas dbang gi rim pa ma nges pas /
NK022(za)001:7088: de bas na dbang gang yang rung bas mgo drangs nas bskur ba yang 'gal ba med do //
NK022(za)001:7089: mngon par byang chub pa'i rgyud las //
NK022(za)001:7090: dus dang dus min bye brag las //
NK022(za)001:7091: slob ma rnam bzhir shes bya ste //
NK022(za)001:7092: gcig ni de yi mod la bsgrub //
NK022(za)001:7093: gnyis su bsgrub dang gnyis kar min //
NK022(za)001:7094: mtshan nyid thams cad yongs rdzogs la //
NK022(za)001:7095: slob ma de yi rgyal ba'i mchog /
NK022(za)001:7097: dbang theg thang du bskur cig /
NK022(za)001:7098: 'dus pa mdo'i yo ga'i dbang gi tsa ka li'i dbang gi rgyab yig klags la dbang bskur ro //
NK022(za)001:7099: rnam snang mngon byang nas byung ba bzhin no //
NK022(za)001:7100: de nas bum pa'i smon lam gdab bo //
NK022(za)001:7101: de nas sgo bzhi'i smon lam btab ste /
NK022(za)001:7102: sgo 'di ni shar phyogs kyi sgo la sogs te /
NK022(za)001:7103: rgya gar gyi sgra las drangs na sur ba zhes bgyi /
NK022(za)001:7104: sngon dang thog ma la yang sur ba zhes bgyi ste /
NK022(za)001:7105: de bas na de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa
NK022(za)001:7106: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rdo rje sems
NK022(za)001:7107: dpa' la sogs pa rnams kyis kyang /
NK022(za)001:7108: zhe sdang chen po ni brtan nas spangs nas shar phyogs byams pa tshad med pa'i sgor zhugs pas /
NK022(za)001:7109: sgrib pa rnam pa gnyis byang /
NK022(za)001:7110: tshogs rnam pa gnyis ni rdzogs te /
NK022(za)001:7111: me long lta bu'i ye shes thob nas /
NK022(za)001:7112: rdo rje rigs kyi dkyil 'khor du mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas par gyur to //
NK022(za)001:7113: de bzhin du ming 'di zhes bya bas kyang zhe sdang chen po ni brtan nas spangs nas /
NK022(za)001:7114: shar phyogs byams pa tshad med pa'i sgor zhugs nas sgrib pa rnam pa gnyis ni byang /
NK022(za)001:7115: tshogs chen po rnam pa gnyis ni rdzogs te /
NK022(za)001:7116: me long lta bu'i ye shes thob nas /
NK022(za)001:7117: rdo rje rigs kyi dkyil 'khor du mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas par gyur cig /
NK022(za)001:7118: shar phyogs byams pa'i sgo ste tshad med pa //
NK022(za)001:7119: byams pas sems can ma lus bsgrol bya ste //
NK022(za)001:7120: rdo rje rigs kyi dbang dang dngos grub dang //
NK022(za)001:7121: byin brlabs dam pa khyod kyis thob par shog /
NK022(za)001:7138: lhug pa dang tshigs su bcad par rigs mthun pas shar ltar bsdeb /
NK022(za)001:7139: de nas dkyil 'khor gyi lha la gtang rag gi pu tsa dbul /
NK022(za)001:7140: bshags pa byas la gshegs su gsol /
NK022(za)001:7141: dam tshig can gyi gtor ma gtang /
NK022(za)001:7144: tshon rtsi phyag la chu klung du bskyal /
NK022(za)001:7146: bsgrims te mtshon rtsi rnams bsdus nas //
NK022(za)001:7147: chu klung chen por bskyal nas kyang //
NK022(za)001:7148: ba yi lci bas byug par bya //
NK022(za)001:7150: thig rjes la sogs pa las kyi 'phro mi mngon par bya'o //
NK022(za)001:7154: rdo rje slob dpon gyis dam tshig gi phyag rgyas rdo rje thal mo phyir bsnol nas /
NK022(za)001:7155: gung mo gnyis bzhibs pa sbreng la /
NK022(za)001:7156: me tog gi phreng ba 'go 'khor cig thogs la /
NK022(za)001:7158: rdo rje sems dpa' bzhugs pa'i steng du bab par rol la /
NK022(za)001:7159: ming 'di zhes bgyi ba bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs kyi lha'i dbang du mchis te /
NK022(za)001:7160: ma rig pas longs ba'i sems can rnams de las bkrol ba'i rigs pa ni /
NK022(za)001:7162: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs kyis 'dul ba rnams bsdu ba'i rim pa ni /
NK022(za)001:7164: dkyil 'khor gyi las rnams bgyid do zhes bka' nod na /
NK022(za)001:7165: de nas me tog gi phreng ba blangs la /
NK022(za)001:7166: bdag gi mgo la bcings te /
NK022(za)001:7167: po ti'i phyag rgyas bcings nas /
NK022(za)001:7168: a be sha a zhes brjod pas nyid bzhengs nas bdag la dbang bskur te /
NK022(za)001:7169: bdag gi khong du zhugs par bsam /
NK022(za)001:7174: de nyid dam tshig yin par bshad //
NK022(za)001:7176: bdag nyid dad pas 'jug lags na //
NK022(za)001:7177: dam bcas pa yi lha rnams kyis //
NK022(za)001:7178: bdag ma byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK022(za)001:7179: bde bar gshegs pa ba ga b+aan //
NK022(za)001:7180: bsod nams can du bdag nyid 'gyur //
NK022(za)001:7181: sngon gyi las kyis 'brel pas na //
NK022(za)001:7182: thugs rjes sras su dgongs par mdzod //
NK022(za)001:7183: bcom ldan 'das kyis sangs rgyas kun //
NK022(za)001:7186: // rje grub thob rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK022(za)001:7187: rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa'i cho ga bcu gcig ni /
NK022(za)001:7188: cho 'phrul bzhi'i ngo bo ye shes bzhi rdzogs par bya ba'i phyir /
NK022(za)001:7190: sangs rgyas kyi spyan thob par bya ba'i phyir ras kyis gdong g.yog pa dang /
NK022(za)001:7191: dam tshig tu byin gyis brlabs pa dang /
NK022(za)001:7192: me tog phreng ba 'dzin du bzhugs pa dang /
NK022(za)001:7193: gdams ngag 'bog cing gsang ba brtan pa dang /
NK022(za)001:7194: man ngag snying pos mna' chu blud pa dang /
NK022(za)001:7195: rdo rje slob dpon gyi bka' mi bcag cing brnyas pa mi bya ba dang /
NK022(za)001:7196: sems dpa' dang ye shes dbab pa dang /
NK022(za)001:7197: dam tshig gi phyag rgya bkrol la snying po brjod nas bskul ba dang /
NK022(za)001:7198: rig pa'i me tog dor la lha dbab pa'i lha
NK022(za)001:7199: gang yin pa brtag pa'i phyir me tog dor ba
NK022(za)001:7200: dang / dkyil 'khor gyi lha ngo bstan pa dang /
NK022(za)001:7201: dkyil 'khor mthong ba'i phan yon no //
NK022(za)001:7205: bud+d+ha'i dbu brgyan gyi dbang dang /
NK022(za)001:7209: legs sam bsam pa yod e go ////
NK022(za)001:7211: da ni bla med theg pa sngags dam tshig /
NK022(za)001:7212: glang chen rab 'bog rgyud dang 'dul lung du //
NK022(za)001:7213: rtsa ba'i dam tshig sku gsung thugs gsum bshad //
NK022(za)001:7214: spang bya mi dge lus ngag yid 'dus sdom //
NK022(za)001:7215: nyan thos nyams na rdza be'u chag 'dra bas //
NK022(za)001:7216: slar gso mi rung slar gso'i thabs med cing //
NK022(za)001:7217: gsang sngags nyams na gser dngul zhom 'dra bas //
NK022(za)001:7218: slar gso'i thabs yod thabs des nyams chag skongs //
NK022(za)001:7219: dngos grub thob cing yon tan rgyas rig 'dzin //
NK022(za)001:7220: ngan song dong sprugs rnal 'byor spyi khrus bshad //
NK022(za)001:7221: bla ma yi dam sku gsung thugs tshogs lam //
NK022(za)001:7222: rang nyid yi dam sku gsung thugs sbyor mthong //
NK022(za)001:7223: snang srid sku gsung thugs sgom mthar lam lnga //
NK022(za)001:7224: a ro ye shes gsang sgron brgyud //
NK022(za)001:7225: tshogs lam bla ma mtshan ldan la //
NK022(za)001:7226: mnyes pa gsum gyis mchod pa dbul //
NK022(za)001:7227: sbyor lam bla ma'i gdams ngag gis //
NK022(za)001:7228: zhi gnas lhag mthong brgyud la sbyar //
NK022(za)001:7229: mthong lam spyan lnga dag pa yis //
NK022(za)001:7230: rang sems skye med mthong bar bya //
NK022(za)001:7231: sgom lam ting 'dzin rnam gsum gyis //
NK022(za)001:7232: gnyug ma yid la goms par bya //
NK022(za)001:7233: mthar phyin nyes pa gnyis zad pas //
NK022(za)001:7234: chos rnams zad par bskyal bar bya //
NK022(za)001:7235: zhes pas gzhi ni ma rig nyes //
NK022(za)001:7236: lam ni rtsol ba'i nyes pas gnyis //
NK022(za)001:7237: ting 'dzin stong nyid snying rje dang //
NK022(za)001:7238: dbyer med bskyed rdzogs rgyu yi ting 'dzin //
NK022(za)001:7239: spyan lnga sha lha sangs rgyas spyan //
NK022(za)001:7240: shes rab spyan dang ye shes spyan //
NK022(za)001:7241: snying rje kun snang rnal 'byor pa //
NK022(za)001:7242: sha yi spyan gyis sna tshogs mthong //
NK022(za)001:7243: mngon shes lha yi mig khyi sogs //
NK022(za)001:7244: chags bral nyan 'phags sangs rgyas spyan //
NK022(za)001:7245: byang chub sems skyes shes rab spyan //
NK022(za)001:7246: sangs rgyas dag pa'i sa spyan zhes dri med //
NK022(za)001:7248: thugs gsang gsung sngags phyag rgya sku bla mched //
NK022(za)001:7249: kun rtsa bla med byang chub sems zhes ni //
NK022(za)001:7250: rang rgyal 'bum bas lhag thob byang chub dang //
NK022(za)001:7251: don dam kun rdzob byang chub sems bskyed dang //
NK022(za)001:7253: sems skyed pa ni gzhan don phyir //
NK022(za)001:7254: yang dag rdzogs pa'i byang chub 'dod ces dang /
NK022(za)001:7256: dri ma zad dang mi skye ba'i //
NK022(za)001:7257: ye shes byang chub ces brjod sngags ltar du //
NK022(za)001:7258: kun rdzob skyed rims don dam rdzogs rims 'brel //
NK022(za)001:7259: dbyer med zung 'jug byang chub sems grub pas //
NK022(za)001:7260: sa bon shu tra thig le byang chub sems //
NK022(za)001:7261: nyan thos 'dul bar 'dod chags rmi lam ni //
NK022(za)001:7262: med pa dang 'dra'o zhes pas lus kyi bcud //
NK022(za)001:7263: chags spyad rmi zags bslab pa mi nyams bshags //
NK022(za)001:7264: sems tsam smon 'jug rtsa nyams skyar dgos kyang //
NK022(za)001:7265: rmi lam bshags dag skya rengs lha sbran te //
NK022(za)001:7266: byang sems nam snying rmi lam byon grol bshad //
NK022(za)001:7267: rmi lam du ni chos kun rmi lam du //
NK022(za)001:7268: shes dang ma shes rtse mo phyin dang ma phyin rtags //
NK022(za)001:7269: rgyun du rmi lam sems ni gnyid kyis nyams //
NK022(za)001:7270: des na 'bras bu 'dra ma yin zhes ni //
NK022(za)001:7271: rmi lam lta bur shes na dngos sdig kyang //
NK022(za)001:7272: dag nges dran pas srid 'chings las grol bshad //
NK022(za)001:7275: chos rnams rmi lam sgyu ma zhes //
NK022(za)001:7276: gang gis tshig brjod dran pas kyang //
NK022(za)001:7279: sngags ltar dngos dang rmi lam 'dra phan gnod //
NK022(za)001:7280: bsnyen bsgrub mthar phyin rgyal ba'i bka' gnang yang //
NK022(za)001:7281: zhag mtha'i bsgrub chen dngos grub ma thob par //
NK022(za)001:7282: bcud nyams dngos rmi 'dra ste bsgrub bskyar dgos //
NK022(za)001:7284: lan gcig rtag tu khu ba lhung ba'i phyir //
NK022(za)001:7285: gnyis ka la'ang mchog gi bde ba med //
NK022(za)001:7286: de bzhin dka' thub can dang 'dod ldan dag /
NK022(za)001:7287: rmi lam pad+ma dag la 'dzag phyir ro //
NK022(za)001:7289: ji ltar gnyid log dag la sbrul gyis ni //
NK022(za)001:7290: so btab mi 'tshe de bzhin dka' thub pa //
NK022(za)001:7291: zhes de gnyid sad dug sbrul gyis dmugs dang //
NK022(za)001:7292: gnyid log dug sbrul gyis dmugs gnyis //
NK022(za)001:7293: 'chi bar 'dra ltar sa bon sad rmi gnyis //
NK022(za)001:7294: gang la zags kyang nyon mongs sgribs bcings brtags //
NK022(za)001:7295: gnas grogs dpa' bo mkha' 'gro 'dus byin barlobasa //
NK022(za)001:7296: bdag grogs rtsal rdzogs lus thob dus tshod shes //
NK022(za)001:7297: thal brgyud skabs gsum po ni ma rtogs par //
NK022(za)001:7298: thig le spro bar bya ba min zhes pa'ang //
NK022(za)001:7299: nad kyi skabs las rgyal mchod sman bka' gnang //
NK022(za)001:7300: bcas pa mtha' dag gis ni skyang zhes gsungs //
NK022(za)001:7301: sras kyi skabs las rgyal sras bsgrub bka' gnang //
NK022(za)001:7302: rigs sras dkrun la gnod byed de bsgral bshad //
NK022(za)001:7303: dbang gi skabs las rgyal tshab bka' bkrol gnang //
NK022(za)001:7304: dag pas skyon rnams chung mar bcas zab dbang //
NK022(za)001:7305: skabs gsum dpe 'dul dus bab de shes nas //
NK022(za)001:7306: sangs rgyas gdung 'tshob bstan skyong srung phan ched //
NK022(za)001:7307: lus la gnas kyang lus la mi ltos bde //
NK022(za)001:7308: lus bde sems bde snang bas mi 'ching bde //
NK022(za)001:7309: stong par grol bade'o g.yeng 'dod bde min bshad //
NK022(za)001:7310: g.yan pa phrugs bade'ang tsha chu ltar mi ngoms //
NK022(za)001:7311: gal te sngags pas ltung byung ldang 'dod na //
NK022(za)001:7312: phan nus bum dbang byis 'jug nyams chag la //
NK022(za)001:7313: dbang zhus pa dang lha skyed gsal ba dang //
NK022(za)001:7314: bzlas pa sum khri drug stong sngags 'bum dang //
NK022(za)001:7315: dkyil 'khor mthong mos thos tsam sgom dad dag /
NK022(za)001:7316: phyis nas mi byed sdom la gnas byed pa'i //
NK022(za)001:7317: yon tan ldan des rtsa ltung byung bshags dag /
NK022(za)001:7318: zab dbang bum dbang thob la rtsa ltung gi /
NK022(za)001:7319: skyon sel 'gyod blos dag bzung 'bras thob 'dod //
NK022(za)001:7320: bla mas bka' stsal rang gi 'bad pas dag /
NK022(za)001:7321: shes rab ye shes dbang thob skyon dag phyir //
NK022(za)001:7322: rang gi bdag 'jug bsod nams tshul khrims stobs //
NK022(za)001:7323: sdig bshags rgyal dang rgyal sras byin thob dag /
NK022(za)001:7324: zhes ni sangs rgyas bzhed ces dus 'khor bshad //
NK022(za)001:7325: lha mi'i khrims dang nyan thos dge bsnyen dang //
NK022(za)001:7326: gso sbyong bsnyen gnas dbu ma sems bskyed rnams //
NK022(za)001:7327: nyams dang ma nyams gang la'ang bslab bskyar skye //
NK022(za)001:7328: bskyar len tshe na dbul chog mi dgos gsung //
NK022(za)001:7329: sngar nyams nyes bshags sdig dag dge chub bsngo //
NK022(za)001:7330: nyan thos gnas brtan 'os bskos byed de dang //
NK022(za)001:7331: 'phags thob de la ltung gleng gnas 'byin dor //
NK022(za)001:7332: shes dang 'khor mang sde snod 'dzin mi dbyung //
NK022(za)001:7333: nyan thos dge slong dge tshul bskyar len tshe //
NK022(za)001:7334: sngar sdom dbul dgos ma phul bskyar mi skye //
NK022(za)001:7335: snum dreg can la ma bkrus tshos mi ljen //
NK022(za)001:7336: rdza be'u chag sbyar mi rung bskyar dgos 'dra'o //
NK022(za)001:7337: rtsa ba bzhi'ang gzhi bsam sbyor mtha' tshang nyams kyang //
NK022(za)001:7338: yan lag ma nyams yod srid gser dngul len //
NK022(za)001:7339: khri stan che mtho ma nyams rtsa nyams mthong //
NK022(za)001:7340: po mthon 'dra zhes bslab bskyar 'bul chog mdzad //
NK022(za)001:7341: rtsa ba ma nyams yan lag nyams bshags dag /
NK022(za)001:7342: dbu ma sems tsam gnyis kyi sems bskyed dbang //
NK022(za)001:7343: len dus sngar thob 'bul chog mi dgos par //
NK022(za)001:7344: bslab skye theg pa che chung khyad du bzhed //
NK022(za)001:7345: theg chen sems bskyed dbang thob dam 'bul ba //
NK022(za)001:7346: theg dman ltung zhing the tshom skyon 'byung dang //
NK022(za)001:7347: sngar sdom thos la ma gus dor skyon 'byung //
NK022(za)001:7348: dam tshig dang po sdom bzung gso sbyong blang //
NK022(za)001:7349: mdo dbang nyan thos 'jug sgo byed de'i tshe //
NK022(za)001:7350: dge tshul dge slong gtsang la skyar mi dgos //
NK022(za)001:7351: dge slong gnas brtan dge tshul gnas brtan dang //
NK022(za)001:7352: dge bsnyen gnas brtan 'phags thob mngon shes ldan //
NK022(za)001:7353: nyan thos lugs ltar bskong dang ma bskos dang //
NK022(za)001:7354: sngags ltar bkod dbang thob dgos dbang chu bo //
NK022(za)001:7355: rnal 'byor bla ma phyi dbang ma h+aa yi //
NK022(za)001:7356: nang dbang a nu bsgrub dbang a ti gsang //
NK022(za)001:7360: // // mdo dbang chen po'i gleng gzhi'i le'u 'di la gsum ste /
NK022(za)001:7373: slob dpon la bsam ngan skyes nas barngana byas pa dang /
NK022(za)001:7374: gnyis pa bram ze'i dmod pa bor ba dang /
NK022(za)001:7375: gsum pa rgyal bus sdug bsngal nyams su myong nas tha ma lus srul por skyes pa'o //
NK022(za)001:7376: gleng gzhi'i rgyu la gsum ste /
NK022(za)001:7377: dang po phyag rdor gyis srul po'i du kha mthong nas bston pa la zhus pa dang /
NK022(za)001:7378: gnyis pa gleng gzhi'i rgyu bka' stsal zhing phyag rdor la don gyis shig pa dang /
NK022(za)001:7379: gsum pa phyag rdor gyis dbang don zhus pa'o //
NK022(za)001:7380: dbang gi rim pa la gnyis te /
NK022(za)001:7390: // // de la 'dren pa'i las byang chen po la gsum ste /
NK022(za)001:7391: ston pas 'khor dbang gi lha lnga brgya brgyad cu rtsa gsum du bstan pa dang /
NK022(za)001:7392: 'khor gyis ngo mtshar skyes te zhus pa'o //
NK022(za)001:7396: 'dren pa'i las byang chen po ste /
NK022(za)001:7397: de la mdo dang rgyas pa'o //
NK022(za)001:7398: rgyas pa la phan pa lha'i dbang dang /
NK022(za)001:7399: byin brlabs slob dpon gyi dbang dang /
NK022(za)001:7400: thob pa mig gi dbang ngo //
NK022(za)001:7402: dang po stegs bu'i tshad dang rdul tshon dang /
NK022(za)001:7403: gnyis pa lha dgod pa dang /
NK022(za)001:7404: gsum pa slob ma la dbang ba'o //
NK022(za)001:7408: // // 'dren pa'i las byang chung ngu la don gsum ste /
NK022(za)001:7411: de nyid rgyas par bshad pa dkyus na gsal lo //
NK022(za)001:7415: // // lta ba ye 'byam dbang la gnyis te /
NK022(za)001:7416: blo che ba la bskur mi dgos pa dang /
NK022(za)001:7417: blo chung ba la bskur ba'o //
NK022(za)001:7419: dang po blo che ba la rdzogs pa dang /
NK022(za)001:7420: gnyis pa bskur mi dgos pa'i dpe dang /
NK022(za)001:7421: gsum pa bskur mi dgos pa'i gtan tshigs so //
NK022(za)001:7422: blo chung gi dbang la gnyis te /
NK022(za)001:7423: dbang gi don ston pas spyir bstan pa dang /
NK022(za)001:7426: dang po dbang gi dpe dang /
NK022(za)001:7427: gnyis pa rten med kyi dbang dang /
NK022(za)001:7428: gsum pa gzhan dbang du dbang rag ma lus pa dang /
NK022(za)001:7429: bzhi pa dbang rang la yod pa'i gtan tshigs dang /
NK022(za)001:7430: lnga pa tshig la rag ma lus pa dang /
NK022(za)001:7431: drug pa gnyis med dbang dge mi dge yis ma gos pa dang /
NK022(za)001:7432: bdun pa ma gos pa'i dpe dang /
NK022(za)001:7433: brgyad pa brtsol bsgrub kun rdzogs par bstan pa'o //
NK022(za)001:7437: // // yongs su grub pa'i dbang la don lnga ste /
NK022(za)001:7438: dang po bsrung du med pa'i dam tshig yongs su grub pa dang /
NK022(za)001:7439: gnyis pa blang dor med pa'i spyod pa dang /
NK022(za)001:7440: gsum pa spangs thob med pa'i bsgrub pa dang /
NK022(za)001:7441: bzhi pa phrin las rtsal du med pa dang /
NK022(za)001:7442: lnga pa ji ltar grub pa'i tshul bstan pa'o //
NK022(za)001:7446: // // kun tu bzang po'i gdams ngag gi le'u la gsum ste /
NK022(za)001:7448: gnyis pa rnal 'byor a bcangs pa dang /
NK022(za)001:7449: gsum po snod bzang po la sbyin pa'o //
NK022(za)001:7451: snod ngan pa la mi sbyin pa dang /
NK022(za)001:7454: dang po ngan pa la ma smras pa dang bstan pa'i khyad par dang /
NK022(za)001:7455: gsang ma thub pa'i nyes pa dang /
NK022(za)001:7459: yang na nyes pa la lnga ste /
NK022(za)001:7460: dang po snod ngan pa la byin pas sngags kyi byin nyams pa dang /
NK022(za)001:7461: gnyis pa ngan pa la byin pa'i nyes pa dang /
NK022(za)001:7462: gsum pa sdig pa'i tshad dang /
NK022(za)001:7463: bzhi pa snod ngan pa la mi sbyin pa dang /
NK022(za)001:7464: lnga pa snod ngan pa la mi bsten pa'o //
NK022(za)001:7465: gab pa'i dbang drug le'u drug gi sa bcad brjed byang mdzad pa /
NK022(za)001:7469: dpal rdo rje sems dpa' la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK022(za)001:7470: de la rnam par snang mdzad thig le dbang gi tan tra'i nang nas /
NK022(za)001:7472: dbang bcu drug gi gleng gzhi dang /
NK022(za)001:7473: dbang gi go rims nyi tshe phyung nas bshad do //
NK022(za)001:7474: 'dod khams 'di na bram ze dung gi phreng ba can zhes bya ba /
NK022(za)001:7475: gos su dung gi phreng ba gon pa rdzu 'phrul dang ldan pa zhig la /
NK022(za)001:7476: slob ma rgyal bu phru gu zhig yod pa las /
NK022(za)001:7477: bram zes kyang slob sbyong la sogs pa mang po zhig bslabs pa las /
NK022(za)001:7478: rgyal bu nga rgyal skyes te bsam pas 'di na
NK022(za)001:7479: nga'i gong na su yang shes nyen can med pas
NK022(za)001:7481: bram ze 'di gong du mi gtang bar bsams te /
NK022(za)001:7482: bram ze bos te dgun chang mang du blud nas gzi ru bcug nas myos pa dang /
NK022(za)001:7484: lce lcags kyus drangs te spu gris bcad /
NK022(za)001:7485: lus po rus sbal gyi khrag gis byugs /
NK022(za)001:7486: bud med mang po'i zhabs mas brtums zhing mnan /
NK022(za)001:7487: sgyid pa spu gris bregs nas bzhag pa dang /
NK022(za)001:7488: bram ze de myos pa sangs nas drung na su 'dug 'bod par bsams na /
NK022(za)001:7489: lce med pas smra ma shes /
NK022(za)001:7490: bud med mang po'i zhabs mas btums shing mnan pas dran pa yang cher nyams /
NK022(za)001:7491: ldang bar bsam pas sgyid pas lang ma nus /
NK022(za)001:7492: su 'dug ltas pas mig gis ma mthong /
NK022(za)001:7493: lus la rus sbal gyi khrag gis bskus pas chu bur dang rkong pas gang bar gyur te /
NK022(za)001:7494: sdug bsngal zhing 'dug pa la nyams thag nas bram zes bsams pas /
NK022(za)001:7495: nga kho na 'di 'dra bar gyur pa'i tshe rabs
NK022(za)001:7496: sngon gyi las kyi rnam par smin pa zhig yin
NK022(za)001:7497: nam / 'on te gong du shor gyis dogs pa'i
NK022(za)001:7498: phrag dog gis 'di ltar byas sam snyam na yid
NK022(za)001:7499: nam / la btang nas / rgyal bu slob mas
NK022(za)001:7500: gong du shor gyis dogs nas sdug bsngal rnam pa
NK022(za)001:7501: de dag byas par bram zes mngon shes kyis rig
NK022(za)001:7502: nam / la btang nas / nas / bram zes dmod mos bor bas /
NK022(za)001:7503: 'o rgyal bu phru gu khyod ngas lo zla bsnyen slob sbyong byas pa'i sting la /
NK022(za)001:7504: nga la 'di 'dra ba'i las byed par gyur pa khyod kyang tshe lus 'di la /
NK022(za)001:7505: lus sha za ma stong gis tshang bcas par gyur cig /
NK022(za)001:7506: khyod kyi mig long bar gyur cig /
NK022(za)001:7507: khyod kyi lce lkugs par shog cig /
NK022(za)001:7508: khyod rkang pas 'gro mi shes par shog cig /
NK022(za)001:7509: de nas tshe 'das nas kyang ngan song gsum gyi
NK022(za)001:7510: gnas rim par brgyud nas dmyal ba'i gnas su skyes
NK022(za)001:7511: nas / tshe rabs grangs med par 'phags pa'i zhal
NK022(za)001:7512: nyi zer tsam yang mi mthong shing byang chub kyi
NK022(za)001:7513: myu gu gtan nas skams par gyur cig /
NK022(za)001:7514: ces dmod pa bor ba dang /
NK022(za)001:7515: de nas rgyal bu 'das nas rang gi nyes byas
NK022(za)001:7516: kyi rnam smin dang bram ze'i dmod pa bor ba
NK022(za)001:7517: 'dod khams nas / sems can gyi nang nas lus
NK022(za)001:7518: srul po gcer bu can zhes bya bar skyes te
NK022(za)001:7519: lus la nad rnam pa drug gis phyi nang du
NK022(za)001:7520: 'dod khams nas / thebs / sha za ma stong gi tshang bcas nas mig ni long /
NK022(za)001:7523: sems kyi byang chub kyi myu gu sngo skams su song la thug /
NK022(za)001:7524: de las 'phos nas kyang dmyal khams bco brgyad du
NK022(za)001:7525: kha brgyud nas bskal pa grangs med pa'i bar du
NK022(za)001:7526: 'phags pa'i zhal nyi zer tsam yang mthong ba'i skal
NK022(za)001:7527: ba med par bcom ldan 'das rnam par snang mdzad
NK022(za)001:7528: kyis gzigs nas / nyid kyi thugs kha nas dpal
NK022(za)001:7529: phyag na rdo rje phyung nas mdun drang por gnas
NK022(za)001:7531: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa //
NK022(za)001:7532: lag na rdo rje khyod song la 'dod khams kyi
NK022(za)001:7533: gnas na sems can lus srul po gcer bu zhes
NK022(za)001:7534: bya / tshe rabs snga ma la slob dpon bram
NK022(za)001:7535: ze zhig gi lus la ngan sna tshogs byas pa'i
NK022(za)001:7537: bram ze'i dmod pa'i dbang gis da ltar byang chub kyi myu gu ni skam la thug /
NK022(za)001:7538: lus kyi rgyu ni shin tu myos shing sdug bsngal /
NK022(za)001:7539: de las 'das nas kyang dmyal khams kyi kha brgyud de thar pa'i dus med par gyur pas /
NK022(za)001:7540: lag na rdo rje khyod kyis sems can nyam thag
NK022(za)001:7541: pa 'di la de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi
NK022(za)001:7542: byin gyi brlabs kyi dbang dam pa 'di rnams kyis
NK022(za)001:7543: srung la / du kha'i nad rnams bsal ba dang
NK022(za)001:7544: ngan song dang dmyal ba'i khams su skye ba las
NK022(za)001:7545: slar bzlog par bya ba dang /
NK022(za)001:7546: mtho ris kyi gnas su skye bar gyur pa'i thabs
NK022(za)001:7547: dbang bskur ba'i las byos shig ces bka' stsal pa
NK022(za)001:7548: dang / lag na rdo rje rjes su yi rang nas slar bcom ldan 'das la gsol pa /
NK022(za)001:7549: bcom ldan 'das dbang thams cad kyi rang bzhin bshad du gsol zhus pas /
NK022(za)001:7550: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
NK022(za)001:7551: rgyal rigs btsun par skyes pa'i tshe //
NK022(za)001:7552: rgyal srid 'bangs kyis phul ba ni //
NK022(za)001:7553: tshigs btsun yul la dbang bsgyur ba'i //
NK022(za)001:7554: sa bdag rgyal por gnas pa bzhin //
NK022(za)001:7555: bcom ldan byang chub spyod pa'i tshe //
NK022(za)001:7556: lha dang lha min 'khor bcas pa //
NK022(za)001:7557: dbang bskur rdzas kyi mnga' gsol bas //
NK022(za)001:7558: de nas byang chub mngon sangs rgyas //
NK022(za)001:7559: phyag rgya gsang bas gnas srungs te //
NK022(za)001:7560: bdud rtsi bum pas sdig rnams bkru //
NK022(za)001:7561: phreng ba cod pan tshul khrims dang //
NK022(za)001:7562: rnam lnga'i thur mas bag chags bsal //
NK022(za)001:7563: me long 'khor lo dung rgya gram //
NK022(za)001:7564: sna bdun 'khor lo'i stegs gtsugs te //
NK022(za)001:7565: ral gri shes rab mda' gzhu dang //
NK022(za)001:7566: seng ge nyi zla lta bu yi //
NK022(za)001:7567: 'bras bu bkra shis rdzas brgyad sbyin //
NK022(za)001:7568: bden pa'i bka' brjod dam bdar nas //
NK022(za)001:7569: ting 'dzin tshangs pa'i glu dbyangs dang //
NK022(za)001:7570: rten 'brel rdzas rnams bshams nas ni //
NK022(za)001:7571: dbang mchog des ni dbang bskur ro //
NK022(za)001:7582: rdo rje rgya gram gyi dang /
NK022(za)001:7583: rin po che sna bdun gyi dang /
NK022(za)001:7588: bkra shis rdzas brgyad kyi dbang dang bcu drug go //
NK022(za)001:7589: de nas lag na rdo rje rdo rje lta bu'i ting 'dzin la bsnyoms par bzhugs nas /
NK022(za)001:7590: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs
NK022(za)001:7591: rdo rje rnam par dag pa'i phyag rgyas bcings te
NK022(za)001:7592: / sems can lus srul po'i gnas sngar gtugs te /
NK022(za)001:7593: bskrad pas sha za mo stong gnas pa yang bskrag nas byer ro //
NK022(za)001:7594: de nas 'du 'bral med pa gsang ba'i dbang gis
NK022(za)001:7595: byang chub sems kyi myu gu sngo skams su gyur
NK022(za)001:7596: la thug pa de sos nas de bzhin gshegs pa'i
NK022(za)001:7597: snying po can du byin gyis brlabs so //
NK022(za)001:7598: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa'i thugs rje'i byin gyis
NK022(za)001:7599: brlabs pa'i bdud rtsi'i bum pa'i dbang gis lus kyi
NK022(za)001:7600: mi bde ba'i nad rnams bkrus nas dag cing byang
NK022(za)001:7601: bar gyur to // me tog gi 'phreng bas dbang
NK022(za)001:7602: bskur bas tshul khrims kyi phung po zhig ral yongs
NK022(za)001:7603: bar gyur to // su rdzogs nas / ngan song
NK022(za)001:7604: du lhung ba las ldog pa'i dbang dang ldan par
NK022(za)001:7605: bar gyur to // su rdzogs nas / gyur to
NK022(za)001:7606: // de nas cod pan gyis dbang bskur bas khams
NK022(za)001:7607: gsum na gnas pa'i bsam sbyor ngan pa'i bag chags
NK022(za)001:7609: de nas thur ma mdun du thogs nas /
NK022(za)001:7610: sngon gyi mig mkhan rgyal pos ni //
NK022(za)001:7611: mig gi rab rib bsal ba bzhin //
NK022(za)001:7612: bu khyod ma rig 'thibs pa yi //
NK022(za)001:7613: rab rib rgyal ba rnams kyis bsal //
NK022(za)001:7614: zhes brjod de thur mas dbang bskur nas ma rig
NK022(za)001:7615: pa'i ling thog 'thibs pa byang nas gsal bar gyur
NK022(za)001:7616: to // de'i 'og tu me long byin nas dbang bskur bas /
NK022(za)001:7617: chos kun gzugs brnyan lta bu ste //
NK022(za)001:7618: rten 'brel mthu las snang ba ste //
NK022(za)001:7619: brjod med rang bzhin dag pa yi //
NK022(za)001:7620: don dam chos nyid rtogs par 'gyur //
NK022(za)001:7621: zhes chos thams cad gzugs brnyan rten 'brel sgyu ma lta bur mthong ngo //
NK022(za)001:7625: gzhan don 'di la phan pa'i phyir //
NK022(za)001:7626: rgyal ba 'khor lo bskor ba mdzad //
