NK022(za)001:9096: nas rab gnas byas pa'i sku'am bris sku mdun du
NK022(za)001:9097: bkram la / rang stan bde ba la bsdad /
NK022(za)001:9098: lus ngag yid gsum cha bsnyam /
NK022(za)001:9099: rnam snang gi chos bdun bca' /
NK022(za)001:9100: shes pa snga phyi'i 'khrul thag gcod do //
NK022(za)001:9101: dang po skyabs 'gro sems bskyed bya /
NK022(za)001:9102: bla ma yi dam mdun gyi nam mkha' la spyan drangs /
NK022(za)001:9103: de la mdun rnam dag byas la /
NK022(za)001:9104: mdun du sgom yang rung bdag nyid gsal bar sgom yang rung ste /
NK022(za)001:9105: dang po lha'i gzugs brnyan la dbyibs dang kha dog
NK022(za)001:9106: dang rgyan la sogs par khyab par wal gyis lta
NK022(za)001:9107: ba'o // nyams lnga ni dang po lha la sems gtad pas /
NK022(za)001:9108: lha brang breng las lhar sems su mi 'dod par
NK022(za)001:9109: 'du byed kyi dran pa sna tshogs su sems 'phro
NK022(za)001:9110: ba ni g.yo ba'i nyams te smig rgyu lta bu'o
NK022(za)001:9111: // cung zhig lha'i sku dbyibs dang kha dog gnyis
NK022(za)001:9112: dus gcig la wal gyis bsam pa ni thob pa'i
NK022(za)001:9113: nyams te du ba lta bu'o //
NK022(za)001:9114: de nas lha'i dbyibs dang kha dog tu gsal ba
NK022(za)001:9115: thun gsum tsam du gsal ba ni goms pa'i nyams
NK022(za)001:9116: te srin bu me khyer lta bu'o //
NK022(za)001:9117: lha'i dbyibs dang kha dog rgyan dang bcas pa rkyen
NK022(za)001:9118: ma byung bar la gsal ba ni brtan pa'i nyams
NK022(za)001:9120: lha'i ba spu'i bu ga yan chad rang gis bzhag
NK022(za)001:9121: tshod du rkyen gyis ma gnod na mthar phyin pa'i
NK022(za)001:9122: nyams te ri bo lta bu'o //
NK022(za)001:9123: rnam pa tsam du snang ba la sogs te lam rim ltar ro //
NK022(za)001:9124: tshad ni gsal ba'i tshad bzhi /
NK022(za)001:9125: sa le ba dran pa tsam gyis lhar gsal ba /
NK022(za)001:9126: sang nge ba rnam pa 'od gsol ba dang rims kyis sa'i tshul med pa'o //
NK022(za)001:9127: lhag ge ba skyon dgu ka spangs pa'o //
NK022(za)001:9128: lhang nge ba'o bya byed la 'gro ba'i dus na yang lhar gsal ba'i brtan pa'i tshad bzhi /
NK022(za)001:9129: mi g.yo ba dran mi dgos pa ma ti la gsal bsgrib med pa'o //
NK022(za)001:9130: gnyid dang rmi lam du yang gsal ba'o //
NK022(za)001:9133: rkyen phra hrag gis ma shigs pa'o //
NK022(za)001:9134: cir yang bsgyur du btub pa'o //
NK022(za)001:9135: sna tshogs su gsal bas shes te sems la dbang bsgyur ba'o //
NK022(za)001:9137: rang du ma zad snang ba thams cad sku /
NK022(za)001:9139: dran rtog thams cad thugs su shes par bya'o //
NK022(za)001:9141: 'gro 'dug za nyal du lha dang mi 'bral lha las ma yengs pa'o //
NK022(za)001:9142: thad ka skyed rims par shes par bya'o //
NK022(za)001:9144: brtson 'grus can mkhar lan byed pa lta bu ste /
NK022(za)001:9147: skad cig gam rims kyis lha bskyed /
NK022(za)001:9150: ye shes sems dpa' snyan gsan dbab /
NK022(za)001:9151: spyan drangs de la mchod bstod byas //
NK022(za)001:9152: bzlas pa byas kyin de ltar sgom //
NK022(za)001:9153: nyams ni lha yi dam lha'i drod rnyed pa'i nyams te /
NK022(za)001:9154: tha ma la lus ngag yid gsum gyi 'dzin pa zad /
NK022(za)001:9155: lha'i sku gsung thugs su gsal lo //
NK022(za)001:9156: lus mi snang yang yi dam lha las ma g.yos so //
NK022(za)001:9157: lus lha'i skur gsal ba'i yon tan bzhi ste sngar
NK022(za)001:9158: gyi bag chags 'thug pa la sogs pa dang gang
NK022(za)001:9159: zag gi bdag med pa 'jug pa dang bsod nams
NK022(za)001:9161: ngag lha'i gsung du gsal ba'i yon tan bzhi bka' mtha' dag ston par 'gyur /
NK022(za)001:9164: chos thams cad sgra bsnyan ltar ro //
NK022(za)001:9165: sems thugs su rgyal ba'i yon tan lnga'o //
NK022(za)001:9166: rnam shes tshogs brgyad ye shes lnga ru gnas 'gyur /
NK022(za)001:9168: da mtshan ma dang cha shas kyi sgom pa mi
NK022(za)001:9169: dgos par dug gsum sku gsung thugs su gsal na
NK022(za)001:9171: kho lus kyi rgya mdud grol ba dang /
NK022(za)001:9172: lha sku phyag chen por gsal /
NK022(za)001:9174: ming las rtsa rlung ste steng sgor sgom pa /
NK022(za)001:9175: gdams ngag las drod dang bde ba sgom pa'i gdams ngag /
NK022(za)001:9176: dper na ra gan gyi 'ju 'dul byed pa lta bu'o //
NK022(za)001:9177: rlung shes dbyer med du shes par byed pa de lta ba /
NK022(za)001:9178: de'i ngang la gnas pa de sgom pa /
NK022(za)001:9179: de dang mthun pa de spyod pa /
NK022(za)001:9180: de las mi 'da' ba de dam tshig go //
NK022(za)001:9181: rtsa dang 'khor lo'i gnas thabs shes pa de gnad /
NK022(za)001:9182: de la rlung gzhang mal byed pa de srog /
NK022(za)001:9183: rlung gzhal mar ma shes pas nad du 'chor ba'i nyen yod de 'phrang yin te gsol ba'o //
NK022(za)001:9184: rtsa dang 'khor lo'i gnas thabs ni g.yas g.yon dbus
NK022(za)001:9185: kyi rtsa gsum mchod rten gyi srog shing gi tshul
NK022(za)001:9186: du yod do // rtsa sgo thams cad de la
NK022(za)001:9187: zug pas 'khor lo bzhi las steng sgom thabs bla
NK022(za)001:9188: du yod do // ma'i zhal lo // snying la 'gro ba rigs drug sa bon dang /
NK022(za)001:9189: +aahmh'u la sogs pa lnga gnas so //
NK022(za)001:9190: de nyams su len lugs la 'og rlung gzhu'i lung
NK022(za)001:9191: lta bu'i mchog ma gnyis la dar dpyangs kyis brlabs
NK022(za)001:9194: ya gis dbus pas ra la me byung nas 'gro mngon yar 'bar te song /
NK022(za)001:9195: a ba du te yar song snying la phog 'gro
NK022(za)001:9196: drug gi sa bon sregs 'das pa'i sa bon gzhu
NK022(za)001:9197: / 'od kyis gang na rji lud pa lta bur gyur /
NK022(za)001:9198: rtsa dang yi ge rnams 'od du zhu /
NK022(za)001:9200: klad la 'od du zhu ste yar mar 'bar bar sgom /
NK022(za)001:9203: rtsa la rlung rgyu rlung la shes pa zhen pas /
NK022(za)001:9204: rlung gi sbyang mal ma shes shing rlung lam du ma slongs na /
NK022(za)001:9205: shes pa lam du ma slongs pas /
NK022(za)001:9206: des na rlung la sbyang mal shes pa gal che zhes so //
NK022(za)001:9207: thad ka ni rtsa rlung thig ler sgom par shes par bya'o //
NK022(za)001:9208: sgom chen gyi 'dul tshul ni 'byung ba dar ba'i byis pa lta bu'o //
NK022(za)001:9209: nyams kyi ltags ni rlung shes rjes su 'gro ldog byed cing lus la drod rnyed pa'i nyams so //
NK022(za)001:9210: rang sa zin pa ni 'byung ba non cing lus kyi nad thon pa na rang sa zin pa'o //
NK022(za)001:9211: 'bras bu ni bde ba chen po'i sku thob pa'o //
NK022(za)001:9212: steng sgo thig le sgom pa /
NK022(za)001:9215: gdams ngag las thig le sgom pa'i gdams ngag /
NK022(za)001:9216: dpe dug la sngags kyis btab pa lta bu'o //
NK022(za)001:9217: sbyor ba la lhan cig skyes pa nges bzung bar 'dod pa de lta ba /
NK022(za)001:9218: de'i ngang la gnas pa de sgom pa /
NK022(za)001:9219: de dang mthun pa de spyod pa /
NK022(za)001:9220: de las mi 'da' bar de dam tshig /
NK022(za)001:9221: mtshan ldan phyag rgya bsten pa de gnad /
NK022(za)001:9222: thig le dbab bzlog la sbyang ba de srog /
NK022(za)001:9223: rang dgar spyad na mngal gyi srin bu'am ro myags kyi 'dam du skye 'phrang yin te gol pa'o //
NK022(za)001:9224: las kyi phyag rgya la gsum ste /
NK022(za)001:9225: rten gang la sbyar ba dang /
NK022(za)001:9227: bde ba chen po nyams su blangs pa'i thabs ni chags pa chung na ltas pas tshim /
NK022(za)001:9228: chags pa che na sbyor ba bya ste byang sems
NK022(za)001:9229: phab la ma shor bar yar nur mar nur byas
NK022(za)001:9230: la sgom / kun rdzob bde ba chen por nyams su blang ba dang /
NK022(za)001:9231: don dam bde ba myong tsam du yang 'dzin pa
NK022(za)001:9232: med de stong zhing bde gsal la ma rtogs pa
NK022(za)001:9233: med par nyams su blang ngo //
NK022(za)001:9234: bde ba chen por nyams su blang ba'o //
NK022(za)001:9235: dus tshod kyi skad ni chos sgo dbang gis 'gags /
NK022(za)001:9238: gdams ngag mi mo la brten nas skye zhes pa'o //
NK022(za)001:9239: thad ka las rgyas par shes par bya'o //
NK022(za)001:9241: mi na so dar la bab pa'i shes pa lta bu'o //
NK022(za)001:9242: nyams myong gi ltags ni 'dod chags bde bar 'khyer ba'i nyams so //
NK022(za)001:9244: dngos po gang rung gcig la brten nas bde bar 'char na rang sa zin pa'o //
NK022(za)001:9245: 'bras bu ni bde ba chen po gsang ba'i sku thob pa'o //
NK022(za)001:9249: // // ming las ye shes kyi ngang bsgom chung ngu /
NK022(za)001:9250: gdams ngag las cog bzhag gi gdams ngag /
NK022(za)001:9251: dpe gar spyin la sbrang la 'dus pa lta bu'o //
NK022(za)001:9252: shes pa snga phyi 'khrul thag chod pa de gnad /
NK022(za)001:9253: sems nang du zin pa de srog /
NK022(za)001:9254: phyi rol snang ba de 'phrang yin te gol sa'o //
NK022(za)001:9255: de yang dus tshod kyi skad 'don pa ni rten can zhig la bzhag /
NK022(za)001:9256: de nas rten ci la yang mi bca' /
NK022(za)001:9257: yul gang la yang mi dmigs /
NK022(za)001:9258: lus ngag khong klod la zhog /
NK022(za)001:9260: ma bkrogs pa'i ri dwags lta bur zhog /
NK022(za)001:9261: chu chad kyi rang thag lta bur zhog /
NK022(za)001:9262: 'ben phigs pa'i mda' lta bur zhog /
NK022(za)001:9263: spyil pa zhig pa lta bur zhog /
NK022(za)001:9264: gar spyin la sbrang ma 'dus pa lta bu zhog /
NK022(za)001:9266: thad ka ngang sgom chung ngur shes par bya'o //
NK022(za)001:9267: sgom chen gyi 'dug tshul bag ma gsar ba lta bu'o //
NK022(za)001:9268: nyams kyi ltags ni nyams su len pa'i dus su sgo lnga'i gzhal cha bkag /
NK022(za)001:9269: yid brtson du bzung shes pa kha nang du ltas nas /
NK022(za)001:9270: blo thim pa mi rtog ltengs so //
NK022(za)001:9271: bde ba skyed med zhi gnas tshan po cha /
NK022(za)001:9275: shes pa 'khum mi nus pa snyam byed /
NK022(za)001:9276: shes pa btang yang mi thongs pa snyam byed pa'o //
NK022(za)001:9278: snang rkyen gyis mi shes pa ste /
NK022(za)001:9279: gzhan gyis gshig pa dang sgrogs bya dgos pa'o //
NK022(za)001:9281: gol na 'du shes med pa'i lhar ltung ngo //
NK022(za)001:9286: // // ming las ye shes kyi ngang sgom 'bring po /
NK022(za)001:9287: gdams ngag las thad kar bstan pa'i gdam ngag /
NK022(za)001:9288: dpe mar me rlung gis ma bskyod pa lta bu'o //
NK022(za)001:9289: sems kyis sems la ltas pas sems ma mthong /
NK022(za)001:9290: blo 'khrul par mthong nas blo'i gdar sha gcod pa de lta ba /
NK022(za)001:9291: ngang la gnas pa de sgom pa /
NK022(za)001:9292: de dang mthun pa de spyod pa /
NK022(za)001:9293: de la 'da' ba med pa de dam tshig /
NK022(za)001:9294: rig pa g.yo 'gul med pa de gnad /
NK022(za)001:9295: rig pa gsal la mi rtog pa de srog /
NK022(za)001:9296: gra bzhir shor na 'phrang yin te gol sa /
NK022(za)001:9297: dus tshod kyi skad 'don pa zhig gces /
NK022(za)001:9298: thad ka'i chos shes pa zhig gces /
NK022(za)001:9299: sgom chen gyi 'dug tshul shes pa zhig gces /
NK022(za)001:9300: bcad ldad sre ba zhig gces /
NK022(za)001:9301: dal bar ngo shes nar ter gtang /
NK022(za)001:9302: brel bar ngo shes dor la btang pa zhig gces /
NK022(za)001:9303: rang sa zin pa zhig gces /
NK022(za)001:9304: sgom chen gyi skye gnas shes pa zhig gces /
NK022(za)001:9309: ma snan pa ma spros pa /
NK022(za)001:9311: so ma lhug pa rang snang dang seng zhog /
NK022(za)001:9313: thad ka ye shes kyi ngang 'bring por shes par bya /
NK022(za)001:9314: sgom chen gyi 'dug tshul bye chung zhig khung chags pa lta bu /
NK022(za)001:9315: nyams kyi ltang stong rang shar gyi nyams /
NK022(za)001:9316: bcad ldang bya ba dang sangs sgom pa'o //
NK022(za)001:9317: phye chu sre ba'i rjes la dge sbyor byas kyin sems can gyi don du bsngo ba'o //
NK022(za)001:9318: brel ba ngo shes dor ba ni zhi gnas so //
NK022(za)001:9319: dal ba ngo shes nar btang ba ni dngas sangs 'di nar btang ba'o //
NK022(za)001:9320: ye shes kyi ngang sgom 'bring po'i dus su gsal gdab pa'i thabs dang /
NK022(za)001:9322: gsal thebs drod pa'i rtags so //
NK022(za)001:9324: rang nyams kyis gsal gdab pa dang /
NK022(za)001:9325: lung tshig zab mo'i gsal bdab pa'o //
NK022(za)001:9326: sgo lnga'i dbang po sa le la /
NK022(za)001:9327: yid kyi 'dzin pa ma zhugs na //
NK022(za)001:9328: sems kyi bzhag thabs legs pa yin //
NK022(za)001:9329: sgo lnga'i rnam shes kyi rjes su yid kyis ma
NK022(za)001:9330: bslad par gsal la rtog pa med pa de ye
NK022(za)001:9331: shes so // lus sems phyi bsdam khong klod kyin gda' tsam gsal 'debs pa'i dpe ni /
NK022(za)001:9332: sgeg mo me long blta ba bzhin //
NK022(za)001:9333: yang lta yang lta sems la ltos //
NK022(za)001:9334: spang la g.yang mo skyong pa bzhin //
NK022(za)001:9335: yang skyong yang skyong sems la skyong //
NK022(za)001:9336: byis pa sgong tshang nyul ba bzhin //
NK022(za)001:9337: yang nyul yang nyul sems la nyul //
NK022(za)001:9339: mtshan mar snang ba'i 'dzin pa thams cad rgyun chad /
NK022(za)001:9340: blo don thog tu yal yid nam mkha' ltar du
NK022(za)001:9341: dag nas blo bde lhan ni brtsig byung na yin
NK022(za)001:9342: no // de yang rnam rtog mi rgyu bas bde ba /
NK022(za)001:9343: sgom bya med pas mi rtog pa /
NK022(za)001:9344: snga phyi la sogs 'dogs su ma shor bas mi g.yo ba /
NK022(za)001:9345: bde ba gsal la mi rtog pas bying sa le ba /
NK022(za)001:9346: mi rtog pa dang mi g.yo bas rgod pa sel ba /
NK022(za)001:9348: lus med pa snyam byed pa /
NK022(za)001:9349: dbugs phyi nang rgyu ba mi tshor ba snyam byed /
NK022(za)001:9351: gcig pur 'dug kyang skyo ba med pa /
NK022(za)001:9352: bya rgyu med kyang zin pa snyam byed /
NK022(za)001:9353: grub rgyu med kyang no tshi ba snyam byed /
NK022(za)001:9354: rnyed pa med par nyams dga' ba /
NK022(za)001:9356: rig pa 'od gsal gyi nyams 'ong ste /
NK022(za)001:9357: nyams rang grol du bskyang ngo //
NK022(za)001:9358: de yang rjes thob kyi shes pa la drod rtags su brjod pa las /
NK022(za)001:9359: sgom rang gi ngo bo 'di ltar yin zhes brjod par mi nus te /
NK022(za)001:9360: mig tsam zhes dran rig shes pa ma 'gags la /
NK022(za)001:9361: 'dzin rig yul las rnam par grol /
NK022(za)001:9363: ming tsam de la sgom zhes btags ces 'khor ba rtsad gcod las so //
NK022(za)001:9365: phyogs gcig nas ming btags na thad ka'i gdams ngag ngos bzung ba yin la /
NK022(za)001:9366: gnad ni blo bzhag thabs yin /
NK022(za)001:9367: srog ni sgom pa'i ngo bo yin /
NK022(za)001:9368: 'phrang ni bying dgod yin pas bcos thabs dang nad kyi 'du ba dus tshod kyi sgom thabs dang /
NK022(za)001:9369: thun tshad dang las dang po pas 'di la goms par bya'o //
NK022(za)001:9370: 'di ma brtan bar du snang rkyen gyis yengs nas
NK022(za)001:9371: 'gro bas dgon pa bsten cing gcig pur bsdad dgos
NK022(za)001:9372: so // smra bcad byas na mtshams kyi mchog tu gsungs so //
NK022(za)001:9373: thun mtshams su dge sbyor phri le bya'o //
NK022(za)001:9374: rang sa zin pa ni nam sgom pa dang gsal na rang sa zin pa'o //
NK022(za)001:9376: 'di la 'tshang ma rgyas kyang phyi ma la sangs rgyas te /
NK022(za)001:9377: rgyal po grong srang du shor bas rgyal sa ma zin kyang /
NK022(za)001:9378: rigs bzang mo chung mar bslangs te bus rgyal sa 'dzin pa bzhin no //
NK022(za)001:9379: lta ba dum bur rtogs pas sgrib pa thams cad rtsad nas 'byang bar gsungs so //
NK022(za)001:9380: phyogs bcu rgyas pa'i mdo las /
NK022(za)001:9382: drang por 'dug la yang dag ltos //
NK022(za)001:9383: yang dag nyid la yang dag lta //
NK022(za)001:9384: yang dag mthong na rnam par grol //
NK022(za)001:9385: de ni 'gyod tshangs mchog yin no //
NK022(za)001:9387: rtogs pa'i don la brtan pa ma thob kyang /
NK022(za)001:9388: phyi sa la skye ba mi len par gsungs so //
NK022(za)001:9390: tha ma phyi rol brtas pas brjed //
NK022(za)001:9391: dus tshod rkyen dang phrad pa'i tshe //
NK022(za)001:9392: skad cig zur tsam bda' yis ni //
NK022(za)001:9393: the tshom med par don rtogs nas //
NK022(za)001:9394: skye ba gcig gis sangs rgyas 'grub //
NK022(za)001:9396: chos nyid lam du nyams su len //
NK022(za)001:9401: bar 'dir rmi lam kha bsgyur ba yod do //
NK022(za)001:9406: yang ming las ye shes kyi ngang sgom chen po /
NK022(za)001:9407: gdams ngag las thog babs kyi gdams ngag /
NK022(za)001:9408: dpe skyes bu nad kyis gdungs pa lta bu /
NK022(za)001:9409: yid chags sdang la ma spros par nges shes pa de lta ba /
NK022(za)001:9410: ngang las gnas pa sgom pa /
NK022(za)001:9411: de dang ma bral ba spyod pa /
NK022(za)001:9412: de las mi 'da' ba dam tshig yid chags sdang
NK022(za)001:9413: gi bsam sbyor ngan pa mi byed pa de gnad
NK022(za)001:9414: / chags sdang la ma spros par gsal ba rgya che ba de srog /
NK022(za)001:9415: gu yangs na gsal te yong /
NK022(za)001:9416: tha mal du shor ba ma tshor ba de 'phrang ngo //
NK022(za)001:9417: 'di la yang gces pa brgyad ngang sgom 'bring po dang 'dra /
NK022(za)001:9421: sna tshogs snang ba rig pa'i nyams dpe dran pa bsten pa gces /
NK022(za)001:9422: dran cing rig pa rang sar yal //
NK022(za)001:9423: des na ngo yis zin pa gces //
NK022(za)001:9424: don du gnyer cig rigs kyi bu //
NK022(za)001:9425: dran pa bsten cig rang sar zhog /
NK022(za)001:9426: bya bral nam mkha'i ngang la sgom //
NK022(za)001:9427: mi sgom na'ang cer tsam lta //
NK022(za)001:9428: nyon mongs rang dngas nam mkha'i sprin dang 'dra //
NK022(za)001:9429: byung tshor rang grol sbrul gyi mdud pa 'dra //
NK022(za)001:9431: thad ka ngang sgom chen po sgom chen gyi 'dug tshul ni /
NK022(za)001:9432: gcong can gyi nad pa lta bu'o //
NK022(za)001:9433: kho sgom sgom mi 'dra ste yid chos gnyis las ma yengs pa'o //
NK022(za)001:9434: nyams myong ni dran pa dus mtshungs kyi nyams so //
NK022(za)001:9437: dran pa rang stongs su yal ba'o //
NK022(za)001:9438: brel ba ngo shes dor ba ni /
NK022(za)001:9439: yid sgom bya sgom byed dor ba'o //
NK022(za)001:9440: dal ba ngo shes nar gyis thong ni /
NK022(za)001:9446: dpe ni nam mkha'i glog gam /
NK022(za)001:9447: gnad du phebs pa'i sems sdug can nam ming yang dran pa skyes pa ltar bsten no //
NK022(za)001:9448: drod ni gnyen po zhib mo'i rgyun gyis ma bkrol bar yul sems thug phrad du thur skyed /
NK022(za)001:9449: dur thu rtu yan chu dang 'o ma 'dres pa bzhin rang sar yan /
NK022(za)001:9450: blo bde lhan lhan gyur na nyams kyi drod yin /
NK022(za)001:9451: nyams ni ci la yang blo mi chags rtsol grub byed snying mi 'dod /
NK022(za)001:9456: nyams la res ci 'char res ci 'char 'ong ste
NK022(za)001:9457: gzhan gyis ltas tsa na bcos ma'am bcos chung du
NK022(za)001:9459: gzhan gyis zhub pa med par byed snying 'dod pa /
NK022(za)001:9460: rang gi nyams dang sbyar bar bya'o //
NK022(za)001:9461: rang kha mar byas na tha mal par 'chor bas chos nyid dang mi 'bral bar dgos so //
NK022(za)001:9462: dus der nyams tshan po che skyes pa bya ba yin te /
NK022(za)001:9463: gnas lugs ji lta ba lhag rtogs nas de yang yal nas 'gro /
NK022(za)001:9464: nyams thog nas bzlas pa byas na bar chod sel ba yin /
NK022(za)001:9465: tshogs dang gtor ma byas na byin brlabs 'byung ba yin /
NK022(za)001:9466: de yang zhen med 'dod med du bya'o //
NK022(za)001:9467: dus der rkyen sna tshogs la sbyang ste /
NK022(za)001:9469: rgyal khams su phyin gyin lta /
NK022(za)001:9470: nyon mongs pa slang gin lta /
NK022(za)001:9471: 'jigs pa dang mi gtsang ba dang yul bzang ngan
NK022(za)001:9472: 'gal rkyen thams cad la sems yongs su bcug gin
NK022(za)001:9473: lta / nyams la phan gnod thams cad la nyams su byung rgyal du bsten la sbyong /
NK022(za)001:9474: de tsam ma shes na dge sbyor dmigs dang bcas pa bya /
NK022(za)001:9475: chags sdang dmigs gtad dang bcas pa spang ngo //
NK022(za)001:9476: rang la rtogs pa'i nyams med na bka' brgyud kyi
NK022(za)001:9477: rjes su 'brengs la lus ngag gi dge sbyor la
NK022(za)001:9478: 'bad pa bya / thad ka'i 'bras bu mi bslu nges pa'o //
NK022(za)001:9479: rang sa zin pa ni yengs kyang mi sto yo /
NK022(za)001:9480: sgom chen de'i skye gnas ni /
NK022(za)001:9481: nyin bar dang rmi lam 'chi ka dang nyams su blangs pas bar do rang sa zin no //
NK022(za)001:9483: ma sgoms kyang chos nyid dang ma bral ba /
NK022(za)001:9484: sgom kyang de la bgos sngon du med pa /
NK022(za)001:9485: rmi lam gyi rnam grangs ma 'gyur kyang ting nge
NK022(za)001:9486: 'dzin rgyal po grong srang du shor ba ni gzhug
NK022(za)001:9487: tu ngos zin rgyal sar bton pa dang /
NK022(za)001:9488: rgyal chos mi shes te blon pos slabs pas rgas
NK022(za)001:9489: khar rgyal chos shes nas rgyal sa 'dzin pa ltar
NK022(za)001:9490: du ngo shes pa yod kyang rkyen grag zhan thams
NK022(za)001:9493: gnad gcod kyi zug zer nyams len du blangs so //
NK022(za)001:9494: des bar ma dor shes pa dngos med la rang
NK022(za)001:9495: sa zin pa'am skye gnas la rang dbang thob pa'o
NK022(za)001:9496: // ye shes kyi ngang sgom chen po /
NK022(za)001:9500: // // bla ma dam pa rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK022(za)001:9501: yang ming las a ti lta thag /
NK022(za)001:9502: gdams ngag las rig pa rtsal gyi dbang bskur ba'i man ngag /
NK022(za)001:9503: dpe rin po che gser gyi gling du phyin pa lta bu /
NK022(za)001:9505: nyon mongs pa slang gin lta /
NK022(za)001:9506: 'jigs pa dang mi gtsang ba dang yul bzang ngan
NK022(za)001:9507: 'gal rkyen thams cad la sems yengs su bcug giin
NK022(za)001:9508: lta'o // gnyis med kyi ye shes rang shar ba de lta ba /
NK022(za)001:9509: de'i ngang la gnas pa de sgom pa /
NK022(za)001:9510: de dang mi 'bral ba spyod pa /
NK022(za)001:9511: de las mi 'da' ba de dam tshig gi /
NK022(za)001:9512: cer cer lta tur tur dran par bya mi dgos pa de gnad /
NK022(za)001:9513: mtshan mar 'dzin rtsol rang sar grol ba de srog /
NK022(za)001:9514: rang gi mtshan nyid ma rtogs par tshig phyir 'brengs
NK022(za)001:9515: nas spyi mtshan du shor na rtol chos lhug par
NK022(za)001:9517: 'dir yang gces pa brgyad la bcad ldad bya /
NK022(za)001:9518: phye chu sre ba'i la mi rtsi /
NK022(za)001:9519: bdun po ngang sgom chen pos 'dre /
NK022(za)001:9520: dus tshod kyi snang ba la ngos bzung med /
NK022(za)001:9522: gsal la ma 'dres nam mkha'i gzha' tshon /
NK022(za)001:9523: spyod la ma chags chu zla'i dal /
NK022(za)001:9524: 'khrul pa brtsad bcad rma bya'i mdongs 'dra /
NK022(za)001:9525: ye shes rang snang 'dam gyi pad+ma 'dra /
NK022(za)001:9526: de bzhin du rnam grangs kyi chos rang byung ye shes su ngo shes /
NK022(za)001:9527: shes lugs chu la ral gri rgyab pa ltar du rjes med du shes /
NK022(za)001:9528: de ka bza' btad med pa'i lta ba yang de yin /
NK022(za)001:9529: dmigs gtad med pa'i sgom pa yang de yin /
NK022(za)001:9530: blang dor med pa'i spyod pa yang de yin /
NK022(za)001:9531: spang thob med pa'i 'bras bu yang de yin /
NK022(za)001:9532: lta ba lta rgyu yod med kyi mtshan ma yang rang sar grol /
NK022(za)001:9533: de yang ye grol sgom pa dang spyod pa des 'dre /
NK022(za)001:9534: de lta bu des yod ces sgros mi 'dogs /
NK022(za)001:9536: de lta bu gcig tu rtogs shing shes pa'i mi
NK022(za)001:9537: de 'khor 'das thams cad sems la rdzogs pas rdzogs
NK022(za)001:9539: shes ma thag tu shes pa dang bral nas 'dug
NK022(za)001:9540: na rtogs thob dus cig tu smin pa bya ba
NK022(za)001:9541: yin no // da mi de la lta ba bsar mi dgos /
NK022(za)001:9546: da dung du lta ba phyogs ris med par rtogs pa bsnyam byed kyang /
NK022(za)001:9547: zhen pa dang ma bral bar 'dug na lta ba gsar dgos /
NK022(za)001:9550: dran pa'i tshe dran pa dngos med cig dgos /
NK022(za)001:9551: goms shing rtogs pa de lta ba /
NK022(za)001:9552: rtsol ba can gyi lam la goms par byas pa
NK022(za)001:9553: bya ba yin te nyams su blangs pas 'byung ngo
NK022(za)001:9554: // bar der bya ba gtongs phod na rtogs pa yin /
NK022(za)001:9555: zhen 'dod rang grol du song na bde ba yin /
NK022(za)001:9556: khong du chud na yid ches pa yin /
NK022(za)001:9557: gzhan la ston na gdams ngag yin /
NK022(za)001:9558: rtogs pas bdag bsgral nas thugs rjes gzhan sgrol ba yin /
NK022(za)001:9559: thad ka ni a ti lta thag bcad par shes par bya'o //
NK022(za)001:9560: sgom chen gyi 'dug tshul ni gdon ma zhugs pa'i smyon pa lta bu zhig yong /
NK022(za)001:9561: nyams kyi ltang ni shes bya chig chod kyi nyams 'char ro //
NK022(za)001:9562: dran pa sems kyi shar ba yin pas 'brel bar ngo shes na la dor ba'o //
NK022(za)001:9563: dal bar ngo shes na lta ba'i ngang nar re gtang ngo //
NK022(za)001:9565: gsal thebs pa'i ngo bo ni phyi nang gi chos
NK022(za)001:9566: thams cad rang rig pa'i mngon sum du gsal zhing
NK022(za)001:9567: rig pa las gzhan med par rtogs na snang bas
NK022(za)001:9568: mi skyon pa zhes bya ste /
NK022(za)001:9569: de tsam na khal cig gi rna sun gcig gis ma 'gegs /
NK022(za)001:9570: g.yag rna lug gis ma bsgyil /
NK022(za)001:9571: gdams ngag gi re hrul du bkra shis kyi mkhar rtsigs /
NK022(za)001:9572: yugs sa mo sman du bdur ba'i lta ba zhes bya /
NK022(za)001:9575: rgod na rgod du bas bying na bying du bas /
NK022(za)001:9580: zhen pa chos nyid du bzlog /
NK022(za)001:9584: ci byed kyang mi bde ba skad cig kyang med /
NK022(za)001:9585: ci mthong ci snang thams cad ci dran thams cad ye shes su 'char ro //
NK022(za)001:9586: rang mtshan ma rtogs te tshig la gdeng byas na
NK022(za)001:9587: kheng grags don du gnyer zhing sdig pa la bag
NK022(za)001:9588: med par spyod na dmyal bar skye bar gsungs so
NK022(za)001:9589: // yul thams cad 'dir grogs su 'char te phan par byed na ched du bsten rgyu med do //
NK022(za)001:9590: mnyam bzhag dang rjes thob med don rang sa zin pa yin /
NK022(za)001:9591: sgom chen de'i skye gnas ni /
NK022(za)001:9592: dper na rgyal po grong sprang du song ba ngos zin te rgyal sar bton pa dang /
NK022(za)001:9593: rgyal chos slabs pas shes pa dang /
NK022(za)001:9594: sngon goms pa'i stobs kyis sprang po'i shom ras 'ong ba ltar du /
NK022(za)001:9596: bag chags phra mo rgyu bas lus dang ma bral
NK022(za)001:9597: bar du bza' bgo'i rtog pa bag re 'ong ste
NK022(za)001:9598: / shi nas lus dang bral ma thag sangs rgyas so //
NK022(za)001:9600: 'phur bya'i bya ni sgong chags mkha' la 'gro //
NK022(za)001:9605: // // ming las rdzogs pa chen po bya rtsol dang bral ba /
NK022(za)001:9606: gdams ngag las klong du gyur pa'i gdams ngag /
NK022(za)001:9607: dpe rgya mtsho'i gting gi chu lta bu /
NK022(za)001:9608: 'dir sgom la sogs pa mi rtsi /
NK022(za)001:9609: lta sgom gyi mdzad spyod dang bral ba de gnad /
NK022(za)001:9610: dus thams cad du nga dang bdag med phyogs dang
NK022(za)001:9611: ris med mnyam pa'i klong na phyad de ba srog
NK022(za)001:9612: / ngang chung ngus dpe chad lta zhu bar 'chor nyen yod /
NK022(za)001:9614: 'dir thos bsam las byung kyang rung /
NK022(za)001:9615: gdams ngag las byung kyang rung ste /
NK022(za)001:9616: dper na rgyal bu rmangs su 'khyam pa ngos bzung
NK022(za)001:9617: nas rgyal sar bton pas rgyal sa zin pa ltar
NK022(za)001:9618: rtogs thob dus gcig tu smin pas da dran par
NK022(za)001:9619: bya mi dgos / lhangs kyis rtogs /
NK022(za)001:9622: yengs pas gnod pa ma bskyal /
NK022(za)001:9623: ma yengs pas phan ma btags /
NK022(za)001:9624: yar re ba'i spyod pa byed mkhan kyang med /
NK022(za)001:9625: mar dgos pa'i spyod pa byed mkhan kyang med /
NK022(za)001:9628: de tsa na rtsis bdab las 'das te /
NK022(za)001:9629: rtsis gdab ma byas pa ma phyin par song ba'o //
NK022(za)001:9630: thad ka klong du gyur par shes par bya'o //
NK022(za)001:9631: sgom chen gyi 'dug stangs srog ma bcad pa'i nyams kyi ltangs spyad pa chen po'o //
NK022(za)001:9632: mnyam bzhag rjes thob med pa'i spyad pa dang /
NK022(za)001:9633: bskyon yul du mi lta ba'i phyad pa chen po las 'dir 'og ma'o //
NK022(za)001:9634: de yang dga' rab rdo rjes /
NK022(za)001:9635: 'jam dpal bshes gnyen las bsam gtan las /
NK022(za)001:9636: yang rabs snang srid rig pa'i klong du shar nas ni /
NK022(za)001:9637: snang ba shar bas mun pa log pa dang /
NK022(za)001:9638: gnyis med shar bas gzung 'dzin log pa dang /
NK022(za)001:9639: gcig tu rtogs pas re dogs log pa dang /
NK022(za)001:9640: mnyam nyid log pas dgag bsgrub log pa dang /
NK022(za)001:9641: lhun grub rtogs pas bya rtsol log pa dang /
NK022(za)001:9642: gsang sngags 'bras bu thob ces de la bya //
NK022(za)001:9644: dper na nyi ma'i snying po shar ba dang /
NK022(za)001:9645: zer gyis mun pa sel ba dang /
NK022(za)001:9646: 'od kyis kun la khyab pas dus gsum mnyam /
NK022(za)001:9647: mi rtog klong du brdal ba dang /
NK022(za)001:9648: dag pa'i snang ba shar ba dang /
NK022(za)001:9649: bdag tu 'dzin pa'i srog chad pa gsum dus mnyam /
NK022(za)001:9650: chos sku klong na gsal ba dang /
NK022(za)001:9651: longs sku rang la gsal ba dang /
NK022(za)001:9652: sprul sku 'gro ba 'dul ba gsum dus mnyam /
NK022(za)001:9655: byin brlabs 'byung ba gsum dus mnyam /
NK022(za)001:9656: rtsal chen drang ngo gnyis can thams cad zad /
NK022(za)001:9657: des gnyis med du sgom pa min /
NK022(za)001:9659: des na btsal mi dgos kyi shes pa rtsi mi dgos kyi spyod /
NK022(za)001:9660: yengs ba med pa'i dam tshig /
NK022(za)001:9662: dmigs pa med pa'i thugs rje /
NK022(za)001:9663: rtal med rtol med des 'khor 'das thams cad sems su rtogs la /
NK022(za)001:9664: sems ngos ris las grol nas lta bas dgos pa mi gada'o //
NK022(za)001:9665: de nyid dran rig tu shar kyang der 'dzin dang bral na sgom pas dgos pa mi gada'o //
NK022(za)001:9666: mtshan mas rgyas thebs shing ci spyad kyang rang grol du rtogs na spyod pas dgos pa mi gada'o //
NK022(za)001:9667: yang dag chen po dang ldan zhing srungs mtshams kyi
NK022(za)001:9668: rtog pa las grol na dam tshig gis dgos pa
NK022(za)001:9669: mi gada'o // rang sems chos skur rtogs shing re
NK022(za)001:9670: dogs kyis rtsol grub las grol na 'bras bu las
NK022(za)001:9676: rang don chos sku thob nas de'i byin brlabs gzugs
NK022(za)001:9677: sku gnyis su snang nas 'gro don byed pa 'byung
NK022(za)001:9678: ngo // a ti lta thag man chod ni gzhi snang gi dus so //
NK022(za)001:9679: gzhi snang gi dus su dad pa kun nas dge
NK022(za)001:9680: bcu bzang po'i rtsol 'dzin gyis 'khor bar bde 'gror
NK022(za)001:9681: 'khor bar 'khor / mi dge ba bcus ngan song du ngan 'gror 'khor ro //
NK022(za)001:9682: mi g.yo ba'i ting nge 'dzin gyis khams gong ma gnyis su 'khor ro //
NK022(za)001:9683: de gsum gyis gzhi las sa bon bzhag pas so //
NK022(za)001:9684: lam pa rnams gzhi la nyams su len te /
NK022(za)001:9685: gzhi phyogs ris las ma mthong bas /
NK022(za)001:9686: phyogs re la ngos 'dzin byas pas shes rab che chung byung ste /
NK022(za)001:9687: de ka theg pa che chung ngo //
NK022(za)001:9688: phyogs re de las dam mthong ngo //
NK022(za)001:9689: klong du gyur pa ni gzhi dang lam gyi nyes pa zad pa ste /
NK022(za)001:9690: de gnyis su 'dzin pa'i bdag 'dzin med pas so //
NK022(za)001:9691: des mtshams phye la lus ngag gi chos spyod nas /
NK022(za)001:9692: a ti man chad rang rang gi rtogs pa ngos lon du bcug la /
NK022(za)001:9693: rang rang gi rtogs pa ltar goms par bya /
NK022(za)001:9694: brtan par byas kyin gong ma gong ma la 'jug go //
NK022(za)001:9695: gol sgrib brdar sha bcad pa'i lung khrol bu zhes bya'o //
NK022(za)001:9696: nyams su len pa'i theg pa rim pa dgu zhes kyang bya /
NK022(za)001:9697: khams gsum 'khor sgom byang chub lam sgom yang dag pa'i sgom zhes kyang bya /
NK022(za)001:9700: shes bya drug skor gyi bshad thabs dang /
NK022(za)001:9701: dbang rim par bskur ba bkras gdang lta bu'i man ngag zhes kyang bya /
NK022(za)001:9702: 'gro nyal 'dug bsdod du nyams su blang /
NK022(za)001:9703: 'khor ba yongs kyi sems can la blo zhog /
NK022(za)001:9704: dga' rab rdo rje'i snyan rgyud la /
NK022(za)001:9705: sangs rgyas ye shes rin po ches zhabs thog tu mdzad pa rdzogs so //
NK022(za)001:9708: // // 'di gsang dbang mdo la bskur ba legs /
NK022(za)001:9709: dpal rdo rje sems dpal la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK022(za)001:9710: gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa chen po'i sgor zhugs pa'i rnal 'byor pas /
NK022(za)001:9711: tshe 'di nyid la de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku gsung
NK022(za)001:9712: thugs kyi dngos grub thob par 'dod pa rnams kyis
NK022(za)001:9717: nyams su ting nge 'dzin las blang /
NK022(za)001:9718: de ni lung dang man ngag rtsad bcad de sgrub dgos pas /
NK022(za)001:9719: dbang mi bskur du yang mi rung la mi nod du yang mi rung ste /
NK022(za)001:9720: bskur na ji ltar bskur zhe na /
NK022(za)001:9721: rdo rje rgyal po chen por dbang bskur na phyi nang gsang ba gsum gyis dbang bskur /
NK022(za)001:9722: gsang sngags nang gi slob dpon la nang gi dbang bskur /
NK022(za)001:9723: sngags kri ya'i slob dpon la phyi'i dbang bskur /
NK022(za)001:9724: 'chad par 'dod pa la rkang pa'i 'og tu 'khor lo gding /
NK022(za)001:9725: lag tu dung 'bud du bzhugs pa'i dbang tsam bskur /
NK022(za)001:9726: thos pa bsag par 'dod pa la po tis dbang bskur /
NK022(za)001:9727: dbang don dgos pa ni lung las /
NK022(za)001:9728: slob dpon mnyes par ma byas shing //
NK022(za)001:9729: zhes pa la sogs pa dang /
NK022(za)001:9731: so ma btang ba'i rdzas spyod dang //
NK022(za)001:9732: sgyid ma rtas par khal 'gyed dang //
NK022(za)001:9733: dbang ma nod par bka' rdzogs pa //
NK022(za)001:9734: tshul bstan tsam gyi brlag par byed //
NK022(za)001:9735: ces pas dbang mi nod du mi rung ste /
NK022(za)001:9736: dang po rgyud nas byung ba bzhin du yon dbul /
NK022(za)001:9737: rdzogs par 'dod na dang po la phyi'i dbang bskur te /
NK022(za)001:9739: de nas rdo rje dbyings chen po'i dkyil 'khor bzhes su gsol /
NK022(za)001:9740: bsnyen pa zhag gsum byas te thon khar dbang bskur /
NK022(za)001:9743: slob dpon gyi zhabs gnyis la 'ju ru bcug la 'di skad do //
NK022(za)001:9744: byang chub rdo rje sangs rgyas la //
NK022(za)001:9745: mchod cing ji ltar bgyis pa ltar //
NK022(za)001:9746: bdag kyang rab tu bsgral ba'i phyir //
NK022(za)001:9747: nam mkha'i rdo rje bdag la gsol //
NK022(za)001:9749: khyod ni dga' ba ci la dga' //
NK022(za)001:9751: bdag ni skal ldan rab bden pas //
NK022(za)001:9752: rab dges 'phrul la bdag dad de //
NK022(za)001:9753: mchog tu dga' la bdag dga' 'o //
NK022(za)001:9755: sangs rgyas dag ni thams cad kyis //
NK022(za)001:9756: rdo rje gsang ba gsum las byung //
NK022(za)001:9757: khams gsum kun gyis phyag byas pa //
NK022(za)001:9758: dbang bskur gnang ba chen po sbyin //
NK022(za)001:9759: de nas lag tu me tog gtad la /
NK022(za)001:9761: rdo rje ye shes thob byed pa'i /
NK022(za)001:9762: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi //
NK022(za)001:9764: bdag gi slob ma bzhug par bya //
NK022(za)001:9765: slob mas gdong g.yogs kyis bkab la me tog dor du bzhugs pa ni /
NK022(za)001:9766: de ring dad pa'i shugs kyis ni //
NK022(za)001:9767: dkyil 'khor dam pa blta bar bya //
NK022(za)001:9769: slob dpon gyis sngags dang phyag rgyas byin rlabs nas /
NK022(za)001:9770: dngos grub thams cad thob byed cing //
NK022(za)001:9771: dam tshig mchog tu grub par byed //
NK022(za)001:9772: badz+ra tsak+shu pra be sha ya phata ces dbye /
NK022(za)001:9773: dkyil 'khor gyi lha gang la babs pa bstan /
NK022(za)001:9774: dkyil 'khor gyi rang bzhin dang yon tan kyang bshad la slob mas lha de la phyag 'tshal /
NK022(za)001:9775: phyi nang gi mchod pas mchod la /
NK022(za)001:9776: de nas slob ma shar sgor bzhag /
NK022(za)001:9777: slob dpon nub sgor seng khri'i steng du 'dzegs te phyogs bzhir lha phyag 'tshal thal mo sbyar te /
NK022(za)001:9778: na mo bdag slob dpon ming 'di zhes bya bas /
NK022(za)001:9779: slob ma 'di zhes bya ba la dbang bskur bar 'tshal gyis /
NK022(za)001:9780: bcom ldan 'das ye shes kyi gtso bo khyed rnams kyis /
NK022(za)001:9781: de bzhin gshegs pa'i dbang bcu bskur ba'i rim pa bzhin du bskur zhing byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK022(za)001:9782: slob mas shar sgo nas dkyil 'khor gyi lha dang slob dpon la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK022(za)001:9783: slob dpon gyis sangs rgyas kun gyi rdo rje'i dbang /
NK022(za)001:9784: de ring khyod la bskur bar bya //
NK022(za)001:9785: sangs rgyas kun tu rab bsgrub phyir //
NK022(za)001:9786: rdo rje 'di ni khyod kyis zung //
NK022(za)001:9787: zhes dkyil 'khor gyi dbus su bzhag la /
NK022(za)001:9788: dbang rdzas gang gis dbang bskur ba de slob dpon gyi lag tu thogs la bskur /
NK022(za)001:9789: bskur ba'i rting la gang dbang bskur ba'i slob ma'i lag tu rim pa bzhin du gtad /
NK022(za)001:9790: slob ma de man+dala gyi steng na 'khor lo bsgyur ba'i rgyal po'i cha lugs su bcug /
NK022(za)001:9791: lag tu me tog phreng ba'am rin po che'i phreng ba thogs te mig btsum pa'i tshul du bya /
NK022(za)001:9792: slob dpon gyis gser gyi thur ma mdun du thogs la /
NK022(za)001:9793: sngon gyi mig mkhan rgyal po yis //
NK022(za)001:9794: ma rig ling thog gsal ba ltar //
NK022(za)001:9795: bu khyod kyis ni mi shes pa'i //
NK022(za)001:9796: ling thog rgyal ba rnams kyis bsal //
NK022(za)001:9797: badz+ra tsak+shu pra be sha phata kyis mig phye ste /
NK022(za)001:9798: phreng ba de phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba'i zhing khams rnams la gtor ba bsam ste bar snang la gtor /
NK022(za)001:9799: mig phye bas rgyal ba'i zhing khams mthong bar bsam /
NK022(za)001:9802: ma rig pa'i ling thog bsal te shes rab kyi spyan dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK022(za)001:9803: thur ma yang slob ma'i lag tu gtad /
NK022(za)001:9804: slob dpon gyis phreng ba de gang babs pa'i sa nas lcags kyus blangs te /
NK022(za)001:9805: slob ma'i spyi bor bzhag ste sgrib pa sbyang /
NK022(za)001:9806: ngan song las thar bar bya ba'i phyir de bzhin
NK022(za)001:9807: gshegs pa'i sku gsung thugs su byin gyis brlabs te
NK022(za)001:9808: / rdo rje rtse lnga pa'i phyag rgya bcas bcings la spyi bor gtugs la /
NK022(za)001:9809: pra ti n+ri ti sarba a pa ra ni h'u phata /
NK022(za)001:9810: pad+ma'i phyag rgya bcings te lkog mar gtad la /
NK022(za)001:9811: bi tra ba byi tra ba ya /
NK022(za)001:9812: sarba a pa y+aa sarba a pa ra ni h'u phata /
NK022(za)001:9813: 'khor lo'i rgya lte bar gtugs la /
NK022(za)001:9814: 'bu ta ka ya sarba ka ya ni h'u phata /
NK022(za)001:9815: rtog sgrib dag par bya ba'i phyir /
NK022(za)001:9816: da ha la sogs pa ngan song sbyong ba'i sngags gsum po yang bzlas /
NK022(za)001:9817: de nas me long thogs la /
NK022(za)001:9818: chos kun gzugs brnyan lta bu ste //
NK022(za)001:9819: rten 'brel mthu las snang ba'i phyir //
NK022(za)001:9820: brjod med rang bzhin dag pas na //
NK022(za)001:9821: don dam chos nyid brjod par 'gyur //
NK022(za)001:9823: tshe dang ldan pa khyed la me long gi dbang bskur bas /
NK022(za)001:9824: chos thams cad gzugs brnyan ltar rten 'brel sgyu ma
NK022(za)001:9825: ltar mthong ba'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig
NK022(za)001:9826: / 'khor lo rkang pa'i 'og tu bcug la /
NK022(za)001:9828: brjid pa'i don du 'bru bkod nas //
NK022(za)001:9829: gzhan don 'di la phan pa'i phyir //
NK022(za)001:9831: badz+ra tsakra a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK022(za)001:9832: 'khor los dbang bskur bas 'khor los bsgyur ba'i rgyal tshabs thob par gyur cig /
NK022(za)001:9834: chos dung rgyas pa bus nas ni //
NK022(za)001:9835: 'jig rten sems can skal ldan la //
NK022(za)001:9836: rna bsal sdig sbyangs chos thob pa'i //
NK022(za)001:9837: skyob pa'i mgon pos tshangs skad sgrogs //
NK022(za)001:9839: dung gi dbang bskur bas tshangs pa'i sgra skad phun
NK022(za)001:9840: sum tshogs pa sgrogs pa'i dbang thob par gyur cig
NK022(za)001:9842: rdo rje 'di ni sna tshogs te //
NK022(za)001:9843: las rnams rgya mtshos dbang bskur gyis //
NK022(za)001:9844: de ring phan chad bu khyod kyis //
NK022(za)001:9845: 'gro ba'i don la brtson par gyis //
NK022(za)001:9846: badz+ra karma a b+hi shiny+tsa a /
NK022(za)001:9847: rgya gram gyi dbang bskur bas phyogs bcu nas sngags
NK022(za)001:9848: 'chang rnams kyis rtag tu srung ba'i dbang dam pa
NK022(za)001:9851: slob ma'i spyi bor ma las nyi ma'i steng du /
NK022(za)001:9858: badz+ra ra ga ra ti hri /
NK022(za)001:9867: rgyal ba sangs rgyas kun 'dus pas //
NK022(za)001:9868: gzi byin rigs lnga rgyal ba'i dbu //
NK022(za)001:9869: bu khyod gtsug na nor bu 'bar //
NK022(za)001:9871: dbu rgyan gyis dbang bskur bas khams gsum chos kyi rgyal por dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK022(za)001:9873: rin chen sna tshogs brgyad las byas //
NK022(za)001:9874: kha dog dbyings su ldan pa yi //
NK022(za)001:9875: shes rab yum gyi bum pa 'dis //
NK022(za)001:9876: dbang mchog 'dis ni dbang bskur ro //
NK022(za)001:9877: bud+d+ha ka lak+sha la sogs pa brjod /
NK022(za)001:9878: bum pas dbang bskur bas rang gi sems spros pa'i
NK022(za)001:9879: mtshan ma dang bral te ye shes lnga dang ldan
NK022(za)001:9880: zhing / 'gro ba'i don chu bo rgyun chad med pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK022(za)001:9881: me tog phreng ba thogs la /
NK022(za)001:9882: byang chub yan lag me tog spos //
NK022(za)001:9883: khams gsum btsun pa'i bdag po dang //
NK022(za)001:9884: bde gshegs mchod pa thob pa dang //
NK022(za)001:9885: 'gro don byed pa'i dbang bskur ro //
NK022(za)001:9886: rat+na ma l+ye tra tra tra /
NK022(za)001:9887: me tog thod kyis dbang bskur bas tshul khrims kyi
NK022(za)001:9888: phreng ba yongs su rdzogs pas sgrib pa'i tshogs rnam
NK022(za)001:9889: par dag ste byang chub sems dpa'i dbang thob par
NK022(za)001:9890: gyur cig / cod pan thogs la /
NK022(za)001:9891: ye shes mnga' bdag cod pan 'dis //
NK022(za)001:9892: klu gdug gnod pas mi rdzi zhing //
NK022(za)001:9893: 'khor ba'i nyes pas ma gos pa'i //
NK022(za)001:9894: dbang mchog des ni dbang bskur ro //
NK022(za)001:9895: badz+ra ba da ba'i lam pa na a b+hi shiny+tsa hri /
NK022(za)001:9896: cod pan gyi dbang bskur bas khams gsum chos kyi rgyal po'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK022(za)001:9898: phyag rgya'i mchog ni chen po ste //
NK022(za)001:9899: dam tshig chos kyi phrin las dang //
NK022(za)001:9900: bdag nyid chen pos che ba yis //
NK022(za)001:9901: rigs kyi bdag por dbang bskur ro //
NK022(za)001:9902: badz+ra mu tra a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK022(za)001:9903: phyag rgyas dbang bskur bas ye shes rnam pa lnga'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK022(za)001:9905: khyod ni rdo rje che ge mo //
NK022(za)001:9906: khams gsum kun tu grags pa yi //
NK022(za)001:9907: rdo rje zhes ni brjod pa yis //
NK022(za)001:9908: rdo rje mtshan ni thob bya'i phyir //
NK022(za)001:9909: ming mchog grags pas dbang bskur ro //
NK022(za)001:9910: badz+ra na ma a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK022(za)001:9911: rdo rje ming gis dbang bskur bas rig 'dzin rgyal
NK022(za)001:9912: po'i gral du 'khod pa'i dbang thob par gyur cig
NK022(za)001:9914: tshig gi gzungs dang don gyi gzungs //
NK022(za)001:9915: mi brjed za ma tog gi gzungs //
NK022(za)001:9916: rigs kyi gsang ba'i gzungs spyod pa'i //
NK022(za)001:9917: gzungs kyi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK022(za)001:9918: badz+ra d+ha ra a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK022(za)001:9919: gzungs kyi dbang bskur bas de bzhin gshegs pa thams
NK022(za)001:9920: cad kyi yum shes rab kyi pha rol du phyin
NK022(za)001:9921: ma'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK022(za)001:9923: rdo rje sems dpa' thogs te /
NK022(za)001:9924: nus pa'i mthu ldan yang dag don mi spong //
NK022(za)001:9925: kun gzhi gnas 'gyur me long ye shes te //
NK022(za)001:9926: zhe sdang mthar phyin rdo rje sems dpa'i sku //
NK022(za)001:9927: me long lta bu'i ye shes ldan 'gyur ro //
NK022(za)001:9928: ma h+aa a ta ri sha brjod /
NK022(za)001:9929: spyi bor tra las mi bskyod pa ye re bsam /
NK022(za)001:9930: rdo rje rigs kyi dbang bskur bas nyon mongs pa zhe sdang gnas su dag nas /
NK022(za)001:9931: rdo rje rigs me long lta bu'i ye shes kyi dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK022(za)001:9933: stong pa nyid la yon tan ma lus 'byung //
NK022(za)001:9934: de phyir stong mchog de la chos rnams ma lus gsal //
NK022(za)001:9935: dmigs med stong pa ye shes nyid las 'das //
NK022(za)001:9936: gti mug rmongs sel thams cad mkhyen pa'i sku //
NK022(za)001:9937: stong pa nyid kyi ye shes ldan 'gyur ro //
NK022(za)001:9938: shu dz+nya tas dpral bar bsam mo //
NK022(za)001:9939: de bzhin rigs kyi dbang bskur bas nyon mongs pa gti mug gnas su dag nas /
NK022(za)001:9940: de bzhin gshegs pa'i stong pa nyid kyi ye shes dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK022(za)001:9942: che ba'i yon tan mthar phyin gnyis med snying po'i don //
NK022(za)001:9943: nga rgyal mthar phyin rin chen 'byung ldan sku //
NK022(za)001:9944: gnyis med yon tan tshogs 'chang yon tan sku //
NK022(za)001:9945: mnyam pa nyid kyi yon tan ldan 'gyur ro //
NK022(za)001:9946: ma h+aa sa man+tasa rna ltag g.yas su rin 'byung bsam mo //
NK022(za)001:9947: rin chen rigs kyi dbang bskur bas nyon mongs pa nga rgyal gnas su dag nas /
NK022(za)001:9948: rin chen rigs mnyam pa nyid dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK022(za)001:9950: chos dbyings ye nas dag pa'i ngang //
NK022(za)001:9951: dbyings las thabs kyi cho 'phrul sku ru ston //
NK022(za)001:9952: 'dod chags gnas dag snang ba mtha' yas gsung //
NK022(za)001:9953: so sor rtog pa'i ye shes ldan 'gyur ro //
NK022(za)001:9954: ma h+aa pra tas mtha' yas ltag par bsam mo //
NK022(za)001:9955: pad+ma rigs kyis dbang bskur bas /
NK022(za)001:9956: nyon mongs pa 'dod chags gnas su dag nas /
NK022(za)001:9957: so sor rtogs pa'i ye shes pad+ma'i rigs kyi dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK022(za)001:9959: snang med snying po bcud kyi don yod med //
NK022(za)001:9960: de phyir spros med mnyam pa'i ngo la snang //
NK022(za)001:9961: snang med snying po'i ngang nyid las //
NK022(za)001:9962: cho 'phrul bye brag sna tshogs gsal //
NK022(za)001:9963: phrag dog gnas dag don yod grub pa'i sku //
NK022(za)001:9964: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes ldan 'gyur ro //
NK022(za)001:9965: ma h+aa kri tas rna ltag g.yon du don grub bsam /
NK022(za)001:9966: las kyi dbang bskur bas nyon mongs pa phrag dog gnas su dag nas /
NK022(za)001:9967: las kyi rigs bya ba grub pa'i ye shes kyi dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK022(za)001:9968: sku lngas dbang bskur bas bde bar gshegs pa rgyal
NK022(za)001:9969: ba rigs lnga'i mtshan phun sum tshogs pa dang ldan
NK022(za)001:9970: pa'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK022(za)001:9972: rigs kyi rigs te rigs kyi gtso //
NK022(za)001:9973: sku gsung thugs la 'jug pa dang //
NK022(za)001:9974: gsang ba gsang chen gsang mchog gi //
NK022(za)001:9975: bdag por khyed ni dbang bskur ro //
NK022(za)001:9976: b+hud+d+ha a b+hi shiny+tsa sogs brjod /
NK022(za)001:9977: gsang dbang bskur bas byang chub kyi sems sngo skams las sos nas /
NK022(za)001:9978: byang chub kyi snying po can du gyur gsang ba'i bdag por dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK022(za)001:9979: thabs shes rab kyi tho ba thogs la /
NK022(za)001:9980: 'di ni rdo rje chen po ste //
NK022(za)001:9981: khyed kyi lag tu 'di byin pas //
NK022(za)001:9982: ye shes rdo rje'i mchog nyid kyis //
NK022(za)001:9983: thabs kyi bdag por dbang bskur ro //
NK022(za)001:9986: shes rab pha rol phyin pa'i rtags //
NK022(za)001:9987: dril bu 'di yis dbang bskur bas //
NK022(za)001:9988: gsung rabs rgya mtsho sgrogs pa yi //
NK022(za)001:9989: shes rab mchog tu dbang bskur ro //
NK022(za)001:9990: prad nya pa ya sa ma /
NK022(za)001:9991: yo ga a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK022(za)001:9992: thabs dang shes rab kyi dbang bskur bas /
NK022(za)001:9993: bdag dang gzhan gyi don phun sum tshogs pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK022(za)001:9995: brjid pa'i seng ge shin tu myur ba yi //
NK022(za)001:9996: gzugs can 'di ni lag tu byin pa yis //
NK022(za)001:9997: gsung rabs rgya mtsho kun gyi sgra sgrogs te //
NK022(za)001:9998: log pa'i phyogs kun zil gyis gnon par shog /
NK022(za)001:9999: badz+ra sing ha a b+hi shiny+tsa a /
NK022(za)001:10001: gsung rabs rgya mtsho brda'i sgrogs pas log pa'i phyogs
NK022(za)001:10002: thams cad zil gyis gnon pa'i dbang thob par gyur
NK022(za)001:10004: steng phyogs mnga' mdzad thugs rje nyi ltar bdal //
NK022(za)001:10005: thugs rjes mun sel thugs rje zla ba'i 'od //
NK022(za)001:10006: stong gsum mun pa kun tu bsal nas ni //
NK022(za)001:10007: 'jig rten kun tu snang ba bskyed par shog /
NK022(za)001:10010: skye 'gro ma lus pa'i sems can gyi rgyud ye
NK022(za)001:10011: shes kyi rgyud dus dang rnam pa med par shar
NK022(za)001:10013: khams gsum gyi mun pa dus dang rnam pa med
NK022(za)001:10014: par sel ba'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig
NK022(za)001:10015: / bkra shis rdzas brgyad kyis dbang bskur te /
NK022(za)001:10016: nyungs dkar gyis bar du gcod pa'i bgegs kyi tshogs 'joms pa dang /
NK022(za)001:10017: zho yis bkrag dang gzi mdangs ldan pa dang //
NK022(za)001:10018: dur bas dge ba grags pa dpag med chos ldan zhing //
NK022(za)001:10019: li khris lha mi mang po 'du bar shog /
NK022(za)001:10020: 'gi ha gis ni dug gsum zhi byed chos sgrogs 'tsho ba dang //
NK022(za)001:10021: me long gis ni chos kun gzugs brnyan lta bur rtogs //
NK022(za)001:10022: bil bas byang chub go 'phang thob par shog /
NK022(za)001:10023: dung gis 'jig rten gsum du sgra chen sgrogs gyur cig /
NK022(za)001:10024: brgyad po des kyang khyed dbang thob par shog /
NK022(za)001:10025: rin po che sna bdun lag tu gtad cing dbang bskur ro //
NK022(za)001:10027: gdugs mdzes gser gyi yu ba can //
NK022(za)001:10028: nyon mongs sdug bsngal gdungs pa'i skyabs //
NK022(za)001:10029: khyed kyi lag tu 'di byin pas //
NK022(za)001:10030: 'gro ba'i mgon skyabs byed par shog /
NK022(za)001:10031: bkra shis kyi gdugs lag tu blangs zhing dbang bskur
NK022(za)001:10032: bas thugs rje chen pos sems can la skyobs shing
NK022(za)001:10033: gdung ba sel ba'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK022(za)001:10034: rgyal ba'i rgyal mtshan rgyal mtshan gang //
NK022(za)001:10035: chu srin rgyal mtshan 'di byin pas //
NK022(za)001:10036: bdud rnams kun las rgyal ba yi //
NK022(za)001:10037: chos kyi rgyal mtshan thob par shog /
NK022(za)001:10038: bkra shis rgyal mtshan lag tu bskur bas bdud bzhi las rgyal ba'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK022(za)001:10039: chos kyi rnga yab 'di byin pas //
NK022(za)001:10040: mi shes nyal nyil dri ma dag /
NK022(za)001:10041: nyon mongs skyon rnams sel byed pa'i //
NK022(za)001:10042: dbang mchog dam pa thob par shog /
NK022(za)001:10043: ye shes chos kyi rnga yab kyi dbang bskur bas
NK022(za)001:10044: nyon mongs pa sel bar byed pa'i dbang dam pa
NK022(za)001:10046: srid gsum 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal sel //
NK022(za)001:10047: yongs su gdung ba'i skyabs dam pa //
NK022(za)001:10048: ye shes bsil yab 'di byin pas //
NK022(za)001:10049: chu shel lta bu'i bde bar shog /
NK022(za)001:10050: bsil yab lag tu gtad de dbang bskur bas /
NK022(za)001:10051: srid pa gsum gyi sems can nyon mongs pa tsha
NK022(za)001:10052: bas gdungs ba las chu shel ltar bsil ba'i dbang
NK022(za)001:10053: dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK022(za)001:10054: gzugs sgra dri ro reg pa dang //
NK022(za)001:10055: 'dod pa lnga yi yon tan gyis //
NK022(za)001:10056: phongs pa rnams kyi re skong zhing //
NK022(za)001:10057: lha'i longs spyod kyis ni rgyas par shog /
NK022(za)001:10058: skye shi med pa rdo rje dbang gi tshe //
NK022(za)001:10059: rang rig byang sems gdod nas skye shi med //
NK022(za)001:10060: gzhan gyi mi phrogs khams gsum bdud las rgyal //
NK022(za)001:10061: 'chi med rdo rje tshe yi dbang bskur ro //
NK022(za)001:10062: badz+ra a yu dz+nya na a b+hi shiny+tsa a /
NK022(za)001:10063: bza' btung kha zas sna tshogs dag /
NK022(za)001:10064: pad+ma lta bur nyes skyon med //
NK022(za)001:10065: ro brgya ldan pa'i zas mchog gis //
NK022(za)001:10066: rtag tu dbang po tshim byed shog /
NK022(za)001:10067: lham sogs gos brgyan gyis dbang bskur te /
NK022(za)001:10068: yon tan lha ldan mtshungs med kyis //
NK022(za)001:10069: gtsang la kha dog legs bsgyur ba'i //
NK022(za)001:10070: gos rgyan mdzes pa 'di byin pas //
NK022(za)001:10071: rdzu 'phrul rkang par ldan pa dang //
NK022(za)001:10072: lha yi na bza' thob par shog /
NK022(za)001:10074: rdo rje srin por byin rlabs pa'i //
NK022(za)001:10075: rdo rje'i go cha 'di byin pas /
NK022(za)001:10076: gdug pa'i mtshon chas mi tshugs shing //
NK022(za)001:10077: brtson 'grus go cha bgo bar shog /
NK022(za)001:10079: zhi gnas gzhu dang lhag mthong mda' //
NK022(za)001:10080: shes rab ral gri 'di byin pas //
NK022(za)001:10081: nyon mongs g.yul las rnam rgyal zhing //
NK022(za)001:10082: shes rab ting 'dzin mchog thob shog /
NK022(za)001:10083: de ring phan chad bu khyod la //
NK022(za)001:10085: dbang mchog rnams kyis dbang bskur bas //
NK022(za)001:10086: rgyal ba rnams dang mtshungs par byas //
NK022(za)001:10087: de bas rigs kyi bu khyod kyis //
NK022(za)001:10088: rgyal ba rnams kyi mdzad spyod dang //
NK022(za)001:10089: sems can don ni mnyam byed byos //
NK022(za)001:10090: 'on kyang sangs rgyas bzhin du skye //
NK022(za)001:10091: dbang po rnams kyi skyon bsal bas //
NK022(za)001:10092: thos pa rgya mtsho bsgrub pa dang //
NK022(za)001:10093: bde gshegs chos sprin nyan pa yi //
NK022(za)001:10094: dbang mchog dam par dbang bskur ro //
NK022(za)001:10095: de nas dkyil nas babs la /
NK022(za)001:10096: gu ru'i zhabs slob ma'i spyi bor bzhag la /
NK022(za)001:10097: de ring phan chad bu khyod kyi //
NK022(za)001:10098: phyag na rdo rje nga yin pas //
NK022(za)001:10099: nga yis ji skad bsgo ba bzhin //
NK022(za)001:10100: bu khyod kyis ni bya dgos so //
NK022(za)001:10103: // // de nas nang dbang bskur te /
NK022(za)001:10104: gnas gzhung dang mthun pa dang /
NK022(za)001:10105: yum mtshan dang ldan pa btsal la dbang rdzas bsog /
NK022(za)001:10106: sgyu 'phrul snying po ltar dkyil 'khor bri /
NK022(za)001:10107: bsnyen bsgrub zab mo zhag gsum mam lngar byas la thon khar dbang bskur te /
NK022(za)001:10108: dang po slob dpon dang slob ma ji ltar bya
NK022(za)001:10109: ba'i phyi'i dbang bskur ba bzhin gong dang 'dra bar
NK022(za)001:10110: bya'o // man+dala gyi stengs su drangs pa la //
NK022(za)001:10111: phyi'i dbang bskur na gong mas chog /
NK022(za)001:10112: ma bskur bar nang dbang bcu gcig pu nod pa yin na /
NK022(za)001:10113: snying po nas byung ba ltar /
NK022(za)001:10114: phan pa'i dbang bcu phyi dbang nas bsdus la /
NK022(za)001:10115: dang po phan dbang bcus dbang bskur ro //
NK022(za)001:10116: de nas dam rdzas bdud rtsi lngas dbang bskur te /
NK022(za)001:10117: dri chen de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs //
NK022(za)001:10118: bde gshegs rigs kyi dam rdzas te //
NK022(za)001:10119: rdo rje lce stengs dbang bskur bas //
NK022(za)001:10120: rdo rje sku yi dbang yang sbyin //
NK022(za)001:10121: a mri ta ka ya a b+hi shiny+tsa /
NK022(za)001:10122: byang chub sems ni rdo rje'i rigs //
NK022(za)001:10123: rdo rje rigs kyi dam rdzas te //
NK022(za)001:10124: rdo rje lce stengs dbang bskur bas //
NK022(za)001:10125: rdo rje thugs kyi dbang yang sbyin //
NK022(za)001:10126: a mri ta tsit+ta a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK022(za)001:10127: sha chen rin po che'i rigs /
NK022(za)001:10129: rin chen rigs kyi dam rdzas te //
NK022(za)001:10130: rdo rje lce yon tan chen po'i dbang yang sbyin //
NK022(za)001:10131: a mri ta g+hu na a b+hi shiny+tsa tra /
NK022(za)001:10133: pad+ma rigs kyi rdo rje lce gsung mchog dag pa'i dbang yang sbyin //
NK022(za)001:10134: a mri ta waka a b+hi shiny+tsa /
NK022(za)001:10135: gur gum dri chu las kyi rigs //
NK022(za)001:10136: las kyi rigs kyi rdo rje lce phrin las grub pa'i dbang yang sbyin //
NK022(za)001:10137: a mri ta karma a b+hi shiny+tsa ha /
NK022(za)001:10138: bdud rtsi dam rdzas lnga'i dbang bskur bas /
NK022(za)001:10139: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK022(za)001:10140: sha lnga yis dbang bskur te /
NK022(za)001:10141: ma h+aa ma sa'i dam tshig ni /
NK022(za)001:10142: de bzhin rigs kyi dam rdzas te //
NK022(za)001:10143: spyi bo nas ni dbang bskur bas //
NK022(za)001:10144: sku gsung thugs kyi dbang yang sbyin //
NK022(za)001:10145: ma h+aa ma sa sa ma y+aa a b+hi shiny+tsa /
NK022(za)001:10146: glang po'i sha'i dam tshig ni //
NK022(za)001:10147: rdo rje rigs kyi spyi bo mngon shes lnga'i dbang yang sbyin //
NK022(za)001:10148: ha ti a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK022(za)001:10150: rin chen rigs kyi spyi bo snang ba med pa'i dbang yang sbyin //
NK022(za)001:10151: ha ya g+h+ri ba a b+hi shiny+tsa tra /
NK022(za)001:10152: ba glang sha'i dam tshig ni /
NK022(za)001:10153: pad+ma rigs kyi spyi bo gsung rabs rgya mtsho'i dbang yang sbyin //
NK022(za)001:10154: a ti a b+hi shiny+tsa h+r+ai /
NK022(za)001:10155: sho na na'i dam tshig ni /
NK022(za)001:10156: las kyi rigs spyi bo nas ni las mchog grub pa'i dbang yang sbyin /
NK022(za)001:10157: sho na a b+hi shiny+tsa a /
NK022(za)001:10158: de'i rjes su khong du yang blud /
NK022(za)001:10159: dbang po lnga la thig le byas te /
NK022(za)001:10160: mig la thig le byas pa yis //
NK022(za)001:10161: 'jig rten khams ni thams cad na //
NK022(za)001:10162: yid kyi rdo rje bdag zhugs la //
NK022(za)001:10163: lag tu shing thog bzhag pa yis //
NK022(za)001:10164: mngon shes mthong ba'i dbang yang sbyin //
NK022(za)001:10166: rna bar thig le 'jig rten khams ni thams cad na //
NK022(za)001:10167: sgra ru grags pa ji snyed pa //
NK022(za)001:10168: mngon shes rna bas thos pa yi //
NK022(za)001:10169: dbang mchog des ni dbang bskur ro //
NK022(za)001:10171: sna la thig le byas pa yis //
NK022(za)001:10172: 'jig rten khams ni thams cad na //
NK022(za)001:10173: dge dang mi dge thams cad kun //
NK022(za)001:10174: dri yis tshor ba'i dbang yang sbyin //
NK022(za)001:10175: na ma a b+hi shiny+tsa tra /
NK022(za)001:10176: lce'i thig le 'jig rten khams sems can sgra skad thams cad kun //
NK022(za)001:10177: mngon shes smra ba'i dbang yang sbyin //
NK022(za)001:10178: ji ba a b+hi shiny+tsa a /
NK022(za)001:10179: snying khar thig le byas 'jig rten khams sems can kun gyi sems shes pa'i //
NK022(za)001:10180: mngon shes thugs kyi dbang yang sbyin //
NK022(za)001:10182: sha lngas dbang bskur zhing thig le byass pas /
NK022(za)001:10183: snang ba'i chos thams cad ji ltar 'dod pa bzhin du dbang bsgyur ba'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK022(za)001:10184: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga la ci dgar spyod pa'i dbang bskur te /
NK022(za)001:10185: gzugs la rnam gsum shes byas nas //
NK022(za)001:10186: lha rnams la ni dbul bar bya //
NK022(za)001:10187: de nyid bcom ldan sna tshogs pa'i //
NK022(za)001:10188: sangs rgyas rnam par snang mdzad gco //
NK022(za)001:10189: gzugs la spyod pa'i dbang yang sbyin //
NK022(za)001:10190: sgra la 'dre lha rnams de nyid 'dod chags chos kyi 'byung gnas gtso //
NK022(za)001:10191: sgra la spyod pa'i dbang yang sbyin //
NK022(za)001:10192: dri la rnam gsum lha rnams de nyid sangs rgyas rin chen 'byung ldan gtso //
NK022(za)001:10193: dri la spyod pa'i ro la rnam gsum lha rnams de nyid mi bskyod pa yi tshul shes pas //
NK022(za)001:10194: ro la spyod pa'i dbang yang sbyin //
NK022(za)001:10195: reg la lha rnams de nyid sangs rgyas don yod grub pa gtso //
NK022(za)001:10196: reg la spyod dug lnga ru bzlog pa'i dbang bskur te /
NK022(za)001:10197: 'dod chags sems can don la chags //
NK022(za)001:10198: zhe sdang snying rje chen po yin //
NK022(za)001:10199: gti mug shes rab zab mo yin //
NK022(za)001:10200: nga rgyal gzhan gyis zil mi non //
NK022(za)001:10201: phrag dog mnyam nyid rtogs pa yin //
NK022(za)001:10202: nyon mongs thams cad zil gyis gnon //
NK022(za)001:10203: nyon mongs lnga la spyod 'gyur yang //
NK022(za)001:10204: 'dam bu chu yi pad bzhin te //
NK022(za)001:10205: nyes pa'i skyon gyis mi gos pa'i //
NK022(za)001:10206: dbang mchog des ni dbang bskur ro //
NK022(za)001:10207: de nas rigs lngas dbang bskur te //
NK022(za)001:10208: phyi dbang bzhi rdo rje sems dpa' la sogs pas dbang bskur te /
NK022(za)001:10209: rigs lnga'i rgya bcings la bu'i mgo'i gnas lngar gtug cing /
NK022(za)001:10210: h'u badz+ra d+h+rika la sogs pa brjod pas rigs lnga yab yum bcu grang nge bskyed /
NK022(za)001:10211: mig la sogs pa'i dbang po bzhi /
NK022(za)001:10212: rnam shes bzhi ste brgyad la sems dpa' brgyad kyi rgya bcas la /
NK022(za)001:10214: k+shi hi ra tsa la sogs pa brjod pas sems dpa' brgyad du bkra ye re bskyed /
NK022(za)001:10215: de rnams kyi g.yon du la s+ye la sogs pa'i rgya bcas la /
NK022(za)001:10216: badz+ra la s+ye h'u la sogs pa brjod pas sems ma brgyad bsam /
NK022(za)001:10217: lkog ma dang snying kha dang lte ba dang gsang sgor sgo ba bzhi'i rgya bcas la gtug cing /
NK022(za)001:10218: ya man ta krita la sogs 'dre de'i g.yon du
NK022(za)001:10219: sgo ma 'dre snying kha dang sog phrag tu kun
NK022(za)001:10220: bzang yab yum / barla'i nang gi g.yas g.yon du thub pa gsum gsum /
NK022(za)001:10221: de lta bu'i lus la rtogs pa zhe gnyis lha zhe gnyis kyi dkyil 'khor du bskyed pa ni /
NK022(za)001:10225: // // nang gi dbang rdzogs par bdun /
NK022(za)001:10226: sgyu 'phrul khro bo'i dbang bskur ba ni /
NK022(za)001:10227: dpal chen sh+ri he ru ka /
NK022(za)001:10228: 'bar ba chen po gar dgu pa //
NK022(za)001:10229: sems dpa' sngon po 'bar ba yi //
NK022(za)001:10231: 'jig pa yi ni dus ltar drag /
NK022(za)001:10232: dbu gsum phyag drug zhabs bzhi bgrad //
NK022(za)001:10233: spyan dgu 'bar ba gyen du bzlog /
NK022(za)001:10234: sku gsung thugs kyi bdag nyid ni //
NK022(za)001:10235: lus dang ngag dang sems la dbab //
NK022(za)001:10236: bsnyen bsgrub bdag por dbang bskur ro //
NK022(za)001:10237: ma h+aa sh+ri he ru ka /
NK022(za)001:10240: zhes pas gong gi sgyu 'phrul gyi rgyal ba rigs lnga las /
NK022(za)001:10241: 'jigs byed chen po he ru ka ltar bskyed //
NK022(za)001:10242: de la slob ma'i phung po he ru ka lngar bkra sa le gsal ba de la /
NK022(za)001:10243: dang po la dbu rgyan gyi dbang bskur te /
NK022(za)001:10244: dbu rgyan thod pa rkam barlona tshar gsum gyi steng
NK022(za)001:10245: du he ru ka lnga'i tsaka lis dbang bskur te
NK022(za)001:10246: / dbu brgyan thod pa'i phreng bas brgyan //
NK022(za)001:10247: dbu skra kham nag ral pa can //
NK022(za)001:10249: stobs chen mi 'byed dbang du bsdud //
NK022(za)001:10250: dus gsum sangs rgyas dbu brgyan 'dis //
NK022(za)001:10251: rnal 'byor dbang phyug dbang bskur ro //
NK022(za)001:10252: ka pa la ka ma la ma ku ta a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u h'u h+r+ai ya a /
NK022(za)001:10253: bskon la rnal 'byor dbang phyug chen po 'di la dbu brgyan gyis dbang bskur bas /
NK022(za)001:10254: dus gsum sangs rgyas rnams kyi dbang rdzogs par thob ste /
NK022(za)001:10255: khams gsum dbang bsdud srid gsum zil gyis gnon 'khor
NK022(za)001:10256: ba phyags mas 'debs pa'i dbang dam pa thob par
NK022(za)001:10257: gyur cig / rten gyis dbang bskur te /
NK022(za)001:10258: dur khrod dregs pa pho mo dang //
NK022(za)001:10259: khyu mchog ma he gzigs dang stag /
NK022(za)001:10260: gtum pa dom dang nyi zla'i gdan //
NK022(za)001:10261: zhabs bzhi bdud bzhi 'dul ba'i rtags //
NK022(za)001:10262: dregs pa gdan gyis dbang bskur ro //
NK022(za)001:10263: rak+sha ya ka sur+ya tsan+t+ra man+dala a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK022(za)001:10264: rnal 'byor gyi dbang phyug chen po 'di la gdan gyi dbang bskur bas /
NK022(za)001:10265: log pa'i dregs pa dang gdug pa can ma rungs
NK022(za)001:10266: pa thams cad tshar gcod pa'i dbang dam pa thob
NK022(za)001:10267: par gyur cig / gzugs brnyan du bris pa'am /
NK022(za)001:10268: phyag mtshan gyis dbang bskur te /
NK022(za)001:10269: rdo rje khor yug dung chen dang //
NK022(za)001:10270: ral gri dgra sta thong gshol dang //
NK022(za)001:10271: thugs mtshan rang rtags 'bar ba yi //
NK022(za)001:10272: phyag mtshan drug gis dbang bskur ro //
NK022(za)001:10273: badz+ra lo ka ka pa la khad ga par shu a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK022(za)001:10274: rnal 'byor gyi dbang phyug la phyag mtshan gyi dbang bskur bas /
NK022(za)001:10275: thugs ye shes rtse gcig pa'i don dang ldan pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK022(za)001:10276: dur khrod rgyan cha brgyad la /
NK022(za)001:10277: rna la bzhis dbang bskur te /
NK022(za)001:10278: glang chen ko rlon theg mchog dang //
NK022(za)001:10279: bsdud byed zhing gi g.yang gzhi dang //
NK022(za)001:10280: mnyen lcug 'khril ba'i sbrul chun dang //
NK022(za)001:10281: dpa' gtum stag gi sham thabs dang //
NK022(za)001:10282: rgyan cha bzhi'i dbang bskur ro //
NK022(za)001:10283: ba ya nyo ba ti ba ya ga shan gyi ra bya kri tsa ra a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK022(za)001:10284: rnal 'byor gyi dbang phyug la brgyan cha bzhi'i dbang bskur bas /
NK022(za)001:10285: theg pa rim pa dgu'i don la mnga' brnyes te
NK022(za)001:10286: tshad med pa bzhis 'gro ba rnams 'khor ba las
NK022(za)001:10287: drangs te khams gsum 'khor ba las rgyal ba'i dbang
NK022(za)001:10288: dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK022(za)001:10289: lhag pa'i rtags gsum gyi dbang bskur te /
NK022(za)001:10290: thugs rje chags pa'i rak+ta dang //
NK022(za)001:10291: don dam bcud kyi zo ris dang //
NK022(za)001:10292: gdul bya thal ba'i theg le dang //
NK022(za)001:10293: lhag pa'i rtags kyi dbang bskur ro //
NK022(za)001:10294: sarba ta th+aa ga ta sid+d+hi he a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK022(za)001:10295: rnal 'byor gyi dbang phyug la lhag pa'i rtags gsum gyi dbang bskur bas /
NK022(za)001:10296: dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas rnams kyis ni grogs por gzigs /
NK022(za)001:10297: rig 'dzin pho mo rnams kyis ni lhar mkha' 'gro
NK022(za)001:10298: dang ging dang dam can rnams kyis ni rje bo
NK022(za)001:10299: dang dpon por 'dzin pa'i dbang dam pa thob par
NK022(za)001:10300: gyur cig / me yi chas kyis dbang bskur te //
NK022(za)001:10301: rang rtags 'bar ba'i ye shes me //
NK022(za)001:10302: khams gsum nyon mongs sreg pa'i me //
NK022(za)001:10303: bskal pa'i me yi chas mchog ste //
NK022(za)001:10304: dbang mchog 'dis kyang dbang bskur ro //
NK022(za)001:10305: dz+nya na a b+hi shiny+tsa ra /
NK022(za)001:10306: rnal 'byor dbang phyug chen po la bskal pa ye shes kyi mes dbang bskur bas /
NK022(za)001:10307: thugs rje ye shes las me 'bar te khams gsum
NK022(za)001:10308: nyon mongs pa dus gcig la sreg pa'i dbang dam
NK022(za)001:10310: bu'i lus la koo sing dang ma mo phan chad dgod do //
NK022(za)001:10311: de ring phan chad bu khyod kyis //
NK022(za)001:10312: dbang phyug chen por dbang bskur gyis //
NK022(za)001:10313: bsnyen bsgrub gsang chen bdag po dang //
NK022(za)001:10314: khams gsum bdag por nga rgyal bskyed //
NK022(za)001:10315: bskyed rdzogs kyi gzhung du bskur na /
NK022(za)001:10317: gdan dang phyag mtshan mi 'dra ste //
NK022(za)001:10318: zhabs bzhis bdud bzhi bcom nas ni //
NK022(za)001:10319: lha chen brgyad dang dur khrod kyi //
NK022(za)001:10320: bdag po non pa'i dbang yang sbyin //
NK022(za)001:10322: phyag drug phyag mtshan sna tshogs te //
NK022(za)001:10323: phyag g.yas rdo rje rtse lnga pa //
NK022(za)001:10324: ye shes lnga yi mtshan nyid kyi //
NK022(za)001:10325: g.yon pa ban d+ha rak+tasa bkang //
NK022(za)001:10326: nyon mongs 'khrug cing zhal du gsol //
NK022(za)001:10327: dbang mchog des kyang dbang bskur ro //
NK022(za)001:10328: rdo rje kha tam pho nya mo //
NK022(za)001:10329: dam nyams rnams la gtong ba yi //
NK022(za)001:10330: dbang mchog dam pa des kyang dbang bskur ro //
NK022(za)001:10331: g.yas kyi tha ma rnge'u chung ste //
NK022(za)001:10332: rnga yi sgra skad mang po yis //
NK022(za)001:10333: gdug pa thams cad brdul du barloga /
NK022(za)001:10334: dbang mchog 'agre'o dril bu sgra dbyangs sna tshogs kyis //
NK022(za)001:10335: nyan pa chos kyi sgra sgrogs pa'i //
NK022(za)001:10336: dbang mchog g.yon gyi tha ma rgyu zhags te /
NK022(za)001:10337: rgyud lnga'i lam la gnas pa yi //
NK022(za)001:10338: sems can thugs rje'i zhags pas 'dren //
NK022(za)001:10339: dbang mchog gzhan kun gong ma dang sbyar la bskur ro //
NK022(za)001:10344: koo sing la sogs par bskyed /
NK022(za)001:10345: mig la sogs pa la koo ri la sogs pa'i gzugs byas la gtug cing /
NK022(za)001:10346: badz+ra koo'u ri ha la sogs pa brjod pas skur gsal la bsam /
NK022(za)001:10352: barla g.yas kyi nang rol na yar shar gyi ma bdun /
NK022(za)001:10353: phyi zur nas lho'i ma bdun /
NK022(za)001:10354: g.yon gyi nang rol na yar nub kyi ma bdun /
NK022(za)001:10355: phyi zur nas byang gi ma bdun /
NK022(za)001:10356: de ltar ting nge 'dzin gsal bar sgom du bzhugs /
NK022(za)001:10357: de ka rang la gsang ba'i dbang bskur te /
NK022(za)001:10358: yum mtshan dang ldan pa bla ma dang slob bu gnyis la re re 'tshogs na rab /
NK022(za)001:10359: med na gnyis cha gcig gi chog /
NK022(za)001:10360: brgyan gyis brgyan la gzhung bzhin du byin gyis brlabs la /
NK022(za)001:10361: sbyor ba'i dgongs pa dag par byas la /
NK022(za)001:10362: byang chub kyi sems mkha' la phebs pa dang mkha' nas mtheb srin gyis blangs la bu la sbyin /
NK022(za)001:10363: rdo rje pad+ma las byung ba'i //
NK022(za)001:10364: byang chub sems ni mngon snang ba //
NK022(za)001:10365: mthe bong dang ni srin lag rtse //
NK022(za)001:10366: rdo rje gnas su bzhag bya ste //
NK022(za)001:10367: rtag par zhi ba bde ba che //
NK022(za)001:10368: kye ma dam tshig 'di brjod pa'i //
NK022(za)001:10369: skye ba'i bde ba blang bar bya //
NK022(za)001:10370: 'di ni gsang sngags thams cad kyi //
NK022(za)001:10371: dbang bskur ba yis bde ba thob //
NK022(za)001:10372: +aahb+ho d+hi tsit+ta sid+d+hi ku ru a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK022(za)001:10373: zhes lce la lan gsum bzhag /
NK022(za)001:10374: slob ma'i khong du song ba dang ting nge 'dzin las lus mgo mjug khyab pa ste /
NK022(za)001:10375: lha'i dkyil 'khor du gnas pa de /
NK022(za)001:10376: byang chub sems su ltems su zhu ste /
NK022(za)001:10377: de nyid kyang mi dmigs te /
NK022(za)001:10379: chos kyi skur gyur par sgom mo //
NK022(za)001:10380: de yang gong ma'i byang sems lhag ma de rigs
NK022(za)001:10381: lnga yab yum gyi byang chub sems su bsam zhing
NK022(za)001:10382: dbang bskur te / rnam par snang mdzad bcom ldan 'das //
NK022(za)001:10383: gnyis med rol pa'i byang chub sems //
NK022(za)001:10384: spyi bo nas ni dbang bskur zhing //
NK022(za)001:10385: lce yi steng du bzhag pa yis //
NK022(za)001:10386: rdo rje sku yi dbang yang sbyin //
NK022(za)001:10387: badz+ra ka ya b+ho d+hi tsit+ta a b+hi shiny+tsa /
NK022(za)001:10388: mi bskyod rdo rje de bzhin gshegs //
NK022(za)001:10389: kun tu bzang dang mnyam par sbyor //
NK022(za)001:10390: gnyis med sbyor ba'i snying kha nas ni dbang lce
NK022(za)001:10391: yi steng du rdo rje thugs kyi dbang yang sbyin
NK022(za)001:10392: // badz+ra tsit+ta b+ho d+hi a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK022(za)001:10393: rin chen 'byung ldan rin chen spyan dang 'dre gnyis
NK022(za)001:10394: med sbyor ba'i lte ba nas ni lce'i steng yon
NK022(za)001:10395: tan rgya mtsho'i dbang yang sbyin //
NK022(za)001:10396: rat+na b+ho d+hi a b+hi shiny+tsa /
NK022(za)001:10397: snang ba mtha' yas de bzhin gshegs //
NK022(za)001:10398: pad+ma spyan gnyis med sbyor lkog ma lce'i steng gsung rabs rgya mtsho'i dbang yang sbyin //
NK022(za)001:10399: pad+ma ma bo d+hi a b+hi shiny+tsa /
NK022(za)001:10400: don yod grub pa de bzhin gshegs //
NK022(za)001:10401: las rab spyan dang gnyid med sbyor gsang ba'i sgo
NK022(za)001:10402: nas lce'i stengs phrin las rgya mtsho'i dbang yang sbyin
NK022(za)001:10403: // karma bo d+hi tsit+ta a b+hi shiny+tsa /
NK022(za)001:10404: ye shes lnga yi dbang bskur bas //
NK022(za)001:10405: sku lnga lhun gyis grub pa dang //
NK022(za)001:10406: thams cad mkhyen pa'i dbang yang sbyin //
NK022(za)001:10407: ma h+aa shu dz+nya na la sogs pa brjod /
NK022(za)001:10408: de ring phan chad bu khyod la //
NK022(za)001:10409: dbang mchog rdzogs par bskur ba yis //
NK022(za)001:10410: bcom ldan rdo rje sems dpa' yi //
NK022(za)001:10411: sku gsung thugs dang mnyam gyur nas //
NK022(za)001:10412: 'gro ba ma lus thams cad kyi //
NK022(za)001:10413: don mchog spyod pa rgya mtsho spyod //
NK022(za)001:10415: bsnyen bsgrub zab mo'i bdag por 'gyur //
NK022(za)001:10416: lha mi mang pos bkur bar 'gyur //
NK022(za)001:10417: de nas bu dkyil 'khor nas phab la slob dpon gyi zhabs spyi bor blangs la /
NK022(za)001:10418: gu rus de ring phan chad ces bka' bsgo /
NK022(za)001:10419: gu rus slob ma'i lag pa g.yas g.yon gnyis ka nas srin lag gis bzung la /
NK022(za)001:10420: dkyil 'khor bskor zhing dam tshig bsgrags te /
NK022(za)001:10421: thabs dang shes rab sems nyid kyis //
NK022(za)001:10422: rtag tu dgos pa med gyis la //
NK022(za)001:10423: 'dod pa lnga yi yon tan spyod //
NK022(za)001:10424: gzhan yang dam tshig nyams pa dang //
NK022(za)001:10425: skye bo gang zhig dam la gnas //
NK022(za)001:10426: brtul zhugs can gyis de drongs la //
NK022(za)001:10427: khrag chen po ni 'thung bar bya //
NK022(za)001:10428: gang dag slob dpon smod pa dang //
NK022(za)001:10429: theg pa chen po smod byed dang //
NK022(za)001:10430: gang dag bka' bzhin mi byed dang //
NK022(za)001:10431: rdo rje spun la 'khu byed rnams //
NK022(za)001:10432: rdo rje khro bo drag po yis //
NK022(za)001:10433: dam tshig bsgos te bsgral bar bya'o //
NK022(za)001:10434: khyod kyis srog chags bsad par bya //
NK022(za)001:10435: rdzun gyi dam tshig smra bar bya //
NK022(za)001:10436: ma byin par ni blang bar bya //
NK022(za)001:10437: bud med dag kyang khyod kyis bsten //
NK022(za)001:10438: bdag gi ngo bo yongs spangs shing //
NK022(za)001:10439: dkar thub kyis ni gzir mi bya //
NK022(za)001:10440: bde ba ru ni bde ba spyod //
NK022(za)001:10441: 'di ni phyogs dus sangs rgyas yin //
NK022(za)001:10442: sdig pa med kyis khyod ma 'jigs //
NK022(za)001:10443: dge dang mi dge'i chos rnams la //
NK022(za)001:10444: lhag par bsten par mi bya ste //
NK022(za)001:10445: mnyam nyid rig pa'i rlung zhugs pas //
NK022(za)001:10446: ci la'ang thogs pa med par spyod //
NK022(za)001:10447: de yan chad ni bya dgos pa'i dam tshig go //
NK022(za)001:10448: sangs rgyas thams cad mnyam sbyor ba'i //
NK022(za)001:10449: sdom pa nyams par khyod byed na //
NK022(za)001:10450: ji snyed sangs rgyas thams cad dang //
NK022(za)001:10451: byang chub sems dpa' rdo rje 'dzin //
NK022(za)001:10452: lha rnams dang ni mi rnams dang //
NK022(za)001:10453: de bzhin rnal 'byor bsgrub pa pos //
NK022(za)001:10454: snying la khrag chen 'thung bar byed //
NK022(za)001:10455: bu khyod nga la brnyas ma byed //
NK022(za)001:10456: gal te nga la brnyas btsugs na //
NK022(za)001:10457: dus min par ni tshe zad nas //
NK022(za)001:10458: dmyal bar ltung bar gyur ta re //
NK022(za)001:10459: de yan chad ni srung dgos pa'i dam tshig go //
NK022(za)001:10460: de nas slob mas mchod pa rnams dang /
NK022(za)001:10461: yo byad kyi tshogs mngar la /
NK022(za)001:10463: ro dang zas mchog me tog spos //
NK022(za)001:10464: glu gar sil snyan mar me dri //
NK022(za)001:10465: bla re rgyal mtshan 'phan gdugs rnams //
NK022(za)001:10468: rdo rje bla ma chen po dang //
NK022(za)001:10469: rgyal theb dam pa'i grogs po dang //
NK022(za)001:10470: yid bzhin nor dang dpag bsam shing //
NK022(za)001:10471: rin chen gzhong dang 'dod yon lnga //
NK022(za)001:10472: phyi nang longs spyod sna tshogs 'bul //
NK022(za)001:10475: gsang sngags spyod pa rnams kyi srog shing /
NK022(za)001:10476: phyi nang gsang ba gsum gyi dbang lag len gab cing sbas pa rdzogs so //
NK022(za)001:10479: // // rgya gar gyi dbang gi chu bo gsum dang /
NK022(za)001:10481: rgyud khungs ma nor ba'i phyag bzhes 'di /
NK022(za)001:10482: gang rung rung du 'di mi phyar ro //
NK022(za)001:10483: 'di snod med pa la byin na bka' zab pa'i dbang gis /
NK022(za)001:10484: rgyu dang shi sha gnyis ka dmyal bar 'agro'o //
NK022(za)001:10485: gab sbas byas kyang nyes pa med do //
NK022(za)001:10486: bla ma gtsang pa chen po'i bka' ma 'khyar ba /
NK022(za)001:10490: // // h'u bum pa chos dbyings dag pa'i gzhal yas nas //
NK022(za)001:10491: bdud rtsi rgya mtsho rang bzhin bsil ba'i chus //
NK022(za)001:10492: dug gsum sgrib pa ma lus dag gyur te //
NK022(za)001:10493: bkra shis des ni chos nyid rtogs gyur cig /
NK022(za)001:10494: sarba b+hi shud+d+he sarba d+harma sam b+ha ba b+hi shud d+ho ha /
NK022(za)001:10495: h'u mgul chings ras mchog ka shi ka yin te //
NK022(za)001:10496: dga' ldan lha yi na bza' byin brlabs can //
NK022(za)001:10497: tshul khrims rnam dag gos dang ldan gyur te //
NK022(za)001:10498: bkra shis de yis grags gro snyoms gyur cig /
NK022(za)001:10499: ka tsa lin ta a b+hi shiny+tsa +aahmh'u /
NK022(za)001:10500: 'bru lnga bde gshegs sku yi rang bzhin te //
NK022(za)001:10501: sku mchog lhun gyis grub pa'i dbang thob nas //
NK022(za)001:10502: tshe rabs kun tu mu ge rgyun chad de //
NK022(za)001:10503: bkra shis des ni don 'grub phun tshogs shog /
NK022(za)001:10505: dri lnga bde gshegs gsung gi rang bzhin te //
NK022(za)001:10506: gsung mchog lhun gyis grub pa'i dbang thob nas //
NK022(za)001:10507: dri mchog sna tshogs yid bzhin 'byung gyur cig /
NK022(za)001:10508: bkra shis des ni gsung rab sgrogs gyur cig /
NK022(za)001:10510: snying po rnam lnga bde gshegs thugs kyi rang bzhin te //
NK022(za)001:10511: thugs mchog lhun gyis grub pa'i dbang thob nas //
NK022(za)001:10512: rnam rtog mi mnga' ci yang sa le mkhyen //
NK022(za)001:10513: bkra shis des ni thugs rjes mtha' dag mkhyen gyur cig /
NK022(za)001:10515: rin chen sna lnga bde gshegs yon tan rang bzhin te //
NK022(za)001:10516: yon tan lhun gyis grub pa'i dbang thob nas //
NK022(za)001:10517: mi zad gter la rtag tu longs spyod pa'i //
NK022(za)001:10518: bkra shis des ni dgos 'dod 'grub gyur cig /
NK022(za)001:10520: sman lnga nad rnams sel ba'i phrin las te //
NK022(za)001:10521: phrin las lhun gyis grub pa'i dbang thob nas //
NK022(za)001:10522: dug gsum nad kyi sdug bsngal zhi gyur pa'i //
NK022(za)001:10523: bkra shis des ni nad rnams byang gyur cig /
NK022(za)001:10524: a mri ta pany+tsa sid d+hi +aahmh'u /
NK022(za)001:10525: kha rgyan dpag bsam shing chen rgyas pa la //
NK022(za)001:10526: yal kha me tog 'bras bu spud pa las //
NK022(za)001:10527: ji ltar bsams pa bzhin du 'byung gyur cig /
NK022(za)001:10528: bkra shis des ni bsam pa 'grub gyur cig /
NK022(za)001:10529: glag sha na pany+tsa sid d+hi +aahmh'u /
NK022(za)001:10533: wa tra ye pany+tsa sid d+hi +aahmh'u /
NK022(za)001:10647: // // mdo'i dbang dang dkyil 'khor gyi las byang rin chen phreng ba bzhugs so //
NK022(za)001:10649: a be she ke man+dala rat+na ma le karma bri ta na ma /
NK022(za)001:10651: dbang dang dkyil 'khor gyi las rin chen phreng ba zhes bya ba /
NK022(za)001:10652: nyes bcom legs ldan mtshan gzhi mtha' las 'das //
NK022(za)001:10653: bdag med byams mgon don gyis bdag gzhan dpal //
NK022(za)001:10654: don dam gsang sbas nam mkha'i dkyil du 'khyil //
NK022(za)001:10655: rdo rje che mchog dbang phyug kun gyi bdag /
NK022(za)001:10656: 'dzin pa mi rtog sha rus khrag la rol //
NK022(za)001:10657: thugs kyi gdung thag 'khor ba'i mtha' la rje //
NK022(za)001:10658: yul med ma skyes mtshan ma'i yul las rgyal //
NK022(za)001:10659: bde chen rgyal po nyid la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK022(za)001:10660: shes rab chen po nam mkha'i nyi mar gsal //
NK022(za)001:10661: byang chub sems kyi 'od zer dbyings su 'char //
NK022(za)001:10662: dpal brtul myur ba'i thugs rjes 'gro drug 'dul //
NK022(za)001:10663: rtog 'joms ye shes rdo rjes cho 'phrul 'phro //
NK022(za)001:10664: dam pa'i don gsungs gnyis med ston pa'i sku //
NK022(za)001:10665: smra ba'i seng ge nyid la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK022(za)001:10666: rin chen gter ltar 'dod dgu re bskang zhing //
NK022(za)001:10667: lung dang rigs pa'i gtan tshigs kun gyi mdzod //
NK022(za)001:10668: gda' can yang dag len pa me long gsal //
NK022(za)001:10669: rdo rje kun 'dus 'jigs byed rgyal po'i brgyud //
NK022(za)001:10670: chos kyi me long 'di la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK022(za)001:10671: rgyal ba'i sras po cang mi gsum //
NK022(za)001:10672: mi gsung pa ni rgya cher bshad //
NK022(za)001:10673: bshad du med pa'ii chos 'di ni //
NK022(za)001:10674: rgyal ba rnams kyis ma bshad de //
NK022(za)001:10675: de ltar ston pa rgyal mchog kyang //
NK022(za)001:10676: rnam par brjod par mi bya ste //
NK022(za)001:10677: rgya cher bshad par dgongs pa'o //
NK022(za)001:10678: skye ba med pa'i chos rnams ni //
NK022(za)001:10679: ma skyes par yang snying por bzhed //
NK022(za)001:10680: snying po'i don du gang gyur pa //
NK022(za)001:10681: tshig tu smra ba legs ma yin //
NK022(za)001:10682: spros pa nyid na gol ba zhes //
NK022(za)001:10683: rgyal ba rnams kyis yang dag bshad //
NK022(za)001:10684: de bas rdo rje rgyal po nyid //
NK022(za)001:10685: bka' ma gsal bar dgongs pa ni //
NK022(za)001:10686: dgongs pa'i don rnams gang 'byin pa //
NK022(za)001:10687: ji ltar me long gzugs brnyan ltar //
NK022(za)001:10688: dgongs don rig la gsal gyur pa //
NK022(za)001:10689: ma skyes pa yis don gyis na //
NK022(za)001:10690: tshig tu spro ba ma yin yang //
NK022(za)001:10691: mtshan ma tshig gi rnal 'byor pa //
NK022(za)001:10692: tshig la zhib cing don la rtsing //
NK022(za)001:10693: tshig phyir blo 'brangs rtsal zhan rnams //
NK022(za)001:10694: bkri phyir bsam pa rangs bya ba //
NK022(za)001:10695: mi dmigs pa la yang dmigs pa yis //
NK022(za)001:10696: cho 'phrul tshig gis mtshan pa ni //
NK022(za)001:10697: bder gshegs rgyal ba kun gyi thugs //
NK022(za)001:10698: gsang ba de nyid snying po'i don //
NK022(za)001:10699: mnyam phyir byang chub sems chen po'i //
NK022(za)001:10700: rnal 'byor lnga dang bcu sogs pa //
NK022(za)001:10701: dper na rgyal rigs rgyud byung ba'i //
NK022(za)001:10702: mang po'i dbang por dpon stabs te //
NK022(za)001:10703: 'khor lo la sogs rin chen gyis //
NK022(za)001:10704: kun la dbang bsgyur thob par ltar //
NK022(za)001:10706: chos kyi dbang por dpon stabs te //
NK022(za)001:10707: phyag rgya la sogs rtags chen gyis //
