NK022(za)001:10708: rim pa kun gyis thog mar 'gro //
NK022(za)001:10709: 'di ni dbang gi khyad par te //
NK022(za)001:10710: sa la rim par byung ba yi //
NK022(za)001:10711: brtsal gyis bgrod cing slab pa'i mtha' //
NK022(za)001:10712: goms par bya ba rab gces phyir //
NK022(za)001:10713: gsal bar bkod de brjod kyis nyon //
NK022(za)001:10714: stong par sbas pa'i don 'di la //
NK022(za)001:10715: dpes mtshon tshig gi lde mig gis //
NK022(za)001:10716: mnyam nyid rig pa'i sgo dbye bya //
NK022(za)001:10717: sbas pa'i don 'byin gsal byed pa //
NK022(za)001:10718: sa lu phub khrod snang me bzhin //
NK022(za)001:10719: gsal tog snang rnyed sa le 'dug /
NK022(za)001:10720: des na lung rigs 'brel ba yis //
NK022(za)001:10721: gab sbas don la phebs par bya'o //
NK022(za)001:10722: rnal 'byor chen po grub pa'i brgyud //
NK022(za)001:10725: lam gyi dam pa rnams kyi mchog /
NK022(za)001:10726: sngon 'gro gang bsal snod gyur nas //
NK022(za)001:10728: gzugs brnyan rim pa'i 'bras thob phyir //
NK022(za)001:10729: thabs dang thabs byung rgyu 'bras tshul //
NK022(za)001:10730: 'brel pas go rims nges par bzhag /
NK022(za)001:10731: chu bo 'dus pa'i bla ma la //
NK022(za)001:10732: rgyud du byung ba'i bu mchog gis //
NK022(za)001:10733: man+dala mkhar bsil tshad tsam la //
NK022(za)001:10734: gos sogs rin chen bkod byas la //
NK022(za)001:10735: 'dun par lan gsum gus byas te //
NK022(za)001:10736: 'dod pa'i don mchog zhu bar bya //
NK022(za)001:10737: gnang ba'i yul 'byung dgos pa gsog /
NK022(za)001:10738: de ltar 'di ltar lo zla yi //
NK022(za)001:10739: sngon dang yang sngon brtsam par bya //
NK022(za)001:10740: de nas 'di ltar dpung bskyed pas //
NK022(za)001:10741: gags sbyangs snod ldan 'chags rgyu'i phyir //
NK022(za)001:10742: rtsol sgrub sngon nam yang sngon nam //
NK022(za)001:10743: zhag grangs dag gi sngon rol nas //
NK022(za)001:10744: sdig sbyangs byang chub sems bskyed de //
NK022(za)001:10745: dge ba'i don la 'dun par bya //
NK022(za)001:10746: slong mo pa dang slong la dga' //
NK022(za)001:10747: slong la dga' ba'i tshe spyod rnams //
NK022(za)001:10748: sde dang tshan dang grar bcas te //
NK022(za)001:10749: snying rje khud pa'i zhing du bya //
NK022(za)001:10750: sman dang 'bru dang rtsi rnams dang //
NK022(za)001:10751: bcud kyi mchog tu gyur pa dag /
NK022(za)001:10752: btags bab phye mar byas nas kyang //
NK022(za)001:10753: klu ngam chu klung mtsho chen du //
NK022(za)001:10754: don de chags med sbyin par bya //
NK022(za)001:10755: dge ba'i yon bdag dang blangs te //
NK022(za)001:10756: nad gso shes slob spyod sgom gra /
NK022(za)001:10757: gtsugs te sti gnas mchog bya zhing //
NK022(za)001:10758: dus kyi 'khor lo mchod chen bya //
NK022(za)001:10759: gsung sgra rgya mtshor sgrogs pa yi //
NK022(za)001:10760: glegs bam zab mo kun bsten te //
NK022(za)001:10761: brjod dang bsnyen bkur bsti gnas kyis //
NK022(za)001:10762: rgya cher yongs pa'i las rnams bya //
NK022(za)001:10763: ye shes tshogs chen bya ba'i phyir //
NK022(za)001:10764: shes rab tshogs kyi sbyin mchog dag /
NK022(za)001:10765: bsten nam glegs bam la sogs pa'i //
NK022(za)001:10766: blo mchog ldan pa rnams la sbyin //
NK022(za)001:10767: sho gams gsar du sho gams lam //
NK022(za)001:10768: mi bde gnod pa kun bsal te //
NK022(za)001:10769: tshad med snying rje 'khor lo bskor //
NK022(za)001:10770: sbyin pa'i 'khor lo rgyun mi gcad //
NK022(za)001:10772: me 'am de bzhin rlung rnams la //
NK022(za)001:10773: sku gdung spel mchod ring srel rnams //
NK022(za)001:10774: brtsam pa'i las chen 'khor lo bya //
NK022(za)001:10775: mtshams med bzlog par byed pa yi //
NK022(za)001:10776: lus sems rgyud la rdul brlag ste //
NK022(za)001:10777: 'phags pa'i sprin tshogs pho brang du //
NK022(za)001:10778: rdul bsnyed lus kyi mchod sems bshags //
NK022(za)001:10779: rgyal mnyes las kyi cho ga ba //
NK022(za)001:10780: thabs chen sbyor ba'i las chen las //
NK022(za)001:10781: rnam bzhi me yi las mchod bya //
NK022(za)001:10782: des ni mtshams med bzlog pa yin //
NK022(za)001:10784: gang ltar lcogs ltar 'bad rtsol bya //
NK022(za)001:10785: bstan pa skyong ba'ii tshogs rnams la //
NK022(za)001:10786: mchod sbyin spel ba'i las rnams bya //
NK022(za)001:10787: de la sogs pa dge ba'i tshogs //
NK022(za)001:10788: don du mi 'gyur bzhi spangs la //
NK022(za)001:10789: nan tan tshogs kyi spung sems bskyed //
NK022(za)001:10790: 'di ltar las chen ltang tshogs pa //
NK022(za)001:10791: gzhan du bskyed pa ma yin te //
NK022(za)001:10792: rtse gcig don ldan rnal 'byor pas //
NK022(za)001:10793: rgyud ldan snod ldan bya phyir dang //
NK022(za)001:10794: gal te rtsal gzhan ma grub na //
NK022(za)001:10795: bgegs bsags ltang chen kun sdom ste //
NK022(za)001:10796: las kyi bsags pa bsngo bya zhing //
NK022(za)001:10797: gdung ba'i shugs phyung rtsal sprugs nas //
NK022(za)001:10798: nyi shar chu klung gzugs brnyan ltar //
NK022(za)001:10799: rang bzhin shugs kyis 'grub pa gces //
NK022(za)001:10800: de phyir phra mo yan chad kyang //
NK022(za)001:10801: dam pa'i don du gyur par bya //
NK022(za)001:10802: bya ba sngon du kun byas nas //
NK022(za)001:10803: rang bzhin ting nge 'dzin gzugs brnyan //
NK022(za)001:10804: snying por gyur pas don gyi rdzogs //
NK022(za)001:10805: rang rig gtso 'khor sku ru shar //
NK022(za)001:10806: de las khyad par skal ldan mi //
NK022(za)001:10807: spyod yul gyur pas gzugs brnyan no //
NK022(za)001:10808: thams cad tshang bar rdzogs pas na //
NK022(za)001:10809: phun sum tshogs zhes de la bya //
NK022(za)001:10811: thams cad ye nas 'brel bkod rdzogs //
NK022(za)001:10812: de dag 'brel pa'i mtshan nyid ni //
NK022(za)001:10813: rang bzhin ji bzhin mngon byed pa'i //
NK022(za)001:10814: dngos po gnyan mas mtshon pa ste //
NK022(za)001:10815: gang gi gzugs brnyan gang yin dang //
NK022(za)001:10816: de yi rang bzhin gcig pas na //
NK022(za)001:10817: mtshon bya byed dang ngo bos 'brel //
NK022(za)001:10818: de nas shes bya shes byed dang //
NK022(za)001:10820: rang bzhin tshogs dang ting nge 'dzin //
NK022(za)001:10821: lung las gsal bar snang ba dang //
NK022(za)001:10822: sgra yis 'jigs phyir bri ma byas //
NK022(za)001:10823: gnas rab brtags pa'i gal chen yang //
NK022(za)001:10824: nam mkha'i 'khor lo rdo rje dang //
NK022(za)001:10825: rin chen zur brgyad pad+ma'i dbyibs //
NK022(za)001:10826: rgya gram la sogs 'dra bar brtag /
NK022(za)001:10827: sa gzhi'i yang ni de bzhin te //
NK022(za)001:10828: ri bo brtsegs dang bzur ba dang //
NK022(za)001:10829: de bzhin sbreng dang gtams pa'i tshul //
NK022(za)001:10830: 'dra bar mkhas pas brtag par bya //
NK022(za)001:10831: de yang rigs kyi khyad par ni //
NK022(za)001:10832: lnga la sogs pa so so yi //
NK022(za)001:10833: gnas gnas dag tu rtogs nas ni //
NK022(za)001:10834: nor bu rin chen der bsgrub bya //
NK022(za)001:10835: skyon gyis gnas gang spang ba ni //
NK022(za)001:10836: gshin rje gdug pa'i mdung rtse dang //
NK022(za)001:10837: ma mo rngam pa'i sbar shad dang //
NK022(za)001:10838: srin po dus pa'i 'chi rjes dang //
NK022(za)001:10839: gnod sbyin pho mo'i rbab shul dang //
NK022(za)001:10841: gnas kyi skyon dang dgra rnams kun //
NK022(za)001:10842: mkhas pas nges par spang bar bya //
NK022(za)001:10843: ri bo lhun sdug nags tshal can //
NK022(za)001:10844: snum bsnag ldan zhing mnyam pa dang //
NK022(za)001:10845: chu bo chu bdag phyogs nas 'bab //
NK022(za)001:10846: me tog tshal dang ljon pa'i shing //
NK022(za)001:10847: bkra shis bya skad sgrogs pa dang //
NK022(za)001:10848: lo rgyus shis pa mchog yin te //
NK022(za)001:10849: yid 'ong gnyen zhing nyams dga' ba //
NK022(za)001:10850: sde dpung chen pos mi tshugs shing //
NK022(za)001:10851: rna gnyan phra gsag med gyur cig /
NK022(za)001:10853: rang bzhin grub pa'i mthur ldan phyir //
NK022(za)001:10854: gsang chen spyod pa'i gnas su shis //
NK022(za)001:10855: dge dang mi dge'i mtshan nyid ni //
NK022(za)001:10856: bo dang dma' bar gyur pa yi //
NK022(za)001:10857: ro lnga'i mtshan ma brtags par bya //
NK022(za)001:10858: gyo mo rus pa zug rdo dang //
NK022(za)001:10859: gram pa shing sogs la sogs pa //
NK022(za)001:10860: gal te shes par ma gyur na //
NK022(za)001:10861: skyes bu thabs la mkhas pa yis //
NK022(za)001:10862: mtshan mas mtshan ma gzhom pa'i phyir //
NK022(za)001:10863: gnan nam spo ba'i las kyis sbyar //
NK022(za)001:10864: dge bar gyur na der gnas bya //
NK022(za)001:10865: de ltar brtags pa'i gnas dbus su //
NK022(za)001:10866: sa zhag spos chen rnam lnga'i zhu //
NK022(za)001:10867: bsres pas kun tu gru bzhi ni //
NK022(za)001:10869: bdag po tshim byed rdzas bshams te //
NK022(za)001:10870: dgon pa chen po'i sa phyogs su //
NK022(za)001:10871: bkra shis mtshan ma 'byung ba dag /
NK022(za)001:10872: dga' ba skye bar 'gyur ba yis //
NK022(za)001:10874: rtsod pa nye bar zhi bya'i phyir //
NK022(za)001:10875: snying rje ldan pa'i rnal 'byor gyis //
NK022(za)001:10876: bsgrub dbang gnag pa mthar dbyung phyir //
NK022(za)001:10877: rgyal po brten dang 'khor bcas la //
NK022(za)001:10878: bden pas basgo'am sa blangs pa'am //
NK022(za)001:10879: bdag nyid grags mor ldan pa yis //
NK022(za)001:10880: zhi ba'i chas gos bgo byas te //
NK022(za)001:10881: bdud rtsi khro bo dran byas la //
NK022(za)001:10882: mthun pa'i rdzas rnams byin gyis brlab //
NK022(za)001:10883: lha mo bskyed dgug mchod byas nas //
NK022(za)001:10884: rnal 'byor mchog gi sgrub pa po //
NK022(za)001:10885: bdud 'dul phyag rgya rdzogs pa'i tshe //
NK022(za)001:10886: r+au tra tshogs kyi rgol ba la //
NK022(za)001:10887: skyes bu las kyi don bsgrangs te //
NK022(za)001:10888: don gyis dbang po phyir sbran pas //
NK022(za)001:10889: rgyal ba dbang phyug thams cad kyis //
NK022(za)001:10890: don mchog yang dag mdzad pa'i tshe //
NK022(za)001:10891: skyes bu rtsal gyi khyad par las //
NK022(za)001:10893: sngon tshe dpal chen gar dbang gis //
NK022(za)001:10894: thugs rje'i sa la gshegs nas kyang //
NK022(za)001:10895: r+au tra de bzhin bsgral nas ni //
NK022(za)001:10896: gsang ba'i bstan pa rgyas mdzad nas //
NK022(za)001:10897: 'gro drug thugs rjes bsgral ba ltar //
NK022(za)001:10898: lha mos mkhyen pa mdzad nas kyang //
NK022(za)001:10899: bde chen sa la bgrod pa'i tshe //
NK022(za)001:10900: r+au tra'i rgol ba byung ba'am //
NK022(za)001:10901: spyan ldan khyod kyis dpang mdzod cig /
NK022(za)001:10902: rin chen la sogs gtor ma yis //
NK022(za)001:10903: sa bdag tshim byas bslang ba ni //
NK022(za)001:10904: dgongs shing thugs rjes rgyal ba'i lha //
NK022(za)001:10905: lha klu gnod sbyin sde dpon bcas //
NK022(za)001:10906: gangs ri rtse dang rin chen ri //
NK022(za)001:10907: kun dga' ldum ra skyed mos tshal //
NK022(za)001:10908: mtsho rdzing lu ma 'bab chu'i gnas //
NK022(za)001:10910: gang dag bdag por gyur pa rnams //
NK022(za)001:10911: rnal 'byor dbang phyug bdag nyid kyis //
NK022(za)001:10912: sa 'di lhun gyis grub bya'i phyir //
NK022(za)001:10913: 'dzam gling grub pa'i sa gling na //
NK022(za)001:10915: rin chen gser gyi sa 'di blang //
NK022(za)001:10916: des ni bdag gi der 'gyur zhing //
NK022(za)001:10917: nyes pa de dang bral ba yin //
NK022(za)001:10918: byang chub spyod pa gso ba dang //
NK022(za)001:10919: bsod nams dga' ba bskyed pa dang //
NK022(za)001:10920: shes ldan rdzu 'phrul can gyi bu //
NK022(za)001:10921: ma skrag phrag dog yong ma bskyed //
NK022(za)001:10922: sgom bya h'u bzhes byin bsdus la //
NK022(za)001:10923: zhe sdang rdo rje'i rnal 'byor gyis //
NK022(za)001:10924: khro bo drag po'i sngags bzlos shing //
NK022(za)001:10925: rdo rje khro bo'i stabs kyis bskor //
NK022(za)001:10926: rang gi 'dug par brjid bag gis //
NK022(za)001:10927: 'dug ste rin chen sa gzhi bslang //
NK022(za)001:10928: lha mo dpang mkhyen gsol byas nas //
NK022(za)001:10929: dri shul phyag rgyas man+dala gnan /
NK022(za)001:10930: rat+na ba sa cang si ti ku ru /
NK022(za)001:10932: lha mo 'dzum zhu thim pa yis //
NK022(za)001:10933: ye shes rin chen sa brtan bya //
NK022(za)001:10934: sa gzhi sbyong ba rnam gsum ste //
NK022(za)001:10935: lto 'phyo'i dus tshod mkhas pa yis //
NK022(za)001:10936: ma nor phyogs nas bkod byas shing //
NK022(za)001:10937: khru gang rgyas pa'i thab dbyibs su //
NK022(za)001:10938: ro lnga'ii mtshan ma shin tu'ang btag /
NK022(za)001:10939: chus bkang gom pa brgyar lta bya //
NK022(za)001:10940: shin tu bzang ba'i sa der ni //
NK022(za)001:10941: bsod nams gter dang ldan bya'i phyir //
NK022(za)001:10942: rin chen lnga la sogs pa'i rdzas //
NK022(za)001:10943: sa gzhi gter chen rgyas par bya //
NK022(za)001:10944: bkra shis mchog tu sngags pa yin //
NK022(za)001:10945: nyi zla dri chen ma sa dang //
NK022(za)001:10946: dri chu rang bzhin ye shes lngas //
NK022(za)001:10947: byugs te shin tu skams par bya //
NK022(za)001:10948: ting 'dzin phyag rgya sngags ldan pas //
NK022(za)001:10949: mtshan ma'i dngos po kun sbyangs te //
NK022(za)001:10950: rgyal ba bzhugs pa'i rten du bya //
NK022(za)001:10951: ngan na gnas spo bya ba 'am //
NK022(za)001:10952: zhi ba'i sreg sbyang rgyas pa brtsam //
NK022(za)001:10953: khro bo h'u chen kun 'dus nas //
NK022(za)001:10954: gsad cing gnan pa'i las byas te //
NK022(za)001:10955: ri rab chen po'i rmang du gtang //
NK022(za)001:10956: ya ma ra tsa'i zas su sbyar //
NK022(za)001:10957: chu srin 'bar ba'i kha ru bardzanga //
NK022(za)001:10959: bdun brgyud rigs ni brlag 'gyur nas //
NK022(za)001:10960: nam yang ldang bar mi nus te //
NK022(za)001:10961: byang chub sems ni bskyed na gtang //
NK022(za)001:10963: ma ma pa sha ku ru nan //
NK022(za)001:10964: sum b+ha ni sum b+ha ni nan //
NK022(za)001:10965: chos nyid nam mkha' bdal ba la //
NK022(za)001:10966: ye shes lnga yi 'byung chen brtsegs //
NK022(za)001:10967: kun gzhi bdal ba'i nam mkha' la //
NK022(za)001:10968: bskyed pa'i 'byung chen rnam lnga brtsegs //
NK022(za)001:10969: b+h+r+aum chen rin chen 'bar ba'i gzhal //
NK022(za)001:10970: mtha' dbus med par kun tu khyab //
NK022(za)001:10971: ta la'i skyed shing gser tsong dril //
NK022(za)001:10972: mu khyud bdun phreng drug rtsegs 'bar //
NK022(za)001:10973: b+h+ru kha tri kha ta li b+h+ru /
NK022(za)001:10974: rdo rje byin brlabs 'byung gnas dang //
NK022(za)001:10975: gnas rnams shin tu brten bya'i phyir //
NK022(za)001:10976: de nas rdo rje'i gnas dag tu //
NK022(za)001:10977: seng ge'i lta bas ltas nas ni //
NK022(za)001:10978: khro dmigs 'bar bar phyir ltas te //
NK022(za)001:10979: 'gying bag tshul du brjid pa yis //
NK022(za)001:10981: phyi nang rdul chen gsal bar bya //
NK022(za)001:10982: h'u ho stong gsum stong gi 'jig rten na //
NK022(za)001:10983: skye 'gro rtsi shing nags tshal dang //
NK022(za)001:10984: mthong yod snang grags ji snyed pa //
NK022(za)001:10986: rngam chen gtum thung sha stag 'bar //
NK022(za)001:10987: dur khrod dkyil 'khor lhun gyis grub //
NK022(za)001:10989: rak+sha kro ta dza la kha /
NK022(za)001:10990: ha la ha la ti ta phata /
NK022(za)001:10991: zhes pa khro bo rol pa yi //
NK022(za)001:10992: stabs dang ma mo rngam tshul dang //
NK022(za)001:10993: phra men lhags pa'i rngam stabs kyis //
NK022(za)001:10995: rdo rje dkrigs pa'i phreng ba dang //
NK022(za)001:10996: tho ba lcags kyu 'bar ba dang //
NK022(za)001:10997: 'khor lo ral gri la sogs rdzas //
NK022(za)001:10998: kun gyi phyag rgya mtshan mas bskor //
NK022(za)001:10999: de las 'bar ba'i phyag rgya dang //
NK022(za)001:11000: mig las 'bar ba'i me mched pas //
NK022(za)001:11002: dmigs pa dngos su sbyangs nas kyang //
NK022(za)001:11003: 'bar ba drag po'i yi ge las //
NK022(za)001:11004: bsreg pa'i dpal chen gur du gtams //
NK022(za)001:11005: h'u ra rdo rje me yi ri //
NK022(za)001:11006: lhun po 'bar ba'i rtse brgyad la //
NK022(za)001:11007: 'bar ba'i lha brgyad bsgyel nas kyang //
NK022(za)001:11008: dbang chen rdo rje bka' bstod nas //
NK022(za)001:11009: shin tu mi bzad 'bar ba yi //
NK022(za)001:11010: gtum chen ha la rngam pa'i gzugs //
NK022(za)001:11011: lha chen khyab 'jug pags bshus nas //
NK022(za)001:11012: zhing chen g.yang gzhi na bza' mnabs //
NK022(za)001:11013: gshin rje ma tang 'bar ba yi //
NK022(za)001:11014: ro dbyug chen po phyag na 'bar //
NK022(za)001:11015: phra men dgu khri mang po dag /
NK022(za)001:11016: 'bar ba'i tshogs ni gtibs thag chad //
NK022(za)001:11017: gang la cis 'dul der bston pa //
NK022(za)001:11019: do shal mgur chu phreng bas sbrengs //
NK022(za)001:11020: bskal pa'i me dpung 'bar ba'i klong //
NK022(za)001:11022: nam mkha'i khams kun me dpung gtibs //
NK022(za)001:11024: dur khrod dgon pa'i sa phyogs dag /
NK022(za)001:11025: me yi ri bo 'bar ba las //
NK022(za)001:11026: me'i yi dwags ma dag las //
NK022(za)001:11027: gang yang gnas par mi phod pa //
NK022(za)001:11028: steng gi me lce 'bar ba ni //
NK022(za)001:11031: gyen du 'khyil zhing steng du thal //
NK022(za)001:11032: me lce dgu phreng 'bar ba dag /
NK022(za)001:11034: dur khrod me ri smug nag 'bar //
NK022(za)001:11036: nga rgyal sregs pas ser nag 'bar //
NK022(za)001:11038: phrag dog sregs pas ljang nag 'khrug /
NK022(za)001:11039: gti mug sel bas smug nag 'khyil //
NK022(za)001:11041: dz+wa la man+dala ha la ha la ra /
NK022(za)001:11042: me ri lag chu'i phyag rgya yis //
NK022(za)001:11043: gnas sam dkyil 'khor bskor bar bya'o //
NK022(za)001:11044: de ltar bar chad skabs med par //
NK022(za)001:11045: srung ba'i go cha dam pa yin //
NK022(za)001:11046: rnam pa lnga yi rdor dbyugs pa'i //
NK022(za)001:11047: ma nges tshad la thig gnyis gdab /
NK022(za)001:11048: bskrul tshig srog dang ldan pa yis //
NK022(za)001:11049: sa gzhi yongs su gzung bar bya //
NK022(za)001:11050: brtsam par bya ba'i las chen po //
NK022(za)001:11051: dngos grub 'byung bar byed pa'i brten //
NK022(za)001:11052: phyag rgya chen po'i gzugs mchog gis //
NK022(za)001:11053: stegs bu legs par sbyangs na 'grub //
NK022(za)001:11054: mtshon pa 'khrid par byed pa yi //
NK022(za)001:11055: rdul tshon 'dus byas rgyu rnams 'dus byas la //
NK022(za)001:11056: gnyan ma'i dkyil 'khor bshad bgyi ba //
NK022(za)001:11057: so sor brtags pa'i bshad bgyi ba //
NK022(za)001:11058: brtan zhing ngos 'jam kham bu la //
NK022(za)001:11060: kha dog lnga yi gzugs byas nas //
NK022(za)001:11061: dpe ni mtshan ma'i dngos grub ster //
NK022(za)001:11062: shin shun ras sam dur khrod kyi //
NK022(za)001:11063: zhing chen ras la kha dog lngas //
NK022(za)001:11064: phyag rgya 'bar ba'i gzugs bris nas //
NK022(za)001:11066: rdo dang shel rdo la sogs pa //
NK022(za)001:11067: dung dang ba so'i rgyu las ni //
NK022(za)001:11068: mkhas pas 'bur du brtod byas nas //
NK022(za)001:11070: gser dngul rin chen la sogs pa //
NK022(za)001:11071: lcags zangs 'khor ba'i rgyu dag las //
NK022(za)001:11072: mkhan gyi blugs te ma nyams na //
NK022(za)001:11073: de yang mtshan ma'i brten du 'gyur //
NK022(za)001:11074: blag sha byang chub shing la sogs //
NK022(za)001:11075: rgyu shing yal ga mnyen pa las //
NK022(za)001:11076: phyag rgya gzugs de legs sbyar na //
NK022(za)001:11077: de yang rten la mkhas par bya //
NK022(za)001:11078: mnyen zhing spyin pa'i mchog rnams la //
NK022(za)001:11079: bzhin dang dril khungs legs sbyar te //
NK022(za)001:11080: phyag rgya chen po'i gzugs byas te //
NK022(za)001:11082: de la sogs pa'i rgyu rnams la //
NK022(za)001:11083: yi ge'am yang na mtshan brtags sam //
NK022(za)001:11084: ming ngam thig le rdzas la bri //
NK022(za)001:11085: bsgrubs na mtshan ma'i rten du 'gyur //
NK022(za)001:11086: de las re zhig 'dir bshad pa //
NK022(za)001:11087: stegs bu la brten mtshan ma dag /
NK022(za)001:11088: bsgrub pa'i don du rtags bzung pa //
NK022(za)001:11089: brtsam pa'i thabs ni 'di lta ste //
NK022(za)001:11090: stegs bu mdzes shing mnyam bya ste //
NK022(za)001:11091: kun tu gru bzhi mnyam byas la //
NK022(za)001:11092: bdud rtsi lnga yi sbyor ba yis //
NK022(za)001:11093: me long lta bur snying por byas //
NK022(za)001:11094: rang byung rnam dag byin brlabs can //
NK022(za)001:11095: ye shes rang 'byung grub pa'i rdzas //
NK022(za)001:11096: bka' gsang rmad 'byung pho brang du //
NK022(za)001:11097: dur khrod rdzas lngas brkyal bsnul la //
NK022(za)001:11098: rdo rje srad bus thig gdab pa'i //
NK022(za)001:11099: cho ga'i rnam pas bshad bgyi ba //
NK022(za)001:11100: gsang ba'i lcang lo 'khril mngas dang //
NK022(za)001:11101: rdo rje rgyun thig la sogs pa //
NK022(za)001:11104: sum sgril snyoms pa'i tshad ldan pas //
NK022(za)001:11105: ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin gsal //
NK022(za)001:11106: rgyu de byin gyis brlabs pa'i thabs //
NK022(za)001:11107: thabs dang shes rab 'brel pa yi //
NK022(za)001:11110: rdo rje gsang ba thabs kyi snyad //
NK022(za)001:11112: nges par brtags te 'dir bzung ba //
NK022(za)001:11113: mtshan ldan bkra shis gsang ba'i yum //
NK022(za)001:11114: smin skyung ring la phyag sor 'phra //
NK022(za)001:11115: tshig mig bzlum la phra bar bshad //
NK022(za)001:11116: kha nas ut+pala ngad ldang zhing //
NK022(za)001:11117: lus la ga pur tsan+dana dri //
NK022(za)001:11118: yid 'ong mtshan ldan rked skabs phyed //
NK022(za)001:11120: so dkar thags dam dkar dmar phyed //
NK022(za)001:11121: mig gi rgyus ring smin skyus ring //
NK022(za)001:11122: zar ma'i me tog rgyas 'dra'i spyan //
NK022(za)001:11124: sna bzo mdog gsal pad+ma'i rigs //
NK022(za)001:11125: lus drang skye ring sems ma'i tshul //
NK022(za)001:11127: so dkar thags dam 'khril bag chags //
NK022(za)001:11129: skad ni ngang pa gzhon tshul sgrogs //
NK022(za)001:11130: cir yang mdzes pa'i ltas tshul ldan //
NK022(za)001:11131: skyes bu bla mas yum du bzung //
NK022(za)001:11132: gzungs ma byin gyis brlab pa ni //
NK022(za)001:11133: yum gyi phung po gnas lnga ni //
NK022(za)001:11134: bde bar gshegs pa'ii sa bon lnga //
NK022(za)001:11136: brgyas btab byin brlabs dbang bskur nas //
NK022(za)001:11137: rigs lnga yum lnga'i sku mchog gsal //
NK022(za)001:11138: rdo rje yab la'ang de bzhin te //
NK022(za)001:11139: 'di ltar gsal bar gyur pa dang //
NK022(za)001:11140: yum gyi mkha' la me ri bsgom //
NK022(za)001:11141: gsang ba dbus kyi zla kham la //
NK022(za)001:11142: byang chub sems kyi spro bsdu bya //
NK022(za)001:11143: gzugs brnyan ji ltar gsal ba bzhin //
NK022(za)001:11144: yum gyi mkha' la'ang de bzhin no //
NK022(za)001:11145: de nas rdo rje'i tshig 'di yis //
NK022(za)001:11146: las kyi yum la nges par bsgom //
NK022(za)001:11147: shes rab lha mo gsang ba'i yum //
NK022(za)001:11149: chags pa'i tshul gyis thabs la 'khyud //
NK022(za)001:11151: 'dzum pa'i mdangs kyis zla kham sbyor //
NK022(za)001:11152: gsang ba'i byang chub sems 'dren ma //
NK022(za)001:11153: khyod ni lha mo rgyal ba'i sras //
NK022(za)001:11154: rang bzhin chos kyi mtshan ldan pa //
NK022(za)001:11155: rdo rje las kyi yum yin pas //
NK022(za)001:11156: gsang ba'i las rnams kun byos shig /
NK022(za)001:11157: lag pa'i 'khor lo gzhal yas su //
NK022(za)001:11158: nyi zla 'bar ba'i tshogs bkod de //
NK022(za)001:11159: gsang ba'i byang chub dkar dmar 'di //
NK022(za)001:11160: thig le'i ngo bo yi ger gdab //
NK022(za)001:11161: las kyi rdo rje 'bar ba yi //
NK022(za)001:11162: rdo rje gar gyi phyag rgya yis //
NK022(za)001:11163: byang chub sems kyi thig 'di drongs //
NK022(za)001:11164: rdo rje gsang ba'i las 'di gyis //
NK022(za)001:11165: tsan tra da ra hri zhes pa'i //
NK022(za)001:11166: gsang ba sngags kyi sbyor ba 'dis //
NK022(za)001:11167: rdo rje nyi ma'i gzhal yas su //
NK022(za)001:11168: rdo rje dpal be'u 'od kyi thig /
NK022(za)001:11169: me long ye shes rang bzhin can //
NK022(za)001:11170: rnal 'byor can gyi gdab par bya //
NK022(za)001:11171: de bzhin rin chen 'bar ba'i gzhal //
NK022(za)001:11173: dpag med nam mkha'i gzhal yas su //
NK022(za)001:11174: rigs kyi dpal be'u 'od kyi thig /
NK022(za)001:11175: ye shes bzhi yi rang bzhin gyis //
NK022(za)001:11176: rnal 'byor can gyis gdab par bya'o //
NK022(za)001:11177: rdo rje nam mkha' 'khor los bskor //
NK022(za)001:11178: thabs dang shes rab zung ya bzhi //
NK022(za)001:11179: so so'i phyag rgya gnas nas ni //
NK022(za)001:11180: nam mkha'i dbus kyi snying po la //
NK022(za)001:11181: srad bu bzhi yi rgya gram bri //
NK022(za)001:11182: de nas rdo rje bstan pa'i sa //
NK022(za)001:11183: dbus kyi pho brang dgu pa ni //
NK022(za)001:11184: rdo rje srad bu'i thig chen gyis //
NK022(za)001:11185: phyag rgya bzhugs pa'i gnas rnams kun //
NK022(za)001:11186: che chung med par snyoms par bya //
NK022(za)001:11187: 'di ni rdo rje mu khyud bdun //
NK022(za)001:11188: 'byung ba'i rim pa drug bar du //
NK022(za)001:11190: gru chad phyi nang sgo snam dang //
NK022(za)001:11191: khyams lnga sgo lnga srad bus dbye //
NK022(za)001:11192: yang na pho brang rigs lnga la //
NK022(za)001:11193: sum brtseg sgo yi thig tu bya //
NK022(za)001:11194: srad bu'i bya ba de rdzogs nas //
NK022(za)001:11195: gol sgrib rtag chad skyon bral ba'i //
NK022(za)001:11196: che chung ya yo med pa ste //
NK022(za)001:11197: rdo rje dbu ma'i thag 'di bgyi //
NK022(za)001:11198: chos kyi dbyings kyi gzhal yas su //
NK022(za)001:11199: mi dmigs bdal ba'i man+dala la //
NK022(za)001:11200: ye shes lnga yi thig 'phros pas //
NK022(za)001:11201: bde chen rnam pa phyag rgya'i tshogs //
NK022(za)001:11202: kun gzhi nam mkha'i gzhal yas su //
NK022(za)001:11203: nyon mongs rtogs pa'i man+dala la //
NK022(za)001:11206: mkha' dbyings gsang ba'i gzhal yas su //
NK022(za)001:11208: byang chub sems kyi thig 'phros pas //
NK022(za)001:11209: ye shes sems dpa' gsal ba'i tshogs //
NK022(za)001:11210: bkra shis dben pa'i gzhal yas su //
NK022(za)001:11211: mtshan ma rten gyi man+dala la //
NK022(za)001:11212: rdo rje srad bu'i thig 'phros pas //
NK022(za)001:11214: las 'di dus su bgegs bskrad pa //
NK022(za)001:11215: stong gsum gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK022(za)001:11217: gsang ba'i dam la mi gnas pa'i //
NK022(za)001:11218: 'byung po skye bo gdol pa can //
NK022(za)001:11219: rdo rje rtsal gyi h'u rings las //
NK022(za)001:11220: rdo rje mtshon cha'i bu yug 'tshub //
NK022(za)001:11221: phyogs mtshams bla 'og khro bor gtams //
NK022(za)001:11222: 'bar ba gsang ba'i mtshams bzung ste //
NK022(za)001:11223: phyi rol sde pa'i 'drul rnams bcad //
NK022(za)001:11224: rdo rje mtshon cha 'bar ba'i me //
NK022(za)001:11225: bsreg dang 'joms pa'i las rnams la //
NK022(za)001:11226: 'joms par mdzad pa'i drag shul can //
NK022(za)001:11228: sta gon gnas pa'ang gsum shes te //
NK022(za)001:11229: lha mi'i yo byad rnam pa gsum //
NK022(za)001:11230: thog ma lha yang 'di bzhin te //
NK022(za)001:11231: srad bu bya ba kun byas nas //
NK022(za)001:11232: shes rab yum gyi 'jo tshul gyis //
NK022(za)001:11233: rdzas mchog 'bar ba'i thig le ni //
NK022(za)001:11234: rnam pa gnyis kyi 'di gu dag /
NK022(za)001:11235: srin bal spe'u sbyar ba yis //
NK022(za)001:11236: gnas lnga dag gi gzhal yas su //
NK022(za)001:11237: gsang ba thabs kyi thig le dag /
NK022(za)001:11238: kun tu zla ba'i thig le bya //
NK022(za)001:11239: rdo rje rgyal po 'phags rnams kyis //
NK022(za)001:11240: so so'i sngags dang rtsa ba'i rgya //
NK022(za)001:11241: so so'i gtang thabs sbyar nas kyang //
NK022(za)001:11242: de dag gnas su byin gyis brlabs //
NK022(za)001:11243: lhag pa'i ting 'dzin mchog rdzogs bya //
NK022(za)001:11244: dam tshig phyag rgya mu yis gshegs //
NK022(za)001:11245: de bzhin mi'ang rgyal po dang //
NK022(za)001:11246: slob bu khrus byas sta gon gnas //
NK022(za)001:11247: yo byad dkyil 'khor chas gos dang //
NK022(za)001:11248: mchod rdzas dbang rdzas 'tshogs par bya'o //
NK022(za)001:11249: rin chen lnga rgyus byas pa'i tshon //
NK022(za)001:11250: gter dang mu tig byi ru dang //
NK022(za)001:11251: in tra ni le ma rgad sogs //
NK022(za)001:11252: 'byor pa mchog gis brtsal bar bya //
NK022(za)001:11253: de bzhin 'bru dang rdul tshogs bsham //
NK022(za)001:11254: kha dog lnga sogs byin brlabs la /
NK022(za)001:11255: ma mthong rmongs pa bkri ba'i phyir //
NK022(za)001:11256: rang bzhin ci 'dra dbye bar bya'o //
NK022(za)001:11257: de nas bri ba'i las brtsam pa'am //
NK022(za)001:11258: blo ldan g.yas g.yon byin brlabs te //
NK022(za)001:11259: rdo rje rgyal pos ting 'dzin bskyed //
NK022(za)001:11260: gzhan rnams dbus nas bri bar brtsam //
NK022(za)001:11261: zlum sor bzhi spang pa'i dbus //
NK022(za)001:11262: zhi bar bris la me 'od bskor //
NK022(za)001:11263: le'u tshe dbu ma'i dkyil 'khor du'o //
NK022(za)001:11264: dbus kyi pho brang dgu pa ni //
NK022(za)001:11265: rigs kyi kha dog phyogs bzhir sbyar //
NK022(za)001:11266: mtshams ni 'dren mar brtsam par bya //
NK022(za)001:11267: mu khyud bdun dang 'khor lo drug /
NK022(za)001:11270: bar 'khyams lngas mdzes gru chad sgo //
NK022(za)001:11271: pho brang de yi gnas rnams su //
NK022(za)001:11272: phyag rgya'i tshul rnams bri ba ni //
NK022(za)001:11273: pho brang lte bar gtso gzungs nyid //
NK022(za)001:11274: le tse phyogs la zhe sdang sogs //
NK022(za)001:11275: de bzhin mtshams bzhir cho 'phrul bzhi //
NK022(za)001:11276: mu khyud mthar zad yan chad du //
NK022(za)001:11277: yab yum drug cu rtsa drug pa'o //
NK022(za)001:11278: 'khor lo dam tshig tshad med bzhi //
NK022(za)001:11280: tsa ka li la sogs pa bri //
NK022(za)001:11281: de bzhin za byed yab yum bzhi //
NK022(za)001:11282: las kyi lha ste he ru ka /
NK022(za)001:11283: 'khor lo tha ma rtsibs la dgod //
NK022(za)001:11284: gnas dang yul gyi phyag rgya dag /
NK022(za)001:11285: gru chad phyi dang nang la bkram //
NK022(za)001:11286: de bzhin sgo bzhir sgo ma bkod //
NK022(za)001:11287: h'u chen bcu yi yab yum dag /
NK022(za)001:11288: shin tu mdzes par dang po la'o //
NK022(za)001:11289: de nyid la ni ma brgyad dang //
NK022(za)001:11290: gi nga chen bco brgyad rgyas par dgod //
NK022(za)001:11292: shugs 'gro brgyad kyang de bzhin no //
NK022(za)001:11293: gsum pa'i 'khyams la phra men brgyad //
NK022(za)001:11294: de bzhin 'bar ma brgyad rnams bri //
NK022(za)001:11295: bzhi pa'i khyams la phor thogs brgyad //
NK022(za)001:11296: de bzhin srin mo gzhong thogs brgyad //
NK022(za)001:11297: kun tu mdzes par bri bar bya //
NK022(za)001:11298: lnga pa'i khyams ni tha ma la //
NK022(za)001:11299: rdo rje slas dang bran mo dang //
NK022(za)001:11300: pho nya la sogs rgyas par bkram //
NK022(za)001:11301: de'ang tshul du bkod pa ni //
NK022(za)001:11302: gong ma dag gi rgyu rnams las //
NK022(za)001:11303: tsaka li la sogs pa dang //
NK022(za)001:11304: ji ltar 'byor pa de ltar bri //
NK022(za)001:11305: dkyil 'khor chen po'i phyi rol du //
NK022(za)001:11306: rdo rje spun dang me ri dang //
NK022(za)001:11307: de bzhin rdo rje'i rig 'dzin sogs //
NK022(za)001:11308: rjes su mthun par bri bar bya //
NK022(za)001:11309: mchod pa'i yo byad thams cad dang //
NK022(za)001:11310: rmad du 'byung ba'i rdzas mchog dang //
NK022(za)001:11311: rdo rje gsang ba'i rim pa bzhin //
NK022(za)001:11312: nang dang phyi ru dgod par bya //
NK022(za)001:11313: de min 'khor lo dpal be'u dang //
NK022(za)001:11314: zur brgyad le tshe sgo gsum bri //
NK022(za)001:11315: rgyan ni rin chen sna tshogs dang //
NK022(za)001:11316: pan tsa ra ga ta ra na //
NK022(za)001:11317: dra ba gzhal yas mgul 'khor dang //
NK022(za)001:11318: rta babs bzhis ni rnam par brgyan //
NK022(za)001:11319: za ra tshags dang chun 'phyang dang //
NK022(za)001:11320: dril bu g.yer kha sna tshogs bri //
NK022(za)001:11321: ye shes lda ldi mngon bris shing //
NK022(za)001:11322: rdo rje'i rgyan dang 'phan blubs dang //
NK022(za)001:11323: sbrul nag chen po'i za ra tshags //
NK022(za)001:11324: mu tig rin chen phreng ba dang //
NK022(za)001:11326: bang rim che chung khog smad stod //
NK022(za)001:11327: ring thung yan lag dbang po'i phreng //
NK022(za)001:11328: rdo rje kun tu spras par bri //
NK022(za)001:11329: dbus su nya chen ka gdung la //
NK022(za)001:11330: zla bas ka ba'i brgyan byas la //
NK022(za)001:11331: nyi ma'i ka lo sbrul chun gyis //
NK022(za)001:11332: ka rgyan byas pa bri bar bya //
NK022(za)001:11333: so so'i byin gyis brlab byas te //
NK022(za)001:11334: nus pa'i mthu dang ldan byas pa //
NK022(za)001:11335: sa thig sum sgril sku gsung thugs //
NK022(za)001:11336: yi ge gsum sbyangs rab tu gnas //
NK022(za)001:11337: de bzhin gnam thig ye shes lnga'o //
NK022(za)001:11338: rang bzhin nyid du gnyis med kyang //
NK022(za)001:11339: tshon la rigs kyi yig sbyangs la //
NK022(za)001:11340: ye shes rin chen gsum du gsal //
NK022(za)001:11341: de ltar slob bu gnas pa'ang //
NK022(za)001:11342: 'byor pa'i rkyen rnams tshang byas na //
NK022(za)001:11343: sta gon tshe na las brgyas sbyar //
NK022(za)001:11344: shar lho man+dala brtsams byas te //
NK022(za)001:11345: slob bu phyi'i dri sbyangs shing //
NK022(za)001:11346: chas gos bzang ldan thal sbyar la //
NK022(za)001:11347: rmongs pa gsang phyir sems bskyed do //
NK022(za)001:11350: 'khor ba thams cad bsgral ba'i phyir //
NK022(za)001:11351: rnal 'byor can la bshad par bya //
NK022(za)001:11352: dkyil 'khor don dang mtshan nyid dang //
NK022(za)001:11354: sku la yongs su rdzogs tshul rnams //
NK022(za)001:11355: gsal byas drod pa bskyed byas te //
NK022(za)001:11356: 'jig rten drug las drang byas te //
NK022(za)001:11357: 'gyur dbang ma nges par bzhag bya //
NK022(za)001:11358: lha bskyed srung ba byas zin nas //
NK022(za)001:11359: ku sha chu dang srung skud dang //
NK022(za)001:11360: so shing sbyin bya brus bshal te //
NK022(za)001:11361: srung zhing mtshan ma rtog tu bzhugs //
NK022(za)001:11362: gang zhig ngan pa lus srungs la //
NK022(za)001:11363: thams cad ngan na drag pos sreg /
NK022(za)001:11364: des ni skyon dbang 'gyur ma yin //
NK022(za)001:11365: dkyil 'khor rab gnas bshad par bya //
NK022(za)001:11366: mchod pa'i ling long spyad par bsham //
NK022(za)001:11367: 'phel ba'i sreg sbyangs shar brtsams te //
NK022(za)001:11368: rab gnas yo byad ldan par bya //
NK022(za)001:11369: mkhar bsil ba yu lngas byugs la //
NK022(za)001:11370: bkra shis shing shun rnams kyis phyi //
NK022(za)001:11371: chu yis gzugs brnyan gyis gzugs sbyangs //
NK022(za)001:11373: gzugs brnyan rang sems ma skyes pa'i //
NK022(za)001:11374: snang stong dbyer med gsal byas te //
NK022(za)001:11375: gzhal yas rims rdzogs bcas par bskyed //
NK022(za)001:11376: so so'i gdan ldan sa bon nyid //
NK022(za)001:11377: rnam gsum gang yin lhar bskyed de //
NK022(za)001:11378: dbang dang byin brlabs nus pa bskyed //
NK022(za)001:11379: 'jig rten dbang po'i chos lugs su //
NK022(za)001:11380: rang bzhin yul nas phab byas la //
NK022(za)001:11381: bstims brtan gzi byin ldan par bya //
NK022(za)001:11382: de la dbu brgyan cod pan sogs //
NK022(za)001:11383: sku yi rgyan rnams dbul ba dang //
NK022(za)001:11384: so so'i gdan dbul dbang skyon gsal //
NK022(za)001:11385: chu bdun khrus gsol la sogs dang //
NK022(za)001:11386: mchod pa bla na yod med kun //
NK022(za)001:11387: ji ltar 'byor ldan nan tan dbul //
NK022(za)001:11388: rgyal srid longs spyod bcas pa dang //
NK022(za)001:11389: glu bro gar dang rol mor bcas //
NK022(za)001:11390: gling bzhi ye bkram man+dala la //
NK022(za)001:11391: dbul rtsegs gzhung bzhin mthun par brtsam //
NK022(za)001:11392: sbyin sreg dus dang dngos po ste //
NK022(za)001:11393: dus ni sa dang sta gon dang //
NK022(za)001:11394: rab gnas dbang gi dus rnams su //
NK022(za)001:11395: zhi drag rgyas dbang ngo bor sbyar //
NK022(za)001:11396: de ltar gang zhig rtsom byed pa //
NK022(za)001:11397: shin tu'ang shis par 'gyur ba yin //
NK022(za)001:11399: chas gos lnga ldan shar sgor 'jug /
NK022(za)001:11400: rin chen snyim thogs lha mngon bya //
NK022(za)001:11401: bskul ba'i 'od kyis gzi ldan bya //
NK022(za)001:11402: sangs rgyas bde mchog thams cad kyi //
NK022(za)001:11403: rdo rje dbang mchog thob bya ba'i //
NK022(za)001:11405: bdag gi slob ma bzhugs par bgyi //
NK022(za)001:11406: bzod pa mdzad de dgongs su gsol //
NK022(za)001:11407: 'dzum pas gnang ba thob par bsam //
NK022(za)001:11408: snod du rung ba'i slob ma dag /
NK022(za)001:11409: gsang ba'i don du 'jug pa na //
NK022(za)001:11410: lus kyi dri ma sbyang ba'i phyir //
NK022(za)001:11411: tsan dan chu yi bkru bar bya //
NK022(za)001:11412: rin chen snyim pas mdzes thogs nas //
NK022(za)001:11413: dmar po ras kyis gdong g.yogs bya //
NK022(za)001:11414: e ma ho bde mchog dga' tshal 'dir //
NK022(za)001:11416: dga' ba byang chub sems bskyed nas //
NK022(za)001:11417: gsang ba'i don 'di spyad par bgyi //
NK022(za)001:11419: skyes bu chen pos bzhugs su gsol //
NK022(za)001:11421: 'jig rten drug tu drangs nas kyang //
NK022(za)001:11423: 'gyur dbang ma nges pa la bzhag /
NK022(za)001:11424: phyi phyir dang po yin pas na //
NK022(za)001:11425: byis pa blo shed ma bye bas //
NK022(za)001:11426: bzang ngan bde sdug mi shes shing //
NK022(za)001:11427: bstan dang gsang ba'i dmigs mi phyed //
NK022(za)001:11428: dpa' bo chen po dgongs su gsol //
NK022(za)001:11429: bdag cag skal ldan 'dus pa'i tshogs //
NK022(za)001:11431: rgyal ba'i sras su bzung du gsol //
NK022(za)001:11432: skal ldan 'dus pa'i tshogs chen khyod //
NK022(za)001:11434: su dag 'ongs pa slar mi ldog /
NK022(za)001:11435: bdag cag mtha' yas sems can rnams //
NK022(za)001:11436: don gyi sangs rgyas yin mod kyang /
NK022(za)001:11437: rtog pa'i dbang gis 'khor ba las //
NK022(za)001:11438: byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed do //
NK022(za)001:11439: sems nyid sangs rgyas yin pa la //
NK022(za)001:11440: mus pas sgribs pas de ma shes //
NK022(za)001:11441: byang chub sems kyi lam 'di nas //
NK022(za)001:11442: sangs rgyas pa la 'jug par bgyi //
NK022(za)001:11443: bde chen lhun grub gzhal yas 'dir //
NK022(za)001:11444: rnam par thar pa'i sgo bzhi nas //
NK022(za)001:11445: tshad med thugs rje'i sgo phye nas //
NK022(za)001:11446: byams pa'i zhal bzangs bstan du gsol //
NK022(za)001:11447: e ma ho skal ldan 'dus pa'i tshogs //
NK022(za)001:11448: byang chub lam la bzud pa'i phyir //
NK022(za)001:11449: rdo rje gsang sgo dbye bar bya //
NK022(za)001:11450: pho brang rmad 'byung gzhal yas na //
NK022(za)001:11451: rgyal ba rgya mtsho kun bzhugs la //
NK022(za)001:11452: rnal 'byor nges par lhag par mos //
NK022(za)001:11453: rdo rje gdung la skyabs su mchi //
NK022(za)001:11454: rdo rje rnal 'byor mchog gi lha //
NK022(za)001:11456: rdo rje can la phyag 'tshal te //
NK022(za)001:11457: byams mgon khyod la skyabs su mchi //
NK022(za)001:11458: de skad gsol ba btab pa dang //
NK022(za)001:11459: rnal 'byor chen po'i zhabs gnyis la //
NK022(za)001:11460: 'jug pa de yi spyi bos gtug /
NK022(za)001:11461: sangs rgyas bde mchog thams cad kyi //
NK022(za)001:11462: rdo rje gsang mchog gsum las byung //
NK022(za)001:11463: srid pa gsum gyis phyag bgyis pas //
NK022(za)001:11464: dbang bskur gnang ba chen po sbyin //
NK022(za)001:11465: a ti ho sta d+h+ri sta kha //
NK022(za)001:11466: thog ma med pa'i dus mtha' nas //
NK022(za)001:11467: ma rig log rtog dbang gis na //
NK022(za)001:11468: sdig pa bgyis pa ci mchis pa //
NK022(za)001:11469: de dag thams cad so sor bshags //
NK022(za)001:11470: rgyal mchog skyes bu khyed ci 'dra //
NK022(za)001:11471: de 'dra kho nar spyod par bgyi //
NK022(za)001:11472: spyod pa bsam yas rmad 'byung ba //
NK022(za)001:11473: 'gro la phan pa'i don du spyad //
NK022(za)001:11475: ma bsgral ba ni bsgral bar bgyi //
NK022(za)001:11476: ma grol pa ni grol bar bgyi //
NK022(za)001:11477: dbugs ma phyung ba dbugs dbyung ste //
NK022(za)001:11478: mya ngan 'das pa'i zhing khams su //
NK022(za)001:11479: snying po byang chub nyid du sbyar //
NK022(za)001:11480: khyod ni dga' ba ci la dga' //
NK022(za)001:11481: khyod ni dad pa ci la dad //
NK022(za)001:11482: khyod ni mos pa ci la mos //
NK022(za)001:11483: khyod ni 'dod pa ci lta ba //
NK022(za)001:11484: bdag cag skal ldan bde chen po //
NK022(za)001:11485: rab dges sems la bdag cag dga' //
NK022(za)001:11486: mchog nyid don la bdag cag dad //
NK022(za)001:11487: e ma ho bde mchog dga' tshal 'dir //
NK022(za)001:11488: sangs rgyas mdzad dka' spyad nas ni //
NK022(za)001:11489: 'gro ba thams cad sgral bar mos //
NK022(za)001:11490: rgyal ba pha dang 'gro rnams la //
NK022(za)001:11491: tshogs phyir rnam smin lus dbul te //
NK022(za)001:11492: bdag cag dregs pa'i mtha' la zhen pa rnams //
NK022(za)001:11493: las dang las kyis 'khor ba'i dra ba 'di //
NK022(za)001:11494: bka' yi tan tshogs zhib mos ma bkrol zhing //
NK022(za)001:11495: shes rab zab mos dmigs su ma phye bas //
NK022(za)001:11496: rang bzhin ye shes blo dang mi ldan zhing //
NK022(za)001:11497: nges par legs pa'i gros kyis ma chod de //
NK022(za)001:11498: gar thabs glog gi zhags pas ma zin pas //
NK022(za)001:11499: rnam shes las kyi rgya mtsho lbas bsgribs te //
NK022(za)001:11500: de nyid de bzhin nyid du ngo ma mtshar //
NK022(za)001:11501: gti mug rang sems bdag tu bzung bas nongs //
NK022(za)001:11502: ngan du 'gyod pas nongs pa'i tshul bzung nas //
NK022(za)001:11503: dpa' bo chen po khyod la skyabs su mchi //
NK022(za)001:11504: dngos por spyad phyir bdag lus gdan du dbul //
NK022(za)001:11505: thabs mkhas thugs rjes lus 'di bzhes su gsol //
NK022(za)001:11506: g.yas g.yon nyi zlar yig 'bru bcu //
NK022(za)001:11507: sbyor ba 'od kyis sgrib pa bral //
NK022(za)001:11513: gsang ba mchog gi dbang po yis //
NK022(za)001:11514: rgyud sbyangs rgyud drug lam sgo bcad //
NK022(za)001:11516: dkyil 'khor chen por gsal btan te //
NK022(za)001:11517: phyag rgya dbang dang bcas pa yis //
NK022(za)001:11518: 'khor ba'i rgyud rnams sbyangs bar bya //
NK022(za)001:11519: 'jug pa de yi gnas lnga ru //
NK022(za)001:11520: brgyud drug sa bon bskyed nas kyang //
NK022(za)001:11521: h'u lnga dag gis gnan par bya //
NK022(za)001:11522: 'jug pa de yi spyi bor ni //
NK022(za)001:11523: sa yi ye shes las bkrun pa //
NK022(za)001:11524: pad+ma kha bzhi bye ba la //
NK022(za)001:11525: mi dang lha yi sa bon dgod //
NK022(za)001:11526: shar lho nub dang byang dag tu //
NK022(za)001:11527: lha min dud 'gro yi dwags dang //
NK022(za)001:11528: dmyal ba rnams kyi sa bon gdab //
NK022(za)001:11529: h'u gis lam sgo bcad par bya //
NK022(za)001:11530: lag gnyis mthe chung mthe bos mnan //
NK022(za)001:11531: sor mo gsum sbyar dpral bar snol //
NK022(za)001:11532: lha dang lha min gnas dag tu //
NK022(za)001:11533: mi gtong bzlog pa'i phyag rgya yin //
NK022(za)001:11534: lag gnyis bsnol nas mchan khung bstam //
NK022(za)001:11535: mi yi khams nas bzlog pa'i rgya //
NK022(za)001:11536: khu tshur bcangs te 'bru sbreng nas //
NK022(za)001:11537: g.yon gyi steng du mnan pa ni //
NK022(za)001:11538: byol song gnas nas bzlog pa'i rgya //
NK022(za)001:11539: thal mo mnyam sbyar gus rtse sprad //
NK022(za)001:11540: gung mo rgyab tu srin lag snol //
NK022(za)001:11542: yi dwags khams las bzlog pa'i rgya //
NK022(za)001:11543: g.yon thogs g.yas kyi rgyab sbyar te //
NK022(za)001:11544: srin lag gung mdzub gcig nas gcig /
NK022(za)001:11545: 'khyud pa dmyal ba'i sgo gcod rgya //
NK022(za)001:11546: lag pa'i phyag rgya bcas nas ni //
NK022(za)001:11547: ngag gi rdo rje sngags brjod pas //
NK022(za)001:11548: kye ma r+au tra kro ta ki h'u /
NK022(za)001:11549: h+r+ai sa ma pa ta h'u /
NK022(za)001:11550: rnam shes rigs kyi lhar bskyed de //
NK022(za)001:11551: go chas khyab byas srung bar bya //
NK022(za)001:11552: sku gsung thugs su brtan par bya //
NK022(za)001:11554: mi phyed gsang ba'i rnal 'byor pa //
NK022(za)001:11555: gnyis med don gyi dbyings las byung //
NK022(za)001:11556: dbyings ni mi 'jig rdo rje ste //
NK022(za)001:11558: gsang ba gsum gyi dbyings nyid du //
NK022(za)001:11559: gnyis su med par nan tan mdzod //
NK022(za)001:11560: rdo rje can gyi rnal 'byor khyod //
NK022(za)001:11561: rdo rje can du nges gcig na //
NK022(za)001:11562: gsang ba gsum du mnyam pa'i phyir //
NK022(za)001:11563: mi phyed rdo rje'i dam tshig sbyin //
NK022(za)001:11564: mi phyed rdo rje'i dam tshig ni //
NK022(za)001:11565: gsang ba gsum gyi dbyings nas phyung //
NK022(za)001:11566: dkyil 'khor gsum gyi dam tshig ni //
NK022(za)001:11567: grub na 'jig pa'i dus med do //
NK022(za)001:11568: badz+ra a mri ta a hi hi sarba man h'u h+r+ai tha zhes /
NK022(za)001:11569: bdud rtsi lnga lce la thim par bzhag /
NK022(za)001:11570: rdo rje dam tshig sdom pa rnams //
NK022(za)001:11571: thams cad thams cad 'bog par bya //
NK022(za)001:11572: slob ma'i gnyer yang dbog par bya //
NK022(za)001:11573: kye rig 'dzin rdo rje bu mchog khyod //
NK022(za)001:11574: rnal 'byor rgyal ba'i sras yin gyis //
NK022(za)001:11575: gzhan la gsang ba ma smra shig /
NK022(za)001:11576: gal te smra na dmyal bar 'tshig /
NK022(za)001:11578: rigs mi mthun yang dam tshig gcig /
NK022(za)001:11579: 'da' bar dka' bas bsdus pas na //
NK022(za)001:11580: dam tshig can du nan tan mdzod //
NK022(za)001:11581: gsang ba gsum gyi dam pa rnams //
NK022(za)001:11582: khyed kyis rab tu bslus 'gyur na //
NK022(za)001:11583: de kun khros nas khrag chen po //
NK022(za)001:11584: nyams pa'ii snying nas drangs te 'thungs //
NK022(za)001:11585: rgyal ba kun dang mnyam sbyor ba'i //
NK022(za)001:11587: rgyal ba thams cad bslus pa yin //
NK022(za)001:11591: i nan te na ra kan /
NK022(za)001:11595: si ti pyi ta badz+ra a mri ta ho kha /
NK022(za)001:11596: rdo rje tha tshig chu blud nas //
NK022(za)001:11597: rdo rje gal chen mna' mdor ro //
NK022(za)001:11598: de nas dam tshig chen po bsgrags //
NK022(za)001:11599: ma 'ongs sangs rgyas blo ldan khyod //
NK022(za)001:11600: bla med ye shes bskyed pa'i phyir //
NK022(za)001:11601: rgyud sbyongs gsang ba'i lam du zhugs //
NK022(za)001:11602: rang gi me long nyid la ltos //
NK022(za)001:11603: gsang gsum nyid du bkod pa yi //
NK022(za)001:11604: gsang chen gsang ba rab bsags pa //
NK022(za)001:11605: mthong bas de bzhin nyid du 'gyur //
NK022(za)001:11606: gzhan min rang byung de kho na'o //
NK022(za)001:11607: blo chung rnams la ma smra shig /
NK022(za)001:11608: gal te smras par gyur na ni //
NK022(za)001:11609: tha tshigs drags pa nyams gyur nas //
NK022(za)001:11610: me chen 'bar ba'i gnas su bsreg /
NK022(za)001:11611: sngon tshe gong nas 'brel pa yi //
NK022(za)001:11612: bdag gi nye na gang lags pa //
NK022(za)001:11613: las 'phro dang ni thugs rje yis //
NK022(za)001:11614: da lta nyid du 'bab par shog /
NK022(za)001:11615: me tog phog pa'i lha byin te //
NK022(za)001:11616: rang mtshan thugs dam h'u bcas kyis //
NK022(za)001:11617: dam tshig bstan la lcags kyus drang //
NK022(za)001:11618: legs nyes gsal byas phyag rgya bzhis //
NK022(za)001:11619: kha na'i snying la bstim byas te //
NK022(za)001:11620: rang bzhin gnyis med gsal bar bya //
NK022(za)001:11621: yang na thabs kyi gar thabs kyis //
NK022(za)001:11622: bde ba chen po'i lha nyid dbab //
NK022(za)001:11623: so so'i rigs kyi khyad par dag /
NK022(za)001:11624: ji ltar bsgom pa'i nan tan gyis //
NK022(za)001:11625: gsang ba'i mig ni dbye bar bya //
NK022(za)001:11626: badz+ra tsak+shu pra be sha ya //
NK022(za)001:11627: dkyil 'khor mngon mthong che ba bskyed //
NK022(za)001:11628: rin chen chag shing lag thogs te //
NK022(za)001:11629: le tshe dgu dang 'khor lo drug /
NK022(za)001:11630: mu 'khyud bdun phreng gru chad gnyis //
NK022(za)001:11631: ye shes sgo dgu la sogs pa //
NK022(za)001:11633: rang bzhin don gyi mtshan nyid dang //
NK022(za)001:11635: de ltar gsal byas mos skyes shing //
NK022(za)001:11636: shin tu'ang dbang mchog rgyu ru 'gyur //
NK022(za)001:11637: dbang phyug chen po dgos bskyed nas //
NK022(za)001:11638: dgos pa rnam pa gnyis ldan phyir //
NK022(za)001:11639: gser shel bee d+aur+ya byi ru dang //
NK022(za)001:11640: in tra la sogs rigs kyi yon //
NK022(za)001:11641: ser sna spangs pa'i sems kyis dbul //
NK022(za)001:11642: mdor na rgyal srid rang lus dang //
NK022(za)001:11643: dam pa'i yo byad brgyad rdzogs pas //
NK022(za)001:11644: dam pa de la rdzogs par dbul //
NK022(za)001:11645: dkyil 'khor dam pa legs bzhugs pa'i //
NK022(za)001:11646: rang rang bskal ba'i rim pa bzhin //
NK022(za)001:11648: la la rigs chen 'byed la gnas //
NK022(za)001:11649: la la dbugs chen phyin pa nyid //
NK022(za)001:11650: la la lung chen thob par 'gyur //
NK022(za)001:11651: la la rtsal chen yongs su rdzogs //
NK022(za)001:11652: de bzhin yon tan bsam mi khyab //
NK022(za)001:11653: de byas zin nas thob bya ba'ang //
NK022(za)001:11654: da ltar 'das pa'i dus dang gnyis //
NK022(za)001:11655: sngon du gshegs pa gnyis bstan te //
NK022(za)001:11656: dngos 'byung lung bstan rnam gnyis po //
NK022(za)001:11657: dang po'i dang po bsgrang bya ba'ang //
NK022(za)001:11658: khungs dang grags pa chu bo dang //
NK022(za)001:11659: yul dang dbang po dgos pa dang //
NK022(za)001:11660: thabs dang gnas dang rtags dang don //
NK022(za)001:11662: khungs ni lo rgyus bsnyad pa ste //
NK022(za)001:11663: rgyal rigs brgyud du gang byung nas //
NK022(za)001:11664: rgyal srid dmangs kyis gang stabs pas //
NK022(za)001:11665: tshig btsun yul la dbang bsgyur ba'i //
NK022(za)001:11666: kun gyi spyi bor 'gyur ba bzhin //
NK022(za)001:11667: rgyal rnams yongs su rdzogs pas na //
NK022(za)001:11668: lha dang bcas pa'i 'jig rten pas //
NK022(za)001:11669: chos kyi rgyal por mnga' bstabs pas //
NK022(za)001:11670: de nas byang chub mngon sangs rgyas //
NK022(za)001:11671: dam pa'i khye'u lnga'ang de bzhin gyur //
NK022(za)001:11672: grags pa'i ming gi dbang bskur ba //
NK022(za)001:11673: rgyal ba dpag tu med pa rnams //
NK022(za)001:11674: ji bzhin mkha' la sprin dpung bzhin //
NK022(za)001:11676: rgyal tshab chos la ming dbang bskur //
NK022(za)001:11677: de bzhin rgyal ba la las ni //
NK022(za)001:11678: rdo rje'i gdung ste rgyud dbang 'dzin //
NK022(za)001:11679: la las rin chen pad+mo dang //
NK022(za)001:11680: gzhon nu glang po'i sde brgyud sbyin //
NK022(za)001:11681: la las mtshan gyi 'od zer gyi //
NK022(za)001:11682: dbang gi mtshan gyi dbang rnams sbyin //
NK022(za)001:11683: de ltar dpe byad rjes su 'dzin //
NK022(za)001:11684: la las rgyan dang kha dog 'od zer gyis //
NK022(za)001:11685: brgyan dang kha dog drug dbang sbyin //
NK022(za)001:11686: la las ma 'dres bco brgyad dang //
NK022(za)001:11687: stobs dang mi 'jigs bcu bzhi dbang //
NK022(za)001:11688: so sor rig pa bzhi dbang gis //
NK022(za)001:11689: de dag nyid kyi dbang rnams sbyin //
NK022(za)001:11690: la las mthun par bsdus pa'i dbang //
NK022(za)001:11691: de ltar phyogs med par bsdus dang //
NK022(za)001:11692: gtong pas bsdu dbang longs spyod pas //
NK022(za)001:11693: bsdu ba'i dbang dang spyod mthun dbang //
NK022(za)001:11694: 'dren pas bsdu dang dbang gis bsdu //
NK022(za)001:11695: mnyam pas bsdu dang rag las pas //
NK022(za)001:11696: bsdu dbang rgyus bsdu 'bras bsdu dbang //
NK022(za)001:11697: de nyid dbang gis de dbang sbyin //
NK022(za)001:11698: la las tshe dbang sems la dbang //
NK022(za)001:11699: skye la dbang dang yo byad chos //
NK022(za)001:11700: rdzu 'phrul mos las las dbang dang //
NK022(za)001:11701: ye shes smon lam dbang bcu rnams //
NK022(za)001:11702: rgyal ba re res de de byin //
NK022(za)001:11703: tog dkar don grub sh+aaka thub dang //
NK022(za)001:11704: phyag na rdo rje khye lnga dag /
NK022(za)001:11705: thun mong kun la dbang bskur ba //
NK022(za)001:11706: la las rgyal tshab skyes bu dbang //
NK022(za)001:11707: byin brlabs dbang dang lung ston dbang //
NK022(za)001:11708: rtsal chen nus dbang de nyid kyis //
NK022(za)001:11709: bzhi la so sor de nyid byin //
NK022(za)001:11710: chu bo bzhi ni rgyud kyi chu //
NK022(za)001:11711: 'byung ba'i chu bo grags pa'i chu //
NK022(za)001:11712: rdzogs pa'i chu bo de dbang bskur //
NK022(za)001:11713: rjes su mthun par de nyid sbyin //
NK022(za)001:11714: thob bya'i yul yang chos rgyal po //
NK022(za)001:11715: byin brlabs dbang phyug sgron ma byed //
NK022(za)001:11716: gsang ba 'dzin pa'i dbang bzhin bskur //
NK022(za)001:11717: slob ma bzhi la rim pa sbyin //
NK022(za)001:11718: dbang po bshes gnyen mtshan nyid ni //
NK022(za)001:11719: phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba 'dus pa yis //
NK022(za)001:11720: dam pa tog la chos rgyal nyid //
NK022(za)001:11721: don grub rigs lnga sangs rgyas dang //
NK022(za)001:11722: sh+aaka thub rgyal ba dpag tu med //
NK022(za)001:11723: gsang bdag longs spyod sprul pa'i bskur //
NK022(za)001:11724: ched ni dus la bab phyir ro //
NK022(za)001:11725: tog dkar rgyal bar 'byung ba yi //
NK022(za)001:11726: dus la bab phyir dbang bskur dang //
NK022(za)001:11727: de bzhin don grub gzugs skur rgya //
NK022(za)001:11728: sh+aaka thub nges par lung thob dus //
NK022(za)001:11729: gsang bar nges pa'i dus bab bskur //
NK022(za)001:11730: gang 'dir thabs kyi mtshan nyid brjod //
NK022(za)001:11731: rin chen tog ltar dbang bskur rdzas //
NK022(za)001:11732: nyi zla rdo rje 'bar ba byin //
NK022(za)001:11733: la las rigs kyi phyag rgya byin //
NK022(za)001:11734: rdo rje pha lam lta bu'i dbang //
NK022(za)001:11735: rdzas de gtad nas de dbang byin //
NK022(za)001:11736: bskur ba'i gnas ni dga' ldan dang //
NK022(za)001:11737: 'og min snying po byang chub gnas //
NK022(za)001:11738: dbang bsgyur khang bzangs gyad yul du //
NK022(za)001:11739: bzhi la so so'i gnas su bskur //
NK022(za)001:11740: bskur ba'i rtags kyang 'di lta ste //
NK022(za)001:11741: dam tog chos kyi rgyal tshab byin //
NK022(za)001:11742: don grub rdzogs longs spyod par byin //
NK022(za)001:11743: thub la chos kyi mnga' bdag nyid //
NK022(za)001:11744: mthu stobs can la gsang bdag byin //
NK022(za)001:11745: de ltar snang ba thob pa'i rtags //
NK022(za)001:11746: 'das dang da ltar thun mong pa //
NK022(za)001:11747: rgyu dang thob dang mi thob dang //
NK022(za)001:11748: yul dang snod dang khyad par rtags //
NK022(za)001:11750: rgyu ni rnal 'byor rnam pa lnga'o //
NK022(za)001:11751: thob tshad bslab pa chub pa dang //
NK022(za)001:11752: de nyid mthong dang shes bya rnams //
NK022(za)001:11753: gang la'ang nyam mi nga 'jigs bral //
NK022(za)001:11754: mi thob pa ni gang rlom dang //
NK022(za)001:11755: gang dag ma nges gang la'ang //
NK022(za)001:11756: dam par dmigs dang gang mi 'byung //
NK022(za)001:11757: yul ni mchod rten sgra snyan dang //
NK022(za)001:11758: tshad ma dang ni nges pa'o //
NK022(za)001:11759: snod ni rgyud 'byung rtsal rdzogs dang //
NK022(za)001:11761: khyad par gnyis te rtsal bskur 'thob //
NK022(za)001:11762: rtsal gyis thob pa 'di lta ste //
NK022(za)001:11763: rgyal ba rnams kyi gsang ba'i thugs //
NK022(za)001:11764: rtogs na gang la gsal byed pa //
NK022(za)001:11765: dbang rnams kun gyi mchog yin te /
NK022(za)001:11766: srid pa gsum gyis de dbang bskur //
NK022(za)001:11767: gang dag thob pas bskur ba'ang //
NK022(za)001:11768: gang la phan pa'i dbang bskur dang //
NK022(za)001:11769: gang gis nus dbang tsam bskur ba'o //
NK022(za)001:11770: gtsug tor dam par 'byung ba'i rtags //
NK022(za)001:11771: gang la ma bzhag lhan ne ba //
NK022(za)001:11772: lhun gyis yongs su grub pa dang //
NK022(za)001:11775: lnga bzhi rang bzhin dkyil 'khor du //
NK022(za)001:11776: de ltar dbang bskur sa bon ltar //
NK022(za)001:11778: rim pa brgyud bzhiin rdzogs byas nas //
NK022(za)001:11779: slab bcu'i chib pa'ang de bzhin 'gyur //
NK022(za)001:11780: des na sngon 'byung lo rgyus bshad //
NK022(za)001:11781: brod pas basnguna bsu 'bad par gyis //
NK022(za)001:11782: de ltar da ltar shes thob phyir //
NK022(za)001:11783: chos mig skal ldan 'dir bya'i don //
NK022(za)001:11784: rnal 'byor pa dang skabs bgrod phyir //
NK022(za)001:11785: ngo bo rnam bzhi 'chad pa bzhin //
NK022(za)001:11786: yongs su rdzogs par byed pa'o //
NK022(za)001:11787: bla ma rdo rje 'khor lo rgyal //
NK022(za)001:11788: yon tan mchog gi ster 'gyur cing //
NK022(za)001:11789: srid pas zhus kyang zad mi shes //
NK022(za)001:11790: rkyen thub dbang lung rdzogs pa bzung //
NK022(za)001:11791: bla ma'i yul dang bdag po'i phyir //
NK022(za)001:11792: skabs su yul dang dbang por brjod //
NK022(za)001:11793: rdo rje slob ma'i mtshan nyid kyang //
NK022(za)001:11794: snod kyi skyon spangs gags la ring //
NK022(za)001:11795: brtson dang 'grus ldan ngang tshul can //
NK022(za)001:11796: rang bzhin bzang la khong rdig can //
NK022(za)001:11797: gsang thub spyod dag zon bag che //
NK022(za)001:11798: khro gnyer med par spyod pa mdzes //
NK022(za)001:11799: sgo gsum gtsang spyod nyes gsum sdom //
NK022(za)001:11800: bla ma'i thugs dang mthun spyod pa'o //
NK022(za)001:11801: chos mthun pa yis gnyis su 'gyur //
NK022(za)001:11802: spyi yi khyad par spyi don du //
NK022(za)001:11803: rgyal rigs dra ma spyir 'gyur ba //
NK022(za)001:11804: rigs kyi rgyud du 'byung ba dang //
NK022(za)001:11805: mtshan dang ldan zhing rgyal chos shes //
NK022(za)001:11806: 'khor dang ldan dbang dbang thob ldan //
NK022(za)001:11807: mang pos bkur thob chos drug dang //
NK022(za)001:11808: ldan nas bdun bskur spyir 'gyur bzhin //
NK022(za)001:11809: khyad par rtsal dang sbyor ba ste //
NK022(za)001:11810: sna tshogs gter gyi khang pa dag /
NK022(za)001:11811: rgyal po'i mngon du gyur pa ni //
NK022(za)001:11813: dka' thub phyi nang khyad par gyis //
NK022(za)001:11814: rin chen sna dgu'i rim pa dag /
NK022(za)001:11815: so so'i las rnams mtho dman gyis //
NK022(za)001:11816: yul de gcig las med na yang //
NK022(za)001:11817: yig tshang sgo dgu so sor spyod //
NK022(za)001:11818: rgyal por gyur na de kun la //
NK022(za)001:11819: dbang bsgyur byed pa'i bdag po yin //
NK022(za)001:11820: stsal dbang bskur thob de bzhin no //
NK022(za)001:11821: gang gi rgyu yis thob bya ba //
NK022(za)001:11822: gnyis te bskur rgyu thob rgyu'o //
NK022(za)001:11823: thog mar thob par brjod pa nyid //
NK022(za)001:11824: rnal 'byor chen po rnam pa lnga //
NK022(za)001:11825: dam tshig ting 'dzin shes rab dang //
NK022(za)001:11826: byang chub sems dang snying rje yi //
NK022(za)001:11827: yo byad lnga dang lhag par ldan //
NK022(za)001:11828: de dag shin tu 'tsham par byin //
NK022(za)001:11829: gang gi gang de thob byed rgyu //
NK022(za)001:11830: mtshungs ldan lhan cig go 'byed pa'i //
NK022(za)001:11831: rgyu gsum mtshungs par ldan pa ni //
NK022(za)001:11832: slob ma'i sgo gsum ma skyes pa'i //
NK022(za)001:11833: ye shes lhun rdzogs ngo bo'i phyir //
NK022(za)001:11834: thob bya rim pa ji snyed pa //
NK022(za)001:11835: til 'bru mar bzhin ye gnas pa //
NK022(za)001:11836: rang bzhin thabs kyis 'brel pa ste //
NK022(za)001:11837: de min bye ma'i mar bzhin du //
NK022(za)001:11838: 'brel gnyis chad pas snang mi rung //
NK022(za)001:11839: dang po sems sogs snang mi rung //
NK022(za)001:11840: dang po sems sogs lnga dang bcu //
NK022(za)001:11841: rim pa ji bzhin rgyud ldan pas //
NK022(za)001:11842: gcig shes rgyu ru bstan pa ste //
NK022(za)001:11844: gsal byed rgyu ni rim pa bzhin //
NK022(za)001:11845: snga ma thob byas phyi ma'i rgyu //
NK022(za)001:11847: de ma thag tu 'brel zhes bya //
NK022(za)001:11849: rgyu dang dmigs bdag de ma thag /
NK022(za)001:11850: rgyu rkyen bu yi skal ba bzhin //
NK022(za)001:11851: shin tu dngas pa'i sems ldan pas //
NK022(za)001:11852: gzugs brnyan me long bzhin snang ba //
NK022(za)001:11853: dbang gi stongs phyir nges tshig ldan //
NK022(za)001:11854: rdo rje rgyal po dbang lung rnams //
NK022(za)001:11855: rdzogs shing chu bo 'dus pa dang //
NK022(za)001:11856: dam pa'i yo byad lngas phyug pa'i //
NK022(za)001:11858: gzugs brnyan rdzogs pa'i yan lag rnams //
NK022(za)001:11859: byin brlabs 'dzom mthun bdag por bshad //
NK022(za)001:11860: sngon bzhin go phye snang 'gyur na //
NK022(za)001:11861: de ma thag pa'i mtshan nyid do //
NK022(za)001:11862: bu yi blo gros rim pa yis //
NK022(za)001:11863: rnam par bsdus pa bzhi ru bstan //
NK022(za)001:11864: phyi yi dbang dang nang gi dbang //
NK022(za)001:11865: bsgrub pa'i dbang dang gsang ba'i dbang //
NK022(za)001:11866: bcu dang bcu gcig bcu gsum dang //
NK022(za)001:11867: rnam pa gnyis kyis rdzogs par 'gyur //
NK022(za)001:11868: mdor na mang po 'dus pa'i mthu //
NK022(za)001:11869: byin brlabs thob bya'i dngos gzhir 'dod //
NK022(za)001:11870: rim pa spyi dang khyad par te //
NK022(za)001:11871: spyir ni snod dang sbyar nas kyang //
NK022(za)001:11872: brtsal med mi nus yul can la //
NK022(za)001:11873: phan pa 'ba' zhig basngagasa pa yin //
NK022(za)001:11874: rdo rje lung gi tshang can la //
NK022(za)001:11875: ji ltar nus pa de dbang bskur //
NK022(za)001:11876: bslab pa'i gnyer dang rim pa rnams //
NK022(za)001:11877: ci rigs rtsal gyi rim par sbyar //
NK022(za)001:11878: khyad par phan dang 'ba' zhig la //
NK022(za)001:11879: glegs bam nyi zla rin chen bdun //
NK022(za)001:11880: g.yu rung brgyad dang tog stong 'bar //
NK022(za)001:11881: rnal 'byor lnga la rim bzhin pa'o //
NK022(za)001:11882: gnas 'dir yod dang med pa dag /
NK022(za)001:11883: 'od mi gsub cing ljid mi dbab //
NK022(za)001:11884: rdo rje 'dus pa'i dbang dral du //
NK022(za)001:11885: rdo rje gdan gyi ltang chen gsher //
NK022(za)001:11886: rtsal dang rim pa'i khyad par dbye //
NK022(za)001:11887: rtsal gyi thob ldan mchog tu 'gyur //
NK022(za)001:11888: chos drug ldan par gyur pa dang //
NK022(za)001:11889: bkra shis lha yi nyi ma sogs //
NK022(za)001:11891: khyad par lam gyi rnal 'byor gyi //
NK022(za)001:11892: rim pa'i lha mod skabs sbyar nas //
NK022(za)001:11893: de ma thag pa'i tshul bzhin du //
NK022(za)001:11895: rdzogs pa'i sbyin pa'i khyad par ni //
NK022(za)001:11896: mtha' bcu rdzogs dang nye bar 'dris //
NK022(za)001:11897: rigs dban 'du dang lta ba rtsal //
NK022(za)001:11899: skye bo mang sngags gdeng dang ldan //
NK022(za)001:11900: bya ba rdzogs zhes gsum gsum ldan //
NK022(za)001:11901: de tshe shin tu dus la bab //
NK022(za)001:11902: gsang ba gnyis dang bcas par sbyin //
NK022(za)001:11903: dbang gi tshad ni gang bya ba //
NK022(za)001:11904: sbyin dang thob par byed pa gnyis //
NK022(za)001:11905: sbyin pa'i dbang tshad gang zhe na //
NK022(za)001:11906: dad ldan sri zhur ldan pa la //
NK022(za)001:11907: gsang ba nyan pa'i dbang chen bskur //
NK022(za)001:11908: rnam bzhi las kyi don tshang na //
NK022(za)001:11909: las rnams byed pa'ii dbang thob pa'o //
NK022(za)001:11910: lta ba'i dmigs bus chos mthong na //
NK022(za)001:11911: rgyal theb 'chad pa'i dbang thob pa'o //
NK022(za)001:11912: rkyen thub tshad ma gsum ldan na //
NK022(za)001:11913: bla ma rdo rje slob dpon dbang //
NK022(za)001:11914: dam pa'i mdzod gsum thams cad la //
NK022(za)001:11915: phyogs med par ni 'chad shes na //
NK022(za)001:11916: rab 'byams rgyal po'i dbang thob pa'o //
NK022(za)001:11917: thob pa rno la ngar btang bzhin //
NK022(za)001:11918: shin tu nus pa snang ldan pa'ang //
NK022(za)001:11919: ded dpon lnga ltas smin pa gsum //
NK022(za)001:11920: ded dpon goms dang rig pa dang //
NK022(za)001:11921: 'du dang thob dang rdzogs pa dang //
NK022(za)001:11922: snga ltas mthong dang 'byor pa dang //
NK022(za)001:11923: nus dang lung bstan thob pa'o //
NK022(za)001:11924: smin pa gnyis dang mngon spyod dang //
NK022(za)001:11925: thob pa'i las rnams mi skyor ba'o //
NK022(za)001:11926: thob pa sngon bzhiin brtsal nus te //
NK022(za)001:11927: shes rab brtsal gyis de kho na //
NK022(za)001:11928: byang chub snying por sems dkyil 'khor //
NK022(za)001:11929: mthong med tshul gyis mthong 'gyur ba //
NK022(za)001:11930: srid dang rgyal bas de dbang bskur //
NK022(za)001:11931: dbang phyug chen po nyid du gsungs //
NK022(za)001:11932: skur bas thob pas skal ba bzhin //
NK022(za)001:11934: bskur thabs las rims bsgrags bya ba //
NK022(za)001:11935: shin tu dbang la mos bskyed phyir //
NK022(za)001:11936: ngo mtshar bka' yis 'du shes bsgyur //
NK022(za)001:11937: shes mig can la shes bya'i yul //
NK022(za)001:11938: thams cad rims kyis bstan par bya //
NK022(za)001:11939: drod can 'khyil pa'i blo ldan pa //
NK022(za)001:11940: rnal 'byor na yar gsang sgo dbye //
NK022(za)001:11941: rtsing po 'gros kyis dmu dgod la //
NK022(za)001:11943: rdo rje blo yi yul can la //
NK022(za)001:11944: rtsal chen sbyong zhes gdam par bya //
NK022(za)001:11945: rdo rje dbang gi yon tan rnams //
NK022(za)001:11946: gang ltar mtshams par rgyas par brjod //
NK022(za)001:11947: de nas 'dod pa rags bya ba'ang //
NK022(za)001:11948: rim pa bskur ba'i thog ma ru //
NK022(za)001:11949: phyi yi dbang bcu sbyin bya ba //
NK022(za)001:11950: rdzas rnams rab gnas ldan byas te //
NK022(za)001:11951: chu skyes gdan la bzhag byas nas //
NK022(za)001:11952: bu rnams thugs kyi lhar bskyed la //
NK022(za)001:11953: dang por sbyin pa 'di yin te //
NK022(za)001:11955: gnas bkod yongs su gyur pa las //
NK022(za)001:11956: rdo rje rtags kyi phyag rgya sbyin //
NK022(za)001:11957: kun gyis 'da' bar dka' ba yi //
NK022(za)001:11958: tshig btsun yul la dbang bsgyur ba'i //
NK022(za)001:11959: rgyal po'i bka' btang phyag rgya'i dbang //
NK022(za)001:11960: sku lnga yongs su rdzogs par 'gyur //
NK022(za)001:11961: rjes su mthun pa'i smon lam btab //
NK022(za)001:11962: rol mo'i sgra yis drangs te sbyar //
NK022(za)001:11963: rigs kyis phyag rgya rang snying las //
NK022(za)001:11964: so so'i rab gnas sbyin par ldan //
NK022(za)001:11965: rigs rnams so so'i rgyud 'dzin cing //
NK022(za)001:11966: rtags kyi mtshan ma chen po 'di //
NK022(za)001:11967: sbyor ba chen po'i phyag 'tshal te //
NK022(za)001:11968: dam tshig phyag rgya rdzogs par 'gyur //
NK022(za)001:11969: smon lam rjes mthun kun la'ang sbyar //
NK022(za)001:11970: rol mo'i sgra yang de bzhin no //
NK022(za)001:11971: shes rab gzungs kyi dbang mchog ni //
NK022(za)001:11972: rtogs pa ldan par gyur pa yi //
NK022(za)001:11973: mtha' gnyis don du mi rtogs pa'i //
NK022(za)001:11974: gzungs ma'i rgyal mo chen mo yin //
NK022(za)001:11975: gnyis med yongs su rdzogs pas na //
NK022(za)001:11976: thams cad bde ba chen po'i ngang //
NK022(za)001:11977: byang chub sems dang don du 'brel //
NK022(za)001:11978: shes rab chen po'i rdzogs dbang sbyin //
NK022(za)001:11979: dril bu'am phyag rgya ma nyid gtad //
NK022(za)001:11981: bkra shis chen po'i bum pa ni //
NK022(za)001:11982: bder gshegs bzhugs pa'i pho brang ste //
NK022(za)001:11983: dkyil 'khor rdzogs par gyur pa yi //
NK022(za)001:11984: dbang mchog de yang sbyin par bya //
NK022(za)001:11985: gsang ba'i bstan pa rgyas nas ni //
NK022(za)001:11986: yun rings gnas par gyur pa yi //
NK022(za)001:11987: bkra shis rdzas kyi dbang mchog kyang //
NK022(za)001:11988: gnang ba chen po sbyin par bya //
NK022(za)001:11989: don rnams grub par gyur pa yi //
NK022(za)001:11990: 'dod dgu re skong rin po che //
NK022(za)001:11991: rgyal srid rin chen sna bdun gyis //
NK022(za)001:11992: rgyal po mchog tu dbang bskur ro //
NK022(za)001:11993: rin chen pad+ma'i seng ge'i khri //
NK022(za)001:11994: bla mar gyur pa'i gdan mchog ste //
NK022(za)001:11995: khyad par chen por gyur pa'i dbang //
NK022(za)001:11996: khri chen dag la bzhag par bya //
NK022(za)001:11997: yon tan skyon med mi 'jigs bzhi //
NK022(za)001:11998: stobs dang rdzu 'phrul dbang bcu las //
NK022(za)001:11999: de sogs yon tan thob 'gyur bas //
NK022(za)001:12000: smon lam bden par sbyar bar bya //
NK022(za)001:12001: dar gyi cod pan me tog phreng la sogs //
NK022(za)001:12002: dbang mchog brjid pa'i rgyan gyis klubs //
NK022(za)001:12003: dbu rgyan do shal se mo do //
NK022(za)001:12004: dpung rgyan rkang gdub lag gdub rnams //
NK022(za)001:12005: dbang thob rgyal po de la sbyin //
NK022(za)001:12006: so so'i yon tan grub par smon //
NK022(za)001:12007: dbang thob mdzes pas brjid pa'i rgyal po de //
NK022(za)001:12008: dbang phyug yin pas de la gus phyag 'tshal //
NK022(za)001:12009: rdo rje dbang phyug dbang phyug zhes par ni //
NK022(za)001:12010: kun gyis sgra cher 'bod cing bsgrags par bya //
NK022(za)001:12011: gser gyi 'khor lo'i rtsibs khyud ldan pa zhig /
NK022(za)001:12012: rgyal po'i lag tu bskur nas ni //
NK022(za)001:12013: 'jig rten kun la kha lo bsgyur ba yi //
NK022(za)001:12014: dbang mchog rgyal po 'di yang sbyin par bya //
NK022(za)001:12015: phyi 'khor skyong ba'i rgyal por gyur phan chad //
NK022(za)001:12016: bla med mchog gi rtags dang ldan par 'gyur //
NK022(za)001:12017: rnal 'byor theg chen rtags dang ldan gyur pa //
NK022(za)001:12018: gsang sgo phye nas nang du bzhugs par bya //
NK022(za)001:12019: bus gus rdo rjes drang byas la //
NK022(za)001:12020: gsang ba chen po'i rigs tshogs su //
NK022(za)001:12021: deng nas bdag gi gzung bar bya //
NK022(za)001:12022: phyir mi ldog par gyur thob phyir //
NK022(za)001:12023: bdag la gsang sgo dbye bar gsol //
NK022(za)001:12024: shin tu gsang ba'i rdzas dang ldan gyur nas //
NK022(za)001:12025: gsang sgo gang 'dod don rnams de ltar zhu //
NK022(za)001:12026: gsang ba chen po'i rtags su byin gyiis brlabs //
NK022(za)001:12027: slob bu 'byung gnas rab gnas gsal ba la //
NK022(za)001:12028: gsang ba'i don la nyan cing slob pa'i dbang //
NK022(za)001:12029: dbang thob skal can de la sbyin par bya //
NK022(za)001:12030: bdud rtsi chu 'dis rna ba'i gsang sgo dbye //
NK022(za)001:12031: sarba ta tha ga ta d+harma si ti ho //
NK022(za)001:12032: glegs bam zab mo la sogs thams cad rnams //
NK022(za)001:12033: rigs kyi bu mchog de la sbyin par bya //
NK022(za)001:12034: de nas 'gro ba'i don byed nus pas na //
NK022(za)001:12035: bu mchog de ni don grub gsal byas la //
NK022(za)001:12036: las rnams rgya mtsho thams cad nus pa'i rtags //
NK022(za)001:12037: rdo rje rgya gram la sogs rnam bzhi'i rdzas //
NK022(za)001:12038: bu mchog de la thabs kyis sbyin par bya //
NK022(za)001:12039: slob bu smra byed h+r+ai las mtha' yas bskyed //
NK022(za)001:12040: de ltar re 'dod bskong nus bu mchog de //
NK022(za)001:12041: rgyal po rgyal rigs brgyud du byung ba bzhin //
NK022(za)001:12042: rgyal tshab chos kyi brgyud du 'byung bas na //
NK022(za)001:12043: tan tra la sogs dam pa'i mdzod gsum sbyin //
NK022(za)001:12044: rjes mthun smon lam bden pas drangs te btab //
NK022(za)001:12045: des ni slob ma'i tshogs kun skyong nus phyir //
NK022(za)001:12046: h'u las rdo rje sems dpar gsal byas la //
NK022(za)001:12047: bstan pa bsgrogs pa'i sa la gnas bya'i phyir //
NK022(za)001:12048: rdo rje rgyal po dpal gyi dbang mchog 'di //
NK022(za)001:12049: theg chen gus pa'i rtags dang bcas te sbyin //
NK022(za)001:12050: glegs bam 'on te rdo rje rtse dagu'o //
NK022(za)001:12051: de ni bla med rgyal por gyur pas na //
NK022(za)001:12052: sa rnams non pa'i gdan mchog gdan khri'i dbang //
NK022(za)001:12053: lha chen la sogs zhing chen nyi zlar bcas //
NK022(za)001:12054: khyu mchog seng ge ma he gzig dang stag /
NK022(za)001:12055: gtum pa dom gyis spar te sbyin par bya //
NK022(za)001:12056: khams gsum zil gnon thabs dang shes rab dbang //
NK022(za)001:12057: lto ba zil gnon gzhan skrag yon tan brjid //
NK022(za)001:12058: mthun 'jug las mkhan mngon sum dpa' ba'i dbang //
NK022(za)001:12059: brtul zhugs chen po thogs med 'jug pa'i dbang //
NK022(za)001:12060: smon lam yid kyis zin par sbyin par bya //
NK022(za)001:12061: rgyal po yin pa'i rtags ni rnam pa bdun //
NK022(za)001:12062: skye ba rnam 'gyur rgyal po mnyes pa'i gzungs //
NK022(za)001:12063: pha rol dpung 'joms srid thub 'dzin pa dang //
NK022(za)001:12064: bdag gzhan don bsgrub rdzu 'phrul rkang par ldan //
NK022(za)001:12065: dgos 'dod yid bzhin skong ba rin po che //
NK022(za)001:12066: rgyal po de las thabs kyis sbyin par bya //
NK022(za)001:12067: yi dam lha yul mu dang byang chub spos blangs so //
NK022(za)001:12068: stobs chen khro bo sems dpa' rdo rje dang //
NK022(za)001:12069: rta mgrin rdo rje rin chen rnam bdun gyis //
NK022(za)001:12070: rab tu gnas byas rims bzhin gtad par bya //
NK022(za)001:12071: de ni rgyal ba'i sras po yin pas na //
NK022(za)001:12072: phyag rgya chen po'i dbang mchog sbyin par bya //
NK022(za)001:12073: ras sam 'bur ram lugs su blugs pa yi //
NK022(za)001:12074: phyag rgya'i gzugs ni de yi spyi bor bzhag /
NK022(za)001:12075: ye shes chen po'i don dang de ldan pas //
NK022(za)001:12076: ye shes lnga yi rtags mchog phyag rgya yis //
NK022(za)001:12077: gnas lngar gtugs te thugs kyi dbang mchog sbyin //
NK022(za)001:12078: 'bru bcus rigs lnga'i rab gnas ldan par bya //
NK022(za)001:12079: ma h+aa shu dz+nya na ta gnya' na badz+ra swa b+ha ba at+ma ko&a ham /
NK022(za)001:12080: ma h+aa a ta ri sha gnya' na badz+ra swa b+ha ba at+ma ko&a ham /
NK022(za)001:12081: ma h+aa sa man+ta dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa ba ad ma ko&a ham /
NK022(za)001:12082: ma h+aa pra ta be sha gnya' na badz+ra swa b+ha ba ad ma ko&a ham //
NK022(za)001:12083: ma h+aa kri ta a nush+ta na gnya' na badz+ra swa b+ha ba ad ma ko&a ham /
NK022(za)001:12084: gnas gsum 'bru gsum rdo rje gsum //
NK022(za)001:12085: bsams te yi ge'am sku gsum gtad //
NK022(za)001:12086: sku dang gsung dang thugs ldan rdo rje'o //
NK022(za)001:12087: rnal 'byor bde mchog de yin pas //
NK022(za)001:12088: sku gsung thugs kyi dbang mchog 'di //
NK022(za)001:12089: rdo rje can la sbyin par bya //
NK022(za)001:12090: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ka ya badz+ra swa b+ha ba ad ma ko&a ham /
NK022(za)001:12091: sarba ta th+aa ga ta badz+ra swa b+ha ba ad ma ko&a ham /
NK022(za)001:12092: sarba ta th+aa ga ta waka badz+ra swa b+ha ba ad ma ko&a ham /
NK022(za)001:12093: sarba ta th+aa ga ta tsit+ta badz+ra swa b+ha ba ad ma ko&a ham /
NK022(za)001:12094: sarba ta th+aa ga ta a nu ra ga badz+ra swa b+ha ba ad ma ko&a ham /
NK022(za)001:12095: sarba ta th+aa ga ta pu tsa badz+ra swa b+ha ba ad ma ko&a ham /
NK022(za)001:12096: dbang mchog thob pa'i bu mchog ste //
NK022(za)001:12097: don rnams grub par bkra shis phyir //
NK022(za)001:12098: bdud 'dul bkra shis rdzas mchog rnams //
NK022(za)001:12099: rtags kyis brgyan te sbyin par bya //
NK022(za)001:12100: dpal be'u thams cad mkhyen pa'i dbang //
NK022(za)001:12101: rgyal mtshan bdud bzhi las rgyal dang //
NK022(za)001:12102: dung gi dgol ba dpa' skong sgrogs //
NK022(za)001:12103: phyag mthil 'khor lo chos bskor dbang //
NK022(za)001:12105: phyag zhabs nya bzhis don mdzad dpal //
NK022(za)001:12106: ljags kyi pad+ma gos med dbang //
NK022(za)001:12107: dbu skra gdugs kyis gdung sel dbang //
NK022(za)001:12108: rjes su mthun pa'i smon bcas sbyin //
NK022(za)001:12109: don rnams grub pa'i bu mchog ste //
NK022(za)001:12110: rdo rje dbang mchog thob pa na //
NK022(za)001:12111: zhing khams kun tu grags pa yi //
NK022(za)001:12112: rtsal gyi rdo rje thig le sbyin //
NK022(za)001:12113: nang du 'jug pa'i dbang thob nas //
NK022(za)001:12114: de dag kun la spyod bsgrub pa'i //
NK022(za)001:12115: dbang mchog dam pa sbyin par bya //
NK022(za)001:12116: skye med chos kyi dbyings nyid las //
NK022(za)001:12117: sems kyi dbang bskur thob pa yi //
NK022(za)001:12118: shes rab chen po rig pa'i dbang //
NK022(za)001:12119: sems lon don gyi gtan tshigs sbyin //
NK022(za)001:12120: bya ba'i mtshan ma kun bral zhing //
NK022(za)001:12121: rtsol med gnas pa'i byang chub sems //
NK022(za)001:12122: snying rje chen po'i bde mchog gis //
NK022(za)001:12123: khams gsum kun la dbang bsgyur zhing //
NK022(za)001:12124: srid gsum 'gro ba'i don rnams kun //
NK022(za)001:12125: thams cad rdzogs par nus pa yi //
NK022(za)001:12126: rtags kyi dbang mchog dam pa ni //
NK022(za)001:12127: thong gshol 'bar ba sbyin par bya //
NK022(za)001:12128: dug gsum gting nas sprugs pa yi //
NK022(za)001:12129: rtags chen ga'u rnam pa gsum //
NK022(za)001:12130: dmar chen dag gis bkang nas kyang //
NK022(za)001:12131: dbang thob de yi lag tu sbyin //
NK022(za)001:12132: srid gsum sgrol bar bya ba yi //
NK022(za)001:12133: dbang mchog chen po sbyin pa'i phyir //
NK022(za)001:12134: ka tar la sogs mtshon cha rnams //
NK022(za)001:12135: dbang thob de yi lag tu sbyin //
NK022(za)001:12136: 'khor ba'i chos la ci spyad kyang //
NK022(za)001:12137: skyon gyis gos par mi 'gyur ba'i //
NK022(za)001:12138: rtags kyi phyag rgya chen po ni //
NK022(za)001:12139: rnam dag rdzas kyi pad+ma sbyin //
NK022(za)001:12140: las rnams rdzogs par 'gyur ba yin //
NK022(za)001:12141: dbang mchog dam pa'i rtags chen ni //
NK022(za)001:12142: sti ra'i dbyug pa chen po dag /
NK022(za)001:12143: dbang thob de yi lag tu sbyin //
NK022(za)001:12144: yum dang gnyis med 'khril ba yi //
NK022(za)001:12145: chos nyid don dang gnyis med rtags //
NK022(za)001:12147: dbang thob de yi lag tu sbyin //
NK022(za)001:12148: gsang ba sbyor ba'i shes rab ma //
NK022(za)001:12149: dri med rnam dag lha mo zhig /
NK022(za)001:12150: mtshan ldan shin tu brgyan byas la //
NK022(za)001:12151: dbang thob de la sbyin par bya //
NK022(za)001:12152: dbang thob rgyal po chen po de //
NK022(za)001:12153: kun gyi bdag po yin pas na //
NK022(za)001:12154: rol mo'i dri dang zhal zas dang //
NK022(za)001:12155: 'dod yon lnga las sogs pa dang //
NK022(za)001:12156: nye ba'i longs spyod rgyan rnams kun //
NK022(za)001:12157: thams cad thams cad sbyin par bya //
NK022(za)001:12158: bsgrub pa'i rgyal po de la ni //
NK022(za)001:12159: bsgrub pa'i las la dbang thob phyir //
NK022(za)001:12160: rdo rje sems dpa' la sogs pa'i //
NK022(za)001:12161: rgyal ba thams cad bsgrub pa dang //
NK022(za)001:12162: rdo rje tshe dang sman la sogs //
NK022(za)001:12163: bsgrub pa ma lus bsgrubs shig ces //
NK022(za)001:12164: bsgrub rdzas thab mas sbyin par bya //
NK022(za)001:12165: rgyal ba sangs rgyas thams cad dang //
NK022(za)001:12166: dbang mchog de gnyis gcig pa'i phyir //
NK022(za)001:12167: rig 'dzin rdo rje rtsal gyi dbang //
NK022(za)001:12168: rdo rje'i ming ni sbyin par bya //
NK022(za)001:12169: bsgrub pa'i dbang mchog thob pa dang //
NK022(za)001:12170: gsang ba'i bdag po yin pas na //
NK022(za)001:12171: gsang ba'i dbang mchog sbyin par bya //
NK022(za)001:12172: dga' ba byang chub sems chen po //
NK022(za)001:12173: kun tu tshim par byed pa yi //
NK022(za)001:12174: dkar dmar lhag pa'i byang chub sems //
NK022(za)001:12175: dbang thob de yi lce la bzhag /
NK022(za)001:12176: 'di yang phyag rgya rtsal sgrib bral //
NK022(za)001:12177: byin brlabs chos bshad dbang bskur dang //
NK022(za)001:12178: bum khrus rin chen bsnyim thogs la //
NK022(za)001:12180: gnang nas gsol dang dbugs dbyung dang //
NK022(za)001:12181: sems bskyed gsang sgo dbye bar gsol //
NK022(za)001:12182: gnang nas skyabs gsol bshags pa dang //
NK022(za)001:12183: ci la dga' dris lan gsol nas //
NK022(za)001:12184: dam bcas dbang don zhu ba dang //
NK022(za)001:12185: rdo rje rgyal po'i rol pa yis //
NK022(za)001:12186: bda' yis bos te sems sbyin pa'o //
NK022(za)001:12187: thog mar phyag rgya mtshan ldan pa'i //
NK022(za)001:12188: nyi ma 'dzag par btsal ba yi //
NK022(za)001:12189: mtshan nyid thig yum rjes mthun pa //
NK022(za)001:12190: rnyed nas khrus bya 'bru bcu yis //
NK022(za)001:12191: sbyor bas na bun gsal bya ste //
NK022(za)001:12192: ban d+ha tra tha'i sngags kyis bskul /
NK022(za)001:12193: de la rang gi yum bskyed la //
NK022(za)001:12194: lus la rigs lnga'i dkyil 'khor bkod //
NK022(za)001:12195: bum pa dbu rgyan cod pan sbyin //
NK022(za)001:12196: yang na gong nas tshul bzhin bskur //
NK022(za)001:12197: bu yis khrus byas 'byor thogs te //
NK022(za)001:12198: thal sbyar gus 'dug zhu sogs pa //
NK022(za)001:12199: rjes su mthun pas brtsam par bya //
NK022(za)001:12200: dbang don zhu bar brjod pa ni //
NK022(za)001:12201: rig 'dzin rdo rje rgyal po yis //
NK022(za)001:12202: 'khor ba ji ltar bsgral ba ltar //
NK022(za)001:12203: bdag cag rab tu bsgral ba'i phyir //
NK022(za)001:12204: rdo rje nyi ma gsal du gsol //
NK022(za)001:12205: bla ma tshul bzhin rol ba yi //
NK022(za)001:12206: sems 'dres bde ldan blangs te sbyin //
NK022(za)001:12208: bus kyang bde dang mtshan ma btang //
NK022(za)001:12209: shes rab ye shes rtsal med dbang //
NK022(za)001:12210: thog mar bya ba zin pa'i bus //
NK022(za)001:12211: zla bar ldan pa'i yum btsal na //
NK022(za)001:12212: byin brlabs rol te bde ba'i dag /
NK022(za)001:12213: las dang dgag sogs sngon goms nas //
NK022(za)001:12214: rol pa'i char dang thal mo'i 'brug /
NK022(za)001:12215: 'pho ba'i glog dang bde mchod dang //
NK022(za)001:12216: klu yis bde skyid lag bskyor gar //
NK022(za)001:12217: rdebs bzhi rnga dang dbugs 'bud dung //
NK022(za)001:12218: sen mo'i ker ko tsum pi gling bu'o //
NK022(za)001:12219: rgyan dang mdangs bzhin bsgyegs pa dang //
NK022(za)001:12220: steg mig steg tshig lag gis mkhyud //
NK022(za)001:12221: lus steng zhal sbyor rdo rje stim //
NK022(za)001:12222: mdzum mnyes lce mchu gzhib gsol dang //
NK022(za)001:12223: bde ba'i ro myong pos rtse 'chad //
NK022(za)001:12224: ro myong shing sems 'phro ba dang //
NK022(za)001:12225: khu ba 'jo dang thig le rnams //
NK022(za)001:12226: rtsar 'jug rol sogs tshul bzhin bya //
NK022(za)001:12227: brtsal med byang chub sems chen po //
NK022(za)001:12228: shes rab chen po'i rtsal gyis ni //
NK022(za)001:12229: chos kun sgyu mar dbang bsgyur nas //
