NK022(za)001:13787: thugs rje nyi gsal 'od bzhin snyoms mdzad lha //
NK022(za)001:13788: bder gshegs bzhugs shing bdag la dgongs su gsol //
NK022(za)001:13789: brjod med shes rab mi g.yo chos kyi sku //
NK022(za)001:13790: bde chen longs spyod rdzogs sku rigs lnga'i gtso //
NK022(za)001:13791: thugs rje thabs mkhas rgya che rol pa yi //
NK022(za)001:13792: cho 'phrul sprul pa'i lha la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK022(za)001:13793: dngos su 'byor dang yid kyis sprul pa yis //
NK022(za)001:13794: kun tu bzang po bla med mchod sprin gyis //
NK022(za)001:13795: mkha' dbyings rnam dag rgya cher yongs bkod de //
NK022(za)001:13796: phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod pa rgya mtshos mchod //
NK022(za)001:13797: kun tu bzang mo yum gyi ba ga la //
NK022(za)001:13798: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor ma lus yongs bkod cing //
NK022(za)001:13799: 'du 'bral med pa'i ngang du ro gcig pa'i //
NK022(za)001:13800: gnyis med byang chub sems kyis mnyes gyur cig /
NK022(za)001:13801: sems kyi rang bzhin chos dbyings nam mkha' che //
NK022(za)001:13802: chos rnams rnam dag rgya cher 'od gsal ba //
NK022(za)001:13803: rnal 'byor nyid dbyings smra bsam las 'das pa //
NK022(za)001:13804: mnyam nyid byang chub sems la rtag tu 'dod //
NK022(za)001:13805: kun tu bzang po'i rdzogs chen ye nas bdal ba la //
NK022(za)001:13806: phyi nang gas nga ba'i dkyil 'khor bkod pa ni //
NK022(za)001:13807: snang srid rnam dag kun bzang yum gyi dbyings //
NK022(za)001:13808: 'byung dang 'byung 'gyur yab yum lhun rdzogs rnams //
NK022(za)001:13809: gsang chen rab rdzogs gzungs chen bdag nyid ma //
NK022(za)001:13810: gnyis med thig le chen por 'od gsal ba //
NK022(za)001:13811: cir yang snang bas bde chen g.yung drung lha //
NK022(za)001:13812: 'du 'bral med pa'i gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor ni //
NK022(za)001:13813: bdag nyid chen po bcom ldan yab yum dang //
NK022(za)001:13814: byang chub lcam dral khro bo khro mo'i tshogs //
NK022(za)001:13815: rdo rje lha mo tshogs rje tshogs kyi bdag /
NK022(za)001:13816: ma ltar byams shing sring ltar gdung la sogs //
NK022(za)001:13817: legs nyes ltang 'dzin dam tshig rjes gcod ma //
NK022(za)001:13818: dpang gyur rdo rje dam can dgongs su gsol //
NK022(za)001:13819: thugs rje gdung 'tshob rdo rje che mchog mos //
NK022(za)001:13820: bdag cag sgrub pa'i rnal 'byor 'dir 'tshogs kun //
NK022(za)001:13821: 'gro ba'i don phyir byang chub sems bskyed de //
NK022(za)001:13822: bla med go 'phang bgrod par bya ba'i phyir //
NK022(za)001:13823: bstan pa rgya mtsho so so'i 'dul khrims dang //
NK022(za)001:13824: sku gsung thugs dang mnyam sbyor sdom pa'i mchog /
NK022(za)001:13825: 'da' dka' rdo rje dam tshig gtan gyi gnyer //
NK022(za)001:13826: spyi dang khyad par lhag pa'i dam tshig rnams //
NK022(za)001:13827: snga phyir mnos zhing gnyer du smra'o 'tshal //
NK022(za)001:13828: don las gol zhing ldog sems ma mchis kyang //
NK022(za)001:13829: gdod bya long yod snyam pa'i le lo yis //
NK022(za)001:13830: klong du ma gyur rtsal shugs chung ba yis //
NK022(za)001:13831: shes bzhin mi ldan bag med g.yeng 'gyur te //
NK022(za)001:13832: dang po tha tshigs bka' la btags pa'i tshe //
NK022(za)001:13833: bka' la ma gus 'gal gyis dpyas long btags //
NK022(za)001:13834: bar du bslab pa'i gnyer chen phog pa'i tshe //
NK022(za)001:13835: bslab la mi brtson don la g.yel ba dang //
NK022(za)001:13836: tha ma 'di tshe 'bras bu bsgrub pa na //
NK022(za)001:13837: bka' dang gzhung bzhin ma lcogs don dang 'gal //
NK022(za)001:13838: tshor dang ma tshor sgrib pa che chung rnams //
NK022(za)001:13839: shin tu mi shes ma rig dbang gis na //
NK022(za)001:13840: ston pa'i bka' dang dam las 'gal bgyis pa //
NK022(za)001:13841: dpal bo thugs rjes bdag la bzod par gsol //
NK022(za)001:13842: 'khor ba thog mtha' med pa'i dus mtha' nas //
NK022(za)001:13843: las kyi dbang gis bdag cag 'khor bar 'khyams //
NK022(za)001:13844: nyon mongs log par lta ba'i dug 'thung ste //
NK022(za)001:13845: sdug bsngal nad kyis shin tu gdungs ba la //
NK022(za)001:13846: bder gshegs thugs rje sman pa'i rgyal po yis //
NK022(za)001:13847: dam chos bdud rtsi thar pa'i sman btsal bas //
NK022(za)001:13848: nyon mongs 'khrul pa'i nad rnams zhi mdzad cing //
NK022(za)001:13849: bla med byang chub snying por 'tsho mdzad de //
NK022(za)001:13850: byams mgon thugs rje'i bdag la skyabs su mchi //
NK022(za)001:13851: zhes gcer bu zang mar byung la rnal 'byor gyi phyag yan lag sa la brdabs te /
NK022(za)001:13853: rgyal mchog skyes bu khyod ci 'dra //
NK022(za)001:13854: de dra kho nar spyod par bgyi //
NK022(za)001:13855: spyod pa rmad 'byung bsam yas pas //
NK022(za)001:13856: 'gro la phan pa'i don du spyad //
NK022(za)001:13858: ma bsgral ba ni bsgral bar bgyi //
NK022(za)001:13859: ma grol ba ni grol bar bgyi //
NK022(za)001:13860: dbugs ma phyung pa dbugs dbyung bya //
NK022(za)001:13861: mya ngan 'das pa'i zhing khams su //
NK022(za)001:13862: snying po byang chub nyid du bya //
NK022(za)001:13863: de nas kun kyang rang lus la //
NK022(za)001:13864: bsdus te sgo gsum bag chags sbyangs //
NK022(za)001:13865: ma skyes ngang las lhar gsal te //
NK022(za)001:13866: byin brlabs mchog gi bdag por gsal //
NK022(za)001:13867: mi gnas mi rtog bsam dang bral //
NK022(za)001:13868: ma chags chags bral yul las 'das //
NK022(za)001:13869: ci yang mi 'byung cir ma yin //
NK022(za)001:13870: rang 'byung rang bzhin brjod dang bral //
NK022(za)001:13871: yongs la khyab pas nyi ma'i 'od //
NK022(za)001:13872: snying rje byang chub sems yin te //
NK022(za)001:13873: rnam rtog mun pa sel bar snang //
NK022(za)001:13874: yid bzhin rin chen 'bar ba yi //
NK022(za)001:13875: a ni chags med yi ge'i mdzod //
NK022(za)001:13876: cho 'phrul rtog pa kun gyi rgyu //
NK022(za)001:13877: nyon mongs skyon bral zla ba'i mdog /
NK022(za)001:13879: a ni e yi rang bzhin te //
NK022(za)001:13880: a las e byung mkha' khyab bdal //
NK022(za)001:13882: mtha' dang dbus med kun tu bdal //
NK022(za)001:13883: a yi byin brlabs ye shes las //
NK022(za)001:13884: rlung gi cho 'phrul yang du shar //
NK022(za)001:13885: thams cad 'degs pa'i stobs ldan zhing //
NK022(za)001:13886: rang bzhin g.yo med thogs med 'phyo //
NK022(za)001:13887: rgyu yi yi ge 'od zer las //
NK022(za)001:13888: chu yi snying po cho 'phrul shar //
NK022(za)001:13889: mkha' yi mtha' dang mnyam pa yi //
NK022(za)001:13890: rlung mtsho thams cad rgyas par 'gyur //
NK022(za)001:13891: mi dmigs pa las sna tshogs par //
NK022(za)001:13893: rnal 'byor sa bcu rdzogs pa'i don //
NK022(za)001:13894: lhun gyis grub pa'i bde ba che //
NK022(za)001:13895: rnam dag shes rab mkha' klong nas //
NK022(za)001:13896: rdo rje 'bar ba'i ri bo shar //
NK022(za)001:13897: rgya che gting zab nam 'phangs gcod //
NK022(za)001:13898: rtog pa'i ri bo 'joms par byed //
NK022(za)001:13899: a yi byin brlabs ye shes las //
NK022(za)001:13900: cho 'phrul me yi snying po shar //
NK022(za)001:13902: dngos po kun zad me klong 'tshub //
NK022(za)001:13903: rig pa'i 'byung chen lnga brtsegs pa //
NK022(za)001:13904: rgya khyon tshad med mnyam par snang //
NK022(za)001:13905: e ya ra ba ra kem /
NK022(za)001:13906: b+h+ru ba ga gsang ba'i 'od zer las /
NK022(za)001:13907: bde gshegs bzhugs pa'i gzhal yas khang //
NK022(za)001:13908: nam mkha'i mtha' ltar dpag tu med //
NK022(za)001:13909: dus gsum rgyal ba rgya mtsho'i dbyings //
NK022(za)001:13910: 'di ni rdo rje mu khyud bdun //
NK022(za)001:13911: 'byung ba'i rim pa drug bar du //
NK022(za)001:13913: mu khyud dbus las le tshe dgu //
NK022(za)001:13915: mu khyud tshar gsum 'bar ba'i phreng //
NK022(za)001:13916: de bzhin gru chad phyi dang nang //
NK022(za)001:13917: bar khyams bzhis mdzes phyi 'khyams dang //
NK022(za)001:13918: lngar gsal sgo dgu shar du brtsegs //
NK022(za)001:13919: de yang 'khyams lnga gru chad gnyis //
NK022(za)001:13920: sgo snam mu khyud tha ma rnams //
NK022(za)001:13921: rdo rje sgo dang ldan pa ni //
NK022(za)001:13922: phyogs kyi dang po gnas brjod yin //
NK022(za)001:13923: phyogs bcu rgya yongs su ma chad cing //
NK022(za)001:13924: mtha' dang dbus med rtse mo mnyam //
NK022(za)001:13925: cho 'phrul sprin gyis kun nas gtibs //
NK022(za)001:13926: byang chub char gyis nyon mongs spangs //
NK022(za)001:13927: ye shes myu gu mngon par bskyed //
NK022(za)001:13928: yid bzhin rin chen rgyal po dang //
NK022(za)001:13929: mu tig lcang lo chun 'phyang dang //
NK022(za)001:13930: chos nyid bla res kun tu bres //
NK022(za)001:13931: ye shes lda ldis mngon mdzes cing //
NK022(za)001:13932: h'u gi thog dang me char 'bab //
NK022(za)001:13933: rdo rje rgyan dang 'phan gyis klubs //
NK022(za)001:13934: zhe sdang smin pa'i za ra tshags //
NK022(za)001:13935: sprin nag grib so bzhin gzhol ba'i //
NK022(za)001:13936: bar bar rin chen phreng ba dang //
NK022(za)001:13937: mu tig me tog phreng bas mdzes //
NK022(za)001:13939: bam ril che chung khog stod smad //
NK022(za)001:13940: yan lag ring thung dbang po'i phreng //
NK022(za)001:13941: rdo rje phreng bas kun nas spras //
NK022(za)001:13942: nya chen po yis ka gdung la //
NK022(za)001:13943: nya bran dral gyi drab gtams pa //
NK022(za)001:13944: zla ba'i ka gdan nyi ma yi //
NK022(za)001:13945: ka lo sbrul chun ka rgyan nang //
NK022(za)001:13946: 'og gzhi mu tig gcal bkram zhing //
NK022(za)001:13948: nor bu rin chen brag gis gdams //
NK022(za)001:13949: de steng rtse gsum rtse lnga'i brag /
NK022(za)001:13951: nyi zla bzhi bcu rtsa brgyad sbyar //
NK022(za)001:13952: de steng dbang phyug khyo shug ni //
NK022(za)001:13953: spyi bcings nyi shu rtsa bzhi'i gdan //
NK022(za)001:13954: steng na byol song gtso brgyad gnas //
NK022(za)001:13955: dpa' stag 'jigs seng gdug pa'i gzig /
NK022(za)001:13956: gtum dom stobs glang ma he brjid //
NK022(za)001:13957: 'dzin pa'i chu srin zhe sdang sbrul //
NK022(za)001:13958: rig 'dzin sgrib pa sbyang phyir gnas //
NK022(za)001:13959: dbang phyug sde tshogs gsum gsum mnan //
NK022(za)001:13960: 'khor rnams nyi ma zhing chen gdan //
NK022(za)001:13961: bu mo nyi shu zhing gi gdan //
NK022(za)001:13962: h'u chen nyi ma phyogs skyong ste //
NK022(za)001:13963: gzhan dag zhing skam gdan sogs sbyar //
NK022(za)001:13964: ma skyes yi ge'i byin brlabs las //
NK022(za)001:13965: thugs kyi yi ge'i mthi nga nag nyid //
NK022(za)001:13966: dbus su babs pa'i bdag nyid la //
NK022(za)001:13968: sang nga he ru yab yum khyod //
NK022(za)001:13969: mthing nag nyi shu rtsa gcig ni //
NK022(za)001:13970: dus gsum rgyal ba bdun gsum las //
NK022(za)001:13971: 'khor lo rin chen mchod rten dang //
NK022(za)001:13972: nor bu rin chen bdun gyis spras //
NK022(za)001:13974: zhabs brgyad bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis phyag /
NK022(za)001:13975: phra men bcu dbyug lag na khyung //
NK022(za)001:13978: lag na seng ge kha dbyal brgyad //
NK022(za)001:13981: lag na stag seng mche gtsigs brgyad //
NK022(za)001:13982: kha nas rdo rje sna tshogs 'phro //
NK022(za)001:13983: ma brgyad dbyug 'phyar lag pa na //
NK022(za)001:13984: mi mgo rdo rje lu gu brgyud //
NK022(za)001:13985: glad la bskor bar byed pa'o //
NK022(za)001:13987: lag na me brgyad thu lum 'phro //
NK022(za)001:13989: ma brgyad 'bar ma g.yon pa ste //
NK022(za)001:13990: phra men bcu phyed g.yas g.yon snams //
NK022(za)001:13991: dur khrod sbrul brgyad thod gsum dang //
NK022(za)001:13992: de bzhin ko ba rtags gsum drug /
NK022(za)001:13993: sro ta a 'dza' na la sogs pa yis //
NK022(za)001:13994: dur khrod brtags brgyan bco brgyad 'bar //
NK022(za)001:13995: yum yang lus dang grib ma'i tshul //
NK022(za)001:13996: gtso bo'i thugs las mthun nas ni //
NK022(za)001:13997: mthing nag dur khrod brgyan dang ldan //
NK022(za)001:13998: g.yas 'khyud g.yon pa gtso la stobs //
NK022(za)001:13999: de nas byin gyis brlabs bya ba //
NK022(za)001:14000: h'u las rdo rje lnga pa yis //
NK022(za)001:14001: sa las pad mor gyur pa dngos //
NK022(za)001:14002: bsnyen pa dang ni nye bsnyen dang //
NK022(za)001:14003: bsgrub pa dang ni bsgrub chen pos //
NK022(za)001:14004: yum gyi pad+ma gzhal yas su //
NK022(za)001:14005: gsang ba'i byang chub sems 'phro ba'ang //
NK022(za)001:14008: ra ga ya mi ra ho ham //
NK022(za)001:14009: chags pa'i bda' yis bskul nas ni //
NK022(za)001:14010: yum gyi bskul ba 'di sta ste //
NK022(za)001:14011: mi g.yo mchog gi rgyal po dgongs su gsol //
NK022(za)001:14012: rnam par mi rtog shin tu dri med sku //
NK022(za)001:14013: 'od zer mdangs ldan zla rgyas 'dra ba'i zhal //
NK022(za)001:14014: dges par rol pa'i don la bzhengs su gsol //
NK022(za)001:14015: yid 'ong 'byor ldan rgyal ba rgya mtsho'i dbyings //
NK022(za)001:14016: shes rab zab mo rnam dag pad+mo'i lam //
NK022(za)001:14017: sgyu 'phrul brlabs la mkhas pa'i spyod mchog la //
NK022(za)001:14018: yid 'ong 'byor ldan cho 'phrul sna tshogs bstan //
NK022(za)001:14021: dges pa rdo rje cho 'phrul las //
NK022(za)001:14022: byang chub char sprin dbab tu gsol //
NK022(za)001:14023: e ma ho yid kyi dga' sde mo //
NK022(za)001:14024: gdung ba'i snying phreng shes rab gzungs //
NK022(za)001:14026: bde ba'i rdo rje byang chub 'bar //
NK022(za)001:14030: byang chub sems kyi dges sprin las //
NK022(za)001:14031: h'u chen drug cu rtsa bzhi dang //
NK022(za)001:14032: ha he phata bcu phrag gnyis dang //
NK022(za)001:14033: de bzhin h'u chen nyi shu dag /
NK022(za)001:14034: spros nas gdan la rims bzhin bkod //
NK022(za)001:14035: de las rgya mtsho gza' skar tshul //
NK022(za)001:14036: so so'i sngags kyis rdzogs par bskyed //
NK022(za)001:14037: ma brgyad la sogs 'khor sde rnams //
NK022(za)001:14038: rang bzhin ting 'dzin las gsum gyis //
NK022(za)001:14039: phye bas so so sngags kyis bskyed //
NK022(za)001:14040: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa sh+ri he ru ka h'u /
NK022(za)001:14041: ma h+aa tsan d+ha sarba dus bstan /
NK022(za)001:14042: sang nga sh+ri he ru ka /
NK022(za)001:14043: ta ka ha na pa tsa h'u h'u /
NK022(za)001:14044: sarba ta th+aa ga ta sang ha kro ta shwa ri h'u h'u sa ma y+aa sa ma y+aa /
NK022(za)001:14045: sa nu sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa sh+ri he ru ka h'u /
NK022(za)001:14046: pa sa ni sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa sh+ri he ru ka h'u /
NK022(za)001:14047: sang na sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa sh+ri he ru ka h'u /
NK022(za)001:14048: h'u sarba ra sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa sh+ri he ru ka h'u /
NK022(za)001:14049: badz+ra garba sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa sh+ri he ru ka h'u /
NK022(za)001:14050: rat+na garba sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa sh+ri he ru ka h'u /
NK022(za)001:14051: pad+ma garba sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa sh+ri he ru ka h'u /
NK022(za)001:14052: karma garba sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa sh+ri he ru ka h'u /
NK022(za)001:14053: me tri garba sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa sh+ri he ru ka h'u /
NK022(za)001:14054: ka ru garba sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa sh+ri he ru ka h'u /
NK022(za)001:14055: lo ga garba sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa sh+ri he ru ka h'u /
NK022(za)001:14056: ba du ma garba sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa sh+ri he ru ka h'u /
NK022(za)001:14057: yak+sha sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa sh+ri he ru ka h'u /
NK022(za)001:14058: rak+sha sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa sh+ri he ru ka h'u /
NK022(za)001:14059: big sha sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa sh+ri he ru ka h'u /
NK022(za)001:14060: bi sha sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa sh+ri he ru ka h'u /
NK022(za)001:14061: te shwa sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa sh+ri he ru ka h'u /
NK022(za)001:14062: ke shwa ra sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa sh+ri he ru ka h'u /
NK022(za)001:14063: bee sha sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa sh+ri he ru ka h'u /
NK022(za)001:14064: bi sha sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa sh+ri he ru ka h'u /
NK022(za)001:14065: trag shwa sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa sh+ri he ru ka h'u /
NK022(za)001:14066: d+h+ri shwa sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa sh+ri he ru ka h'u /
NK022(za)001:14067: k+aa shwa sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa sh+ri he ru ka h'u /
NK022(za)001:14068: bag shwa sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa sh+ri he ru ka h'u /
NK022(za)001:14069: ru ti sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa sh+ri he ru ka h'u /
NK022(za)001:14070: rag+ta sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa sh+ri he ru ka h'u /
NK022(za)001:14071: kha'i sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa sh+ri he ru ka h'u /
NK022(za)001:14072: sa ha sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa sh+ri he ru ka h'u /
NK022(za)001:14073: pa na shwa ri kha mu /
NK022(za)001:14074: pa sa ni shwa ri kha mu /
NK022(za)001:14075: sa no shwa ri kha mu /
NK022(za)001:14076: pa ra pa shwa ri kha mu /
NK022(za)001:14079: pad+ma ma shwa ri kha mu /
NK022(za)001:14081: me tri shwa ri kha mu /
NK022(za)001:14082: ka ru shwa ri kha mu /
NK022(za)001:14083: lo ga shwa ri kha mu /
NK022(za)001:14084: bi du kha shwa ri kha mu /
NK022(za)001:14085: yag sha kro ti shwa ri kha mu /
NK022(za)001:14086: raka sha kro ti shwa ri kha mu /
NK022(za)001:14087: 'big sha kro ti shwa ri kha mu /
NK022(za)001:14088: byi sha kro ti shwa ri kha mu /
NK022(za)001:14089: te sha shwa ri kha mu /
NK022(za)001:14090: ke sha shwa ri kha mu /
NK022(za)001:14091: pe sha shwa ri kha mu /
NK022(za)001:14092: bi sha shwa ri kha mu /
NK022(za)001:14093: trag sha shwa ri kha mu /
NK022(za)001:14094: hri sha shwa ri kha mu /
NK022(za)001:14095: ka sha shwa ri kha mu /
NK022(za)001:14096: bag sha shwa ri kha mu /
NK022(za)001:14097: ru ti shwa ri kha mu /
NK022(za)001:14098: rag ti shwa ri kha mu /
NK022(za)001:14100: pa ha shwa ri kha mu /
NK022(za)001:14109: badz+ra sing ha mu ka he /
NK022(za)001:14110: badz+ra bya tri mu ka he /
NK022(za)001:14111: badz+ra sh+ri la mu ka he /
NK022(za)001:14112: badz+ra shwa na mu ka he /
NK022(za)001:14113: badz+ra kri ta mu ka he /
NK022(za)001:14114: badz+ra kam ka mu ka he /
NK022(za)001:14115: badz+ra kha kha mu ka he /
NK022(za)001:14116: badz+ra hu lu mu ka he /
NK022(za)001:14117: badz+ra phata dza ar+ya te dza teng nga dza /
NK022(za)001:14118: badz+ra phata h'u pa sha h'u /
NK022(za)001:14119: badz+ra phata ba lo ka ba /
NK022(za)001:14120: badz+ra phata ho ba smi ba la ya ba ti ho /
NK022(za)001:14121: badz+ra kro ta h'u ka ra h'u /
NK022(za)001:14122: badz+ra kro ta bi dza ya h'u /
NK022(za)001:14123: badz+ra kro ta ya man+ta ka h'u /
NK022(za)001:14124: badz+ra kro ta ha ya g+h+ri ba h'u /
NK022(za)001:14125: badz+ra kro ta kun ta li h'u /
NK022(za)001:14126: badz+ra kro ta ni la tan tra h'u /
NK022(za)001:14127: badz+ra kro ta ar+ya a tsa la h'u /
NK022(za)001:14128: badz+ra kro ta a pa ra tsit+ta h'u /
NK022(za)001:14129: badz+ra kro ta tre lo kya bi dza ya h'u /
NK022(za)001:14130: badz+ra kro ta ma h+aa ba la h'u /
NK022(za)001:14131: kro ti shwa ri sha ya h'u /
NK022(za)001:14132: kro ti shwa ri la s+ye ke h'u /
NK022(za)001:14133: kro ti shwa ri sta na ba ti h'u /
NK022(za)001:14134: kro ti shwa ri tsan+d+ha re ya ti h'u /
NK022(za)001:14135: kro ti shwa ri ba ya ti h'u /
NK022(za)001:14136: kro ti shwa ri pra ti dza h'u /
NK022(za)001:14137: kro ti shwa ri mu la h'u /
NK022(za)001:14138: kro ti shwa ri k+sha ya bya h'u /
NK022(za)001:14139: kro ti shwa ri ma ra na h'u /
NK022(za)001:14140: kro ti shwa ri tsin da mu ne h'u /
NK022(za)001:14141: 'khor rnams rgyud gzhan sngags tshul sbyar /
NK022(za)001:14153: ma h+aa ka pa la gnya' na par sa ra /
NK022(za)001:14154: pho brang de yi gnas gnas su //
NK022(za)001:14155: phyag rgya'i tshul rnams 'byung ba ni //
NK022(za)001:14156: mu khyud mtha' zad yan chad du //
NK022(za)001:14157: yab yum drug cu rtsa bzhi po /
NK022(za)001:14158: phyogs mtshams le tser dor sogs bzhi //
NK022(za)001:14159: cho 'phrul bzhi po rang bzhin bsam //
NK022(za)001:14160: 'khor lo dam tshig tshad med dang //
NK022(za)001:14162: de bzhin za byed yab yum bzhi //
NK022(za)001:14163: las kyi lha ste he ru ka /
NK022(za)001:14164: 'khor lo tha ma'i rtsibs la bkod //
NK022(za)001:14165: gnas dang yul gyi phyag rgya dag /
NK022(za)001:14166: gru chad phyi dang nang la bkram //
NK022(za)001:14167: gus pa'i bu mo sgo bzhir bzhag /
NK022(za)001:14168: h'u chen bcu yi yab yum dag /
NK022(za)001:14169: shin tu mdzes par dang po la'o //
NK022(za)001:14170: de nyid la ni ma brgyad dang //
NK022(za)001:14171: ging chen bco brgyad rgyas par bkod //
NK022(za)001:14172: gnyis pa'i khyams la mkha' 'gro brgyad //
NK022(za)001:14173: shugs 'gro brgyad kyang de bzhin no //
NK022(za)001:14174: gsum pa'i khyams la phra men brgyad //
NK022(za)001:14175: de bzhin 'bar ma brgyad rnams bri //
NK022(za)001:14176: bzhi pa'i khyams las phor thogs brgyad //
NK022(za)001:14177: de bzhin srin mo gzhung thogs brgyad //
NK022(za)001:14178: lnga pa'i khyams ni tha ma la //
NK022(za)001:14179: rdo rje slas dang bran mo dang //
NK022(za)001:14180: pho nya la sogs rgyas par bkram //
NK022(za)001:14181: gtso bo mthing nag chen po ste //
NK022(za)001:14182: smug nag ser nag dmar nag dang //
NK022(za)001:14183: ljang nag khrag 'thung drug cu bzhi //
NK022(za)001:14184: rdo rje rin chen pad+ma gri //
NK022(za)001:14185: gar sogs cir yang 'gyur ba thogs //
NK022(za)001:14186: rdo rje snying po la sogs rnams //
NK022(za)001:14187: spyi mthun yo byad sna tshogs dang //
NK022(za)001:14188: thod khrag sor phreng mche ba thogs //
NK022(za)001:14189: ser phreng thod pa kha glal bzhi //
NK022(za)001:14190: de bzhin ba chen thogs pa dang //
NK022(za)001:14191: bam chen lag thogs khas bzung nas //
NK022(za)001:14193: gnas dang yul gyi phyag rgya ni //
NK022(za)001:14194: ko'u ri b+han dmar byis dbyug sngo //
NK022(za)001:14195: tso'u ri mda' gzhu 'gengs ma ser //
NK022(za)001:14196: pra mo chu srin rgyal mtshan 'phyar //
NK022(za)001:14197: be ta byis za rdo 'phyar nag /
NK022(za)001:14200: sma sha mthing nag byis snying za //
NK022(za)001:14202: sing ha kha ro snol ser seng //
NK022(za)001:14203: bye kri gnas lta snol ma stag /
NK022(za)001:14204: sri la nag mo byis ldag wa //
NK022(za)001:14205: pu ska dmar ser byis rgyu 'dren //
NK022(za)001:14206: shwa na drang lta mthing ka khyi //
NK022(za)001:14208: kang ka rkang 'phrag snar mog ring //
NK022(za)001:14209: kha kha kha ro b+han gri nag /
NK022(za)001:14210: hu lu mthing ka rgyu tshong 'ug /
NK022(za)001:14211: gus pa'i bu mo sgo srungs bzhi //
NK022(za)001:14212: rta gdong sngon mo lcags kyu 'dzin //
NK022(za)001:14213: phag gdong nag mo mche zhags can //
NK022(za)001:14214: nyi zla lcags sgrog seng gdong ma //
NK022(za)001:14215: thal chen dril bu sna tshogs mchod //
NK022(za)001:14216: h'u chen mthing kha mda' gzhu dang //
NK022(za)001:14217: rnam rgyal dkar po rdo rje 'dzin //
NK022(za)001:14218: dbyug sngon sdigs mdzub rin chen khro //
NK022(za)001:14219: gshin rje mthing nag be con thogs //
NK022(za)001:14220: mi g.yo ljang sngon ral gri can //
NK022(za)001:14221: rta mchog dmar po sbrul zhags bsnams //
NK022(za)001:14222: dpal ldan dmar skya ba dan de //
NK022(za)001:14223: bdud rtsi ljang nag dbyug tho'o //
NK022(za)001:14224: khams gsum ljang skya kha tong ka /
NK022(za)001:14225: stobs chen dud kha gtun shing thogs //
NK022(za)001:14226: yum rnams g.yas pa yab la 'khyud //
NK022(za)001:14227: g.yon pa b+han d+ha stobs pa'i tshul //
NK022(za)001:14228: 'khor rnams so so'ang gzhung bzhin no //
NK022(za)001:14229: yod med stong pa shin tu rnal 'byor mthus //
NK022(za)001:14230: nam mkha' bzhin las dam tshig nye bar gshegs //
NK022(za)001:14231: ye shes rgya mtsho rnam par grol ba'i klong //
NK022(za)001:14232: mi gnas mi dmigs nam mkha'i dbyings nas bzhengs //
NK022(za)001:14233: tshogs chen gnyis rdzogs thugs dam dbyings kyi lha //
NK022(za)001:14234: longs spyod rdzogs mdzad rol pa chen po'i sku //
NK022(za)001:14235: rdo rje sems dpa'i skal bzang dpal khyod bdag /
NK022(za)001:14236: thabs kyi rol pas bde chen dbyings nas bzhengs //
NK022(za)001:14237: ye shes sgyu mas rnam par rol pa'i sku //
NK022(za)001:14238: thabs dang shes rab che la mnga' brnyes pa'i //
NK022(za)001:14239: 'phags rjes sprul pa mang po 'byung ba'i gnas //
NK022(za)001:14240: bder gshegs bde bar gshegs mdzad bzhengs su gsol //
NK022(za)001:14241: rang bzhin yul nas phab nas ni //
NK022(za)001:14242: bsgrub pa'i dkyil 'khor de rdzogs bya //
NK022(za)001:14243: spyan drang bstim brtan phyag rgya la sogs sbyar /
NK022(za)001:14246: e ha hi ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u dza dza /
NK022(za)001:14247: badz+ra sa ma ya mu tra h'u a /
NK022(za)001:14248: badz+ra sh+ri he ru ka ti sta sa ma ya lhan /
NK022(za)001:14249: ma h+aa sh+ri he ru ka /
NK022(za)001:14256: rnal 'byor mchog gi lag gnyis las //
NK022(za)001:14257: nyi zla 'bar ba'i ling kar ni //
NK022(za)001:14258: a dang ma gnyis gsal bzhag ste //
NK022(za)001:14259: thabs dang shes rab gnyis med sbyar //
NK022(za)001:14260: mnyam pa'i tshul du gnas pa las //
NK022(za)001:14261: ma yi steng du a nyid bzhag /
NK022(za)001:14262: bya ba thams cad bral ba'i rgya //
NK022(za)001:14263: a dang ma yi 'bru bcu rnams //
NK022(za)001:14267: a dang ma yi 'bru bcu rnams //
NK022(za)001:14268: so sor bcas te myu gu bya //
NK022(za)001:14269: shin tu bstod de kun tu bsgyur //
NK022(za)001:14271: ma yis sbyin pa gtong tshul la //
NK022(za)001:14272: a yis thams cad skyob byed pa //
NK022(za)001:14273: 'di ni tshad med chen po yin //
NK022(za)001:14274: kun la snyoms pa'i phyag rgya yin //
NK022(za)001:14275: ma nyid khrag 'phrog sa yi snod //
NK022(za)001:14276: a nyid sor phreng mche ba sbyar //
NK022(za)001:14277: 'di ni thams cad rol pa yi //
NK022(za)001:14278: 'jigs tshul ston pa'i phyag rgya yin //
NK022(za)001:14279: a dang ma gnyis gting sbyar te //
NK022(za)001:14280: sor phreng 'chi ba'i tshul gyis ni //
NK022(za)001:14281: shin tu kha blal ba yi tshul //
NK022(za)001:14283: ma yis bzung ste 'then nas ni //
NK022(za)001:14284: a yis gtings zhing 'joms byed pa //
NK022(za)001:14285: 'joms byed chen po'i phyag rgya yin //
NK022(za)001:14287: bzung ba'i tshul du byas nas ni //
NK022(za)001:14289: za byed chen po'i phyag rgya yin //
NK022(za)001:14290: a dang ma yi shes rab las //
NK022(za)001:14291: g.yas g.yon tshul gyis bsgyur byas te //
NK022(za)001:14292: so so ji ltar yin thabs sbyar //
NK022(za)001:14293: bu mo nyi shu snga ma bzhin //
NK022(za)001:14294: dpa' bo gdan las bzhengs nas ni //
NK022(za)001:14295: phyogs tsam kun tu bltas byas nas //
NK022(za)001:14296: shin tu 'gying shing brjid par bya //
NK022(za)001:14297: a dang ma yi 'bru rnams ni //
NK022(za)001:14298: so sor bsdams nas bskur brten bya //
NK022(za)001:14299: 'gying ba'i tshul gyis spyad byas nas //
NK022(za)001:14300: stag gi stabs kyis kun tu bskor //
NK022(za)001:14301: de nas rmun bya'i stobs kyis bskor //
NK022(za)001:14302: de bzhin rus sbal gzig dang stag /
NK022(za)001:14303: spyang ki seng ge dom stabs dang //
NK022(za)001:14304: phag chen dred kyi stabs kyis ni //
NK022(za)001:14305: thams cad thams cad skor bar bya //
NK022(za)001:14306: de bzhin 'dab chags thams cad kyi //
NK022(za)001:14307: 'jo tshul stabs rnams rdzogs byas nas //
NK022(za)001:14309: h'u 'byung ba chen po'i nam mkha' ni //
NK022(za)001:14310: 'byung ba chen po lnga yi mdzod //
NK022(za)001:14313: nam mkha' mdzod kyi sngags kyis bskul //
NK022(za)001:14314: rdo rje rol pa'i tshogs mchod 'di //
NK022(za)001:14315: mchod sprin kun tu rgyas gyur cig /
NK022(za)001:14316: zla rgyas la sogs snying po'i mchog /
NK022(za)001:14317: ma sa la sogs rnam lnga'i rdzogs //
NK022(za)001:14318: me tog la sogs tsan+da phreng //
NK022(za)001:14319: sna tshogs mchod pa 'byung gyur cig /
NK022(za)001:14320: 'chi med bdud rtsi g.yung drung chu //
NK022(za)001:14321: ro yi khams rnams slong bar byed //
NK022(za)001:14322: dug gi phung po 'joms byed pa //
NK022(za)001:14323: rtsi mchog sman gyi mchod pa bzhengs //
NK022(za)001:14324: dug gsum rtsegs pa'i ri bo 'di //
NK022(za)001:14325: sku gsung thugs kyi klong du stabs //
NK022(za)001:14326: dug lnga rol pa'i tshogs mchod 'di //
NK022(za)001:14327: ye shes lnga yi ngang du thim //
NK022(za)001:14329: dbyings dang ye shes klong du thim //
NK022(za)001:14331: chos nyid dbyings kyi ngang du thim //
NK022(za)001:14332: phung po tshogs kyi yan lag 'di //
NK022(za)001:14333: rnam grol phung po lnga ru thim //
NK022(za)001:14335: mkha' klong 'bar ba lnga ru thim //
NK022(za)001:14336: rol pa chen po'i mchod sbyin la //
NK022(za)001:14337: rgyal ba rgya mtsho'i tshogs rnams rol //
NK022(za)001:14338: mi mo rnams kyi reg bya'i mchog /
NK022(za)001:14340: dbang po sbyor ba'i dges mchog ste //
NK022(za)001:14341: bde ba'i mchod pas tshim gyur cig /
NK022(za)001:14342: bla med stan dgon mchod pa 'di //
NK022(za)001:14343: sngon chad rgyal ba bgrod pa'i lam //
NK022(za)001:14344: dug gsum gting nas gsod pa'i thabs //
NK022(za)001:14345: sngon gyi thugs dam bzhin du bzhes //
NK022(za)001:14350: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha ra kha hi /
NK022(za)001:14351: ma h+aa rak+ta ru ti tig sna /
NK022(za)001:14355: ma h+aa tsit+ta kha ra kha hi /
NK022(za)001:14356: kha kha le sha ta kha hi /
NK022(za)001:14362: u tsi ra sa ma ya phata /
NK022(za)001:14365: bdud rtsi sman gyi rjes su sbyar //
NK022(za)001:14366: mkha' 'gro ma rnams dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:14367: gnas sgags dam dbog gnad du bya'o //
NK022(za)001:14368: de nas tshogs kyi mchod sbyar te //
NK022(za)001:14369: zla ba rgyas dang rdzogs pa dang //
NK022(za)001:14370: zla ba dkar dang zla phrom mchog /
NK022(za)001:14371: che mchog kun gyi gtso bo dang //
NK022(za)001:14372: 'jam por thar pa chen po dang //
NK022(za)001:14373: gal phyis zhes bya ba'i ro mchog dang //
NK022(za)001:14374: gzi brjid chen po ro zhim dang //
NK022(za)001:14375: bran mo dang ni g.yo can ma //
NK022(za)001:14376: 'jam dpal rnon po'i sgral sogs pa'i //
NK022(za)001:14377: 'byor pa'i yo byad sna tshogs bsham //
NK022(za)001:14378: de nas rgyal po'i byin brlabs kyis //
NK022(za)001:14379: yo byad 'di dag bdud rtsi lngar //
NK022(za)001:14380: dam rdzas ngo bor bsdus nas ni //
NK022(za)001:14382: zhu nas phyag mtshan rnam lngar 'bar //
NK022(za)001:14383: dag pa'i bdud rtsi chen por zhu //
NK022(za)001:14384: de nas lha mo nam mkha' gang //
NK022(za)001:14385: shes rab lha mo rig 'dzin ma //
NK022(za)001:14386: bzhi'am yang na rnam pa brgyad //
NK022(za)001:14387: yo byad rdzas sam rang bzhin la //
NK022(za)001:14388: zas mchog gar gyis spyir blangs te //
NK022(za)001:14389: bdag cag rig 'dzin shes rab ma //
NK022(za)001:14391: rgyal ba lha yi dngos grub 'dzin //
NK022(za)001:14392: dgyes pas tshim pa'i longs spyod dag /
NK022(za)001:14393: ji ltar yid bzhin nor bu'am //
NK022(za)001:14395: ma rmos lo thog dges par sbyar //
NK022(za)001:14396: rnal 'byor longs spyod chen po dag /
NK022(za)001:14397: nam mkha'i khams su gtibs nas kyang //
NK022(za)001:14398: rdo rje dges tshogs kun 'dus nas //
NK022(za)001:14399: skal ldan rnams kyis rab sprul cing //
NK022(za)001:14400: rdo rje gar gyi dbang bsgyur nas //
NK022(za)001:14401: sgegs pas lha mo 'jo tshul dag /
NK022(za)001:14402: 'dud cing stobs pa'i tshul gyis ni //
NK022(za)001:14403: rol mo'i tshogs kyis dga' ba bskyed //
NK022(za)001:14404: h+r+ai badz+ra la s+ye h'u h'u /
NK022(za)001:14412: rdo rje dkar ma'i thabs mchog gis //
NK022(za)001:14413: rdo rje glu 'dis gzi byin skyed //
NK022(za)001:14414: rdo rje bdud rtsi'i longs spyod 'di //
NK022(za)001:14415: gzi mdangs rgyas par byed pa'i mchog /
NK022(za)001:14416: bkrag 'dzin gzungs mchog dran pa'i dpal //
NK022(za)001:14417: rdo rje can gyi byin stobs kyis //
NK022(za)001:14418: skal ldan rnams kyi zas su bya //
NK022(za)001:14419: skal med rnams kyi dug tu 'gyur //
NK022(za)001:14420: dper na sbrul la 'o ma bzhin //
NK022(za)001:14421: 'jam dpal rnon pos sngon bsgral ba'ang //
NK022(za)001:14422: bsgral ba'i rgyu mchog man chad nas //
NK022(za)001:14423: shel can tsa ra la sogs pa //
NK022(za)001:14424: bsgral ba'ang stan 'gan sprugs byas te //
NK022(za)001:14425: bud med bud med thams cad kun //
NK022(za)001:14426: bskyed par byed pa'i rten yin te //
NK022(za)001:14427: 'bras bu smin pa'i zhing yang yin //
NK022(za)001:14428: sgral zhing gdon pa'i gnas yin te //
NK022(za)001:14429: shes rab go ba'i yum yin no //
NK022(za)001:14430: 'di la sems gsum gnas pa ste //
NK022(za)001:14431: ye nas dag pa chos nyid sems //
NK022(za)001:14432: mkha' dag sbyor ba byang chub sems //
NK022(za)001:14433: snying rjes sgral ba gsum sbyar te //
NK022(za)001:14434: chos nyid gsang ba nyi shar khyab //
NK022(za)001:14435: snying rjes sgrol ba gsum gyis sbyor //
NK022(za)001:14436: snying rjes sgral ba'i rnam gsum ste //
NK022(za)001:14437: ting 'dzin chos nyid ngang du sbyar //
NK022(za)001:14438: byin rlabs dur khrod chen po sgrol //
NK022(za)001:14439: ye shes chen po mkha' la bsgral //
NK022(za)001:14440: thog mar sgral ba'i thabs mchog kyang //
NK022(za)001:14441: dgongs pa gsal btab drang bya ste //
NK022(za)001:14442: khog srungs gshed dang dbral bya ste //
NK022(za)001:14443: thugs rjes rgyu drug bkug bstim bya //
NK022(za)001:14444: gsang ba mchog gi bdag po yis //
NK022(za)001:14445: rgyud sbyang rgyud drug lam sgo gcad //
NK022(za)001:14447: dkyil 'khor chen por gsal bton te //
NK022(za)001:14448: phyag rgya dbang dang bcas pa yis //
NK022(za)001:14449: 'khor ba'i rgyud rnams sbyang bar bya //
NK022(za)001:14450: sgral byed de yi gnas lnga ru //
NK022(za)001:14451: rgyud drug sa bon bskyed nas kyang //
NK022(za)001:14452: h'u lnga dag gis gnas par bya //
NK022(za)001:14453: sgral byed de yi spyi bor ni //
NK022(za)001:14454: sa yi ye shes las bskrun pa //
NK022(za)001:14455: pad+ma kha bzhi bye ba la //
NK022(za)001:14456: lte bar lha mi sa bon bkod //
NK022(za)001:14457: shar lho nub dang byang dag tu //
NK022(za)001:14458: lha min dud 'gro yi dwags dang //
NK022(za)001:14459: dmyal ba rnams kyi sa bon gdab //
NK022(za)001:14460: h'u gi lam sgo bcad par bya //
NK022(za)001:14461: lag gnyis mathe'u chung mthe bos mnan //
NK022(za)001:14462: sor mo gsum sbyar dpral bar bzlog /
NK022(za)001:14463: lha dang lha min gnas dag tu //
NK022(za)001:14464: mi gtang bzlog pa'i phyag rgya yin //
NK022(za)001:14465: lag gnyis bsnol nas mchan khung bsdam //
NK022(za)001:14466: mi yi khams nas bzlog pa'i rgya //
NK022(za)001:14467: khu tshur bcings nas 'bru sbreng nas //
NK022(za)001:14468: g.yon gyi steng du mnan pa'i 'di //
NK022(za)001:14469: byol song gnas nas bzlog pa'i rgya //
NK022(za)001:14470: thal mo mnyam sbyar gung rtse sprad //
NK022(za)001:14471: gung mo'i rgyab tu srin lag snol //
NK022(za)001:14473: yi dang khams nas bzlog pa'i rgya //
NK022(za)001:14474: g.yon thog g.yas kyi rgyab sbyar te //
NK022(za)001:14475: srin lag gung 'dzub gcig nas ni //
NK022(za)001:14476: 'khyud pas dmyal ba'i sgo gcod rgya //
NK022(za)001:14477: lag g.yas phyag rgya bcas nas ni //
NK022(za)001:14478: ngag gi rdo rje brgya brjod pa //
NK022(za)001:14479: kyi ma r+au tra kro ta kyi h'u /
NK022(za)001:14480: hri sa ma pa tsa h'u /
NK022(za)001:14481: yang na snying la pad 'dab bzhir //
NK022(za)001:14482: de bzhin rgyud drug sa bon btab //
NK022(za)001:14483: rang bzhin ye nas de gzhom bya //
NK022(za)001:14484: khyad par 'dus pa'i yi ge lnga //
NK022(za)001:14485: gnas bskyod spros pas mtha' yas bkang //
NK022(za)001:14486: thams cad stongs shing zad byas nas //
NK022(za)001:14487: 'dus par ye shes lnga ru gsal //
NK022(za)001:14488: de las phyag mtshan ye shes lnga //
NK022(za)001:14489: mi gnas ye shes ngang du thim //
NK022(za)001:14490: de nas mkha' la sgral ba'ang //
NK022(za)001:14491: bskang ba'i cho ga rdzogs byas nas //
NK022(za)001:14492: rdo rje sra yi las byas las //
NK022(za)001:14493: sgrib po'i phung po smin pa de //
NK022(za)001:14494: rdo rje rol pa'i rngam tshegs kyis //
NK022(za)001:14495: 'jo tshul stabs kyis sbyang bar bya //
NK022(za)001:14496: kha ta la sogs sngags bcas pas //
NK022(za)001:14497: bsgyel te ma rig sgo dbye bya //
NK022(za)001:14498: rnam shes lcags kyi sgrom drangs la //
NK022(za)001:14499: rdo rje rgyal po'i rlung sgrom du //
NK022(za)001:14500: bsdus te rdo rje lcugs can la //
NK022(za)001:14501: h'u byas bsgrol mas de la brlab //
NK022(za)001:14502: gsang ba thugs kyi dkyil 'khor du //
NK022(za)001:14503: tshon gang 'od du thim par bya //
NK022(za)001:14504: yu ti a ha gyis spar te //
NK022(za)001:14505: gsal ba de dang mnyam du gsal //
NK022(za)001:14506: rdo rje tshe la bslun par bya //
NK022(za)001:14507: rdo rje rlung gis lcugs spar te //
NK022(za)001:14508: thugs las rlung sgrom lam du spar //
NK022(za)001:14509: nam mkha' chos kyi gzhal yas su //
NK022(za)001:14510: nyi ma'i steng na h'u du gsal //
NK022(za)001:14511: ye shes sems dpa' tshon gang ba //
NK022(za)001:14512: nyi zla'i ga'u bar na gsal //
NK022(za)001:14513: a yang phata kyis skyod 'phangs pa'i //
NK022(za)001:14514: rdo rje sems dpa'i thugs khar 'phros //
NK022(za)001:14515: ye shes sems dpa' gsal ba la //
NK022(za)001:14516: dngos por snang dang 'dzin dang bral //
NK022(za)001:14518: rdo rje ming gi dbang bskur te //
NK022(za)001:14519: rigs kyi lha dang snying por sbyin //
NK022(za)001:14520: rdo rje gdung ba'i glu blangs te //
NK022(za)001:14521: man ngag gnas kyi smon lam gdab //
NK022(za)001:14522: gsum pa dur khrod sgral ba'i phyir //
NK022(za)001:14523: bzhi tshal dag tu byas nas ni //
NK022(za)001:14524: sman gyis btab ste phung por rtsal //
NK022(za)001:14525: 'khor ba'i phung po de bsdus nas //
NK022(za)001:14526: rdo rje stabs dang gru yis sbyangs //
NK022(za)001:14527: phrin las rnam bzhi 'tsham par sbyar //
NK022(za)001:14528: phung po mchod pa'i rdzas su bstim //
NK022(za)001:14529: des ni mnyes dang skongs ba dang //
NK022(za)001:14530: rdo rje las rnams grub pa yin //
NK022(za)001:14531: rgyal ba bskul ba'i sa la bzhengs //
NK022(za)001:14532: rnal 'byor gso ba'i cho ga byed //
NK022(za)001:14533: lnga dang gcig tu bya ba'i phyir //
NK022(za)001:14534: bzlas brjod drangs dang bsnyen pa dang //
NK022(za)001:14535: sbyor bas don la nye bar 'gyur //
NK022(za)001:14536: rin chen 'bar ba'i ling ga la //
NK022(za)001:14537: sangs rgyas ye shes dpal gyi sku //
NK022(za)001:14538: rin chen 'bar ba'i ngos brgyad la //
NK022(za)001:14539: rig pa'i ma mo dpal 'bar ma //
NK022(za)001:14540: brgyad du gsal bar gyur pa dang //
NK022(za)001:14541: ye shes rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor rdzogs //
NK022(za)001:14545: gsung gi rtsa ba'i phyag rgya yin //
NK022(za)001:14546: rdo rje 'bar ba'i ling ga la //
NK022(za)001:14547: yi ge h'u gi 'bru yis bskor //
NK022(za)001:14548: mtha' ma rin chen yig 'bru brgyad //
NK022(za)001:14549: kha dog mthing kas bskor ba ni //
NK022(za)001:14550: thugs kyi gsang ba'i ye shes yin //
NK022(za)001:14551: dpal be'u thugs kyi sgo phye bas //
NK022(za)001:14553: mthing nag ser nag dmar nag ljang //
NK022(za)001:14555: yi ge rigs kyis phreng ba drang //
NK022(za)001:14556: glu yi rgyal po 'di drug gis //
NK022(za)001:14557: don drug yongs su rdzogs par 'gyur //
NK022(za)001:14558: shab+ta pa yis glu blangs pas //
NK022(za)001:14559: gnod byed thams cad rdul du brlag /
NK022(za)001:14560: cang ka te yi glu blangs pas //
NK022(za)001:14562: pa ka te yi glu blangs pas //
NK022(za)001:14563: drag po gtum po lhan ner 'gyur //
NK022(za)001:14564: breng nga pa yis glu blangs pas //
NK022(za)001:14566: dung nga pa yis glu blangs pas //
NK022(za)001:14567: srid pa'i bu mo dbang du bsdud //
NK022(za)001:14568: bdag nyid dpal chen 'bar ba'i thugs //
NK022(za)001:14569: tsit+ta dpal be'u zur brgyad dam //
NK022(za)001:14570: rin chen yi ge brgyad du gsal //
NK022(za)001:14571: dpal chen rin chen 'bar ba'i thugs //
NK022(za)001:14572: dpal be'u smug po zur brgyad las //
NK022(za)001:14573: gser gyi nyi ma dgu shar bar //
NK022(za)001:14575: rdo rje 'bar ba'i rlung sgrom du //
NK022(za)001:14577: spros nas rnal 'byor dbang phyug gis //
NK022(za)001:14578: na pa g.yas su drang bar bya //
NK022(za)001:14579: go ro tsa na'i gzhal yas su //
NK022(za)001:14580: sen zlum tsam gyi rgya khyon la //
NK022(za)001:14581: gser gyi nyi ma ga'u dgu //
NK022(za)001:14582: shar ba'i dkyil na yig 'bru brgyad //
NK022(za)001:14583: gsal ba 'od kyi gzhal yas khang //
NK022(za)001:14584: dngos po'i bag chags kun sregs te //
NK022(za)001:14585: sems ni gser chu zhun ma bzhin //
NK022(za)001:14587: rtsal las gyur pa'i zla dkyil na //
NK022(za)001:14588: nyi ma'i steng na dpal be'u 'bar //
NK022(za)001:14594: dper na me tog 'bar ba las //
NK022(za)001:14595: bcud len bung bas bcud blangs te //
NK022(za)001:14596: rtsi yi bum par sogs par ltar //
NK022(za)001:14597: dpal be'u thugs kyi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK022(za)001:14599: ru lu yig 'bru bcud kyis brgyas //
NK022(za)001:14600: rnal 'byor sems las byas pa yi //
NK022(za)001:14602: phar ldings yig 'bru'i bcud phyung nas //
NK022(za)001:14603: tshur ldings sems kyi ga'ura thim //
NK022(za)001:14604: dang po shel gyi kha dog las //
NK022(za)001:14606: gnas dgu dag tu zla ba yi //
NK022(za)001:14607: thig le dkyil gyi dpal be'u las //
NK022(za)001:14608: 'bru bkod gsal bar gyur pa dang //
NK022(za)001:14609: shel gyi bung ba mang po dag /
NK022(za)001:14610: khyung chen ldings pa'i bongs tshod la //
NK022(za)001:14611: phar ldings bcud phyung bab pas ni //
NK022(za)001:14613: bag chags bud shing phung po bsregs //
NK022(za)001:14614: phar 'phros thugs rje'i ngang la bskul //
NK022(za)001:14615: ji ltar nyi zer tsha tsha ltar //
NK022(za)001:14617: bar du byi ru'i kha dog la //
NK022(za)001:14618: gong ma bzhin du bkod gsal ba //
NK022(za)001:14619: byi ru'i bung ba mang po dag /
NK022(za)001:14620: gong ma bzhin du 'phur ldings pas //
NK022(za)001:14621: bcud phyung bstim zhing slar yang 'phro //
NK022(za)001:14623: dpal be'u smug po klong du bstim //
NK022(za)001:14624: kun gyi tha mar bsdu ba ni //
NK022(za)001:14625: bkod pa gong ma thams cad kun //
NK022(za)001:14626: mthing nag 'bar bar bsgyur nas ni //
NK022(za)001:14627: khyung chen gzan la 'dzums tshod tsam //
NK022(za)001:14628: h'u sgra 'byin cing phan tshun ldings //
NK022(za)001:14629: ru lu bcud 'byin dngos grub thob //
NK022(za)001:14630: dran pa'i dkyil nas dza byung ste //
NK022(za)001:14632: dpal be'u dkyil na spungs pa yi //
NK022(za)001:14633: ru lu rin chen phung po dag /
NK022(za)001:14634: bsdus zhing drangs te gnas su stim //
NK022(za)001:14635: bab pa'i shugs sam byin rlabs ni //
NK022(za)001:14636: mtsho la gser chen 'dril ltar ro //
NK022(za)001:14637: 'di ltar yi ge sbyar ba'i tshe //
NK022(za)001:14638: rnal 'byor nyag cig ma yin gyi //
NK022(za)001:14639: lha mchog dbyings nas bzhugs pa yang //
NK022(za)001:14640: chos nyid ngang du mi dmigs kyang //
NK022(za)001:14641: rnal 'byor mchog gis bskul ba'i tshe //
NK022(za)001:14642: thugs rje chags pa'i mdangs phyung nas //
NK022(za)001:14643: srog rtsol dran rig gsung gsung ltar //
NK022(za)001:14646: gug skyed klad kor tsheg dbar phyin //
NK022(za)001:14647: ra ri khal khol bsgrib med pa //
NK022(za)001:14648: ye shes don la mkhyen gsal rig /
NK022(za)001:14649: klu yi yon tan bsam mi khyab //
NK022(za)001:14650: sngon kyang rgyal ba glu yis 'grub //
NK022(za)001:14653: bstan pa rgya mtsho glu yis spel //
NK022(za)001:14654: srid pa'i bu mo glu yis ston //
NK022(za)001:14655: bdud dang srin po glu yis 'dul //
NK022(za)001:14656: dngos grub rgya mtsho glu yis 'bebs //
NK022(za)001:14657: chos nyid dbyings kyi klong dkyil nas //
NK022(za)001:14658: dpal be'u nyi ma dgu shar ba //
NK022(za)001:14659: rnam thar sgo bzhir rab gsal yang //
NK022(za)001:14660: ma rig mun nag 'thibs pa yis //
NK022(za)001:14661: bsgribs pas rig pa'i sgo ma phye //
NK022(za)001:14662: 'khor ba'i mun nag klong rum nas //
NK022(za)001:14663: byang chub sems kyi zla shar bas //
NK022(za)001:14664: mun gsal rnam thar sgo bzhir snang //
NK022(za)001:14665: rin chen 'bar ba'i nyi ma rnams //
NK022(za)001:14666: dpal chen thugs las nyi shar bas //
NK022(za)001:14667: bag chags sprin mthong phye bar du //
NK022(za)001:14668: rnal 'byor thugs khar gzer btab pas //
NK022(za)001:14669: mun gsal rig pa'i sgo phye ste //
NK022(za)001:14671: rig pa thugs kyi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK022(za)001:14672: ru lu'i 'od zer sgo phye bas //
NK022(za)001:14674: srid pa gsum gyi byo bzlog byed //
NK022(za)001:14675: 'khor ba rgya mtsho'i gting nas skyems //
NK022(za)001:14676: nyon mongs rgyud drug gnas nas sgrol //
NK022(za)001:14677: dug gsum rtsa ba brtsad nas gcod //
NK022(za)001:14678: bdud dang srin po gdug pa 'dul //
NK022(za)001:14679: byin rlabs dngos grub char ltar 'bebs //
NK022(za)001:14680: yi ge 'bru dgu'i rang bzhin la //
NK022(za)001:14681: phyag rgya'i dkyil 'khor thams cad rdzogs //
NK022(za)001:14682: de bzhin 'khor lo mu khyud bcas //
NK022(za)001:14683: khyams dang sgo khyud gsal ba'o //
NK022(za)001:14684: srid pa yod mthong snang grags kyang //
NK022(za)001:14685: thams cad sngags kyi tshig tu rdzogs //
NK022(za)001:14686: yi ge brgya pa kun dang 'brel //
NK022(za)001:14687: 'khor lo'i sa la nye ba yi //
NK022(za)001:14688: yi ge dmigs pa thams cad 'grub //
NK022(za)001:14689: chags med lhun grub don po che //
NK022(za)001:14690: rnam bzhi las kyi khyad par yang //
NK022(za)001:14691: bya ba med par don du 'gyur //
NK022(za)001:14693: dam pa'i ngo mtshar sna tshogs 'byung //
NK022(za)001:14694: de bzhin srid pa'i bud shing sregs //
NK022(za)001:14695: gti mug mun sel ye shes 'bar //
NK022(za)001:14696: rig pa'i nyi ma gsal bar 'bebs //
NK022(za)001:14697: de kun yi ges rnam sprul pas //
NK022(za)001:14698: rang bzhin dngos med chos kyi dbyings //
NK022(za)001:14699: dngos grub yum gyi mkha' la dbab //
NK022(za)001:14701: mkha' nas mkha' dang zhal nas zhal //
NK022(za)001:14703: yab yum sbyor ba'i lhag sems dag /
NK022(za)001:14704: ma phebs bar du de bzhin bya //
NK022(za)001:14705: 'di ltar sbyor ba'i dus dag tu //
NK022(za)001:14706: byin rlabs phan sems g.yo ba yi //
NK022(za)001:14707: rtags sam drod dam mtshan ma ni //
NK022(za)001:14708: lus kyi drod dang rmi lam dang //
NK022(za)001:14709: sems kyi rtags su gsal ba dang //
NK022(za)001:14710: dbugs dag la yang nges pa 'byung //
NK022(za)001:14711: shing bal lta bur yang ba dang //
NK022(za)001:14712: mi bde'i gnod dang bral ba yin //
NK022(za)001:14713: rig pa ting 'dzin gsal ba dang //
NK022(za)001:14715: dang zhing dga' ba mgu ba skye //
NK022(za)001:14716: gdung ba'i byang chub sems skyed zhing //
NK022(za)001:14717: ngo mtshar skyes pa de bzhin no //
NK022(za)001:14718: 'gyu ba'i dbugs la dbang thob ste //
NK022(za)001:14719: dgag dang 'byung ba ji lta ba'o //
NK022(za)001:14720: snyen par dbang thob de bzhin brtsam //
NK022(za)001:14721: zin nas bstod de dngos grub bstim //
NK022(za)001:14722: e ma ho chos kun sku la ye nas rdzogs pas chos kyi sku /
NK022(za)001:14723: rdo rje che mchog phyag 'tshal he ru ka /
NK022(za)001:14724: chos nyid sku la skar tshogs rgyas pa'i sku //
NK022(za)001:14725: dbyar gyi char sprin gtibs pa lta bu'i gzugs //
NK022(za)001:14726: chu rlabs lta bur brjid pa'i zhal gdangs shing //
NK022(za)001:14727: nyi ma 'bum gyi 'od zer bdal ba bzhin //
NK022(za)001:14728: theg chen dgu dang 'khor ba'i chos rnams kun //
NK022(za)001:14729: phyag rgya gcig tu bkod nas rdzogs pa'i sku //
NK022(za)001:14730: sku gsum lhun grub chos sku tog stong 'bar //
NK022(za)001:14731: dbu skra kham nag ral ba'i cod pan can //
NK022(za)001:14732: klu rgyal 'bum gyis klubs shing mchod pa 'bul //
NK022(za)001:14733: rdo rje gsung gi ljags sgra gdabs pas kyang //
NK022(za)001:14734: h'u dang phata kyi sgra skad 'jigs par sgrogs //
NK022(za)001:14735: theg chen don dam gsang sngags sgrogs pa'i tshig /
NK022(za)001:14736: 'bar ba'i smin ma mun rum glog ltar 'gyu //
NK022(za)001:14737: spyan dmar zlog pa'i sdang mig nyi ltar 'bar //
NK022(za)001:14738: 'bar ba'i shangs nas skal pa'i 'tshub nag 'khyil //
NK022(za)001:14739: rdo rje thog dang gnam lcags ser chen 'bebs //
NK022(za)001:14740: rno dpal mche ba zang yag gtsigs pa yis //
NK022(za)001:14741: nyon mongs log lta'i tshogs la rngam zhing 'khrug /
NK022(za)001:14742: thod rus sha khrag rkang rus 'bu dang rnag /
NK022(za)001:14743: za byed rngam pa'i zhal du chem chem gsol //
NK022(za)001:14744: sbrul gdug ko rlon la sogs 'jigs pa'i rgyan //
NK022(za)001:14745: rngam pa'i sku la shin tu brjid par bgyi //
NK022(za)001:14746: za byed rngam dang 'jigs byed mang po'i tshogs //
NK022(za)001:14747: 'bar ba'i phyag mtshan sprul pa'i pho nya'i tshogs //
NK022(za)001:14748: 'khor ba kun dang thar pa'i chos rnams ni //
NK022(za)001:14749: dpa' bo chen po gdan du brjid cing rol //
NK022(za)001:14750: 'gran gyi zla med che btsan gcig pu nyid //
NK022(za)001:14751: gsang mchog 'bar ba'i sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK022(za)001:14752: de ltar las rnams rdzogs byas nas //
NK022(za)001:14753: rmad du byung ba'i gtor ma dag /
NK022(za)001:14754: cha gsum dang po sbyin sreg bya //
NK022(za)001:14755: bar pa mi zad gter du sba //
NK022(za)001:14756: byang chub sems kyi chu 'o dang //
NK022(za)001:14757: chos nyid nam mkha'i dbyings chen dang //
NK022(za)001:14758: ba ga gsum gyi sa gzhi la //
NK022(za)001:14759: shin tu sba ba'i tshul du bya //
NK022(za)001:14760: cha gcig gzhal byas shar sgo nas //
NK022(za)001:14761: bcu gsum bcal bar stegs bu bya //
NK022(za)001:14762: de ni gnas bdun gtso rnams kyang //
NK022(za)001:14763: de bzhin bcu gsum lan re la //
NK022(za)001:14764: gnas kyi 'dron ni ma sring rnams //
NK022(za)001:14765: las las grub pa kun bkug ste //
NK022(za)001:14766: bdun cu'i bar du kun rdzogs bya //
NK022(za)001:14767: tha mar man+dala zla gam la //
NK022(za)001:14768: nus na lha mo nam mkha'i hom /
NK022(za)001:14769: rdzogs bya ma lus de mgu bya //
NK022(za)001:14770: lhag mar gyur pa kun rdzogs bya //
NK022(za)001:14771: dkyil 'khor thugs la bsdus byas shing //
NK022(za)001:14772: rtog pa bral ba'i dbyings su gsal //
NK022(za)001:14773: chad dang bral ba'i sku bskyed de //
NK022(za)001:14774: bar chad bgegs las rgyal ba'i phyir //
NK022(za)001:14775: go bgo lus srung brtan par bya //
NK022(za)001:14776: de nas bkra shis tshul bzhin brtsam //
NK022(za)001:14778: phyag rgya bzhi las nyams pa med //
NK022(za)001:14779: yul drug dbang po rnam shes kun //
NK022(za)001:14780: lha nyid mnyam sbyor mthong thos med //
NK022(za)001:14781: gang 'gro tshe na goms pa gdan //
NK022(za)001:14782: gtso bo zhabs brgyad bzhugs par bsam //
NK022(za)001:14783: de bzhin 'dug tshe brjid par bzhugs //
NK022(za)001:14784: de dag sprul pas gdug pa sgrol //
NK022(za)001:14785: longs spyod bza' btung zhal hom du //
NK022(za)001:14786: lha la lha 'am dgra bgegs stim //
NK022(za)001:14787: rdo rje spar shad blangs byas te //
NK022(za)001:14788: rdo rje mche bas btsems nas ni //
NK022(za)001:14789: ljags kyi mes sbyangs h'u gyur pa //
NK022(za)001:14790: bsgrol bas tshon gang thung la brlan //
NK022(za)001:14791: langs tshe don las bzhengs pa yi //
NK022(za)001:14792: ral pa me stag 'phros pa yis //
NK022(za)001:14793: srid rtser gnas pa kun bsgral bya //
NK022(za)001:14794: shes rab mchog gi 'di sgom mo //
NK022(za)001:14795: stong gsum b+han d+ha bzang khong du //
NK022(za)001:14796: srid gsum sems can dug chen las //
NK022(za)001:14797: dug gsum sangs rgyas rtsir sbyar bas //
NK022(za)001:14798: bdud rtsi dkyil 'khor lhun gyis rdzogs //
NK022(za)001:14799: 'khor ba chos kyi dbyings nyid las //
NK022(za)001:14800: sems can sangs rgyas snying po shar //
NK022(za)001:14801: sgra skad bsam gyis mi khyab pa //
NK022(za)001:14802: thams cad bzlas brjod sngags kyi tshig /
NK022(za)001:14803: dri za gnas pa'i rang bzhin ni //
NK022(za)001:14804: mkha' 'am stong pa'i ngos dag la //
NK022(za)001:14805: dri za'i gzugs ni gar byung yang //
NK022(za)001:14806: grong khyer de yang de nas byung //
NK022(za)001:14807: byung nas de ltar mi rtag ltar //
NK022(za)001:14808: gsang sngags grub pa'i gnas dag kyang //
NK022(za)001:14809: chos sam yid kyi mkha' ngos la //
NK022(za)001:14810: rnal 'byor gsang bdag gar skyed par //
NK022(za)001:14811: de nyid gnas pa'i gzhal yas khang //
NK022(za)001:14812: byung yang de la gnas mi 'gyur //
NK022(za)001:14813: ji ltar chu yi zla ba ni //
NK022(za)001:14814: sgrib mi mkha' la nyi shar ba //
NK022(za)001:14815: gzugs brnyan dang pa'i chu nang snang //
NK022(za)001:14816: snang yang gzung ba'i rtog pa med //
NK022(za)001:14817: de bzhin gzugs snang phyag rgya yang //
NK022(za)001:14818: sems kyi mkha' la bskur gsal ba //
NK022(za)001:14819: phyag rgya rig 'dzin ngo la snang //
NK022(za)001:14820: de ltar snang yang 'dzin rtog bral //
NK022(za)001:14821: ji ltar char gyi brgyun bzhin du //
NK022(za)001:14822: chu las chu bur rnam par byung //
NK022(za)001:14823: de yang gcig gi rnam pa las //
NK022(za)001:14824: mang po'i rnam grangs du ma 'byung //
NK022(za)001:14825: bsdud cing phyir yang dum bur 'chad //
NK022(za)001:14826: de bzhin rnal 'byor bsgrub pa yi //
NK022(za)001:14828: brag cha drag pa'i mtshan nyid ni //
NK022(za)001:14829: dper na ngos la sgras brkyen pas //
NK022(za)001:14830: ji bzhin sgra ltar brag cha 'byung //
NK022(za)001:14831: byung yang sgra thos dmigs pa med //
NK022(za)001:14832: de bzhin sngags tshig bzlas pa'i sgra //
NK022(za)001:14833: dper na med pa yod brtags pa'i //
NK022(za)001:14834: mtshan ma ma bsten stong pa'i sgra //
NK022(za)001:14835: brjod pa tsam du bstan par zad //
NK022(za)001:14836: ji ltar sgyu ma'i mtshan nyid ni //
NK022(za)001:14837: skyes bu dag gi brtsol ba las //
NK022(za)001:14838: sman dang sngags kyi sbyor ba las //
NK022(za)001:14839: dbang po yid 'phrog cir snang yang //
NK022(za)001:14841: de ltar bsgrub pa'i mtshan nyid kyang //
NK022(za)001:14842: yig 'bru rdzas kyi sbyor ba las //
NK022(za)001:14843: grub par snang yang rang bzhin med //
NK022(za)001:14844: ji ltar 'gal me'i rang bzhin ni //
NK022(za)001:14845: gang dag lag na 'gal me thogs //
NK022(za)001:14846: skor na 'khor lo'i rgyun ltar snang //
NK022(za)001:14847: de la 'khor lo'i rang bzhin med //
NK022(za)001:14848: de bzhin sngags kyi cho 'phrul yang //
NK022(za)001:14849: mi mnyam mnyam pa'i rang bzhin las //
NK022(za)001:14850: ji ltar dmigs pa bzhin 'byung ste //
NK022(za)001:14852: 'khrul ba snang ba'i rang bzhin ni //
NK022(za)001:14853: spros bral dngos po stong pa las //
NK022(za)001:14854: srog dang gshed can byed pa po //
NK022(za)001:14855: sems can pa la sogs par snang //
NK022(za)001:14856: mig nad ngo la rdzas snang ltar //
NK022(za)001:14857: 'khrul pa kho nar snang bar zad //
NK022(za)001:14858: de bzhin sngags kyi lta ba yang //
NK022(za)001:14860: snang ba med pa'i rang bzhin la //
NK022(za)001:14861: 'khrul pa sna tshogs snang bar zad //
NK022(za)001:14862: rnal 'byor can gyis de ltar lta //
NK022(za)001:14863: dper na rmi lam rang bzhin ni //
NK022(za)001:14864: skyes bu gnyid kyi dbang gyur pa //
NK022(za)001:14865: thang cig skad cig yud tsam dang //
NK022(za)001:14866: lo la sogs pa de nyid du //
NK022(za)001:14867: bde dang sdug bsngal de bzhin myong //
NK022(za)001:14868: sangs na ci yang mi dmigs ltar //
NK022(za)001:14869: de bzhin sngags kyi spyod pa dag /
NK022(za)001:14870: stong pa nyid kyi rang bzhin pas //
NK022(za)001:14871: spyod pa'i rnam pa cir yang snang //
NK022(za)001:14872: brtags na dmigs pa kun dang bral //
NK022(za)001:14873: gang gis a h'u la sogs pa'i //
NK022(za)001:14874: rgyu yi yi ge thams cad kun //
NK022(za)001:14875: mtshan ma nyid du de brtags na //
NK022(za)001:14876: tsan+da sbrul gdug la sogs par //
NK022(za)001:14877: ltung 'gyur rtog pa'i gags chen yin //
NK022(za)001:14878: ting 'dzin rtog pa thams cad kun //
NK022(za)001:14879: mtshan ma nyid du brtags 'gyur na //
NK022(za)001:14880: ci la'ang rtog cing chags pa yi //
NK022(za)001:14882: bde gshegs rgyal ba bsgom bzlos pa //
NK022(za)001:14883: cho 'phrul khro tshul ston pa ltar //
NK022(za)001:14884: mtshan ma nyid du der kho na //
NK022(za)001:14885: las kyi srin po'i rig 'dzin yin //
NK022(za)001:14886: rgyan dang cha lugs thams cad kun //
NK022(za)001:14887: mtshan ma nyid du brtags gyur na //
NK022(za)001:14888: bram ze mi sdug lus rig 'dzin //
NK022(za)001:14890: bder gshegs mnyes bya'i las rnams la //
NK022(za)001:14891: yan lag tshig tu ma dag na //
NK022(za)001:14892: nyes byas las kyi rgyun dpe ni //
NK022(za)001:14893: gang gi dus rnams thams cad du //
NK022(za)001:14894: dbang po yan lag ma tshang zhing //
NK022(za)001:14895: dran pa'i snying po nyams par 'gyur //
NK022(za)001:14896: khrag la sogs pa'i rdzas chen lnga //
NK022(za)001:14897: de nyid dngos po der brtags na //
NK022(za)001:14898: 'byung po khrag ni dri snom pa'i //
NK022(za)001:14899: lus len rigs ni 'dzin pa yin //
NK022(za)001:14900: ma bdun rngam pa'i cha lugs su //
NK022(za)001:14901: gang zhig rtog pa der go na //
NK022(za)001:14902: srin po mi sdug sha za mor //
NK022(za)001:14903: lang ka'i yul du de dag 'khor //
NK022(za)001:14904: mtshan mi bla thabs mgo brnyan can //
NK022(za)001:14905: de brtsan der bzung dmigs pas ni //
NK022(za)001:14906: sho gam gnas kyi gcan chen rigs //
NK022(za)001:14908: las kyi dbang btsan bran mo'i tshogs //
NK022(za)001:14909: de 'dra nyid du der brtags na //
NK022(za)001:14910: gnod sbyin chen po'i tshogs su 'gyur //
NK022(za)001:14911: gzhan gyi tshe la 'tshe ba yin //
NK022(za)001:14913: khur du bshal ba'i gdos yin phyir //
NK022(za)001:14914: thams cad rang rig snang ba'i sku //
NK022(za)001:14915: sna tshogs snang la ngo bo med //
NK022(za)001:14916: tshig gis brjod par mi nus pa'i //
NK022(za)001:14917: rang bzhin gser ltar rtogs par bya'o //
NK022(za)001:14918: de ltar goms pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK022(za)001:14919: drod ni g.yo thob bstan pa dang //
NK022(za)001:14920: rtags ni 'byung dang brtan pa dang //
NK022(za)001:14921: cho 'phrul byung dang rdzogs pa dang //
NK022(za)001:14922: rig pa phra mo thams cad gsal //
NK022(za)001:14923: tha ma rang byung nyid kyis rdzogs //
NK022(za)001:14924: dper na mun pa sangs ba dang //
NK022(za)001:14925: snang ba 'byung dang nam mkha' dang //
NK022(za)001:14926: kun tu mthong dang thams cad gsal //
NK022(za)001:14927: de ltar shes pa'i mthu yis ni //
NK022(za)001:14928: bag chags mun pa kun gsal te //
NK022(za)001:14929: ji ltar rlung gis sprin chags ltar //
NK022(za)001:14930: skad cig tsam gyi ting 'dzin gyis //
NK022(za)001:14931: sgrib pa'i phung po phyag par 'gyur //
NK022(za)001:14932: ji ltar mar me mun bsal na //
NK022(za)001:14933: mun nyid snang bar 'gyur ba bzhin //
NK022(za)001:14934: skad cig ma yi don rig pas //
NK022(za)001:14935: sngon nas bsags pa'i mun pa sel //
NK022(za)001:14936: rnal 'byor don la sbyor ba'i tshe //
NK022(za)001:14937: spyod pa las kyi khyad par gyis //
NK022(za)001:14938: khams dang sa ni gar 'gro ba //
NK022(za)001:14939: mdo don tshul lngas lung bstan to //
NK022(za)001:14940: 'dis ni gdon mi za ba dang //
NK022(za)001:14941: ma nges snyoms zhugs the tshom med //
NK022(za)001:14942: rnam smin phung po ma nor bar //
NK022(za)001:14944: de tshe yang dag mngon sangs rgyas //
NK022(za)001:14945: rdzogs pa'i spyir chibs mthar thug 'gyur //
NK022(za)001:14946: las 'phro yid ches bstan pa dang //
NK022(za)001:14947: rmongs pa gang zhig the tshom skye //
NK022(za)001:14948: rgyu 'bras bka' la khyad med bsnyam //
NK022(za)001:14950: dus la re shig sbyong ba dang //
NK022(za)001:14951: 'dir na de ltar brtson ldan pa //
NK022(za)001:14952: las dang dus la rag ma lus //
NK022(za)001:14954: ji ltar 'khor lo ngag mchu yi //
NK022(za)001:14955: tshul gyis brgyud las 'di bsdus pa //
NK022(za)001:14956: rnal 'byor lnga dang bcu yis mun bsal yang dag sa non nas /
NK022(za)001:14957: bka' las 'gal byed gsum sogs rtsar bcad stan pa'ang mi nub cing /
NK022(za)001:14958: mtha' yas 'gro ba thar cing gshog thag yin pa'ang bde thob shog /
NK022(za)001:14959: tha tshigs lnga la mi gnas shing //
NK022(za)001:14960: dgra bzhi dbang du gyur pa dag /
NK022(za)001:14961: sgo dgu'i sa bon 'debs byed pa'i //
NK022(za)001:14962: g.yo can rnams dang ma 'phrad cig /
NK022(za)001:14963: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor bsgrub pa'i thabs kyi las rtsar phreng rdzogs so //
NK022(za)001:14965: lung gi zhi khro lhag ma dang bcas pa snang //
NK022(za)001:14968: // // h'u gdod nas ma skyes rnam dag chos kyi sku //
NK022(za)001:14969: chos nyid byang chub sems su dbyer med kyang //
NK022(za)001:14970: srid pa srog gis bsdus pa'i 'jig rten pa //
NK022(za)001:14971: log rtog dngos por gol ba'i dbang gis na //
NK022(za)001:14972: sdug bsngal brgyad khri bzhi stong rang las byung //
NK022(za)001:14973: sdug bsngal brgyad dang gsum gyis 'gro ba rnams //
NK022(za)001:14974: rgyu 'bras theg pa gzhan gyis mi 'dul te //
NK022(za)001:14975: gsang sngags gsang chen nges pa'i dus la bab /
NK022(za)001:14977: h'u srid gsum phyi nang snod bcud thams cad nas //
NK022(za)001:14978: snyigs ma lnga dang skye 'gro ma lus kun //
NK022(za)001:14979: thams cad sangs rgyas nyid kyi rang bzhin pas //
NK022(za)001:14980: thabs la mkhas pas 'di ltar brtags shing bsgom //
NK022(za)001:14982: h'u phyogs mtshams steng 'og dngos po cir snang yang //
NK022(za)001:14983: khro bcu yab yum sgom pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK022(za)001:14984: phyogs bcur gnas pa'i bgegs rnams kun bsal nas //
NK022(za)001:14985: dngos grub bar chad ming yang med par shog /
NK022(za)001:14987: h'u sgrib pa rnam gnyis dngos po cir snang yang //
NK022(za)001:14988: yid kyis mngon du bshags pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK022(za)001:14989: sgrib pa ye nas dag pa'i don rtogs nas //
NK022(za)001:14990: sems nyid rang bzhin med pa'i don rtogs shog /
NK022(za)001:14992: h'u srid gsum phyi nang snod bcud thams cad nas //
NK022(za)001:14993: snyigs ma lnga dang skye 'gro thams cad kun //
NK022(za)001:14994: thams cad sangs rgyas nyid kyi rang bzhin pas //
NK022(za)001:14995: thabs la mkhas pas 'di ltar brtags shing bsgom //
NK022(za)001:14997: h'u mthu dang bral ba'i sdug bsngal cir snang yang //
NK022(za)001:14998: bde gshegs byin phab gsal bar rdzogs pa'i mthus //
NK022(za)001:14999: rgyal ba'i sku ru lhun gyis grub nas kyang //
NK022(za)001:15000: thams cad byin rlabs mthu nyid lhun grub shog /
NK022(za)001:15002: h'u bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi'i nad rnams cir snang yang //
NK022(za)001:15003: bdud rtsi sman mchog bsgrubs shing mchod pa'i mthus //
NK022(za)001:15004: yun du glags lta'i gnod pa kun bsal nas //
NK022(za)001:15005: skye 'chi med par lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK022(za)001:15007: h'u brgyad khri bzhi stong gdon rnams cir snang yang //
NK022(za)001:15008: tshogs dang gtor mas mchod pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK022(za)001:15009: 'phral du skabs tshol gnod pa kun bsal nas //
NK022(za)001:15010: 'pho 'gyur med pa lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK022(za)001:15012: h'u zhen cing chags pa'i dngos po cir snang yang //
NK022(za)001:15013: khams gsum khrag gi rgya mtshos mchod pa'i mthus //
NK022(za)001:15014: dug lnga ma lus brtsad nas dag gyur nas //
NK022(za)001:15015: gnyis med mchod pa lhun gyis grub par mdzod //
NK022(za)001:15017: h'u thun mong dngos po rdzas kyi cir snang yang //
NK022(za)001:15018: mchod pa byin gyis brlabs pa'i nus mthu yis //
NK022(za)001:15019: 'dod pa'i yon tan mngon du rdzogs gyur nas //
NK022(za)001:15020: dus gsum bde gshegs ma lus mchod par shog /
NK022(za)001:15022: h'u gnam ri sa brag dngos po cir snang yang //
NK022(za)001:15023: de bzhin nyid kyi ting 'dzin sgom pa'i mthus //
NK022(za)001:15024: chos nyid stong pa nyid du don rtogs nas //
NK022(za)001:15025: spros pa med par lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK022(za)001:15027: ma rtogs sems can sdug bsngal cir snang yang //
NK022(za)001:15028: kun tu snang gi ting 'dzin sgom pa'i mthus //
NK022(za)001:15029: chos nyid skye ba med par don rtogs nas //
NK022(za)001:15030: gnyis su med par lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK022(za)001:15032: ma rig sems kyi dngos po cir snang yang //
NK022(za)001:15033: rgyu yi ting 'dzin rtse gcig sgom pa'i mthus //
NK022(za)001:15034: chos nyid byang chub sems kyi don rtogs nas //
NK022(za)001:15035: rang 'byung ye shes lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK022(za)001:15037: 'gro ba'i lus ngag yid gsum cir snang yang //
NK022(za)001:15038: yongs su rdzogs pa'i ting 'dzin sgom pa'i mthus //
NK022(za)001:15039: cho ga rnam pa gsum po'i don rtogs nas //
NK022(za)001:15040: sku gsung thugs su lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK022(za)001:15042: snod kyi 'jig rten dngos po cir snang yang //
NK022(za)001:15043: gzhal yas dbang chen sgoms pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK022(za)001:15044: chos nyid mtha' dbus med pa'i don rtogs nas //
NK022(za)001:15045: 'og min gnas su lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK022(za)001:15047: kha dog sna tshogs dngos po cir snang yang //
NK022(za)001:15048: gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor dngos su bris pa'i mthus //
NK022(za)001:15049: rang bzhin dkyil 'khor chen po'i don rtogs nas //
NK022(za)001:15050: ting 'dzin dkyil 'khor lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK022(za)001:15052: phung po lnga dang 'byung ba cir snang yang //
NK022(za)001:15053: rigs lnga yab yum sgoms pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK022(za)001:15054: yab yum gnyis su med pa'i don rtogs nas //
NK022(za)001:15055: thabs dang shes rab 'du 'bral med par shog /
NK022(za)001:15057: dbang po rnam shes yul dus cir snang yang //
NK022(za)001:15058: sems dpa' sems ma sgoms pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK022(za)001:15059: thams cad lha dang lha mo'i don rtogs nas //
NK022(za)001:15060: rgyal ba'i sras su lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK022(za)001:15062: lus kyi chos bzhi rtag chad cir snang yang //
NK022(za)001:15063: sgo ba yab yum sgoms pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK022(za)001:15064: thams cad khro bo khro mo'i don rtogs nas //
NK022(za)001:15065: tshad med rnam bzhi lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK022(za)001:15067: yid dang chos kyi dngos po cir snang yang //
NK022(za)001:15068: kun bzang yab yum sgoms pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK022(za)001:15069: dbyings dang ye shes gnyis med don rtogs nas //
NK022(za)001:15070: chos sku 'gyur med lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK022(za)001:15072: 'gro ba rigs drug dngos po cir snang yang //
NK022(za)001:15073: thub pa drug tu sgoms pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK022(za)001:15074: rol pa cir yang snang ba'i don rtogs nas //
NK022(za)001:15075: sangs rgyas mdzad pa lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK022(za)001:15077: lus ngag yid gsum dngos po cir snang yang //
NK022(za)001:15078: dbang bskur byin gyis brlabs pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK022(za)001:15079: nyon mongs dngos po ma lus kun byang nas //
NK022(za)001:15080: sku dang ye shes lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK022(za)001:15082: sangs rgyas sems can dngos po cir snang yang //
NK022(za)001:15083: bde gshegs spyan drangs bstims pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK022(za)001:15084: ye nas sangs rgyas yin pa'i don rtogs nas //
NK022(za)001:15085: gnyis su med pa lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK022(za)001:15087: bdag gzhan che chung dngos po cir snang yang //
NK022(za)001:15088: dkyil 'khor lha la phyag 'tshal byin rlabs kyis //
NK022(za)001:15089: ye nas 'dres pa chen po'i don rtogs nas //
NK022(za)001:15090: gnyis su med par lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK022(za)001:15092: 'gro drug sems can sdug bsngal cir snang yang //
NK022(za)001:15093: dam bcas rnam gsum byas pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK022(za)001:15094: bsam pa mtha' ru phyin pa'i don rtogs nas //
NK022(za)001:15095: bdag gzhan gnyis kyi don nyid mthar phyin shog /
NK022(za)001:15097: gzung 'dzin rnam rtog dngos po cir snang yang //
NK022(za)001:15098: phyag rgya'i mchod pa phul ba'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK022(za)001:15099: phyag rgya rnam bzhi lhun gyis grub nas kyang //
NK022(za)001:15100: thams cad phyag rgya chen por lhun grub shog /
NK022(za)001:15102: phyi nang gsang ba'i dngos po cir snang yang //
NK022(za)001:15103: kun tu bzang po'i mchod pa phul ba yis //
NK022(za)001:15104: dngos po thams cad mchod par gyur nas kyang //
NK022(za)001:15105: spyod yul thams cad yongs su dag par shog /
NK022(za)001:15107: bdag gzhan dngos por khyad par cir snang yang //
NK022(za)001:15108: mchod pa rnam lnga phul ba'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK022(za)001:15109: thams cad 'gag pa med pa'i don rtogs nas //
NK022(za)001:15110: 'khor gsum ma lus yongs su dag par shog /
NK022(za)001:15112: bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi'i nad rnams cir snang yang //
NK022(za)001:15113: bdud rtsi sman gyi mchod pa phul ba'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK022(za)001:15114: 'phral du skabs tshol dngos po kun bsal nas //
NK022(za)001:15115: skye shi med par lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK022(za)001:15117: h'u 'dus pa chen po mdo'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK022(za)001:15118: dngos grub rnam gsum gzhung bzhin blangs ba'i mthus //
NK022(za)001:15119: tshe 'dir rdo rje 'chang gi gral thob nas //
NK022(za)001:15120: 'gro don mthar phyin kun kyang de bzhin shog /
NK022(za)001:15122: stong phrag brgyad cu'i bgegs rnams cir snang yang //
NK022(za)001:15123: dam rdzas gtor mas mchod pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK022(za)001:15124: yun du glags lta gnod pa kun bsal nas //
NK022(za)001:15125: 'pho 'gyur med par lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK022(za)001:15127: sems kyi rtogs pa'i dngos po cir snang yang //
NK022(za)001:15128: lhag pa'i ting 'dzin mchod pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK022(za)001:15129: dngos po yo byad lnga ru grub nas kyang //
NK022(za)001:15130: rig pa cir yang snang ba lhun grub shog /
NK022(za)001:15132: chags sdang rnam gnyis dngos po ci snang yang //
NK022(za)001:15133: stan 'gan rnam gnyis mchod pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK022(za)001:15134: spyod yul yongs su dag pa'i don rtogs nas //
NK022(za)001:15135: bdag gzhan don gnyis lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK022(za)001:15137: yul dang dbang po'i dngos po cir snang yang //
NK022(za)001:15138: 'dod yon lnga yi mchod pa phul ba'i mthus //
NK022(za)001:15139: yul sems gnyis su med pa'i don rtogs nas //
NK022(za)001:15140: spyod yul ma lus yongs su dag par shog /
NK022(za)001:15142: nyon mongs sdug bsngal dngos por cir snang yang //
NK022(za)001:15143: glu dang rol mo'i sgra snyan phul ba yis //
NK022(za)001:15144: thams cad theg pa chen po'i sgrar gyur nas //
NK022(za)001:15145: gsang sngags don gnyis kun gyis rtogs par shog /
NK022(za)001:15147: ho phyogs bcu dus gsum bde bar gshegs pa thams cad kyi bdag nyid /
NK022(za)001:15148: bcom ldan 'das dpal rdo rje sems dpa' la sogs pa /
NK022(za)001:15149: rigs lnga rgyal ba rgya mtsho 'khor bsam gyis mi
NK022(za)001:15150: khyab pa dang bcas pa thams cad gsan cing dgongs
NK022(za)001:15151: su gsol lo // bdag cag gis rnal 'byor gyi
NK022(za)001:15152: mchod pa dam pa rig pa'i khyad par phyi nang
NK022(za)001:15153: gsang gsum du sbyar te phul bas /
NK022(za)001:15154: sku gsung thugs kyi brgyud mnyes pa'i chen por gyur cig /
NK022(za)001:15155: de'i byin rlabs kyis mtha' yas pa'i sems can thams
NK022(za)001:15156: cad rdo rje 'chang gi gral thob par gyur cig
NK022(za)001:15157: / bdag cag gi dam tshig nyams pa skongs te dngos grub kyi snod dam par gyur cig /
NK022(za)001:15158: yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi sa ru mngon
NK022(za)001:15159: par rdzogs par sangs rgyas nas 'khor ba ka dag
NK022(za)001:15160: par gyur cig / a la la ho /
NK022(za)001:15161: bdag cag dam tshig 'di la zhes 'dod don gsol ba brjod /
NK022(za)001:15162: h'u yid la bsams pa'i dngos po cir snang yang //
NK022(za)001:15163: smon lam mngon du btab pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK022(za)001:15164: yid la bsams pa lhun gyis grub nas kyang //
NK022(za)001:15165: 'gro don ma lus lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK022(za)001:15167: khams gsum lha'i dkyil 'khor du byas la 'dzab bya'o //
NK022(za)001:15168: rgyu 'bras rtsol ba'i sdug bsngal cir snang yang //
NK022(za)001:15169: bsnyen bsgrub rnam bzhi 'dzab bsnyen byas pa'i mthus //
NK022(za)001:15170: thams cad kun tu bzang po'i don rtogs nas //
NK022(za)001:15171: dngos grub rnam gsum lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK022(za)001:15173: bstod mchod bshags rig pa'i me tog dngos grub blang ba'i rjes su /
NK022(za)001:15174: h'u bdag gzhan che chung dngos po cir snang yang //
NK022(za)001:15175: dkyil 'khor lha bstod phyag 'tshal byin rlabs kyis //
NK022(za)001:15176: ye nas 'dres pa chen po'i don rtogs nas //
NK022(za)001:15177: gnyis su med par lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK022(za)001:15179: 'dod pa lnga'i yon tan cir snang yang //
NK022(za)001:15180: tshogs kyi mchod pa sbyar ba'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK022(za)001:15181: mtha' la zhen pa'i gdug pa kun bral nas //
NK022(za)001:15182: bde ba chen po lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK022(za)001:15188: rjes rnams khro bo dang mthun no //
NK022(za)001:15193: dur khrod rdzas kyi dngos po cir snang yang //
NK022(za)001:15194: 'bar ba'i gzhal yas sgoms pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK022(za)001:15195: rdzas su lta ba'i rtog pa kun bral nas //
NK022(za)001:15196: gnas mchog rab 'byams lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK022(za)001:15198: r+au tra rnam gsum dngos po cir snang yang //
NK022(za)001:15199: he ru dgu ru sgoms pa'i byin gyis brlabs //
NK022(za)001:15200: bdud dang srin po bar chad kun bral nas //
NK022(za)001:15201: ye shes dgu ru lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK022(za)001:15203: khams gsum sa dgu'i dngos po cir snang yang //
NK022(za)001:15204: yum chen dgu ru sgoms pa'i byiin gyis brlabs //
NK022(za)001:15205: ma bdud srin mo'i bar chad kun bsgral nas //
NK022(za)001:15206: thig le dgu ru lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK022(za)001:15208: rnam shes brgyad kyi dngos po cir snang yang //
NK022(za)001:15209: koo'u ri brgyad du sgoms pa'i byin gyis brlabs //
NK022(za)001:15210: yul las mngon par rtog pa'i kun bcom nas //
NK022(za)001:15211: rnam par rtog pa'i 'du shes med par shog /
NK022(za)001:15213: dur khrod brgyad kyi dngos po cir snang yang //
NK022(za)001:15214: phra men brgyad du sgoms pa'i byin gyis brlabs //
NK022(za)001:15215: mtshan mar snang ba'i dngos po kun bral nas //
NK022(za)001:15216: rnam par rtog pa'i bag chags med par shog /
NK022(za)001:15218: phyogs mtshams brgyad kyi dngos po cir snang yang //
NK022(za)001:15219: spor ma brgyad du sgoms pa'i byin gyis brlabs //
NK022(za)001:15220: lha srin sde brgyad bar chod kun bsgral nas //
NK022(za)001:15221: 'jig rten bar chod ming yang med par shog /
NK022(za)001:15223: chu bo bzhi po dngos po cir snang yang //
NK022(za)001:15224: sgo ma bzhi ru sgoms pa'i byin gyis brlabs //
NK022(za)001:15225: tshad med bzhi ru rdzogs pa'i don rtogs nas //
NK022(za)001:15226: phrin las rnams bzhi lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK022(za)001:15228: 'byung ba bzhi yis dngos po cir snang yang //
NK022(za)001:15229: gsang ba'i yum bzhi sgoms pa'i byin gyis brlabs //
NK022(za)001:15230: chos nyid dngas snyigs med pa'i don rtogs nas //
NK022(za)001:15231: thabs dang shes rab 'du 'bral med par shog /
NK022(za)001:15233: sgal tshigs rnams kyi dngos po cir snang yang //
NK022(za)001:15234: dbang phyug nyer brgyad sgoms pa'i byin gyis brlabs //
NK022(za)001:15235: rnam par rtog pa'i bar chod kun bsal nas //
NK022(za)001:15236: bar chod rkyen gyi sdug bsngal med par shog /
NK022(za)001:15238: rus mgo tshigs kyi dngos po cir snang yang //
NK022(za)001:15239: khro bo khro mo sgoms pa'i byin gyis brlabs //
NK022(za)001:15240: khams gsum gdug pa ma lus kun bsgral nas //
NK022(za)001:15241: sangs rgyas phrin las ma lus lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK022(za)001:15243: so dang rus pa'i dngos po cir snang yang //
NK022(za)001:15244: mkha' 'gro so gnyis sgoms pa'i byin gyis brlabs //
NK022(za)001:15245: bar du gcod pa ma lus kun bsgral nas //
NK022(za)001:15246: bsgrub pa'i bar du gcod pa med par shog /
NK022(za)001:15248: rgyu tshigs bco brgyad dngos po cir snang yang //
NK022(za)001:15249: ging chen bco brgyad sgoms pa'i byin gyis brlabs //
NK022(za)001:15250: bsgral ba'i zhing bcu ma lus bsgral nas kyang //
NK022(za)001:15251: sangs rgyas zhing khams ma lus dag par shog /
NK022(za)001:15253: rtsa phran mang po'i dngos po cir snang yang //
NK022(za)001:15254: pho nya sum brgya drug cu sgoms pa'i mthus //
NK022(za)001:15255: dam tshig nyams dang dgra bgegs kun bsgral nas //
NK022(za)001:15256: gnod pa'i bar chod ming yang med par shog /
NK022(za)001:15258: sha khrag rtsa yi dngos po cir snang yang //
NK022(za)001:15259: ma dang sring mor sgoms pa'i byin gyis brlabs //
NK022(za)001:15260: tshe srog gnod pa'i bar chod kun bsal nas //
NK022(za)001:15261: nyin mtshan rtag tu thams cad skyob par shog /
NK022(za)001:15263: bstan theg rtsa spung sgra rtog cir snang yang //
NK022(za)001:15264: rig 'dzin khro tshogs yang sprul sgoms pa'i mthus //
NK022(za)001:15265: yang sprul spro zhing nyid la bsdu //
NK022(za)001:15266: rtog pa gar skyes der bsdud pas //
NK022(za)001:15267: rang 'byung rang grol dkyil 'khor thob par shog /
NK022(za)001:15269: bdag gzhan che chung khyad par cir snang yang //
NK022(za)001:15270: bde gshegs lha la phyag 'tshal byin gyis brlabs //
NK022(za)001:15271: ye nas 'dres pa chen po'i don rtogs nas //
NK022(za)001:15272: gnyis su med par lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK022(za)001:15275: de yan chad dam brgyan dang 'agre'o srin mo'i cha lugs shin tu 'jigs par ston //
NK022(za)001:15276: phyogs mtshams 'dzin pa'i spor ma brgyad rnams la //
NK022(za)001:15277: rnam dag dpal chen sku la 'du 'bral med pa yis //
NK022(za)001:15278: ye shes thugs kyi rgyud sde bzhi rnams la //
NK022(za)001:15279: rnam dag 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor chen po mtha' srung ba'i //
NK022(za)001:15280: dam can dbang phyug nyi shu rtsa brgyad la //
NK022(za)001:15281: rnam dag khams gsum gdug pa ma lus 'dul mdzad pa'i //
NK022(za)001:15282: khro bo khro mo rol pa'i tshogs rnams la //
NK022(za)001:15283: rnam dag phrin las ma lus myur du grub byed pa'i //
NK022(za)001:15284: rdo rje mkha' 'gro sum cu rtsa gnyis la //
NK022(za)001:15285: rnam dag zhing bcu ma lus gtan nas 'dren byed pa'i //
NK022(za)001:15286: rdo rje ka dar ging chen bco brgyad la //
NK022(za)001:15288: ye shes rol pa'i phyag rgya cir snang ba'i //
NK022(za)001:15289: mgyogs ma pho nya sum brgya drug cu la //
NK022(za)001:15290: rnam dag phyi 'khor srung zhing nang 'khor skyong mdzad pa'i //
NK022(za)001:15291: dam can rgya mtsho ma mo'i tshogs rnams la //
NK022(za)001:15292: rnam dag rdo rje 'chang gral rim par non mdzad pa'i //
NK022(za)001:15293: rnal 'byor dbang phyug rig 'dzin tshogs rnams la //
NK022(za)001:15294: rnam dag thugs rje che dgongs dbang dang dngos grub rtsol //
NK022(za)001:15295: bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi'i nad rnams cir snang yang //
NK022(za)001:15296: bdud rtsi sman gyi mchod pa'i byin gyis brlabs //
NK022(za)001:15297: 'phral du skabs tshol gnod pa kun bsal nas //
NK022(za)001:15298: skye shi med pa lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK022(za)001:15300: h'u dur khrod gsang ba mchog gi dkyil 'khor du //
NK022(za)001:15301: dngos grub rnam gsum gzhung bzhin blangs pa'i mthus //
NK022(za)001:15302: tshe 'dir rdo rje 'chang gi gral thob nas //
NK022(za)001:15303: 'gro don mthar phyin kun kyang de bzhin shog /
NK022(za)001:15305: stong phrag brgyad cu'i bgegs rnams cir snang yang //
NK022(za)001:15306: dam rdzas gtor ma phul ba'i byin gyis brlabs //
NK022(za)001:15307: yun du glags lta gnod pa kun bsal nas //
NK022(za)001:15308: 'pho 'gyur med pa lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK022(za)001:15310: chags sdang rnam gnyis dngos po cir snang yang //
NK022(za)001:15311: khams gsum khrag gi rgya mtsho phul ba'i mthus //
NK022(za)001:15312: nyon mongs sems su bsal ba'i don rtogs nas //
NK022(za)001:15313: sems nyid dbye ba med pa'i don rtogs shog /
NK022(za)001:15316: h'u zhen cing chags pa'i dngos po cir snang yang //
NK022(za)001:15317: khams gsum khrag gi rgya mtshos mchod pa'i mthus //
NK022(za)001:15318: dug lnga ma lus brtsad nas dag gyur nas //
NK022(za)001:15319: gnyis med mchod pa lhun gyis grub par mdzod //
NK022(za)001:15321: ho phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi bdag nyid /
NK022(za)001:15322: bcom ldan 'das dpal che mchog he ru ka la sogs pa /
NK022(za)001:15323: he ru ka dgu klong 'bar ba 'khor khro bo
NK022(za)001:15324: khro mo bsam gyis mi khyab pa thams cad gsan
NK022(za)001:15326: bdag can rnal 'byor gyi mchod yon dam pa rig pa'i khyad par /
NK022(za)001:15327: phyi nang gsang ba gsum gyi tshul du phul bas /
NK022(za)001:15328: sku gsung thugs kyi rgyud mnyes pa chen pos khyab par gyur cig /
NK022(za)001:15329: de'i byin rlabs kyis mtha' yas pa'i sems can thams
NK022(za)001:15330: cad rdo rje 'chang gi gral thob par gyur cig
NK022(za)001:15331: / bdag gi dam tshig nyams pa skongs nas dngos grub kyi snod du gyur nas /
NK022(za)001:15332: yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi sar mngon par
NK022(za)001:15333: rdzogs par sangs rgyas nas 'khor ba ka dag par
NK022(za)001:15334: gyur cig / a la la ho /
NK022(za)001:15335: bdag cag dam tshig 'di la zhes brjod /
NK022(za)001:15336: khams gsum lha'i dkyil 'khor du byas la 'dzab bya'o //
NK022(za)001:15337: khro bo la lha mang nyung ma nges te gang la mos pa la bya'o //
NK022(za)001:15338: g+hu ya dz+nya na bo d+hi tsit+ta ma h+aa su ka h'u h'u h'u /
NK022(za)001:15340: rgyu 'bras rtsol ba'i sdug bsngal cir snang yang //
NK022(za)001:15341: bsnyen bsgrub rnam bzhi'i 'dzab bsnyen byas pa'i mthus //
NK022(za)001:15342: thams cad kun tu bzang po'i don rtogs nas //
NK022(za)001:15343: dngos grub rnam gsum lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK022(za)001:15345: 'dod yon lnga yi dngos po cir snang yang //
NK022(za)001:15346: tshogs kyi mchod pa byas pa'i byin gyis brlabs //
