NK022(za)001:15347: mtha' la zhen pa'i gdung ba kun bral nas //
NK022(za)001:15348: bde ba chen po'i longs spyod rdzogs par shog /
NK022(za)001:15350: bdag mchod kun mnyes thams cad drangs //
NK022(za)001:15351: kun la phan pa'i sman yin no //
NK022(za)001:15352: rnal 'byor bdag nyid chen po yis //
NK022(za)001:15353: thams cad bza' zhing btung bar bya'o //
NK022(za)001:15357: lo zur zla keg gnod pa cir snang yang //
NK022(za)001:15358: mkha' 'gro dbang phyug lhag phud mchod pa yis //
NK022(za)001:15359: mo ngan rmi ngan gnod pa kun bsal nas //
NK022(za)001:15360: bar chod rkyen gyi sdug bsngal med par shog /
NK022(za)001:15362: 'jig rten srin mo 'gro drug cir snang yang //
NK022(za)001:15363: gtor ma phri bkod med par bsngosa pa yi //
NK022(za)001:15364: 'jig rten srin mo 'gro drug kun tshim nas //
NK022(za)001:15365: zhing bcu sgrol zhing 'gro don rdzogs par shog /
NK022(za)001:15367: gzung 'dzin rnam gnyis dngos po cir snang yang //
NK022(za)001:15368: lha dang gzhal yas bsdus pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK022(za)001:15369: rtag chad gnyis su snang ba'i mtha' bral nas //
NK022(za)001:15370: snang srid chos kyi sku ru rtogs par shog /
NK022(za)001:15372: rnam rtog chos kyi dngos po cir snang yang //
NK022(za)001:15373: spyod lam rgyun gyi ting 'dzin byin rlabs kyis //
NK022(za)001:15374: bdag nyid yi dam lha ru gyur nas kyang //
NK022(za)001:15375: 'gro don ma lus rdzogs par byed par shog /
NK022(za)001:15380: na mo h'u gis gzi byin bskyed nas ni /
NK022(za)001:15381: rdzogs pa chen po'i klong du la bzlas nas //
NK022(za)001:15382: bskyed rdzogs rnam gsum don nyid rdzogs par 'gyur //
NK022(za)001:15383: skyes bu blo rtsal can gyi spyod yul te //
NK022(za)001:15384: thun mong med par kun bzang nyid kyis gsungs //
NK022(za)001:15391: de ltar lhag ma kun la mar me skya zhig gtad /
NK022(za)001:15392: de nas gom pa bdun 'phags par phrin las rnam bzhi gang byed pa'i man+dala bya /
NK022(za)001:15393: rdo rje dril bu'i dal bya /
NK022(za)001:15394: rdo rje slob dpon gyis rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor ma nyams par bzung /
NK022(za)001:15395: las mkhan la sogs pas sgo ma yan chad sngags kyis gsal btab /
NK022(za)001:15396: de nas lhag ma'i mgron snyan gsan dbab /
NK022(za)001:15398: pad+ma'i phyag rgya bcas la lhag ma dang kha chu'i dam tshig la the ba rnams /
NK022(za)001:15399: sngon gyi thugs dam las ma 'da' bar bsgrub po bdag cag gi sdong grogs la gshegs shig /
NK022(za)001:15400: e a ra li hring hring zhes thal mo lan gsum du brdab bo //
NK022(za)001:15401: lhag ma'i mgron so sor rag ma lus par bsam /
NK022(za)001:15402: ta ki ni'i phyag rgyas spyan drang /
NK022(za)001:15403: bdag nyid dkyil 'khor gyi phyi rim du /
NK022(za)001:15404: khyung gi gshog pas zil gyis mnan rta stong gi byas dbang du bsdu /
NK022(za)001:15408: h'u dpal chen rak+sha he ru ka /
NK022(za)001:15409: koo'u ri'i tshogs kyis bskor ba ni /
NK022(za)001:15410: byang chub sems dpa' brgyad rnams kyis //
NK022(za)001:15411: koo'u ri khro mo brgyad du sprul //
NK022(za)001:15412: srin mo chen mo brgyad rnams btul //
NK022(za)001:15413: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15414: byang chub sa yi snying po yis //
NK022(za)001:15415: khro mo chen mo koo'u rir sprul //
NK022(za)001:15416: srin mo chen mo kem thod btul //
NK022(za)001:15417: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15418: rdo rje'i dam las bro bskyal te //
NK022(za)001:15419: brtan gyi bran du mchis kyis 'tshal //
NK022(za)001:15420: sngon gyi khas blangs dam bcas bzhin //
NK022(za)001:15421: rdo rje dam las ma 'da' bar //
NK022(za)001:15422: las kyi lhag ma 'di long la //
NK022(za)001:15423: khas blangs dam bcas ji bzhin du //
NK022(za)001:15424: bcol ba'i las rnams grub par mdzod //
NK022(za)001:15425: phyi yi dkyil 'khor mtha' srungs shig /
NK022(za)001:15426: byang chub nam mkha'i snying po yis //
NK022(za)001:15427: khro mo chen mo tso'u rir sprul //
NK022(za)001:15428: srin mo chen mo mda' 'phen btul //
NK022(za)001:15429: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15430: byang chub spyan ras gzigs dbang gis //
NK022(za)001:15431: khro mo chen mo pra mor sprul //
NK022(za)001:15432: srin mo chen mo 'dzin byed btul //
NK022(za)001:15433: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15434: byang chub phyag na rdo rje yis //
NK022(za)001:15435: khro mo chen mo be tar sprul //
NK022(za)001:15436: srin mo chen mo nag mo btul //
NK022(za)001:15437: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15438: byang chub byams pa me tri yis //
NK022(za)001:15439: khro mo chen mo pus skar sprul //
NK022(za)001:15440: srin mo nang khrol 'dren ma btul //
NK022(za)001:15441: lha ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15442: byang chub sgrib pa rnam sel gyis //
NK022(za)001:15443: khro mo chen mo kasmara sprul //
NK022(za)001:15444: srin mo chen mo rab 'jigs btul //
NK022(za)001:15445: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15446: byang chub kun tu bzang po yis //
NK022(za)001:15447: khro mo chen mo sma shar sprul //
NK022(za)001:15448: srin mo chen mo sro gcod btul //
NK022(za)001:15449: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15450: byang chub chen po 'jam dpal gyis //
NK022(za)001:15451: khro mo chen mo tsan d+har sprul //
NK022(za)001:15452: srin mo chen mo bsnyen ma btul //
NK022(za)001:15453: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15454: h'u dpal chen rak+sha he ru la //
NK022(za)001:15455: phra men tshogs kyis bskor ba ni //
NK022(za)001:15456: dpal chen he ru'i zhal bzhad pas //
NK022(za)001:15457: mchod pa'i lha mo brgyad rnams kyis //
NK022(za)001:15458: seng ha phra men brgyad du sprul //
NK022(za)001:15459: srin mo mgo brnyan brgyad rnams btul //
NK022(za)001:15460: shar phyogs lha mo la s+ye mas //
NK022(za)001:15461: phra men chen mo seng mgor sprul //
NK022(za)001:15462: srin mo 'jigs byed seng mgo btul //
NK022(za)001:15463: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15464: rdo rje brtan gyi bro bskyal te //
NK022(za)001:15465: brtan gyi bran du mchis kyis 'tshal //
NK022(za)001:15466: sngon gyi khas blangs dam bcas bzhin //
NK022(za)001:15467: rdo rje dam las ma 'da' bar //
NK022(za)001:15468: las kyi lhag ma 'di long la //
NK022(za)001:15469: khas blangs dam bcas ji bzhin du //
NK022(za)001:15470: bcol ba'i las rnams grub par mdzod //
NK022(za)001:15471: phyi yi dkyil 'khor mtha' srungs shig /
NK022(za)001:15472: lho phyogs lha mo ma le mas //
NK022(za)001:15473: phra men chen mo stag mgor sprul //
NK022(za)001:15474: srin mo za byed stag mgo btul //
NK022(za)001:15475: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15476: nub phyogs lha mo g+hir rti mas //
NK022(za)001:15477: phra men chen mo wa mgor sprul //
NK022(za)001:15478: srin mo len byed wa mgo btul //
NK022(za)001:15479: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15480: byang phyogs lha mo nir ti mas //
NK022(za)001:15481: phra men chen mo spyang mgor sprul //
NK022(za)001:15482: srin mo ra ro khyi mgo btul //
NK022(za)001:15483: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15484: shar lho lha mo d+hup+pe mas //
NK022(za)001:15485: phra men bya rgod mgo ru sprul //
NK022(za)001:15486: srin mo bya rgod mgo can btul //
NK022(za)001:15487: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15488: lho nub lha mo me tog mas //
NK022(za)001:15489: phra men kang ka'i mgo ru sprul //
NK022(za)001:15490: srin mo rkang za rkang mgo btul //
NK022(za)001:15491: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15492: nub byang lha mo mar me mas //
NK022(za)001:15493: phra men bya rog can du sprul //
NK022(za)001:15494: srin mo bya rog mgo can btul //
NK022(za)001:15495: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15496: byang shar lha mo dri chab mas //
NK022(za)001:15497: phra men hu lu mu kar sprul //
NK022(za)001:15498: srin mo rku byed 'ug mgo btul //
NK022(za)001:15499: lhag ma byin nas rdo rje'i dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15500: h'u bcom ldan dpal chen rak+sha he ru la //
NK022(za)001:15501: sgo ma tshogs kyis bskor ba ni //
NK022(za)001:15502: tshad med sgo ma bzhi rnams kyis //
NK022(za)001:15503: rta gdong sgo ma bzhi ru sprul //
NK022(za)001:15504: shar phyogs byams pa lcags kyu mas //
NK022(za)001:15505: sgo ma rta gdong lcags kyur sprul //
NK022(za)001:15506: srin mo rta yi mgo can btul //
NK022(za)001:15507: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15508: lho phyogs snying rje zhags pa mas //
NK022(za)001:15509: sgo ma phag mgo zhags par sprul //
NK022(za)001:15510: srin mo phag gi mgo can btul //
NK022(za)001:15511: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15512: nub phyogs dga' ba lcags sgrog mas //
NK022(za)001:15513: sgo ma dred gdong lcags sgrogs sprul //
NK022(za)001:15514: srin mo dred kyi mgo can btul //
NK022(za)001:15515: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15516: byang phyogs btang snyoms dril bu mas //
NK022(za)001:15517: sgo ma chen mo spyang mgor sprul //
NK022(za)001:15518: srin mo spyang ku'i mgo can btul //
NK022(za)001:15519: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15520: h'u dpal chen rak+sha he ru la //
NK022(za)001:15521: spor ma'i tshogs kyis bskor ba ni //
NK022(za)001:15522: dpal chen thugs kyi sbyor ba las //
NK022(za)001:15523: thub drug yid chos brgyad po yis //
NK022(za)001:15524: spor ma chen mo brgyad du sprul //
NK022(za)001:15525: phyogs skyong brgyad kyi bu mo btul //
NK022(za)001:15526: kun tu bzang pos gnas 'gyur ba //
NK022(za)001:15527: 'bar ma nyi zer zhags par sprul //
NK022(za)001:15528: spor ma nyi zer zhags pa btul //
NK022(za)001:15529: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15530: yi dwags thub pa gnas 'gyur ba //
NK022(za)001:15532: spor ma chen mo glog phreng btul //
NK022(za)001:15533: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15534: mi yis thub pa gnas 'gyur ba //
NK022(za)001:15536: spor ma gtum mo mdung thung btul //
NK022(za)001:15537: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15538: dmyal ba'i thub pa gnas 'gyur ba //
NK022(za)001:15539: 'bar ma gshin rje ral gri sprul //
NK022(za)001:15540: spor ma gshin rje ral gri btul //
NK022(za)001:15541: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15542: kun tu bzang mo gnas 'gyur ba //
NK022(za)001:15544: spor ma rdo rje dril 'khrol btul //
NK022(za)001:15545: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15546: lha min thub pa gnas 'gyur ba //
NK022(za)001:15547: 'bar ma skar mda' gdong du sprul //
NK022(za)001:15548: spor ma thog 'bebs skar mda' btul //
NK022(za)001:15549: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15550: byol song thub pa gnas 'gyur ba //
NK022(za)001:15552: spor ma ban glang sna tshogs btul //
NK022(za)001:15553: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15554: lha yi thub pa gnas 'gyur ba //
NK022(za)001:15555: 'bar ma khyung thogs ma ru sprul //
NK022(za)001:15556: spor ma gnod sbyin khyung thogs btul //
NK022(za)001:15557: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15558: h'u dpal chen rak+sha he ru la //
NK022(za)001:15559: gsang ba'i yum bzhis bskor ba ni //
NK022(za)001:15560: dpal chen thugs kyi sbyor ba las //
NK022(za)001:15561: yi ge h'u bzhi sprul byas nas //
NK022(za)001:15562: de las gsang ba'i yum bzhir sprul //
NK022(za)001:15563: de bzhis sring mo bzhi btul te //
NK022(za)001:15564: shar phyogs bde ba za byad mas //
NK022(za)001:15565: srin mo za byed khrag 'thung btul //
NK022(za)001:15566: lho phyogs bde ba rmongs byed mas //
NK022(za)001:15567: srin mo chen mo rus 'cha' btul //
NK022(za)001:15568: nub phyogs bde ba rgyas 'debs mas //
NK022(za)001:15569: srin mo dur khrod re rkun btul //
NK022(za)001:15570: byang phyogs bde ba tshe 'phel mas //
NK022(za)001:15571: srin mo chen mo dur khrod btul //
NK022(za)001:15572: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15573: h'u dpal chen rak+sha he ru la //
NK022(za)001:15574: dbang phyug tshogs kyi bskor ba ni //
NK022(za)001:15575: dpal chen thugs kyi sbyor ba las //
NK022(za)001:15576: tshangs pa la sogs ye shes kyi //
NK022(za)001:15577: dbang mo nyi shu rtsa brgyad kyis //
NK022(za)001:15578: las kyi dbang mo mgo brnyan tshogs //
NK022(za)001:15579: 'jig rten rnams kyi sring mo ste //
NK022(za)001:15580: lag na glo snying nang khrol thogs //
NK022(za)001:15581: nyi shu rtsa brgyad tshogs su sprul //
NK022(za)001:15582: rgyu skar nyi shu rtsa brgyad la //
NK022(za)001:15583: 'gal byed gnod pa'i tshogs rnams btul //
NK022(za)001:15584: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15585: rdo rje brtan gyi bro bskyal te //
NK022(za)001:15586: gtan gyi bran bcas ji bzhin du //
NK022(za)001:15587: sngon gyi khas blangs dam bcas bzhin //
NK022(za)001:15588: rdo rje'i dam las ma 'da' bar //
NK022(za)001:15589: las kyi lhag ma 'di long la //
NK022(za)001:15590: khas blangs dam bcas ji bzhin du //
NK022(za)001:15591: bcol ba'i las rnams grub par mdzod //
NK022(za)001:15592: phyi yi dkyil 'khor mtha' srungs shig /
NK022(za)001:15593: h'u dpal chen rak+sha he ru la //
NK022(za)001:15594: mkha' 'gro tshogs kyis bskor ba ni //
NK022(za)001:15595: dpal chen sku yi 'od zer las //
NK022(za)001:15596: sems dpa' sum cu rtsa gnyis kyis //
NK022(za)001:15597: mkha' 'gro sum cu rtsa gnyis sprul //
NK022(za)001:15598: srin mo sum cu rtsa gnyis btul //
NK022(za)001:15599: sems dpa' rdo rje sems dpa' yis //
NK022(za)001:15600: mkha' 'gro dga' byed ma ru sprul //
NK022(za)001:15601: srin mo chen mo dga' byed btul //
NK022(za)001:15602: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15603: sems dpa' rdo rje rgyal po yis //
NK022(za)001:15605: srin mo rgyu ma 'dren ma btul //
NK022(za)001:15606: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15607: sems dpa' rdo rje chags pa yis //
NK022(za)001:15608: mkha' 'gro spor byed ma ru sprul //
NK022(za)001:15609: srin mo spor ma chen mo brtul //
NK022(za)001:15610: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15611: sems dpa' rdo rje legs pa yis //
NK022(za)001:15612: mkha' 'gro gsod byed ma ru sprul //
NK022(za)001:15613: srin mo chen mo gsod byed btul //
NK022(za)001:15614: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15615: sems dpa' rdo rje rin chen gyis //
NK022(za)001:15617: srin mo chen mo 'bar ma btul //
NK022(za)001:15618: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15619: sems dpa' rdo rje nyi ma yis //
NK022(za)001:15620: mkha' 'gro gzi brjid ma ru sprul //
NK022(za)001:15621: srin mo chen mo gzi brjid btul //
NK022(za)001:15622: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15623: sems dpa' rdo rje rgyal mtshan gyis //
NK022(za)001:15624: mkha' 'gro bdud bzhi rgyal byed sprul //
NK022(za)001:15625: srin mo rgyal byed dbang ldan btul //
NK022(za)001:15626: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15627: sems dpa' rdo rje bzhad pa yis //
NK022(za)001:15629: srin mo chen mo 'joms ma btul //
NK022(za)001:15630: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15631: sems dpa' chen mo rdo rje yis //
NK022(za)001:15632: mkha' 'gro chags byed ma ru sprul //
NK022(za)001:15633: srin mo chen mo chags ma btul //
NK022(za)001:15634: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15635: sems dpa' rdo rje rnon po yis //
NK022(za)001:15636: mkha' 'gro chags bral ma ru sprul //
NK022(za)001:15637: srin mo chen mo chags bral btul //
NK022(za)001:15638: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15639: sems dpa' rdo rje 'khor lo yis //
NK022(za)001:15641: srin mo chen mo 'khor lo btul //
NK022(za)001:15642: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15643: sems dpa' rdo rje smra ba yis //
NK022(za)001:15645: srin mo chen mo rgyas ma btul //
NK022(za)001:15646: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15647: sems dpa' rdo rje sna tshogs kyis //
NK022(za)001:15648: mkha' 'gro sna tshogs gzugs su sprul //
NK022(za)001:15649: srin mo chen mo sna tshogs btul //
NK022(za)001:15650: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15651: sems dpa' rdo rje go cha yis //
NK022(za)001:15652: mkha' 'gro chen mo srung byed sprul //
NK022(za)001:15653: srin mo chen mod srung ba btul //
NK022(za)001:15654: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15655: sems dpa' rdo rje mche ba yis //
NK022(za)001:15656: mkha' 'gro gnod sbyin ma ru sprul //
NK022(za)001:15657: srin mo chen mo gnod sbyin btul //
NK022(za)001:15658: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15659: sems dpa' rdo rje khur tshur gyis //
NK022(za)001:15661: srin mo chen mo 'phrog ma btul //
NK022(za)001:15662: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15663: byang chub dpa' bar 'gro ba yis //
NK022(za)001:15664: mkha' 'gro bya rog gdong du sprul //
NK022(za)001:15665: srin mo chen mo dmigs 'byin btul //
NK022(za)001:15666: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15667: byang chub kun tu bzang po yis //
NK022(za)001:15669: srin mo chen mo 'jigs byed btul //
NK022(za)001:15670: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15671: byang chub zla 'od gzhon nu yis //
NK022(za)001:15673: srin mo chen mo mun mthong btul //
NK022(za)001:15674: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15675: byang chub bzang skyong kun skyong gis //
NK022(za)001:15676: mkha' 'gro bzhad gdong ma ru sprul //
NK022(za)001:15677: srin mo bzhad kyi mgo can btul //
NK022(za)001:15678: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15679: byang chub d+r+wa ba can gyis kyang //
NK022(za)001:15680: mkha' 'gro khyi mgo ma ru sprul //
NK022(za)001:15681: srin mo khyi yi mgo can btul //
NK022(za)001:15682: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15683: byang chub rdo rje snying po yis //
NK022(za)001:15684: mkha' 'gro phag gdong ma ru sprul //
NK022(za)001:15685: srin mo phag gi mgo can btul //
NK022(za)001:15686: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15687: byang chub nam mkha' mdzod kyis kyang //
NK022(za)001:15688: mkha' 'gro rngam mgo ma ru sprul //
NK022(za)001:15689: srin mo rnga mo'i mgo can btul //
NK022(za)001:15690: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15691: byang chub 'od dpag med pa yis //
NK022(za)001:15692: mkha' 'gro bung bu'i mgo ru sprul //
NK022(za)001:15693: srin mo bung bu'i mgo can btul //
NK022(za)001:15694: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15695: byang chub ngan song kun sbyong gis //
NK022(za)001:15696: mkha' 'gro ra mgo ma ru sprul //
NK022(za)001:15697: srin mo ra yis mgo can btul //
NK022(za)001:15698: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15699: byang chub rgyal ba'i ye shes kyis //
NK022(za)001:15700: mkha' 'gro byi ba'i mgo ru sprul //
NK022(za)001:15701: srin mo byi ba'i mgo can btul //
NK022(za)001:15702: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15703: byang chub blo gros mi zad pa //
NK022(za)001:15704: mkha' 'gro kem rus ma ru sprul //
NK022(za)001:15705: srin mo kem rus 'dzin ma btul //
NK022(za)001:15706: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15707: byang chub spobs pa brtsegs pa yis //
NK022(za)001:15708: mkha' 'gro rus phreng can du sprul //
NK022(za)001:15709: srin mo rus pa'i phreng can btul //
NK022(za)001:15710: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15711: byang chub byams pa m+aee tri yis //
NK022(za)001:15712: mkha' 'gro bum sna ma ru sprul //
NK022(za)001:15713: srin mo bum sna'i chung ma btul //
NK022(za)001:15714: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15715: byang chub ngan song kun 'dren gyis //
NK022(za)001:15717: gshin rje rnam 'joms chung ma btul //
NK022(za)001:15718: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15719: byang chub spos kyi glang po yis //
NK022(za)001:15720: mkha' 'gro d+ha sha g+h+ri bar sprul //
NK022(za)001:15721: d+ha sha g+h+ri ba'i chung ma btul //
NK022(za)001:15722: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15723: byang chub don yod grub pa yis //
NK022(za)001:15725: gnod sbyin 'bod sgrogs chung ma btul //
NK022(za)001:15726: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15727: h'u dpal chen rak+sha he ru la //
NK022(za)001:15728: pho nya tshogs kyis bskor ba ni //
NK022(za)001:15729: 'od zer sum brgya drug cu las //
NK022(za)001:15730: pho nya sum brgya drug cur sprul //
NK022(za)001:15731: shar phyogs 'od zer dkar po las //
NK022(za)001:15732: dung gi mi mo drug cu sprul //
NK022(za)001:15733: dri za'i gdon tshogs drug cu btul //
NK022(za)001:15734: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15735: lho phyogs 'od zer mthing kha las //
NK022(za)001:15736: lcags kyi mi mo drug cu sprul //
NK022(za)001:15737: gshin rje'i gdon tshogs drug cu btul //
NK022(za)001:15738: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15739: nub phyogs 'od zer dmar po las //
NK022(za)001:15740: zangs kyi mi mo drug cu sprul //
NK022(za)001:15741: klu yi gdon tshogs drug cu btul //
NK022(za)001:15742: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15743: byang phyogs 'od zer ljang gu las //
NK022(za)001:15744: g.yu yi mi mo drug cu sprul //
NK022(za)001:15745: gnod sbyin gdon tshogs drug cu btul //
NK022(za)001:15746: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15747: steng gi 'od zer ser po las //
NK022(za)001:15748: gser gyi mi mo drug cu sprul //
NK022(za)001:15749: ma bdud gdon tshogs drug cu btul //
NK022(za)001:15750: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15752: bse yi mi mo drug cu sprul //
NK022(za)001:15753: ma mo'i gdon tshogs drug cu btul //
NK022(za)001:15754: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15755: h'u dpal chen rak+sha he ru la //
NK022(za)001:15756: ging chen tshogs kyis bskor ba ni //
NK022(za)001:15757: dpal chen he ru'i zhal bzhad pas //
NK022(za)001:15758: rdo rje ging chen bco brgyad sprul //
NK022(za)001:15759: gdon gyi rgyal po bco brgyad btul //
NK022(za)001:15760: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15761: h'u dpal chen rak+sha he ru la //
NK022(za)001:15762: ma bdun tshogs kyis bskor ba ni //
NK022(za)001:15763: dpal chen thugs kyi sbyor ba yis //
NK022(za)001:15764: yi ge h'u phata sprul pa las //
NK022(za)001:15765: gsang ba'i ma mo bdun du sprul //
NK022(za)001:15766: srin mo chen mo bdun po btul //
NK022(za)001:15767: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15768: h'u dpal chen rak+sha he ru la //
NK022(za)001:15769: sring mo bzhi yis bskor ba ni //
NK022(za)001:15770: gling bzhi dbang bsgyur chen mo la //
NK022(za)001:15771: sring mo chen mo bzhi ru sprul //
NK022(za)001:15772: bgegs kyi rgyal po bzhi po btul //
NK022(za)001:15773: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15774: rdo rje'i dam las bro bskyal te //
NK022(za)001:15775: gtan gyi bran du mchis kyis 'tshal //
NK022(za)001:15776: sngon gyi khas blangs dam bcas bzhin //
NK022(za)001:15777: rdo rje dam las ma 'da' bar //
NK022(za)001:15778: las kyi lhag ma 'di long la //
NK022(za)001:15779: khas blangs dam bcas ji bzhin du //
NK022(za)001:15780: bcol ba'i las rnams grub par mdzod //
NK022(za)001:15781: phyi yi dkyil 'khor mtha' srungs shig /
NK022(za)001:15786: // // bcom ldan rdo rje mi bskyod pas //
NK022(za)001:15787: dpal chen badz+ra he rur sprul //
NK022(za)001:15788: dbus kyi yi dwags dregs pa btul //
NK022(za)001:15789: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15790: bcom ldan rnam par snang mdzad kyis //
NK022(za)001:15791: dpal chen bud+d+ha he rur sprul //
NK022(za)001:15792: shar gyi dri za'i srin po btul //
NK022(za)001:15793: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15794: bcom ldan rin chen 'byung ldan gyis //
NK022(za)001:15795: dpal chen rat+na he rur sprul //
NK022(za)001:15796: lho yi gshin rje'i srin po btul //
NK022(za)001:15797: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15798: bcom ldan snang ba mtha' yas kyis //
NK022(za)001:15799: dpal chen pad+ma he rur sprul //
NK022(za)001:15800: nub kyi klu yi srin po btul //
NK022(za)001:15801: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15802: bcom ldan don yod grub pa yis //
NK022(za)001:15803: dpal chen karma he rur sprul //
NK022(za)001:15804: byang phyogs gnod sbyin srin po btul //
NK022(za)001:15805: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15806: rigs kyi yum chen lnga rnams kyis //
NK022(za)001:15807: khro mo chen mo lnga ru sprul //
NK022(za)001:15808: srin mo chen mo lnga rnams btul //
NK022(za)001:15809: lhag ma byin nas dam la btags //
NK022(za)001:15810: sngon gyi dam las ma g.yel bar //
NK022(za)001:15811: bka' yi gtor ma 'di bzhes la //
NK022(za)001:15812: thugs dam chen po ji bzhin du //
NK022(za)001:15813: rnal 'byor bcol ba'i phrin las mdzod //
NK022(za)001:15814: lung gi lhag ma rdzogs so //
NK022(za)001:15818: gsang sngags 'dus pa chen po'i dbang gi 'dzab kyi las kyi go rims bstan pa la /
NK022(za)001:15821: rig 'dzin gsum gyi dang po zhi ba'i 'dzab bya ba la /
NK022(za)001:15823: dang po 'dzab khang dbye ba ni /
NK022(za)001:15824: tshogs chen 'dus pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi dbus na /
NK022(za)001:15825: rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor chags gang gis mtho
NK022(za)001:15826: ba la rgyal ba sangs rgyas bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis
NK022(za)001:15827: / lha'i ngo bor bkod nas bzhugs pa de gsal btab par bya ste /
NK022(za)001:15828: de yang 'byung ba rim rtseg skyed nas /
NK022(za)001:15830: b+h+ru bi sha b+hi shud d+he /
NK022(za)001:15840: zhes brjod pas gzhal yas khang de nyid /
NK022(za)001:15842: 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi gang ros dang ldan pa /
NK022(za)001:15843: gru chad bzhi la glo 'bur bzhi /
NK022(za)001:15844: lha snam la sgo dang sgo khyud ldan pa /
NK022(za)001:15847: d+r+wa ba d+r+wa phyed la sogs pa mdzes shing /
NK022(za)001:15848: tha ma pad+ma dang rdo rje ra bas yongs su
NK022(za)001:15849: 'khor bar byas pa'i gzhal yas khang yongs su gsal
NK022(za)001:15850: bar byas pa'i dbus su lha'i gtso bo kun bzang
NK022(za)001:15851: yab yum gnyis / h'u h'u h'u badz+ra tsit+ta h'u /
NK022(za)001:15852: a a a badz+ra b+ha tra sa man+ta a /
NK022(za)001:15853: zhes kun bzang yab yum dbus su bskyed /
NK022(za)001:15854: de'i mdun du rdo rje mi bskyod pa yab yum bskyed nas /
NK022(za)001:15855: rgyal ba zhi ba'i lho phyogs thams cad rang rang gi gnas su bskyed nas /
NK022(za)001:15856: de la shu nya tas dbang bskur /
NK022(za)001:15857: sku gsung thugs su byin gyis brlabs la /
NK022(za)001:15858: sa man dzas snyan gsan dbab /
NK022(za)001:15861: ka ya waka tsit+ta sa brtan par bzhugs su gsol /
NK022(za)001:15862: mchod pa gzhan dbul mi dgos /
NK022(za)001:15863: lhag pa'i ting nge 'dzin bsdus pa dang /
NK022(za)001:15864: glu ye shes bsdus pas bstod pa bya ba ni /
NK022(za)001:15866: gnyis pa 'dzab dbul ba dngos la /
NK022(za)001:15868: rtog pa'i gnas gsal gdab cing 'dzab bya ba dang /
NK022(za)001:15869: stod pa bya ba dang gsum gsum ston pa'i thog ma /
NK022(za)001:15871: h'u h'u h'u badz+ra tsit+ta h'u /
NK022(za)001:15872: a a a badz+ra b+ha tra sa man+ta a /
NK022(za)001:15873: zhes pa'i sngags kyis kun bzang yab yum gsal bar byas la /
NK022(za)001:15874: rang gi snying kha nas 'od zer gtso bo'i thugs khar spros pas /
NK022(za)001:15875: gtso bo kun bzang yab yum la phog pas brgyud mnyes /
NK022(za)001:15876: gtso bo'i thugs kha nas 'od zer 'phros pas rang la phog pas /
NK022(za)001:15877: rang gi snod ngan pa'i bag chags dang dri ma kun dag pa la /
NK022(za)001:15878: dbus kyi kun bzang yab yum zhal 'dzum pa dang bcas nas /
NK022(za)001:15879: bdag la mchog thun mong gi dngos grub ster bar bsams la /
NK022(za)001:15881: h'u rig pa gsung gis byin brlabs kyis //
NK022(za)001:15882: ljags kyi rtse la bkram nas ni //
NK022(za)001:15883: du ma nyid du so sor go //
NK022(za)001:15885: seng chen snol ba'i khri stengs nas //
NK022(za)001:15886: rin chen nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan stengs nas //
NK022(za)001:15887: e ma kun bzang rdo rje nyid //
NK022(za)001:15888: rig pa tshul snang sangs rgyas pa //
NK022(za)001:15889: sangs rgyas thams cad bskyed pa'i yab //
NK022(za)001:15891: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus mthing zhal //
NK022(za)001:15892: dang po byang chub mchog gi rgya //
NK022(za)001:15893: bar pa rdo rje dril bu 'dzin //
NK022(za)001:15894: tha ma mnyam bzhag ye shes 'phro //
NK022(za)001:15895: yum gyi dam par mtshan gsol ba //
NK022(za)001:15896: phyi yi yul las sangs rgyas pa //
NK022(za)001:15897: snang srid thams cad chos kyi dbyings //
NK022(za)001:15898: thabs dang shes rab 'brel ba'i yum //
NK022(za)001:15899: bya ba mo dang gnyis su med //
NK022(za)001:15900: bdag gi yi dam lha lags kyis //
NK022(za)001:15901: yi dam lha la mchod par 'bul //
NK022(za)001:15902: bla med sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub stsol //
NK022(za)001:15903: h'u yid shes rang rig ma skyes sems //
NK022(za)001:15904: kun bzang yab kyi rang bzhin la //
NK022(za)001:15905: ting 'dzin byed par dbang bskur nas //
NK022(za)001:15906: ma lus kun gyi byed par shog /
NK022(za)001:15907: chos kyi skye mched ma skyes sems //
NK022(za)001:15908: kun bzang yum gyi rang bzhin la //
NK022(za)001:15909: ting 'dzin bya bar dbang bskur nas //
NK022(za)001:15910: chos rnams kun kyang bya bar shog /
NK022(za)001:15911: h'u h'u h'u badz+ra tsit+ta h'u /
NK022(za)001:15912: a a a badz+ra b+ha tra sa man+ta a /
NK022(za)001:15913: h'u h'u byang chub sems mchog ye shes rdo rje'i thugs //
NK022(za)001:15914: srid gsum dbang bsdud thams cad mkhyen pa'i dpal //
NK022(za)001:15915: bsnyel ba mi mnga' 'gro ba'i skyabs mdzad pa //
NK022(za)001:15916: kun bzang rdo rje yid la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK022(za)001:15917: h'u gdod nas ma byung ma skyes chos kyi dbyings //
NK022(za)001:15918: mi skye mi 'gag dngos po 'dzin dang bral //
NK022(za)001:15919: 'byung byed thams cad bskyed pas yum gyi tshul //
NK022(za)001:15920: bzang mo bya ba mo la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK022(za)001:15921: de nas dbus kyi gtso bo kun bzang yab yum gyi mdun du /
NK022(za)001:15922: rdo rje mi bskyod pa yab yum /
NK022(za)001:15924: mu d+ha du shwa ri zhes rtsa ba'i sngags brjod nas /
NK022(za)001:15925: zhal gsum phyag drug par bskyed la /
NK022(za)001:15929: h'u rig pa gsung gi byin rlabs kyis //
NK022(za)001:15930: ljags kyi rtse la bkram nas ni //
NK022(za)001:15931: du ma nyid du so sor go //
NK022(za)001:15933: seng chen bsnol ba'i khri stengs nas //
NK022(za)001:15934: rin chen nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan stengs nas //
NK022(za)001:15935: ston pa rdo rje sems dpa' gtso //
NK022(za)001:15937: zhal gsum phyag kyang drug pa ste //
NK022(za)001:15938: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus mthing zhal //
NK022(za)001:15939: g.yas pa gsum na snams pa ni //
NK022(za)001:15940: rdo rje 'khor lo rin po che //
NK022(za)001:15941: g.yon pa gsum na snams pa ni //
NK022(za)001:15943: yum gyi dam par mtshan gsol ba //
NK022(za)001:15944: kun tu bzang dang gnyis su med //
NK022(za)001:15945: bdag gi yi dam lha lags kyis //
NK022(za)001:15946: yi dam lha la mchod par 'bul //
NK022(za)001:15947: bla med sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub stsol //
NK022(za)001:15949: h'u rnam shes nam mkha'i ngo bo nyid //
NK022(za)001:15950: sems phyir mtshan nyid ma skyes pas //
NK022(za)001:15951: mi bskyod yab yum rang bzhin las //
NK022(za)001:15952: ting 'dzin thugs su dbang bskur nas //
NK022(za)001:15953: dngos grub las rnams mngon byed shog /
NK022(za)001:15958: chos sku nam mkha' bzhin du dbyer med kyang //
NK022(za)001:15959: gzugs sku stong pa nyid kyi tshul 'dzin cing //
NK022(za)001:15960: yon tan ye shes lnga don thugs chud pa'i //
NK022(za)001:15961: rgyal mchog mi bskyod pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK022(za)001:15962: don dam gnyis med rdo rje dbyings su bsal //
NK022(za)001:15963: rdo rje dbyings phyug yum mchog tshul 'dzin cing //
NK022(za)001:15964: yon tan rnam rtog mi mnga' cha 'dzin cing //
NK022(za)001:15965: rgyal yul kun tu bzang la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK022(za)001:15966: 'dzab phal che na bstod bshags gsung yang /
NK022(za)001:15967: bla ma rtson seng pa bshags pa sngon la byed gsung /
NK022(za)001:15968: 'dzab bshags yin pas 'dzab bgrangs nas byed gsung /
NK022(za)001:15969: rang rig ye shes blo dang mi ldan pas //
NK022(za)001:15970: phung po rgyal ba'i rigs su ma rtogs pas //
NK022(za)001:15971: rnam shes phung po rnam par rtog pa rnams //
NK022(za)001:15972: rdo rje mi bskyod sku la bzod par gsol //
NK022(za)001:15973: de bzhin du 'byung ba nam mkhar rnam par rtog pa sogs sbyar ro //
NK022(za)001:15974: rnam shes dbang po yul dus lus rtog /
NK022(za)001:15975: log rtog nyon mongs sangs rgyas zhe gnyis su'o //
NK022(za)001:15976: de nas shar gyi 'khor lo'i rtsibs la /
NK022(za)001:15977: rnam snang zhal gsum phyag drug par //
NK022(za)001:15980: zhes rtsa ba'i sngags kyis bskyed la /
NK022(za)001:15982: h'u shar phyogs 'khor lo'i rtsibs stengs nas //
NK022(za)001:15983: glang chen snol ba'i khri stengs nas //
NK022(za)001:15984: rin chen nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan stengs nas //
NK022(za)001:15985: bcom ldan rnam par snang mdzad gtso //
NK022(za)001:15987: zhal gsum phyag kyang drug pa ste //
NK022(za)001:15988: g.yas sngo g.yon dmar dbus dkar zhal //
NK022(za)001:15989: g.yas pa gsum na snams pa ni //
NK022(za)001:15990: 'khor lo rdo rje rin po che //
NK022(za)001:15991: g.yon pa gsum na snams pa ni //
NK022(za)001:15992: dril bu pad+ma rgya gram g.yon //
NK022(za)001:15993: yum gyi dam par mtshan gsol ba //
NK022(za)001:15994: sangs rgyas spyan dang gnyis su med //
NK022(za)001:15995: bdag gi yi dam lha lags kyis //
NK022(za)001:15996: yi dam lha la mchod par 'bul //
NK022(za)001:15997: bla med h'u gzugs phung sems phyir mtshan nyid snang
NK022(za)001:15998: mdzad yab yum ting 'dzin sku ru dngos grub las
NK022(za)001:16001: a chos sku nam mkha' gzugs sku me long lta
NK022(za)001:16002: bu'i yon tan chos kyi 'khor lo bskor mdzad pa
NK022(za)001:16003: // rgyal mchog rnam snang mdzad la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK022(za)001:16004: don dam gnyis med rdo rje dbyings su gsal //
NK022(za)001:16005: de bzhin dbyings phyug yum mchog tshul 'dzin cing //
NK022(za)001:16006: yon tan yod med stong pa'i cha 'dzin cing //
NK022(za)001:16007: rgyal yum sangs rgyas spyan la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK022(za)001:16008: lho phyogs kyi 'khor lo'i rtsibs la rin 'byung zhal gsum phyag drug par /
NK022(za)001:16011: zhes rtsa sngags kyis bskyed la /
NK022(za)001:16013: h'u lho phyogs 'khor lo'i rtsibs stengs nas //
NK022(za)001:16014: rta mchog bsnol ba'i khri stengs nas //
NK022(za)001:16015: rin chen nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan stengs nas //
NK022(za)001:16016: bcom ldan rin chen 'byung ldan gtso //
NK022(za)001:16018: zhal gsum phyag kyang drug pa ste /
NK022(za)001:16019: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus ser zhal //
NK022(za)001:16020: g.yas pa gsum na snams pa ni //
NK022(za)001:16021: rin chen 'khor lo rdo rje g.yas //
NK022(za)001:16022: g.yon pa gsum na snams pa ni //
NK022(za)001:16023: dril bu pad+ma rgya gram g.yon //
NK022(za)001:16024: yum gyi dam par mtshan gsol ba //
NK022(za)001:16025: ma m+aa ki dang gnyis su med //
NK022(za)001:16026: bdag gi yi dam lha lags kyis //
NK022(za)001:16027: yi dam lha la mchod par 'bul //
NK022(za)001:16028: bla med sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub stsol //
NK022(za)001:16029: h'u tshor ba chu yi ngo bo nyid //
NK022(za)001:16030: sems phyir 'byung ldan ting 'dzin yon tan du dngos grub sa rat+na d+h+rika /
NK022(za)001:16032: chos sku gzugs sku mnyam pa nyid kyi tshul 'dzin cing //
NK022(za)001:16033: yon tan yid bzhin re ba skong mdzad pa //
NK022(za)001:16034: rgyal mchog rin chen 'byung ldan la dom dam rin
NK022(za)001:16035: chen dbyings phyug yon tan dang bdag med cha 'dzin
NK022(za)001:16036: cing // yon tan yid bzhin re ba skong mdzad pa //
NK022(za)001:16037: rgyal yum ma ma ki la nub phyogs kyi 'khor
NK022(za)001:16038: lo'i rtsibs la snang ba mtha' yas zhal gsum phyag
NK022(za)001:16039: drug par / a ro lika pya ra ga ra ti /
NK022(za)001:16042: h'u nub phyogs 'khor lo'i rma bya snol ba'i rin
NK022(za)001:16043: chen nyi zla bcom ldan snang ba mtha' yas ni
NK022(za)001:16045: zhal gsum g.yas ser g.yon ljang dbus dmar zhal //
NK022(za)001:16046: g.yas pa gsum na pad+ma 'khor lo rin chen g.yas //
NK022(za)001:16047: g.yon pa gsum na dril bu rdo rje rgya gram g.yon //
NK022(za)001:16048: yum gyi dam par na bza' dkar dang gnyis su med //
NK022(za)001:16049: bdag gi yi dam yid dam lha la bla med h'u 'du shes me yi ngo bo nyid //
NK022(za)001:16050: sems phyir mtshan nyid ma skyes pas //
NK022(za)001:16051: mtha' yas yab yum rang bzhin las //
NK022(za)001:16052: ting 'dzin gsum du dbang bskur nas //
NK022(za)001:16053: dngos grub las rnams mngon byed shog /
NK022(za)001:16054: chos sku nam mkha' bzhin du dbyer med kyang //
NK022(za)001:16055: gzugs sku so sor rtoogs pa'i tshul 'dzin cing //
NK022(za)001:16056: yon tan mtha' gnyis skyon gyis ma gos pa'i //
NK022(za)001:16057: rgyal mchog snang mtha' yas la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK022(za)001:16058: don dam gnyis med rdo rje dbyings su gsal //
NK022(za)001:16059: pad+ma dbyings phyug yum mchog tshul 'dzin cing //
NK022(za)001:16060: yon tan spyi dang rang gi cha 'dzin ma //
NK022(za)001:16061: rgyal yum na bza' dkar la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK022(za)001:16062: de nas byang gi 'khor lo la don grub zhal gsum phyag drug par /
NK022(za)001:16065: zhes rtsa sngags kyis bskyed nas /
NK022(za)001:16066: h'u byang phyogs 'khor lo'i rtsibs stengs nas //
NK022(za)001:16067: shang shang snol ba'i khri stengs nas //
NK022(za)001:16068: rin chen nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan stengs nas //
NK022(za)001:16069: bcom ldan don yod grub pa ni //
NK022(za)001:16071: zhal gsum phyag kyang drug pa ste //
NK022(za)001:16072: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus ljang zhal //
NK022(za)001:16073: g.yas pa gsum na snams pa ni //
NK022(za)001:16074: ral gri rdo rje 'khor lo g.yas //
NK022(za)001:16075: g.yon pa gsum na dril bu rin chen pad+ma g.yon //
NK022(za)001:16076: yum gyi dam par dam tshig sgrol dang gnyis su med //
NK022(za)001:16077: bdag gi yi dam yi dam lha la bla med
NK022(za)001:16078: h'u 'du byed rlung gi sems phyir don grub yab
NK022(za)001:16079: yum ting 'dzin phrin las dngos grub las rnams ha
NK022(za)001:16080: prad nya d+h+rika / ta badz+ra ra ti /
NK022(za)001:16081: chos sku gzugs sku bya ba grub pa yi //
NK022(za)001:16082: yon tan phrin las sna tshogs don mdzad pa'i //
NK022(za)001:16083: rgyal mchog don yon grub la don dam gnyis med
NK022(za)001:16084: las kyi dbyings phyug yon tan bdag gzhan don grub
NK022(za)001:16085: cha 'dzin ma // rgyal yum dam tshig sgrol ma phyag 'tshal lo //
NK022(za)001:16087: sa snying yab yum shar lho'i gong ras la //
NK022(za)001:16089: h'u la s+ye sa ma ya stom phata dza /
NK022(za)001:16092: h'u shar lho'i 'khor lo'i gong ras la //
NK022(za)001:16093: nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan stengs na //
NK022(za)001:16094: byang chub sa yi snying po dang //
NK022(za)001:16095: yum chen la s+ye sgeg mo gnyis //
NK022(za)001:16096: gnyis med rol pa'i byin rlabs las //
NK022(za)001:16097: las dang nyon mongs bag chags sbyang du gsol //
NK022(za)001:16098: mig gzugs sems phyir ma skyes pas //
NK022(za)001:16099: sa snying yab yum rang bzhin las //
NK022(za)001:16100: ting 'dzin sems dpa' dbang bsgyur nas //
NK022(za)001:16101: spyod yul yongs su dag byed shog /
NK022(za)001:16103: h'u me long lta bu'i ye shes khyad par las //
NK022(za)001:16104: mtshan dper ldan pa sems dpa'i skur ston cing //
NK022(za)001:16105: yon tan che ba'i yon tan bskyed mdzad pas //
NK022(za)001:16106: rgyal sras sa snying sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK022(za)001:16107: gnyis med chos kyi dbyings kyi khyad par las //
NK022(za)001:16108: mtshan dper ldan pa'i lha mo'i skur ston cing //
NK022(za)001:16109: yon tan rnam rtog zil gyis gnon mdzad ma //
NK022(za)001:16110: la s+ye dkar mo'i sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK022(za)001:16111: lho nub kyi gong ras la nam mkha'i snying po yab yum tra a gar b+ha ya /
NK022(za)001:16112: tra ma l+ye sa ma ya stom phata dza /
NK022(za)001:16113: h'u lho nub 'khor lo'i nyi zla pad+ma'i byang chub nam mkha'i snying po dang //
NK022(za)001:16114: yum chen lha mo ma l+ye gnyis //
NK022(za)001:16115: gnyis med las dang nyon mongs sna dri sems phyir ma skyes pas //
NK022(za)001:16116: nam snying yab yum ting 'dzin sems dpar spyod yul yongs su tra a gar b+ha bsgrang /
NK022(za)001:16117: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes khyad par las //
NK022(za)001:16118: mtshan dper yon tan rnam rtog dra ba gcod mdzad pa //
NK022(za)001:16119: rgyal sras nam snying sku la gnyis med chos kyi
NK022(za)001:16120: dbyings mtshan dper yon tan 'khor ba zil gyis gnon
NK022(za)001:16121: mdzad pa // ma l+ye phreng ba ma la nub
NK022(za)001:16122: byang gi gong ras la spyan ras gzigs yab yum
NK022(za)001:16123: mdzad pa // / h+r+ai ha h'u pad+ma ba da ma /
NK022(za)001:16124: h+r+ai g+h+rir rti ra ho ha phata dza /
NK022(za)001:16126: h'u nub byang 'khor lo'i nyi zla pad+ma'i byang chub spyan ras gzigs dbang dang //
NK022(za)001:16127: yum chen lha mo g+hir rti gnyis //
NK022(za)001:16128: gnyid med las dang nyon mongs lce ro'i sems phyir
NK022(za)001:16129: spyan ras gzigs dbang yab yum ting 'dzin sems dpar
NK022(za)001:16130: spyod yul yongs su h+r+ai ha ho bsgrang /
NK022(za)001:16131: h'u so sor rtog pa'i ye shes mtshan dper yon tan mtha' yi dri mas ma gos pa //
NK022(za)001:16132: rgyal sras spyan ras gzigs gnyis med mtshan dper yon tan gnyis med don gyis tshim mdzad pa //
NK022(za)001:16133: g+hir rti glu dbyangs ma la byang shar gyi gong ras la phyag rdor yab yum /
NK022(za)001:16134: dz+him ku ru pa na hri /
NK022(za)001:16135: a nirti ra ga ya mi phata dza /
NK022(za)001:16137: h'u byang shar 'khor lo'i nyi zla pad+ma'i byang chub phyag na rdo rje dang /
NK022(za)001:16138: yum chen lha mo nirti gnyis //
NK022(za)001:16139: gnyis med las dang nyon mongs rna sgra sems phyir
NK022(za)001:16140: phyag rdor yab yum ting 'dzin spyod yul dz+him ku
NK022(za)001:16142: h'u bya ba grub pa'i ye shes mtshan dper yon tan rnam rtog ma lus 'joms mdzad pa //
NK022(za)001:16143: rgyal sras phyag rdor sku la h'u gnyis med chos
NK022(za)001:16144: kyi mtshan dper yon tan phrin las sna tshogs rdzogs
NK022(za)001:16145: mdzad ma // nirti gar bsgyur ma la de nas phyi'i sems dpa' bzhi'i 'dzab ni /
NK022(za)001:16148: me d+ha ra ni s+w+aa h+aa /
NK022(za)001:16149: dza d+hup+pe pra be sha ya phata dza zhes bskyed /
NK022(za)001:16150: h'u dkyil 'khor shar lho'i gru chad la /
NK022(za)001:16151: nyi zla pad+ma'i byang chub byams pa me tri dang //
NK022(za)001:16152: yum chen lha mo d+hup+pe gnyis //
NK022(za)001:16153: gnyis med rol las dang h'u mig dbang 'das dus ma skyes pas //
NK022(za)001:16154: byams pa yab yum ting 'dzin spyod yul yongs su mee d+ha ra ni bsgrang /
NK022(za)001:16155: h'u ye shes rig pa thugs kyi khyad par las /
NK022(za)001:16156: mtshan dper yon tan rgyal ba'i yon tan rgyas mdzad pa //
NK022(za)001:16157: rgyal sras byams pa'i sku la h'u skye med chos kyi dbyings kyi byin rlabs las //
NK022(za)001:16158: mtshan dper yon tan skye med don nyid ston mdzad pa //
NK022(za)001:16159: lha mo d+hup+pe ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK022(za)001:16160: lho nub kyi gru chad la sgrib sel yab yum th+l+him ni sa ra pa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK022(za)001:16161: h'u push+pe a be sha ya phata dza /
NK022(za)001:16163: nyi zla pad+ma byang chub sgrib pa rnam sel dang //
NK022(za)001:16164: yum chen lha mo push+pe gnyis //
NK022(za)001:16165: gnyis med las dang rna dbang da ltar ma skyes sems //
NK022(za)001:16166: sgrib sel yab yum ting 'dzin spyod yul yongs su th+l+him ni bsgrang /
NK022(za)001:16167: h'u ye shes rig pa thugs kyi byin rlabs las /
NK022(za)001:16168: mtshan dper ldan pa yon tan skye med chos skur ston mdzad pa //
NK022(za)001:16169: rgyal sras sgrib sel sku la h'u skye med chos
NK022(za)001:16170: kyi dbyings kyi mtshan dper yon tan rig pa nyid
NK022(za)001:16172: lha mo push+pe ma la nub byang gi gru chad la kun bzang yab yum /
NK022(za)001:16173: h'u sa ra tsa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK022(za)001:16174: ba di ba su ki ni phata dza zhes pas bskyed la /
NK022(za)001:16175: h'u dkyil 'khor nub byang gru chad la //
NK022(za)001:16176: nyi zla pad+ma'i byang chub kun tu bzang po dang //
NK022(za)001:16177: yum chen lha mo a lo ke /
NK022(za)001:16178: gnyis med las dang rna dbang ma 'ongs ma skyes sems //
NK022(za)001:16179: kun bzang yab yum ting 'dzin spyod yul yongs su h'u sa ra tsa ya bsgrang /
NK022(za)001:16180: h'u ye shes rig pa mtshan dper yon tan 'bras bu'i chos rnams rdzogs mdzad pa //
NK022(za)001:16181: rgyal sras kun tu bzang la h'u skye med mtshan
NK022(za)001:16182: dper yon tan rig pa nyid la gsal mdzad ma
NK022(za)001:16183: // lha mo a lo ke la byang shar gyi gru chad la 'jam dpal yab yum /
NK022(za)001:16184: mu sh+ri a ta ga ya /
NK022(za)001:16185: ho g+han+d+he tsit+ta ho phata dza zhes bskyed la /
NK022(za)001:16186: h'u dkyil 'khor byang shar gru chad la //
NK022(za)001:16187: nyi zla pad+ma'i byang chub 'jam dpal gzhon nu dang //
NK022(za)001:16188: yum chen lha mo g+han+d+he gnyis //
NK022(za)001:16189: gnyis med las dang lce dbang ma nges ma skyes sems //
NK022(za)001:16190: 'jam dpal yab yum ting 'dzin spyod yul h'u ye
NK022(za)001:16191: shes rig pa mtshan dper yon tan 'khor ba'i mtshan
NK022(za)001:16193: rgyal sras 'jam pa'i dpal la h'u skye med chos
NK022(za)001:16194: kyi dbyings mtshan dper yon tan mtha'i skyon rnams dag
NK022(za)001:16195: mdzad ma / lha mo g+han+d+he ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK022(za)001:16196: de nas lha snam la kun bzang yab yum h'u h'u h'u badz+ra tsit+ta h'u /
NK022(za)001:16197: a a a badz+ra b+ha tra sa man+ta a /
NK022(za)001:16199: gzhal yas snam bu'i shar nub nas //
NK022(za)001:16200: rin chen nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan stengs na //
NK022(za)001:16201: bcom ldan kun tu bzang po yab yum gnyis //
NK022(za)001:16202: mnyam bzhag phyag rgya ye shes 'od zer 'phro //
NK022(za)001:16203: mnyam bzhag phyag rgya rdo rje thal mo can //
NK022(za)001:16204: yab yum thabs dang shes rab gnyis su med //
NK022(za)001:16205: bdag gi yi dam bla med yid chos sems phyir ma skyes pa //
NK022(za)001:16206: kun bzang yab yum byed po bya bar dbang bskur nas //
NK022(za)001:16207: byed po bya bar dbang thob shog /
NK022(za)001:16211: chos sku kun bzang sngar rigs bdag kun bzang las /
NK022(za)001:16212: khyad par zhal gcig phyag gnyis mthing kha'o //
NK022(za)001:16213: thub pa drug sgyu 'phrul bla ma nas bshad pa bzhin bskyed de /
NK022(za)001:16214: mu ne krim s+w+aa h+aa man chad brjod la phata dza /
NK022(za)001:16215: h'u gzhal yas snam bu'i shar lho nas //
NK022(za)001:16216: rnam dag pad+ma'i gdan stengs nas //
NK022(za)001:16217: thub chen brgya byin pi wam snams //
NK022(za)001:16218: sku mdog dkar po lha rnams 'dren //
NK022(za)001:16219: thugs rje chen po'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK022(za)001:16221: h'u nyon mongs dregs pa ma skyes sems //
NK022(za)001:16222: lha yi thub pa'i rang bzhin las //
NK022(za)001:16223: ting 'dzin thub par dbang bsgyur nas //
NK022(za)001:16224: gdul bya ma lus 'dren byed shog /
NK022(za)001:16226: h'u mnyam nyid thugs kyi ngang las ma g.yos kyang //
NK022(za)001:16227: nga rgyal 'joms phyir lha yi thub par sprul //
NK022(za)001:16228: thugs rjes ltung ba'i sdug bsngal zhi mdzad pa //
NK022(za)001:16229: bcom ldan lha yi thub la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK022(za)001:16230: byang du lha min gyi thub pa bskyed de //
NK022(za)001:16231: mu ne h'u dru s+w+aa h+aa phata dza /
NK022(za)001:16232: h'u gzhal yas snam bu'i byang phyogs nas //
NK022(za)001:16233: rnam dag pad+ma'i gdan stengs nas //
NK022(za)001:16234: thub pa thag bzangs go cha 'dzin //
NK022(za)001:16235: sku mdog mthing kha lha min 'dren //
NK022(za)001:16236: thugs rje chen po'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK022(za)001:16237: 'thab rtsod sdug bsngal sbyang du gsol //
NK022(za)001:16238: nyon mongs khong khro ma skyes sems //
NK022(za)001:16239: lha min thub pa'i rang bzhin las //
NK022(za)001:16240: ting 'dzin thub par dbang bsgyur nas //
NK022(za)001:16241: gdul bya ma lus 'dren byed shog /
NK022(za)001:16242: mu ne h'u dru s+w+aa h+aa /
NK022(za)001:16243: h'u mnyam nyid thugs kyi ngang las ma g.yos kyang //
NK022(za)001:16244: phrag dog 'dul phyir lha min thub par sprul //
NK022(za)001:16245: thugs rjes khong khro'i sdug bsngal zhi mdzad pa //
NK022(za)001:16246: bcom ldan lha min thub la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK022(za)001:16247: lhor mi'i thub pa bskyed de /
NK022(za)001:16248: mu ne sru s+w+aa h+aa zhes bskyed /
NK022(za)001:16249: h'u gzhal yas snam bu'i lho phyogs nas //
NK022(za)001:16250: rnam dag pad+ma'i gdan stengs nas //
NK022(za)001:16251: thub pa bcom ldan sh+aakya thub //
NK022(za)001:16252: gser shang par bu'i tshul 'dzin cing //
NK022(za)001:16253: sku mdog ser po mi rnams 'dren //
NK022(za)001:16254: thugs rje chen po'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK022(za)001:16255: 'gyur ba'i sdug bsngal sbyang du gsol //
NK022(za)001:16256: nyon mongs 'dod chags ma skyes sems //
NK022(za)001:16257: mi yi thub pa'i rang bzhin las //
NK022(za)001:16258: ting 'dzin thub par dbang bsgyur nas //
NK022(za)001:16259: gdul bya ma lus 'dren byed shog /
NK022(za)001:16261: h'u mnyam nyid thugs kyi ngang las ma g.yos kyang //
NK022(za)001:16262: 'dod chags 'joms phyir mi yi thub par sprul //
NK022(za)001:16263: thugs rjes 'chi 'pho'i du kha zhi mdzad pa //
NK022(za)001:16264: bcom ldan mi yi thub la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK022(za)001:16265: nub byang du byol song gi thub pa bskyed de //
NK022(za)001:16266: mu ne bra s+w+aa h+aa zhes pas bskyed /
NK022(za)001:16267: h'u gzhal yas snam bu'i nub byang nas //
NK022(za)001:16268: rnam dag pad+ma'i gnad stengs nas //
NK022(za)001:16269: thub pa dam stan po ti 'dzin //
NK022(za)001:16270: sku mdog ser nag byol song 'dren //
NK022(za)001:16271: thugs rje thub par dbang bsgyur nas //
NK022(za)001:16272: bkol spyod sdug bsngal sbyang du gsol //
NK022(za)001:16273: nyon mongs gti mug ma skyes sems //
NK022(za)001:16274: byol song thub pa'i rang bzhin las //
NK022(za)001:16275: ting 'dzin thub par dbang bsgyur nas //
NK022(za)001:16276: gdul bya ma lus 'dren byed shog /
NK022(za)001:16277: mu ne bra s+w+aa h+aa zhes bzlas /
NK022(za)001:16278: h'u mnyam nyid gti mug 'joms phyir byol song thub par sprul /
NK022(za)001:16279: thugs rjes glen lkugs sdug bsngal zhi mdzad pa //
NK022(za)001:16280: bcom ldan byol song thub pa la phyag 'tshal //
NK022(za)001:16281: lho nub tu yi dwags thub pa bskyed de //
NK022(za)001:16282: mu ne k+sham swa h+aa phata dza zhes pas bskyed /
NK022(za)001:16283: h'u gzhal yas snam bu'i lho nub nas //
NK022(za)001:16284: rnam dag pad+ma'i thub pa kha 'bar sgrom bu 'dzin //
NK022(za)001:16285: sku mdog dmar nag yi dwags 'dren //
NK022(za)001:16286: thugs rje bkres skom du kha sbyang du gsol //
NK022(za)001:16287: nyon mongs ser sna yi dwags ting 'dzin gdul bya /
NK022(za)001:16288: mu ne k+sham s+w+aa h+aa bzlas /
NK022(za)001:16289: h'u mnyam nyid ser sna 'joms phyir yi dwags thub par sprul //
NK022(za)001:16290: thugs rje bkres skom sdug bsngal zhi mdzad pa //
NK022(za)001:16291: bcom ldan yi dwags thub pa la phyag 'tshal //
NK022(za)001:16293: mu ne ye s+w+aa h+aa phata dza zhes pas dmyal ba'i thub pa bskyed /
NK022(za)001:16294: h'u gzhal yas snam bu'i byang shar nas //
NK022(za)001:16295: rnam dag pad+ma'i gdan stengs nas //
NK022(za)001:16296: thub pa gshin rje chos kyi rgyal //
NK022(za)001:16297: sku mdog dud kha dmyal ba 'dren //
NK022(za)001:16298: thugs rje tsha grang sdug bsngal sbyang du gsol //
NK022(za)001:16299: h'u nyon mongs zhe sdang ma skyes sems //
NK022(za)001:16300: dmyal ba'i thub pa'i rang bzhin las //
NK022(za)001:16301: ting 'dzin thub par dbang bsgyur nas //
NK022(za)001:16302: gdul bya ma lus 'dren byed shog /
NK022(za)001:16304: h'u mnyam nyid thugs kyi ngang las ma g.yos kyang //
NK022(za)001:16305: zhe sdang 'joms phyir dmyal ba'i thub par sprul //
NK022(za)001:16306: thugs rje tsha grang sdug bsngal zhi mdzad pa //
NK022(za)001:16307: bcom ldan dmyal ba'i thub la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK022(za)001:16308: de nas sgo bzhi'i shar sgo'i /
NK022(za)001:16310: h'u ya man ta krita h'u phata /
NK022(za)001:16311: badz+ra d+ha ra ma h+aa kro ti shwa ri dz+wa la ni h'u phata phata dza zhes bskyed la /
NK022(za)001:16312: h'u gzhal yas shar gyi sgo khyud la //
NK022(za)001:16313: rdo rje brag gi khri stengs nas //
NK022(za)001:16314: nyi ma gsal ba'i gdan stengs nas //
NK022(za)001:16315: 'joms pa'i khro rgyal gshin rje gshed //
NK022(za)001:16316: 'gugs pa'i lha mo lcags kyu gnyis //
NK022(za)001:16317: gnyis med rol pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK022(za)001:16318: shar phyogs dri za'i gdon rnams gdul du gsol //
NK022(za)001:16319: reg shes rtag par ma skyes sems //
NK022(za)001:16320: gshin rje gshed yab yum rang bzhin las /
NK022(za)001:16322: gdul bya ma lus thar byed shog /
NK022(za)001:16323: h'u ya man ta krita bsgrang /
NK022(za)001:16324: h'u me long lta bu'i ye shes byin rlabs las //
NK022(za)001:16325: dri za 'dul zhing khro bo'i skur ston cing //
NK022(za)001:16326: thabs kyis lha yi bu yi bdud 'joms pa //
NK022(za)001:16327: khro rgyal gshin rje gshed la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK022(za)001:16328: h'u gnyis med chos kyi dbyings kyi byin rlabs las //
NK022(za)001:16329: 'gro ba 'dul zhing khro mo'i skur ston cing //
NK022(za)001:16330: thabs kyis 'khor ba'i gnas nas 'dren mdzad ma //
NK022(za)001:16331: rdo rje lcags kyu ma la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK022(za)001:16332: lho'i sgor stobs po che yab yum bskyed de //
NK022(za)001:16333: h'u bika nan ta krita h'u phata /
NK022(za)001:16334: rat+na d+ha ra ma h+aa kro ti shwa ri dz+wa la ni h'u phata phata dza /
NK022(za)001:16335: h'u gzhal yas lho yi sgo khyud la //
NK022(za)001:16336: rin chen brag gi khri stengs nas //
NK022(za)001:16337: nyi ma gsal ba'i gdan stengs nas //
NK022(za)001:16338: 'joms pa'i khro rgyal stobs chen dang //
NK022(za)001:16339: 'ching ba'i lha mo zhags pa gnyis //
NK022(za)001:16340: gnyis med rol pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK022(za)001:16341: lho phyogs gshin rje'i gdon rnams gdul du gsol //
NK022(za)001:16342: h'u reg bya chad pa ma skyes sems //
NK022(za)001:16343: stobs chen yab yum rang bzhin las //
NK022(za)001:16345: gdul bya ma lus thar byed shog /
NK022(za)001:16347: h'u mnyam nyid ye shes ngang las ma g.yos kyang //
NK022(za)001:16348: gshin rje 'dul zhing khro bo'i skur ston cing //
NK022(za)001:16349: thabs kyis 'chi bdag bdud rnams 'joms mdzad pa //
NK022(za)001:16350: khro rgyal stobs po che la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK022(za)001:16351: h'u gnyis med chos kyi dbyings kyi byin rlabs las //
NK022(za)001:16352: khro ba 'dul phyir zhags pa ma ru sprul //
NK022(za)001:16353: thabs kyis bla med gnas su 'dren mdzad pa //
NK022(za)001:16354: rdo rje zhags pa ma la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK022(za)001:16355: nub kyi sgor rta mgrin yab yum bskyed de /
NK022(za)001:16356: h'u pad+ma ta krita h'u phata /
NK022(za)001:16357: pad+ma d+ha ra ma h+aa kro ti shwa ri dz+wa la ni h'u phata phata dza /
NK022(za)001:16358: h'u gzhal yas nub kyi sgo khyud la //
NK022(za)001:16359: rdo rje brag gi khri stengs nas //
NK022(za)001:16360: nyi ma gsal ba'i gdan stengs nas //
NK022(za)001:16361: 'joms pa'i khro rgyal rta mgrin dang //
NK022(za)001:16362: sdom byed lha mo lcags sgrog gnyis //
NK022(za)001:16363: gnyis med rol pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK022(za)001:16364: nub phyogs klu yi gdon rnams gdul du gsol //
NK022(za)001:16365: h'u reg byed bdag 'dzin ma skyes sems //
NK022(za)001:16366: rta mgrin yab yum rang bzhin las //
NK022(za)001:16368: gdul bya ma lus thar byed shog /
NK022(za)001:16370: h'u so sor rtog pa'i ye shes byin rlabs las //
NK022(za)001:16371: klu chen 'dul phyir khro bo'i thabs kyis phung po'i bdud rnams 'joms mdzad pa //
NK022(za)001:16372: khro rgyal rta mchog dpal la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK022(za)001:16373: h'u gnyis med chos kyi dbyings kyi byin rlabs las //
NK022(za)001:16374: 'gro ba 'dul phyir rta mgrin rgyal mor sprul //
NK022(za)001:16375: thabs kyis nyon mongs gnas nas 'dren mdzad ma //
NK022(za)001:16376: nyi zla lcags sgrog ma la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK022(za)001:16377: byang gi sgor bdud rtsi 'khyil pa yab yum bskyed de /
NK022(za)001:16378: h'u prad nyan ta krita h'u phata /
NK022(za)001:16379: karma d+ha ra ma h+aa kro ti shwa ri dz+wa la ni h'u phata phata dza zhes bskyed la /
NK022(za)001:16380: h'u gzhal yas byang gi sgo khyud la //
NK022(za)001:16381: rdo rje brag gi khri stengs nas //
NK022(za)001:16382: nyi ma gsal ba'i gdan stengs nas //
NK022(za)001:16384: 'bebs pa'i lha mo dril bu ma //
NK022(za)001:16385: gnyis med rol pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK022(za)001:16386: byang phyogs gnod sbyin gyi gdon tshogs 'dul du gsol /
NK022(za)001:16388: bdud rtsi 'khyil pa yab yum rang bzhin las //
NK022(za)001:16390: gdul bya ma lus thar byed shog /
NK022(za)001:16391: h'u prad nyan ta krita bzlas /
NK022(za)001:16392: h'u bya ba grub pa'i ye shes byin rlabs las /
NK022(za)001:16393: gnod sbyin 'dul phyir khro bo'i skur ston pa //
NK022(za)001:16394: thabs kyis nyon mongs bdud rnams 'joms mdzad pa //
NK022(za)001:16395: khro rgyal bdud rtsi 'khyil la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK022(za)001:16396: h'u gnyis med chos kyi dbyings kyi byin rlabs las //
NK022(za)001:16397: 'gro ba 'dul phyir myos byed ma ru sprul //
NK022(za)001:16398: thabs kyis 'gro ba ma lus don mdzad ma //
NK022(za)001:16399: rdo rje dril bu ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK022(za)001:16400: de nas b+ho d+hi tsit+ta ma h+aa su kha dz+nya na d+har du a /
NK022(za)001:16401: zhes spyir spros la gser gyi sa gzhi brjod nas /
NK022(za)001:16403: de nas phyogs bcu dus bzhis bstod do //
NK022(za)001:16404: ye nas mnyam nyid kyis bshags /
NK022(za)001:16405: ye shes rgyal po'i sngags tshig gis dngos grub bskul /
NK022(za)001:16411: // // rin chen gser gyi sa gzhi brdal ba'i steng //
NK022(za)001:16412: gser btso lta bu'i yi ge b+h+ru //
NK022(za)001:16413: rin chen sna lnga'i rgyan gyis brgyan //
NK022(za)001:16414: rin po che yi gzhal yas khang //
NK022(za)001:16415: seng chen khri dang nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan stengs na //
NK022(za)001:16416: bcom ldan rdo rje mi bskyod la sogs pa'i //
NK022(za)001:16417: rgyal ba bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis bzhugs pa la //
NK022(za)001:16418: bzlas brjod grangs dang dus kyi bsnyen pa 'bul //
NK022(za)001:16419: bla med sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub stsol //
NK022(za)001:16420: a li ka li dz+nya na pany+tsa sa t+wa kro ta mu ne ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK022(za)001:16422: a nu la theg dgu dril ba'i mdo'i sngags /
NK022(za)001:16423: +aahmh'u gu ya dz+nya na bo d+hi tsit+ta ma h+aa su kha h'u h'u h'u /
NK022(za)001:16424: lung chen a nu'i theg pa la //
NK022(za)001:16425: dbyings dang ye shes rnam pa gnyis //
NK022(za)001:16427: 'jug sgo cig char rims kyis so //
NK022(za)001:16429: cig char 'jug pa gang zhe na //
NK022(za)001:16430: lha rnams ma bskyed snying po dran rdzogs //
NK022(za)001:16431: rims kyis 'jug pa gang zhe na //
NK022(za)001:16432: dbyings dang ye shes rims bzhugs nas //
NK022(za)001:16433: rdo rje 'dzin gyi sa la 'bras bu thob //
NK022(za)001:16434: bsrung ba'i dam tshig 'di lta ste //
NK022(za)001:16435: gsang sngags don ston rtag tu bkur bar bya //
NK022(za)001:16436: gsang sngags don dam ston pa'i bla ma la //
NK022(za)001:16438: slob dpon dang ni de bzhin gshegs //
NK022(za)001:16439: khyad med gcig gi ngo bor gnas //
NK022(za)001:16440: mdor bsdus dbyings dang ye shes ni //
NK022(za)001:16441: lung chen a nu'i grub mtha' 'o //
NK022(za)001:16442: man ngag a ti'i dgongs don smon //
NK022(za)001:16446: // // gsang sngags 'dus pa chen po'i zhi ba'i lha rnams kyi 'dzab zin nas /
NK022(za)001:16447: khro bo'i lha tshogs rnams kyi 'dzab bya ste /
NK022(za)001:16448: sngon la 'dzab khang dbye ba ni /
NK022(za)001:16449: b+h+ru spar sa b+h+ru bi sha bi shud+d+he b+han d+ha dz+nya na tsakra sur+ya tsan+t+ra pad+ma e man+dala /
NK022(za)001:16452: r+au tra kro ti ra ba ti ra ba /
NK022(za)001:16453: a kra ma h+aa kro ta sh+ri he ru ka /
NK022(za)001:16454: ka ta ma h+aa kro ti shwa ri h'u /
NK022(za)001:16455: sarba ta th+aa ga ta kro ti shwa ri h'u /
NK022(za)001:16457: rak+sha kro ti shwa ri h'u /
NK022(za)001:16459: b+hud+d+ha kro ti shwa ri h'u /
NK022(za)001:16461: rat+na kro ti shwa ri h'u /
NK022(za)001:16463: pad+ma kro ti shwa ri h'u /
NK022(za)001:16465: karma kro ti shwa ri h'u /
NK022(za)001:16467: rak+sha kro ti shwa ri h'u /
NK022(za)001:16481: steng phyogs khro bo drug cu /
NK022(za)001:16482: pho nya nyis brgya bzhi bcu /
NK022(za)001:16484: rig 'dzin rtsal 'chang rnams rim pas rtsa sngags dang bcas pa bskyed /
NK022(za)001:16485: de dag la ye shes lngas bdag bskur /
NK022(za)001:16486: sku gsung thugs su byin gyis brlabs /
NK022(za)001:16487: sa man dzas snyan gsan dbab /
NK022(za)001:16490: ka ya waka tsit+tasa brtan par byas la /
NK022(za)001:16491: tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor chen po ru //
NK022(za)001:16492: bsgrub dang gdug pa 'dul ba yi //
NK022(za)001:16493: 'bar ba khro bo'i lha tshogs la //
NK022(za)001:16494: sgo gsum gus pas phyag 'tshal lo //
NK022(za)001:16495: 'di ni rgyal bas phyag rgya'i mchod pa dbul /
NK022(za)001:16496: snang srid kun bzang lha mo bzhi snol sman raka gtor gsum sngags kyi dbul /
NK022(za)001:16501: glu ye shes rnams dbyangs dang bcas pa zhi ba ltar rgyas par dbul /
NK022(za)001:16502: rgya mtsho lnga'i smon lam gdab /
NK022(za)001:16503: de nas a kra ma h+aa kro ta sh+ri he ru ka h'u /
NK022(za)001:16504: ka ra ma h+aa kro ti shwa ri h'u phata dza /
NK022(za)001:16505: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK022(za)001:16506: h'u tshogs chen 'dus pa dbang gi dkyil 'khor gyi //
NK022(za)001:16507: 'khor lo 'bar ba dbus kyi lte ba la //
NK022(za)001:16508: bcom ldan che mchog dpal chen he ru ka /
NK022(za)001:16509: ston pa kun tu bzang po gnas gyur pa //
NK022(za)001:16510: rgyal ba khro rgyal kun gyi rje btsan yab //
NK022(za)001:16511: che ba'i nang nas yang che bla na med //
NK022(za)001:16512: che btsan 'gran zla bral ba kun gyi mchog /
NK022(za)001:16513: sku gsung thugs kyi bdag la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK022(za)001:16514: 'bar ba'i dbu ni nyi shu rtsa gcig gis //
NK022(za)001:16515: sa ni nyi shu rtsa gcig rims pas mnan //
NK022(za)001:16516: g.yas g.yon phyag ni bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis na //
NK022(za)001:16517: rgyal ba sangs rgyas bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis bzhugs //
NK022(za)001:16518: zhabs brgyad bgrad pas khro mo'i dbu brgyad bardzisa //
NK022(za)001:16519: nyi ma stong gi 'od zer sku la brjid //
NK022(za)001:16520: dpal gyi chas brgyad dur khrod rgyan rnams rdzogs //
NK022(za)001:16521: che mchog he ru ka la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK022(za)001:16522: kun tu bzang mo'i chos nyid gnas 'gyur pa //
NK022(za)001:16523: dpal 'bar khro mo kun gyi rje btsun yum //
NK022(za)001:16524: shes rab dbyings nas bskur bskyed thugs rjer ldan //
NK022(za)001:16525: khro mo gnam zhal ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK022(za)001:16526: a kra ma h+aa kro ta sh+ri he ru ka h'u /
NK022(za)001:16527: ka ta ma h+aa kro ti shwa ri h'u zhes pa dang /
NK022(za)001:16529: bcom ldan dbang mchog he ru ka /
NK022(za)001:16531: dbu gsum dang por byung ba ni //
NK022(za)001:16532: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus mthing zhal //
NK022(za)001:16533: sku gsung thugs dang ldan pa'i dbu //
NK022(za)001:16534: khams gsum mya ngan 'das pa'i zhal //
NK022(za)001:16535: dbu gsum bar du rngam pa ni //
NK022(za)001:16536: g.yas sngo g.yon ljang dbus mthing zhal //
NK022(za)001:16537: thabs dang shes rab sems kyi dbu //
NK022(za)001:16538: srid gsum dbyings su rdzogs pa'i zhal //
NK022(za)001:16539: dbu gsum thog mar rngam pa ni //
NK022(za)001:16540: g.yas mthing g.yon mthing dbus mthing zhal //
NK022(za)001:16541: lung dang man ngag sems kyi dbu //
NK022(za)001:16542: khams gsum re ba bskong ba'i zhal //
NK022(za)001:16543: bco brgyad phyag rgya rol pa ni //
NK022(za)001:16544: stong pa bco brgyad dbyings su thim //
NK022(za)001:16545: bco brgyad phyag na bsnams pa ni //
NK022(za)001:16546: rdo rje glo snying zhing chung g.yas //
NK022(za)001:16547: bag d+ha zhing chung sti ra g.yon //
NK022(za)001:16548: zhing zhags nyi ma khyung chen g.yas //
NK022(za)001:16549: zhing chen zla ba 'ug pa g.yon //
NK022(za)001:16550: me dang rgya mtsho ga'u g.yas //
NK022(za)001:16551: klu dang rin chen ri rab g.yon //
NK022(za)001:16552: yon tan bco brgyad dbyings su rdzogs //
NK022(za)001:16553: khro rgyal rgyan rnams sku la brjid //
NK022(za)001:16554: rgyud rgyal che mchog he ru ka /
NK022(za)001:16555: dbang mchog sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK022(za)001:16556: sarba ta th+aa ga ta sh+ri he ru ka sarba ta th+aa ga ta kro ti shwa ri h'u /
NK022(za)001:16557: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK022(za)001:16558: h'u dbang gi dkyil 'khor chen po yi //
NK022(za)001:16560: dregs pa snol ba'i gdan stengs su //
NK022(za)001:16561: rdo rje mi bskyod gnas gyur pa //
NK022(za)001:16563: 'jigs byed chen po'i skur bskyed pa //
NK022(za)001:16564: mchod cing byin rlabs gsal bsgrubs pa //
NK022(za)001:16565: badz+ra he ru ka la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK022(za)001:16566: nam mkha' kun bzang gnas 'gyur pa //
NK022(za)001:16567: khro mo dbang phyug skur gsal bas //
NK022(za)001:16568: thabs dang shes rab gnyis su med //
NK022(za)001:16569: badz+ra kro ti shwa ri'i sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK022(za)001:16571: badz+ra kro ti shwa ri h'u /
NK022(za)001:16572: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK022(za)001:16573: h'u dbang gi dkyil 'khor chen po yi //
NK022(za)001:16575: shar phyogs 'khor lo'i rtsibs steng na //
NK022(za)001:16576: dri za bsnol ba'i gdan stengs na //
NK022(za)001:16577: rnam par snang mdzad gnas 'gyur ba //
NK022(za)001:16580: mchod cing bsgrubs te byin rlabs pa //
NK022(za)001:16581: b+hud+d+ha he ru ka la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK022(za)001:16582: sangs rgyas spyan ma gnas 'gyur ba //
NK022(za)001:16583: khro mo dbang phyug skur gsal bas //
NK022(za)001:16584: thabs dang shes rab byang chub sems //
NK022(za)001:16585: spyan drangs mchod cing bsgrubs pa yi //
NK022(za)001:16586: b+hud+d+ha kro ti shwa ri'i sku la phyag 'tshal bstod /
NK022(za)001:16588: b+hud+d+ha kro ti sh+ri shwa ri h'u /
NK022(za)001:16589: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK022(za)001:16590: h'u dbang gi dkyil 'khor chen po yi //
NK022(za)001:16592: lho phyogs 'khor lo'i rtsibs steng na //
NK022(za)001:16593: gshin rje bsnol ba'i gdan stengs na //
NK022(za)001:16597: spyan drangs mchod cing bsgrubs pa'i lha //
NK022(za)001:16598: rat+na he ru ka la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK022(za)001:16599: h'u ma ma ki las gnas gyur pa //
NK022(za)001:16600: 'jigs byed khro mo'i skur byung bas //
NK022(za)001:16601: yab yum thabs dang shes rab las //
NK022(za)001:16602: spyan drangs mchod nas bsnyen bsgrubs pa //
NK022(za)001:16603: rat+na kro ti shwa ri'i sku la phyag 'tshal bstod /
NK022(za)001:16605: rat+na kro ti shwa ri h'u /
NK022(za)001:16606: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK022(za)001:16607: dbang gi dkyil 'khor chen po yi //
NK022(za)001:16609: nub phyogs 'khor lo'i rtsibs steng na //
NK022(za)001:16610: klu dbang bsnol ba'i gdan stengs na //
NK022(za)001:16611: snang ba mtha' yas gnas gyur ba //
NK022(za)001:16613: 'jigs byed dmar nag ral pa can //
NK022(za)001:16614: bsgoms shing mchod de bsgrubs pa las //
NK022(za)001:16615: pad+ma he ru ka la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK022(za)001:16616: na bza' dkar mo gnas 'gyur ba //
NK022(za)001:16617: 'jigs byed khro mo'i skur byung ste //
NK022(za)001:16618: yab yum thabs dang shes rab las //
NK022(za)001:16619: gnyis med byang chub sems bsgrubs pa //
NK022(za)001:16620: pad+ma kro ti shwa ri'i sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK022(za)001:16622: pad+ma kro ti shwa ri h'u /
NK022(za)001:16623: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK022(za)001:16624: h'u dbang gi dkyil 'khor chen po yi //
NK022(za)001:16626: byang phyogs 'khor lo'i rtsibs stengs na //
NK022(za)001:16627: gnod sbyin bsnol ba'i gdan stengs na //
NK022(za)001:16628: don yod grub pa gnas 'gyur ba //
NK022(za)001:16631: gsal bar bskyed cing mchod bsgrubs pa //
NK022(za)001:16632: karma he ru ka la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK022(za)001:16633: dam tshig sgrol ma gnas 'gyur bas //
NK022(za)001:16634: 'jigs byed khro mo'i skur ston pa //
NK022(za)001:16635: lhag pa byang chub sems 'phros pa //
NK022(za)001:16636: yab yum thabs dang shes rab las //
NK022(za)001:16637: karma kro ti shwa ri'i sku la phyag 'tshal bstod /
NK022(za)001:16639: karma kro ti shwa ri h'u /
NK022(za)001:16640: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK022(za)001:16641: h'u dbang gi dkyil 'khor chen po yi //
NK022(za)001:16642: shar lho 'khor lo'i rtsibs steng na //
NK022(za)001:16643: mthu stobs mnga' bdag gnas 'gyur ba //
NK022(za)001:16644: sgrol byed chen po bdud rnams 'joms //
NK022(za)001:16645: bdud dang srin po sgrol la brtson //
NK022(za)001:16646: mthing nag 'jigs pa'i cha lugs can //
NK022(za)001:16647: rak+sha he ru ka la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK022(za)001:16648: lha mo ral gcig gnas 'gyur bas //
NK022(za)001:16649: khro mo yab kyi cha lugs can //
NK022(za)001:16650: yab yum thabs dang shes rab las //
NK022(za)001:16651: rak+sha kro ti shwa ri'i sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK022(za)001:16653: rak+sha kro ti shwa ri h'u /
NK022(za)001:16654: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK022(za)001:16655: h'u dbang gi dkyil 'khor chen po yi //
NK022(za)001:16656: lho nub 'khor lo'i rtsibs steng na //
NK022(za)001:16657: badz+ra sa ma ya las gnas 'gyur ba //
NK022(za)001:16658: dpal chen dam tshig mnga' mdzad pa //
NK022(za)001:16659: ser nag 'jigs pa'i cha lugs can //
NK022(za)001:16660: bskal pa brgyar yang dam tshig lta //
NK022(za)001:16661: sa nu he ru ka la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK022(za)001:16662: yum chen dam tshig gnas 'gyur bas //
NK022(za)001:16663: khro mo dam tshig bya ra mkhan //
NK022(za)001:16664: sangs rgyas sems can 'da' mi byed //
NK022(za)001:16665: dam tshig dbyings su bskul byed ma //
NK022(za)001:16666: sa nu kro ti shwa ri'i sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK022(za)001:16667: sa nu sh+ri he ru ka /
NK022(za)001:16668: sa nu kro ti shwa ri h'u /
NK022(za)001:16669: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK022(za)001:16670: h'u dbang gi dkyil 'khor chen po yi //
NK022(za)001:16671: nub byang 'khor lo'i rtsibs steng na //
NK022(za)001:16672: mkhyen rabs mnga' bdag gnas 'gyur ba //
NK022(za)001:16673: sgrol byed chen po dregs pa 'dul //
NK022(za)001:16674: ljang nag 'jigs pa'i cha lugs can //
NK022(za)001:16675: dus rnams rtag tu gsang ba'i lha //
NK022(za)001:16676: zhe sdang 'khor ba bsgrol la brtson //
NK022(za)001:16677: g+hu ya he ru ka yi sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK022(za)001:16679: khro mo yab kyi cha lugs 'dzin //
NK022(za)001:16680: yab yum thabs dang shes rab las //
NK022(za)001:16681: g+hu ya kro ti shwa ri'i sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK022(za)001:16682: g+hu ya sh+ri he ru ka /
NK022(za)001:16683: g+hu ya kro ti shwa ri h'u /
NK022(za)001:16684: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK022(za)001:16685: h'u dbang gi dkyil 'khor chen po yi //
NK022(za)001:16686: byang shar 'khor lo'i rtsibs stengs na //
NK022(za)001:16687: thugs rje'i mnga' bdag gnas 'gyur ba //
NK022(za)001:16690: gang bsgrub mthu dang dbang stsol ba'i //
NK022(za)001:16691: yak+sha he ru ka yi sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK022(za)001:16693: khro bo dbang phyug kun gyi rje //
NK022(za)001:16694: sprul pa kun gyi yang sprul ma //
NK022(za)001:16695: thabs dang shes rab dbyer med pas //
NK022(za)001:16696: yak+sha kro ti shwa ri'i sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK022(za)001:16698: yak+sha kro ti shwa ri h'u /
NK022(za)001:16699: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK022(za)001:16700: h'u tshogs chen 'dus pa dbang gi dkyil 'khor gyi //
NK022(za)001:16701: 'bar ba'i glo 'bur gru chad bzhi po nas //
NK022(za)001:16702: koo'u ri la sogs khro mo brgyad rnams ni //
NK022(za)001:16703: gdug pa thabs kyis 'dul ba'i drag shul can //
NK022(za)001:16704: sku mdog phyag mtshan sna tshogs cir yang ston //
NK022(za)001:16705: ye shes khro bo brgyad la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK022(za)001:16707: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK022(za)001:16708: zhes khro mo brgyad kyi rtsa sngags dang /
NK022(za)001:16709: ru lu spel gyin bzlas so //
NK022(za)001:16710: h'u tshogs chen 'dus pa dbang gi dkyil 'khor gyi //
NK022(za)001:16711: 'bar ba'i bar khyams dang po gser mdog na //
NK022(za)001:16712: sing ha la sogs phra men brgyad rnams ni //
NK022(za)001:16713: ye shes las la 'gyed pa'i phra men ma //
NK022(za)001:16714: rnam sprul las kyis 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa'i //
NK022(za)001:16715: sing ha phra men brgyad la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK022(za)001:16716: badz+ra sing ha mu ka he /
NK022(za)001:16717: ru lu zhes phra men brgyad kyi rtsa sngags dang ru lu spel la bzlas so //
NK022(za)001:16718: bar khyams sgo bzhi'i shar lho nub byang bzhin //
NK022(za)001:16719: tshad med bzhi yis 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa //
NK022(za)001:16720: rta gdong phag gdong seng gdong spyang gdong bzhi //
NK022(za)001:16721: zhi rgyas dbang drag las la thogs med brtson //
NK022(za)001:16722: rtag chad bdag 'dzin mtshan ma lta las grol //
NK022(za)001:16723: ye shes sgo ma bzhi la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK022(za)001:16724: phata badz+ra ar+ya te dza te nga dza /
NK022(za)001:16725: ru lu zhes sgo ma bzhi'i rtsa sngags dang ru lu spel ba bzlas so //
NK022(za)001:16726: h'u tshogs chen 'dus pa dbang gi dkyil 'khor gyi //
NK022(za)001:16727: 'bar ba'i bar khyams gnyis la mdog dkar nas //
NK022(za)001:16728: chos nyid rnam dag ngang las rang snang ba'i //
NK022(za)001:16729: sna tshogs cir yang 'gyur ba'i sku mnga' zhing //
NK022(za)001:16730: srid gsum zhing du sbyor bas g.yang gzhi gsol //
NK022(za)001:16731: spor ma chen mo brgyad la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK022(za)001:16732: badz+ra a pra ti ar+ya ni tsa dur ta ra phata /
NK022(za)001:16735: bar khyams de yi shar lho nub byang sgor //
NK022(za)001:16736: dges pa bskyed pa'i gsang ba'i yum chen bzhi //
NK022(za)001:16737: gnyis med rol pa'i byin rlabs sna tshogs 'phro //
NK022(za)001:16738: shes rab yum chen bzhi la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK022(za)001:16739: sh+ri badz+ra kha ra mu kha sha ra ya ya na ma /
NK022(za)001:16740: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK022(za)001:16741: sh+ri badz+ra ra ga sha ra ya ya na ma /
NK022(za)001:16742: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK022(za)001:16743: sh+ri badz+ra kha thogs kha pra dza la ya ya na ma /
NK022(za)001:16744: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK022(za)001:16745: sh+ri badz+ra g+han d+ha pra dza la ya ya na ma /
NK022(za)001:16746: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK022(za)001:16747: h'u tshogs chen 'dus pa dbang gi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK022(za)001:16748: 'bar ba'i bar khyams gsum pa mdog dmar na //
NK022(za)001:16749: mi srin la sogs dbang phyug nyi shu brgyad //
NK022(za)001:16750: dregs pa lha chen rnams kyi chung ma ste //
NK022(za)001:16751: dbang drag las la thogs pa med par spyod //
NK022(za)001:16752: dbang phyug nyi shu brgyad la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK022(za)001:16753: b+h+yo ma nu rak+sha si la sogs pa rtsa sngags nyer brgyad dang /
NK022(za)001:16755: h'u tshogs chen 'dus pa dbang gi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK022(za)001:16756: 'bar ba'i bar khyams bzhi pa gser mdog na //
NK022(za)001:16757: nam mkha'i lus can gar yang thogs med cing //
NK022(za)001:16758: 'dod dgur bsgyur ba'i gzugs can 'phrul mo che //
NK022(za)001:16759: ma sring byams pa'i tshul gyis grogs mdzad ma //
NK022(za)001:16760: mkha' 'gro sum cu gnyis la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK022(za)001:16763: h'u tshogs chen 'dus pa dbang gi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK022(za)001:16764: 'bar ba'i bar khyams lnga pa dmar po la //
NK022(za)001:16765: 'jig rten dregs pa 'dul ba'i ma mo'i tshogs //
NK022(za)001:16766: phyi 'khor 'dul zhing nang 'khor skyong mdzad pa //
NK022(za)001:16767: dur khrod ma bdun las kyi sring mo bzhi //
NK022(za)001:16768: bgegs srungs ma mo rnams la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK022(za)001:16770: zhes pa bdun dang ru lu spel la bzlas /
NK022(za)001:16771: dun ting b+h+yo zhes pa bzhi dang ru lu spel zhing mang du bzlas so //
NK022(za)001:16772: h'u tshogs chen 'dus pa dbang gi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK022(za)001:16773: 'bar ba'i bar khyams drug pa mdog dkar nas //
NK022(za)001:16774: khams gsum sgrol ba'i ging chen bco brgyad ni //
NK022(za)001:16775: srid gsum las la thogs med sgrol la brtson //
NK022(za)001:16776: bsgral ba'i zhing bcu gtan nas brlag par byed //
NK022(za)001:16777: ging chen ging lcam tshogs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK022(za)001:16781: h'u tshogs chen 'dus pa dkyil 'khor nas //
NK022(za)001:16782: 'bar ba'i bar khyams bdun pa mdog nag la //
NK022(za)001:16783: bcom ldan h'u mdzad sa gsum brjid kyis gnon //
NK022(za)001:16784: khams gsum 'dul mdzad ye shes lha yi lha //
NK022(za)001:16785: 'jigs byed 'bar bas gdug pa'i tshogs rnams 'joms //
NK022(za)001:16786: khro bo khro mo rnams la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK022(za)001:16788: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK022(za)001:16789: h'u tshogs chen 'dus pa dbang gi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK022(za)001:16790: 'bar ba'i bar khyams brgyad pa phyogs mtshon nas //
NK022(za)001:16791: ye shes thugs rjes phyogs bcur khyab pa yi //
NK022(za)001:16792: gdon bgegs 'dul ba'i las la thogs pa med //
NK022(za)001:16793: ci bgyi bka' nyan las rnams myur mdzad pa'i //
NK022(za)001:16794: phyogs bzhi'i pho nya'i tshogs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK022(za)001:16797: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK022(za)001:16798: ha la ha la pa sha h'u /
NK022(za)001:16799: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK022(za)001:16801: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK022(za)001:16802: pa tsa pa tsa g+han d+ha ho /
NK022(za)001:16804: h'u tshogs chen 'dus pa dbang gi dkyil 'khor gyi //
NK022(za)001:16805: 'bar ba'i bar khyams dgu pa mdog ljang na //
NK022(za)001:16806: stong khams yongs su las la dbang ba yi //
NK022(za)001:16807: ma chen rgyal mo srid pa gsum gyi bdag /
NK022(za)001:16808: yum chen las la dbang ba'i dbang mo che //
NK022(za)001:16809: ma mo drug cu'i tshogs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK022(za)001:16812: h'u tshogs chen 'dus pa dbang gi dkyil 'khor gyi //
NK022(za)001:16813: 'bar ba'i bar khyams bcu pa mdzes mtshon nas //
NK022(za)001:16814: rig 'dzin bla ma byin rlabs ldan pa'i tshogs //
NK022(za)001:16815: lhun grub phyag chen tshe dbang rnam smin gyi //
NK022(za)001:16816: rgya gar bod kyi grub thob bla ma rnams //
NK022(za)001:16817: bskyed rdzogs gsum gyi pi ti 'dir stsol cig /
NK022(za)001:16819: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
